Comment: Waited with, ran on doggedly under pressure to just get up on line.

Began from a poor draw, niggled along to obtain rails position in 6th about 3L off the pace, remained similar turning in, hit the front under pressure 200 metres out only to be collared close to home.
Settled behind midfield on rails, took closer order around home bend, ran on passing the 300 metres but unable to sustain effort 100 metres out.
Broke well, raced keenly within 3L of pace in 5th, remained similar to straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled behind midfield, ran on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Settled in midfield, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped moderately, travelled in last few on rails, did not find much room early in straightening, ran past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Slowly away and remained in last few, switched wide for a run entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Began well, amongst leaders early settling one-out-one-back, lost cover when leader shifted to the rails approaching home bend, joined the lead upon straightening but soon found no extra.
Settled in midfield, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped well and gradually took up running, led the field to the 300 metres, weakened under pressure. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Very slowly away, always well behind.
Broke well but soon restrained for cover on rails, switched off the rails rounding home bend, had nothing to give in the run home.

Driven to vie for the lead early settling just off the speed on the rails, given reminders over 600m out, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance. Blood in trachea, lame next day)
Raced behind the pace until being asked for an effort 400M out. Ran down leader inside 200M and kept on well to line.
Held stand's rail and 3Ls off 600M. Had to go around a weakening runner 250M. Closed off well but unable to draw closer final stages.
Led and being challenged 300M. Overtaken by winner inside 200M. Kept on well for a minor placing.
Raced towards the rear. 4Ls off the lead 400M. Ran on fairly and made up a bit of late ground.
Behind midfield. 3 to 4Ls off the lead at 400M. Ran on without making up ground final stages.
Raced towards the rear. Ran on but unable to make up ground final stages.
Raced keenly near the pace. Dropped out final 300M.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, finished off strongly to score by 1L.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to settle in a prominent position, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on strongly until final 50M weakened.
Eased back to settle midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast sectionals, ran on fairly.
Sent forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
At rear, settled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls off the leader 3 wide without cover, kept on until 250M weakened.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at fast tempo, run ended 250M.
Always at rear, settled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on. (Rider reported the horse's tendency to lay out throughout the race)
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast pace, no turn of foot.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast sectionals, made no impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Failed to muster despite ridden along, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Raced midfield, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Moderate break, mustered to sit close 2nd on rail, rolled to lead 400m, shaken up 350m, kept on determinedly & always in command.
Led from gate, soon headed & trapped 3 wide no cover in 3rd, ridden 430m & progress to 2nd 320m, boxed on in pursuit but always held.
Broke well, sat rail midfield, shifted out home turn, not clear run until switched & shaken up 300m, one-paced & battled to claim 3rd.
Tardy start, pushed forward to race 4th 1 off with cover, under pump on inner 500m, kept on evenly.
Taken back at break, over-raced 3 wide no cover midfield, driven turning in, plugged on dourly.
Taken back from wide, sat rail last pair, ridden at tail 450m, boxed on for minor late headway.
Awkward start, over-raced midfield 1 off with cover, to rail 750m, driven into stretch & shifted out, lacked pace & plodded tamely.
Taken back from wide berth, camped last pair 1 off, taken widest home turn, driven 400m, one-paced.
Slow start widest, slotted 1 off with cover near rear, shifted wide final turn & driven into stretch, one-paced in run to wire.
Moderate break, rolled to narrow lead 1080m, driven turning in & headed under pressure 400m, emptied 350m & wilted tamely.
Rousted from gate, outpaced & taken back to eventually sit rail near rear, over-raced 780m, hard-ridden final turn, struggled in run.
Smart start, settled back in midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, under pump 500m, outpaced & faded in run.
Broke well, raced 3 wide with cover near tail, 4 wide progress from 800m, shaken up 430m, rattled home centre track to lead last stride.
Broke well & prominent, settled 1 back on rail, niggled 600m, under pump 500m, shifted out in stretch, grinding run to lead 100m, headed last stride.
Fair break, edged lead 1300m, 1L clear & to rail 1000m, extended early in stretch, shaken up 300m, soon all out, tapered & headed 100m.
Broke with others, soon restrained to 1 off no cover 3rd, over-raced 1030m, settled 1 off 1 back at 850m, niggled 600m, driven 430m, stayed on dourly.
Smart start to race prominently 3 wide no cover, rolled 1000m to press lead 1 off, driven turning in, outpaced but battled dourly to wire.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, driven 430m, shifted out 400m, boxed on dourly.
Good break, settled back 3 wide with cover midfield, wide turning in & driven 400m, plugged on evenly centre track.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched out & hard-ridden home turn, unbalanced 400m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Lacked early pace & bustled, slotted rail behind midfield, niggled 650m, driven home turn, plugged on evenly.
Taken back from widest gate, soon to rail at tail, off rail & last turning in, driven 400m, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Broke well, soon trapped wide midfield, rapid progress 900m to race wide no cover in 3rd, driven 500m, fading when wandered under pressure 300m.
Tardy start, taken back to race wide with cover at tail, advanced a spot 800m, driven widest home turn, plodded on tepidly.
Fast break, snagged to sit midfield 1 off with cover, hard-ridden turning in, found nothing & weakened in run home.
Broke OK, trapped 5 deep no cover midfield, 4 wide 900m, shaken up 430m, soon struggled & faded out.
Settled behind midfield, not suited by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts to score.
Pressed forward, settled just off the leaders, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Eased back, dashed strongly for 3rd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 300M.
Pressed forward but trapped 3 wide, favoured by the slow sectionals, flattened in straight.
Eased back, checked 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pressed forward to take rail and shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, out of fuel in straight.
Pushed to share lead 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, but soon weakened in straight.
Behind midfield and trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Box seat, held up badly behind weakening runners in straight, not tested.
Very slow away, midfield on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Began well but allowed to drift 3-back from leader in one-off position. Peeled 4-wide entering straight, rolled forward to hit front 200m, gradually pulling away.
One of the first out but eased to sit one-back, one-off. Pressed forward entering straight to look a chance 300m, battled but unable match winner final stages.
Began fairly, hard ridden to hold rail behind leader. Closed in 400m but blocked for run until 200m when checked and switched out. Finished off nicely when clear.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader on settling. Closed in top of straight to look a chance but unable to find extra.
Began OK, gradually taken in from wide draw, dropping to last but still 3-wide entering turn. Widest into straight but closed off well.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail two-back from leader. Closed in top of straight but no run till 300m when switched out. Kept on steadily.
Began fairly, shifted across behind runners from wide draw to find the rail before turn. Checked 800m after which raced keenly. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along but failed to muster dropping to near last at 800m. Found little under the whip in straight.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set steady pace to 200m when collared, kept on one-paced.
Ridden along early but held three-wide behind midfield. Covered extra ground turn and one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold position in midfield but held wide without cover. Wide into straight, faded.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Reared and stayed in box after gates opened. Took no part but ruled a starter.
Soon led, travelled well along the stands' rail, driven out 350M and quickened clear, was strongly challenged by runner up late stages but found the necessary to hold on.
Settled 3Ls behind leader on the outside of field, quickened to go 2nd 300M, lay out under pressure final 200M, pushed winner all the way to the line, nearest finish.
Held up near last towards the outside of the field, stayed on evenly under pressure, went 3rd 100M but made no impression on first two.
Travelled behind midfield 3Ls off the pace, badly held up for clear running until 200M, ran on well when clear, went 4th near 50M.
Began awkwardly, tracked leader in 4th along the stands' rail, kept on steadily passing 400M but unable to match finishing pace of first two, faded to 5th final stages.
In mid-division 2-3Ls off the pace, had difficulty obtaining clear running for some distance inside 400M, stayed on for non-threatening 6th.
Settled 2-3Ls behind leader towards the outer of field, couldn't match finishing pace of leaders passing 400M, kept on same pace to line.
Slow to begin, travelled along the stands' rail in a midfield position, stayed on fairly over final 400M, no significant progress.
At the rear of the field 5Ls behind leaders, kept on same pace when taken out to center of track passing halfway mark, never a serious threat.
Began awkwardly, held up towards the rear but not far off from pace, checked 350M, shifted back to the stands' rail for run, stayed on without threat to leaders.
Always in firing line, failed to pick up under pressure inside 400M, faded passing 250M, steadied close home.
Ridden forward to take up a forward position, off the bridle 500M, lay in under pressure, badly hampered 200M but already a beaten horse.
In touch, came under serious pressure halfway, soon beaten.
Never far off from the pace, driven midway but not quickened, checked 350M and again near 200M, eased towards the line. (Blood in trachea)
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Still last entering straight, switched widest, gradually wore down leaders to win on the line.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide back stretch. Covered extra ground turn, wide into straight, pressed forward gradually overhauling leader but pipped on post.
First out, crossed to rail and set good pace. Tried to kick clear top of straight, holding narrow lead until swamped last stride.
Began awkwardly, crowded for room 1150m, crowded and checked 1000m, dropping three-back in one off position. Blocked for run entering straight but finished nicely when clear 150m.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail behind leader. Looked a chance when rolled forward top of straight but flattened 100m out.
Jumped OK and quickly taken to fence 3-back from leader. Asked for effort soon after straightening and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began well but outpaced and slipped back to near last in one-off position. Switched wide entering straight and kept on fairly.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader. Bumped and unbalanced 500m dropping to third. Weakened gradually in straight.
Pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off but wide without cover from 1000m. Started to give ground soon after straightening for home.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 4th, same position on turn, finished off well in straight to score by a neck.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back in midfield, still there on turn, no clear running until near 200M, finished off strongly thereafter to get 2nd.
Slightly slowly away, recovered, raced a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, took the lead near 200M, but unable to hold off other rivals closing stages.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back behind midfield, similar position turning, finished off well in straight to make frame, just missed 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 8 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Began well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, raced 3wide and without cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position turning, stayed on evenly in straight.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, stayed on evenly until headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail throughout, checked off heels 150M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Slightly slowly away, raced 5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, got head up near 750M, awkwardly placed near 600M, steadied early in straight and got traffic final 100M, not ridden out.
Began well, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced a length back in 2nd, difficult to settle after 900M, still in 2nd on turn, showed no response in straight and dropped off gradually. (Bled from both nostrils)
Moderately away, raced a length or so back in 3rd, easy run on turn, finished off well in straight to score.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in 5th, 2 to 3 lengths back, angled out turning in, closed off well to get 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, still 3 wide turning, finished off very strongly to get 3rd.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, angled out turning in, finished well in straight to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced with cover at rear, 8 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in 4th, 2 lengths back, difficult to settle near 1200M, angled out turning in, made minor progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began with them, raced 2-3 lengths back in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, bumped near 100M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, same position turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently in 2nd, next to the leader, took the lead turning in, but failed to quickened thereafter, and weakened gradually.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 10 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, only passed a few tired runners in straight, never a threat.
Crowded out start, no early speed and raced 8-9 lengths back at rear, similar margin back turning, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and became unbalanced, raced 5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame left front the next day)
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead, headed turning in, emptied early in straight and finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Broke well, settled just off the pace on stands rails, switched in for a run passing the 400 metres, responded well to take command over 100 metres out, won easily.
Settled in midfield near the stands rails racing keenly in middle stages, made steady progress under pressure closing stages. (Blood in trachea)
Soon dropped behind midfield despite ridden along, commenced move coming onto course proper, unable to sustain effort nearing finish.
Towards the rear on stands rails, shifted off the rails halfway out, improving when briefly baulked 100 metres out, ran on.
Settled in last few near the centre of the track after beginning from a low draw, move slightly closer coming onto course proper, failed to quicken under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Driven to lead from a low draw crossing to the stands rails, came under pressure to maintain advantage coming onto course proper, but overhauled close to home.
Not far off in 4th, kept on at the one pace closing stages.
Began from a low draw, worked his way across to join the leader on stands rails, disputed the lead to 200 metres, faded inside final 50 metres.
Jumped moderately, travelled at the back nearer the centre of the track, made modest headway closing stages.
Settled in midfield without cover nearer the centre of the track, yielded ground inside final 200 metres.
Gradually shifted across in forward of midfield without cover after beginning from the worst gate, dropped out tamely inside final 200 metres.
Broke well settling in midfield on stands rails, hung in and a difficult ride from halfway out dropping out. (Lame next day)
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, remained in last few most of way despite coming under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Never a danger.
Raced along the rails at midfield. 2-3Ls down on straightening. Closed off well and ran down early leader final 50M.
Niggled along and took the lead 1200M. Stayed on well after straightening but caught by winner inside final 50M.
Box-seated nicely behind the lead. Kept on well in the straight and held on for a minor placing.
Settled 3-wide at midfield. Improved around the turn and was 3-wide among leaders turning in. Kept on steadily to make the frame.
Caught wide early and was allowed to stride forward. 2-wide behind leaders 1000M out. Held up for some distance after straightening. Switched out for daylight 250m and ran on fairly.
Towards the rear early and middle stages. Rallied and made up ground in the straight.
Niggled along and raced along the rails behind midfield. 3-4Ls off the lead turning in and ran on same pace thereafter.
Midfield early but allowed to stride forward 1400M. Outside leader 800M. Failed to keep pace on straightening and faded out of contention.
Behind the pace early stages. 3Ls off the lead making the turn. Took some time to quicken after straightening. Made up some late ground.
Behind midfield. Towards rear making home turn and made up some ground in the straight.
Trailed field until making a move wide at the turn. Ran on fairly in the straight.
Settled in rear section. Took a wide turn home and ran on only fairly in the straight.
Caught wide without cover midfield. Showed nothing in the home straight.
Settled 2-wide at midfield. Switched out 3-wide to improve 700M. Crowded 300M, dropped off and pulled up lame after race.
Eased back, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, dashed well to score by 1/2L.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly until final 50M headed by the winner.
At rear, settled 6Ls behind the leader, despite trapped 5 wide without cover throughout, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace to the line without any threatening.
Ridden forward as usual, travelled 1L behind the leader 3 wide without cover, one paced until final 100M weakened.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced home.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls off the leader 4 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Taken back, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Rolled forward to share the lead on the fence, hung on until final furlong weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover, under pressure 600M, weakened badly soon after straightening.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, checked 700M, one paced until final 250M flattened badly. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 5.5Ls off the pace 2 wide with cover, never looked likely. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Fast break & rousted to lead 1340m, to rail 1050m & had uncontested lead, shaken up 390m, quickened clear under strong drive, kept on well.
Speed to lead, soon headed & sat 1 back on rail, driven turning in, chased dourly to edge 2nd at 100m & kept on evenly.
Missed break, rolled wide to slot 2nd 1 off no cover at 1000m, shaken up final turn, driven in pursuit but peaked on run 150m & tapered.
Sluggish start, driven along rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off & driven final turn, stayed on for solid headway without threatening.
Good break, raced handy 1 off with cover, driven 430m, 4th & hung in under pressure 250m, boxed on same speed.
Broke well, nudged along to race rail fore of midfield, shifted 1 off & ridden 400m, plugged on evenly.
Taken back from wide, niggled 1 off near rear, shifted 3 wide 800m, driven 500m, kept on for minor inroads.
Tardy start & niggled along, checked 1200m, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven into stretch, kept on evenly.
Missed break & rousted early to settle rail near tail, shifted out & ridden 400m, plugged on one pace.
Missed break, detached & rousted, settled 1 off at tail, edged wide on turn, driven widest into stretch, stayed on moderately centre track.
Tardy start, advanced to settle handy 3 wide no cover at 1000m, driven 450m, shifted & bumped rival 300m, found nothing & faded tamely.
Tardy start & bustled, crowded & bumped 1200m, settled 3 wide with cover midfield, under pump 550m, struggled & faded in stretch.
Fast start wide, snagged back but trapped 4 wide no cover midfield, driven turning in, outpaced & bumped 300m, faded out.
Smart break, taken back gradually to sit near rear 4 wide with cover at 800m, under pump turning in, found nothing & weakened tamely.
Bustled at break & soon at tail, progress home turn, 7L back & driven 400m, stayed on through the field & burst to lead last stride.
Fast start wide & rousted to lead 1150m, trapped 4 wide & edged to 1 off 800m, snagged rail 700m, shaken up & extended 360m, all out 100m & tapered, mugged at wire.
Smart start, bustled to sit handy wide no cover, forced 5 wide & driven home turn, stayed on gradually to snag 3rd at wire.
Sharp start, taken back to midfield but trapped wide, driven 900m & advanced to 2nd 1 off 650m, driven turning in, boxed on, edged out of frame last strides.
Broke well, taken back to midfield 1 off with cover, progress & shifted out 500m, 4 wide turning in, grinding progress to 3rd 200m, edged out of frame last strides.
Tardy start, nudged along 2 deep near rear, driven very wide home turn, stayed on for minor late headway.
Fast start, raced close 3rd 1 off no cover, checked back & 1 off with cover 800m, shifted 3 wide & driven home turn, plugged on evenly.
Smart start & rousted, outpaced & settled rail midfield, hung out & lost ground 600m, hard-ridden into stretch, kept on one pace.
Prominent at break, driven to sit rail fore of midfield, checked 700m, shifted 1 off & driven 450m, ran home evenly.
Snagged back from wide gate to race 3 deep with cover behind midfield, niggled at, under pump & wide into stretch, plodded & faded.
Good break, speed to press lead 3 wide 900m, to rail 800m, squeezed & checked 700m to 1 back 3rd, 4th turning in & hard driven, tapered to wire.
Outpaced early &bustled, scrubbed along on inner near tail, under pump a long way out, last turning in & never a factor.
Slow away, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M amongst horses and scored.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Obtained a more prominent spot than usual, 2Ls off the leader on the rail, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly to the line for 3rd.
Pressed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, led 400M, hung on well until 50M flattened, used up too much fuel to keep up with the fast sectionals.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, ran on very well until 150M flattened.
Pushed early, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 200M.
Settled in midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, but held up most straight and checked 200M, not tested.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, however blocked all straight, not tested.
Eased back, 9Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, made some late ground 200M.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, never progressed.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, reduced quickly 400M.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1L, clocked very fast sectionals, faded rapidly 400M.
Never a factor.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set steady pace, put under pressure and given reminders passing 300m, kept finding to the line.
Shifted out and bumped start, forced wide 950m but with cover. Began forward move entering straight and finished well though failed to overhaul winner.
Out quickly, settling behind leader to straight. Looked a chance 300m when almost drew level but found no extra close home.
Ridden along to hold forward position and race three-wide without cover for most of the trip. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Began well, hidden along to stay with the pace behind leading trio in a one-off position. Put under pressure on straightening but only one-paced.
Taken in from wide draw but held three-wide with cover towards the rear. Made forward move passing 400, wide into straight, kept on fairly.
Began fairly, quickly cut to fence, settling three-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn and kept on one-pace in straight.
Began OK, eased and taken across behind runners to find rail. Dropped to last entering turn, one paced in straight, running past beaten horses final stages.
Hard ridden to go forward but didn't muster and allowed to settle behind midfield in a one-off position. One-paced in straight despite hard riding.
Began fairly, ridden but failed to muster, dropping to rear. Proved difficult to settle and switched out abruptly passing 700m. Found little in straight when asked.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to hold rail. Improved position around turn, looked a chance top of straight but spent force passing 200m.
Ridden along from wide draw, racing 3-wide to turn. Taken wider passing 700m, widest into straight, found nothing under hard riding.
Began well, restrained to sit behind leader, travelled well to straight, smooth headway to lead 200M, drew clear under confident handling.
Driven to take up the lead, unable to hold off winner mid-straight, kept on well for 2nd, well clear form rest.
Bustled along from wide barrier, chased leaders in 3rd, kept on steadily final 400M and not a serious threat to first two.
Settled in midfield along the 2-path, 5Ls off the pace middle stages, driven along 500M out, kept on evenly and not making much progress on leaders.
Held up in midfield, stayed on only fairly turning into straight, no impression on first two.
Travelled in 4th, 5Ls off the pace 400M, ran on same speed final 300M.
Settled behind midfield, lost ground when checked 700M, failed to quicken under pressure.
Towards the rear, well off the pace going into final 400M, made limited progress on straightening.
Outpaced early stages, 2nd last making the turn for home, finished off final quarter fastest, best work late stages.
Behind mid-division, 7Ls off the pace turning for home, not quickened under pressure, weakened final 150M.
Began only fairly, settled towards the rear in 10th, plenty to make up turning home, not picked up under pressure.
Began very awkwardly, failed to muster speed, trailed in last over 10Ls behind leader, didn't respond to riding at any stage.
Began well, rolled forward to sit 1L behind leader in one-off position. Drew level soon after straightening but had to dig deep to hold off runner-up.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting steady pace to 300m when passed momentarily. Fought back along rail but just failed.
Began OK, ridden along 3-wide, 3-back from leader. Had clear running on straightening and kept on steadily under hard riding.
Shifted in and bumped start, ridden along 3-wide before cutting in three-back, one-off at turn. Kept on steadily in straight under hard riding.
Taken in from wide draw, settling last along fence by the turn. Stayed inside on straightening and ran on strongly between horses to just miss the frame. (Inquiry into handling)
Ridden forward from wide draw sitting three-wide in 3rd place around turn. Difficult ride in straight, hanging in badly to 200m when one-paced.
Began well and soon in box seat behind leader. Held ground around turn before turning one paced in straight.
Ridden along but unable hold position, slipping to behind midfield. Raced ungenerously around turn, checked and lost ground, bumped and unbalanced 100m when tiring.
Began fairly, ridden forward settling three-back the fence. Stayed on fence around turn and into straight, not much room to 200m, one-paced final stages.
Jumped OK and gradually taken to fence four-back from leader. Saved ground turn, given several reminders passing 300m but only one-paced.
Jumped with field, eased and shifted across behind runners to settle in one-off position towards rear. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Rolled forward from good draw to settle one-off, one-back before turn. Held position around turn, boxed on fairly in straight until hampered and lost ground 200m.
Shifted in from wide draw to find the rail but towards the rear. Taken out passing 500m, very wide in straight, one-paced.
Switched in behind runners from wide draw but kept in one-off position towards the rear. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored easily.
Jumped well, raced prominently in 2nd, a length or so back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, found cover near 1000M, positioned 3 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, ran home strongly to take 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some ground in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line. (See racing incidents)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 5th, similar position turning, finished off evenly in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Jumped well, raced 1-2 lengths back along the rail in 3rd, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, difficult to settle near 1300M, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Slowly away, taken back to race 5-6 lengths back on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rail and saved ground on turn, but failed to close off in straight.
Began well, difficult to settle early, raced 3 wide without cover in 4th, still 3 wide on turn, weakened early in straight and dropped off gradually. (See racing incidents)
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail throughout, 7-8 lengths back, still last turning in, taken widest in straight and made minor progress, never a threat.
Slow to begin, recovered to race 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 6 lengths back on rail at tail, showed no response to riding in straight, never a threat.

Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Broke well, settled just off the pace on rails, produced for a run after straightening, fought on dourly under pressure to just get up on line.
Soon taken back to last few with rails run, badly baulked for a run until after the 200 metres, finished off race nicely.
Soon taken back to settle in rear of midfield, came to challenge entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Slightly slow out, soon dropped well back, commenced move passing the 400 metres, went widest turning for home, ran on down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately from the middle draw, settled outside the slow-paced leader before taking slender lead on straightening, swamped close to home.
Stumbled at the start losing ground, remained well behind to straight, produced good late impression under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Broke well from the middle draw, gradually moved across to take up running setting a sedate pace, narrowly headed after straightening, fought on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Slightly slow out, settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily under pressure in straight, never nearer.
Given reminders for a prominent position early after beginning from a poor gate, travelled wide without cover in 3rd down far side, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Checked at start, soon recovered to midfield but wide throughout, ran out of room in similar position shortly after straightening, never recovered.
Settled in 5th and just better than midfield, given reminders halfway out, dropped out tamely from the same position after straightening.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, raced wide towards the rear, made no impression in home straight.
Held the rails among the leading trio. Had a slim advantage turning in. Kept on strongly and just managed to hold off a late challenger.
Ridden along the rails at midfield. 2-3Ls off turning for home. Finished strong but no luck in finding a run inside 200M. Just failed to catch winner.
Raced 2-wide among a trio of leaders. 1/2L down into home straight. Stayed on well but unable to find extra to regain advantage final stages.
Outpaced by early leaders. Better than midfield and 3Ls off the lead early stages. Asked to be closer 600M and was right behind leader turning in. Kept on well but unable to draw closer final stages.
Raced 3-wide behind midfield. Closed off well and made up ground in the straight.
Raced behind the leading trio. Ran on fairly in the straight but unable to draw any closer final stages.
2-wide behind midfield. Made a ground saving trip around the turn and kept on fairly in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly and soon trailed field. Remained in last place 200M out but made a late charge home.
Near the pace early stages. Urged to keep up at the rock. 3Ls off the lead making the turn. Ran on and made up a bit of late ground.
Raced 3-wide at midfield. Niggled to keep up at turn. Made up some late ground but encountered traffic final stages.
Raced towards the rear. Did not quicken and maintain same pace to line.
Jumped well from wide draw and urged under the whip to go forward. Raced 3-wide among leaders until dropping out final 200M.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, finished off strongly to score by a neck when clear 200M.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well for 2nd. (Close to the finishing line turned its head and attempted to savage the winner)
Ridden forward to take the lead along the fence, kept on well until final 40M headed by the winner.
Rolled to obtain the box seat, kept on steadily to the line.
Prominent, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on until final 50M weakened.
Midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, unable to find a clear run at any stage in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Taken back from the wide draw, settled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed to take a midfield position, however trapped wide without cover throughout, never ran on.
Ridden forward to race outside the leader, kept on one pace until 200M flattened badly.
Jumped slowly, at rear throughout, never looked competitive.
Tardy start but rolled to 1 off 1 back, driven 3 wide home turn, quickened to lead 120m, kept on to wire.
Broke well & bustled to sit 1L 2nd outside lead, driven to lead 310m, soon all out & headed 120m, battled to hold 2nd.
Taken back to camp 1 off near rear, strong traveller, shaken up for progress 400m, switched out 300m & driven, crowded & unbalanced in stretch run but battled to nick 3rd.
Tardy start, posted 1 off with cover midfield, raced keenly, shifted out & ridden 400m, 4 wide home turn, battled to 3rd 130m, edged out of frame last stride.
Good break, camped 1 back on rail, under pump 400m, shifted out & hard driven 300m, boxed on evenly.
Snagged at start to sit 1 off in rear, hard-ridden home turn & shifted out, stayed on for minor late headway.
Broke OK, sat rail midfield, under pump 700m, plugged on one pace.
Sharp start to lead & soon crossed to snag rail, niggled 550m, pushed along under pressure turning, headed 310m & tapered.
Snagged to race 3 wide midfield, checked 1200m & shuffled to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, hard-ridden turning in, plodded home.
Slow start, raced rail in rear, niggled 650m, hard-ridden turning in, found nothing & wilted.
Broke well & ridden, caught wide no cover 1st turn, eased back to 3 wide in rear, clear last & ridden 400m, struggled in run home.
Broke well, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, niggled along 600m, driven widest home turn & faded tamely.
Speed to lead, soon to rail & set tempo, driven 400m, unable to shake off pursuers but battled grimly to hold on under pressure.
Moderate start, unable to slot & raced 3 wide no cover midfield, advanced 900m to sit outside leader 800m, driven 500m in close pursuit, closed gradually but just missed.
Broke well, sat 1 off with cover midfield, shifted 3 deep & advanced a spot 850m, driven wide on turn, stayed on to 3rd 200m, closed to wire.
Broke well & bustled initially, sat 1 off fore of midfield, shuffled back & checked off heels 520m, lost ground, shaken up 300m, closed off soundly.
Fast start, parked close-up 1 off no cover, shuffled to 1 back 800m, 4th & ridden 400m, shifted out & boxed on evenly.
Restrained from wide gate to 1 off near tail, ridden 3 wide 500m, stayed on one pace.
Fair break to sit rail midfield, shuffled back behind midfield 850m & niggled, checked 500m, driven 450m, stayed on one pace.
Moderate start, raced 3 wide at rear, minor progress 800m, ridden wide 600m, kept on same speed.
Crowded start, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, rolled 900m to fore of midfield, wide progress & under pump in 3rd final turn, wilted in run.
Broke OK, taken back to sit 3 wide with cover near rear, advanced 850m to midfield 4 wide no cover, ridden 480m & widest turning in, struggled in run.
Taken back to rail & raced near rear, shuffled to tail 800m & niggled, driven 460m, plodded on one pace.
Broke OK, raced 1 back on rail, over-raced 1250m, under pump 400m & soon under pressure, emptied 200m & faded.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the lead 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader along the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Slow away, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M flattened.
Slow away, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, just held ground.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash in straight.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Ridden early to hold rail behind leader. Stayed on rail around turn, took inside run in straight, urged forward to lead 150m, challenged but held.
Began well, pushed forward settling one-off, one back. A little wide into straight, challenged strongly from 150m, just failed.
Began fairly, not much speed and taken to fence four-back from leader. Switched out 500m, wide into straight, ran on strongly.
Began OK, no pace, shifted across behind horses and last into turn. Urged forward passing 500m, widest into straight, finished off nicely.
Jumped fairly, settling three-back along the rail. A little flat-footed passing 500m, picked up, three-wide into straight, kept on steadily in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling in last pair along rail. Took inside run entering straight, forced to switch in 100m, kept on fairly.
Pushed forward but caught 3-wide without cover. Allowed to stride forward to lead passing 500m. Led to 150m when caught but kept on well till flattened 50m.
Began well, not much speed, settling towards rear in a 3-wide position with cover. Taken very wide entering straight and boxed on one-paced.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting slow pace till challenged and passed 500m, kept on steadily in straight until crowded for room 180m.
Jumped well, ridden forward but held 3-wide in second tier behind leader. Under pressure from 500m but only one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden early to sit outside leader to turn. Shuffled back to 3rd passing 500m, gave ground gradually in straight.
Began fairly, pressed forward between horses three-back from leader. Put under pressure from 500m but found little and gradually slipped back.
Strolled forward, crossed to the lead passing 1200M and set a steady pace, continued on well when ridden out 300M and always holding off pursuers.
Moved forward, tracked the pace from 1200M, chased winner in straight but always held.
Soon taken across behind runners, settled near rear 7Ls off the pace, had some work to do turning in, stayed on well down inside, nearest finish.
Reared at the start and slowly away, reserved in last over 8Ls behind leader, switched wide 400M, ran on well for 4th, never nearer.
Travelled in 4th 2-3Ls off the pace, had every hope turning in, stayed on evenly for close 5th.
Caught 3-wide early then strolled to a 2-wide spot chasing leader, kept on under pressure in straight, faded final stages only.
Dropped in behind mid-division, travelled along the 2-path, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on over final 300M but only slowly getting to leaders.
Settled in midfield, driven out 350M, stayed on under pressure but lacked the extra.
Up with early pace, sat back to race in midfield, remained on the inner throughout, kept on without threatening over final 300M.
Settled towards the rear about 7Ls off the pace, shaken up passing 500M, stayed on fairly, never a serious threat.
Held up towards the rear, starting to gather momentum inside 250M but had no clear run final 150M, not properly tested.
Settled in mid-division, saved ground on the inner, 4-5Ls behind leader turning for home, failed to pick up when driven, soon beaten.

Hard ridden but only found himself in midfield far side, kept on at the same pace before quickening inside final 200 metres to just get up on line.
Never far off after beginning from a poor draw, caught very wide far side and 3-wide home bend, ran on steadily under pressure but outsprinted close to home.
Ridden positively from a wide draw to gain narrow advantage early stages, disputed the lead around home bend before taking over inside the 200 metres, but only to be headed final strides.
Niggled along from the middle gate to get up with the pace eventually gaining narrow advantage around the bend, headed about 200 metres out, swamped for a placing close to home.
Ridden early but failed to muster travelling behind midfield to home straight, produced good impression after straightening making up good ground, jockey charged for failing to ride the horse out.
Jumped fairly, soon picked up along rails to join the leading group about one to two off the pace, slightly worse entering straight, soon found nothing.
Settled in last few from the widest gate, ran on past well-beaten horses in the straight.
Began moderately, trailed the field to straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Driven to reach a prominent position 800 metres out, dropped out from 5th into straight.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Broke well, niggling along in a prominent position when crowded for room at about 800 metres, carried wide around the bend, never recovered in straight.
Jumped moderately, prominent in far side before hanging out badly around the bend, dropped out of contention from approaching home straight. (Blood in trachea)
Settled on fence at midfield. Responded well when asked turning in and ran down rivals inside final 100M for the win.
Raced along the rails behind leader. 3Ls off turning in. Ran on well and caught early leader inside 100M but unable to hold off the winner at the same time.
Soon led. Opened up a 3Ls advantage turning for home but headed by top pair inside final 100M. Found enough to keep a minor placing.
Raced along the rails in rear section. Ran on nicely in the straight but never a threat.
Settled towards the rear. Got galloped on 900M out. Remained near the back turning for home but closed the race off nicely and made up ground in the straight.
Jumped well but restrained to settle 3-wide behind midfield. Widest turning for home. Made up ground over tired runners.
Behind midfield. Clipped heels and stumbled badly after 500M. Last into the straight and made up some late ground.
Better than midfield and kept within 3Ls of the pace. Unable to quicken in the straight.
Hard ridden early to take up a midfield spot. Urged to keep up 500M and unable to find more in the straight.
Niggled along to go forward from wide draw. Wide into 1st turn and raced behind the pace back straight. Pressured to keep pace 600M and dropped out soon after straightening.
Settled at the rear until home straight. Made no impression in the thereafter.
No worse than midfield but out wide facing the breeze. Heavy pressure rounding home turn and weakened in the straight.

Placing: UR
Comment: Sat down when gates opened and came out riderless.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on strongly to the line, just held on by a head.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, closed off strongly for 2nd, missed by a head.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led as usual, hung on strongly until final 50M headed by the winner.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on steadily to the line.
Pushed to midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Eased back to rear, settled 7.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in and showed some dash in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Taken back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 -3 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Sent forward to occupy the box seat, kept on until final 150M flattened.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Showed some early pace to settle in a prominent position, however weakened rounding the Home Turn.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward to race outside the leader, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Good start, sat handy 1 off with cover, shifted out 350m & driven, quickened to lead 190m, drew clear for smooth win.
Fast break, raced 2nd 1 off no cover, driven 400m & closed to press lead, no match for winner, kept on.
Broke OK, bustled along 3 wide with cover behind midfield, shaken up 430m & shifted wider, closed off for solid gains to take 3rd 50m out.
Sharp start, sat 1 back on rail, ridden turning in, outpaced but kept on evenly under strong drive.
Lacked pace at break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, trapped in pocket 400m, switched out for clear run 310m, stayed on evenly.
Broke OK but outpaced & rousted initially, settled midfield 1 off with cover, driven 400m, plugged on one pace.
Taken back from wide to 1 off near rear, over-raced 900m, driven 400m, switched inside, stopped in run 220m & again 120m, clear & driven 100m, ran on.
Taken back to last pair from wide gate, rolled on rail to sit behind midfield, ridden 400m, boxed on steadily.
Speed to lead, to rail 1000m, shaken up 340m, soon under pressure & pressed, headed 190m, faded tamely.
Dropped back from wide gate to 3 wide with cover near rear, driven 400m, lacked pace but plugged on.
Missed start & rousted at tail, 1L detached & driven turning in, ran home tepidly to pass fading rivals.
Quick break, sat handy 3 wide no cover, driven 400, emptied 300m & weakened tamely.
Fair start, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden 400m, struggled & weakened out.
Missed break, recovered to race midfield on rail, driven 400m, found nothing & faded tamely.
Broke OK, camped rail midfield, shuffled back 700m & at tail turning in, shaken up 420m, progress & shifted 1 off 300m, back to rail 230m, rattled to lead 120m.
Fast start to lead 1 off, headed 1040m & sat 1 back on rail, ridden 520m, outpaced home turn, shifted out 420m, closed off dourly to 2nd 50m.
Tardy break, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, pushed 4 wide no cover 700m, driven 430m, battled to 2nd 300m, brief lead 150m, no extra & tapered.
Missed break & rousted to midfield, rolled 3 wide to lead 600m, shifted in final turn, all out 400m & headed 360m, boxed on dourly.
Good break & prominent early, taken back to midfield 1 off with cover, edged 3 wide 700m, driven & shifted out 400m, boxed on evenly to wire.
Fair break, raced 1 off behind midfield, driven 450m & shifted out, plugged on one pace for minor late headway.
Taken back, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven 530m, fought on centre track for gradual inroads until tapered final strides.
Snagged back from wide gate to sit 3 deep last trio, pushed 4 wide 680m, widest turning in & driven, closed off for minor inroads centre track.
Taken back from wide gate to last trio 1 off, forced 3 deep 680m, ridden 420m, ran on centre track for minor gains.
Speed to vie for initial lead, snagged to sit handy 1 off, switched 3 deep turning in, driven to lead 360m, emptied & headed 150m, quickly faded.
Taken back from widest gate, sat 4 wide no cover behind midfield, smooth traveller final turn, shaken up 400mbut found little, emptied 180m & faded.
Dropped in from wide to race rail behind midfield, over-raced 900m & settled last trio, shifted 1 off 680m, fanned out home turn & driven 420m, struggled in run.
Fast start, rousted to push on & lead 1040m, to rail 850m, headed 600m, driven under pressure final turn, weakened tamely & eased.
Sharp start, raced rail 2L back in mid pack, outpaced & lost ground 700m, rolled off rail & driven 420m, found nothing.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 400M to score.
Eased to rear, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 400M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 3 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pressed forward, 2.5L off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, made early move 600M around the field, ran on strongly until 200M run ended.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, held up 4-2, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground when clear.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1L at slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 350m.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout, not suited by the slow tempo, emptied 400M.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, reduced quickly 300M.
Eased back, never competitive, tailed out.
Driven forward to lead on settling, crossing to rail 750m. Under strong challenge from 400m but kept lifting to score easily.
Ridden out early to hold rail inside leader before being crossed 750m. Came off fence 600m, threw out strong challenge from 400m, unable to close gap.
Shifted out and bumped start, taken to fence three back from leader. Came off fence on straightening and ran on steadily to snatch third.
Began OK, shifted in behind runners, settling three-back one off to straight. Had open run on straightening and kept on fairly.
Began fairly, ridden to take forward position, settling in box seat around turn. Kept on steadily in straight until finding no extra final 50m.
Ridden along between horses settling one-out, one-back. Had opening running on straightening but only one-paced under hard riding.
Began OK, no speed, dropping to last but kept three-wide with cover. Widest into straight, given reminders but found nothing.
Began only fairly but mustered quickly, racing three-wide without cover outside leading pair. Given reminders on entering straight but weakened gradually,
Pushed forward from wide draw, racing three-wide with cover towards the rear. Very wide entering straight but found nothing and faded gradually.
In touch behind leaders, travelled smoothly and loomed a big threat passing halfway, quickened to lead 300M under hands and heels riding, lengthened away for an impressive debut victory.
Never far off within 2.5Ls from leader, finished with a steady bid to go 2nd nearing 50M but unable to make ground on the runaway winner.

Sprinted clear passing 800M from a middle barrier, clipped along the stand's rail at a steady tempo, could not hold off impressive winner near 300M, kept on steadily to the line, lost 2nd nearing 50M.
Allowed to settle just off the pace, driven 400M and mustered up a mild response only, faded late stages. (Jockey stated his mount felt flat)
Took up rearward position after the start, was patiently ridden, stayed on moderately over final 400M, not reached leaders but fine effort having been off the track for 10 months.
Within striking distance 2-3Ls behind leader, kept on same pace when driven passing 400M, not reached contention.
Towards the stands' rail and always close up, driven 400M but not pace to challenge, lacked further response passing 200M.
Tracked leader, off the bridle passing halfway mark and came under serious pressure, gave ground 300M.
Taken across behind runners, near the rear 5Ls behind leaders, made limited progress over final 300M.
Dropped back to a rearward position about 5Ls off the pace, shaken up midway but lacked the necessary response, never threatened.
Towards the rear and had to be niggled along to keep up with the group, brief effort passing 400M, soon no extra and weakened.
Raced off the pacesetters along the Stands' rail, outdashed 450M, faded towards the finish.
Checked on jumping, shifted back to stands' side racing towards the rear, was slowly making ground along the rail but had to shift ground 200M, not reached leaders.
Void of early speed, settled at the rear, not picked up under pressure 500M, dropped away.
Ridden to hold the rail three-back from leader. Not much room top of straight but found gap 250m and powered though to win drawing clear.
Given early reminders to go forward, settling one-out, one-back. Battled on under hard riding in straight to hold second.
Used up from wide draw to get outside leader by 1100m. Lay out turn, rolled forward top of straight to look chance 300m. Kept on steadily.
Pressed forward from wide draw, cutting to fence 1300m. Saved ground turn, came off fence 400m, led 300m, flattened 50m.
Jumped OK, not pushed, allowed to settle towards rear in one-off position. Taken out turn, found gap between horses 300m and finished off nicely.
Outpaced, drifting back to be clear last passing 1300m. Cut to rail before turn, held for clear running top of straight, finished off well when clear 200m.
Ridden along early to hold position three-back, one-off. Not pushed turn, blocked for running top of straight and again at 200m and 150m. Checked from heels 100m, not properly tested.
Ridden to obtain forward position but unable to cross and held 3-wide without cover from 1400m. Wide into straight but only one-paced.
Shifted out and bumped start, ridden along to hold midfield position but 3-wide mostly. Wide into straight, kept on one-paced.
Began OK, not pushed, settling 4-back the rail. Given a couple of reminders early in straight but only one-paced.
Jumped with field but proved hard to settle and caught 4-wide entering turn. Widest into straight, one-paced.
Began awkwardly, then held between horses at the rear. Three-wide around turn, taken wider entering straight, one-paced.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, crossing to rail 1250m. Set decent pace to 250m when collared and faded.
Ridden along early but unable to find cover and trapped 4-wide, mostly without cover. Improved position around turn, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead easily, enjoyed the easy lead turning, showed good turn of foot to kick clear 300M, safely held rivals to score comfortably.

Slightly slow out, raced 4-5 lengths back at rear, severely checked near 900M, difficult to regain balance on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to get 2nd. (See racing incidents)
Jumped well, raced 2 lengths or so back in midfield, 2 wide turning, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear final 150M to get 3rd.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race a length back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Fast into stride, raced prominently in 2nd, same position on turn, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from gate 10, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 1-2 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked on run near 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.

Moderately away, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced 4 lengths or so back at rear, checked near 1200M, failed to settle on turn, positioned 3 to 4 wide at rear, finished off evenly in straight. (See racing incidents)
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail behind midfield, crowded for room near 1200M, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4-5 wide in the early stages, 4 wide with cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out from a wide draw, raced 4 lengths back at rear, 2 wide turning, no clear running until near 150M, make minor progress thereafter.

Jumped with them, raced 3 lengths back in midfield, 2-3 wide with cover, bumped near 900M, still 2 wide turning, no clear running early in straight and steadied near 200M, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 lengths back in midfield, difficult to settle near 1000M, 3 to 4 wide with no cover on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Checked start, raced 5 lengths or so back at tail, carried out on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Slightly slow out, raced 4-5 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle near 1100M, still 5 lengths back turning, was a beaten horse early in straight, never competitive.

Settled in rear of midfield, responded well to assert authority over 100 metres out.
Began well settling in joint 4th just better than midfield, ran on steadily without threatening.
Waited with, did not find much room early in straight, ran on inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well from the one draw settling on rails in midfield, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from the middle gate to travel just worse than midfield, shaken up entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Broke well settling in joint 4th on the rails and just better than midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon amongst leaders after beginning from a wide gate, settled in 2L 3rd on rails, came under pressure upon straightening, faded inside final 200 metres.
Towards the rear, went wide into straight, fought on steadily under pressure.
In similar position throughout.
Very slowly away, tailed off most of the way to straight, went past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Led the field to the 200 metres, folded up quickly.
Jumped fairly, moved up gradually to settle outside the leader, dropped out under pressure soon after straightening.
Nicely box-seated behind the pace. Quickened when asked on straightening and ran down early leader 200M. Kept on well and never threatened final stages.
Raced along the rails at midfield. 2Ls off turning for home and kept on well in the straight.
Soon in the lead. Set a comfortable pace all the way until being challenged turning in. Headed 200M and managed to hang on for a minor placing.
Contested for the early lead but caught wide 1st turn. Raced just off the pace but 3-wide no cover until straightening. Kept on well to make the frame.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield. Rallied in the straight and closed off well.
Raced among early leaders before settling behind the pace 800M. Kept on well after straightening and not much room to improve 200M out. Faded final stages.
Eased back from wide draw and settled in rear section. 3-wide making home turn and steadily made up ground in the straight.
Stood flat-footed when gates opened and lost a lot of ground. Caught up with field 600M and was last to turn for home. Made up ground over beaten runners.
Best out and allowed to settle at midfield. Ridden along to keep up making the turn at 500M. Ran on without quickening in the straight.
Niggled forward from wide draw. Raced outside the lead until straightening. Faded final 250M.
3-wide and no better than midfield. Pressured home turn but lacked a response. Stayed same pace in the straight.
Bad jump and raced towards the rear. Near last to turn in and weakened shortly after.
Camped handy, despite trapped 3 wide without cover from 800M, ran on strongly to score by a neck.
Taken back from wide gate, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow pace, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, gradually improved mid-stages, kept on steadily to the line.
Settled worse than midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, ran on gradually.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, checked 500M, closed off well over the concluding stages.
Jumped slowly, then settled at rear about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow tempo, ran on well.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on until final 100M weakened.
Pushed to settle in midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, one paced home.
Always at rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow pace, made some ground until final 50M checked.
Sent forward to race outside the leader, despite benefited by the slow sectionals, weakened over the last furlong.
Prominent early, however, reluctant to maintain its position from 800M, never looked likely thereafter.
Broke well, settled 1 off 1 back, bustled up 450m, fanned out & driven in 3rd turning in, quickened to lead 50m, held on.
Missed break, detached until tagged on 1050m, angled out & bustled for 4 wide progress 650m, hard-ridden 440m, very wide home turn, rattled centre track to nick 2nd.
Dropped in from wide gate, parked 3 wide near tail, shifted 4 deep 670m & advanced, driven very wide home turn, closed to 3rd 100m, kept on to wire.
Speed to lead, dictated tempo & wound it up exiting backstretch, shaken up 400m & kicked 1L clear, tapered & headed 50m, no extra.
Sharp start, snagged to 3 wide with cover midfield, travelled well & edged wide home turn, shaken up 300m, kept on without threatening.
Taken behind from widest gate to near tail on inner, under pump 440m, stayed on for minor gains.
Broke well, trapped 4 wide no cover midfield until dropped to rear 1000m, ridden at tail 550m, fanned widest into stretch, closed steadily for solid inroads.
Fast start, rolled to sit handy 2nd 1off no cover, niggled 550m, hard-driven 400m, boxed on in pursuit until emptied 200m & tapered.
Slow start, outpaced & bustled early, on fence midfield & squeezed up 1400m, shifted out final turn & driven, plugged on moderately.
Good start, taken back to midfield 1 off with cover, driven under pressure 450m, plodded on tepidly & eased late.
Moderate break, bustled to post handy 3 wide no cover, nudged along 550m, hard-ridden & drifted wide home turn, weakened tamely in stretch.
Awkward break, bustled to settle 1 back on rail, niggled 650m, under pump & fading 450m, no extra in stretch & wilted.
Sharp start, trapped 3 wide with cover midfield, shuffled toward rear 700m, began move 400m, shaken up turning in, shifted out 200m, rattled to lead 100m, drew clear.
Good break, led 1 off 1470m, worked to rail 1100m, steady tempo & headed 770m, bustled to regain lead 540m, driven 300m & pressed, headed 100m, boxed on.
Steadied start, at tail & shifted out 900m for 4 wide advance to 3rd 700m, driven 300m to vie for lead, hung in 200m, tapered to wire.
Fast break, raced 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 750m, under pump turning in, boxing on when bumped 200m, stayed on.
Speed to lead, soon headed & settled 1 back on rail, bustled 750m, travelled final turn, shaken up 300m & kept on evenly.
Tardy start, sat rail near rear, to tail 900m, niggled 700m, minor progress on turn, driven into stretch & shifted out, stayed on moderately.
Broke well, bustled to sit 2nd 1 off with cover, niggled 750m & shuffled to midfield, shifted 3 deep & ridden 500m, wide into stretch, plodded one pace.
Sluggish start, raced rail midfield, shuffled back 850m, niggled 700m & some progress, edged out 300m & driven, badly checked 200m, plugged on.
Missed break, raced at rear until 900m when rapid wide progress to lead 1 off 770m, headed 540m, driven 300m & emptied, faded & impeded 200m.
Moderate start, raced 1 off behind midfield, to last pair 850m, to tail 500m, ridden turning in, plodded on tamely.
Broke OK, caught 4 wide midfield, rolled to 3 wide no cover 4th 900m, shuffled back & bustled 700m, very wide into stretch, found nothing.
Hard ridden forward, enjoyed the slow sectionals just off the leader 2 wide, closed off strongly to win just by narrow margin.
Pushed to keep up in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace, just missed.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung in 300M, ran on until 150M overhauled, just hold on for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Eased for box seat just off the slow pace, blocked most straight and checked 200M, not tested.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, lack room in straight, dashed well to the line despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, made the turn awkwardly, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, held up most straight, little dash.
Pushed early but not muster, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok final stages.
Slow away, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Ridden along early to hold forward position, settling one-out, one-back. Shaken up 300m, rolled forward to hit front 150m, raced tight concluding stages, just held.
First out, set up big lead middle stages, caught 150m, bumped and unbalanced 100m, but kept battling to the line.
Hampered start, dropping back. Mustered along rail to sit three-back from leader 800m. Got rails run in straight and ran on strongly to just fail.
Began well, hard ridden to hold rail but raced keenly when crossed 1000m, taking box seat. Looked chance top of straight but unable match top three in run to the line.
Bumped start, dropped back when crowded for room, crossing to rail four back from leader. Got inside run in straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Began fairly, ridden along behind midfield but mostly three-wide. Swung wide into straight and kept on one-paced. Raced tight final stages.
Jumped OK, ridden along between horses initially before settling three-wide at the rear. Switched 4-wide around turn, widest into straight, one-paced.
Bumped start, ridden forward, settling one-off, two back. Rolled forward approaching straight to look chance but effort was short-lived. One-paced.
Little slow into stride, taken in from wide draw to settle in one-off position towards rear. Raced keenly passing 1000m, improved position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Given early reminders, ridden forward, settling three-wide outside leader without cover. Lost position around turn and faded gradually.
Restrained soon after start and taken in from wide draw, settling in one-off position at the rear. Raced fiercely approaching 800m, unbalanced 450m, one-paced straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Improved position around turn, kept on early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Began well, restrained in midfield about 3Ls behind leaders, quickened up well inside 250M and swept to the front 150M, kept on strongly towards finish.
Taken across behind runners from draw 12, settled near last 6Ls off the pace, took inside route in straight and closed willingly, pressed winner late.
Held up towards the rear 5-6Ls back, moved out to the 3-path 800M, fanned wide into straight, hung inwards under pressure, ran on well to go 3rd 50M, not reached first two.
Caught 3-wide early stages, moved up to chase leader, kept on over final 300M but couldn't match the acceleration of first two, lost 3rd near line.
Switched off to last and given a patient ride, 7Ls to make up 400M, taken widest off the bend, ran on moderately.
Sluggish start, improved along the inside to settle in midfield about 3Ls off the pace, hampered 300M, stayed on mildly towards finish.
Enjoyed uncontested lead early stages, pressed by rival from 1000M, headed nearing 150M, flattened out final stages.
Soon guided across to the fence, settled behind midfield 4-5Ls back, angled out 350M but made limited progress only.
Settled just off the pace inside, saved ground throughout but failed to muster a closing response turning home, out of contention 200M.
Slowly away, settled 4-5Ls back behind mid-division, hampered 200M, ran on without threat over final stages.
Tracked leader early, remained close up to straight, shifted out 400M, didn't respond to riding and soon beaten. (Blood in trachea).
Caught 3-deep and raced without cover after 1100M, strolled forward to join leaders passing 900M, lacked further response 250M, weakened to last.
