Jumped well, made all.
Jumped awkwardly, soon picked up to travel outside the leader, fought on dourly in straight but unable to peg back the winner throughout.
Well there, hampered entering straight, kept on behind runners early on, unable to quicken under pressure closing stages.
Began awkwardly, travelled towards the rear on rails, badly baulked for a run after straightening, finished off race well inside final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield, held up for a run in straight until 250 metres out, kept on well in closing stages.
Jumped moderately and raced wide throughout, settled in last few early, made headway around the bend, ran on steadily under pressure in straight.
Wide in midfield far side, improved to join the leaders rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Failed to muster early stages, travelling in midfield on rails before checked about 800 metres out, did not find much room after entering straight, kept on same pace under pressure.
Broke well, settled in midfield, hampered and lost position coming out of back straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to the last, trailed the field to straight, kept on steadily under pressure past well-beaten horses.
Broke well from a poor draw, raced wide in forward of midfield, hampered approaching home straight, dropped out tamely.
Raced wide in last few from a wide draw, circled the field rounding home bend, hung out badly approaching home straight, never recovered. (Tongue over bit)
Never a danger.
Jumped moderately, soon picked along rails, saved ground entering straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Raced within 2 to 3Ls of the leader. Never got a clear run from 400M to 200M. Charged past others once finding daylight and won with ease.
Raced 2-3Ls off the lead. Responded well ran down early leader 100M out. Failed to hold off a late challenger.
Ridden along and kept within 3 to 4Ls of the pace. Ran on fairly closing stages but unable to find extra gear.
Soon in the lead. Held advantage until being headed final 100M. Just held on to make the frame. (Bled)
Raced at midfield. 3Ls off at 400M. Kept on fairly but unable to turn up a notch closing stages.
Raced along the outside fence at midfield. 4Ls off at 400M but badly held up over final 200M and never got a shot.
Kept within 2Ls of the leader until final 200M. Unable to find extra over the concluding stages to remain in contention.
Raced behind the pace till 300M. Unable to keep up and faded thereafter.
Slow out and was ridden along. Checked 800M out and raced behind midfield. 5 to 6Ls off at 400M and unable to quicken final stages.
Raced behind the lead. Beginning to lose touch 200M. Took a bad check 150M out and unable to recover.
Raced greenly in rear section. Ran on same pace and caught in traffic final stages.
In rear section throughout. Little response under the stick halfway point. Only ran past beaten runners final stages.
Niggled along but didn't find much speed. Rear section halfway point and found nothing in the final stages.
Raced mostly towards the rear. Unable to quicken when asked and finished last.
Sent forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by a neck.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly for 2nd, just missed by a neck.
Raced midfield, settled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Rolled forward to settle 1L outside the leader, despite suited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace only to the line.
Eased back to rear, settled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow sectionals, dashed well.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, despite benefited by the slow pace, kept on until final 100M weakened.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dropped off 200M. (Bled)
Speed to lead, headed 1180m & settled 2L 2nd 1 off no cover, nudged along on turn, driven to close 350m, gradual progress to lead 75m & edged clear.
Broke ok, taken back to sit 3 wide with cover behind midfield, ridden 450m & shifted out turning in, closed off centre track to nick 2nd.
Good start, raced 1 back on rail, driven 400m, switched out 270m, kept on dourly.
Sharp start widest, bustled to lead 1180m, 2L clear & to rail 1000m, driven 350m, battled on but headed 75m & tapered.
Moderate start, raced 1 off behind midfield, checked & back to near tail 950m, shifted out turning in, not clear run in stretch, driven 220m, kept on for late inroads.
Snagged back to rail near tail, ridden turning in, closed off gradually down inner without threatening.
Outpaced & rousted early, advanced on rail to sit fore of midfield, over-raced 850m, shaken up & shifted out final turn, boxed on evenly.
Broke well & raced handy but caught 3 wide no cover, ridden turning in, boxed on until weakened out final 150m.
Slow start & settled wide with cover near tail, under pump 500m, plugged on evenly.
Broke well & rousted to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, driven 430m, plugged one pace, checked off heels 70m.
Slow start, to rail & advanced to sit midfield at 850m, driven 400m & shifted out, kept on one pace.
Tardy break & raced at tail, shifted widest into stretch & driven 430m, drifted in 150m, never a factor.
Broke well & sat 3 deep with cover midfield, ridden 500m, found little in tepid run to wire.
Smart start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, not clear run at any point in stretch, untested at wire.
Sharp start, raced 3rd 1 off with cover, edged 3 deep 620m, nudged to advance 500m, driven 400m & led 300m, shifted in but drew clear, tapered late & just held on.
Slow break, sat back in field 1 off with cover, 5L back & shaken up 400m, stopped in run 260m, driven through gap 200m, rattled to 2nd 50m & closed hard to wire.
Good break & bustled to 2nd 1 off ridden to press lead 430m, outpaced & battled on determinedly for 3rd.
Broke OK, taken back & raced 4 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide & driven final turn, stayed on without threatening.
Speed to lead from wide gate, to rail 1330m & 2.5L clear, joined turning in, pressed & shaken up 350m, headed 300m, all out & wilted in run to wire.
Broke well, sat 4th on rail, shifted out turning in, not clear run & switched 250m, raced in close quarters & kept on same speed.
Missed start & taken to rail at tail, shifted wide final turn, stayed on centre track for minor headway.
Outpaced at start, raced last trio, shifted out & driven 430m, kept on for minor late inroads.
Broke well, sat midfield 1 off with cover, handy & shaken up 400m, outpaced & plugged on evenly.
Moderate start, niggled at early, raced 3 deep with cover behind midfield, driven 500m, kept on one pace.
Tardy start & bustled to settle rail midfield, driven 550m, outpaced & plodded home.
Slow start & camped near tail on outer, ridden 520m, plodded home tamely.
Sharp start, snagged back & caught 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, ridden 500m, bottomed out 300m & weakened tamely.
Missed break & near rear, rolled 4 wide no cover to sit midfield, wide advance on turn & driven 530m, emptied 400m & faded weakly.
Pushed forward to hold a prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace on the rails, lack room 4-2, closed off strongly when clear, just missed by a neck.
Eased back, 8Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in final stages.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at good sectionals, hung on until 200M flattened.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, made steady ground 300M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the good pace on the fence, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 8Ls off the good pace, switched 3 wide on straightening to make ground, one paced until 200M to progress.
Very slow away, 6Ls off the good pace along the fence, lack room 300M, made minor ground when clear, looking for further.
Very slow away, at back, 5.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, made early move 800M, flattened 300M.
Pushed early, settled in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, reduced quickly 350M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, race keenly, no progress in straight.
Eased back, never a factor.
Began well, not pushed, settling behind midfield but 3-wide. Switched 4-wide around turn while rolling forward. Hit front 350m, switching in abruptly, before pulling cleat.
Ridden along but didn't muster and then shifted across behind horses to be last before turn. Taken out turning for home and finished strongly but no match for winner.
Fractious in gate, removed, reloaded. Began well, sitting behind pacemakers. Caught flat-footed before turn, recovered and ran on strongly in straight.
Not pushed, settling towards rear but three-wide. Lost position turn, dropping to near last. Blocked for run early in straight but finished off nicely when clear.
Began OK, taken closer to rail, settling four-back from leader. Improved position turn, but blocked for run until passing 200m. Finished off well.
Ridden along to obtain forward position but held three and four wide. Took closer order turning for home but spent force from 300m. One-paced.
First into stride before easing into box seat behind leader. Steadied and lost ground 800m when outside runner crossed. Steadied from heels 300m, switched out 250m, kept on fairly.
Ridden along early, holding rail position three back from leader. Popped off the fence around turn and lost position. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw but still held three-wide at the rear. Very wide into straight, made up some ground initially before turning one-paced.
Crowded start, ridden along, settling four-back, one-off. Crowded and lost position 500m, kept shifting out to find run in straight but only one-paced.

Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in one-off position at the rear. Stayed close to rail around turn, unable get clear run in straight despite shifting out several times, not properly tested.
Bumped start, ridden to take forward position, unable to find cover and pressed ahead to lead before turn. Caught 400m but kept on to 100m when flattened.
Bumped heavily start, ridden along to maintain forward position and caught three-wide without cover. Slid forward around turn to challenge leader entering straight before tiring badly from 200m.
Began fairly, ridden forward to sit 2-back the rail before turn. Took inside run entering straight to look a chance before condition ran out.
Settled 4Ls off the pace in early and middle stages, 3-wide towards the rear making the home turn, quickened up smartly and forged to command 250M, drew clear for a decisive victory.
Well covered in midfield, never far off 3Ls back, lacked winner's acceleration passing 350M, no impression on winner thereafter but boxed on well to hold 2nd.
In mid-division, sat 3-wide with cover and never far away from leaders, loomed a strong chance turning in, not finishing pace of winner inside 300M, dueled for 2nd place
Began only fairly, soon hustled along to obtain a spot just behind leaders, ran on well early straight but turned one pace over final 150M.
Strolled forward, unable to slot in and was left 3-wide without cover throughout, led briefly early straight, headed 250M, kept on same pace final 200M.
Dropped back to last, well off the pace and detached from main group early stages, got back to it 900M, ran past beaten rivals turning in but never reached leaders.
Voided of early speed, detached form main group early on, got back to it 900M, picked up only fairly when asked in straight, never reached contention.
Always in touch behind leaders, soon outdashed by first five passing 350M, lacked further response inside 200M.
Began only fairly, shaken up early and improved to a midfield position, had little to offer turning in, never in the hunt.
Driven along early, moved up to share the lead on the inner, first to be beaten passing 400M, gave ground rapidly.
Shared lead on the outside, tried to break away 450M, soon headed and weakened.
Began well, ridden along to settle one-out, one-back before turn. Slid forward entering straight, hit from 400m, kept finding to the line despite strong challenge.
Crowded out start, settling midfield in one-off position. Rolled forward entering straight, threw out strong challenge from 200m, just failed.
Jumped OK, ridden along patiently between horses towards the rear. Taken out around turn but bumped 400m when looking for run. Finished strongly final 200m.
Ridden along to maintain forward position but wide. Crowded at turn and lost position, taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began well, ridden to hold rail position three-back from leader. Popped off fence around turn, rolled forward to look a chance entering straight, kept on until flattened 100m.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader back stretch and around turn. Looked a chance entering straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Outpaced, settling at rear but well away from the fence. Still well back entering straight, ran past tired horses final 200m.
Shifted in from wide draw but still held three wide at rear. Improved position but wide around turn. Bumped 400m but kept on well until 200m when one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw to rail and improved position before turn. No run early in straight but only one-paced when clear.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Caught up to main field entering straight, switched out wide and ran past beaten horses.
Hard ridden to lead, crossing to rail before turn. Caught soon after entering straight but kept on to 100m before flattened. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Ridden along early from good inside draw to take box seat behind leader. Started to give ground shortly after straightening.
Ridden along early but caught wide without cover. Rolled forward around turn but was soon running on empty and slipped back gradually.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off very strongly in straight and scored by a neck.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in 5th, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position turning, closed off well in straight to get 2nd, just missed.
Began fairly, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well to get 3rd without threatening the first two.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, steadied near 900M, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to make frame. (Lost left hind plate)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6-7 lengths back, difficult to settle near 1400M, similar position on turn, finished off well in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader in 3rd, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover after 900M, wider turning in, but still made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, got its head up on a number of occasions in the early stages, raced 7-8 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover turning, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Began well from gate 10 but unable to find cover in the early stages, sent forward near 1200M, positioned next to the leader in 2nd, peaked on run near 300M, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, only passed a few tired runners in straight.
Began fairly, raced 6 lengths or so back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, made some progress early in straight before checked severely near 200M, eased down.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd in the early stages, got cover on turn, failed to close off in straight and steadied near 250M.
Jumped with them, raced 4-5 lengths back in midfield, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea)

Made all from a poor draw, held on well under pressure.
Jumped well settling 2-wide 3L back in 4th or 5th to straight, fought on steadily to reach 2nd 100 metres out.
Broke well from a low draw settling one back on rails, kept on steadily without quickening in straight, lost 2nd 100 metres out.
Jumped moderately from the one draw, settled mainly in 3L 5th on rails in just better than midfield, kept on at the one pace under pressure.
Pressed on from the widest gate before settling 2-wide in 2L 3rd, similar position turning in, faded gradually after straightening.
Began moderately, remained in last few, made modest progress in straight, nearest at finish.
At rear early, improved steadily along rails to reach rear of midfield at the Rock, kept on same pace under pressure.
Jumped moderately, settled one from last, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
In midfield racing keenly at time, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back from a wide draw to trail the field, produced no impression in straight.
Wide in midfield early before dropping back to last few, made no impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly, raced wide without cover in midfield, gave ground from around home bend.
Jumped fairly and was urged to take the early lead. Eased to settled behind the pace backstraight. Nicely box-seated around the bend and ran down rival final 50M.
Best out and raced in a disputed lead early. Took sole possession of the lead 800M and held advantage into home straight. Kept on well and only headed by winner final 50M.
Among early leaders. Settled behind the pace after 800M. Kept on well after straightening but unable to sustain effort closing stages and settled for a minor placing.
Raced along the rails and no better than midfield. Crowded and lost a bit of ground 600M. Towards rear turning in and steadily made up ground.
2-wide and no better than midfield. 3-wide under pressure making home turn. Kept on fairly after straightening but unable to turn up a notch closing stages.
Among early leaders. Raced along the rails and 2Ls off at the rock. Ran on without quickening in the straight.
3-wide and no better than midfield. 4-wide and 3Ls off the lead turning for home. Stayed on same pace in the straight.
Jumped well but soon got crowded and raced in rear section. Remained towards the back turning for home. Made a late dash and was closest at finish.
Jumped awkwardly and raced wide towards the rear. Under pressure 600M out and was widest turning for home. Ran on fairly thereafter.
Raced 2-wide at midfield. Ridden along and was within 3Ls making home turn. Unable to turn up a notch in the straight.
Hampered on jumping and raced towards the rear. Ridden along rounding home turn. Made up a bit of ground early straight but caught in traffic near 200M. No improvement thereafter.
Blew start and raced at the rear. Dropped further behind backstraight and became detached. Never recovered.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, ran on well to get 2nd.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 - 3 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow sectionals, stormed home for 3rd.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow pace, kept on nicely until final 100M headed.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, suited by the slow tempo, hung on well until final 80M weakened.
Eased back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow sectionals, ran on gradually.
Began awkwardly, then settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight despite harmed by the slow pace and checked 200M.
Prominent, settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the slow tempo, one paced only until final 100M was steadied.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, unable to show any dash in straight. (Lame right front)
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the slow sectionals, dropped off soon after straightening.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Speed to grab lead, set tempo on rail & soon scooted 2L clear, bowled along until shaken up turning in, kicked on & won easily.
Smart break, caught 4 wide no cover & rolled to 3rd 3 wide no cover at 500m, still wide & driven 300m, boxed on & edged to 2nd 120m.
Fast start, restrained to midfield 3 wide with cover, under pump 500m, hard-ridden 300m, shifted inside & stayed on to take 3rd late.
Smart break, raced 2nd 1 off no cover, nudged along 570m, driven in pursuit final turn, one-paced & tapered to wire.
Good start, settled back rail midfield, shifted 1 off & driven 300m, kept on evenly.
Taken back from widest, sat tail of main body, wide home turn & driven, ran on centre track for minor inroads.
Fast break, raced handy 3 deep no cover, slotted 1 off with cover 600m, under pump 500m, staying on when bumped rival 150m, plugged on.
Broke OK, taken back to outer near rear, ridden along 500m, driven wide into stretch, tepid run home.
Sharp start, slotted 1 back on rail 780m, bustled 500m, hard-ridden 300m, no extra & weakening when impeded 150m.
Moderate start, dropped to rail near rear, driven 300m, struggled in run home.
Missed break & rousted, mustered to sit midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, found nothing & faded, eased final stages.
Missed break, detached last, driven along & soon 5L adrift, never a factor.
Speed to lead, headed 1050m, tracked 1 back on rail, shaken up 300m, battled to lead 100m & edged away.
Smart start & bustled, worked to lead 1050m, headed 850m, led again 630m, shaken up final turn, all out & headed 100m, boxed on.
Sharp break, camped midfield 3 wide with cover, driven 350m, closed to 3rd 100m & kept on.
Slow start & bustled initially, settled on inner near tail, shifted out 450m & wide into stretch, driven 300m, sound closer to take 4th late.
Fast start, drifted back to midfield on rail, hard-ridden turning in, stayed on without threatening.
Broke OK from widest gate, rousted & worked to sit handy 3 wide no cover, wide progress turning in & driven, boxed on in 3rd until tapered final 100m.
Moderate break, bustled throughout, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, hard-driven in stretch & stayed on centre track for minor inroads.
Slow break, raced 1L detached at tail, ridden final turn, switched centre 200m & ran on for minor late gains.
Settled back at break, sat midfield 1 off, checked off heels 520m & lost momentum, driven turning in, shifted inside & plugged on one pace.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 500m, driven 300m, ran home same speed.
Slow start, mustered to settle 1 back 1 off, niggled under pressure 520m, weakened out in stretch.
Broke well & driven wide, advanced 1 off to narrow lead 850m, headed 630m, driven 300m, found nothing & wilted tamely.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L, clocked advantageous slow sectionals and made all.
Pushed to keep up in front of midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Pushed to hold the box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, however no turn of foot, just ran on.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, however soon reduced 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3LS off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Behind midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased to rear, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Very slow away, at back, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.

Placing: UR
Comment: Rider dislodged on jumping.
Began well, allowed to set own pace, kicked ahead when momentarily headed 800m, unchallenged in straight pulling clear for easy victory.
Jumped with field, taken straight to rail and thereafter followed leader from start to finish without being able to narrow the gap.
Pressed forward between horses to settle one-back, one-off back stretch. Got shuffled back final turn, taken very wide entering straight, ran on steadily to grab third on the line.
Bumped start, outpaced and taken in to fence towards the rear. Improved position back stretch, ran on steadily in straight under hard riding.
Ridden to maintain forward position but left wide without cover from 800m, 3L from leader. Rolled forward final turn, 3rd into straight, hung in under pressure and difficult to ride from 200m.
Jumped well, sharing early pace before settling outside leader passing 1200m. Got shuffled back 600m when outside horses moved forward, blocked for run 200m, kept on one-paced.
Began fairly, restrained and shifted across being horses, settling in last pair. Improved position from 1000m to 600m but found nothing when given open run from 200m.
Ridden vigorously early before slotting into one-off position behind midfield. Under pressure from turn, wide into straight, plodded past tired horses.

Ridden along from wide draw but failed to muster, dropping back to clear last entering back stretch. Tagged on to main field final turn but unable to get clear running from 100m and not properly tested.
Ridden aggressively from wide draw to obtain forward position but held 3-wide without cover. Slid forward to sit outside leader by 700m but spent force soon after straightening for home. Faded.
Crowded start, cut to fence and improved position to midfield. Took closer order turning for home but ran out of steam entering straight and drifted back gradually.
Began well, raced with pacemakers before being shuffled back first turn. Started to give ground shortly after entering back stretch, becoming clear last by 700m. Unacceptable performance.
Reserved near the rear 6Ls off the pace, driven wide 400M, closed off strongly to get up near line.
Began well, sat handily behind leader along the rails, came with a strong looking challenge 300M out, led inside 200M and continued willingly, caught close home.
In 5th place 2-3Ls behind leader, travelled well to straight, ran on gamely for 3rd.
Settled behind midfield along the 2-path, held up early straight then switched back to inside for running, kept on steadily to the finish.
Dropped back to a rearward spot, no closer than 3-wide from 1100M, angled out further entering the straight, stayed on moderately.
Travelled 3-wide in mid-division with cover, nudged along 450M, stayed on without threatening.
Crossed to the lead nearing 1200M, set steady pace upfront, joined by rivals 400M, battled on early straight but lacked further response inside 200M, weakened.
Switched off to the rear, 7-8Ls off the pace early and middle stages, waited with on the inside, made some progress final 300M but never reached contention.
Went forward as usual, sat at the hindquarters of leader, took keen hold, led briefly passing 350M, faded mid-straight.
Urged along after the jump to hold a midfield position along the rails, failed to quicken with main rivals 400M, beaten early straight.
Not far off from the pace but was caught 3-wide without cover, gave ground entering straight.
Slow to begin, guided to the rails and settled behind mid-division, failed to muster when driven along passing 400M, soundly beaten.

Settled behind midfield on rails, angled out for a run entering straight, quickened well down the centre of the track to snatch victory final strides.
Attempted to make all, fought on dourly to hold advantage only to be worn down close to home.
Niggled at early, settled within 3L of pace in 5th on rails, shifted out for a run entering straight.
Settled one back in 3rd on rails, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.
Began from a tricky draw, settled wide in midfield, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield near rails, ran on in straight to be nearest at finish.
Soon taken back to race in rear on rails, saved a lot of ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide towards the rear, made modest progress under pressure down the centre of the straight.
Settled well behind, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Settled well behind from the widest draw, went past well-beaten horses in straight.
Vied for lead early, settled 2-wide in 2nd from 1200 metres, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in 4th, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Never on terms.
Midfield, dropped away quickly in straight.
Among early leaders. Settled behind the pace back straight. Nicely box-seated at the turn and quickened nicely after switching out. Ran down leader 150M out and coasted home.
Settled 2-wide behind midfield. Switched out turning for home and rallied in the straight.
Raced towards the rear until 1100M. Allowed to stride forward and caught up with leader 800M out. Shook off rival and was in front final 250M. Caught by winner 150M and just held on for 3rd.
Raced along the rails and no worse than midfield. 2-3Ls off turning for home and ran on well to make the frame.
Soon at the rear. Trailed field and under heavy pressure 600M. Took a wide turn home and steadily made up ground in the straight to be closest at finish.
No better than midfield. In rear section but had a ground saving trip around home turn. Stuck in traffic inside 300M and ran on fairly final stages.
Dropped back from wide draw and raced along the rails in rear section. Near last turning for home. Caught in traffic 300M to 200M, quickened well once in the clear.
Jumped well and raced among early leaders. Better than midfield and kept within 3Ls of the lead backstraight and at home turn. Ran on same pace in the straight.
Niggled forward from wide draw and eventually took the lead before entering back straight. Held a slim lead into home straight but bowed out of contention final 200M.
Settled towards the rear. Placed under pressure 600M out but last to enter home straight. Made up some late ground over beaten runners.
Nicely positioned near the lead early. Kept getting shuffled back in backstraight. 5Ls off making home turn and not much respond when pressured. Checked 300M and never picked up again.
Settled 3-wide at midfield. 3Ls off rounding home turn. Faded shortly after straightening.
Among early leaders. Settled behind the lead backstraight, kept pace around home turn but weakened after straightening.
Tracked nicely behind the leader, despite harmed by the fast pace, ran on strongly to score comfortably.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls at fast sectionals, kept on strongly until final 100M headed by the winner.
Pushed to settle in midfield, travelled 5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, finished off nicely to get 3rd.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, then travelled 9Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, ran on well for 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace without any acceleration.
Settled worse than midfield, 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, checked 350M, despite suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Prominent early, however was steadied and taken wider 600M, never looked likely thereafter.

Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast pace and also hampered 600M, weakened soon after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, then settled 7Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on. (Questioned for performance, see incident report)
Hard ridden forward to settle in midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, flattened badly 300M.
Began awkwardly and stumbled, then did not stretch out and remained detached from the field. (Lame left front next day)
Broke well, snagged to midfield 1 off with cover, edged out 630m, driven 430m & quickened to lead 230m, held on under pressure.
Broke OK, raced 1 off behind midfield, niggled 550m, shifted out & ridden 430m, ran on to 2nd 170m, chased hard to wire.
Smart start, settled midfield on rail, shifted out 630m, driven final turn, checked off heels 330m & switched inside, kept on to seal 3rd.
Outpaced at start, raced rail near rear, to last 600m, shifted out home turn, 5L back & driven 400m, stayed on readily for solid gains.
Taken back from widest & soon detached, tagged on at tail 800m, switched wide & progress 600m, quickened 380m & closed until levelled out 100m.
Slow start, raced 1 off near tail, shifted out 560m, checked off heels 360m & not clear run, driven 240m, kept on but not fully tested.
Tardy start & bustled to race rail midfield, shifted out 430m & ridden, checked off heels 320m, not clear run 120m, plugged on.
Moderate start, mustered to vie for early lead, raced rail & settled 1 back, shifted 1 off 380m & driven soon after, plugged on one pace.
Speed to lead but soon joined, settled back 4th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide for progress 530m, soon driven, led 380m, emptied & headed 230m, faded out.
Good start, settled 3 wide with cover midfield, niggled 600m & ridden 450m, plugged on one pace.
Broke OK, soon outpaced & driven, to rail 1150m, under pump 400m, plugging on when stopped in run 250m, shifted out & kept on one pace.
Broke OK & bustled 4 wide to lead outright 1150m, to rail 900m, shaken up under pressure 400m, headed 380m & faded tamely.
Sharp start, battled to vie for early lead, snagged back & caught handy 3 wide no cover, shifted 4 deep 520m, driven final turn, found nil & wilted.
Fast start & vied for early lead 5 deep, settled 2nd 1 off 900m, ridden 450m, found nothing & weakened.
Speed from wide gate, caught wide no cover 2nd, closed to press leader final turn, shaken up to lead 400m, driven clear & kept on to wire.
Lacked early pace & niggled at rear, smooth progress top of home stretch, switched out & shaken up 330m, rattled home late & fast to take 2nd.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 1050m & raced handy 1 back, driven & switched out 380m, battled to 2nd 100m, boxed on but lost place final strides.
Good break widest & driven to slot 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, rolled wide no cover final turn & driven 400m to 2nd, no extra final 100m & tapered.
Sharp break & bustled, slotted midfield 1 off, hard-ridden turning in, outpaced but ran on again for late headway.
Speedy start, snagged back to rail fore of midfield, driven 400m & boxed on to wire.
Sluggish break & rousted, mustered to 1 off behind midfield & over-raced 850m, wide home turn, driven 430m, ran on for minor inroads.
Fast start, settled handy 1 off with cover, ridden along 500m, plugged on tepidly.
Taken behind from wide gate & settled rail near tail, shifted out 550m & ridden turning in, kept on evenly.
Snagged from wide gate to back of midfield 3 wide with cover, advanced to midfield 650m & over-raced, shaken up 400m, one-paced & weakened in run.
Tardy break, mustered to lead 1050m & crossed to rail 800m, nursed in front until headed 400m & found nil, faded thereafter.
Slow start, raced on outer near rear, niggled throughout, outpaced 380m, plodded on weekly.
Missed break & bustled, raced rail behind midfield, under pump 720m, struggled in run home.
Eased at start, 8.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M whist hanging in, scored by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden forward, occupied the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, closed off strongly 300M, just missed by a neck.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, checked 150M, ran on for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail behind the field, then progressed into a midfield spot, 5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and share the lead at fast sectionals, hung on until 200M flattened.
Pushed forward for a more prominent spot, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on until 100M flattened.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok in final stages.
Hard ridden forward but trapped 3 wide, continued on to shifted to 2 wide and share lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
At rear, 8.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, checked 700M, benefited by the fast tempo, just ran on ok in straight.
Behind midfield, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Took rail at back, 7.5Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly in straight, checked 150M.
In front of midfield early, 6Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3-4 wide, checked 400M then weakened.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster enough speed to cross in front, trapped 4 wide throughout behind the front runners, hampered by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the fasts pace, dropped off quickly 500M.
Began well, pressed forward to sit 2L behind leading pair. Came off bridle 400m, threw out challenge 200m, lunged forward final strides to win on line.
First into stride, not pushed and content to sit outside leader before re-taking lead 400m. Battled strongly when challenged final 200m, losing only in final strides.
Began well, rolled forward to sit in second tier being leading pair. Held up for run from 400m. but kept on well when clear.
Jumped with field but not enough speed, settling toward rear while edging closer to outer fence. Lay out passing 300m, kept on under pressure, bumped and unbalanced final stages.
Crowded out at start, recovered and taken to outer fence 2L from leaders. Put under pressure final 300m but only one-paced.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear but well away from outer fence. Switched to centre track 300m to make challenge but only one-paced under hard riding.
Began awkwardly and lost ground. Hard ridden to course proper when unable to get clear run from 400m to 100m. Not properly tested.
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered, pressed forward to lead. Set pace to 400m before giving ground and dropping back. Substantial blood in trachea, lame left hind.
Held up towards the rear, patiently ridden in a slowly run race, picked up pace 350M, cantered past rivals under gentle handling, led 100M and cruised to an emphatic victory.

Soon led, enjoyed a soft lead and set a slow pace first half of the race, quickened up tempo 600M out, still going well into final 200M but failed to hold off the mighty ABLE FRIEND nearing 100M. hung on for 2nd.
Settled in midfield about 3Ls off the pace, shifted out 300M for clear run, stayed on well enough for 3rd but had no chance with the impressive winner.
Always in touch, 4th making the turn for home, driven along 500M out, briefly threatened but turned one pace over final 200M.
Reserved near the rear, saved ground along the rails, stayed on moderately over final 400M, lay in under pressure and awkwardly placed final stages.
Tracked the pace along the fence, kept up the chase on leader until weakening final 100M. (sustained cut to right hind leg and found to be lame next day.)
Positioned one out one back, driven along 500M but lacked the needed response, grudgingly gave way passing 200M.
Settled in mid-division, steadied 300M, failed to quicken thereafter.
Slow to begin, 7Ls back in the rear early stages, shaken up 500M but gave limited response only, never reached contention.
Began well, ridden forward along fence settling 3-back from leader. Took inside run on straightening, held for clear run passing 200m, switched out 150m and finished off strongly.
Bumped heavily start, recovered, pressed forward to take box seat before turn. Came off fence 400m, hard ridden but failed to muster until final 100m when doing best work.
Bumped heavily start, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back before turn. Had clear running from 350m and battled on under vigorous riding to grab 3rd on line.
Pressed forward from wide draw, settling ahead of midfield but 3-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, battled on gamely in straight.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Temporarily headed 800m, retook lead 600m, kicked clear 400m, led to 50m when swamped.
Ridden along between horses, settling 4-back, one-off. Turned wide and kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Began well, ridden along 3-back, one-off. Held for run half-way up straight, kept on fairly when clear.
Jumped with field, taken to fence 4-back from leader. Close on heels 750m and switched out, entered straight behind horses, one-paced.
Began fairly, then crowded for room. Shift across behind horses settling four-back, one-off. Swung wide into straight and boxed on fairly.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling last but away from fence. Turned a little wide but only one-paced under hard riding in straight.
Taken straight to fence three-back from leader. Unable maintain pace and shuffled back turn. Checked 550m, losing ground. Found nothing in straight.
Steadied soon after start, taken to fence but unable maintain position, dropping to last pair. Stayed on fence around turn but found nothing in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader on settling. Led from 800m to 600m before easing to 2nd. Kept on in straight before tiring final 200m.
Ridden along early from wide draw before shifting in but still held 3-wide at rear. Widest into straight, one-paced under hard riding.
Jumped well, positioned behind the midfield on rail, 7 lengths back, angled out near 550M, finished off very strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Began with them, positioned nicely in 3rd, 1 to 2 lengths back on rail, same position turning, finished off well in straight, just missed.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, travelled keenly near 1200M, similar position on turn, closed off well in straight to get 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to make frame.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, carried wider turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear entering straight, kept on well until emptied and headed from 100M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 8 lengths or so back at rear, same position turning, made reasonable headway in straight. (Laceration to its right front leg)
Began well, raced 6 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground turning, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, positioned 2-3 lengths back in 4th, 2 wide turning, showed no turn of foot in straight and hampered near 100M.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, same position turning, kept on one-paced in straight and hampered final 100M.
Began with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, no daylight early in straight and checked near 200M but already a beaten horse.
Began well, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight and hampered final 100M.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 8 lengths back on rail at rear, still there on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.

Soon taken across for rails run in rear of midfield, slightly worse half-way out, switched out for a run entering straight, responded well to take command inside final 200 metres.
Niggled at early, prominent on rails when checked and lost position 500 metres out, renewed effort shortly after straightening but found winner too good.

Tight between runners early, towards the rear before making rapid progress out wide far side, two-out-one-back when hampered and lost position 600 metres out, wide in midfield into straight, heavily bumped 250 metres out, kept on.
Broke well, settled in rear, widest runner turning in, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.
Taken back from the widest gate, remained well back to straight, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without threatening.
Moderately away, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, checked near 400M, angled out in straight, crowded and bumped near 300M, made some headway thereafter.
Soon taken back to race in rear, checked on rails and lost position 400 metres out, saved ground turning for home, ran home one-paced. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced.
Vied for lead from wide draw settling outside the leader 1200 metres out, hit the front coming out of back straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well, in front early before ceded advantage coming onto stables bend, settled just off the pace down far side, dropped out tamely in straight.
With leaders early, travelled wide without cover in better than midfield, took off half-way down back straight, unbalanced and lost position 500 metres out, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Vied for lead early eventually taking up running on rails 1200 metres out, gave ground from home bend. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Lame next day)
Better than midfield and kept within 4Ls of the pace back straight. Closed to within 2Ls turning for home. Ran on strongly and ran down early leader final 50M.
Soon in the lead. Held advantage deep into the home straight but unable to find extra to fend off eventual winner final 50M.
Travelled nicely behind midfield. 4Ls off making home turn. Responded well and steadily made up ground in the straight to land a minor placing.
Jumped well and kept pace behind the speed throughout. Kept on well but unable to turn up a notch in the closing stages.
Raced along the rails midfield. Steadily made up ground in the straight and was closest at finish.
Jumped well and allowed to settle midfield. 3Ls off turning for home. Kept on fairly in the straight.
Raced along the rails behind midfield. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Taken back from wide draw and raced towards the rear. Made up some late ground.
Dropped back from wide draw and raced in rear section. Widest turning for home and ran on only fairly in the straight.
Raced behind the pacesetters. A length off turning in but faded out of contention before being crowded final 100M.
Dropped back to race in rear section. Lacked a response when pressured rounding home turn and ran on same pace thereafter.
Dropped back from widest draw and trailed field throughout. No impression in the straight.
Eased to midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, finished off strongly to take the victory.
Pushed forward to share the lead along the fence, kept on well until final 50M headed by the winner.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Jumped awkwardly, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, closed to the line well when clear 150M.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on steadily.
Taken back, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
At rear, settled 10Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground over the last 150M.
Eased back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Rolled forward to settle in midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until final 200M was checked.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, flattened badly over the last furlong. (Hung in badly in the straight)
Ridden forward to share the lead, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened badly 200M. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Good break & soon led, crossed to rail 1340m & set tempo, 1L clear & shaken up turning for home, all out closing stages, just held on.
Fast start, tracked 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shaken up 3 deep 450m, driven very wide final turn, closing run but just failed to get there.
Smart start, snagged & raced rail behind midfield, rolled on a spot 730m, shifted out & driven 400m, gradual closer to nick 3rd late.
Smart start, sat 1 back on rail in 3rd, ridden 400m, shifted out turning in, boxed on in pursuit but tapered & swamped close home.
Broke well but bustled to sit midfield, rolled forward a place backstretch, ridden 450m, battling run to press for minors, edged out of frame late.
Taken back to tail from widest, sat 1 off, driven turning in, progress checked 150m, switched off heels 100m, driven & kept on.
Slow start & bustled early, sat near tail 1 off, switched very wide 400m & hard-ridden, closed off centre track for solid inroads.
Slow break, raced rail near tail, ridden final turn, plugged on one pace.
Tardy start, sat 1 off behind midfield, slid back near tail exiting back stretch, checked 200m, plugged on tepidly.
Broke OK, niggled initially, raced fore of midfield 3 wide no cover, over-raced 1200m & slotted midfield 1 off, driven wide 470m, widest home turn, found little.
Started well, settled handy 4th 1 off with cover, driven under pressure 400m, shifted out into stretch, struggled & faded in run.
Speedy break to race prominently, caught 3 deep no cover until settled close 2nd 1 off 850m, niggled 550m, under pump 450m, emptied final turn & weakened out.
Smart start, sat midfield 1 off, shifted wide home turn, shaken up 300m, quickened & closed to lead 120m, drew ahead comfortably.
Pace to snag lead 1060m, set tempo, 2L clear & shaken up turning in, battled on but all out & headed 120m, no extra.
Smart start, advanced to 2nd 1020m, settled 1 back on fence 930m & over-raced, driven into stretch & kept on evenly.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover midfield, driven 350m & ran on soundly without threatening.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 1060m & restrained, handy when checked off heels 830m & lost ground, shifted out & driven 310m, ran on evenly.
Broke well, raced wide no cover & settled 3rd 1 off, driven 310m, kept on one pace.
Lacked early pace & bustled to settle rail behind midfield, driven into stretch, stayed on one pace.
Broke well, sat midfield on rail, checked off heels 800m, niggled 550m & soon under pump, drifted out on turn, outpaced, plugged on until tapered late.
Settled back at start to race 1 off near tail, niggled 550m & soon driven, one-paced in run home.
Slow start, raced at tail on rail, over-raced 950m, ridden turning in & plodded on evenly.
Sluggish break, camped rail near tail, driven 300m, plodded on tepidly.
Broke OK, niggled 3 deep near rear, soon last pair 1 off, under pump 450m, found nothing in weak run home.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Eased at start, took rail, 5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M around the field in 3 wide, ran 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in the lead, being pressured at fast sectionals until 800M, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden early, 4Ls off the fast tempo 2 wide, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed forward, shared lead 2 wide, continued to clocked fast sectionals until 800M, emptied 200M.
Pushed early, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, no turn of foot in straight.
At rear, 6Ls off the leaders, suited by the fast tempo, switched to 4 wide at home bends to make its run, never improved.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 3 wide behind midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace, made early move 800M, soon reduced 250M.

Placing: DISQ
Comment: Settled in midfield along the fence, 4Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Ridden along to hold rail about 2L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn, popped off fence 200m, picked up momentum to hit front 50m before pulling clear.
Hard ridden to get up inside early leader before taking over narrowly but wide around turn. Hit front soon after straightening but run down final 50m.
Began best but caught wide without cover and forced to race three-wide around turn. Wide into straight but battled on gamely to the line.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping to near last but close to rail. Saved ground turn, finished off strongly in straight but forced to switch in final 50m when running out of ground.
Began well, kicked up inside leader to hold rail. Looked chance entering straight, kept on strongly till flattened and swamped final 50m.
Hard ridden from wide draw to go forward, settling in one-off, one-back position by turn. Looked chance on straightening but only one-paced final stages.
Ridden along early to hold one-off position two-back from leader. Bumped and unbalanced 600m, turn wide, kept on one-paced in straight.
Began OK, not pushed, settling three-back from leader. Turned a little wide and kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Crowded out start, raced at tail throughout, hung in and proved difficult to ride in straight, never a threat.
Began fairly, ridden along to hold position 3-back from leader before shifting out and bumping another 600m, losing ground. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, ridden along but unable find cover, slipping back gradually. Widest into straight but found nothing under hard riding.
Ridden forward but wide and forced to race three-wide around turn. Very wide into straight and never competitive.
Held up in mid-division 4Ls off the pace, picked up pace gradually from 400M, had to switch ground near 100M, rallied strongly along the rail to get up near line.
Began well, settled 3Ls off the pace in 5th, responded well passing 300M, continued gamely to the line, just held in a blanket finish.
Enjoyed an uncontested soft lead to 600M, pressed by rival entering home turn, dueled for most of the straight and only caught by first two final stages.
Caught 3-wide and left with no cover from 1300M, strode forward to join leader 600M, dueled for most of the straight, lost out late stages.
Reserved in the rear 6-7Ls off the leader in a slowly run race, closed off well in straight and finished the final 400M fastest, never nearer.
Strolled forward from wide barrier and crossed to race just off the pace, bustled along over home turn, kept on final 300M but no threat to leaders.
Began awkwardly, guided to the fence and settled about 5Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, waited with till 350M but only gave limited response in straight, never a serious threat.
Settled behind midfield entering back straight, stayed on fairly over final 300M.
Held up towards the rear, turned 3-wide back straight, taken widest 450M out, ran on steadily without threat.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along early stages, tracked leaders to straight, shaken up home turn but found nothing in reserves.
Settled midfield along the 3-path, came under pressure passing 500M and failed to muster a response.
Soon shifted across behind runners from wide barrier, settled last 6-7Ls off the pace, failed to pick up entering straight, never threatened.

Settled well behind from the widest gate, baulked for a run until passing the 200 metres, quickened well to snatch victory near the line.
Settled in last few, did not find much room early in straight, finished off race well to just fail to get up on line.
Waited with, switched out for a run entering straight, made up good ground down the centre of the track.
Jumped awkwardly, settled wide behind midfield, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Began well from the middle draw, settled just off the pace one off the rails, hit the front on straightening, unable to sustain effort and swamped under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Settled in midfield, produced modest late impression closing stages. (Blood in trachea)
Began well from a wide draw, settled wide just better than midfield, improved to reach 3rd entering straight and then 2nd over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Jumped fairly, not far off early stages, drifted back to forward of midfield passing the 1000 metres, renewed effort approaching home turn, kept on well in the run home.
Never better than midfield, made no impression in striaght.
Jumped well from a poor draw, taken back to race wide in midfield, remained similar to straight, failed to quicken under pressure.
Pressed on from a wide draw to soon take up running, led the field to the straight, folded up quickly.
Midfield early, steadied on rails and lost position on home bend, never recovered.
Ridden for pace early, settled for one-back position on rails coming out of back straight, similar in 3rd turning for home, weakened under pressure.
Travelled just better than midfield on rails, came under pressure approaching home turn, weakened soon after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Took cover behind the pace before letting loose 400M. Quickened nicely and took control final 200M.
Off slowly but was ridden along to race behind the pace. Took the lead 300M out but had no answer when challenged by the winner at 200M.
Raced at midfield. Improved to be within 2Ls of the lead 400M. Kept chasing but unable to draw any closer finish stages.
Raced near midfield. 3 to 4Ls off at 400M. Kept on fairly closing stages but unable to turn up a notch.
Shifted to outside and raced in rear section early. Within 5Ls of the lead at 400M. Ran on without quickening.
Raced towards midfield. Within 4Ls of the lead at 400M, ran on without threatening.
Kept within 3Ls of the lead but racing ungenerously. Got to within 2Ls 200M but unable to pick up when the race got serious.
Raced towards the rear. Hampered 500M out and made up ground over beaten runners.
Lead or dispute lead before being swamped inside final 300M.
Raced in rear section. Stayed on same pace over the final stretch.
Settled behind midfield early. Towards the rear and got very unbalanced near 400M and only ran past beaten runners.
Reared as gates opened and lost ground. Raced towards the rear. Improved to within 4Ls of the lead 500M. Unable to find more final 300M.
Lead or disputed lead until 400M. Dropped out quickly thereafter.
Jumped well but struggled to keep pace with leaders shortly. Gradually slipped back and was trailing field midway through. Finished tailed out.
Crowded start, then travelled 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to take the prize by a short head.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to the line until final stride headed by the winner.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, gradually improved when the pace slacked down 650M, closed to the line well to get 3rd.
Sent forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, kept on steadily to the line.
Rolled forward to get a prominent position 2 wide without cover, benefited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Hard ridden forward to settle in midfield along the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, ran on steadily.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suite by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, kept on the same pace to the line.
Taken back to rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, gradually improved rounding the Home Turn, kept on until 250M weakened.
Always at rear, never a factor.
At rear, settled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow tempo, unable to show any turn of foot in straight.
Camped handy, despite suited by the slow pace, kept on until 250M flattened badly.
Midfield, travelled 4Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, eased down soon after straightening.
Broke OK, raced midfield, edged 3 wide with cover 1000m & advanced a spot, steadied 750m to 1 off & fired up, shifted 4 deep home turn, cruised to lead 300m, driven clear.
Steady start, raced behind midfield, shifted 1 off 1000m, ridden 430m to chase winner, kept on to take 2nd late.
Sharp break & soon led, to rail 1500m & set tempo, shaken up 400m, all out & headed 300m, kept battling but tapered.
Fair break, raced 1 off with cover fore of midfield, driven 460m, outpaced but plugged on.
Fast start & sat 1L back 1 off, bustled to close on lead 850m, ridden in 2nd 500m, boxed on evenly until tapered late.
Rousted & outpaced early, niggled along behind midfield 1 off, edged 3 wide 1000m, driven wide into stretch, stayed on evenly.
Tardy start, raced at tail 1 off, carried wide final turn, plugged on for minor headway.
Broke well, settled back 1 off near tail, driven wide final turn, stayed on one pace.
Taken behind from widest gate to rail at tail, advanced gradually to race behind midfield 700m, held in run 430m until driven 300m, stayed on moderately.
Taken back at start & rolled to 3 deep no cover midfield, forced 4 wide 1000m, niggled 850m, wide turning in, found little in one-paced run.
Driven from gate to settle rail midfield, driven & shifted 1 off 700m, labored one pace & tapered out.
Bustled initially& settled1 back on rail, ridden 400m, faded in tame stretch run.
Slow start, trapped 4-deep no cover midfield, gradual progress from 1300m, pressed lead 850m, lost ground on turn, emptied 350m & faded.
Tardy start, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, gradual progress from 1300m & handy 1000m, under pump 550m & wide into stretch, struggled in fading run.
Speed to lead & rousted to snare rail 1000m, set tempo, joined in front turning in, shaken up 430m, kicked on 300m & soon 1L clear, held off closing rivals.
Fast start & driven to vie for lead 1000m, settled handy 1 off, crept to share lead turning in, shaken up but outpaced 300m, kept on again to reduce margin at wire.
Taken back from widest to race on outer in rear, to tail 850m, cruising turning in, not clear run, shifted to inner 300m, driven 250m, strong run to 3rd late.
Good break, parked 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 deep 500m, driven turning in, battled on evenly.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, over-raced 750m, 4 deep final turn, driven 400m but outpaced, closed off for minor late gains.
Smart break, rousted early to sit 1 off fore of midfield, shifted 3 wide 600m, 4 deep home turn, shaken up 400m & progress to 3rd 300m, tapered late.
Broke OK, sat 1 back on rail, ridden 360m & shifted out, kept on evenly, tight for room close home.
Moderate start, raced on inner fore of midfield, shifted out & ridden 400m, crowded & not clear run in stretch, not fully tested.
Taken back at start, soon bustled at tail, progress & shifted 1 off 800m, over-raced 700m, switched out & ridden 400m, kept on one pace.
Moderate start, bustled to race 3 wide with cover near rear, widest & driven 430m, plugged on tepidly.
Outpaced at start & ridden, mustered to race midfield 1 off, shifted 3 wide home turn & driven 430m, plodded on tamely.
Broke OK, outpaced & soon niggled on rail behind midfield, driven 400m, found little.
Settled 1L off the good pace, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Pushed forward, 1L off the good pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace, lack room 400M, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Pushed forward to lead by 1L at good pace, ran on until 150M flattened.
Bumped badly at start, 3Ls off the good pace, made minor ground 200M.
Settled in a more prominent spot, 1L off the good pace, ran on until 200M emptied.
Bumped start, 2.5Ls off the good pace, flattened 200M.
Pushed early but not muster, 6Ls off the good pace, no dash.
Eased at start, crossed towards the stand side behind the field, 6Ls off the good pace, no turn of foot.
Bumped at start and lost ground, 7Ls off the good pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace, ran on until 150M flattened.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 3Ls off the good pace, out of fuel 300M.
Bumped at start and lost ground, never competitive.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace, reduced 300M.
Began well, ridden along between horses before settling one-off, one-back around turn. Urged forward from 350m, hit front 200m, pulled clear for easy win.
Jumped with field, not pushed, easing back towards rear but away from fence. Three-wide around turn, widest into straight, finished off strongly to grab second.
Steadied shortly after start, shifted across behind horses and last on settling. Still last passing 250m when switched out and picked up momentum, finishing strongly.
Began well, sharing early pace before easing half a length behind leader. Took over lead shortly after straightening, collared 200m but kept on well till swamped final strides.
Inconvenienced soon after start, switched in to find cover, settling three-back, one-off. Switched out 400m to make run, doing best work final 200m.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing three-wide outside leader to and around turn. Spent force soon after straightening and weakened gradually.
Began awkwardly, mustered along fence to sit in slipstream of leader around turn. Came off fence 400m but only one-paced under hard riding in straight.
Began well, taken quickly to fence three-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn but only one-paced in straight (lame right front leg).
Pressed forward to lead on settling, travelling keenly into and around turn. Found nothing when put under pressure 400m and gave ground gradually.
Positively ridden, settled one off in 2nd, waited with till 200M, continued on well once in the lead, was strongly challenged late stages but held on.
Up with early pace then sat behind leaders long the rails, held up for clear running early straight, switched out 150M and closed off strongly, just denied.
Fractious in stalls, crossed to the 3-path just behind the pace but left with no cover form 900M, moved closer nearing home straight, kept on steadily to line, held on for 3rd in a close finish.
Tracked leaders in a steadily run race, well placed in 5th turning in, kept grinding away under pressure, just missed 3rd in a close finish for the minor placings.
Rushed forward to lead from 1100M, led at steady pace, placed under pressure 250M, continued on well despite losing the lead 200M, only swamped late.
Settled midfield along the rails, held up for clear running 450M-300M, stayed on but lacked the pace to seriously challenge.
Restrained behind midfield, 3-wide for much of the way, made some progress down the center of track without seriously threatening leaders. (Blood in trachea).
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, failed to quicken when driven out nearing 400M, not reached leaders.
Near the rear in 10th place, gave limited response turning into straight, flattened out final 200M.
Caught wide without cover from 12, taken back for cover and settled much further back than intended, fanned wide into straight but showed little and was done with around 200M.
Dropped back to a position near the rear, 4-5Ls behind leader, not quickened in straight, never threatened.
Restrained in the rear but proved difficult to settle, 6Ls off the pace 400M, had little to offer entering straight, no impression.
Began well, raced with leading pack before eased into box seat before turn. Took split between horses 350m, hit front 300m and pulled clear.
Began well, raced keenly before being eased approaching turn, settling along the fence three back from leader. Popped off fence 400m and followed winner's path for second.
Shifted in and bumped start, ridden along patiently, settling four-back, one off. A little awkward around turn, switched in for run 300m and finished off nicely.
Pressed forward from wide draw, before settling half a length behind leader entering turn. Looked chance on straightening but unable to find extra.
Ridden along between horses early, settling three-back, one-off before turn. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped well, led on settling but eased to one-back, one-off before turn. Urged forward entering straight and boxed on fairly under hard riding.
Began fairly but pressed forward from wide draw to lead passing 1100m. Crossed to rail, led to 300m when passed, kept on one-paced.
Began OK, ridden along looking for cover but held three-wide without cover into turn. One-paced in straight under hard riding.
Began fairly, shifted across behind horses, last on settling but kept away from fence. Took turn 3-wide, switch in top of straight but one-paced under vigorous riding.
Jumped OK, quickly taken to fence five-back from leader. Came off fence 450m but found little when put under pressure in straight.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped. Taken closer to face settling between horses at the rear, Swung wide into straight but only one-paced.
Got off OK, taken to fence, settling four-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn but found nothing in straight when asked.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing with leading pack initially before easing back slightly but three-wide without cover. Gave ground shortly after entering straight.
Ridden along early before being eased to find cover but held three-wide at rear. Proved difficult to settle early and never competitive.

Began well, Raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, no cover after 900M, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score. (Lost right front plate after passing the winning post.)

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, waited with till 300M, kept on very well to the line but just unable to hold off the winner. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when cleared to get 3rd. (Lost right front plate.)
Jumped well, showed early speed to race prominently, 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 4th on turn, bumped turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1000M to race outside leader in 2nd, same position turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 to 3 lengths back in front of midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Away with them, unable to slot in early, raced 3 wide with cover in 6th until 1000M, 2 wide on turn, angled out near 550M, peaked early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, showed early speed to race prominently, a length or so back, similar margin back turning, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, angled out after turning in, showed minor progress in straight.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, raced 7 lengths back at rear, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight, never a threat.
Slightly slowly away, taken back to race 6 lengths or so back at rear, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, but only showed limited response thereafter.
Slowly away, recovered to race 5 lengths back on rail in midfield, same position turning, kept to inside after straightening but failed to close off.
Taken back from the widest draw, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced at tail throughout, taken wide turning in, finished off one-paced in straight, never competitive.
Moderately away from gate 13, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, got no cover for the majority of the race, emptied early in straight when workload took toll.
