Vied for lead from a wide gate, obtained rails run in the front on stables bend, kicked clear upon straightening, won readily.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside leader in 2nd, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Broke well, settled two wide in 5th within 3L of pace, came under pressure on rails entering straight, failed to quicken.
Broke well, settled about 3L off in joint 4th on rails, shuffled back around the bend, produced good late impression closing stages.
Slowly away, soon recovered to midfield on rails, angled out turning in, produced modest late impression closing stages.
Jumped fairly, settled 2-wide in midfield, one-paced under pressure.
Being taken back when clipped heels early, settled towards the rear on rails, kept on steadily without quickening.
Failed to muster travelling at the back, only ran past well-beaten horses in the straight.
Gradually came across from the widest gate, travelled at rear to straight, only ran past well-beaten horses in the run home. (Tactic questioned)
Settled wide behind midfield, made no show in straight.
Settled wide behind midfield, circled field from leaving the Rock to reach 3rd on top of home bend, folded up quickly after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
In front early, ceded advantage coming out of home straight the first time to settle in 3rd on rails, dropped away quickly passing the 500 metres. (Heart irregularity)
Ridden along for some distance in the early stages to race behind the pace. Switched out on straightening and quickened nicely. Ran down the leader a few strides before the post.
Urged along from wide draw and took the lead 800M out. Stayed on well in the straight but was caught a few strides before the post.
2-wide and no better than midfield. Responded well when asked on straightening and was closest at finish.
Raced along the rails behind midfield. Saved ground making the turn and 4Ls off turning in. Kept on well in the straight to make the frame.
Raced along the rails at midfield. Within 3Ls of the speed rounding the turn, kept on but unable to turn up a notch in the straight.
Settled behind midfield. Widest turning in and steadily made up ground in the straight.
Allowed to drop back from wide draw and raced in rear section. Had a ground saving trip around the turn and ran on steadily in the straight.
Disputed lead early but had to settle behind the speed after 800M. 3-wide turning in and unable to find more in the straight.
Hard ridden out of the gates and raced 2Ls off the speed. Unable to keep pace home turn and gradually faded in the straight.
Battled for the early lead but had to settle wide at midfield. 3Ls off rounding the turn and weakened on straightening.
Not enough speed and raced in rear section. Towards rear on straightening and never quickened.
Soon outpaced and was detached most of the way. Got closer to field at the end but still finished last.
Pushed to settle midfield, steadied 1000M, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, dashed well to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 2nd in a bunched finish.
Pushed forward to share the lead along the fence, kept on strongly until final 20M headed by the winner in a bunched finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, ran on nicely for 4th in a bunched finish.
Jumped fairly, then settled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, closed to the line strongly.
At rear, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, kept on steadily to the line until final 25M was steadied.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on fairly until final 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, hung on until final 200M weakened, also was checked 75M.
Always at rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made ground nicely however unable to be tested inside 100M.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, soon flattened after straightening.
Smart start, settled behind midfield 1 off, moved 3 wide 800m, ridden 500m, shifted wide turning in, grinding progress to nick it on wire.
Sharp break, settled 1 back on rail, niggled 400m, ridden turning in & shifted out, driven to lead 150m, joined 50m & rallied but headed on wire.
Moderate start, soon prominent, slotted midfield 1 off with cover, raced keenly & shifted 3 deep 850m, driven turning in & progress to 3rd, kept on evenly.
Broke OK, crossed to rail & rolled to midfield, ridden 500m, stayed on for minor gains.
Broke OK, restrained to camp at tail, bustled a touch 600m for progress, shaken up 250m, ran on for sound inroads.
Speed to lead on rail, joined 1st turn & challenged, soon edged ahead again & set tempo, pressed 600m & extended, 1L clear & driven 300m, headed 150m & swamped.
Snagged back from widest, sat rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off 800m, shuffled to tail 540m & ridden, wide final turn, kept on for minor gains.
Missed break & last, progressed to race 3 wide with cover near tail, progress 4 wide 600m, driven 500m, wide on turn, stayed on until tapered final 100m.
Broke OK, bustled initially, sat 1 back 1 off, ridden 500m & outpaced, checked off heels turning in, plodded on tamely.
Missed break, recovered to race 1 off near tail, niggled 3 deep 600m, hard ridden 450m, very wide in rear final turn, boxed on moderately.
Started OK, snagged back & caught 3 wide midfield, forced 4 deep 850m, pushed forward 650m, all out to hold 2nd on turn, emptied 200m, faded.
Slow start, bustled & mustered to vie for lead 3 deep 1st turn, settled close 2nd 1 off, ridden 600m, emptied on turn & faded out.
Burst to lead & driven to clear advantage, soon eased & settled 0.5L in front, dictated tempo, shaken up & kicked on turning in for dominant win.
Good break, sat 1 back on rail, ridden into stretch, outpaced initially but closed off well final 150m, always held.
Moderate start, rolled 3 deep no cover to race handy, driven turning in, boxed on one pace.
Tardy start & rousted early, worked 4 deep no cover until slotted 3 wide 800m, niggled throughout, driven 400m, wide final turn, ran on one pace.
Fast start but no match for leader, raced close 2nd 1 off no cover, driven 320m, emptied 200m & faded.
Broke OK, raced midfield 1 off with cover, driven 350m, plugged on one pace.
Tardy break, soon 3L detached from main body in second-last, tagged on 400m, wide on turn, kept on past beaten rivals for late headway.
Broke OK, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, checked 850m, niggled along, driven 350m, plugged on one pace.
Moderate start, taken back to race rail near rear, driven 300m & drifted out in run, never a factor.
Broke well, sat rail midfield, ridden 350m, found nil & faded tamely.
Slow start & rousted at tail, soon well adrift, niggled & gradually closed on main body, plodded on same speed in stretch.
Sharp start, sat fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shaken up 330m, found nothing & wilted, tailed off in stretch.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the leaders, made its run around the field 3-5 wide, dashed strongly 300M to score despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, closed off strongly for 2nd whilst hanging in.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 2 wide, dashed strongly for 3rd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well to the line, just missed a place.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked most straight, dashed well to the line.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leaders 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, made early move 600M, dashed well to the line.
Hard ridden forward, shuffled back along the fence from 1000M, 4Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
Pushed early but checked, shuffled back, 5.5Ls off the leaders on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 200m, little dash when clear.
Pushed early in midfield, steadily went forward and shared the lead 2 wide at slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back early, trapped 3 wide throughout, allowed forward 1000M, 3.5Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, reduced 250M.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pressed forward from wide draw before seeking cover 3-back, one-off 900m. Held for running turn and top of straight, switched out 300m, finished strongly when clear.
Ridden along early, settling one-off, one-back before turn. Swung 4-wide entering straight, hit the front 250m but run down final strides.
Began well, raced outside leader till left in front 1000m when leader broke down. Led to 150m when swamped by first two.
Ridden along to hold rail, slipping into box seat from 900m. Came off fence 400m to look a chance but unable close gap.
Slow into stride, outpaced, dropping to near rear. Taken to one-off position back stretch, finished off steadily between horses in straight to be closest at finish.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail, settling three-back from leader entering back stretch. Looked a chance turning for home but only one-paced under hard riding final 300m.
Jumped with field, ridden along early but taken wide when leading horse fell. Slid forward to sit outside leader turn, looked chance turning for home, one-paced final 200m.
Slow into stride, shifted across behind runners, settling close to rail but towards the rear. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Began fairly, taken to fence, settling 4-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn, one-paced in straight while drifting out.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing three-wide outside leading pack without cover. Dropped back slightly around turn, very wide into straight, one-paced.
Began awkwardly, losing significant ground, and soon trailing field. Never competitive and finished tailed out in straight.

Placing: UR
Comment: Began best, led to 1000m when broke down, dislodging rider.
Began well, raced handily along the fence just behind leader, quickened to lead inside 200M, kept on well to hold off pursuing rivals.
Began awkwardly, guided to the fence and sat 5Ls off the pace, unable to improve position until passing 300M, charged through a narrow passage mid-straight and mounted a late challenge, just held.
Settled midfield along the fence, waited with till passing 300M, chased home the winner but always held.
Held up in mid-division along the 2 path, stayed on well over final 300M and pushed winner all the way to the finish, lost out on 3rd narrowly.
Eased to a 2-wide spot behind mid-division, fanned 3-wide into straight, stayed on evenly for a moderate 5th.
Dropped back to a rearward spot 7-8Ls off the pace, switched away from fence entering home turn, closed off final 400m fastest, nearest finish.
Sent forward, slowed down tempo once crossed to the lead passing 1200M, kept on same pace turning in, headed inside 200M, weakened towards line.
Never far off in 5th, 2.5L behind leader, driven out 400M, had every chance but lacked the needed response, flattened out late stages.
Caught 3-wide in midfield but raced with cover, swung wide 400M, stayed on mildly and never a serious threat.
Strolled forward, tracked leader one out one back, came under pressure nearing home straight, faded out of contention passing 250M.
Switched off to the rear, not helped by slow pace middle stages, moved to 3-wide and swung widest home, ran on same pace final 300M.
More prominently placed than the most recent start, 3-wide and left without cover from 1200M, found disappointingly little when driven along 450M, soon dropped out of contention.

Jumped fairly, settled 3L back in joint 4th, showed a great turn of foot upon straightening, took command 200 metres out.
Began moderately, picked up under pressure to better than midfield, just behind the leading trio entering straight, kept on at the same pace without quickening.
Jumped moderately settling in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without quickening.
Settled behind midfield, ran on steadily in straight without threatening.
Settled well behind, ran on steadily in straight, did best work late.
Vied for lead from the widest gate, travelled 3-wide most of the way to straight, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Soon taken back from a wide gate travelling well behind, made up ground in straight, never nearer.
Jumped awkwardly travelling in forward of midfield to straight, soon faded after straightening.
Shared the fast pace to straight, folded up quickly after straightening. (Blood in trachea) (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Niggled along from the one draw to hold narrow advantage from two others, folded up quickly after straightening.
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.

Placing: PU
Comment: Travelling in midfield before running off the track rounding home bend, pulled up.
Allowed to settle back, ridden along passing 500m, challenged at 200m, too strong final 50m.
Lost left fore plate shortly after start, early pace to settle off speed, ridden along passing 400m, made strong ground late to just miss.
Began well, showed pace to travel outside leader on stand rail near 500m, quickened at 400, fought on strongly, over powered late.
Jumped well and led stand rail, travelled well quickened at 400, fought on strongly, over powered final 50m.
Settled mid, steadied at 500m, held up between 300-150m, taken to inside and finished strongly.
Settled mid 3Ls off leader, drifted back near 500m wen unable to quicken, urged along from 300m, eased at 150m, finished well.
Showed speed racing in leading group, couldn't quicken at 400m, one-paced to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, allowed to settle mid, hard ridden from 400m, battled on.
Urged along early, settled midfield on stand rail, couldn't make ground and weakened out of it.
Jumped awkwardly, hard ridden early, settled mid and gradually gave ground.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, settled on speed, hard ridden passing 400m and commenced to give ground (blood in trachea).
Slow out, ridden hard towards stand rail early to settle worse than mid, made no ground.
Settled at rear, unable to keep up, mad some late ground.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, finished off nicely to take the victory by a neck.
Eased back from a wide barrier, settled 8Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed strongly for 2nd when clear 300M.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace to the line.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, closed home well final 100M.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on steadily to the line.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on until final 150M weakened.
Prominent early, improved gradually to park outside the leader 800M, kept on steadily until final 150M weakened.
Jumped slowly, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Prominent, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.
Good start, pushed on from wide to sit outside leader, shaken up 400m, outpaced a stride our two, rallied to overhaul leader at 200m, drew clear.
Settled back at break to rail near tail, driven & reminders 450m, slicing stretch run to claim 2nd late.
Speed to lead, ridden to snare rail & scooted along, driven turning in, kicked on for a few strides, emptied & headed 200m, faded & lost 2nd late.
Slow start & rousted 1 off near tail, wide on turn, checked in run 250m, rattled late for solid inroads.
Driven at break & rowed along midfield on inner, shifted out on turn & driven 500m, stayed on for moderate headway.
Missed break & driven at rear, settled at tail on inner, driven & shifted out on turn, stayed on for minor gains.
Broke well, rousted & unable to hold prominent spot, settled 6L back 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, driven wider turning in, one paced & tapered late.
Broke well & prominent early, ridden & soon outpaced, pumped along 1 off fore of midfield, shifted out on turn, found nothing in tepid run home.
Slow start, rousted to race midfield 1 off, 3 deep & reminders 600m, hard-ridden & forced widest home turn, struggled in stretch.
Tardy start, claimed rail & rolled to race 4L 4th, shifted out 450m & driven, outpaced & faded in run.
Broke well, ridden forward from wide to race 3rd 1 back on inner, under pressure 500m, weakened tamely in stretch.
Fast start but lacked toe & driven, soon outpaced in midfield, driven along 3 wide & gradually drifted back to last at 500m, tailed off.
Broke OK, camped rail midfield, edged out on turn, waited with until driven 300m, quickened to lead 150m & drew clear, eased late.
Taken back to midfield, checked off heels 1200m to 1off behind mid rank, shuffled toward tail on turn, progress & shaken up 300m, ran on to 2nd 50m.
Vied for early lead, snagged & headed 1400m, restrained to 3rd 1 off with cover, to 4th 650m, smooth progress to close turning in, driven & led 300m, all out & headed 150m.
Smart start, prominent early, snagged to slot 1 off with cover midfield, forced 3 deep on turn, driven 430m to challenge, boxed on until tapered.
Tardy break & bumped, sat behind midfield 3 deep with cover, shuffled toward tail on turn, driven 450m, nudged rival 400m, closed off for minor inroads.
Slow break, soon at tail 3 wide, raced last pair, shifted wide 550m, driven widest in stretch, stayed on for minor gains.
Tardy start, raced near tail 1off, checked off heels 1100m, to tail 950m, minor progress 700m, hard-ridden home turn, one-paced, shifted out 200m, stayed on.
Started OK & soon over-raced, restrained 1150m to midfield 1 off with cover, continued to over-race, waited with until driven 300m, stayed on moderately.
Fast break, settled 2L 4th 1 back on rail, niggled 850m, to 3rd 650m but shifted out & driven in 4th 430m, outpaced & plodded on tamely.
Sharp start, worked to lead on rail 1400m, pressed 1070m & vied for lead, nudged to outright lead 850m, shaken up 420m, headed 300m & weakened out.
Taken back from widest gate, trapped 4 deep no cover in rear rank, very wide into stretch, bumped 400m, driven but struggled.
Slow start & bumped, raced rail behind midfield, progress on turn, travelled on bridle but never had clear running in stretch, checked 200m, not extended.
Broke well, rolled on to dispute lead 3 wide 1070m, slotted 1 off 950m, all out to challenge lead 400m, soon emptied & faded tamely.
Moderate start, trapped wide & rolled to sit 3 deep no cover midfield, hard-ridden 350m, plugged on until emptied & weakened out final 150m.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at good pace, made all.
Hard ridden forward, shared the lead 2 wide at good pace, closed off strongly 300, bumped 100M, ran on for 2nd.
Midfield, 4Ls off the good pace on the fence, lack room 400M, progressed steadily 300M.
3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, on heels 700M, made ground 200M.
Very slow away, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made some ground 200M.
Eased to obtain box seat, pace good, flattened 200M.
At rear, 7Ls off the good pace 3 wide, ran on ok.
Failed to muster at rear, 7Ls off the good pace, 2-3 wide, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, soon out of fuel 400M.
At back, 6Ls off the good pace along the fence, never nearer.
Midfield, 4Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 wide throughout, emptied 300M.
Eased behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Ridden along early, settling three-back, one-off. Pushed out for clear running 350m, hit front 150m, pulled clear.
Bounced well, holding rail behind leader. Stayed on rail turn, picked up momentum gradually in straight, doing best work final 100m when had clear running.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, put under pressure from 300m, battled gamely until passed by first two final 100m.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped, shifted across behind runners, settling near rear. Lay out turn, held for run early in straight, finished off well when clear.
Began well, ridden along to hold position one-off, one-back between horses, no clear run top of straight, switched out 200m for run and kept on fairly.
Pressed forward from wide draw but held three-wide outside leading pair to turn. Urged forward top of straight to look a chance 300m but only one-paced final 150m.
Bounced well, pressed forward, settling 3-wide, 3-back from leader. Stayed wide around turn, boxed on one-paced in straight.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail, 3-back from leader. Drifted further back around turn, one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Ridden forward from wide draw to sit outside leader on settling. Urged forward on straightening to look chance before turning one-paced final 200m.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Turned wide, switched out further 300m for clear running but only one-pace.
Jumped with field but soon outpaced, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Turned widest into straight but found nothing when put under pressure.

Jumped fairly, outpaced, settling 4-back from leader. Switched out 800m to move forward, turned very wide, but soon under pressure, weakening gradually. (Irregular heart rhythm. Substantial amount of blood in trachea).

Towards the rear, not hurried early stages, moved closer passing 600M and swung 3-wide for home, picked up pace gradually under top weight, joined leading group inside 50M, class prevailed in the end.
Settled 5Ls off the pace in midfield, held up early straight, responded well when gap opened up 300M, hit the line strongly and almost won it only to be denied by DESIGNS ON ROME at the post.
More prominent than usual, settled 2-wide in the group chasing leaders, travelled well and loomed a serious threat at 300M, led narrowly 150M, fought on well to the line, headed last strides.
Led slowly early stages, relinquished lead near 1200M, tracked leader to straight, shifted out for clear run 300M, stayed on well and only beaten to 4th in a blanket finish.
Slow to begin, sent forward taking the lead near 1200M, took them along at good pace, kept on evenly when drive out 450M, swamped by rivals inside 150M, not beaten far.
Waited with in the rear, well off the pace early stages, crept closer to be 5Ls down 400M, ran on steadily down the outside.
Settled behind midfield 6-7Ls behind leader in middle stages, stayed on moderately over final 400M but offered no serious threat to leaders.
Never far off the pace, saved ground on the inside, kept on evenly in straight but lacked the needed response, always well held by leaders.
In mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace, shaken up 500M, had every chance to 150M, one paced thereon and steadied at 100M, eased towards the line.
Began very awkwardly, assumed a forward position just behind leader, found little to pressure 400M out, soon out of contention, weakened rapidly final 100M.
Got off OK, switched to rail, settling three-back from leader. Unbalanced 650m and shifted out, found gap between horses 300m, driven hard to get up and win in final stride.
Ridden along to hold forward position, settling one-out, one-back. Got clear running soon after straightening, hit the front 300m, kept on strongly only to lose in last stride.
Ridden along from wide draw to sit three-back, one-off on settling. Pressed forward on entering straight, joint leader 200m out, battled to line.
Began fairly, switched across behind horses, settling last along fence. Saved ground turn but unable get clear running in straight until 200m, finished off nicely.
Ridden forward to sit outside leader on settling. Rolled forward entering straight, hit front 300m, kept on well until swamped final stages.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set comfortable sections to 300m when collared, kept on fairly until tightened final stages.
Began awkwardly, taken to fence at rear, lost position around turn. Switched out entering straight and ran on fairly.
Pushed forward from inside draw to hold box seat on settling. Took closer order around turn but disappointed for run 300m. Finished off fairly when clear final 200m.
Ridden forward from wide draw to get midfield position but held three-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, kept on well in straight until 200m when flattened.
Ridden along from good draw to hold midfield position but proved difficult to settle from 1300m. Switched out around turn but found little in straight under hard riding.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Switched out around turn, made some ground initially in straight, turning one-paced final 200m.
Pushed along early to hold position just behind midfield but got shuffled back around turn. One-paced in straight. (Lame left from leg).
Crowded for room soon after start and then raced fiercely, refusing to settle, dropping to near last. One-paced in straight under hard riding.
Pressed forward from wide draw but trapped three-wide outside leader without cover. Lost position around turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths or so back in 5th, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 250M to score narrowly.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very well in straight but just losing out narrowly late.
Jumped well, raced 1-2 lengths back in 3rd, easy run on turn, was still in contention 200m from home but peaked on its run soon after, stayed on for 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back in midfield, same position on turn, angled out in straight and made some headway to make frame without threatening.
Began well, raced with cover, 4-5 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway thereafter to be nearest on line.
Crowded out start, raced 10 lengths back at rear, still well back turning, made some progress in straight (See racing incidents).
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover throughout, 4 lengths back in midfield, finished off evenly in straight.
Fairly away from gate 10, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, same position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail behind midfield, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 7-8 lengths back at rear, 2 wide on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off evenly.
Began well, raced prominently in 2nd, same position on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight and dropped out tamely (Blood in trachea).
Crowded out start, raced 11 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Prominent early, steadied and gradually shuffled back to behind midfield down the straight the first time, made rapid progress leaving the Rock to take up running, hung on dourly in the run home.
Well back, made rapid progress behind eventual winner down far side to reach 3rd 3-wide leaving the Rock, similar turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield, carried backward approaching the Rock, towards the rear into the straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Well back early stages, gained 3-wide around stables bend to reach midfield, improved further under pressure at Rock chasing leader into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Soon taken well behind and waited with, switched out for a run entering home straight, made steady headway down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.

Settled behind midfield on rails gaining closer when pace slackened but steadied 1200 metres out, carried further back down far side, shifted wide into straight, kept on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Midfield, made steady headway to join the leader from around stables bend, yielded ground leaving the Rock.
Settled in midfield, slightly worse when wide coming down the straight the first time, regained midfield position going up the Rock, ran home one-paced under pressure.

Broke well to lead early, ceded advantage to settle just off the speed approaching the winning post the first time, carried further back to midfield approaching the Rock, made no show in the run home.

Travelled wide with leaders early crossing to rails 1200 metres out steadying the pace, ceded advantage mid-way down far side, faded under pressure from home bend. (Lame) (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Ridden early, settled just off the pace on rails, gradually shuffled back to midfield from stables bend when pace slackened, dropped further back at Rock, made no impression thereafter.

Vied for lead early stages, settled for one-out-one-back position turning into home straight the first time, dropped further back to midfield going up the Rock, soon weakened out of contention. (Lame next day)
Bumped and unbalanced at start, urged forward to settle behind leader, inside run on straightening and once balanced sprinted quickly from the 200m to win well.
Taken back from wide gate at the start, commenced a wide run passing 500m, widest on straightening and ran home strongly despite laying in under pressure.
Jumped well, settled behind leaders, awkwardly place near 400m, challenged strongly at 200m but no match for winner.
Settled worse than midfield, momentarily held up on straightening and ran on well through the field without threatening.
Hard ridden for a midfield spot in 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Settled midfield on rail, took an inside run on straightening, challenged briefly near 200m, weakened final 50m.
Jumped awkwardly and settled worse than midfield on the rail, urged along from the 400m, one paced in the straight.
Jumped well, took lead near the 1300m, held together on home turn but found nothing when asked to quicken at the 300m, weakened out of it final 150m.
Ridden forward from wide gate to settle outside leader at 1200m, pushed along from 400m but found nothing and weakened out of it in the straight.
Crowded on jumping and taken back to settle in a rearward position, never in it and one paced to the line.
Settled midfield 3 wide with cover, awkwardly placed on heels near 400mand did not run on in straight.
Urged forward early, caught 3 wide without cover, under pressure from 400m, never in it.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader along the fence, enjoyed the slow tempo, dashed well to take the victory by 3/4L.
Settled in front of midfield about 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, gradually improved rounding the Home Turn, dashed well to get 3rd despite harmed by the slow tempo.
Settled in front of midfield about 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slow sectionals, ran on steadily.
Taken back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, closed to the line well.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Ridden positively to cross from a wide barrier to park outside the leader at slow tempo, kept on until 150M flattened.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, kept on steadily until 150M was checked, dropped off thereafter.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, checked 600m, rousted 530m, shifted out final turn, shaken up 300m & quickened, driven to lead last stride
Broke well, rolled 4 wide to lead 850m, bustled a touch to snag rail 800m, narrow lead & shaken up 300m, driven 1L clear, all out closing stages & headed at wire.
Slow start. Soon mustered & rolled to midfield 1 off with cover, progress on turn, shifted wide 330m & driven on, edged to 2nd 150m, tapered final strides.
Broke well, taken back to 3 deep with cover near rear, niggled 650m, under pump final turn, shifted out 300m, crowded & bumped 250m, strong closer, just missed frame.
Decent start to race handy 3 deep no cover, advanced to press lead 600m, driven 300m, outpaced & plugged on, tapered late.
Fast break, taken back to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven wide final turn, boxed on without threatening.
Taken back at start, bustled 1000m to race 1 off near rear, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on for minor inroads.
Disputed early lead 1 off, settled just behind leader, gained cover 600m, driven turning in, outpaced & faded in run.
Speedy start, caught 5 wide & keen, snagged back 900m & slotted 3 wide with cover midfield, hard-ridden 250m & minor bump, tepid effort.
Moderate start, niggled to race rail behind midfield, steadied away from heels 600m, driven & shifted out 320m, soon emptied & eased.
Speed to lead on rail, restrained & headed 850m to sit 1 back 800m, hard-ridden 300m, found nil & wilted.
Dropped in at break, raced at tail & soon detached, niggled from 900m, hard-ridden turning in & plodded on same speed.
Fast start, tracked lead in 2nd 1 off no cover, closed on leader final turn, driven to lead 200m & kept on well to wire.
Speedy break, driven early to settle handy 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, wide into stretch, closed off for late gains.
Slow start, camped rail at back of pack, progress on inner 500m, shifted out turning in, good headway to 3rd 50m, no extra final strides.
Smart start, settled back in midfield 1 off with cover, shifted wide final turn, shaken up 300m, stayed on without threatening.
Speed & rousted to lead, set tempo on rail 2L clear, 1L clear turning in & driven under pressure 300m, headed 200m, no extra & faded.
Moderate start & bustled to sit midfield on rail, niggled along, hard-ridden 400m, plugged on evenly.
Sharp start, driven to settle 3rd 1 back on rail, shifted out & driven 300m, one-paced, crowded & checked off heels 70m.
Tardy start, driven to settle rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off 500m & shuffled back to rear rank, driven 300m, plugged on for minor late headway.
Taken back to sit 1 off with cover behind midfield, shuffled to rear rank on turn, driven wide into stretch, kept on evenly.
Slow start, settled rear of group 1off with cover, shifted 4 wide 500m & niggled, widest & driven into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Broke OK, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, rolled forward a spot 600m, driven along 500m, very wide final turn, soon emptied & faded in run.
Sluggish start, soon several lengths detached in last & driven, never a factor.
Awkward away but soon resumed a prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M for 2nd.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace and got 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at slow sectionals, soon reduced 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, very one paced in straight.
Very slow away, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight, lack room 200M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, no dash.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 250M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Jumped OK, settling in midfield in one-off position. Urged forward three-wide from 600m, wide into straight, rolled forward to lead 100m, held on.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail three-back from leader. No run top of straight, got split 200m out, powered through to just fail.
Began fairly, taken across behind horses and last on settling but kept away from fence. Took inside runs on straightening and finished off nicely.
Began awkwardly but pressed forward from widest draw to lead passing 800m. Set good pace to 120m when caught and swamped final strides.
Allowed to find feet, settling four-back from leader along rail. Held for run around turn, took rails run on straightening and finished off nicely.
Began best and led to 800m before settling in box seat. Got inside run on straightening to look a chance but flattened final 50m.
Ridden along between horses, settling behind midfield in a threw-wide position. Kept three-wide around turn, boxed on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Ridden along three-wide to hold forward position before settling one-off, one-back around turn. Looked a chance on straightening, kept on fairly until checked 100m.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling four-back, one-off. Lost position around turn, turned wide, boxed on one-paced till checked 100m.
Ridden along early to hold forward position three-back, one-off. Got close to heels turn, slipping back, one-paced in straight. (Found to be a roarer as previously reported).
Bounded in air at start and lost ground, then hard ridden to get up and race alongside leader around turn. Looked chance on straightening before tiring final 200m.
Hard ridden from jump but failed to muster and trapped four-wide at the rear. Urged forward turning for home, widest into straight, tired final 200m.
Quickly into stride, led through steady fractions, joined by rival inside 300M, rallied under pressure to force a dead-head on the line.
Tracked leader along the fence, moved up to join leader inside 300M, dueled all the way up the straight and hit the wire together for a dead-heat.
Began well, settled one-out-one-back, came to have every chance turning home, ran on well but was always held by first two.
Held up in mid-pack but never far off from leaders, into clear 200M and did beset work late, just missed 3rd.
In 4th 2Ls off the pace, kept on evenly turning home but not pace to challenge leaders.
Settled towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, waited with till 250M, switched out to clear and closed off the race moderately.
Dropped back after the start and guided towards the rails, difficult to settle 800M, kept on one pace when driven, never a serious threat to leaders.
Began only fairly, settled 2-wide in midfield, gave limited response down the outside in straight.
Caught 3-wide without cover from 11, settled midfield, swung widest home, failed to muster a challenge, no impression.
Held up in a 3-wide position towards the rear but not picked up turning home on this first attempt over 1200M.
Dropped back to last 7Ls off the pace, not quickened passing 350M, never involved.
Held up near last, soon outpaced turning home and behind.

Vied for the lead early from a poor draw, settled just off the pace in 3rd, held slender advantage around the bend kicking over 1L clear over 200 metres out, held on nicely.
Waited with, made significant progress under pressure down the straight, nearest at finish.
Jumped well from a poor draw, settled wide in mid-division of spread out field, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on under pressure in straight without threatening the winner.
Niggled at just worse than midfield, closer up turning in, did not find much room early in straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon taken back from the widest gate and waited with, baulked for a run until after the 200 metres in straight, finished off race very well.
Broke well, gradually settled in midfield, took closer order rounding home bend reaching 2nd upon straightening, but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 meters.

Soon picked up along rails to settle just better than midfield, awkwardly placed on heels approaching home straight, looked for a run just off the rails after straightening, kept on same pace without threatening.
Settled in midfield, switched off rails for a run entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards the rear from a wide draw, went widest turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Mainly in midfield to straight, made modest progress early in straight before fading in closing stages.
Always well behind dropping to tail-end into straight, made some late impression in the run home.

Driven forward to hold 4th place one off the rails, closer up before coming backing 3L off around the bend, renewed effort to dispute lead briefly entering straight, dropped away quickly after straightening.

Worked his way to the lead from a wide gate, increased pace to stretch to 2L lead briefly passing the 1000 metres, folded up quickly after straightening. (Jockey warned for ill-judged pace in the second section)
Broke well from the gate two, shared the pace before the leader quickened his pace coming out of back straight, yielded ground steadily from the 500 metres.
Settled worse than mid, pushed along making home turn, angled out at 300m and finished strongly to gain upper hand final 50m.
Settled in midfield position wide with cover, pushed along approaching home turn, challenged strongly at 200m and fought right to the line.
Settled behind leaders, worked into it to challenge strongly near 200m and tried all the way to the finish.

Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, urged forward to recover and settled just off the pace, held up for clear running on straightening, gained inside run near the 300m to briefly challenge but could not sustain the effort.
Jumped well, eased back to settle worse than mid, unbalanced when bumped at 400m, ran home well in the straight without threatening.
Settle 3 wide without cover behind leaders, tried to challenge on straightening but couldn't quick and was one paced to the line.
Pushed forward from wide gate to settle outside the leader, challenged strongly to take lead near the 300m but overpowered final 200m.
Urged along early stages to settle midfield on rail, tried to make ground between runners in straight, awkwardly place on heels near 150m.
Jumped well but eased back towards rear from wide draw, brief challenge on straightening, one paced to the line.
Travelled well in midfield position, held up for clear in straight running until 200m but did not finish off.
Settled towards the rear, widest on straightening and made no significant ground.
Slow out and settled at rear, made some late ground in straight.
Jumped well, pushed forward to lead, was challenged on straightening and tried to respond but was no match, weakened out of it final 150m.
Taken back at start, could not quicken in the straight and was well beaten.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at slow sectionals, fought on gamely, led 100M, scored by 3/4L.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow tempo, battled on strongly, headed by the winner 100M, kept on for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow pace, closed the line strongly for 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield about 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow sectionals, one paced home.
Settled worse than midfield about 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow tempo, ran on steadily.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, suited by the slow pace, kept on one pace until 250M weakened.
Taken back from a wide barrier, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Failed to muster speed despite niggled along, settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced until 250M flattened.
Jumped slowly, was badly hampered 1100M, 11Ls behind the leader along the fence, never looked likely.
Settled worse than midfield 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, dropped off soon after straightening. (Found to be a "roarer")
Camped handy, caught wide and without cover throughout, hung out from 700M and proved difficult to ride in straight, tailed out.

Placing: FE
Comment: Near the 1100M rider was dislodged.
Bumped start, settled rail at rear, progress from 800m, angled out & driven 400m, stormed centre track to lead close home, cozily.
Speed to lead & snagged rail, set tempo, shaken up 400m, battled to maintain advantage until headed close home, no match for winner.
Driven early to race 1 off outside leader's flank, driven 430m, boxed on in pursuit of long-time leader, always held & tapered.
Broke well & sat 1 back on rail, niggled along, driven & shifted out 500m, stayed on dourly.
Broke OK widest, 4 deep midfield 1st turn, advanced 1100m to 3 deep outside leader 950m, under pressure 650m, kept on evenly under drive.
Broke well but outpaced & rousted, raced 1 off behind midfield, niggled 850m & drifted back to tail, dour progress in stretch for minor inroads.
Broke OK, ridden forward & settled 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, niggled 850m, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on one pace.
Broke well but outpaced & raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, scrubbed along 900m & lost place, driven at tail final turn, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Slow start, raced 1 off in rear rank, checked off heels 800m & driven 400m, switched very wide for progress, plodded on in stretch.
Slow start & rousted to rail midfield, niggled 950m, hard-ridden & edged out turning in, plodded on tepidly.
Decent start, bustled early to sit 1 off with cover fore of midfield, ridden 950m & unable to hold position, struggled in run & eased.
Good break, caught 4 wide midfield, lost cover 900m & tucked in 3 deep 700m, driven 500m, found nil & eased.
Slow start, raced very wide no cover rear rank, progress from 950m to race midfield turning in, all out & emptied 400m, faded.
Sluggish break, raced near rear 4 deep, minor progress 850m but hard-ridden & widest turning in, to tail 300m & wilted tamely.
Good break, snagged to midfield 1 off with cover, crowded & bumped turning in, driven 370m, quickened & ran on to lead close home for cozy win.
Broke well, taken back to 1 off near rear, shaken up 400m & switched out, flew home late under strong drive to snag 2nd.
Sharp break & prominent early, camped 4th 1off with cover, nudged a touch 500m for easy progress, shaken up 300m to lead 250m, tapered close home & headed.
Smart start, camped 1 off fore of midfield, bustled 750m, driven 500m & switched out on turn, driven to challenge & kept on soundly.
Broke OK, sat rail fore of midfield, ridden 500m & shifted out, battled on evenly.
Tardy start, raced rail near tail, shifted out turning in, outpaced 400m, responded to drive & ran on for smart late headway.
Good break, prominent early, sat 2nd 1 off, shaken up 430m to press lead, one-paced & tapered late.
Broke OK, restrained to race near tail 1off, shifted 3 deep for progress 750m, mid rank & widest turning in, flattened out 250m, plugged on.
Missed break, mustered to sit rail midfield, driven 400m, outpaced but boxed on.
Speed to lead, set tempo on rail, driven 420m, all out & headed 250m, faded in run.
Decent start widest, snagged to tail, driven along 700m, outpaced & detached early in stretch, stayed on for minor late headway.
Smart start & front rank 1st turn, camped 1 back on rail, every chance & driven 430m, plugging evenly when crowded & checked 170m.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace, trapped 300M, ran on well to score.
Eased at start, 5.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide, made good ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader 2 wide at good pace, flattened 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1 L at good sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Slow away, Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, flattened 200M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost ground, emptied 200M.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, never improved.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never a factor at rear.
Pushed to sit in midfield along the fence, 3.5Ls off the good pace, soon dropped off 400M.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost far too much ground, faded 500M.
Began OK, ridden along rail to grab box seat passing 800m. Came off fence on straightening, found gap between horses 350m, picked up momentum to win on the line.
Jumped best and led field to 850m before allowing another to go forward. Stayed within 1L of leader, took over passing 300m, looked winner before pegged on line.
Ridden along wide to hold forward position, settling one-off, one-back going into the turn. Rolled forward on straightening to look a chance 200m but failed to catch first two.
Began well, raced keenly with leading pack before hampered 850m, falling 3-back. Blocked for run 400m, shifted out, ran home strongly.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after the start, settling towards rear along the rail. Not much room early in straight, found split near 200m, finished off nicely.
Jumped OK, restrained, shifted across behind horses, settling last. No run top of straight, got clear running final 200m and finished off strongly.
Began awkwardly, then crowded, dropping towards rear but away from fence. Found clear running halfway up the straight and kept on fairly.
Worked forward from wide draw but unable to cross in and held three-wide without cover. Boxed on fairly in straight without looking dangerous. (Lame right front leg)
Ridden along early, settling behind midfield in a 3-wide position. Lost position around turn, kept on fairly in straight. (Laceration right hind leg)
Began well, ridden along to hold rail three-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but found little in straight and faded final 200m.
Pressed forward from a wide draw to lead passing the 850m. Caught shortly after entering straight, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Began fairly, ridden along 3-wide behind midfield till checked 850m when crowded. Lost position round turn, eased down shortly after entering straight. (Jockey not happy with action)
Caught 3-wide no cover down the back-straight, strolled forward passing 800M to join leaders, led 450M out, fought off a challenge 150M, kept finding extra in the run home.
Up with pace early, 3Ls back in 5th making the turn for home, closed off soundly on straightening, nearest finish.
Held up in midfield about 5Ls behind leaders, saved ground along the inside, driven 500M, ran on steadily. Encouraging debut.
Guided to a 3-wide spot in midfield 5Ls off the pace, made steady progress over final 300M for a never nearer 4th. (Jockey suspended for not riding out all the way to the end)
Began awkwardly, held up towards the rear 6Ls behind leaders, closed off final 400M well and made late impression on leaders.
Sat 3-4Ls off the pace, lacked a turn of foot to challenge leaders when driven 450M, stayed on moderately towards the line.
Settled 2Ls back in the group chasing leaders, quickened up smartly to challenge eventual winner 300M, dueled to 150M, run ended and weakened to 7th.
Held up in mid-division, bustled along 550M, stayed on moderately, lacked room near 150M, angled out and kept on without threat to leaders.
Driven forward, tracked leader from 1000M, not mustered the pace to challenge in straight, held 3rd until 200M, faded towards finish.
Unbalanced at start, dropped back to a rearward position 6-7Ls off the pace, made some progress past beaten horses but never seriously threatened.
Settled near rear 7-8Ls off the pace, plenty to make up passing 400M, stayed on only fairly in straight and never reached contention.
3-wide towards the rear, travelled keenly early stages, driven passing 400M but could not offer the necessary response.
Up with early pace, took sole lead 1000M, came under pressure inside 600M when taken on by rival, weakened rapidly mid-straight. (Blood in trachea. / Unacceptable Performance)
Dropped back from 14, failed to muster speed despite ridden along, detached in last over 10Ls off the pace, never involved.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead field to 1600m before allowing another to go forward. Took over shortly after straightening, passed 150m but fought back to win on the line.

Ridden along from wide draw, settling one-off, two-back. Rolled forward on straightening, shifted out 200m forcing rider to stop riding, took lead 150m, shifted in under pressure 100m and caught on line.
Ridden along early, holding rail 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn, kept on well in straight but no match for first two.
Began well, ridden along but kept away from fence, gradually angling out to a three-wide position around turn. Wide into straight and boxed on only fairly.
Jumped with field, no speed and held at rear away from fence. Began forward move entering straight and ran on fairly final 200m.
Began only fairly, ridden along to hold midfield position three-back from leader. Kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Pressed forward to grab box seat on settling. Took closer order entering straight, looked chance 200m, flattened final 100m.
Outpaced early and last on settling. Taken wide entering straight and ran on fairly to be closest at finish.
No early pace, settling along rail towards rear. Stayed on rail around turn, but only one-paced in straight, tiring final stages.
Began well, ridden along in midfield before steadied 1500m then left wide without cover from 1400m. Spent force soon after entering straight, one-paced.
Ridden along from wide draw to lead from 1600m. Set steady pace to straight, caught soon after straightening for home and faded.
Jumped well but proved difficult to manage and overraced, dropping to rear. Never competitive. (Jockey reported saddle slipped 1600m)
Moderately away, raced 2 lengths back in 5th, travelled well throughout, angled out turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 3-4 lengths back in midfield, slightly improved and wider after 550M, finished off strongly in straight but always held by the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6-7 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and closed off well to get 3rd, but no chance with leading pair.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back behind midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, just missed 3rd.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 550M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, 2 wide turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 5 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and made reasonable headway in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, took the lead easily and set a moderate tempo, travelled well throughout, headed near 200M and kept on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Fairly away, positioned 1-2 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, but only finished off one-paced when clear thereafter.
Slightly slow out, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 900M to race in 2nd, there to turn, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, sent forward to race a length back in 3rd, checked near 850M, 2 wide with cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced at tail throughout, 7 lengths back, never a threat.

Jumped well from a low draw, led or disputed lead on rails, soon drew clear, won easily.
Moderate start, settled in 5th on rails within 3L of pace, gained closer turning in, failed to quicken under pressure.
Always thereabouts, unable to quicken to threaten in straight, hung in throughout closing stages.
Jumped moderately, niggled along in forward of midfield, commenced run approaching straight but carried wide turning in, fought on steadily, nearest at finish.
Jumped well, settled behind midfield, tight inside runner after straightening, finished off race nicely.
Moderate start, settled in midfield on rails, switched off rails for a run entering straight, produced only modest impression closing stages.
Slow out and slow to muster, trailed the field to home bend, saved ground turning in, hung in badly and a difficult ride in straight.
Settled in last few on rails, saved ground turning in, did not find much room in the run home.
Vied for the lead from a poor draw, obtained lead outside 2nd coming out of far side, retreated to 2nd spot approaching home turn, faded gradually after straightening.
Jumped well, gradually settled in midfield, kept on early in straight before fading inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, remained wide without cover in midfield most of way to straight, found nothing under pressure.
Always towards the rear.
Raced prominently and wide without cover, folded up quickly in straight.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, raced greenly as a back-marker throughout.
Pushed along early to briefly lead before taking sit near 1000m, travelled well and challenged strongly to hit lead at 300m and held off all challengers.
Jumped well and settled behind leaders on the rail, travelled strongly turning for home and challenged strongly at 300m but unable to match winner in run to the line.
No early speed, settled towards rear on rail, stoked up home turn and made good ground along the inside entire straight.
Settled midfield and raced keenly, angled out at 350m for clear running, tendency to wander around and made strong late ground.

Shuffled back to settle worse than midfield and urged along rounding home turn and made steady ground in the straight.
Jumped well, settled behind leaders, pushed along turning for home, one paced to the line.
Taken forward early but caught wide without cover in midfield position, pushed along at 450m, widest on straightening, brief challenge early in the straight but weakened final 200m after tough run.

Crowded for room at the start, settled worse than mid in wide position with cover, travelled well home turn, held up in early in the straight and then never really clear for the remainder and went to line untested.
Settled worse than mid and raced keenly, when asked for an effort in straight failed to respond.
Began awkwardly and taken back from wide gate, unable to make any ground along the inside in straight.
Pushed forward early to hold position on rail and eventually found the lead near 1000m, travelled strongly in middle stages, asked to quicken at 400m, briefly responded but then weakened final 200m.

Crowded for room on jumping and lost ground, settled at rear and travelled well into the home turn, looked to shift out to obtain clear running in straight but could not do so, tightened at 100m and went to line not fully tested.
Ridden forward early but caught wide without cover, eased back to midfield and still unable to gain cover, hard ridden turning for home and weakened from 400m. Vet: no abs. Must trial.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls, kicked away 300M and scored comfortably.
Settled midfield 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 2nd however not match with the winner.
Taken back to rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well for 3rd.
Eased back from wide barrier, settled 6Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on strongly for 4th.
Missed start, then pushed to occupy the box seat, kept on steadily without threatening.
Taken back to rear from widest gate, settled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, closed to the line nicely.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until 150M weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked chance.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, raced greenly early straight, unable to be tested until 150M, made minor ground thereafter.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on, flattened badly 200M.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never ran on.

Placing: PU
Comment: Prominent, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, eased down 200M. (Bled)
Taken to rear rank, sat 3 wide with cover, smooth progress to midfield 840m, shaken up 540m for wide run, strong advance to lead 220m, extended clear.
Slow start & hefty bump, raced rear rank 4 wide with cover, advanced 850m but soon outpaced & back to rear, hard-ridden 540m, stayed on to snag 2nd at wire.
Heavy bump at start, mustered to sit midfield 3 wide with cover, wide into stretch & shaken up, kept on but always held.
Slow start, raced 1 off with cover rear rank, driven 550m & shifted wide on turn, stayed on strongly, just missed frame.
Sharp start, sat fairly handy on rail, squeezed & checked 880m, driven 430m, shifted out 250m & boxed on for dour inroads.
Led at break, headed 1530m & sat 2nd 1 off no cover, keen 900m, back to 3rd 800m & niggled, shifted out & driven 400m, brief lead 250m, all out & swamped.
Broke well, raced handy 1 off with cover, ridden 500m, shifted out 400m, every chance but found little in one-paced run.
Tardy start & niggled on rail to race midfield, driven 400m, shifted out 200m, stayed on evenly.
Tardy break, ridden & soon led, to rail 1400m & set tempo, driven 400m, all out & headed 250m, faded out.
Broke OK, taken back to rear rank & snagged rail, last & ridden turning in, plugged on tepidly.
Broke well, raced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled along, hard-ridden turning in, outpaced & struggled in stretch.
Slow start, caught 4 wide no cover midfield, advanced 950m to 2nd 800m, shaken up 400m, found nil & faded right out.
Sluggish break, bustled to race handy 3 wide no cover, niggled 800m, under pump 650m, found nothing & tailed off.
Sharp break, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, keen 1000m, shaken up 400m & quickened to press lead, edged ahead 160m & kept on.
Broke OK, parked 3rd 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep & niggled 500m, driven 430m, soon edged lead, unable to assert, all out & headed 160m, boxed on.
Broke well, taken back & eventually slotted 3 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 650m, driven centre track to 3rd 200m, well held in closing stages.
Broke OK, raced fore of midfield 3 wide no cover, rolled to sit handier 850m, 4 wide & driven final turn, kept on one pace.
Missed break, mustered on rail to race fore of midfield, driven 400m, kept on evenly.
Smart start, bustled to lead 1300m, raced 1 off, headed 830m, sat outside leader, shared lead top of stretch, driven 380m but all out & headed, tapered to wire.
Broke OK, lacked early pace & caught wide behind midfield, rolled 900m to 3 deep with cover midfield, wider in stretch, plugged on one pace.
Taken back from wide, raced last pair on outer, some progress on turn, driven widest into stretch, stayed on for minor late gains.
Moderate break, settled midfield 1 off & shifted to rail 900m, driven 430m & edged out, plodded on one pace.
Taken back at break, nudged along on rail last pair, shifted 1 off 650m & ridden, last turning in, plugged on for modest headway.
Moderate start & bustled early to race 1 off behind midfield, driven 850m & minor advance, driven 420m, found little in tepid run home.
Sluggish start & rousted to settle 3 wide with cover midfield, crowded & checked off heels 800m, shifted to 1 off, driven into stretch, faded, eased when beaten.
Slow start, in rear early, bustled 1200m to race rail behind midfield, checked 900m, hung in on turn, 2nd last & driven 650m, plugged on one pace.
Speed to lead, to rail & headed 1300m, advanced on inner to edge lead 830m, driven turning in but emptied & faded out.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, illustrated strong finishing efforts 300M to score by narrow margin.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 0.5L, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, hung on strongly until last few strides.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, pace slow, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear 150M, just beaten by narrow margin in 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, parked outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened, hampered 100M.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, checked early, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 300M.

Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, blocked 4-2, little dash when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster enough speed to lead, 2Ls off the slow tempo 2 wide, reduced 250M.
At rear, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, ran on fairly when clear.
Trapped 5 wide throughout at back and lost substantial amount of ground, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the slow pace but trapped 3 wide, emptied 350M.
Slow, recovered ground along rail settling four-back from leader. Boxed in top of straight, took split 250m and powered home for close victory.
Bumped after start, settling at rear in one-off position. Switched three-wide back stretch, wide into straight, ran on well while shifting, forcing jockey to stop riding twice.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead to 1600m before slipping into box seat. Came off fence turning for home, picked up speed gradually, doing best work at finish.
Quickly into stride, holding rail two-back from leader passing 1400m. Took closer order turn, got run 400m, looked chance 200m, no extra.
Ridden to hold forward position, initially one-off, one-back, but lost position back stretch and turn. Switched wide entering straight and ran on steadily final 200m.

Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Trailed field into straight before running past tired horses in straight.
Bumped on jumping, no speed and soon at rear but kept wide. Improved position around turn, wide into straight, one-paced.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward from wide draw to join leader 1400m. Took lead on entering straight, kept on well to 200m before fading.
Began well, pressed forward but wide into first turn, ridden to take lead passing 1600m then slowed pace. Collared 300m but boxed on till flattened 150m.
Began fairly, settling towards rear but wide. Improved position entering final turn, swung wide into straight, ran out of steam from 200m.
Ridden to maintain forward position but held three-wide without cover outside leading pair. Gave ground soon after straightening for home.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start and then proved difficult to settling, blundering passing 1800m. Lost position final turn and found nothing in straight.
Held up 2Ls behind leader in a very slowly run race, shifted out 400M, sprinted home strongly under top weight to get up near the line.
Soon led, slowed down the pace passing 1200M, niggled along nearing 200m but unable to shake off pursuing rivals, all out inside 150M but not found extra gear, headed close home.
Tracked leader in a very slowly run race, kept responding under pressure, shifted out inside 100M for clear run, closed off well making good late impression.
Travelled one out one back in a very slowly run race, kept up the chase on leader turning home but was always held.
3Ls back in 6th, 3-wide no cover throughout, crept closer to pace home turn, kept on steadily to line without looking a serious threat in particular over final 100M.

Towards the rear 4Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, failed to pick up as well as the main rivals, never reached contention.
Raced as the rear a little over 4Ls off the slow pace, caught flat-footed when the race got serious 400M, never a threat.

Jumped with field, not pressed settling between horses towards the rear. Entered straight behind a wall of horses, got clear running 200m, finished off well.
Ridden along early to hold rail, three back from leader. Held up momentarily turning for home, got clear halfway up straight and finished off nicely.
Restrained on jumping and switched across behind horses to a one-off position at the rear. Swung wide into straight and ran on steadily under hard riding. (Cut tongue before start)
Began awkwardly, then ridden quietly at the rear. Shifted out 400m but took time to get balanced before gaining momentum, doing best work final stages.
Began only fairly, took time to gain momentum, dropping to rear along the rail. Popped off fence turning for home and ran on steadily in straight under hard riding.
Ridden along to find cover but blocked 900m and left racing three-wide thereafter. One-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader on settling. Kept on strongly to 200m, turning one-paced final stages.
Pushed hard to lead on settling, setting good pace to 200m when overhauled. Lay out under pressure from 200m, while giving ground.
First out before settling in box seat behind leading pair. Lay out stop of straight, steadied 200m when blocked for run, faded.
Began fairly, ridden along between horses before switching to rail four-back from leader. Stayed on rail turn but found nothing in straight when asked.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.

Crowded out start, raced 6 lengths back on rail behind midfield, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made some headway without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back, still 3 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Average to begin, sent forward to race 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, peaked on run early in straight, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced at tail throughout, still last turning in, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, positioned 2-3 lengths behind the leader in 4th, easy run to turn, made no progress in straight, just stayed on one-paced.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in 5th, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 3 wide in midfield, 4-5 lengths back, no cover after 1000M, failed to close off in straight after hard run took effect.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4-5 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Slightly slow out, raced 9 lengths or so back at rear, shared last on turn, made no progress in straight, never competitive.
Began fairly from gate 13, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened thereafter, finished last.
Began well from gate 1, showed early speed to race prominently, shared lead to turn, kicked clear in straight and scored easily.
Average to begin, raced a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, finished off well in straight to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, settled slightly worse than midfield, 2 to 3 wide with cover, similar position turning, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line, just missed 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, settled 4 wide with cover, 3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to make frame.
Began very awkwardly, raced 6 lengths back at tail, still last on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, taken back to race 5 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, taken wide for clear running early in straight and made some progress.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2-3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2-3 lengths back behind midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, just kept on evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail at rear, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced 4-5 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead on turn, weakened early in straight and gradually dropped off.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover throughout, emptied early in straight after hard run took toll.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back in 4th, crowded for room near 500M, emptied early in straight and bumped near 250M.
Away with them, raced 3 wide without cover in 3rd, still no cover on turn, emptied early in straight and dropped off gradually.

Eased at start, took rail, 6Ls off the leader, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Determined to hold the box seat, benefited by the slow pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Crossed steadily in front, led by 1L in 2 wide at slow sectionals, ran on well until 100M flattened.
Pushed forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M, held up and checked badly 100M.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, checked early, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster and cross in front, trapped 3 wide throughout, 2Ls off the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Eased back, checked early, 8Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 100M.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.

Began awkwardly, taken straight to fence four-back from leader. Stayed on rail turn but only one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, ridden along in one-off position towards the rear. Switched out turning for home but only one-paced final 300m.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Took inside run on straightening but held for clear running from 150m to 50m.
Jumped well, racing alongside leader till easing to one-back, one-off position back stretch. Gave ground steadily after passing 400m.

Caught wide from draw 12, eased back to the rear , 10Ls off the pace home turn, made limited progress only over final 300M.
4-wide contesting the lead early stages, shifted to 2-wide spot chasing leaders home turn, weakened away 250M.
Held up behind midfield, gave ground 500M, soon beaten.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing 3-wide till taking lead 1300m and cutting to rail. Kicked clear top of the straight and hung on gamely to the line.
First out, led to turn before slipping into box seat behind leader. Took closer order turning for home, got inside run top of straight, just failed.
Ridden along to maintain forward position, settling three-back, one-off. Urged forward from 500m, picked up momentum final 200m to snatch third placing in blanket finish.
Steadied shortly after start, then hampered entering back stretch, dropping to behind midfield along rail. Switched out top of straight and finished off strongly to just miss a place.
Ridden along wide before settling outside leader entering back stretch. Looked chance on straightening, kept on well till flattened final stages.

Began well but got close to heels 1300m, then over-raced entering back stretch before settling three-back along rail. Took inside run top of straight but forced to switch out 200m for run. Raced tight final stages.
Began awkwardly, settling at rear, then hampered entering back stretch. Switched wide on straightening and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Ridden along early but failed to muster, settling between horses five-back from leader. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Fractious before start but passed fit to run. Began fairly, ridden along wide to make up ground, settling behind midfield. Switched out wider in straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward but held 3-wide without cover entering back stretch. Took closer order final turn, kept on well to 200m before tiring.

Shifted across behind runners from wide draw but unable get cover and dragged back toward rear. Raced keenly first turn, ridden along back stretch to hold position, found little in straight. Unacceptable performance.
Slow into stride, shifted across behind horses, settling last. Never competitive.
