Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths back on rail in 5th, easy run to turn, finished off well in straight and scored easily.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to get 2nd.
Jumped well, took the lead easily and set a moderate tempo, kept on well after turning in but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 4-5 lengths back behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, found cover near 1200M, travelled well to turn, ridden near 600M, peaked early in straight, just stayed on evenly in straight.
Moderately away from gate 10, unable to slot in, raced 3-4 wide without cover in midfield, found cover after 1300M, still 3 wide on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 8 lengths back at tail, difficult to settle after 1100M, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and made reasonable headway to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 6-7 lengths back at rear, still 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and closed off one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back at rear, similar position to turn, angled out in straight and finished off one-paced.
Began well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 1-2 lengths back, still no cover on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.

Began with them, awkwardly placed and shifted in abruptly near 1700m, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, no clear running near 300M, was a beaten horse thereafter.
Slow to begin, recovered to race in midfield, sent forward near 1400M to race in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, crowded for room and became badly unbalanced near 1700M, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight and eased.
Jumped well and settled behind leader on rails, eased outwards home turn and challenged strongly before gaining upper hand final 100m to draw away.
Commenced awkwardly and ridden along from wide gate to sit outside leader, travelled strongly to hit the front at the 200m before overpowered final 100m.
Settled midfield on the rail and travelled easily, stayed to the inside turning form home and made good steady ground all the way to the line.
Flew out of the gates to lead, travelled well in front and fought on well when challenged in the straight before weakening over final 100m.
Jumped awkwardly and then urged forward from wide gate to settle on pace with cover, asked for effort on straightening but unable to quicken, battled to the line.
Commenced awkwardly and settled towards rear, improved along rail mid race but one paced to the line.
Settled midfield and travelled well, shifted wide on straightening but failed to run on
Slow to jump and lost ground (4l), pushed along to eventually tack onto the field at the 500m and ran on gamely in the straight.
Settled at rear, urged along passing the 600m but unable to make ground in the straight.
Raced wide without cover in a midfield position and was unable to make ground in the straight.
No early pace and under pressure to stay in touch with the field, made no ground in the straight.
Settled midfield with cover, under pressure from the 600m to hold position and gradually gave ground thereafter.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, enjoyed the fast pace, ran on strongly to score by 2Ls.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast pace, hung on strongly until 150M headed by the winner.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on steadily for 3rd.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, ran on steadily.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, settled 6Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, hampered by the fast pace, weakened 300M.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast tempo, one paced home.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
At rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, kept on until 250M weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 4Ls off the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, dropped off soon after straightening.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Tardy start, mustered & speed to press lead 1060m, restrained to handy 1 off with cover, angled out final turn, ridden to lead 250m, fought on gamely.
Fast break, sat handy 1 back on rail, in pocket 1L back final turn, shaken up 300m, quickened to close, just held at wire.
Restrained, crossed to sit rail midfield, shifted out 430m, ridden & switched centre 300m, ran on to nick 3rd under strong drive.
Speed to lead wide & rousted early, headed 1060m, sat 2nd 1 off, ranged upside leader final turn, shaken up to lead 360m, all out & headed 250m, tapered out.
Broke well, snagged & sat 3 wide with cover midfield, driven 450m & shifted out, ran on soundly to just miss frame.
Smart start, soon driven, shuffled back to midfield 1 off, switched out 430m, crowded & not clear run 400m, out-paced, hard-ridden for gradual headway.
Missed break, settled rail behind midfield, shifted out & driven into stretch, lacked pace, stayed on moderately.
Fast break, led 1060m & soon to rail, pressed home turn, headed & driven 360m but one-paced, weakened in run.
Taken back at start, over-raced 1000m, raced behind midfield 1 off, niggled 700m, shifted out under drive 430m, plugged on evenly.
Slow break & rousted, caught wide no cover behind midfield, very wide final turn & driven 430m, kept on moderately.
Slow start & scrubbed along 2nd last, kept on same speed for gradual late inroads.
Missed break & raced wide at tail, niggled along on turn, detached & driven into stretch, plugged centre track to pass beaten rivals close home.
Moderate start, rolled to sit handy 3 wide with cover, posted 4 wide & ridden turning in, soon emptied & weakened tamely.
Awkward start widest, rolled forward & slotted midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out 430m & driven, found little in tepid stretch run.
Broke well, edged lead on outer 850m, headed 750m & hung in, sat 2L 2nd, ridden in pursuit 350m, quickened to lead 150m, all out to hold on at line.
Stumbled start & raced near tail 1 odd, progress & shifted wide 600m, 4.5L back & driven wide into stretch, rattled home, just failed.
Fast start, led rail, headed 850m, impeded 700m, snatched up & lost ground, 3L 3rd & shifted 1 off 500m, shaken up 400m, outpaced, kept on to nick 3rd.
Sharp start widest, driven to lead 750m & crossed sharply to rail, 2L clear & driven 350m, all out & tapering when headed 150m, lost 3rd last stride.
Moderate break, niggled midfield 1 off, checked to 3 wide 700m, advanced on turn, 3rd & driven top of stretch, emptied 200m & tapered.
Broke OK & bustled initially, sat handy on rail, impeded 700m & checked to 1 off, lost ground & near rear 500m, solid closer for late inroads.
Taken back at break, raced wide near rear, forced very wide exiting backstretch, driven turning in, plugged on moderately.
Slow break & raced last pair on outer, driven into final turn, kept on for minor late headway.
Broke well, rousted to be handy early, soon outpaced & ridden along fore of midfield 1 off, under pump 500m & shuffled back, one-paced in run home.
Moderate start & niggled early, slotted rail midfield, driven 400m, one-paced & tapered late.
Broke OK, lacked early pace & soon at rear on inner, chased along on turn, found little in tame stretch run.
Eased to sit 3 back on the fence, 3Ls off the good pace, held up 400M, progressed steadily when clear and scored.
Settled in midfield, 5Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear and finished 2nd.
Slow away, hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls, pace good, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased back, 8Ls off the good pace 2-4 wide, progressed steadily around the field 400M, run ended 100M.
At back, 7Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, lack room 400M, ran on ok when clear.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 8Ls off the good pace, made ground 300M, lack room final 200M, not properly tested.
Slow away and bumped, 7Ls off the good pace on the fence, made ground 300M, held up final 200M, not fully tested.
Pushed early but not muster, 4Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, no progress.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace, just held ground in straight.
Pressed forward, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, flattened 200M.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, reduced 250M.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on only fairly.
Jumped with field, eased, drifting back to second-last. Made forward move 750m but taken wide and switched back in. Taken wide in straight, swooped around field to lead 200m, pulled clear.
Ridden to hold forward position settling one-back, one-off. Began forward move on straightening, hit front 300m, run down 200m but kept on well while shifting in under pressure.
Began well, settling in box seat behind leader. Unable get run top of straight and awkward on heels till getting clear 200m. Finished off nicely.
One of the first into stride but not pushed, settling outside leader. Looked chance on straightening, led passing 300m, one-paced final 200m.
Jumped well but eased and switched across behind runners, settling last. Made forward mover passing 500m, no clear run early in straight, kept on fairly when clear.
Allowed to stride out at own pace, settling behind midfield along the rail. No clear run top of straight but only one-paced when clear.
Made full use of inside draw to led on settling. Set steady pace until caught 300m. Gave ground gradually.
Settled towards rear in a one-off position. Began forward move 700m, looked a chance entering straight before run ended 300m and faded.
Settled down behind mid-division, travelled smoothly throughout, crept closer home turn and 3Ls behind leader at 400M, ran on well to lead nearing 100M, well in control final stages.
3-4Ls back behind leaders, not much room early straight, did best work final 200M, nearest finish.
Began only fairly, held up near last 7Ls off the pace, made good progress final 400M, got up for 3rd just in time.
Tracked leaders, held up near 200M, continued on well final stages down inner, just missed 3rd in a blanket finish.
Towards the rear early, checked 950M and shifted to a 3-wide position without cover, made his move over the turn to join leaders 500M, dueled to 100M, just edged out of frame last strides.
Sent forward and crossed to race 2-wide just off the lead, led narrowly from 250M, headed 100M, run ended and weakened towards finish.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, switched out passing 600M, ran on steadily, not beaten far.
Settled at the back 8-9Ls behind leader, kept to inside on straightening, no clear run at crucial stage from 300M-100M, should finish closer.
In mid-division along the 2-path, shifted out 550M to improve, ran on same pace, no threat final 150M.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled down 8Ls off the pace in the rear, took outside route passing 600M, made some progress without threatening.
Settled down behind midfield, shuffled back to near the rear approaching home straight, not quickened when asked, no impression on leaders.
Chased leader, travelled keenly passing 1000M, outdashed early straight, checked 200M and eased.
Sent forward and crossed to the lead 1200M, slowed down pace in middle stages, headed 250M, faded and checked 150M, eased.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, ridden along between horses three-back from leader. Got clear run 400m, rolled forward to lead 200m, kept on well and held off late challenge.
Bumped, badly unbalanced start, ridden to make up ground settling in box seat by turn. No clear run till passing 200m, finished off strongly.
Began fairly, ridden along to hold one-off position behind midfield. Switched out turning for home, got run 350m, finished strongly.
First out, headed passing 1000m but retook lead 800m. Joint leader around turn and until collared 200m, kept on well till flattened 50m.
Began fairly, recovered, pressed forward from wide draw to lead passing 1000m. Headed temporarily 800m, joint leader turn, collared 200m but kept on well till flattened 50m.
Got off OK, soon on rail improving position to be three-back turning for home. No clear run early in straight, but kept on fairly when clear.
Severely checked on jumping, dropping to second-last. Still well back turning for home, switched out in straight and made some late ground.
Bumped from behind soon after start and badly unbalanced. Made up ground along rail. Got inside run in straight, looked chance 200m, got close to heels concluding stages and not fully tested.
Pressed forward to obtain forward position, settling 3-back from leader but wide without cover. Kept on fairly to 200m when tired.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw but held three-wide towards the rear. Covered extra ground turning for home and one-paced in straight.
Ridden along to maintain forward position, but raced keenly from 800m to 600m before settling in midfield. Taken very wide into straight but found little under hard riding.
Began OK, not pushed, settling behind midfield. Took inside run on straightening but blocked for run till 150m and then hampered 100m.
Pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward entering straight to look chance passing 300m but tired soon after and faded.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Entered straight behind wall of horses and dragged back when denied run from 200m to 100m.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score easily.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind the midfield, similar position on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off well to get 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, made good progress in straight to get 3rd.

Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter, just barely held 4th. (Saddle shifted near 1400M)
Bumped on jumping, taken back to race 7-8 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back at rear, still 3 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress without threatening.

Began awkwardly, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, bumped a few times near 1000M, carried wider on turn, last turning in, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 6-7 lengths back at rear, bumped a few times near 1000M, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to race 2 wide, 2-3 lengths back in 4th, same position on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no clear running until after 150M, closed off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1400M to race in 2nd, there to turn, emptied early in straight and dropped off gradually.
Began well from a tricky draw, raced 3 wide with some cover, 3-4 lengths back in midfield, no cover after 1000M, emptied after turning in and eased, unacceptable performance. (See racing incidents)

Slightly slow out, settled just off the pace mostly in 5th far side and 4th just over 2L off around the bend, fought on under pressure to gain upper hand final strides.
Slightly slow to begin from the one draw before gaining narrow advantage shortly, held same to the straight before worn down close to home.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved a lot of ground turning in, angled off rails for a run entering straight, nearest at finish.
Settled towards the rear, commenced move entering straight, sustained steady progress down the straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well, niggled along outside the leader, gave ground steadily after straightening.
Taken across for rails run at the back, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Carried backward early stages, travelled behind midfield on rails, saved ground turning for home, ran home one-paced.
Raced keenly in midfield, shuffled back towards the rear entering straight, kept on same pace in the run home.
Began well, travelled 3-wide and one back in 4th to straight, soon faded.
Broke well from a poor gate, travelled prominently but wide without cover, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Settled well behind from the widest gate, never a factor. (Blood in trachea)
Sluggish at start, quickly recovered to forward of midfield but soon dropped back to last few before the Rock, carried wide into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Jumped well, pushed forward to settle outside leader, asked for effort on straightening and fought hard entire length of straight before gaining upper hand late.
Driven hard early to hold rail and lead, held together home turn, challenged at 300m and fought right to the line to just miss.
Jumped well, pushed along early before taking sit behind leaders, hung out near 900m, tried to challenge on straightening but could not run down leaders.
Bumped at start, settle just off pace, travelled well home turn but could not quicken and held position to the line.
Crowded at start and settled midfield, could not make ground in straight but held position.
Eased back from wide gate to settle worse than midfield, hampered when swung wide on straightening, made steady ground to the finish.
Jumped awkwardly and subsequently settled towards the rear, travelled well but only battled to line.
Slow out and settled near the rear, pushed along home turn, stuck to the rails and made steady ground to the line.
Jumped awkwardly and settled at rear, travelled well into home turn, widest on straightening and made some ground in straight.
Pushed hard early to hold midfield position, ridden along mid race to hold position, under pressure home turn, one paced in straight.
Raced wide without cover throughout, hung outwards on straightening and did not run on.
Settled midfield, hampered on straightening, never in it.
Camped handy, 8.5Ls behind the fast leading pair 2 wide without cover, enjoy the fast tempo, led 400M, hung on well to score by a neck.
Prominent, 9Ls behind the fast leading pair on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, held up rounding the Home Turn, dashed strongly when clear, just missed by a neck.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Raced midfield, 12Ls behind the fast leading pair 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, switched wide turning in, ran on strongly for 4th.
Camped handy, 10Ls behind the fast leading pair 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, ran on steadily until final 50M weakened.
At rear, 15.5Ls behind the fast leading pair on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 13Ls behind the fast leading pair on the fence, despite the fast pace, ran on only fairly.
At rear, 14Ls behind the fast leading pair 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, 11Ls behind the fast leading pair 2 wide with cover, despite the fast sectionals, never looked likely.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by fast sectionals, surged 8Ls clear the field 900M, weakened 200M.
Settled worse than midfield 13Ls behind the fast leading pair 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, never ran on.
Pressed forward to follow the leader, surged 6Ls clear the field 900M, flattened badly 500M, tailed out.
Broke well & rousted, settled midfield 1 off, switched wide 400m & driven, quickened in 3-way tussle to edge lead 50m, just held on.
Speed to press early lead on rail, headed 1020m, settled 1 back on fence, shifted out 300m, bumped 220m, in clear & driven 200m, surged in 3-way battle to wire, just failed.
Broke OK, snagged to race behind midfield, taken very wide home turn & driven, ran on in 3-way battle, held at wire.
Fast start & driven 4 deep to edge lead 1020m, headed 850m & sat close 2nd 1 off, shaken up 250m to 1L lead, soon all out, emptied 50m & swamped.
Taken back at start, 2nd last & niggled 850m, switched out & driven 300m, hung awkwardly but kept on for minor inroads.
Broke OK, driven mid rank, advanced 800m to sit handy 3 deep no cover, under pump 500m, all out turning in, faded in run.
Speed & rousted to lead, headed 1020m, settled 1 back 1 off, shifted out & driven 300m, bumped 220m, outpaced & tapered late.
Slow start & bumped, taken to rail & rolled to midfield, behind horses turning in, shifted out & shaken up 200m, kept on evenly.
Outpaced & soon at tail, niggled long on rail, driven into stretch, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Good break, rousted to press lead 3 deep, led 850m & crossed to rail, driven 300m but emptied & faded out.
Taken back from widest, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m, widest final turn & driven, found nothing in tame run home.
Fast break & driven early to sit close-up 1 off, settled 4th 1 off with cover after 1000m, switched 3 deep 350m & shaken up, edged lead 250m, extended clear.
Broke OK but outpaced, bustled early & sat rail midfield, ridden under pressure final turn, shifted out 300m & driven, dug deep to edge 2nd at wire.
Smart start but bumped, sat midfield 1 off with cover, hard-ridden turning in & shifted out, battled to 2nd 150m, tapered final 50m & lost 2nd at wire.
Sharp start, stalked 1 back on rail, stuck in pocket & checked off heels 270m, bumped & lost ground, ran on last 150m.
Speed to race handy 3 wide, rolled to 2nd 1 off 1000m, driven to press lead turning in, soon emptied & tapered final 200m.
smart start, taken back to sit midfield 3 wide with cover, shaken up turning in, boxed on one pace.
Missed break, rousted early & sat rail near rear, bumped fence 870m, driven 320m, outpaced & switched out 300m, stayed on dourly for minor headway.
Snagged start to last, 1 off & checked 1480m, raced last pair & edged 1off 820m for gradual minor advance, driven wide 420m, stayed on for modest inroads.
Speed to lead, set tempo on rail, driven under pressure 300m, headed 250m & no extra, weakened in run.
Broke OK, taken back to 3 deep with cover near rear, slotted 1 off last pair 1100m, to tail & ridden 600m, plodded on one pace.
Began well from a wide gate, slotted midfield 3 wide with cover, lost cover 1000m, driven turning in, found nil & faded.
Smart start, soon snagged to 1 off near tail, lit up & keen, shifted 3 deep into backstretch & continued to over-race, very wide on turn, found nil, tailed off.
Pushed forward, settled 3Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, made early move 500M to take advantages of the slow pace, drifted away 200M to score.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, illustrated strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased at start, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 300M.
Checked start, 6.5Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to cross in front, just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the slow sectionals, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, just held ground when clear.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight, ran on fairly.
Took rail easily and led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 250M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, soon reduced 300M.
At back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, faded quickly 400M.

Bumped start and then crowded. Ridden along to make up ground, settling one-back, one-off around turn. Swung very wide and lost position entering straight, picked up momentum from 200m to win on the line.
Pressed forward to lead on settling. Set good pace, kicked clear 300m and looked the winner before drifting out under pressure and caught on the line.
Began OK, not much speed, ridden along between horses at the rear. Unable to get run top of straight, switched out to centre track, stormed home to just miss.
Ridden along to hold rail three-back from leader. Taken wide entering straight and battled on gamely to be closest at finish.
Began well, ridden along to hold box seat turning into back stretch. Look chance on straightening but unable keep up final 200m.
Crowded out on jumping and then steadied entering back stretch, dropping 4-back from leader. Took inside run in straight and closed in steadily without looking dangerous.
Began OK, raced keenly before settling three-back, one-off. Took inside run on straightening and kept on steadily to the line.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Took rails run around turn and kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
One of the first into stride, ridden along in a one-off position about 1.5L from leader. Started to give ground soon after straightening.
Ridden along early but unable find cover and held three-wide without cover back stretch. Lost position home turn and found nothing in straight despite late reminders.
Began fairly, raced keenly back stretch, switched out at turn for run but forced to steady 600m. One-paced in straight.
Bumped start, ridden along in one-off position at the rear before dropping to last final turn. Found nothing under pressure.
Settled behind midfield but unable to get closer than 3-wide, wide bid 550M and leaders in sight turning home, quickened well down the center, hit lead 150M, won readily.
Began well from draw 1, restrained to sit in midfield 4Ls off the pace, saved ground to straight, picked up well and looked a possible chance mid-straight, not winner's pace final stages.
Caught 3-wide no cover on jumping from 11, never far off from leaders, moved up to join leaders 400M, briefly led 250M but soon collared by winner, turned one pace final stages.
Settled down in midfield along the 2-path, shifted out for clear run 350M, ran on steadily for moderate 4th.
Held up near the rear, 6Ls off leaders in middle stages, wide bid 500M, stayed on over final 300M but no serious threat to leaders.
Tracked leaders along the fence, held up a bit nearing the top of the straight, responded well early straight and briefly went 4th 200M, run ended passing 100M.
Not hurried early and middle stages, reserved behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, took inside route in straight but held up near 300M, stayed on same pace when clear.
Soon guided to the fence then settled down behind mid-division, waited with till 300M but not picked up pace to challenge.
Up with early pace, settled 2-wide chasing leaders from 1300M, pushed along 400M but was gradually outpaced, no extra 150M.
Switched off to last, 8Ls off the pace in middle stages, bid wide near 400M but lacked the necessary response, ran past well beaten runners only.
Pushed forward, raced outside leader from 1300M, took narrow lead 400M but failed to sustain effort, beaten inside 300M.
Sent forward, slowed down the pace once obtained the lead passing 1300M, emptied passing 300M, first to be beaten.

Began well, pressed forward but held three wide first turn. Rolled forward passing 1050m to hold third but still wide. Swung wide and lost position entering straight before picking up momentum to finish strongly.
Quickly into stride, settling one-back, one-off. Made forward move passing 400m, picked up momentum from 200m, hit front momentarily before run down on post.
Jumped well, held rail and pushed forward to settle three-back from leader. Lost position slightly around turn, took inside run in straight and battled gamely to the post.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit on hind quarters of leader. Rolled forward to lead entering straight, still in front 200m, fattened final 50m.
Found the lead quickly without much effort and set steady pace. Collared on entering straight but kept on one-paced.
Began well, grabbing box seat on settling. Took inside run on straightening and kept on steadily without looking a threat.
Jumped with field but no early pace, settling behind midfield and away from fence. Turned a little wide but only one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early to hold position four-back from leader and away from fence. Improved position around turn but only one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Crowded shortly after start, then hampered at first turn, dropping to rear but away from fence. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Began OK, holding midfield position along rail but got dragged back gradually as others moved forward. One-pace in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, then hampered passing 1100m, dropping to last. Never competitive.
Crowded out soon after start, shifted out 1100m losing ground. Proved difficult to settle middle stages and dropped to last home turn. Never competitive.

Jumped well, settled in midfield one off the rails but racing keenly at times far side, came closer turning into straight, fought on well to assert authority close to home.

Wide in midfield early stages, moved up to lead turning into far side setting up a healthy break with fast sectionals, still in the clear turning into home straight and only to be collared final strides.
Broke well from the middle gate, gradually moved up to hold 2nd spot 2-wide about 3L off the speed far side, similar turning in, kept on but lost 2nd under pressure 200 metres out.
Taken back from a wide gate and waited with, ran on well down the centre of the track inside final 250 metres.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Slow to muster, gradually settled in midfield or slightly worse on rails, commenced move entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Travelled in last few, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on steadily without quickening and awkwardly placed behind runners closing stages.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in 4th, 4 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Niggled at from a poor gate in midfield, took closer order in 5th turning into back straight, came under pressure around home bend, gradually faded.
Moderate start from a poor draw, raced wide and never better than midfield to straight, ran home one-paced.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Mainly in midfield, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Lame next day)
Driven to the front before ceding advantage for 3L 3rd on rails far side, came under pressure rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Settled wide in rear from a poor draw, dropped to tail-end coming out of far side, never recovered.
Settled off pace on outside rail, travelled strong waiting for a run from 400m, obtained run passing 200m and finished strongly to win well.
Urged early to hold position, settled midfield, challenged strongly at 300m but could not match winner.
Settled towards rear, commenced to pick up passing 400m gradually warming into it, flew final 100m.
Jumped well, taken across behind runners to settle worse than mid, and travelled easily into race near 300m, clipped heels when angling for a run passing 300m, finished off OK.
Jumped awkwardly but recovered quickly to race with leader on outside rail, challenged and took lead passing 400m, lay in when under pressure near 200m, battled to the post.
Pushed early to hold position settling just off pace, niggled at 500, couldn't quicken at 300m and battled to line.
Eased across behind the field to settle at rear, commenced to pick up near 400m and ran home OK towards the inside of track.
Jumped awkwardly but then sped thru to lead, held together mid race but failed to respond when challenged near the 400m and weakened out of it final 100m.
Jumped well, settled midfield towards centre, hampered at 300m, one paced to the line.
Commenced awkwardly and allowed to settle at rear, travelled easy and asked to extend at 400m, pushed along but didn't pick up until near 100m and finished off OK - rider questioned
Pushed along early but no pace, settled mid, and couldn't make ground when placed under pressure final 300m.
Showed speed to settle off pace, under pressure from 400m, hampered near 300m, gave ground to the finish.
Jumped OK, showed pace to travel on speed, under pressure passing 500m and commenced to give ground, eased down final 150m - Rider & Trainer questioned – must trial
Raced 3-wide at midfield. 4-wide and travelling nicely rounding home turn. Quickened nicely when asked and sealed the race after running down the early leader final 150M.
Nicely box-seated behind the lead. Kept on nicely in the straight but never a threat to the winner.
Ridden early and took the lead 1st turn. Maintained advantage deep into the home straight but was caught final 150M. Held on for a minor placing.
Dropped back from wide draw and went for the rails. Settled behind midfield. Gradually switched out rounding home turn and rallied in the straight to be closest at the line.
Raced along the rails at midfield. 2Ls off the lead turning for home. Gradually made up ground but unable to get clear run final stages.
Among early leaders. Settle 2-wide behind the pace back straight. Did not quicken in the straight and remained same pace to finish.
Soon trailed field. Saved ground making home turn and closed off fairly.
Jumped awkwardly and raced towards the rear. Remained towards the back home turn and was held up for prior to and after straightening. Steered clear 300M and made up some late ground.
Widest into 1st turn and niggle forward to race 3-wide and just off the pace. Faded shortly after straightening.
Caught wide into 1st turn and was ridden forward to race outside the lead. 2-wide in the lead back straight. Unable to keep pace rounding home turn and dropped out shortly after.
Outpaced early and settled towards the rear. Pressured at 600M but never quickened. Last to turn in and only ran past beaten ones.
2-wide and no better than midfield. Pressured to keep pace rounding home turn but no response. No improvement in the straight.
Settled 3-wide and no better than midfield. Hung out and widest making turn home turn. Near last on straightening and no impression thereafter.
Caught wide among early leaders. Slipped to midfield and remained wide no cover thereafter. Dropped out shortly after straightening.
Smart start, slotted rail fore of midfield, shaken up & shifted off fence 400m, good progress & back to rail 200m, battled to lead final strides.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 1200m, shuffled to 1 back 750m, shifted 1 off 540m & cruised to lead 420m, soon shaken up & pressed, tapered late & headed close home.
Good break, sat 1 back on rail until shuffled back a spot 750m, shifted out 400m & driven to press lead, fought on but no extra late.
Prominent early, taken back fore of midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in & shifted out, stayed on evenly.
Taken back from wide gate, sat near tail 1 off with cover, shifted wider turning in, 5L back & shaken up 400m, quickened to close, hung in 150m, flattened out to wire.
Missed break, soon closed to race at tail, 5L back & ridden final turn, closed for minor inroads.
Taken back from widest gate, sat near tail 3 deep with cover, driven very wide into stretch, plugged on for minor headway.
Taken back at start to 3 deep with cover behind midfield, advanced 700m, 5 wide & driven 520m, one-paced to wire.
Slow start, camped rail behind midfield, shuffled back on turn, shifted off fence 430m & driven, minor progress to 200m, tapered thereafter.
Fast start & vied for lead 3 deep, settled 1 back 1 off 1100m, lost cover 750m & soon niggled, pushed 3 deep 540m & driven, all out 300m, weakened in run.
Broke OK & niggled, caught 4 wide no cover behind midfield, minor advance 700m, 6 deep turning in & driven, emptied 300m & faded.
Broke OK, checked off heels 1050m & settled midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled back on turn & ridden 500m, found little in tame run home.
Fast break, caught 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, bustled along 800m, some progress on turn & driven 4 wide into stretch, struggled & faded.
Broke well & bustled to lead 1200m 1 off, rolled 1L clear & to rail 750m, pressed on turn & headed 420m, faded tamely & eased.
Broke well widest, niggled 3 deep & settled handy no cover, driven out 400m & quickened to lead 300m, lay in a touch but soon on even keel, forged clear.
Missed break & disputed lead, to rail 1300m & settled 1 back, driven to share lead 400m, headed 300m, fought on evenly but well held.
Broke well, sat handy 1 off with cover, driven turning in, switched out 380m, closed gradually to nick 3rd late.
Sharp start wide, outright lead 1400m, to rail 1150m, pressed on outer 400m, headed & driven 300m, one-paced & lost 3rd late.
Broke well & disputed lead, to rail 1300m & settled 1 back, driven 400m, & shifted out, tapped for toe, boxed on evenly.
Tardy start, raced 3 deep with cover midfield, niggled 600m, ridden 400m, stayed on one pace.
Sluggish start & driven to race rail behind midfield, checked off heels 950m & shuffled back, last turning in, hard-ridden 350m, kept on past beaten rivals.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, shifted 1 off 950m, driven 400m, one-paced to wire.
Broke OK, rousted to race rail midfield, niggled 600m, ridden 400m, stayed on one pace.
Broke moderately, driven & mustered to snag rail handy, checked off heels 840m, shuffled back a touch & over-raced, driven 400m, plodded on tepidly.
Snagged back from wide to tail, 2nd last 1200m & fought for head 3 deep with cover, pushed 4 wide no cover on turn, never settled, driven 400m, plodded on.
Started wide, taken back to near rear 3 deep, soon slotted 1 off until pushed 3 deep 950m, found little in tame run home.
Sharp break, rousted & soon outpaced, settled 1 off with cover midfield, driven into stretch, found nil & struggled.
Tardy start & taken back, soon niggled in rear, to tail 1150m, taken very wide on turn & driven, struggled in run.
Midfield, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, held up and shuffled backwards 500-300M, dashed strongly when clear and scored.
Eased back, 8.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, dashed strongly 400M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 10Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed its impressive finishing efforts 200M.
Sat in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, made early move 600M to take advantages of the slow tempo, dashed well until 150M, run ended.
Settled in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the slow pace along the fence, saved considerable amount of ground at the home bends, closed off strongly 400M, run ended 100M.
Trapped very wide in midfield early, pushed forward to get closer to the fence, ended up in the lead, clocked slow sectionals, flattened 250M.
Eased back, 10Ls off the leader, trapped 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, commenced to finish off strongly 550M, run ended 150M.
Eased back, 8.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Checked start, 8.5Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Settled 3Ls off the leader, made early move 600M in 3 wide to take advantages of the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 10Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, illustrated some dash in straight.
Behind midfield along the fence, 7Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the slow sectionals, reduced quickly 400M.
Bumped shortly after start, ridden to make up ground settling three back, the fence. Switched out entering straight, rolled forward to hit front 200m, kept on well to line.
Ridden along to hold forward position, settling one-off, one-back. Began forward move entering straight, joint leader 200m, battled but unable hold off winner final stages.
Jumped with field, not much speed drifting four-back, one-off. Switched 3-wide final turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Pushed forward to sit outside leader back stretch. Eye-balled leader around turn, kept on well in straight until flattened final stages.
Began best, set good pace to 200m when caught and weakened gradually.
Not much speed, settling between horses toward the rear. Took closer order turning for home and kept on fairly in the straight without looking dangerous.
Bumped start, hard ridden to get box seat but then over-raced. Tired soon after straightening and faded gradually.
Ridden forward from outside draw but held 3-wide behind midfield and without cover. Taken even wider in straight by inside horses and one-paced final 200m.
Shifted across behind horses shortly after the start, settling in one-off position at the rear. Never really competitive though made up some late ground in straight.
Ridden along early to hold position three-back, one-off. Made forward move turning for home but only one-paced final 200m when hampered and taken wider concluding stages.
Blundered at start, taken across behind runners and last on settling. Found little in straight under hard riding.
Began awkwardly, ridden along 3-wide to make up ground, hung out 700m losing considerable ground. Tailed off.
Held up at rear 4Ls off the pace, responded well passing halfway, came from near last with an irresistible challenge, got up near line.
Soon led along the stand's rail and took time along at good pace, kept on strongly under light weight only caught by fast finishing winner near line.
Began awkwardly, 2Ls back chasing leaders, switched to the rails near 300M for his run, closed well but raced in restricted room final 100M, would have been closer.
Towards the rear early stages, crept closer nearing halfway mark, ran on steadily for modest 4th.
Reserved in midfield along the stand's side, took time to get going over this shorter trip, ran on well final stages making good late impression.
Tracked the pace, loomed outside leader inside 400M but failed to sustain his run passing 200M.
Never far off from the pace but found just the same pace once let down, not reached leaders.
Raced handily just off the good early pace, lacked the necessary response when urged along passing halfway, kept on same speed to the finish.
Sent forward pressing the pace but found little off the bridle, faded out of contention 250M.
Held his position in mid-division throughout but could not find much to challenge leaders. (Jockey reported breathing issues may have attributed to the horse's poor performance)
Raced keenly early stages, settled down near the rear 4Ls off the pace, not picked up and left behind passing 400M.
Settled down behind midfield towards the center of track, badly outpaced from midway, eased when well beaten.
Niggled along to stay in touch, badly outpaced midway, soon beaten.
In mid-division towards the center of track, outpaced halfway, weakened to last.
Began OK, ridden to hold fence in midfield, and taken out 500m but pushed back in and pocketed by outside horses. Found inside run 300m and battled strongly to win on the line.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling behind midfield. Got close to heels 1000m, held for run early in straight, shifted in 350m for run and battled strongly to line to just fail.
Began fairly, racing two and three wide at rear. Taken wider around turn and even wider in straight. Finished strongly down centre track to just fail.
Pressed forward early before getting close to heels 1000m. Urged forward around turn, hit front soon after straightening, looked winner 200m before run down close to line.
Aggressively ridden from wide draw but failed to muster and caught three-wide in midfield. Lost position turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off strongly.
Beaten for early speed, settling toward rear but away from fence. Improved position turn, found inside run soon after straightening and finished off nicely.
Ridden forward to hold position three-back, one-off. Urged forward turning for home, looked chance 200m, tired final stages.
Began fairly and last on settling. Still last entering straight before picking up momentum, doing best work final 200m.
Slow into stride, settling toward rear along the fence. Kept on rail by outside horses on entering straight and plodded to the line. (Jockey reported horse prefers outside run).
Pressed forward from wide draw to hold position one-back, one-off. Rolled forward entering straight to lead 400m, still in contention 200m before weakening.
Began best, then raced outside leader before easing back two-off but wide and without cover. Bumped and unbalanced 900m, wide turn, plodded to line. Lame right front leg.
Ridden along from inside draw to hold box seat to straight. Held up behind tiring horse 350m, shifted out 300m but found little and faded.
Ridden along from wide draw and held behind midfield to 600m when got close to heels. Unbalanced turn, found little in straight.
Hard ridden to get to the front and set very fast times for two quarters. Caught shortly before entering straight and faded.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to score.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 5 lengths back at rear, there to turn, no daylight until near 250M, finished off well to get 3rd.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back in 5th, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, just stayed on to get 4th.

Moderately away from the widest gate, unable to slot in early, steadied to obtain cover near 1000M, positioned 3 wide, 5 lengths back at rear on turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress to be closest at finish.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back in midfield, still 3 wide on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 7 lengths back at rear, well back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running until after 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began well, showed early speed to race prominently, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight and gradually weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned a length back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off one-paced in straight, never a threat.
Began well from a wide gate, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight after hard run took effect. (See racing incidents)
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover throughout, weakened gradually after turning in, never a threat.
Crowded out start, raced 6 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, shared lead to turn, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter and eased final 100M.

Broke well, settled 2-back on rails just better than midfield, quickened well to lead 150 metres out, won readily.

Tightened shortly after start, settled towards the rear on rails shuffling back to last approaching home turn, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off race well inside final 200 metres under hard driving.
Settled in last few from a wide draw, commenced move entering straight, ran on under pressure while shifting ground, nearest at finish.
Jumped well, settled mainly in midfield on rails, carried backward by runners at the Rock, saved ground turning in, produced good late finish inside final 200 metres.
Waited with, widest runner turning in, ran on well down the centre of the straight but inconvenienced by eventual third throughout.
Broke well settling one back on rails, held same into straight, inconvenienced passing the 200 metres, kept on same pace.
Settled towards the rear, came closer when pace slackened down far side, fought on steadily from wide in midfield into straight but never threatening.
Jumped moderately, circled the leading trio passing the winning post the first time, steadied pace once in front near the 1000 metres, headed under pressure 150 metres out.
Settled in midfield, slightly worse around home bend, kept on same pace under pressure in the run home.
Shared early pace 3-wide after beginning from the widest draw, taken back to one-out-two-back position rounding stables bend, remained similar turning into home straight, ran home one-paced.
Began from a poor draw searching for a close-up position near rails settling outside the leader far side, came under pressure turning in, one-paced when hampered 200 metres out, never recovered.

Restrained to 3-wide behind midfield after beginning from the middle gates, continued to travel without cover down far side but gaining closer, came under pressure approaching home straight, dropped out tamely. (Questioned)
Bumped at 800 and then raced wide without cover in midfield position, travelled easy into home turn and made strong challenge at 200m before gaining control final 100m.
Jumped well from outside gate before being eased back near 700m to obtain cover, switched to inside on straightening, checkered run, hit line strongly once clear.
Driven hard early to sit outside leader, travelled strongly, hit lead near 200m but unable to match winner.
Crowded at start before speeding thru to lead, held together home turn, under pressure when challenged at 200m, battled to the line.
Jumped well before being eased back to take a sit midfield, revved up passing 500m, swung wide home turn and ran home well enough in straight.
Crowded at start, pushed along to settle behind leaders, unable to quicken in straight and battled one paced to line.
Crowded at start, hampered passing 900, pushed along to settle forward of mid, behind leaders home turn and gradually weakened out of it in straight.
Eased back from wide gate to settle towards rear, improved along inside to make some ground approaching home turn and held position in run to the line.
Eased back at the start, steadied near 700m, widest on straightening but could not make ground.
Pushed along to hold the rail and settle midfield, immediately under pressure in straight and dropped out of it.
No early pace and did not make any ground in straight.
Bumped at start, hampered near 900m before eased back to settle midfield, gradually gave ground in straight.
Jumped well and had the early lead. Settled towards midfield back straight. 2Ls off making home turn. Ran on well in the straight and beat out rival in a photo finish.
Took the lead into 1st turn. Taken on by another runner and gave up lead 900M. A length off the pace home turn. Regained advantage 100M. Stayed on well but came up short in a photo finish.
Jumped only fairly wide draw and was ridden forward. Disputed lead into backstraight before opening a 3Ls advantage. Remained a length in front turning in and kept on well for a minor placing.
Niggled along and among early leaders. Stayed a few lengths off the breakaway leaders early back straight. 2Ls off the pace rounding home turn. Kept on fairly to make the frame.
Raced along the rails at midfield or worse. 3Ls off rounding home turn. Ran on fairly in the straight.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield. Ran on fairly in the straight but never a real threat.
Among early leaders. Settled 2-wide and better than midfield back straight. Niggled along 400M and was a length down on straightening. Stayed on same pace thereafter.
Eased back and raced along the rails in rear section. Pressured 500M and near last to turn in. Steadily made up ground in the straight.
Eased backed from wide draw and trailed field early and middle stages. Pressured 500M and was widest turning in. Rallied in the straight but unable to sustain effort final 100M.
2-wide at midfield. 3-wide and ridden along making home but found nothing in the straight.
Settled in rear section. Trailed field making home turn and only ran past a beaten runner.
Caught 3-wide early and settled towards the rear. Remained wide and got closer to midfield 600M. Weakened shortly after straightening.
Led at break, soon headed & stalked 1 back 1 off, shifted out & driven into stretch, gradual progress to overhaul leader, nicked verdict last stride.
Broke well, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed lead on turn & led 300m, scooted 1L clear, all out 100m, tapered & mugged on line.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, shifted out final turn & driven 300m, closed gradually to edge 3rd at wire.
Fast start, sat 1 back on rail, driven 370m & shifted out, boxed on evenly to wire, just missed frame.
Speed early to slot 1 off with cover midfield & over-raced, wide & driven turning in, closed off without threatening.
Started OK, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 550m, under pump 450m, swung out into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Slow start, settled back rail at rear, rolled on a spot 960m, shifted out & driven turning in, stayed on for dour headway.
Tardy start & bustled to run rail behind midfield, ridden 500m, one-paced in tepid run home.
Snagged back from widest gate, raced at tail & niggled 650m, ridden 400m, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Speed wide to lead 1540m & crossed to rail, set tempo 1L clear, nudged along 430m & pressed on turn, all out & headed 300m, weakened tamely.
Sluggish break, raced 3 deep no cover near rear, driven wide into stretch, found little in tame run home.
Missed break, raced 7 lengths back at rear, ridden 400m, plodded on same speed.
Fast break, sat 2nd 1 off, 1L back & ridden 600m, hard at it turning in, ran on to lead 150m, edged clear.
Speed to lead, quickly to rail, extended 600m & 2L clear turning in, shaken up 300m, all out & headed 150m, rallied but no extra close home.
Taken back from widest gate, raced rail near rear, minor progress 500m, driven into stretch, switched out 200m, strong closer to nick 3rd late.
Started OK, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, driven 500m, stayed on under strong drive, solid late inroads.
Sharp start, raced 1 back on rail, ridden along 500m, hard driven 3rd into stretch, boxed on until tapered final 150m.
Lacked early pace & bustled to midfield on rail, driven 300m, stayed on moderately.
Broke OK & driven to settle handy 3 deep no cover, outpaced 600m & ridden, all out turning in, kept on one pace.
Broke OK & raced midfield 1 off with cover, ridden along 450m, one-paced in stretch, impeded near 100m & eased.
Moderate start, raced 1 off behind midfield, under pump 500m, tepid stretch run.
Broke well out wide, taken back to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven widest final turn, struggled in run home.
Missed break, bustled along & passed struggling rival 500m, found little in stretch.
Tardy start, raced near rear 1 off, struggling 500m & relegated to last, unable to make inroads, never a factor.
Eased back early, trapped 3 wide, improved rapidly 800M, took rail and led 700M, suited by the slow tempo, drifted away 300M to win.
3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M for 2nd.
Settled in front, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster to lead, trapped 3 wide, sat just off the leader 2 wide 500M, flattened 200M.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Eased at start, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Eased to sit midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased to sit midfield, carried back 600M, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed forward to take rail and led early at slow sectionals, box seat 600M, emptied 250M.
Pressed forward, dropped off quickly 500M.
Began well, held rail initially before switching to one-off, one-back passing 600m. Swung a little wide into straight, picked up momentum from 250m, just got to the line on time.
Pressed forward from wide draw, cutting in to rail behind leader 650m. Made forward move entering straight, taken out by inside horse, crowded and bumped 50m, just failed.
One of the fastest from the gates and soon in front setting steady pace. Kicked ahead entering straight, looked winner until final stride when swamped by first two.
Ridden forward from wide draw to sit in one-off position about 1L from leader. Edged forward entering straight, battled gamely to line while hanging out under pressure.
Jumped with field, ridden along to stay ahead of midfield in one-off position. Take wide around turn, switched wider in straight, finished off strongly.
Began OK, not much speed, settling along fence behind midfield. Closed in around turn, switched out entering straight but switched in again 200m for run. Finished nicely.
Restrained at start and shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Still last entering straight before powering home after finding inside runs.
Began fairly, ridden along to hold fence three back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn and ran on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden along two and three wide towards rear. Raced wide around turn but kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Crowded out at start, taken to rail, hampered 650m and switched out turn, ran on fairly in straight.
Pushed forward from outside draw and caught wide passing 800m when steadied and dropped back looking for cover. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Outpaced, dropped to near last along rail on settling. Stayed on rail throughout. One-paced in straight.
Worked to the lead, led steadily to straight, kept on well under light weight and had enough to hold off late closers.
Guided to the fence, settled down midfield 4Ls off the pace, shifted out for clear run 300M, closed well, nearest finish.
Tracked leader 2-wide, kept on well under pressure but was always held by winner, lost 2nd last stride.
Crowded for room on jumping, improved to a midfield position near 800M, taken wide 350M, closed well under pressure into never nearer 4th close home.
Always within 3Ls of leader, never far off, kept on steadily towards finish without matching leaders.
Caught 3-wide no cover from wide barrier, close up to pace turning for home, kept on same pace to line, no threat to leaders.
Settled down 3Ls back on the fence, ran on same pace under pressure, never a serious threat.
Away well, led early stages, tracked leader from 1000M, loomed a threat 300M but unable to sustain run inside 200M, weakened towards finish.
Switched off to last on jumping from wide barrier,7-8Ls off the pace, made limited progress from 400M, not reached leaders.
Held up towards the rear 6-7Ls behind leader, niggled long 500M, made no real progress turning home.
Settled near the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, not picked up 400M and soon left behind.
In mid-pack early, hung out badly 700M, soon out of contention, eased early straight. (To OBT around a bend)
Slow into stride, distant last on settling. Made up some ground around turn, switched in 200m for run and powered through to win on the line.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and second-last on settling. Improved position around turn along rails, found inside runs in straight and finished strongly to just fail.
Began fairly, settling four-back from leader along rail. Improved position around turn, switched wide in straight, hampered 100m when finishing strongly.
Pressed forward from wide draw, taking over lead passing 1000m and cutting to fence. Kicked ahead 300m, still in front 100m, run down close to the line.
Ridden along between horses to hold midfield position. Improved position around turn, taken wide in straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
One of the first into stride before settling in box seat behind leader. Stayed on rail around turn and in straight, hampered 50m when tiring.
Began OK, settling three-back the fence. Switched out around turn, raced tight approaching and passing 400m, kept on steadily but got close to heels and not ridden out final stages.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped dropping to rear in one-off position. Took turn wide losing ground, last at 300m, ran on steadily final 200 while laying out under pressure.
Ridden along from wide draw, settling toward rear in one-off position. Improved around turn, blocked for run from 200m to 100m, boxed on fairly.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped, hard ridden to make ground before settling one-off, two back. Kept on gamely in straight to 200m before giving ground.
Began fairly, pressed forward to sit three-wide in row behind leader when hampered 900m. Urged forward top of straight but tired final 100m. Blood in left nostril though not a bleeder.
Pressed forward, racing three wide mostly and left without cover from 600m. Gave ground shortly after entering straight and finished tailed off.
