Slightly slow out, settled just worse than midfield near rails, barged his way out for a run shortly after straightening, asserted authority over 100 metres out.
Soon taken back from a poor gate and waited with, wide into straight, ran on well under pressure but without threatening.

Began from the widest gate, gradually shifted across alongside the leader to be one off the rails, taken 1 back coming onto home bend, shaken up to gain 1L advantage over 200 metres out only to be worn down shortly afterwards.
Jumped well travelling worse than midfield, no clear run early in straight, finished off race nicely.
Ridden to gain one-back position on rails, remained similar to straight, kept on steadily without quickening in the run home.
Soon dropped to the rear, remained in last few to straight, no clear passage early on and steadied passing 200 metres, produced good late impression closing stages.
Broke well racing keenly in midfield, similar turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Tightened at start, shifted onto rails in last few, saved ground entering straight, improving when steadied 200 metres out, made no further impression.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths back in 6th, no cover on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, there to turn, raced tight early in straight but found little when clear thereafter.
Jumped moderately, travelled wide in 5th and wide without cover before moving up to dispute lead around home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Pressed on from a wide gate to soon take up running holding narrow lead to straight, dropped away quickly inside final 300 metres.
Jumped moderately, settled in midfield on rails, came under pressure around the bend, saved ground turning in , faded inside final 250 metres.
Jumped awkwardly, raced keenly in first few to straight, weakened passing the 300 metres.
Pushed along early from wide gate to find cover midfield, commenced to improve passing 600m, strong run from 350 to power home over the top.
Crowded for room and checked at start, settled towards rear, improved mid race along inside, angled out on straightening, ran home strongly.
Bumped on jumping before showing pace to settle outside leader, travelled easily and challenged strongly to hit lead at 300m, fought hard but overpowered final 100m.
Jumped well, settled midfield, eased out home turn to challenge but run ended near 150m.
Missed start slightly, pushed along to settle midfield, presented to challenge at home turn and made some ground despite having difficulty obtaining clear running in straight.
Hampered on jumping and went back from wide gate, made brief challenge early in straight.
Jumped well, eased to settle behind leaders, angled out on straightening, tried hard but couldn't quicken.
Jumped well but restrained back to obtain cover, raced greenly and lay out mid race, hung out on straightening and made steady ground.
Eased back at start to settle at rear, tried hard to make ground behind runners in the straight but eventually weakened out of it.
Commenced awkwardly and lost ground, kicked up to settle midfield on rail, tried to make ground in straight, crowded at 200m.
Fast out and pushed along to lead, held together home turn, did not respond when asked to quicken at 300m and weakened out of it.
Urged forward to settle behind leaders, in need of a run home turn with nowhere to go until 200m, but did not finish race off.
Eased back at start from wide gate and never in it thereafter.
Jumped OK, pushed along to settle midfield without cover, forward move near 750m but could not sustain effort and was struggling at the home turn.
Pushed forward to settle outside the leader at slow sectionals, ran on strongly to score by 1-1/4L.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, dashed strongly for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow sectionals, kept on steadily.
Settled worse than midfield about 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow tempo, ran on nicely despite having difficultly to find a clear running near 200M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, ran on steadily.
Eased back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, made some ground in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, weakened 150M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly. (Lame left front)
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, emptied 200M.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, faded 350M.
Jumped awkwardly, then failed to muster despite ridden along, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on. (Questioned for running)
At rear throughout, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Broke Ok, taken back to slot midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in & shifted out, grinding progress to lead 50m & kept on.
Fast break, handy but caught 3 wide no cover, niggled 500m, shaken up turning in, driven to edge lead 180m, pressed on both sides & headed 50m, boxed on.
Snagged back at start to rail behind midfield, smooth traveller final turn, shifted out into stretch & driven 350m, kept on to nick 3rd at wire.
Rousted at start, tracked handy 1 off with cover, ridden turning in, not clear run 300m, driven through gap 250m to press lead, no extra final 50m & lost 3rd late.
Taken back at break & sat 1 off behind midfield, niggled on & off the bridle, off heels 570m, shifted wide 400m, ran on for minor headway.
Taken back from wide at start to 1 off in last trio, shifted out on turn but checked 420m, switched into clear 350m & ridden, closed centre track for late inroads.
Missed break, settled tail last trio, shifted out & ridden into stretch, switched out wider 300m, plugged on evenly.
Fast start, sat close 2nd 1 off no cover, shaken up 380m & edged lead 300m, headed 180m, faded to wire.
Moderate break, checked 1500m, raced rail midfield, shuffled back final turn & switched out 400m, driven but one-paced & little impact.
Broke well, sat rail 2L behind lead, driven 420m but outpaced & plugged on tepidly.
Sharp break, soon led & crossed to rail, driven under pressure 420m, all out & headed 300m, faded out thereafter.
Started OK, raced 3 deep with cover midfield, rolled 4 wide final turn, hard driven into stretch but emptied 300m & weakened tamely.
Dropped in from widest gate to race last trio 3 wide, bustled & never travelled, driven widest final turn, plugged on same speed.
Broke OK from wide gate, settled 3 deep with cover behind midfield, niggled 700m, hard-ridden & forced wide into stretch, soon emptied & tailed off.

Sharp start, snagged back to fore of midfield 3 deep with cover, shuffled back a spot 900m, crowded final turn, shaken up 400m, checked inside off heels 300m, clear & quickened 150m, surged to lead late.
Broke well & bustled, prominent early, settled 1 off 1 back, niggled 750m, driven & shifted out 450m, took time to warm up, stayed on gradually to claim 2nd late.
Dropped in from wide to sit 3 deep with cover behind midfield, shifted out turning in but crowded, 4.5L back when checked 400m, picked up 300m, closed off to nick 3rd.
Early speed to sit 2nd outside leader, every chance & ridden turning in, all out to edge lead 200m, unable to stretch clear & headed 50m, swamped last strides.
Broke well, soon niggled & retreated to rear rank 1 off, to fence 800m, angled out 620m, 5L back & wide into stretch but behind horses, clear & driven 330m, rattled home.
Fast start & ridden to lead, settled on rail & set tempo, 0.5L clear when driven 400m, headed 200m, battled on when beaten.
Missed break & raced 3 wide at rear, smooth wide progress from 600m, 4L down & shaken up 400m, closed centre track but peaked 150m & tapered.
Taken back to tail from widest gate, soon rolled 4 deep to behind midfield, lost cover 900m, ridden 750m & progress, 2L down turning in & wide, kept on evenly.
Snagged back at start, raced 3 deep with cover near rear, niggled 970m & soon in rear rank, driven wide turning in, stayed on for minor headway.
Moderate break, settled rail midfield, driven 430m but lacked pace, plugged on tepidly until eased late when beaten.
Good break, settled 2 wide behind midfield, shifted out home turn, shaken up 400m, found little in tame stretch run.
Smart start, taken back to sit midfield 1 off, driven in pursuit 430m, outpaced & tapered in run.
Broke OK, worked early to settle rail 1 back, niggled 520m, hard-ridden 430m & shifted out, found nil in tame run home.
Broke OK & bustled early, trapped 4 wide & handy, ridden 950m & soon slotted 3 deep, driven 550m, emptied 350m & faded tamely.
Eased to sit just off the lead on the fence, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 300M and drifted away to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leaders in 3 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Slightly further back than usual, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, held ground for 3rd.
Pushed early but not muster, checked badly 900M, 5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M whilst hanging in.
Pushed forward, led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals in 2 wide, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased back, trapped 4 wide, 4Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Behind midfield, 4LS off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly when clear.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Hard ridden early not muster, trapped 4 wide, 2Ls off the slow pace, out of fuel 300M.
Pressed forward, 2Ls off the slow tempo along the fence, emptied 250M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the slow pace, trapped 4 wide throughout, soon reduced 350M.
Jumped with field, allowed to settle towards rear along the rail. Boxed in top of straight, came off fence 300m, shifted out 200m to get run, hit front 100m and pulled clear for easy win.
Quickly into stride, settling 1.5L behind leader. Rolled forward top of straight, took lead 300m, caught 100m but kept on well to the line.
Began fairly, allowed to settle behind midfield, bumped and taken wider 1100m. Settled 3-back, one-off to straight, switched out and ran on steadily to take minor placing.
Ridden to obtain forward position and kept wide without cover 3L from leader. Took turn 3-wide, rolled forward top of straight to look chance 200m, then one-paced.
Began fairly, got close to heels and checked 1100m dropping to last. Got close to heels again entering turn, taken wide in straight, ran on steadily. Lame right front leg.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, hampered 1100m, dropping to last pair but away from rail. Switched out entering straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden along from inside draw to hold rail 3-back from leader. Edged closer entering straight but forced to steady when crossed 200m. One-paced after.
Ridden along early settling 2-back, one-off before getting shuffled back entering turn. Blocked for run early in straight and then struck on nose 350m before checked 200m. One-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, dropping to behind midfield and racing three-wide. Never competitive.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling. Set good pace until collared 300m, faded.
Ridden forward from wide draw to sit third, 2L from leader in a one-off position. Edged forward entering straight to look a chance before running out of steam 250m and fading.
Restrained in midfield about 4Ls behind leader, driven 450M, strong run passing 200M to get up close home.
Always prominent just off the pace, responded well passing 300M, drew alongside leader 100M, caught by fast finishing winner late stages.
Strolled to a one out one back position, took up running 300M, kept on gamely under top weight, was strongly challenged passing 200M and only gave way grudgingly final stages.
Settled down 3Ls off the pace, stayed on steadily towards the finish but was always held by leaders.
Held up 3Ls back in a position ahead of midfield, had every chance turning in, ran on moderately and not going the pace to challenge.
Reserved behind mid-division, 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, took time to get going when driven entering straight, did best work towards finish.
Bounded on jumping and lost ground, settled near last, switched wide 500M, stayed on steadily without threat. (to stalls test)
Raced behind midfield first half of the race, shuffled back a bit home turn, stayed on moderately over final 400M.
Soon led and took them along at steady pace, joined by rival 350M, run ended mid-straight and weakened towards finish.
Crossed to race along the fence and remained handy throughout tracking leading pair, lacked further response turning in, ran on same pace to line.
Taken across behind runners from draw 14, held up in rear pair 8Ls off the pace, checked 500M and ended up last, made minor headway final 300M.
Not hurried after an awkward start, raced as the back-marker until 500M, stayed on only mildly, never reached contention.
In midfield racing along the 2-path, outpaced by leaders inside 400M, no extra final 150M.
Settled down in mid-division, driven along 500M out, outpaced passing 300M, eased when well beaten.
Began well, ridden forward from wide draw settling 3-wide, 2L behind leader. Kept wide back stretch and turn, rolled forward on straightening, hit front 300m and held off rivals final 100m.
Began OK, taken to fence settling 4-back from leader. Got shuffled back approaching final turn, stayed on fence before peeling out 500m, got split between horses and finished off strongly.
Taken back, edging closer to rail but towards the rear. Improved along rail around the turn, found inside runs in straight and finished off nicely.
Bumped start, settling at rear in a one-off position. Still well back entering straight before picking up momentum and finishing well.
Ridden to obtain forward position early before settling three-back, one-off along back stretch. Urged forward turn, looked chance entering straight, boxed on one-paced.
Began fairly, then crowded out dropping four-back, one-off. Improved position around turn, bumped 350m, ran on steadily.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair away from fence. Urged forward turning for home, wide in straight, boxed on one-paced.
Pressed forward, settling one-off, one-back. Got shuffled back final turn, rolled forward again on straightening but only one-paced final 200m.
Won the start, rolled forward from wide draw before settling 1L behind leader. Edged forward entering straight to share lead 300m before tiring.
Bumped start, ridden along behind midfield in a one-off position. Took closer order final turn, urged forward entering straight, ran out of gas passing 200m and faded.
Began OK, ridden forward settling along rail, three-back from leader. Closed in around turn, checked 400m when trying to improve, losing ground. One-paced final 200m.
Began OK, shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Always at rear and never competitive.
Pushed forward from inside draw, holding rail inside leading pack before taking clear lead back stretch. Tried to steady tempo 1200m, under pressure turn, faded final 300m.
Urged forward from inside draw to grab box seat on settling. Stayed close to pace till entering straight, then faded.
Moderately away, positioned 5 lengths or so back in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 1 out 1 back on turn, kicked clear early in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back in 4th, raced tight near 1100M, easy run on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well to get 3rd when clear final 200M.
Jumped well, taken back to race 8 lengths back at tail, similar position on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, got cover near 900M, 2 wide 5 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter.
Began fairly, positioned 4 lengths back in midfield, difficult to settle near 700M, 3 wide without cover thereafter, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 7 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, checked near 250M, made minor progress thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no daylight until passing 300M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 1-2 lengths back in 5th, No clear running early in straight, same position on turn, finished off one paced in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 7 lengths back at tail, took wide on turn and slightly improved, shifted in and difficult to ride near 250M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, but failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5-6 lengths back at rear, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, same position on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.

Hard ridden at start, forward of midfield before swift progress passing the 1000 metres, led approaching the Rock, 1L break around the bend and into the straight, hung on under pressure.

Vied for lead from the widest gate before settling outside the leader far side, became 3rd at around the Rock when eventual winner shot to the lead, re-gained 2nd on home bend but unable to peg back the winner in straight.

Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 to 3 lengths back in midfield, improved on turn, got its head on the side in straight and finished off evenly to get 3rd without threatening.
Tightened after a moderate start, settled at the back, commenced move rounding home bend, made only minor progress from towards the rear into straight.

Failed to muster and soon dropped to last few, checked passing the winning post the first time dropping well behind, angled off the rails for a run on top of home bend, made up good ground from widest in last into straight.
Settled wide in last few from a poor draw, took closer order rounding home bend, slightly unbalanced early in straight, ran home one-paced.
Slightly sluggish at start, pushed forward to reach rear of midfield on stables bend, remained similar into straight, ran home one-paced.
Began well to share early pace 3-wide, shifted back for cover in forward of midfield, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Began well from a low draw, amongst leaders before settling in box-seat on rails, shuffled back behind tiring pace-setter approaching home bend, never recovered from towards the rear into straight.
Jumped fairly, soon taken back to last few, went wide into straight, hung in and a difficult ride in the run home.
Settled in midfield on rails, gradually shuffled backward in back straight, hampered and lost further ground around the bend, never recovered.

Not the best at the start but niggled along to join the leaders before hitting the front shortly, lost lead to eventual winner 800 metres out when steadying the pace, fading when hampered on top of home bend.
Jumped well and allowed to settle midfield, commenced to move forward passing 500m, took a while to wind up in straight before finishing powerfully final 100m to get there on the line.
Sped out of the gates to take up the lead, travelled well and nursed along home turn before kicking strongly on straightening, fought hard to hold of all challengers until run down late to just miss.
Jumped well and settled leaders back, raced keenly mid race, switched to inside of leader on straightening and tried valiantly entire straight.
Eased back from wide gate to settle towards rear, stoked up 400m, widest on straightening and ran home strongly.
Bumped shortly after start and eased back from wide gate, commenced to creep forward near 500m, ran home evenly along inside.
Began awkwardly, settled leaders back, ran home ok in straight and had every chance.
Jumped awkwardly, allowed to settle midfield on rail, crept closer home turn, every chance in straight, crowded at 150m.
Taken back from wide gate and settled last, made a little ground in straight.
Jumped well, pushed along to settle outside leader, unable to quicken when asked for effort on straightening and weakened out of it.
Settled worse than mid, pushed along passing 500m but did not respond and dropped out of it in straight.
No early pace and settled towards rear, pushed along mid race to keep in touch, under pressure home turn and made no ground in straight.
Hampered on jumping, unable to gain cover and raced wide in handy position, tough run took its toll and weakened out of it on straightening.
Began slowly, then pushed to settle 4.5Ls behind the leader along the fence, dashed well to score when hanging in badly in straight.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by a neck, kept on strongly until final 50M headed by the winner.
Taken back from wide gate, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wider 600M, kept on steadily without threatening.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some late ground in straight.
Sent to forward to park outside the leader, emptied over the last furlong.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Eased back from wide gate, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening.
Raced midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Good break & prominent early, soon sat 1 back 1 off, keen 1130m, driven & shifted out home turn, swept to lead 200m, surged clear.
Taken back to sit last pair 3 deep with cover, rolled on a spot 720m, hard-ridden 460m, 8Ldown & swung widest final turn, rattled late to nick 2nd.
Sharp start to lead, restrained & headed 1500m, settled very close 2nd on rail, edged to lead 680m, 1L clear & shaken up final turn, all out & headed 200m, lost 2nd late.
Broke OK, raced midfield 3 deep with cover, niggled 550m, driven wide home turn, stayed on for minor gains.
Dropped in from widest gate to camp at tail, 9L last & driven 400m, shifted out final turn, closed off for sound late gains without threatening.
Broke OK but bustled early, leaned in & bumped rival 1st turn, checked slightly 780m, driven turning in, stayed on for minor inroads.
Slow start, raced rail behind midfield, squeezed up on fence 1st turn, minor progress out of back stretch & niggled 500m, stayed on OK under a drive.
Tardy break, rousted wide to edge lead 1500m, restrained in front & set steady tempo, headed 680m, under pump 520m, plugged on tepidly.
Good break, camped rail 1 back, nudged along 550m, 2L back & hard driven in pursuit turning for home, out-paced & swamped in fading run.
Tardy start & bustled early, settled 3 deep with cover behind midfield, driven 500m, all out turning in, plugged on same speed.
Reared start & lost ground, rolled 3 deep no cover 1st turn to sit 1L off lead, niggled 680m, soon rowed along but outpaced & retreated, plodded on tamely.
Speed early, sat 1 off with cover, outpaced & bustled along 450m, soon under pump in vain pursuit, emptied 250m & faded out.
Broke well, tucked in handy 1 off with cover, over-raced 1070m, niggled 560m, driven 450m, battled to lead 120m & edged clear.
Smart break, caught 3 wide no cover 1st turn & rolled to camp 1L back 1 off no cover, bustled to press lead 400m, fought ahead 150m, headed 120m, boxed on.
Speed to lead & snagged rail 1st turn, headed 1300m, settled 1 back, driven in contention 400m, kept on & rallied late to hold 3rd.
Broke OK, sat 1 off with cover midfield, bustled for progress 550m, 3 wide 450m & driven, wide into stretch, closed off well.
Broke OK but squeezed out & rousted initially, settled rail midfield, overraced 1050m, shifted 1 off 400m & progress, wide into stretch, closed for fair gains.
Moderate start, raced 1 off behind midfield, overraced 850m, minor progress from 600m, edged 3 deep 400m, fanned wide home turn, stayed on for late inroads.
Sharp start & rolled 1 off to lead 1300m, to rail 1050m, pressed & shaken up turning in, emptied 150m & headed, tapered to wire.
Snagged start, sat rail near rear, driven 400m, stayed on without threatening.
Fast start, slotted back rail fore of midfield, shifted out home turn & driven, wilted in run.
Fair break but 3 wide behind midfield 1st turn, overraced 1000m & slotted 1 off near rear 750m, driven wide final turn, plugged on one pace.
Slow start & raced at tail, niggled 800m to advance a spot, driven 500m, plodded on & never a factor.
Broke OK widest, slotted back 1 off near rear, wide on turn 1000m & to last pair, to tail 800m, niggled 550m, plodded on one pace.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly in straight and just scored by a head.
Took rail easily and led by 1L at slow sectionals, drifted away 300M, hung on well until 50M overhauled, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Failed to muster early, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 300M for 3rd.
Hold the rail in front of midfield, 3Ls of the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 8.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, soon out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, but soon reduced 300M.
Never a factor at rear.
Began well, ridden to hold fence behind leader. Got rails run on straightening, hit front 300m, under pressure from 100m, held.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Second last entering straight before finishing strongly along fence while trying to lay out final 200m.
Began well, not pushed, settling midfield in one-off position. Moved forward final turn, switched wide in straight and finished off strongly.
Began well, settling along rail 3-back from leader, Took closer order around final turn, found inside run in straight and finished off nicely to just miss a place.

Began fairly, then steadied, falling four-back along rail. Moved forward turn but got close to heels. Took inside run in straight but had to switch out 250m behind weakening horse. Kept on well to line.
Jumped with field but hampered shortly after then caught 3-wide. Found cover back stretch 3L from leader, closed in final turn, looked chance 200m when bumped and badly unbalanced. One-paced.

Ridden forward from wide draw but unable find cover, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched out entering straight and was finishing nicely when checked 200m, forcing jockey to stop riding.
Began awkwardly, ridden to make up ground settling 3-back, one-off. Switched out entering straight to make run but only one-paced.
Outpaced, settling towards rear. Bumped 800m, dropped to last entering straight, switched out to make run but found little under hard riding.
One of the first into stride, travelled keenly, shifted out first turn, then shuffled back to third when outside runner moved forward. Remained in contention till passing 200m when weakened.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Joined up front and put under pressure passing 900m. Collared soon after straightening and faded.
Began OK, made use of to go forward 3-wide into first turn behind leading pack. Pressed forward to join leader from 900m to 300m before tiring and dropping back.
Positively ridden from wide barrier, emerged as sole leader 800M and carved off good sectionals, had 2Ls in hand inside 200M, held off fast finishing 2nd by a diminishing neck.
Settled down off midfield 8Ls off leader in middle stages, bustled along 500M out, ran on strongly from 250M, just missed.
Closed up early stages, caught 3-wide no cover eased back to midfield, 7Ls off the pace home turn, stayed on well to go 3rd 50M, nearest line.
Vied for lead early stages, chased leader in 2nd 800M, well clear from rest, kept on evenly final 300M but not able to challenge winner, lost 2 placings near 50M.
Reserved in mid-division, 7-8Ls back in 6th, stayed on without threatening.
Aggressively ridden but failed to muster, settled near the rear, had plenty to make up 400M, made some progress in straight but not reached contention.
In 3rd, 3-4Ls off the good pace, kept on same speed in straight, caught by pursuing rivals passing 100M.
Up with pace early, restrained passing 800M to race 4-5Ls off runaway leader, responded only fairly under strong urge, faded final stages.
Eased back to a rearward position over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, driven along 500M, made some progress along fence but never seriously threatened.
Settled towards the rear, over 10Ls behind leader in middle stages, closed off the race reasonably well but left with too much to do.
Taken back from outside barrier, not hurried, in rear over 10Ls off a good pace, ran on mildly from the rear passing 350M, difficult to obtain run final stages.
Towards the rear, caught 3-wide no cover throughout, not picked up pace and soon left behind inside 350.

Broke well from the on draw, settled just off the pace tracking the leader to straight, took charge passing the 200 metres and soon drew clear.
Jumped moderately, ridden early before steadying back to last few, commenced move to circle the field rounding home bend, sustained progress in straight to reach 2nd late.
Pressed on from a wide gate before settling 2-wide in 1L 2nd, came under pressure around home bend, kept on same pace without quickening and lost 2nd late.
Soon took up running on rails from a wide gate attempting to make all, led the field to the 200 metres, weakened. (Tactic questioned)
Settled wide in midfield, remained similar into straight, ran home one-paced.
Broke well, settling in midfield early before inconvenienced and lost position approaching back straight, towards the rear turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled in midfield, fought on steadily along rails in straight, hampered late.
Trailed the field to straight, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the track, nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from a wide draw settling 2-wide in 4th just over 2L off the pace, faded under pressure in straight.
Began moderately, soon dropped to last few, kept on same pace in straight.
Settled wide behind midfield, took closer order rounding home bend, badly checked over 250 metres out, kept on.
Began from the widest gate, wide without cover towards the rear early before moving up to better than midfield in 5th approaching back straight, came under pressure rounding home bend, found nothing.
Jumped fairly settling in forward of midfield on rails, moved slightly closer passing the 1200 metres, soon faded in straight.
Lacked pace and given reminders early, improved to rear of midfield on rails turning into back straight, yielded ground quickly on home bend.
Bumped on jumping, showed speed to settle just off the pace, asked for effort at 400m and responded by challenging strongly at 200m, moved clear final 100m.
Jumped awkwardly and settled worse than midfield, travelled well mid race and commenced to pick up passing 500m, held up at 250 and taken to inside for clear running, finished strongly final 150m.
Jumped well and settled leaders back on outside rail, pushed along at 400m when waiting for run, hampered 250m and then ran home strongly.
Settled midfield, ridden along passing 500m, commenced to make ground near 200m and worked to the line strongly.
Jumped smartly and showed pace to cross and settle on pace, asked for effort at 400m, tried hard and fought all the way to the line.
Jumped well and showed pace to lead easily, lay in when under pressure at 300m, but continued to hold lead, fought hard before overpowered final 150m.

Crowded on jumping, settled at rear, unbalanced at 700m when racing greenly, commenced to make good ground passing 500m despite racing manners, really got going final 150m finishing awkwardly placed on heels.
Settled midfield, travelled strongly mid race, pushed along 450m but unable to pick up, one paced to the line.
No early pace and eased back to settle towards rear in middle of the track, tried hard final 300m making some ground.
Fast out and prominent early behind leaders, pushed along near 400m, hampered at 300m, dropped out passing 150m.
Showed early pace to settle forward of mid, under pressure at 350m and weakened out of it.
Jumped awkwardly, no early pace, hard ridden mid race, did not run on.
Hampered at start but no early pace and settled towards rear, couldn't keep up at 500m and did not run home.
Settled towards rear, under pressure at 500m and commenced to weaken before being eased down passing 250m - Bled.
Eased to rear, travelled 8.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, closed off strongly to score by a neck.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, ran on steadily for 2nd and just beaten by a neck.
Pushed to settle in midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on well for 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
Pushed to settle in midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, shifted out turning in, ran on steadily.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, hung on well until final 100M weakened.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground after straightening.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly and weakened final 100M.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Began well, settling in box seat back stretch. Came off fence 400m, surged forward to lead 300m, kept on well to line holding off late challenge.
Ridden forward from inside draw, settling three-back before taking closer order around turn. Stayed on fence entering straight, got clear run 200m, finished strongly.
Began best but caught wide without cover and allowed to drift back 3L from leader. Was four-wide entering straight, kept on steadily without threatening the first two.
Used inside draw to surge forward to the lead on settling and set a good pace to straight. Overhauled passing 300m but kept on fairly to the lie.
Ridden along behind midfield in a one-off position. Got dragged back around turn, switched wide in straight, kept on steadily.
Not much pace, taken to fence and made up ground around turn. Took inside run in straight and kept on fairly.
Began awkwardly, then shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling near rear. Closed in top of straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Began OK, hard ridden to make up ground, settling in midfield along fence. Taken wide passing 300m but only one paced in straight.
Outpaced, settling at rear along fence. Saved ground turn, stayed on fence in straight, ran past tired horses before being blocked 100m.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Still last at the 200m and never competitive.
Pressed forward outside early leader but trapped wide and allowed to ease back one-off, one-back. Remained in contention to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden from wide draw to get forward position two-back, one-off. Started to weaken soon after entering the straight.

Began best, led to 1200m before taking box seat. Shuffled back to third passing 850m. Got split between horses entering straight, surged forward to lead 300m, kept finding when placed under pressure final 200m.
Jumped with field, ridden at own pace one-off, three-back. Took closer order turn, threw out strong challenge from 200m, just failed.
No early speed, settling towards rear while edging closer to fence. Swung wide entering straight, switched to outside rail, was finishing strongly when momentarily unbalanced 150m. Kept on.
Began well, pressed forward between horses to lead passing 1200m. Challenged around turn but kept lead to 300m when passed. Boxed on gamely.
Not much early speed, settling behind midfield but away from the fence. Picked up momentum early in straight and ran on steadily. Jockey reported saddle shifted back at top of the straight.
Began well, racing with early pacemakers before slipping 3L back but away from fence. Ran on steadily on straight, turning one-paced final 200m.
Quickly into stride, settling one-back, one-off. Shuffled back slightly around turn, kept on steadily to 200m before weakening.
Checked and lost ground at start, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out entering straight, made up some ground initially before turning one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Came off fence turning for home but found little under pressure. One paced.
Ridden forward early but got close to heels 1000m, then awkwardly placed 900m and again 800m, taken wide without cover. Found little in straight under hard riding.
Began awkwardly, shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in a one-off position. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden forward from inside draw, holding rail three-back from leader. Stayed on fence entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along from wide draw to obtain forward position but trapped wide. Allowed to roll forward to sit outside leader at turn. Put under pressure entering straight but found nothing and eased down.
Began OK, holding position four-back from leader but soon under pressure, gradually dropping back. Last on entering straight and tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Led by 1L at fast sectionals, hung on well to win.
Very slow away, 3Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, finished off strongly when clear for 2nd.
Obtained a more prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the fast pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Prominent early, failed to hold its position from 700M, blocked 4-2, made ground when clear.
Pressed forward, just off the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 250M.
Pressed forward, sat just off the fast pace, flattened 200M.
Awkward away, 3Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, no turn of foot.
Checked start, behind midfield, never progressed.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Awkward away, behind midfield, never competitive.
Never a factor.
Midfield, reduced quickly 400M and tailed out.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, soon dropped off 500M.
First out before settling some 5L behind leader before the turn. Picked up momentum gradually in the straight, hit the front 100m, kept on well.
Pressed forward to lead passing 1000m before pulling 5L clear entering final turn. Started to shorten stride 200m, caught 100m, kept on.
Began well, ridden along to hold forward position one-off, one-back. Picked up momentum in straight, slightly inconvenienced 200m, kept on steadily to grab minor placing.
Crowded out start, ridden forward to hold rail, three-back from leader. Switched out entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at the finish.
Began awkwardly and then forced to steady, dropping to rear about 10L from leader. Switched out entering straight and finished off strongly.
Outpaced early, settling four-back from leader. Edged closer around turn, ran on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Bounded in air at the start, unbalanced and lost around, settling last. Picked up momentum in the straight, running on fairly between horses.
Pressed forward from wide gate and held three-wide, mostly without cover. Taken wide in straight and boxed on one-paced.
Ridden along early but trapped wide towards the rear but with cover. Improved position around turn, taken widest in straight, boxed on one-paced.
Steadied shortly after start, then raced fiercely towards rear, refusing to settle. Switched out in straight and ran on fairly.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear along rail. Switched out entering straight but found nothing under hard riding.
Began OK, got close to heels, settling midfield on one-off position. Gave ground shortly after entering straight. Substantial amount of mucopus in trachea.
Within striking distance always, picked up strongly inside 300M, led inside 200M, continued on willingly to the finish and fought off late challenge of 2nd well.
Dropped back to near the rear from 14, patiently ridden, switched widest leaving turn, finished final 400M fastest, shifted in under pressure 100M, held by winner but finished nicely clear from rest.
Settled 3-4Ls behind leader, saved ground along the fence, quickened up to chase winner from 350M but was always held.
Up with early pace, tracked leader from 900M, quickened up to lead briefly 300M out, but did not match finishing pace of first three over final 200M.
Settled down in mid-division, peeled out passing 600M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 5th.
Held up behind midfield along the inside, 5Ls off the pace middle stages, kept on inside in straight, stayed on without threat.
Up with early pace, shifted into a 2-wide just behind leaders 950M, lacked necessary response when driven 350M, ran on same pace, out of contention 150M.
Soon taken across behind runners, settled near rear 6Ls off the pace, stayed on fairly over final 400M, not reached contention.
Not far off but travelled very keenly in early and middle stages, took keen hold in midfield over home turn, ran on same pace in straight, never threatened.
Settled down in mid-division, no closer than 3-wide throughout, driven out 450M and loomed a threat 300M, run ended passing 200M however, no extra late stages.
Eased back on jumping from wide barrier, settled last 8Ls off the pace, detached from field middle of the turn, drifted to wide outside in straight, made some late progress.
Failed to muster speed despite vigorously ridden early stages, caught 4-wide no cover, improved on outer passing 1000M, battled on to 200M, gave ground.
Restrained in a 3-wide position behind midfield, never properly settled, brought wider home turn, had not much to offer in straight. (Unacceptable Performance, to OVE and OBT)
Raced keenly in front, emerged as sole lead passing 950M, headed 350M, dropped out rapidly.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, pulled 2L clear around turn and then kicked further ahead passing 300m. Under siege final 100m but kept finding to win.
Jumped well, not pressed, settling four-back, one-off. Edged closer around turn, looked a big chance passing 200m, unable to match winner final stages.
Began with field, ridden to obtain forward position, settling three-back from leader along rail. Stayed on fence turning for home and kept on well to be closest at the finish.
Shifted across behind runners from awkward draw, settling along fence toward the rear. Took closer order around turn, widest in straight, ran on steadily.
Got off OK but not much speed, settling toward rear in one-off position. Still well back entering the straight, found run between horses, kept on seedily.
Began OK, tightened and bumped 950m, settling four-back the fence. Switched out entering straight and ran on fairly between horses.
Ridden along from wide draw but steadied 950m then left wide without cover from 800m. Improved around turn, was finishing well when switched out and unbalanced 150m. Not ridden out final stages.
Outpaced and last on settling. Last into straight, switched out but blocked for run 200m-150m, finished off nicely down centre track.
Jumped in air when gates opened, hard ridden but failed to muster, settling towards rear along fence. Improved slightly turn but only one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position settling 3-back, one-off. Took closer order around turn, kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Bumped start, ridden to grab box seat before turn. Lost position entering straight, eased away from heels passing 300m, faded.
Pressed forward from widest draw, settling one-back, one-off from leader entering turn. Edged forward top of straight but run ended passing 300m and faded.
Eased out to sit handy. No luck early in the straight, but found a tight gap to squeeze through at 300m. Let down in the last 200m to win well.
Sat midfield, two and three off the fence. Tracked wide on turn. Made a move 250m out and let down strongly, but winner had it wrapped up.
Crowded on jumping, and eventually found a position midfield one off the fence. Pushed hard in straight, but wobbling late and had to share 3rd.
Crowded on jumping, and happy to settle back worse than midfield two off the fence. Came widest on turn, and let down well. Had claims to third late, but had to share the place.
Sat at the back of the pack after drawing wide, and was on heels near the first turn. Held the rail until turn, and was off heels again at 200m and ran on gamely from there.
Drifted across from the wide draw to sit near last on the rail. Held up at the top of the straight when looking for a run. Ran on fairly without threatening a place.
Looked to push forward early, but had to settle for midfield on the rail. Scraping paint down the straight, and improved into a tight gap 200m, but only ran on fairly.
Pushed forward from widest gate to lead and set decent tempo. Plugged away in the straight, but a beaten horse by 150m and faded.
Crowded on jumping and eventually settled worse than midfield, one off the fence. Came wide on turn, and asked for something in the last furlong, but only ran on fairly.
Pushed to sit behind leader early. Asked for something 300 out, but couldn't kick and faded back.
Began OK from the 1 barrier to sit handy on the fence. Was in the gun position on the turn and asked the question from the 250m, but had nothing to give, and eased out late.
Pushed forward from a wide draw to sit handy, but was 3 and 4 wide the trip facing the breeze. Looked a tired horse by the 200m and ran on like one.

Pushed forward early, and then eased slightly to take a sit behind the leaders. Bumped and unbalanced at 300m but under pressure a long way out, and never finished off. Unacceptable performance and to trial.
Drifted back to share back marker duties. Under pressure a long way out, and race was effectively over by the 300m.

In front briefly before settling in 2nd outside the leader, hit the front again over 200 metres out, hung on well.
Given reminders when behind midfield early, took closer order home bend, switched out for a run after straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Attempted to make all, no extra inside final 200 metres.
Broke well, settled just off the speed, kept on at the one pace under pressure in the run home.
Wide in midfield early, gradually improved out wide to reach 3rd approaching home bend, lost position entering home straight, ran home one-paced.
Well behind, made modest progress in straight.
Ridden early from the one draw settling just off the pace in 4th on rails, gave ground steadily from similar position into straight.
Behind midfield early, gradually improved out wide to reach midfield before home bend, lost position turning into straight, produced late impression closing stages.
Never better than midfield, faded gradually in straight.
Broke well from the widest gate, dropped to the last before home bend, only went past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Jumped awkwardly from a poor draw, settled wide behind midfield, similar turning in, one-paced before fading closing stages.
Wide in midfield early, dropped to last few around home bend, ran home one-paced. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Straight to the front, travelled well, challenged on straightening, responded and held off all challengers.
Fast out and sent forward to settle outside leader, challenged for lead on straightening, fought hard entire straight.
Settled just off pace, came out to challenge on straightening, ran home strongly.
Pushed along to hold rail and settle behind leader, travelled well home turn, inclined to lay out in straight and had every chance.
Went forward from wide gate but caught wide and settle midfield, forward move near 500m, worked home evenly after tough run.
Settled midfield and stayed there throughout, held position in straight.
Jumped Ok, pushed along to settle midfield, crept forward passing 600m, asked for effort home turn but no response and one paced to the line.
No early pace and went back, raced keenly at 1400m, checked off heels at 1200m, commenced forward move around field near 600m, immediately under pressure on straightening and one paced to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield, pushed along home turn and had every chance in straight.
Eased back from wide gate at start, crept forward along rail mid race, in need of run home turn, kept on well in straight.
Jumped smartly but allowed to drift back and settle at rear, stuck to rail throughout and made no ground in straight.
Settled towards rear, commence forward move passing 600m, widest on straightening but immediately under pressure and dropped out of it.
Jumped awkwardly, went forward and settled 3 wide without cover outside lead, under pressure 500m, hampered when weakening at 300m.
Jumped awkwardly, eased back to settle towards rear, under pressure 500m and never a chance.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, suited by the track that favoring front runners, scored impressively with plenty in hand.
Prominent, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the track that favoring front runners, ran on well for 2nd but never match with the winner.
Ridden forward to obtain the box seat, suited by the track that favoring front runners, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, suited by the track that favoring front runners, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the track that favoring front runners, made some ground in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the track that favoring front runners, dashed well in straight.
Taken back from wide gate, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the track that favoring front runners, ran on fairly.
At rear, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the track that favoring front runners, ran on fairly.
Pushed to midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the track that favoring front runners, never ran on.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on until final 250M weakened.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, weakened soon after straightening.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Slow into stride, shifted across behind runners and settled four-back, the rail. Improved position back stretch, swung wide into straight, finished strongly down centre track for close win.
Began well, crossed to fence before first turn, settling in box seat behind leader. Came off fence 300m and battled on strongly to the line to just miss.
Jumped best, raced in lead but wide to first turn, before cutting to rail 1200m. Kicked ahead top of straight and kept on well until run down closing stages.
Ridden along early, settling three-back the fence. Stayed on fence around turn and kept on steadily in straight until 100m when steadied and shifted out from heels.
Raced tightly between horses early before settling behind midfield in a one-out position. Had clear run in straight, making ground steadily without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, then steadied 1300m dropping to near last. Stayed on fence around turn and kept on fairly in straight. Tactics queried by stewards.
No much early speed, settling along fence behind midfield. Switched out to get run in the straight and kept on fairly to the line.
Steadied shortly after start before cutting closer to rail at first turn. Kept on steadily in straight to 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward from inside draw to sit one-out, one-back at first turn. Put under pressure turning for home but found nothing and gradually drifted back.
Ridden to get forward position and held three-wide without cover. Spent force when put under pressure turning for home.
Began fairly, no speed, racing at rear in one-out position. Lost contact with the field turning for home and finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Had head down when gates opened, losing considerable ground. Ridden to make up loss, racing three and four wide to get within 4L of leader at the 700m before tiring.
Ridden along early but failed to muster, gradually drifting back until losing contact with main field at the turn. Finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Began OK, then ridden patiently at the rear in a one-out position. Not asked for an effort until turning for home, swung wide in the straight and finished strongly to just get there.
Jumped well but didn't settle and shifted to one-out position, three-back from leader. Urged forward on straightening, hit front passing 150m, run down on line.
Made to work from outside draw to lead clearly before cutting to fence passing 1250m. Set steady pace to straight, looked good with 200m remaining, swamped final stages.
Crowded out at start, settling in last pair but away from rail. Caught behind horses top of straight, switched out for run 250m, finished strongly.
Quickly into stride, snatching box seat on settling. Edged closer around turn, stayed on rails in straight and kept on fairly until tightened final 50m.
Pressed forward from wide draw, settling one-out, one-back. Edged closer turning for home, still in contention 200m, flattened final stages.
Worked early to hold rail inside leader but steadied 1300m and allowed to switch to one-out position about 1L from leader. Under pressure on straightening and weakened gradually.
Outpaced and soon last, some 7L from leader. Got a little closer turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Stumbled at start, recovered, cut to fence, settling in midfield. No run in straight until after 200m but only one-paced.
Eased at start, took rail behind the field, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5L, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield on the fence, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, ran on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden early but not muster, raced ungenerously from 600M, checked 400M, made some ground 200M.
Behind midfield along the fence, checked 600M, made some minor ground in straight.
Eased at start, travelled satisfactorily at rear, attempted to make the move around the field 4 wide, made some late ground 200M.
Pushed early but not muster, midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Pushed forward early, 3 wide, badly checked 600M, never progressed.
Raced 3-4 wide at back, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 4 wide throughout, dropped off quickly 400M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, reduced rapidly 400M.
Began well but allowed to drift back, settling one-out, one-back. Switched 3-wide entering straight, pounced on leaders 300m, pulled clear for easy win.
Jumped with field, not pushed, setting 3-back the rail. Closed in around turn, switched out in straight and finished strongly.
Ridden to hold forward position from wide draw, settling behind leading pack but wide. Threw out challenge from 300m but no match for winner.
Got away fairly, held and switched across behind horses from wide draw settling in last pair. Last on entering straight, switched out 350m and finished strongly.
Began well and quickly in box seat behind leader. Badly held up for run in straight but finished off nicely when clear from 200m.
Began fairly, raced in restricted space behind midfield but wide about 8L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, ran on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward to share early pace, racing three-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, still in contention 200m before weakening.
Began only fairly, then shifted across behind runners, unbalanced first turn and lost ground. Had inside run in straight but forced to check 100m. One-paced.
Taken across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Made up ground along rail to be 7L from leader turning for home, one-paced in straight when checked 100m.
Hard ridden along the rail to lead on settling. Set steady pace to 300m when collared. Weakened.

Pressed forward from inside draw to sit half a length outside leader to straight when weakened badly. Rider reported did not stretch out and not comfortable in action when put under pressure top of straight.
Began OK, outpaced, drifting back towards rear in a one-out position. Tailed off in straight. Never competitive.
Eased back from 14, slotted into a midfield spot 3-wide, travelled well with cover, wide bid 500M, threw down a strong challenge 300M onwards, led 100M out and won in course record time.
Settled down 2-wide 3Ls off the good pace, made stealthy progress up the inside, got up for 2nd near line, nearest finish.
Always prominent behind leading pair, well placed to strike 400M, hit lead mid-straight, grudgingly gave way 100M out, lost 2nd near line.
From draw 10 soon shifted across behind runners, towards the rear and 6Ls off the pace making the home turn, stayed on well to go 4th near the finish.
Dropped back to near the rear, travelled smoothly and 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, produced the fastest 400M finish of the night, nearest finish.
Failed to muster speed, caught wide and covered extra ground to go forward, pressed leader from 800M, briefly led in straight, outpaced by pursuers final 200M.
Towards the rear early stages, moved closer to midfield back straight, driven out 550M, ran on steadily without threatening leaders.
Began well but unable to get closer than 3-wide from draw 9, stayed within striking distance turning home, kept on same pace, out of contention 150M.
Settled down midfield, 3Ls behind leaders along the fence, ran on mildly, not pace to challenge leaders.
Restrained in a 2-wide position behind midfield, guided to clear 300M but failed to muster speed, never dangerous.
Began only fairly from inside draw, recovered to race in midfield 4-5Ls back, held ground only over final 300M, never threatened.
Rushed forward from wide barrier, outright lead from 1200M, quickened up pace 600M, lost lead 400M out, weakened mid-straight.
Slow to begin, travelled in last throughout, failed to respond under pressure home turn, soon beaten,
Positively ridden, led to 1300M, sat behind leading pair in middle stages, found no extra turning home, weakened rapidly 200M.

Settled at the back from a wide draw, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off race well to snatch victory near the line.
Began moderately, pressed on from out wide to share the pace, obtained rails run in the front 1100 metres out, kicked over 2L clear 200 metres only to be collared close to home.
Niggled along in better than midfield on rails, baulked for a run early in straight, ran on steadily down inner inside final 250 metres.

Niggled along in first few before settling in midfield around the bend, similar turning in, bumped a couple of times passing the 300 metres, fought on under pressure to reach 2nd before swamped close to home.
Jumped moderately settling in last few, remained well behind turning in, hung in and a difficult ride early in straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled just worse than midfield, improved to midfield on the bend, not clear run passing the 400 metres, finished off race well.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled in last few on rails, not much room early in straight, made modest impression inside final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled 3-wide in prominent position far side, came under pressure after straightening, ran home one-paced.
Broke well from a wide draw, shared pace early before settling 2-wide in 3rd coming out of far side, gained 2nd into straight, faded under pressure.
Settled towards the rear, switched out for a run after straightening, made modest impression early on, found no extra close to home.
Given reminders early, travelled wide in midfield, commenced move on top of home bend, closer up turning in, unable to sustain effort in the run home.
Amongst leaders on rails, box seated around the bend and into straight, faded under pressure.
Settled in midfield, shuffled backward coming out of back straight, wide turning in, soon faded.
Settled wide in midfield far side, took closer order around the bend, shared second briefly entering straight, soon dropped out.
Jumped well before eased back to settle behind leaders on rail, eased out to obtain clear running on straightening, let down nicely to win easily.
Eased back at start to settle towards rear, travelled well and in need of a run home turn, held up early parts of straight and ran home strongly once clear.
Settled midfield, hampered at 700m, held up between 400-300m and ran home strongly once clear.
Jumped well and settled midfield, every chance in straight and made steady ground to the line.
Pushed forward early to find lead, held together home turn, challenged at 350m and fought on well before overpowered final 100m.
Crowded at start and settle worse than midfield, eased out at home turn for clear running and worked home steadily.
Fats out, held initial lead before taking a sit, eased out on straightening, challenged strongly at 300m before overpowered final 200m.
Missed start badly and settled at rear, widest on straightening, ran home OK making up some ground.
Hampered on jumping and settled midfield, moved closer home turn but could not quicken in straight, one paced to the finish.
Eased back from wide gate to settle towards rear, made up some ground in straight.
Urged forward at start and settled outside leaders wide without cover, under pressure at 400m and dropped out of it.
Settled midfield, travelled well and every chance in the straight – saddle slipped at 800m
Settled worse than midfield wide without cover, weakened out of it after tough run.
Pushed along early to settle behind leaders, held together home turn but found nothing in straight.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly and scored impressively by 4Ls.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to take the lead along the fence, got cover 800M, switched to 2 wide 600M, kept on nicely to get 3rd.
Checked at start, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some late ground in straight to get 4th.
Jumped awkwardly and dipped, then taken back to settle 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched to widest turning in, made some ground in straight.
Settled midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, made an early move 650M, kept on the same pace until final 200M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace to the line.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, faded rapidly soon after straightening.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 -3 wide with cover, flattened badly 250M. (Revealed to be a "roarer")
Eased on jumping, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, no progress.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on and dropped off quickly 300M.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Sharp break to lead, crossed to lead 1000m, cuddled into stretch, pressed 400m & shaken up, stretched 2L clear, tapered close home but held on.
Fast start, snagged back to 3 deep with cover behind midfield, advanced on turn, edged 4 deep & driven 500m, ran on to 2nd 200m, closed to wire but held.
Fast start, sat 1 back on rail, niggled 500m, shifted out 400m & driven, outpaced but boxed on in pursuit, gradually closed but always held.
Tardy break & bustled early to race fore of midfield, driven 450m & shifted out, stayed on soundly without threatening.
Taken back early to 1 off behind midfield, shifted 3 deep 750m & minor progress, wide final turn & driven, kept on centre track for moderate headway.
Slow break, rolled on to race midfield 1 off with cover, off heels 950m & shuffled back, continued to over-race, slid back near rear 600m, ridden 400m, kept on evenly.
Poor start, pushed on to race rail midfield, over-raced 800m, shuffled to near rear 600m, driven 400m, ran on one pace.
Tardy break & bustled early to race fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out final turn & driven, plugged on one pace.
Broke well, raced handy 1 off with cover, shaken up final turn, found nil & weakened.
Taken back to race at tail 1off, edged wide 750m & over-raced, minor progress on turn, driven into stretch, plodded on same speed.
Good start widest, trapped 3 deep, rolled to 2nd & slotted 1 off at 950m, ridden 500m to press lead 400m, soon emptied & faded.
Moderate break, raced 3 deep midfield until progress from 950m to sit 1L 3rd turning in, driven but outpaced & emptied 300m, faded out.
Taken back at break to rail near rear, checked off heels 950m, to last 700m, shifted wide & driven final turn, tepid run centre track.
Snagged back from wide to race near tail 3 deep with cover, shifted out 750m & 4 wide progress to mid rank turning in, driven 400m, soon flattened & faded.
Broke ok, rolled forward but caught 4 deep so taken back 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven 500m, wide into stretch, strong closer to lead 50m, drew clear.
Speedy break, bustled to dispute early lead, settled 1 back 1 off, 3 wide & driven 450m, closing when badly impeded 360m & 200m, ran on to 2nd late.
Niggled early to race midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 500m & progress, behind heels & bumped rival 360m, switched rail 200m, darted to join lead 80m but emptied & brushed aside.
Snagged from wide gate to tail on inner, niggled for progress exiting backstretch, 2nd last & ridden 550m, wide final turn, closed centre for solid inroads.
Broke well, rolled to lead 1070m, set tempo & to rail 850m, pressed & driven 400m, maintained edge in battling duel until drifted out 220m &emptied 100m, swamped when bumped 75m.
Slow start wide, driven on outer to slot 2nd 1 off 850m, nudged to draw upside leader 400m, dueling when badly bumped & clipped about 200m, no extra 100m & swamped in run.
Fast start & bustled to lead, headed 1070m, snagged rail 930m & sat 1 back, driven 430m, kept on evenly.
Broke ok, settled rail near rear, drifted out & driven into stretch, stayed on for dour minor headway.
Broke ok, niggled early to sit midfield 3 wide with cover, shifted out & driven 400m, one-paced in run home.
Broke well but bustled along & settled rail midfield, ridden turning in, plugged on tepidly.
Smart break, soon outpaced & settled back 3 wide near rear, slid back to last 700m, found little in tame run home.
Smart start, snagged to race 1 off with cover near rear, edged out on turn & driven 430m, struggled in fading run home.
Reared in stalls & missed break by many lengths, soon tailed off, never a factor.
Settled just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, closed off strongly to score.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace on the rails, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden forward, took box seat, pace good, flattened 200M.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 500M, run ended 150M.
Slow away, pushed forward, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, blocked most straight, just ran on, not properly tested.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made steady ground 300M, flattened 150M.
Midfield along the fence, 5Ls off the good pace, no dash, one paced.
Hard ridden to take rail, led by 1L at good pace, soon out of fuel 350M.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the good pace 3-4 wide, no turn of foot in straight.
At back, 6.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, no progress.
Eased behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, made early move 700M, emptied 300M.
Never competitive and tailed out.

Began well, led on settling before easing back behind leader 1050m. Shuffled further back to third passing 800m, stayed on fence around turn, got split 450m, hit front 300m and continued strongly to the line.

Ridden along to hold one-out spot ahead of midfield. Switched wide turning for home, then finished strongly down centre track to be closest at the finish. Vet reported had laceration on right hind leg.
Unable to take advantage of good draw, settling in midfield in one-out position. Took closer order around turn and ran on strongly between horses in the straight to grab minor placing.
First out, forced to stay wide, settling outside leader to 1050m before taking over and crossing to fence. Collared passing 300m but kept battling until final strides.
No speed, settling well back along the fence. Improved position around turn, got inside run entering straight and finished off nicely.
One of the first into stride before easing off to settle three-back, one-out. Raced a little keenly to 800m, travelled comfortably turn, put under pressure from 400m but only one-paced final 200m.
Was fractious in gate, began awkwardly resulting in rider becoming badly unbalanced. Second-last around turn, got inside run in straight and ran on steadily between horses to be closest at finish.
Hurried along early, settling two-back, one-out at the 1000m. Lay out turn and swung even wider into straight. Raced in restricted room early in straight turning one-paced.
Ridden along from inside draw to hold fence four-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn, switched out entering straight to make run but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing thee-wide mostly about 1L from leader. Lay out around turn, stayed in contention till 200m before weakening.
Stood flat-footed when gates opened and lost considerable ground, settling a distant last. Caught up to the field around home turn, stayed on rail and ran past tired horses final stages.
Slow into stride, ridden to make up ground but checked off heels 1100m. Improved position around turn but found nothing in straight. One-paced.
Ridden along early from wide draw but unable find cover and drifted towards rear but away from fence. Left wide without cover from 800m and found nothing in straight.
Ridden along from wide draw but failed to muster settling toward rear but wide. Taken even wider around turn but one-paced in straight.
Never far off in 4th, quickened smartly along the 3-path inside 400M, led nearing 150M and ran off a decisive victory.
Unable to slot in from 12, left racing 4-wide without cover from 900M, responded positively to pressure final 300M, stayed on well to chase winner over final 150M.
Not hurried early stages, eased back to a 3-wide sport near last, taken wide leaving the bend and closed off final 400M well, got up for 3rd near line but well held by first two.
Positively ridden, chased leader 2-wide, hung out home turn, ran on well early straight but lacked the needed late kick, plugged on for 4th.
Rushed forward from wide gate, sole lead from 850M, kept on steadily on straightening, headed near 150M, weakened towards finish. (Lost left hind plate at start.)
Held up 3-wide in midfield, 4Ls off the pace 400M, stayed on moderately over final 200M, tight for room late stages.
Sent forward, tracked leader from 850M, well placed to strike turning in, ran on same pace under pressure, no threat to leaders inside 150M.
Up with early pace, settled down in 5th from 800M, kept on same pace final 400M, never a threat.
Showed good pace early stages, restrained to a position ahead of midfield, swung wide 500M, kept on same pace and never dangerous.
Settled down behind mid-division, 4Ls off the pace approaching straight, not quickened under pressure, never a serious threat.
Restrained in mid-division, angled out 500M, gave brief response early straight, run ended 200M and weakened towards finish. (No abnormal findings.)
Taken across behind runners, trailed in last 7Ls off the pace, ran on fairly in straight, no clear run final stages but not making significant progress before then.
Began awkwardly, ended up near rear 6Ls behind leader, not picked up passing 400M, no impression.
Driven along to hold a position towards the rear, no further response passing 350M, dropped away rapidly.
Began OK, not pushed, settling three-wide with cover at rear. Began forward move around turn, hit front 250m, started to shorten stride near post and just held.
Taken in from wide draw, settling last. Still a clear last at 400m before switching to centre track and swooping around the field to just miss on the line.
Bumped start, taken in from wide draw to settle three back, the fence. Took inside run in straight and finished strongly to just fail.
No speed, settling at rear along fence. Improved around turn, took inside run in straight but blocked 400m, tightened 300m, shifted in 200m to restricted room, shifted out 100m before finishing well.
Began fairly, then hard ridden to go forward, sneaking up along fence to lead passing 1050m. Collared shortly after straightening, then one-paced.
Ridden to hold midfield position but forced to race wide and then left without cover passing 800m. Urged forward turn, looked chance early straight, one-paced 150m when bumped and unbalanced.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling behind the pace. Got shuffled back turn and near last into straight. Bumped, unbalanced 400m when switched out, ran on steadily final 200m.
Hard ridden early to stay half length outside leader. Urged forward top of straight, led momentarily passing 400m, kept chasing when passed, hampered 150m when weakening.

Began well, made use of inside draw to hold box seat as other forward runners steered clear of the rails. Put under pressure entering straight but only one-paced. Vet reported galloped on left hind leg.

Jumped well and soon in lead but kept away from fence and not pressed, allowing inside runner to move ahead passing 1050m. Stayed 1L behind leader to straight, still battling 150m when severely checked.
Ridden along in midfield but held three-wide mostly. Urged forward on straightening, still within range passing 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward early to sit alongside leaders before being eased back to midfield entering turn. Stayed in midfield to 200m before weakening.
Bumped start, no speed, settling at rear along fence. Urged forward around turn, switched wide in straight but found nothing and faded.
Had the inside draw, but happy to let others push forward and lead. Smoked the pipe in a handy position until he hit go on the turn. Pulled away, and had too much in the tank late.

Began well, but not used up and sat just forward of mid field. Inside winner when he took off just before turn, and went soon after. Chased hard, and was very slowly gaining late but the post came too soon.
Nicely away, eventually settling mid field. Had the mouth open and looked to be full of horse mid race. Hit go 350m out, but didn't have a huge kick. Battled on late to hold 3rd.

Began fairly, and sat just worse than mid field early. Raced keen in the middle stages, coming off heels and raced without cover. Came widest on the turn, and a reasonable strong run right to the line.
Pushed out hard early to share part of the lead. Led into home turn, but looked one paced from there, dropping back to 5th.
Kicked well, and part of an early speed dual in the back straight. Dropped back to be just off on first turn. Looked a tired horse late, and ran on only fairly in the straight.
Allowed to drift back from the wide barrier to sit at the back of the field. Battled away in home straight, without worrying for a place.
Not the best away, and angled in to sit worse than mid field. Keen up the back straight, and awkwardly placed at the 750m. Race was run by the turn, and only plugged away fairly late.
Began well, and eased in to sit in a handy/mid position one off the rail. Showed nothing when asked in the straight and drifted back.
Sat near tail of the field from the jump and never looked settled. Came three wide off heels 700m. Didn't let down late, and well beaten.
Eased out to sit with the back markers early. Last on turn and only got going last 200m, but race was well and truly gone.
Pushed up early to sit mid field. Under pressure before the turn, and never finished off.
Allowed to drift back from the wide draw to sit last on the rails. Gave nothing late, and dropped out to finish last.
