Never far off settling in 5th about 3L back, became 6th in midfield mid-way down back straight, shaken up approaching home turn, fought on doggedly to just get up on line.

Settled wide in midfield from a poor draw, took closer order to reach 2nd outside the leader on top of stables bend, remained well there before hitting the front passing the 200 metres only to be pipped at post.
Jumped fairly on the rails, raced keenly one back in 3rd and always thereabouts, kept on steadily without threatening.
Jumped moderately, settled just worse than midfield, slightly worse around the bend and into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Jumped moderately, recovered to midfield on rails when severely hampered passing the winning post the first time, remained behind midfield to straight, baulked briefly over 200 metres out, finished off race nicely.

Jumped fairly, soon taken back to midfield but raced keenly causing interference passing the winning post the first time, remained in similar position to straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well to share early lead, settled one-out-one-back in 4th far side, came under pressure approaching home turn, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon restrained to last few on rails, met minor interference passing the winning post the first time, raced keenly in last few far side, ran on well down the centre of the straight.
Began well from the one draw, held narrow lead and attempted to make all racing keenly at times, headed when found no extra passing the 200 metres.
Soon taken back to last for rails run, remained same to straight, saved ground turning in, never nearer.
Jumped fairly, steadily restrained to midfield, slightly worse passing the Rock, found nil in straight.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, never on terms.
Fast out and showed pace to share lead, travelled strongly home turn, quickened nicely 200m and was strong to the line.
Urged along early to share lead, challenged strongly on straightening but could not match for winner.
Fast out before eased back to obtain cover midfield, in need of run home turn, clear running at 200m and ran home well.
Jumped well and pushed along to share lead 3 wide without cover, tried hard in straight, weakened final 100m.
Eased at start to settle worse than mid, ridden along mid race, angled out at 250m for clear running, and got going late to finish strongly.
Slow away, settled midfield, eased out on straightening to challenge but couldn't quicken.
Eased back from wide gate, widest on straightening and made steady ground to the line.
Stood flat footed and missed start badly, pushed along to make contact with field home turn and ran home well.
Jumped well, early pace to settle behind leaders, urged at 400 but did not respond and weakened out of it.
Early pace before eased to obtain cover, niggled home turn, ran home evenly – vet: mucus trachea.
No pace and settled at rear, unable to keep up early, ran home ok.
Pushed early but caught wide without cover, lay out throughout, under pressure home turn and dropped out of it.
Rolled forward to take the fence and settle 1.5Ls behind the leader, gradually moved forward 600M, benefited by the slow pace, won easily by 4Ls.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd but winner too strong.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls at slow sectionals, despite headed by the winner 600M, held ground for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow pace, made some ground in straight.
Taken back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, hampered by the slow tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, gradually made an early move 700M, kept on steadily in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made an early move 700M, kept on until final 150M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, weakened soon after straightening.
Eased back, travelled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, unable to show any dash in straight.
Taken back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow tempo, flattened rapidly rounding the Home Turn.
Fast start, rolled to lead 1050m, eased to 2L lead on fence, in command & shaken up 250m, tapered closing stages but just held on.
Broke OK, settled back of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, 7L back & driven 450m, solid headway initially then rattled home late, just failed.
Led from gate, bustled to snag rail, headed 1050m & raced 2nd 2L back, shifted out & niggled in pursuit 500m, hard-driven but unable to overhaul leader & lost 2nd late.
Broke well, sat handy on rail, ridden 450mm, 3L 3rd turning in, gradual gains but edged out of frame at wire.
Rousted start to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 500m, hard-driven & wide final turn, boxed on for solid gains without threatening.
Smart start & rousted early, unable to slot & snagged 1030m, settled midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 500m, shifted wide in stretch, kept on soundly.
Speedy start & driven 3 wide to slot 1 off in 3rd at 780m, bustled along, driven under pressure turning in, one-paced in run home.
Tardy start but recovered to race rail midfield, driven 440m, one-paced in run home.
Taken back from widest gate, soon at tail & niggled along, hard-ridden into stretch, kept on moderately.
Slow start & crossed to rail, raced near rear, shifted out final turn & driven, ran on evenly.
Snagged back at start, sat behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven wide final turn, plugged on moderately.
Taken back at break to race 1 off near tail, outpaced & wide turning in, struggled in run home.
Fast break widest, led 1st turn & snagged rail, 1L clear on tight rein until driven & quickened turning in, battled on to hold all.
Smart start, settled 1 off with cover midfield, switched 3 deep 450m for progress, driven wide to 2nd turning in, gradual closer, always held.
Moderate break, raced rail near rear, shifted out 400m & driven wide into stretch, ran on to 3rd 120m & closed to wire.
Steady start & raced rail near rear, driven 300m, solid closer, just failed to make frame.
Smart start, snagged to race 1 back on rail, hard-ridden & every chance turning for home, boxed on evenly.
Broke well & bustled initially, checked 1st turn on rail, settled back of midfield, switched out 400m & hard-ridden, boxed on evenly.
Taken back at start to race last at tail, shifted 4 wide 570m for minor advance, 5 wide 400m, driven centre track but only tepid progress.
Broke well & driven early, raced handy 2nd 1 off no cover, driven 540m, all out turning in, emptied 300m & weakened out.
Driven from gate & worked to race 3 wide midfield, gained cover 850m, niggled 550m, outpaced & checked 350m, hard-driven but found nil.
Restrained at start, raced near rear 3 wide, shifted 4 wide 850m & rolled to midfield, over-raced 420m, dropped to rear rank turning in, found little.
Broke OK, bustled early, sat 3 deep with cover behind midfield, outpaced & shuffled to tail 450m, plodded on tamely.
Slow start, rolled forward 3 wide no cover to race handy 3rd on outer, niggled 600m, forced wide & shuffled back final turn, emptied quickly & faded.
Slow away, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5L, drifted away 300M, overhauled 50m, ran on for 2nd.
Eased back, 8.5Ls off the leader, worked around the field 3 wide 600M, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, little dash 300M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, ran on ok in straight.
Struggled to keep up at back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, hampered 400M, little dash 150M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed early, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Pressed forward, sat just off the lead 2 wide, reduced 200M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide behind leaders throughout, emptied 300M.
Missed start badly, saddle slipped back, took no active part in the race.
One of the first out but not pushed to hold position, settling behind leader at the turn. Popped off fence turning for home, rolled forward to lead 150m, easily held off late challenge.
Got off with field, settling three-back the fence. Took closer order around turn, badly checked 250m when looking for run, shifted out and finished strongly final 200m.
Used up from wide draw to lead on settling. Slowed tempo back stretch, tried to kick clear entering straight, caught 150m but boxed on.
Beaten for early speed, settling midfield away from fence. Urged forward around turn, widest into straight, finished off nicely down centre track.
Shifted across behind runners from wide gate and last on settling. Taken to fence and made ground around turn. Stayed on fence in straight and ran home solidly.
Pressed forward from wide draw, settling one-out, one-back. Closed in top of straight, looked chance 200m before turning one-paced. Rider fined for not riding out horse to satisfaction of stewards.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Improved along fence around the turn, switched out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Outpaced, settling at rear. Switched out turn and urged forward, kept on fairly in straight until hampered 250m and checked 200m.
Ridden along behind midfield in one-out position to turn. Very wide into straight and checked 250m when one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, dropping to rear. Was last into turn, shifted out entering straight but found little. Inconvenienced 250m.
Urged forward from middle draw, settling one-out, three-back. Rolled forward to look a chance entering straight before turning one-paced from 200m.

Used up from wide draw to go forward, racing three-wide initially before settling outside hind-quarters of leader before turn. Looked chance 400m when threw out challenged but run was short-lived and tired quickly.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, took inside route passing 400M, responded strongly and advanced to challenge leader 100M out, won tussle by narrowest margin.
Sent forward from wide barrier, pressed leader on outside passing 800M, led from early straight, kept on well when driven 250M, strongly challenged by winner final 100M, lost out by narrowest margin.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, travelled keenly passing 700M, fanned wide 400M, ran on well to get within 0.5L of first two.
Held up behind midfield, 3-4Ls back in middle stages, switched wide 150M and closed off nicely to go 4th just before line.
Urged along to be handy just behind leaders, kept on steadily turning into straight, always held by leaders though.
Eased back to near the rear, wide bid 400M and 5Ls to make up on leader, ran on moderately down outside, late impression.
Rushed to early lead, taken on by rival from 900M, kept on evenly to 200M then faded out of contention over final stages.
Not hurried early stages, held up in 9th about 4-5Ls off the pace, stayed on fairly over final 300M, ran past beaten horses and no threat to leaders.
Began well from draw 1, never far off but had to be niggled along to maintain his position 650M out, soon outpaced turning home, weakened towards finish.
Settled down 3-wide in mid-division, fanned wide into straight, not picked up pace over final 300M, never factored.
Towards the rear, outpaced from 800M and detached from field, soon ridden along but failed to muster speed, never involved.
Caught 3-wide no cover from wide barrier, tracked leading pair to straight, came under pressure on the turn, ridden along half way, gave ground rapidly turning home. (Irregular Heart Rhythm)
Began fairly, settling four-back along the rail. Inched forward around turn, took rails run in straight, got split 200m and powered home under vigorous riding.
Ridden along in one-out position midfield, three-back from leader. Taken wide without cover passing 800m but continued to roll forward, taking the lead 150m only to be run down on the wire.
Used from widest draw to lead on settling, then pulled 2L clear back stretch and turn. Looked chance passing 200m but overhauled 150m. Kept on well.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and near last on settling. Made ground around turn, wide into straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began awkwardly, then ridden to hold spot one-out, three back. Took inside run in straight to get within 2L of leader at 200m before turning one-paced.
Outpaced, dropping to rear but away from fence. Improved position around turn, switched out in straight and kept on fairly.
Began fairly, no speed, dropping to last in one-out position. Last into straight but ran past tired horses closing stages.
Got off with field but no early speed, dropping behind midfield in one-out position. Got close to heels turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Urged forward from an outside draw, racing wide initially before settling 2L behind leader. Kept on steadily to 200m before tiring.
Began well and soon in box seat behind leader. Held position to straight when started to weaken. Never competitive.
Ridden to hold second position initially, before settling in fourth along back stretch. Urged forward entering straight but soon ran out of stamina and faded.
Began OK but unable to hold position, slipping back towards rear along fence. Lost position turn and shuffled back to last entering straight. Never competitive.

Moderate start, settled behind midfield on rails, baulked for a run after straightening, steadied 200 metres out before finishing off well to just get up on line.
Jumped moderately, settled just worse than midfield, took close order when wide around home bend, sustained progress to hit the front over 150 metres out only to be pipped at post. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field to the straight despite ridden along early stages, ran on under pressure down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Settled in last few, went wide for a run entering straight, ran on steadily under pressure to hold some chance passing the 200 metres only to be swamped close to home.
Jumped fairly, raced keenly in midfield far side, did not find much room early in straight, ran on inside final 250 metres, nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately from the one draw settling in midfield, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without quickening.
Just best to lead from the middle gate, obtained rails run after first 250 metres, unable to sustain effort and swamped under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Began moderately, ridden along in midfield 3-wide, came closer rounding home bend, held some chance 200 metres out before fading steadily.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on rails, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Jumped moderately, settled just better than midfield, did not find much room from approaching straight, kept on well when clear inside final 200 metres.
Settled wide in last few from the widest gate, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Raced wide without cover better than midfield after beginning from a poor gate, gained closer approaching home turn, dropped out tamely under pressure.
Well there and wide from a poor draw, settled just outside the leader coming out of back straight, dropped away quickly inside final 300 metres.
Not far off to straight, dropped out abruptly.
Settled worse than midfield on rail, pushed along passing 600m before easing out on straightening for clear running, ran home strongly gaining upper hand final 50m to score narrowly.
Pushed early to race on pace, travelled well home turn and challenged strongly at 350m, fought right to the line to go down narrowly.
Allowed to settle worse than midfield, crept forward passing 700m, let down nicely on straightening to challenge strongly at 300m, fought right to the line to go down narrowly.
Positive early to lead initially before taking sit mid race, tried to challenge on straightening but could not quicken and battled to the line.
Settled towards the rear, travelled well home turn and taken widest on straightening and ran home ok.
Jumped well and settled behind leaders, one paced in the straight.
Urged early to settle just off the pace, travelled well home turn, asked for effort at 350m but could not quicken.
Went forward early before striding to clear lead mid race, clear on straightening before challenged at 300m and battled fairly to the line.
Settled mid field on rail, in need of a run home turn, kept to rail, impeded at 300m and then unable to get clear run remainder – ride questioned.
Jumped well and settled midfield, unable to quicken in the straight.
Jumped well and pushed forward but caught wide, remained wide without cover throughout and weakened in straight after tough run.
Eased back from wide gate, taken wide on straightening and battled one paced to the finish.
Settled towards the rear, under pressure passing 600m and failed to run on.
Eased from wide draw to settle at rear, urged along passing 700m and immediately under pressure and failed to run on – must trial.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow pace, ran on strongly when clear 200M.
Eased to midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, dashed well when clear 150M.
Rolled forward to take the lead along the fence at slow sectionals, kept on well until final 50M headed by the winner.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, fought on steadily without threatening.
Checked at start, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow pace, accelerated strongly after 150M.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at slow sectionals, kept on one pace until final 200M weakened. (Questioned for riding)
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Eased to midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, kept on one pace in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, weakened 250M.
Taken back to rear, settled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader 3 wide without cover, despite the slow tempo, flattened 300M.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Broke well, initially driven to press lead 1 off, held up 1.5L back & raced keenly without cover, rolled to press lead 650m, shaken up 450m & led 360m, quickened clear & in command.
Speed to lead, to rail, snagged & headed 1040m to sit 1 back, in pocket turning in, shifted out 400m & in clear 250m, closed centre track to nick 2nd last strides.
Broke OK, raced 3 wide no cover 4th, advanced final turn & driven to vie for lead 360m, not pace of winner & brushed aside, boxed on but tapered to lose 2nd late.
Smart start wide, bustled to lead 1040m, 1.5L clear & to rail 850m, headed 360m & driven, outpaced but battled on until tapered late & lost 3rd.
Tardy start, sat midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m & driven, closed off for late headway, eased behind heels final strides.
Tardy start, taken to rear 1 off, shifted widest into stretch, quickened & closed without threatening.
Started ok, bustled 3 deep midfield, under pump turning in, out-paced but stayed on for minor late headway.
Broke well, snagged back & caught 4 wide with cover behind midfield, wide & driven 430m, ran on for minor inroads, bumped close home.
Broke ok, sat rail fore of midfield, shuffled back on turn, briefly in pocket & stumbled 400m, driven 350m, one-paced in run.
Missed break & last, bustled & soon raced midfield on rail, shuffled back on turn to near rear, shifted off fence 350m & driven, stayed on moderately.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover fore of midfield, improve to 1 back turning in, shaken up 400m & switched out, found nil & plodded tamely.
Slow start & bustled along 3 wide with cover behind midfield, hard-ridden into stretch, plugged on weakly to wire.
Awkward start, raced rear rank on inner, shifted out turning in, found little in run home.
Broke ok widest, trapped 4 wide no cover fore of midfield, driven 400m, found nil & faded tamely.
Broke ok, bustled early, niggled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, under pump in 5th 550m, progress to 2nd 380m, quickened up 320m & led 300m, drew clear.
Tardy start, speed to sluice through to sit 3rd on rail 2.5L back, bumped 420m, driven to 3rd 360m & 2nd 250m, boxed on in vain pursuit.
Slow start & at rear, soon moved to behind midfield 3 wide with cover, shifted wider home turn & ridden, quickened to 3rd 160m, kept closing to wire without threatening.
Slow start & taken back, sat near tail 1 off with cover, shifted out on turn, driven 400m, checked off heels 320m, lugged in but stayed on for minor gains.
Tardy start, raced rail near tail, niggled 600m, ridden final turn, stayed on dourly for minor headway.
Taken back from wide gate to race 3 deep with cover midfield, driven 500m, wide into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Sharp start widest & rousted, caught wide no cover fore of midfield, 4th & niggled 3 deep 600m, driven 550m, 4 wide & outpaced final turn, plodded one pace.
Taken back from wide to last pair 3 deep, off heels 1020m, niggled along, driven 500m, kept on evenly.
Fast break & prominent initially, snagged to sit 2L 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden turning in, bumped 420m & all out, tapered in run.
Fast break & soon bustled to lead, clear & to rail 1200m, shaken up 400m, headed 280m & weakened out.
Taken back at start, raced wide with cover near rear, very wide home turn, driven 400m, weak effort.
Broke ok, sat rail midfield, 5L off lead & niggled 800m, ridden 580m, under whip turning in & shifted off fence, struggled in fading stretch run.
Broke well, bustled but outpaced & soon slid back to behind midfield 1 off, checked off heels 950m, driven 470m, found nil in tepid run.
Broke with others, raced midfield 1 off, ridden into final turn, found nil for pressure, faded & eased when beaten 200m out.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 400M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed it strong finishing efforts 300M for 2nd.
Secured a more prominent spot in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 400M despite not suited by the slow pace, run ended 100M.
Settled just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1L at slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, lack room 400M, no dash when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, made early move 700M to take advantages from the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 9Ls off the leader, raced keenly, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked most straight, ran on fairly.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the slow pace, out of fuel 300M.
Eased to sit behind midfield on the rails, 6Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Hard ridden to take box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, reduced quickly 400M.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader on the fence, suited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
Began well, eased to one-off position 3L from leader. Allowed to stride at own tempo to straight, niggled 400m, surged forward to lead 250m, kept on strongly to line.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling. Slowed tempo approaching turn, kicked ahead top of straight, caught 250m but kept on well to line.
No speed, settling at rear some 7L from leader in one-off position, Urged forward around turn, wide into straight, finished strongly down centre track.
Ridden to get forward position, settling in box seat behind leader. Closed in top of straight to look a chance and kept on well, getting close to heels near finish line.
Quickly into stride from inside draw, holding fence three-back from leader. Unable to hold position around turn and one-paced in straight.
Got off fairly, not pressed settling in one-off position three-back from leader. Switched out approaching straight but only one-paced.
Had front feet off ground when gates opened and slow. Pressed forward to settle 1L behind and outside leader approaching turn. Drew level entering straight but flattened final 200m.
Steadied shortly after start and then difficult to settle until approaching turn, dropping to rear. Last entering straight. Never competitive.
Positively ridden out the gate, travelled well outside the lead, took over near 400M, responded gamely and kicked 2L clear mid-straight, turned one pace late stages but managed to hold on.
Settled just off midfield 3-wide, moved into contention near 400M, rallied strongly down center of track, did best work final 150M, nearest finish.
Settled down midfield inside, travelled smoothly to straight, quickened to go 2nd 250M, battled well to line but always held by leader, lost 2nd 50M out.
From wide barrier raced no closer than 3-wide, no cover from 1200M, advanced to the front line 500M, kept on steadily turning in for a creditable 4th.
Eased back to a rearward position 7Ls off the pace, waited with till 400M, switched wide 350M and ran home well.
Reserved in a 2-wide spot behind mid-division, taken out to challenge inside 400M, stayed on moderately without threat to first four. (Jockey dropped right rein 50M)
Tracked leading pair along the fence, driven along 500M but not pace to challenge leaders, plodded on same pace to line.
Chased leaders 2-wide, well placed to strike 450M and had his chance, failed to keep up with leaders passing 200M, weakened towards finish.
Sent forward setting steady pace, joined by rivals inside 500M, soon lost lead entering straight and faded from 300M.
Guided to a midfield position 3Ls off leaders, difficult to settle 1300M out, struggled to quicken leaving the bend, ran on same pace never a threat to leaders. (Muco)
Settled towards the rear, took rails run into straight, couldn't quicken. (Jockey reported abnormal breathing)
Lost ground when bumped at the start, travelled much further back than usual, swung 3-wide on the bend but already beaten off home turn, eased mid-straight.
Missed the jump, lost a considerable amount of ground, detached from field and never in contention. (Unacceptable Performance, to OBT and OVE)
Began well, surged through to lead passing 800m, ridden hands and heels from then on but kept finding to maintain clear margin to the line.
Began well, settling close to outer fence three-back from leader. Put under pressure 400m and kept on strongly to the line.
Pressed forward from awkward draw to get within 1L of leader on reaching 800m. Urged forward approaching 400m to look a chance, unable to close gap but kept on well.
Checked start, dropping to rear but edging closer to outer fence. Began forward move approaching 400m and finished strongly final 200m to be closest at the line.
Began OK but inconvenienced when taken to outer fence, and then difficult to settle from 800m. Put under pressure 400m and finished strongly to just miss the frame.
Began OK, raced on own in midfield away from the fence about 4L from leader before switching in 500m and finishing off nicely.
First out, led initially before crossing to outer fence and sitting behind leading pack. Still in contention passing 200m before tiring.
Began fairly, taken to outer fence, bumped 800m, kept on fairly before making forward move 400m. Was one-paced when shifted in and bumped 150m.
No speed, raced on own down centre track 5L from leaders. Urged forward passing 400m but only one-paced.
Knuckled over at start, dropping to rear. Crossed to outer fence but bumped 800m and shifted in. One-paced in straight.
Had front feet off the ground when gates opened and slow into stride, settling last but away from outer fence. Ran past tired horses final stages.
Began well, pressed forward, travelling 2L from leader and three-wide from outer fence. Travelled well till put under pressure from 500m when faded gradually.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling inside but 1L behind leader. Stayed in contention to 400m when gave ground steadily.
Began well, holding outer fence about 3L from leader. Was still battling when crossed and checked 100m, and eased down. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea. Lame left front leg.
Elected to sit midfield early, after breaking well. Full of horse on the turn, and pressed forward from 400m. Far too strong late to win by 3L.

Pushed up to sit in a handy position early, but dropped back to midfield when crowded out at 850m. Positioned in behind winner on turn, but elected to go the wider route. Valiant chase late without threatening winner.
Pushed out early to lead and set early race tempo. Held the rails run and plugged on fairly in straight, before weakening late.
Pushed hard early to share the lead, one off the fence. Battled in straight, dropped back and unbalanced late but just held on for fourth.

Never settled early, and checked 850m before travelling 3 wide with no cover near the lead. Crowded again at the 650, but still managed to find open space on turn. Battled fairly, and lost late race for fourth.
Took the length of the back straight to settle handy on the fence. One paced and only battled in straight.
Clipped heels and blundered early, settling six lengths off the second last horse. Still a long way off on home turn, but strong run in the straight to overtake half the field.
Pushed early to sit handy behind leaders. Looked to press on from turn, but didn't run on and faded late.
Drifted across from the wide barrier to sit at the back of the pack. Looked to run on from home turn, but hampered 350m and never ran on from there.
Pushed hard early, but ended up settling worse than midfield. Only plugged away and never looked likely.
Handy/Mid position early trapped three and four wide. Tracked widest on the turn, and never ran on.
Never found a position from the wide gate, and travelled four wide with no cover for the duration. Rider was unbalanced 650m. Race was run by the 400m, and dropped back from there.
Dropped back to rear of the field early. Gave nothing, and a clear last.

Jumped well, soon gained stands rails position as a joint leader, went clear inside final 150 metres, readily.
Jumped well from a poor draw, soon came to share the pace one off stands rails, matched pace with eventual winner but no answer to winner's turn of foot final stages.
Slightly slow out, settled just off the pace in 5th racing keenly at times, came to challenge under pressure inside final 300 metres, failed to feature closing stages.
Niggled at early, settled just off the pace in 4th, kept on at the same pace without quickening.
Jumped well, soon dropped back behind midfield of small field in 6th, made modest progress in the closing stages.
Close up early, soon came to join the leaders after the first 200 metres, shared the pace onto course proper, gradually faded.
Jumped fairly but soon dropped well behind.
Slightly slow out, well back throughout.
Jumped awkwardly, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Eased back at start to settle at rear, travelled well and kept to rail home turn, gained split at 300m and finished off strongly.
Settled just behind leaders, travelled well home turn, challenged strongly at 300m, hit lead at 200m before overpowered final 50m.
Pushed forward early to hold rail position inside leader, quickened nicely in straight and boxed on gamely.
Crowded at start and eased back to settle worse than midfield, ran home fairly in straight.
Jumped well and pushed along to settle behind leaders, held up passing 350m, ran home OK when clear final 200m.
Sent forward early to settle on pace, leaders back on straightening, challenged briefly approaching 300m but unable to quicken and battled gamely to line.
Slow to begin, quickly improved along rail to settle midfield, held up for clear running early part of straight but did not run on when clear.
Settled worse than midfield, asked to quicken on straightening, tried hard but couldn't make ground.
Fast out and settled in front, held together home turn, unable to quicken at 400m and weakened out of it from 250m
Eased back from wide gate to settle 4 wide at rear, wide on straightening and one paced in straight.
Sent forward but caught wide without cover, under pressure passing 700m and gave ground in straight.
Raced wide without cover in midfield position, never on track and failed to run on in straight.
Taken back from wide barrier, travelled 8.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, dashed strongly to score comfortably.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Pushed to settle in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited the slow tempo, finished off nicely until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals, ran on gradually.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on nicely until final 50M headed.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals, just held ground.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, at back, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Taken back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow pace, made minor ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at slow sectionals, weakened soon after straightening.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, made minor ground, faded 200M.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, never looked likely.
Eased back, settled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, despite the slow pace, soon weakened after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Pushed forward to take the fence and led at slow tempo, dropped off after 700M, tailed out.
Broke well & eased through on rail to lead 900m, soon extended 1L clear, shaken up 350m & quickened impressively, drew well clear for easy win.
Speed to edge narrow lead at break, headed 900m & sat 1L 2nd 1 off no cover, closed on leader turning in, ridden 350m, outpaced & boxed on evenly.
Sharp start, raced behind pace 1 off with cover, driven 450m & shifted out to go 3rd, boxed on dourly but always held by the 2nd.
Taken back from widest gate, bustled along 3 deep with cover near rear, driven widest home turn, stayed on dourly to nick 4th, no threat to principals.
Broke OK & rousted, raced midfield 3 deep with cover, shifted wider & driven 430m, outpaced but battled dourly to 4th 250m, tapered late & edged out to 5th at wire.
Slow start & checked, rousted at tail, advanced on rail to sit 2nd last, hard-ridden 450m, stayed on moderately past well-beaten rivals.
Taken back from wide gate & soon at tail, 2L detached & driven turning in, plugged on one pace past weakening rivals.
Moderate break & driven, unable to hold mid-rank position & bustled along behind midfield on inner, hard-ridden final turn, struggled in run.
Smart break, caught 3 deep no cover but handy, ridden 450m, found nil & faded tamely.
Lacked pace at break & bustled through 1st 300m, settled rail & followed leader 2L back, niggled out of backstretch, driven 450m, emptied 300m & weakened.
Missed break, keen but restrained near rear, allowed to roll on at 900m to sit 1 off with cover midfield, driven 450m, found nil & faded markedly.
Sharp start & driven, soon outpaced & drifted back 4 deep no cover to race back of midfield, under pump 600m, never a factor in weakening run.
Broke with others, soon 2L off lead tracking front rank, niggled 650m, ridden 480m & quickened to lead 350m, joined 200m, dug deep to edge duel.
Bumped start, covered up 2L back mid-track, shifted inside & bustled 450m, driven 400m & quickened to 2nd, joined leader 200m, lost out in tight duel to wire.
Broke well, tracked 1 back on rail, shifted off fence 550m, switched for clear run 340m & driven, quickened to 3rd 150m without threatening.
Broke OK but slight bump & soon near rear centre track, ridden 500m, ran on well down middle for solid late headway but never a threat.
Good break, sat front rank, outpaced & under whip 350m, unable to quicken, plugged on evenly stands' side.
Awkward start, raced near rear towards stands' side, under pump 450m, checked 380m & shifted in, driven & ran on dourly.
Smart start, disputed lead in centre, driven & headed outright 350m, outpaced & tapered final 100m.
Ridden from gate to lead, to stands' rail 800m, soon joined, under pressure 450m & ridden, outpaced & soon beaten, tapered to wire.
Bumped start, bustled & speed to race close to front rank centre track, ridden 450m, one-paced in tepid run home.
Tardy start, raced rail near rear, ridden 400m, shifted inside 200m but outpaced, stayed on moderately.
Broke well, raced front rank 1 off fence, driven under pressure 400m, weakened in run.
Broke well, soon vied for lead centre track until 700m, under pump 550m, outpaced & tapered final 250m.
Broke ok, raced rear pair, niggled 650m, driven 400m, found nil in tame run.
Smart break but soon outpaced & niggled, dropped back until last & ridden 500m, never a factor.
Pushed forward, enjoyed the perfect trip in box seat, closed off well 300M to score.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace on the fence, lack room 400M, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at good pace, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, stumbled 400M, checked 350M, made steady ground 200M.
Very slow away, 9Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, bumped 350M, made steady ground 200M.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, checked 350M, lack turn of foot when clear.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, flattened 400M, checked badly 350M.
At back, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, checked and blundered 350M, not tested.
Pushed forward, 3Ls off the leader 3 wide, weakened 400M, checked severely 350M.
At back, checked badly 350M, not properly tested.

Placing: FE
Comment: In front of midfield, broke down 350M.

Placing: UR
Comment: In front, emptied 450M, rider dislodged 350M.

Placing: FE
Comment: Midfield, near the 350M was brought down and dislodged rider.
Hard ridden from wide draw to hold midfield position but wide. Raced three-wide around turn, taken to centre track in straight and finished strongly to win on the line.
Began OK, holding midfield position close to rail. Caught in traffic top of straight before switching wide and finished strongly to just miss.
No early pace, settling at rear and moving closer to fence. Still well back entering straight, got inside run and finished strongly to just miss.
Crowded out start, urged forward settling one-back, one-out. Edged forward entering straight to look a chance 200m, turning one-paced final 100m.
Made good use of inside draw to lead on settling, setting steady pace to straight. Kicked ahead top of straight, looked winning chance 200m before flattened final stages.
Ridden along from wide draw, settling half a length outside leader along back stretch. Kept battling early in straight before tiring final 100m.
Began well, ridden along to hold box seat behind leader. Stayed on rail around turn but unable to close gap in straight.
Began well, racing outside leader initially before easing one-back, one-out back stretch. Kept tabs on leaders to 200m before tiring. Jockey reported horse raced flat.
Jumped fairly, no speed, dropping to rear between horses. Lost position around turn, got close to heels 300m, one-paced.
No speed, racing at rear but away from fence. Was last entering straight, switched out to make run but found nothing under pressure.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing in midfield but three-wide mostly without cover. Kept on early in straight but tired after passing 200mm.
From inside draw managed to secure a ground saving trip behind leaders, responded well when driven out 350M, hit lead 50M and held off late challenge from 2nd and 3rd.
Held up in midfield 2-wide, travelled smoothly to straight, into clear 400M, closed off well to be nearest at the line.
Fractious in stalls, began only fairly, settled down 4Ls off the pace, taken wide 550M, hit the line well, nearest finish.
Shaken up early, placed outside leader, battled on well turning in under constant drive from 10lb claiming rider, just failed to hold off top three finishers final 50M, narrowly beaten.
Broke sharply, shared lead on the inside at a steady tempo, kept on well in straight, caught 60M out, swamped late and just missed frame.
Restrained to the rear, patiently ridden, ran on well down inside , nice debut over a trip too short.
Raced along the 2-path tracking leading pair, kept on steadily entering straight, always held by leaders.
Began only fairly, settled at the back 5Ls off the pace, difficult obtain run early straight, stayed on well towards the finish over this shorter trip.
Began awkwardly, improved to a midfield position 3Ls off pace, kept on same pace in straight, not serious threat to leaders.
Unable to get closer than 3-wide, no cover from 900M, couldn't muster the pace to challenge in straight. (Jockey dropped rein near 250M)
Settled down 4Ls back in a 3-wide position behind midfield, brought wide 550M, plodded home down outside.
Caught wide early from outside gate, restrained to a 3-wide spot near the rear, kept on same speed turning in, never a threat.
Jumped fairly, ridden along to hold position three-back, one-off. Took closer order around turn, put under pressure top of straight and ran on strongly to win close home.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, crossing to rail passing 1500m. Set steady pace to straight, kicked clear 300m, kept on solidly until caught final strides.
Began well, ridden along from wide draw before settling outside hind-quarters of leader. Threw out challenge top of straight but lay out under pressure. Kept on well to line.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped. Ridden to hold rail three-back from leader. Shifted out top of straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began well but not pushed, settling four-back along rail. Caught flat footed turn when leaders accelerated, switched out straight and ran on fairly.
No early speed, dropping to near last along rail on settling. Switched out turning for home, taken wide in straight and ran on steadily.
No early speed, dropping toward rear along fence. Stayed on rail around turn, took inside run in straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Made good use of inside draw to grab box seat on settling. Followed leader around turn, still in contention 200m out before flattened final stages.
Steadied soon after start, dropping to last. Not pushed until entering straight when took inside run, making some late ground.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw soon after start, dropping toward rear. Hampered passing 1200m, taken out entering straight but one-paced under pressure.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw but still forced to race three-wide mostly. Improved position turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early, settling one-back, one-out back stretch and turn. Kept on fairly early in straight before weakening final 200m.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw settling towards rear away from fence. Covered extra ground turn and found nothing under pressure in straight.
Pressed forward early to settle in midfield but raced fiercely and unable to maintain position, gradually slipping back. Never competitive.
Pushed forward from wide barrier early, and found the lead by first turn. Three lengths clear on the home turn. Was weakening late, but had just enough to hold on the line.
Began well and happy to sit in midfield on the rail. Was a long way off on the turn, but showed plenty of dash in the straight to just miss by a head on the line.
Began well, and ended up just forward of midfield, two and three wide. Ran on strongly from the 400m to figure in the finish late.
Broke well, and pushed forward to sit handy on the rail. Went at the 400m, and ran on well. Went stride for stride with third, and only outmuscled late.
Began well, and elected to ease into a position in midfield, one off the fence. Rider changed whip hand at 250m, and ran on well from there.
Dropped back to sit at the rear of the field. Plugged along fairly in straight, but never threatening.
Bumped early, then pushed up to sit just forward of midfield. Looked to go on turn, but only battled away fairly from there.
Dropped back to sit at the rear of the field on the fence early. Came wide in straight for a run, and ran on steadily from there.
Pushed forward and led early, before eventually sitting just behind leader at the 1000m. Faded from the 300m, and played no part late.
Didn't begin well, then awkwardly placed on heels early. Dropped back to sit just worse than midfield one off the fence. Only ran on fairly late.
Taken back to sit with backmarkers, but never settled early, sitting three wide. Widest on turn, and only battled in straight.
Dropped back from the wide barrier to sit last. Only ran on fairly, and never in it.
Moderate start. Elected to sit midfield, but was left racing three wide with no cover. Was in a handy position at the top of the straight, but peaked at 200m and faded from there.
Got head up on jumping but pushed forward to sit near midfield. Faded badly from the turn, and not persevered with late when out of contention.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-2 lengths back in 4th, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and scored by a length.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in 5th, 4 lengths or so back near 800M, 2-3 wide on turn, finished off well in straight to get 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, crowded near 900M, angled out on turn, no daylight until final 150M, made good progress thereafter to get 3rd.

Bumped start, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, travelled keenly near 1000M, 2 wide 7 lengths back on turn, improved near 500M, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, raced outside the leader in 2nd, same position on turn, found no extra gear in straight, just stayed on evenly.
Began well from gate 13, difficult to slot in and settle early, found cover near 1100M, raced in midfield to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail in the early stages, improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.

Began well, raced in 6th, crowded near 1400M, difficult to settle thereafter, same position on turn, unable to obtain clear running at any stage in the Straight and consequently was not able to be tested.
Moderately away, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 5 lengths or so back in midfield, no clear running early straight, stayed on fairly when switched out final 200M.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide at rear, 8-9 lengths back near 800M, taken wide after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter and eased final 100M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail throughout, made no progress after turning in, never competitive.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.

Settled just worse than midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, quickened well inside final 150 metres to win readily.
Jumped fairly settling just over 2L off in 5th on rails, shifted out for a run entering straight, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in forward of midfield, ran on down the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Vied for lead from the middle gate holding narrow advantage outside the 2nd throughout far side, crossed to rails over 500 metres out, ducked out in front over 100 metres out and soon headed.
Broke well to hold rails run in 2nd inside the leader, allowed leader to cross to rails coming out of back straight, one-paced under pressure when hampered close to home.
Settled just off the pace in 4th, lost position into straight, ran home one-paced.
Taken back from the widest gate to settle at the back, trailed the field into straight, ran on under pressure past beaten horses in the run home.
Taken back towards the rear from a wide draw for rails run, similar entering straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Ridden positively from a wide draw, settled prominently in 3rd 3-wide without cover far side, failed to respond under pressure in the run home.
Jumped moderately, never better than midfield, made no impression in straight.
Ridden to better than midfield early stages, dropped back to midfield approaching the Rock and lost further ground rounding home bend, made no further impression in straight.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Taken back at start to settle at rear, hampered 400, let down nicely once balanced in the straight and powered home over the top of all.
Settled behind leaders, drifted back to midfield, positive move passing 800m and challenged strongly for lead at 500m, kicked clear in straight before swamped final 50m.
Hampered at start before settling midfield, in need of run home turn, clear running 300m and tried hard entire straight.
Jumped awkwardly before settling behind leaders, in need of clear running home turn, angled out and worked home steadily.
Settled towards rear, commenced forward move 700m, ran wide home turn and finished off okay.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled well, crowded at 500m, kept to rail home turn and ran home one paced.

Jumped awkwardly, pushed early and settled midfield, continued to improve albeit wide without cover, outside leader 700m but quickly under pressure to hold position, hard ridden home turn and battled to the line.
Settled midfield, awkwardly placed and checked passing 500m, hard ridden home turn and worked to the line one paced.
Eased back from wide gate to settle at rear, hard ridden when taken wide home turn but did not run on.
Went forward to settle outside leader, under pressure 600m and gave ground in straight.
Jumped well, travelled okay in lead, challenged passing 500m and gave ground quickly in straight.
Pushed along early and caught wide without cover, strode forward to settle outside leader, under pressure 650m and gave ground quickly – must trial.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader, quickened nicely to score by a neck.
Taken back, travelled 5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, made an early move gradually 800M, dashed well for 2nd, missed by a neck.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly until final 100M headed by the winner, just held on for 3rd.
Eased back from a wide gate, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader, dashed well to get 4th.
Taken back from a wide barrier, settled 6Ls off the leader on the fence, switched wide 650M, finished off nicely.
Hard ridden forward to take the lead along the fence, kept on only fairly until final 200M weakened.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on same pace to the line without any acceleration.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced home without any threats.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, emptied soon after straightening.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Pushed to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, weakened rounding the Home Turn.
Broke well, taken back to midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep 500m for progress, driven for strong wide advance, powered to lead 180m, drew clear.
Smart start & ridden to dispute lead 3 deep 1st turn, rolled to 2nd 1 off 1050m, soon back to 3rd & shuffled 1 back 600m, niggled 500m, driven into stretch, stayed on to nick 2nd late.
Broke OK & niggled to settle handy 3 deep no cover, rolled to edge lead 600m, ridden under pressure final turn, headed 180m, lost 2nd late.
Broke with others & vied for lead on fence at 1st turn, soon settled 1 back, ridden 400m, boxed n evenly without threatening.
Sharp start & disputed lead 1 off at 1st turn, in front 1200m & to rail 1050m, set steady tempo & headed 650m, shaken up 400m, wandered 300m & tapered.
Held up at break, to rail 1300m & sat behind midfield, over-raced 1150m & keen 950m, driven 400m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Fast break & prominent wide, soon snagged to 1 off behind midfield, shaken up for progress 400m, wide into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Broke with others, sat rail midfield, shifted off fence & driven 320m, kept on evenly.
Slow start, sat 1 off near rear, ridden 500m for wide run, stayed on for one pace centre track.
Taken back from widest gate, raced rail near rear, niggled 500m, driven 400m but only tepid progress.
Snagged back to race at tail on rail, shifted 1 off & driven 500m, plugged on tamely.
Sharp break but bustled initially, sat 1 off fore of midfield & over-raced 1050m, ridden 400m & shifted out turning in, outpaced & not a factor.
Steadied to camp rail behind midfield, smooth traveler & shifted out home turn, shaken up 250m, quickened centre to lead 80m, in command.
Fast start to dispute initial lead, settled 1L back 1 off, under pump 520m, grinding run to lead 130m, headed 80m.
Fast break, settled 1 back on rail, driven into stretch, grinding progress but held in 3rd.
Tardy start & rousted to race 1 off with cover midfield, wide & driven 320m, stayed on for dour headway.
Moderate break & bustled to sit rail fore of midfield, niggled 500m, driven 350m, boxed on evenly.
Driven from the widest & crossed to handy 3 wide no cover, advance to press lead 1 off 800m, 0.5L back & driven into stretch, led all out 220m, headed 130m & tapered.
Smart break but bustled 4 wide no cover, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, ridden 400m & swung wide into stretch, kept on one pace.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, driven turning in & shifted out, stayed on moderately for minor inroads centre track.
Rousted to edge lead & soon to rail, skipped 1.5L clear 1000m, pressed 800m, nudged 0.5L ahead 600m, driven turning in, headed 220m & faded.
Taken back at start to race at tail on rail, driven home turn, plodded one pace.
Snagged back to sit 1 off with cover near rear, ridden 480m on outer, switched inside 200m, plugged on same speed.
Tardy start & bustled, pushed on to midfield 3 deep, badly impeded 1000m & lost ground, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled along, driven 3 deep 480m, struggled & faded.
Pressed forward steadily, sat 1L off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1L at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
At back, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 350M, progressed steadily when clear.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, just held ground in final furlong.
Pushed forward, trapped 3-4 wide throughout just off the lead, harmed the fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no turn of foot in straight.
Raced 4 wide throughout in midfield and lost significant amount of ground at bends, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, never improved.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Kicked clear around the turn and kept on strongly to the line.
Hard ridden early, staying with leading pack before bumped and unbalanced 700m, dropping three-back from lead. Switched out for run in straight and finished strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling distant last. Caught up with field entering straight, switched to centre track and finished strongly.
Ridden along between horses settling three-back, one-out. Urged forward around turn but wide, kept on gamely in straight to be nearest at finish.
Slow into stride, taken to rail and ridden to make up ground, settling four back from lead when steadied 600m. Popped off rails 300m to make run and kept on steadily.
Quickly into stride, racing inside leader to turn before easing back into box seat. Stayed on rail entering straight and kept on gamely without closing gap.

Beaten for early speed and initially in trailing trio before making ground entering turn. Switched out in straight and ran on fairly before being bogged down inside heels and not fully tested final stages.
Hard ridden early to share pace before dropping 1.5L behind and outside leader at turn. Looked chance entering straight but only one-paced.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, picked up some ground around turn, kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Began well, ridden to stay with pacemakers but wide, started to over-race entering turn, hung out losing ground. Faded final 200m.
Pressed forward from wide draw, and held three wide without cover. Lost ground around turn and weakened gradually in straight.
Crowed out and bumped start, hard ridden but didn't muster, gradually falling back till last at turn. (Rider reported horse lost interest). Unacceptable performance.
Always prominent just off pace, moved out to 3-wide striking position 600M, led 150M but have to fend off challenges from sides for a narrow victory.
Settled 3Ls off the pace in about 5th, travelled well, loomed a strong chance 200M, fought on well to line and was one stride short of catching the winner.
Broke well from inside draw, settled beautifully behind the leaders, responded well when guided to clear 250M, looked a chance but was out-battled by first 2 final stages, clear from rest.
Blundered badly on jumping, recovered to race in midfield 4Ls off the pace, saved ground on inside, stayed on moderately for non-threatening 4th.
Guided to a rail position, settled near the rear 6Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly down inside, no threat to first 3.
Soon led, took them along slowly early stages, taken over by rival back straight, in contention until 200M, faded towards finish.
Sent forward, caught 3-wide until reaching the lead 1000M, led one off the fence at good pace, headed 200M, weakened towards the line.
Held up near the rear, raced 3-wide for much of the trip, ran on mildly over final 300M, not reached contention.
Eased back from wide barrier, taken across behind runners, raced as the back marker over 6Ls away, had much to do turning in, made limited progress only.
Settled down 5Ls off the pace along the 2-path, swung widest for home, stayed on only fairly, no impression.
In mid-division, caught 3-wide from first turn, no cover from 1000M, gave ground in straight, eased towards the finish. (Jockey fined for weighing in 2 lbs overweight)

Never far off on rails, tracked leader into straight, hit the front passing 300 metres and soon went 2L clear, held on well under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled better than midfield, steadied approaching the 800 metres, saved ground turning in, came to challenge upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well and ridden along prominently, lost position around the bend but renewed effort after straightening, kept on steadily under pressure.
Sluggish at start, trailed the field to 600 metres, tight between runners most of way in straight but finished off race impressively.
Settled in last few, made up good ground inside final 200 metres, did best work late.
Taken back from a poor draw travelling 3-wide most of way to straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track, swamped late.
Broke well from a poor draw, gradually shifted back to midfield before home bend, similar turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly settling just worse than midfield one off the rails, similar turning in, ran on steadily down inner of straight but without threatening.
Never far off in 5th one off the rails, similar entering straight, found nothing.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, raced wide just worse than midfield, kept on steadily without quickening down the centre of the straight. (Lame next day)
Jumped well, shared early pace on rails before kicking 1L clear around home bend, held same into straight but headed when found no extra inside final 300 metres.

Taken back for rails run, just improved to midfield on rails when checked 800 metres out losing ground, towards the rear entering straight, kept on same pace without making serious impression in the run home.
Vied for lead from the widest draw, eventually settling 3-wide without cover in a prominent position, remained similar into the straight and soon weakened.
Began moderately but pressed on to join the leader, settled just off the pace around home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Pushed early to settle midfield, travelling well to home turn, obtained split between runners at 300m and driven clear final 150m.
Jumped well and settled outside leader, moved up to challenge home turn, took lead at 300m before overpowered final 150m.
Jumped well but unable to cross from wide gate so eased back to settle midfield, moved forward when pace slowed mid race, tried to challenge on straightening and worked to the line steadily.
Slow to begin, pushed early to settle midfield, commenced wide run passing 700m, widest on straightening, made steady ground to the line.
Eased back from wide gate at start, raced keenly when pace slowed mid race, travelled well home turn and ran home well without threatening in straight. Raced tight concluding stages.
Slow out but driven hard to improve along inside and settle midfield, shuffled back near 800m, lay inwards near 200m, finished nicely in latter stages once clear.
Fast out and settled behind leader, tried to quicken in straight but could not, one paced to the line.
Jumped well but caught wide without cover in handy position, moved up to challenge leaders home turn but soon under pressure and one paced thereafter.
Jumped well from wide gate and went forward, obtained lead near 1200m setting slow tempo, asked for effort at 400m but did not respond and weakened final 200m – rider questioned
No early pace and eased back at start, crowded at 1100m, worked home okay in straight making up a little ground.
Fast out and settled behind leader, shuffled back mid race when pace slowed, kept to inside in straight but could not quicken and one pace to the line, crowded final 50m.
Slow to begin, settled at rear, taken wide on straightening but did not run on.
Pushed hard early to settle behind leaders, niggled approaching 500m, under pressure straightening and dropped out of it.
Settled at rear, tracked up behind runners at 600m, asked for effort on straightening but gave nothing.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, then taken back to rear, despite harmed by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score by a neck.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, kept on until final 150M weakened, hung on for 4th.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, ran on steadily after disappointing for running 200M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader from a wide barrier, despite suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace until final 250M weakened.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final 200M weakened.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited the slow tempo, weakened over the last furlong.
Taken back to rear, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Eased back to rear, travelled 4Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, never a factor.
Always at rear, never looked likely, tailed out.
Began well, hard ridden inside leader to get to the front passing 1000m and kicked clear. Shaken up top of straight, kept finding under pressure to hold off challenges final 200m.
Ridden along three-wide early behind midfield. Urged forward around turn covering extra ground. Looked chance 200m when threw out challenge but unable close gap.
Began well, settling one-back, out-off. Travelled keenly 1100m, got shuffled back turn. Switched out in straight and finished well. Rider dropped whip 300m.

Pressed forward to lead on settling before easing back to second passing 1000m. Urged forward top of straight and kept battling until flattened final stages. Vet reported substantial blood in trachea.
Ridden along early before cutting to fence three-back from leader. Caught behind horses and steadied 500m, blocked for run early in straight, switched out and ran on well before tightened 100m.
Pressed forward along rail to hold box seat on settling. Stayed on rail around turn but blocked for run in straight until passing 200m. Kept on well.
Slow into stride and clear last on settling. Switched wide entering straight and made good progress until 200m turning one-paced. Rider dropped whip 300m.
Began fairly, taken to rail settling four back from leader. Got shuffled back to last around turn, stayed on rail in straight and made some late ground.
Ridden forward from an outside draw, racing three-wide to and around turn and early in straight. Got within range of leaders 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward from outside draw, settling ahead of midfield in one-off position. Taken wider and lost position around turn. Kept on fairly in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw but still caught racing wide at the rear. Switched out entering straight but made little impression.
Hard ridden to get up and race alongside leading pair but wide and without cover. Closed in top of straight before giving ground final 200m.
Began awkwardly, bumped and lost ground start. Started to over-race passing 1000m and steadied off heels 800m. Never got into the race.
Ridden early to stay with pace but soon unable to hold position slipping to behind midfield in one-off position. Weakened in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw, settling one-back, one-out. Not comfortable with pace, took off passing 950m and kicked 2L clear in straight. Kept on strongly.
Began well, settling in box seat. Followed leader into straight, popped off fence 300m, kept om well but unable close gap.
Tightened early before settling three-back from leader along fence. Stayed on fence entering straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden along early settling ahead of midfield but three-wide. Switched wider entering straight and kept on steadily, doing best work final 200m.
Not pressed, settling in midfield away from fence 8L from leader. Taken wide entering straight and boxed on fairly without looking dangerous.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Affected by slow pace and caught 10L behind leader into turn. Ran on fairly in straight.
Began well, grabbing lead on settling. Set extremely slow pace to 950m, dropping to 2nd when another took over. Faded gradually in straight.
Steadied early and then dragged back by slow pace settling more than 10L behind leader. Urged forward around turn but only one-paced final 200m.
Ridden along early, settling two-back, one-off back stretch. Remained in chasing pack to straight turning one-paced from 200m.
Began awkwardly, bumped, then shifted across behind runners to rail, four-back from leader. Popped off fence around final turn but found nothing in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last along rail. Improved position slightly around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Made use of good draw to race inside early leader before dropping back to 3rd passing 950m when another moved forward. Started to weaken soon after straightening.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling toward the rear. Got left behind in last place around final turn and finished tailed off.
Eased at start, 8Ls off the leaders 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score only in last stride by a short head.
Eased at start, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, made steady ground 400M, just beaten by narrow margin in 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, 3.4Ls off the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M, led 250M, overhauled 50M, ran on for 3rd.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well to the line.
Slow away, pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 250M.
In front of midfield, checked early, 3.5Ls off the fast pace 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Pressed forward, shared the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed forward, just off the leaders 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, reduced quickly 450M.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, trapped 3-4 wide just off the leaders, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 400M.
Eased at start, always at rear, checked badly 400M and rider nearly dislodged, not tested.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 4 wide throughout outside the lead, harmed by the fast pace, faded 500M.
Behind midfield, never competitive, hung out badly and tailed out.
Began well, settling along outer fence 3-back from leader. Started to pick up momentum 400m out, pushed though gap along outer rail to win close home.
Quickly into stride, clear leader on settling, moving from inner to outer fence. Lay in under pressure but kept on well under hands and heels riding final 400m only to be run down close home,
Quick from the gates, cutting across track 1L from leader and 3-away from outer fence. Urged forward from 400m but unable to close the gap.
Ridden along in midfield early, edging closer to outer fence and making ground to be 2.5L from leader. Forced to switch in final stages but kept on well.
Began fairly, taken to outer fence, settling in midfield. Picked up speed from 400m, switched in for clear run, finished off nicely.
Began well, racing a half length inside leader. Looked a chance passing 400m but flattened final 150m.
Ridden to hold forward position about 2L from leader until course proper. Urged forward passing 200m but flattened close home.
Hard ridden from inside draw, settling behind midfield while gradually edging towards outer fence. One-paced final 400m.
Outpaced early, taken to centre track, making up some ground to course proper, turned one-paced final 400m.
Ridden but outpaced early, then steadied passing 800m. Weakened gradually from 400m before checked 100m when shifted in.
Began only fairly and soon struggling at rear, three-away from outer fence. Never competitive.
Slow into stride, taken closer to outer fence but at rear. Put under pressure passing 400m but found nothing.
Bounded in air when gates opened and last on settling. Switched in passing 400m but never likely.
Quickly into stride, holding outer fence 2L from leader. Stayed with leading pack to 400m when tired. Vet reported substantial blood in trachea.
Settled down 4th 2-3Ls off the pace, pressed on 450M, quickened to lead 150M, kept on gamely to line under urging.
Shaken up early, tracked leaders in 3rd, came out 350M, closed well to go 2nd near line.
Positively ridden, emerged as sole leader 900M, set steady pace to straight, headed 150M, rallied on, beaten to 3rd near line. (Lost LF plate during race)
In mid-division 4Ls off the pace, urged along 500M, stayed on moderately for 4th.
Sent forward, tracked leader in 2nd, kept on one paced in straight, faded to 5th 100M out.
Niggled along after the start, outpaced by leaders, settled down near rear 8Ls off the pace, made some progress final 350M but not reached leaders.
Behind mid-division, 7Ls off the pace 400M, stayed on only fairly, not reached contention.
Held up in midfield, 3 wide no cover from 800M, lay out home turn, failed to go on entering straight and retreated.
Taken across from wide barrier, well off the pace in rear, not much room passing 300M, gave limited response only over final 200M.
Severely checked after the start, ended up on the outside of rear pair, 10Ls off the pace 400M, failed to pick up on his AWT debut, never threatened.
Towards the rear 8-9Ls behind leader, no closer than 3-wide throughout, lacked a further response passing 300M.
In mid-division, outpaced when race tempo quickened 500M, first to be beaten turning in.
Not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Urged forward around turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly for easy win.
Began OK, holding fence three-back from leader. Switched out entering straight and finished off nicely down centre track.
Ridden along early to hold spot one-back, one-off. Loomed outside leaders entering straight to look a chance and kept on well.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling four back from leader. Made strong forward move around turn to look a chance 400m. Kept on well.
Began well, leading for a few strides before taking the sit on leader. Switched out entering straight to make run but lay in under pressure, tiring final stages.
Hampered soon after start, dropping back 8L from leader in one-off position. Took inside run in straight and ran on fairly.
Pressed forward from awkward draw to lead on settling. Set steady pace to straight before tiring final 200m.
Ridden along to hold forward position, one away from fence. Taken wide around turn and wider in straight. One-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling last. Made up some ground turning for home but never dangerous.
Crowded for room at start, ridden but failed to muster. Made up some ground turning for home but got close to heels and eased. Ridden out final 200m.
Began well, ridden to hold box seat behind leader. Closed in around turn but found little in straight, weakening gradually.
No pace, ridden along at rear but mostly three wide. Hung in early in straight and never competitive.
Pressed forward from wide draw, sitting half a length outer leader on settling. Lost position around turn, weakened quickly in straight.
Ridden along from wide draw, settling in midfield but wide and without cover. Gave ground around turn and finished tailed off.
Slowest out, but had no trouble getting forward to sit handy with cover. Tracked behind leader to the 300m, pulled out and ran on strongly. Kicked again when challenged by second late
Began well, and pushed forward to share the lead on the rails. Got working from the 300m, and pulled away with winner. Kicked again late, but just missed.
Elected to drop back after jumping to sit mid field on the fence. Went looking for runs outside in the straight, before taking a run along the rails. Finished off fairly, but weakening near the line.
Got back early to sit worse than midfield, on the fence with cover. Ran on OK late without threatening.
Jumped with them and pushed to lead early when racing keenly, before sitting 1 off 1 back. Didn't have much kick in the straight, and only finished off fairly.
Began well, and moved forward to sit handy but on heels. Had a small kick when asked the question in the straight, but only ran on fairly after that.
Dropped back from the jump to sit last. Pushed forward from the 800m to sit closer to midfield. Didn't get a run until 200m, and ran on fairly from there.
Jumped well, and taken forward to eventually sit handy, three wide with no cover. Was a tired horse late, and only plugged on fairly.
Jumped OK, and taken back to sit midfield, one off with cover. Had clear air in the straight, but never ran on and only hands and heels in the last 100m.

Trapped 4-5 wide with no cover from the widest gate, before dropping back to rear of the field with cover. Came widest on turn, but didn't have much left in the tank, and was only fair. Blood in the trachea.
Awkwardly away and ridden up early to share the lead. Gave nothing when placed under pressure in straight, and faded badly from the 200m. Unacceptable performance.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the pack, three wide but with cover. Didn't respond in straight, and weakened out from 200m.
Jumped OK, but ended up sitting midfield three wide rounding the first turn. Handily placed on turn, but peaked early in the straight, weakened badly and eased out late.
Began OK, but wouldn't settle early, had the head in the air and was trapped 5 wide midfield, before dropping to the rear. Race was effectively over by the turn, and eased out of it.
