Jumped fairly, held rails run within 2L of speed, closer up turning in, hit the front passing the 200 metres, won readily.

Began moderately, travelled towards the rear on rails, took closer order coming out of back straight, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily to reach 2nd passing the 100 metres but never threatening.
Settled towards the rear, ran on steadily between runners to be nearest at finish.
Waited with, shifted wide into straight, ran on down the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly on rails but soon dropped well behind, saved ground turning in, kept on well despite tightened momentarily 100 metres out.
Never far off, one-out-one back in 4th rounding home bend, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.

Broke well and ridden along from a wide gate, shared pace briefly before coming 2L back in 5th far side, racing wide without cover throughout, slightly further back turning for home, kept on same pace in straight.
Prominent early, dropped to midfield coming out of back straight, hung in badly early in straight, but kept on well at the finish.
Ridden along from the widest gate, with leaders early before shifting back behind midfield far side, remained wide in last few entering straight, failed to quicken under pressure.
Ridden along amongst leaders, clinging onto 2nd outside the leader around home bend, weakened out of contention after straightening.
Broke well, soon gained slender lead on rails, led until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Ridden along amongst leaders after beginning from a poor draw, gave ground from approaching home bend dropping to tail-end after straightening.
Jumped well, urged forward and eventually crossed to obtain lead at 600, travelling well home turn, quickened nicely at 250m to establish a break and fought on strongly to hold off all.
Allowed to settle worse than midfield, travelled nicely home turn, angled out on straightening and ran home strongly.
Slow out and settled at rear, widest on straightening and ran home resolutely.
Settled worse than midfield, commenced positive move around field at 550m, challenged strongly at 200m but inclined to lay in and couldn't finish race off.
Pushed along early before easing to take sit behind speed, crowded at 600m, made steady ground in straight.
Fast out, went forward from wide gate and caught wide before sitting outside leader at passing 600m, urged along home turn, tried to issue challenge in straight but weakened final 100m.
Jumped awkwardly and settled towards rear, crowded at 900m, tried hard in straight and held position to the line.
Jumped smartly and shared early lead, tightened at 600m when crossed, awkward home turn and couldn't quicken in straight but battled to the line.
Pushed along early to settle behind leaders, asked for effort on straightening but didn't respond and one paced to the finish.
Jumped well, caught wide without cover in midfield position, under pressure home turn and gave ground in straight.
Settled midfield and inclined to race keenly, under pressure on straightening and weakened out of it.
Settled midfield, shuffled back at 500m and failed to run on in straight.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, fought on gamely, just scored by a short head.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well for 2nd, missed by a narrow margin.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, enjoyed the slow pace, swung wide rounding the Home Turn, ran on well until final 50M weakened to get 3rd.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, stayed on well until final furlong weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, made ground steadily.
Settled worse than midfield, 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed to midfield from a wide gate, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Sent forward from a wide gate to park outside the leader, despite suited by the slow sectionals, weakened soon after straightening.
Taken back from wide gate, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by slow tempo, one paced home.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Ridden hard early to take lead on settling, set steady pace to straight, shaken up and kicked clear passing 200m, never threatened.
Got off OK, not much speed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched very wide in straight and ran on strongly without looking a danger to winner.
No speed, dropping to last on settling, crowded turn and taken wide, got inside run in straight and ran on steadily to grab minor placing.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear but wide. Hampered around turn, bumped and unbalanced 450m, ran on steadily between horses in straight.
Hard ridden early to hold forward position racing three-wide to turn before dropping one-back, one-off. Unable to accelerate in straight, boxing on one-paced.
Pressed forward inside leader before easing into box seat around turn. Left flat-footed when leader kicked 200m and one-paced thereafter.
Began fairly, shifted out, bumped and unbalanced. Stayed on fence and improved position around turn, straightening 4L behind leader. One-paced final 200m.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing three-wide without cover about 1L from leader. Shaken up entering straight but had little in reserve. One-paced.
Ridden along between horses in midfield but gradually lost position around turn. Dropped back further on straightening. Faded.
Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden to make ground, settling 3L behind leader at turn. Switched in top of straight and weakened gradually.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing three- and four-wide without cover to turn. Started to give ground shortly after straightening.
Slow into stride, taken to rail and made some ground. Dropped back to last in straight and weakened further.
Began well but content to sit 0.5L behind and outside leader despite slow pace. Moved forward 700m to share lead, kicked clear 400m but joined approaching 200m, kept finding for narrow win.
Quickly into stride, following leading pack in a one-off position 1L from leader. Peeled out top of the straight to get run, picked up momentum 200m, pressing leader all the way to the line.
Allowed to stroll to the front and set a sedate pace until 700m when joined up front. Overtaken entering straight but kept boxing on to the line.

Jumped with field but proved difficult to settling going into first bend, settling in midfield away from fence. Improved position turn to look a hope 200m but unable to close gap. Hung in badly throughout.
Not much early pace but able to hold rail position 3-back from leader. Raced tightly around turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began only fairly, but shaken up and quickly made ground along rail to sit behind leader entering final turn. Kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Slow into stride, steadied and then shifted across behind runners to rail but at rear. Checked and switched out turn, switched in again but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from awkward barrier, racing three-wide without cover back stretch and final turn. Started to give ground passing 200m. Jockey reported concern with action.
Ridden along from outside draw to sit in midfield but three-wide. Remained wide around turn and early straight before giving ground final 200m.
Hard ridden wide but didn't have the speed to go forward and held behind midfield. Improved slightly around turn but tired shortly after straightening.
Restrained soon after jump and taken across behind runners from wide draw, dropping to last back stretch. Taken to rail in straight but made little headway.
Slow into stride, shifted out and kept 3-wide at rear. Allowed to stride forward from 1100m circling field tone third passing 550m when ran out of stamina and dropped back.
Pushed early, 5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward for a prominent spot, just off the leaders 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to take rail, shared the lead at slow sectionals, hung on until 100M flattened.
Pushed to occupy a midfield spot, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Pushed to obtain box seat, hampered first turn, benefited by the slow tempo, soon flattened 200M.
Hard ridden forward, shared lead 2 wide at slow sectionals, ran on strongly until 150M emptied.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 8Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, ran on ok in straight despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased at start, 8Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, 6.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Pushed forward along the fence early, checked first bend, 4Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield before settling along rail 3–back from leader. Awkwardly placed top of straight, got split 250m, dashed though to lead from 100m, won easily.
Began fairly, ridden along towards rear until crowded out 900m. Taken to rail and made ground steadily, to 200m, switched out and finished off nicely.
Began well, not pushed, holding rail behind leader to straight. Kept on steadily in straight without threatening first two.
Ridden along from an outside draw, racing wide with little or no cover 4L from leader. Continued to race wide around turn, wider in straight, but kept on solidly.
Jumped well, ridden to lead on settling, setting sedate pace. Kicked clear around final turn, still in front 200m, shortened strides final 100m.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and distant last on settling. Tagged on to field entering straight, took rails run and ran on steadily closing stages.
Raced a little keenly early and ridden to hold midfield position between horses. Improved around turn to look a chance entering straight, turning one-paced.
Began awkwardly, becoming badly unbalanced, losing ground, settling 3-wide at rear. Covered extra ground turn and still wide in straight, becoming one-paced final 200m.
Began OK, settling behind midfield away from fence. Urged forward between horses around turn, kept on fairly early in straight before tiring from 200m.
Pressed forward to sit 1L outside leader back stretch and turn. Closed in top of straight to look a chance before coming under pressure and drifting back.
Ridden vigorously from an outside draw, racing 3-wide abut 2L from leader. Started to feel the pinch turning for home and weakened badly in straight.
Restrained to a 2-wide position behind midfield, bided his time and waited until 250M, quickened impressively, got up just in time.
Sent forward from wide barrier, allowed an uncontested lead, kept on well entering straight, caught near line.
Settled down 3-4Ls off the pace ahead of midfield, ran on well to claim 3rd, nearest line.
Towards the rear, 3-wide trip, stayed on well to go 4th over final 300M.
Tracked leader, given every chance but always held in straight, hung on to 2nd until 30M, hampered late and lost 3 placings near line.
Positively ridden, chased leaders in 3rd, kept on evenly to the finish, but lacked the extra gear to seriously challenge.
Began only fairly, dropped back to rear 6Ls behind the pace, made stealthy progress over final 200M.
No closer than 3-wide throughout, ran on steadily to 100M, faded final stages.
Guided to the fence after the jump, travelled 3-4Ls back, nudged along home turn, kept on evenly final 350M.
Held up in midfield along fence, shuffled back a bit nearing the turn, had task in hand on straightening, made steady progress, however no clear run final stages.
Began awkwardly, caught 3-wide no cover just off the pace, ran on same speed home straight and was swamped 100M, eased towards finish.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, ended up in last over 7Ls off the pace, given reminders middle stages, stayed on fairly down outside entering straight.

Jumped moderately, settled in midfield on rails, commenced move entering straight, hit the front over 350 metres out and soon drew clear, won readily.

Waited with, took closer order briefly half-way out, snuck up on rails entering home straight, obtained a nice passage after switched inside 400 metres reaching 2L 2nd shortly afterwards, never threatened the winner.
Settled towards the rear close to rails, shaken up entering home straight, ran on steadily to reach 3rd 200 metres out.
Settled in last few from a poor gate, did not find much room after straightening for home, finished off well inside final 250 metres.
Settled towards the rear 3-wide without cover to straight, came under pressure on straightening, ran on steadily inside final 250 metres.

Began fairly from a wide gate, gradually settled just better than midfield early in back straight, steadied and lost some ground half-way out, kept on at the same pace without quickening in the run home.
Settled well behind, commenced move wide rounding home bend, made short-lived effort to reach 4L 4th briefly 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Broke well, taken back behind midfield travelling 3-wide down far side, went wider entering straight, found nothing under pressure early in straight.
Began well from a low draw, settled in midfield shifting 3-wide down far side, took closer order round home bend, badly checked 300 metres out, made no impression thereafter.

Jumped well from the one draw, settled mainly just over 2L off the lead on rails, slightly further back coming out of back straight, renewed effort approaching home turn, soon dropped out of contention under pressure in home straight.
Worked his way forward around stables bend after beginning from the widest draw, eventually settled 1L back in 2nd one off the rails, weakened noticeably passing the 300 metres.

Pressed on from a wide gate to soon cross to rails in front on stables bend, steadied pace to hold half a length advantage far side, went 1L clear around home bend before swamped inside final 400 metres.

Jumped fairly, given reminders in early stages settling wide just better than midfield, improved to 3rd within 2L of pace coming out of back straight, folded up quickly after turning into home straight.
Ridden positively from a tricky gate to gain a prominent position, travelled mainly in 3rd far side and 4th around home bend, gave ground under pressure inside final 400 metres.
Jumped well, settled outside leader, quickened nicely off slow pace to challenge strongly in straight holding off all challengers.
Jumped well, settled in front setting slow pace, nursed along home turn, quickened nicely in straight and fought hard to the line.
Raced wide without cover and travelled keenly in the middle stages, moved up to challenge strongly on straightening and fought strongly to the finish.
Jumped awkwardly before pushed along to settle in handy position, tried hard entire straight.
Settled midfield, travelled strongly home turn, worked home nicely once gaining clear running in the straight.
Fats out before eased back to settle behind leader, tendency to race keenly and fought on well without threatening in the straight.
Eased back at start from wide gate, made midrace move around field , wide on straightening before run ended near 200m and then one paced to the line.
Settled midfield, travelled strongly home turn, tried to issue a challenge in straight but could not quicken and one paced to the line.
Settled towards rear, over raced and blundered when awkwardly placed near 1000m, widest on straightening and ran home okay.
Taken back from wide gate, wide on straightening and made some ground in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly and missed the start, quickly improved to settle worse than midfield, hard ridden home turn and did not run on.
Jumped awkwardly and settled towards rear, commenced to lose ground on straightening.
Eased back from wide gate, hard ridden home turn and did not run on in the straight.
Pushed along early to settle midfield, under pressure home turn and weakened out of it final 200m
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, ran home strongly to score by 1L.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, dashed well for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on well until final 100M emptied, hung on for 3rd.
Eased back to rear, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, closed off well to get 4th.
Jumped slowly, then pushed to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
Camped midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made no impression in straight. (Rider stated that became unbalanced in its action over the concluding stages)
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked likely after straightening.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Showed good early pace to take the fence and led by 1/2L, emptied 350M.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, faded rapidly soon after straightening, tailed out.
Broke OK, tracked leader 2L back on rail, closed on lead final turn, shifted out 400m, shaken-up 300m, quickened to lead 130m, drew clear.
Broke OK, outpaced a touch & settled rail midfield, revved up into home turn, stayed on gradually to claim 2nd late.
Speed to lead, crossed to rail 1000m, 1L clear & shaken up 320m, flat to the boards & headed 130m, tapered & lost 2nd 40m, shared 3rd.
Taken back from wide, covered 1 off behind midfield, off heels 600m, back to last trio turning in & driven, switched centre 350m, rattled late to share 3rd.
Fast start & prominent, snagged 1150m & raced 5th 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, driven turning in, boxed on evenly.
Bustled & pressed early lead, snagged at 1000m to race close 2nd 1 off no cover, 1L back & driven 350m, outpaced & soon lost 2nd, lugged in under pressure, tapered late.
Taken back at break to race 3 wide with cover midfield, bumped 650m & shuffled back a spot, driven along 580m, stayed on for minor headway.
Tardy start, raced rail near rear, niggled 850m, hard-ridden home turn, ran on for solid gains until passage blocked final 50m.
Broke OK, lacked early pace & niggled midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 800m, hard ridden into stretch, kept on evenly, checked off heels last strides.
Taken back to tail 10L off pace, niggled 850m, driven turning in, stayed on for moderate inroads.
Settled back from break, raced 1 off near rear, shifted widest into stretch, driven centre track & plodded on for limited headway.
Missed break & shoved at tail, soon advanced to race behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven 800m, all out & wide into stretch, outpaced & faded out.
Sharp start, raced 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, niggled 600m, driven wide into stretch, soon emptied & struggled in fading run.
Smart start widest, unable to slot & rolled to sit 3rd 3 deep no cover, lost place 600m & niggled, wide & driven 430m, emptied 300m, faded out.
Broke well & camped rail midfield, shifted 1 off for progress 650m, shaken up 420m & quickened up, strong run to lead 60m, drew clear.
Speed wide to lead, to rail 1550m, headed 1450m, regained narrow lead 1200m, driven turning in & kicked 2L clear, tapered & headed 60m.
Broke Ok, raced keenly 1 off behind midfield, trapped in pocket turning in until daylight & driven 220m, rattled to 3rd & kept closing to wire.
Broke well, pushed on 3 deep to lead 1450m, slotted 1 off no cover 1200m & settled close 2nd, ridden into stretch, outpaced but boxed on evenly.
Taken back & crossed to rail, bustled to race behind midfield, driven 620m, shifted out in stretch & stayed on for minor headway.
Good break, settled 1 back on rail, niggled 500m, driven 430m, plugged on one pace.
Broke with others, raced 1 off fore of midfield, shifted 3 deep 650m, driven 500m, kept on dourly.
Prominent at break, soon snagged to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 800m, crowded into stretch, driven 300m, stayed on evenly, checked late.
Fair break, taken back to sit 3 deep midfield without cover, wide & driven home turn, outpaced & plugged on same speed.
Snagged back to sit 3 deep with cover behind midfield, driven into stretch, kept on centre track without threatening.
Slow start & settled rail in last trio, driven turning in, plugged on tamely.
Taken back from the widest gate to race in rear rank 1 off, ridden 500m, plodded on evenly.
Taken back to 3 wide with cover in rear rank, pulled hard under restraint, ridden into stretch, found nil in tepid run home.
Sharp start, raced 1 off no cover close up until shuffled 1 back 1200m, a touch keen, shifted 3 deep 650m, driven into stretch, found little & faded.
Eased at start and took rail at rear, improved along the fence to sit 4Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 300M to score.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, sat just off and outside the lead, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, however trapped 3 wide no cover, allowed to improve steadily just off the lead to take advantages of the slow pace, just held ground.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, little dash when clear.
At rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no dash, bumped 100M.
Bumped start, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pressed forward, led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, however soon out of fuel 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, no turn of foot, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace on the fence, soon reduced 300M.
Began well and quickly in box seat stalking leaders. Got split top of straight, ran on strongly to win close home.
Made to work to lead passing 1000m. Kicked head top of straight, looked winner 200m, run down close home.
Pressed forward from awkward draw to settle one-back, own-out before turn. Urged forward entering straight but unable match first two.
Used up early from wide draw to lead initially before eye-balling leader from 1000m to 400m. Boxed on gamely in straight but unable hold position.
Began well, used inside draw to hold rail position three-back from leader on settling. Stayed on rail turn and kept on steadily to the line.
No early speed, racing two- and three-wide behind midfield. Covered extra ground turn, wide into straight, one-paced.
Slow into stride, dropping to last along rail. Last into the straight, no run until 200m when switched out, made late ground.
Hard ridden early to hold one-off position three-back from leader. Moved into contention top of straight then one-paced. Found to have an irregular heart rhythm and bled from both nostrils.
Began only fairly, then crowded out and lost ground 1000m, dropping to near last. Wide around turn and into straight but found nothing under pressure.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw, racing at rear in an one-off position. Never got into the race and finished tailed off. Lame right fore.
Settled down midfield 2-wide, 3-wide bid and moved to contention 600M, responded gamely to urgings, hit lead 150M, drew clear final 100M for a commanding victory.

In midfield, held up in 5th back straight, travelled well behind leaders home turn, switched back inner for clear run 250M, stayed on without matching winner, narrowly prevailed in blanket finish for 2nd.
Away well, restrained to sit just behind leader along the 2-path, vied for lead passing 400M, not finishing pace of winner final 150M, battled on to line, lost 2nd last stride.
Eased back to a rearward position 9Ls off the pace, bid 3-wide passing 700M, did best work final 200M, just missed out on a placing.
Waited with near the rear in a slowly run race, crept closer to leaders home turn, guided to clear 400M and closed off nicely, not getting to winner but was only beaten a nostril by the 2nd.
Blundered at the start, close up in 3rd, kept to inside turning in, battled on well only grudgingly gave way final strides.
Settled down in 4th 3Ls off the pace, ranged 3-wide 600M, vied for lead passing 400M, turned one pace final 150M.

Held up 6-7Ls back in midfield, saved ground on the inside, keen and not helped by the slow tempo midway, stayed on moderately entering straight, steadied 200M, regrouped and closed off the race well.
Dropped back to last, raced as the back-marker throughout, closed off steadily down the outside, held ground only.
Towards the rear, pushed along 500M but failed to make significant progress.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, bustled along 550M, couldn't find extra gear, never a threat to leaders.
Worked to the lead from wide barrier, was restrained once in front and took them along slowly, lost lead inside 400M, no extra 300M and faded to last.
Ridden along from wide draw, settling midfield in one-off position. Swung wide entering straight and ran on strongly to just get up on time.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling along rail 4-back from leader. Had to switch very wide in straight to get run and finished strongly, just missing out.
A little slow into stride but made up ground quickly between horses, settling three-back, one-off at turn. Urged forward top of straight to look a chance 200m and kept on well.
Began well and quickly in box seat, keeping tabs on leader. Blocked for a run in the straight. Surged through gap 150m, but flattened last strides to miss out on third spot.
Bumped and unbalanced start but hard ridden to go forward, settling three-quarters of a length behind leader. Battled on gamely until fading final strides.
Got off well, made full use of inside draw to settle along rail three-back from leader. Stayed on rail entering straight and boxed on gamely without looking dangerous.
No early speed, boxing on towards the rear, five-back from leader. Switched out in straight to make run and kept on fairly.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Put under pressure turning for home but kept on strongly till passing 200m when could find no more and faded.
Ridden along early to hold ideal spot one-back, one-off. Still in contention top of straight but started to give ground from 200m.
No early speed, steadied passing 1300m, dropping to second last. Taken wide in straight to make run nut never competitive.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Never got into the race after that.
Began awkwardly, shifted in and bumped, then urged forward, settling 3L from leader but wide without cover. Kept on well to 200m when tired.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling towards rear but kept well away from fence. Taken wide in straight but found nothing and faded.

Began well, and into a handy position on rail. No luck getting a run on the turn. Came back through a gap 300m. Had the outside horse laying in on top late, but finishing best. Crossed 2nd, but won it in the Stewards room.

Unbalanced on jumping, settling mid, 1 off the fence. Kicked from 400m finishing strongly. Lay in under the stick late, interfering with the run of 2nd who was finishing better. Crossed the line in 1st, but relegated to 2nd.

Fairly away, and found a position midfield on the fence. Began a run on turn, hampered twice between the 400 and 300m. Ran on very strongly once he got clean air, making up 2 lengths in the last 100m to steal 3rd on line.

Began well and pushed forward from the wide alley to sit handily in 3rd behind the leaders. Finished OK in the straight, and momentarily crowded at the 100m. Just lost 3rd place in the barest of margins on line.
Quickly away to lead early on the rails, before sitting just behind the new leader mid race. Plugged away 1 paced late, without threatening a place.
Began well, but elected to ease back to the rear of the field with cover from the wide draw. Ran on OK, and picked off a few in front, in the straight.
Crowded and unbalanced on jumping before finding a position just worse than midfield, 1 off the fence with cover. Travelled only fairly in the straight.
Began well from the outside gate, but had to settle just behind midfield, 3 wide facing the breeze. Came wider on the turn, and was trying hard late, but finished only fairly.
Began well to sit handy, 1 off the fence. Asked the question in the straight, but never let down when placed under pressure.
Began fairly, then elected to drop to the rear of the field, on the fence with cover. Only plugged away late.
Began OK, but dropped back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field. Came widest on turn, but never responded to pressure in the straight.
Taken forward from the jump to lead. Peaked at the 200m and faded quickly from there.
Very awkward to begin and lost ground, settling at the rear. Under pressure before the home turn, but gave nothing and eased out late.
Began awkwardly and settled worse than midfield on the rail. Didn't respond in straight, and eased out. First Hong Kong run.

Never far of in 4th to straight, fought on under pressure to assert authority inside final 100 metres.
Pressed on after a moderate start to gain 2nd outside the leader over 800 metres out, came under strong pressure to hold every chance after straightening only to be outsprinted close to home.
Broke well from a low draw, settled in midfield in 6th on rails, fought on steadily from 5th into straight to be nearest at finish.
Ridden positively, obtained rails run in the lead over 800 metres out, led until finding no extra over 150 metres out.
Settled just worse than midfield on rails, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled 2-wide in rear of midfield, similar turning in, kept on steadily under pressure in the run home.
Broke well, ridden to the front before ceded advantage to hold 3rd behind the leader on rails, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate but soon taken back to last few, kept on same pace in home straight.
Began moderately, travelled mainly 3-wide without cover in 5th to 400 metres, jockey lost use of iron briefly passing the 900 metres, made no impression in the run home.
Ridden along but soon dropped towards the rear racing wide, remained similar entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Always well behind, saved ground turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Settled in last few from a poor draw dropping to tail-end near the Rock, dropped out after straightening.
Pushed early to hold rail and eventually lead, travelled strongly home turn, quickened nicely at 300m and easily held off all challengers.
Jumped well, urged along early to settle outside leader, moved up to issue challenge on straightening, tried hard but no match for winner.
Settled midfield, crept closer along rail approaching home turn and ran home nicely in straight.
Jumped well and eased back to settle behind leader, raced keenly at 1000m, unable to quicken in straight and battled solidly to the line.
Eased back from wide gate to settle at rear, kept to inside in straight and made steady ground.
Eased back from wide gate to settle towards rear, commenced to improve near 500m, widest on straightening and worked home solidly.
Settled worse than midfield, pushed along approaching home turn, shifted out at 250m to obtain clear running and finished fairly.
Jumped okay but no early pace and eventually settled worse than midfield, niggled at near 500m, one paced in straight.
Jumped well, raced keenly early stages in handy position, under pressure on straightening and weakened out of it.
Crowded early, blundered and checked near 1000m, raced wide and without cover from 800m, moved up to challenge on straightening but quickly under pressure and weakened out of it.
No early speed and settled towards rear, urged to move forward passing 450m but unable to make ground in straight.
Raced wide and without cover throughout with a tendency to lay outwards, never in it.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score comfortably.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow pace, kept on steadily to get 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, kept on steadily until final 100M weakened.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, despite suited by the slow sectionals, weakened over the last furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, found nothing in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Eased back to rear from wide gate, settled 7Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked a chance.
Showed no early pace, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, checked 500M, never ran on.
Missed start, always at rear, never a factor.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, dropped off soon after straightening. ( Rider expressed concern regarding its action)
Smart start, raced 1 off 1 back, switched wide 400m & ridden in 3rd, strong progress to lead 250m, kept on to hold late challenge.
Missed break & raced last pair 1 off, over-raced 900m, niggled 650m, shifted wide 450m, 6L back & driven widest final turn, surged to wire too late.
Started OK, bustled initially to rail fore of midfield, shifted 1 off 460m, checked off heels 380m, crowded on turn, driven 250m, closed to 3rd late.
Sharp start, camped 1 back on rail, shifted out & driven top of stretch, advanced to 2nd at 200m but one-paced & edged out of frame in run.
Sluggish start wide & bustled to snag rail behind midfield, niggled 600m, driven 450m, ran on for minor gains but flattened out final 50m.
Snagged at start, sat 1 off behind midfield, driven very wide into stretch, stayed on for minor headway.
Awkward break, outpaced & driven to sit rail midfield, shifted out 400m, wide onto stretch & driven, kept on one pace.
Tardy break, nudged to race 1 off with cover midfield, under pump 500m & 3 deep 400m, wide onto stretch, boxed on evenly.
Broke Ok, snagged to race rail last pair, ridden 400m, struggled on one-paced run.
Fast break, nudged to lead & crossed to rail 1330m, challenged 550m, extended 1L clear final turn, all out & headed 250m, faded tamely.
Sharp break, bustled wide & worked to slot 1L 2nd 1 off no cover 1100m, pressed lead 550m, under pressure 1L back 400m, faded tamely.
Sharp start, snagged to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 520m, forced 3 deep 450m, found nil in stretch & eased when beaten.
Taken back at break, raced rail behind midfield, keen early, nudged along 600m, driven 500m, switched out & advanced on turn, rattled home stands' side to lead close home.
Smart start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, on & off bridle, bustled 650m, driven 500m, very wide final turn, closed to nick 2nd late.
Awkward start, raced rail 5th, driven 400m & shifted out, ran on centre track to snag 3rd close home.
Broke well, raced handy 2nd 1 off no cover, shaken up to press lead 480m, driven to lead turning in, all out final 200m & swamped close home.
Slow start & settled near rear 1 off, driven 500m, strong closer down stands' side, just missed frame.
Good start, settled 4th 1 off with cover, niggled 650m, under pump 450m, grinding run to press lead in stretch, always held & swamped late.
Broke OK, settled back of midfield 1 off, niggled 1000m, bustled along back stretch, driven 500m, wide into stretch, kept on evenly.
Smart start, sat 3rd 1 back on rail, nudged along 500m, hard driven into stretch, struggled in run home.
Slow break, recovered to sit rail midfield, driven 300m, plugged on tepidly.
Speed to lead, set tempo on rail, driven under pressure 480m, headed turning in, faded tamely.
Moderate start & raced rail last pair, bustled 700m, driven 450m, plodded on one pace.
Dropped back at start to sit last pair 1 off, ridden 450m, found nil.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground for 3rd.
Slow away, pushed along the fence, 3Ls off the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden early to keep up with the field, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 150M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 3Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, lack turn of foot, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash in straight.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, little dash 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Bumped start, 7Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide and raced keenly, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Jumped and followed the 3rd placegetter one off the rails. Shifted away at 900m and 750m. Settled after, increase tempo at 400m and shifted in badly at 150m.
Checked at 900m and at 750m. Sat handy on rails. Kept on well to the line.
Jumped cleanly to lead, travelled well, increased tempo at 350m, checked at 150m by the winner.
Jumped well. Sat 3-off the leader and wide with cover. Checked at 1,100m and steadied. Made his run out-wide turning for home, shifted in at 200m. Plugged on late with excuses.
Shifted in at 1,100m, Sat 4-off the leader with cover. Bit keen at 600m. Shifted out-wide turning in and plugged on under whip.
Steadied at 1,000m and bit keen, sat 3-back one-off the fence. Keen at 600m and checked. Ridden after the home turn out wide. Closed off without threatening.
Jumped cleanly to sit outside the leader 3-wide early stages. Shifted in sharply 800m. Weakened right out at 300m.
Jumped fairly. Sat 3-off the leader. Checked at 800m, then travelled. No room and checked at 200m. Had excuses.
Jumped fairly as always. Ridden, improved to sit-5 off the leader and glued to the paint. Closed off in an much-improved effort.
Erratic on number of occasion and 3-wide early stages. No room in closing stages but never a factor.
Slow to begin from gate 10. Made no impression.
Checked at the start. Always at rear. Never a factor.
Eased back to near the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, wide bid 600M, headway to join the front rank 350M, went head to head with runner up over final 200M, gamely prevailed.
Broke well from inside draw, tracked leaders in a slowly run race, responded well turning in and vied for lead with rival over final 200M, just touched off on the line.

Held up behind midfield, hampered by slow pace and difficult to settle, turned 3-wide 800M, severely checked and lost ground 600M, stayed on well down outside entering straight. (Racing manners unacceptable)
Behind mid-division, 3-wide no cover from 1100M, crept closer to leaders 600M, battled on well in straight, not pace of leaders 200M, lost 3rd near line.
Eased back from to last further back than intended, bided his time and waited until top of the straight, stayed on moderately down inside over final 300M.
Shifted across behind runners from wide barrier, not helped by slow pace and raced keenly, wide bid 700M, had his chance early straight, turned one pace final 200M.
Tracked leaders along the 2-path, waited with until 300M, responded only fairly, never a serious threat to leaders.
Reserved in a midfield position, shuffled back a bit nearing home turn, switched wide 400M, stayed on only fairly.
Settled down inside 3-4Ls back in mid-division, gave limited response turning in, never threatened.
Guided to the fence, settled behind midfield, shuffled back to the rear home turn, couldn't pick up.
Rushed to the lead from wide barrier, slowed things down passing 1200M, had little left in tank when rivals move up inside 300M, weakened rapidly over this first attempt over 1650M.
Worked early to obtain a forward spot outside leader, came under pressure making turn for home, first to be beaten entering straight.

Jumped well, settled in midfield in 5th, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend to join the leaders entering straight, fought on dourly to just get up on line.
Ridden positively from a poor draw, soon led and obtained rails run over 600 metres out, fought on well only to be pipped at post.
Broke well, close up on rails, baulked for a run from approaching straight to 300 metres out, finished off race strongly inside final 200 metres.
Not far off in 4th, steadied approaching home turn, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, gradually worked his way forward to hold 1L 3rd one off the rails, remained similar early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Began moderately from the one draw, settled worse than midfield in 6th on rails, in similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.
Always well behind, last and widest turning in, ran past well-beaten horses in straight.
Ridden early, travelled towards the rear, similar turning in, found nothing.
Slowly away, settled at the back on rails, shifted off the rails for a run entering straight, but could find no extra.
Awkward to begin, found rail and settled midfield, pushed along home turn to improve along rail, challenged strongly 150m, gained upper hand concluding stages.
Fast out and sent to front, travelling well and quickened nicely at 400m to establish break, collared late.
Jumped well but allowed to ease back and settle midfield without cover, took time to wind up in straight, finished strongly final 150m.
Jumped awkwardly, no early pace and pushed along to stay in touch, ridden along near 700m to slowly improve, made steady ground in straight.
Settled forward of midfield, travelling well home turn, eased out to challenge on straightening but couldn't quicken and one paced to the line.
Settled worse than midfield, disappointed for a run when checked at 300m, hit line strongly when clear final 150m.
Settled leaders back, asked to challenge on straightening but did not respond, hung out in straight.
Jumped well and sent forward from outside gate to settle outside leader, moved up to challenge on straightening but soon under pressure and weakened out of it final 200m.
Jumped awkwardly and eased back to settle worse than midfield, made some late ground in the straight.
Eased back from wide gate to settle towards rear, travelled well home turn, ran home one paced.
Jumped awkwardly and taken back, raced keenly near 1200m, in need of clear running home turn, but unable to make up ground in straight.
Pushed along early to settle behind leaders, quickly under pressure on straightening and dropped out final 150m, tightened at 100m.
Keen early and settled midfield, angled out for run at 400m but checked when crowded at 300m, checked again near 50m when close to heels.
Pushed along to settle towards rear and raced keenly, failed to run on in straight.
Showed good early pace to cross to the stand side and share the lead, took the lead 400M, won comfortably by 1-3/4Ls.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader the stands side, ran on well for 2nd.
Ridden forward to share the lead along the outer fence, headed by the winner 400M, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Settled midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader in the middle park of the track, kept on steadily to the line.
Bumped on jumping, travelled 3Ls behind the leader in the middle park of the track, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, one paced home.
Eased at start, then settled 3Ls behind the leader the stands side, ran on fairly. (Lost plate on jumping)
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader the stands side, weakened 150M.
Jumped slowly, settled 4Ls behind the leader the stands side, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader in the middle park of the track, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader the stands side, dropped off over the last furlong. (Roarer)
Showed good early pace to cross to the stands side and share the lead, flattened badly 300M.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Fast start widest, bustled initially, soon snagged to 1 off with cover midfield, shifted wide on turn, shaken up 400m, stormed to lead 170m & coasted home.
Taken back from wide gate, raced 8L back near tail, shifted out & hard-ridden final turn, responded for late headway to nick 2nd at line.
Tardy break & rousted wide, worked to 2nd 850m & settled upsides leader, driven to lead 400m & kicked 1L clear, all out & headed 170m, lost 2nd at wire.
Tardy start & bustled on rail behind midfield, shifted out 600m, driven into stretch, closed off for minor headway.
Fast start & vied for lead, slotted 1 back on inner & over-raced, shifted out 350m & driven, plugged on one pace.
Slow start, raced 1 off behind midfield, shifted 3 deep 600m, very wide turning in & driven, ran on for moderate headway.
Moderate start & bustled wide to lead 1000m, soon to rail, pressed on turn, driven into stretch, found little & soon headed, faded in run.
Broke well & bustled initially, settled rail midfield 3L back, switched out away from heels 500m, driven 400m but outpaced & plugged on tepidly.
Sluggish start, midfield & rolling forward 1 off when checked off heels 850m, raced rail mid rank, driven 400m, plodded one pace.
Led early stages, headed 1000m, settled 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 deep 500m, driven 400m, weakened tamely.
Broke well, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, edged out final turn & driven, struggled & faded out tamely.
Taken to tail at start & niggled on rail, hard-ridden into stretch, found nil & weakened out.
Prominent initially, snagged to race 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, shifted 4 deep 500m, ridden 400m but found nil & eased.
Broke OK, settled rail midfield, strong traveller & shifted 1 off 620m, driven into stretch, shifted out 350m, quickened to share lead 200m, edged tight duel close home.
Caught wide & snagged to behind midfield, to fence 1000m & rolled on a spot, shaken up 400m for progress, switched out 270m & joined lead 200m, lost out in duel.
Slow start & rousted to race back of midfield 1 off with cover, driven 500m & shifted out final turn, closed off to 3rd without threatening.
Taken back to rail & niggled near rear, under pump turning in, shied from whip 350m, stayed on for minor late inroads.
Fast start & rousted wide to lead, worked to rail 1300m, narrow lead into stretch, driven & kicked 1L clear, all out & headed 200m, tapered to wire.
Missed break, raced last pair 1 off, shifted 3 wide 850m for progress, driven 500m, stayed on for minor headway.
Started ok, taken back to race 1 off near tail, shifted 3 wide 700m, ridden 440m, not clear run & switched out 350m, ran on for minor inroads.
Fast break, eventually settled 1 off 1 back, shifted 3 deep 600m & niggled, driven 450m, plugged on evenly.
Sharp start, settled back of midfield 3 wide with cover, wide no cover on turn & minor headway, outpaced in to stretch & plugged on evenly.
Missed break, niggled at tail on rail, shifted 1 off at 800m, under pump turning in, kept on moderately.
Broke ok but niggled initially, raced midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide 620m, ridden 500m, plugged on one pace.
Good start, sat 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off & driven into stretch, outpaced & tapered.
Sharp start & handy, caught 3 deep no cover, rolled to press lead 1000m & slotted 1 off, 2nd & driven turning in, emptied 300m & faded.
Driven from widest gate but outpaced, worked hard from midfield to race handy & wide without cover from 1200m, emptied turning in & faded out.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, dashed well 300M to score.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace, trapped 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the good pace on the rails, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear for 3rd.
Settled in front, 2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide, ran on well to the line.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pressed forward, just off the leader 2 wide, led 400M, hung on until 200M flattened.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, flattened 300M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace on the fence, ran on ok in straight.
Box seat, pace good, ran on well until 200M weakened.
Pressed forward early, however trapped very wide, then eased back 6Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, no progress.
Took rail and led by 1L at good pace, reduced quickly 400M.
Bumped start, never a factor.
Hard ridden but not muster, trapped 4-5 wide without cover in front, soon dropped off 500M.
Began well, ridden to hold forward position but trapped 3-wide on settling. Allowed to slide forward to take narrow lead from 1000m. Still in front on straightening and kept finding for narrow win.
Urged forward from good draw, racing inside leader to 1000m before taken box seat. Had to angle out to find run in straight and finished strongly to just miss.
Began OK but restrained to find cover passing 1400m 4L from leader. Switched wide entering straight and finished strongly.
Hard ridden to take lead on settling, but allowed another to go marginally ahead from 1000m. Battled alongside leader all the way up the straight, weakening only in the final strides.
Ridden along to hold midfield position along fence 4L from leader. Stayed on fence around turn and early straight, making ground until blocked final 100m.
Jumped OK but no early speed, dropping to rear in one-off position. Tightened around turn, taken wide in straight and ran on steadily to be closest at the finish.
First into stride, settled 2nd outside leader before easing into one-back, one-off position before turn. Made forward move entering straight to look a chance before running out of steam.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw but kept wide towards the rear. Switched wider entering straight and ran on steadily.
Began awkwardly but recovered quickly settling in one-off position 3L from leader. Stayed close to fence in straight and ran on fairly.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Taken wide in straight and kept on fairly without looking dangerous.
No early speed and last on settling. Made up ground around turn but one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from outside draw settling 3L from leader but wide and without cover. Covered extra ground turn but kept on till 200m before tiring.
No early speed, settling close to rail towards the rear. Improved around turn, tightened 500m, one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear but still wide. Clear last on entering straight and found nothing under pressure.
In 5th of 6, 4-5Ls off the pace in a slowly run race, confidently ridden, cruised to the lead 200M out and soon clear, won unextended.
Settled last 6Ls off the pace in the first half of the race, tracked ABLE FRIEND from 400M, ran on well to go 2nd near line, no match for the winner.
Soon led, took them along slowly in the first half of the race, quickened up things home turn, unable to repel ABLE FRIEND at 200M, kept on evenly, lost 2nd close home.
Tracked leader in 3rd, lacked instant acceleration early straight, stayed on for moderate 4th.
Settled one out one back in a slowly run race, joined leader early straight, run ended 150M, faded towards the line.
In 4th of 6, couldn't pick up when urged along 400M, eased 200M when beaten. (Heart Irregularity 2nd time)
Quickly into stride, taken to outer fence and allowed to coast a half length behind leader to 400m when urged forward. Took clear lead 300m and kept finding to the post.
Began fairly, restrained, dropping to rear, and taken closer to outer fence. Made ground from 500m, taken in 280m and unable to get run till 150m. Finished strongly.
Began well, raced between horses close to outer fence 3L from leader. Took closer order passing 400m, looked chance 200m, denied quinella on the line.
Kicked by another horse before start but passed fit to run. Began well, taken to outer fence settling 2.5L from leader. Shifted out 350m, kept on steadily under hard riding.
Began well, quickly taken towards outer fence, settling neck behind leader. Looked chance when drew level 400m but unable to find more and awkwardly placed closing stages.
Began well, switched out but kept three-away from outer fence 2.5L from leader. Put under pressure from 400m but unable to get closer.
Quickly in front, taken closer to outer fence and set steady pace to course proper. Collared 300m and gave ground gradually.
Began fairly, no speed, settling 7L from leader along outer fence. Picked up momentum from 400m and travelled well but no clear running final stages and not ridden out. Lame right fore.
Began OK, taken towards outer fence about 7L from leader. Caught flat-footed 400m when field speeded up, picked up momentum and was finishing well when blocked for run and not ridden out.
Crowded out start, dropping to clear last. Raced at rear mostly before making up some late ground.
Began well, holding midfield position along outer fence 3L from leader. Still in contention passing 400m before weakening.
Jumped OK, holding outer fence some 3L from leader. Put under pressure from 400m and weakened gradually from 200m. Found to be a "roarer".
Fractious in gate and missed the jump, losing several lengths. Ridden to recover ground in midfield by 800m but under pressure from 500m and weakened. Unacceptable performance.
Began fairly, no speed and soon trailing field. Never competitive.

Kicked well, and made sure he led up the back straight. Never asked the question until challenged at 300m. Tended to lay out under the stick late, and challenged again at the 100m, but kicked again to go 2 from 2.

Began well, and elected to sit in behind the leader, on the rails with cover. Came off at the 300m to challenge. Wanted to lay out, but kept going. Got nose in front at the 150m, but winner kicked and was outmuscled late.

Moderately away, stuck wide up the back straight looking for a run, eventually settling handy 3 wide. Checked 900m. Was running on well late and off heels at 200m, finishing better than 2nd late, but just ran out of room late.
Bounded on jumping and slow away, before finding a position midfield on the rails. Stuck in traffic down the straight before cutting back in for a run at 150m, but never ran on when clear late.
Not used up early, and sat just worse than midfield 3 off the rail. Raced keenly mid race. Came widest on turn and had clear air for the trip, but was only running on fairly late.
Pushed along early, but never mustered and settled at the rear of the field. Last at 300m, and chased hard late to finish creditably.

Flew out of the gates, and proved extremely difficult to settle early. Eventually found a position midfield, 1 off the fence. Checked off heels 1100m. Had a clear run in the straight, but only plugged away.
Dropped back from the wide gate to sit mid-back early. Took the inside passage in straight, but 1 paced and never threatened.
Began fairly, and found a position just behind midfield 1 off the fence. Couldn't get a run until 300m, but only ran on fairly and was easing up late.
Slow to begin, and drifted back to last. Held the rails, but never kicked in the straight and eased out late.
Dropped back from the wide gate to sit at the tail of the field, 1 off the rail. Came wider in straight, but never ran on.
Pushed up early to challenge leader, before sitting just behind 1 off the fence. Race was done by the 350m, and weakened badly in the straight.
Pushed along early to sit in the leading group, despite being trapped 3-4 wide with no cover. Prominent at the top of the straight, but dropped back conspicuously to be tailed off.
Began OK, and sat in a handy position 1 off the rail early. Had difficulty getting a run in the straight, and eased out when steadied off heels at the 200m.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back in 5th, travelled well throughout, finished off strongly in straight to score easily.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, closed off well in straight to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, 3 wide without cover on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 4L or so back on rail in 6th, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, unbalanced near 300M, made some ground thereafter to make frame. (Lost right front plate near 1200M)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead at fast sectionals, kicked clear early in straight, headed near 150M and weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back behind midfield, travel keenly after 1000M, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off strongly.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back in 3rd, peaked early in straight, just kept on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race 2 wide, 8 lengths back at rear, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 8 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle near 800M, finished off evenly after turning in, never a threat.
Slightly slow out, raced 6 lengths back on rail behind midfield, same margin back to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from gate 10, raced 5 to 6 lengths back in midfield, 3 wide with no cover on turn, emptied early in straight.
Moderately away and then ridden vigorously to race outside the leader, similar position throughout, came under pressure 600M, failed to close off in straight. (Jockey questioned re his riding)
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in 4th, there to turn, emptied early in straight and dropped off gradually, unacceptable performance. (Lost left front plate after 1300M)

Settled wide in midfield, took closer order approaching the Rock, continued to improve under pressure around the bend, hit the front 200 metres out, hung on well.

Taken back to race on rails behind midfield, became midfield and awkwardly placed behind heels when pace slackened far side, baulked 400m out but obtained a run over 200m out, fought on steadily without threatening.

Broke well, ceded advantage for cover travelling mainly 2 wide in 2L 5th, steadied and lost positions at around the Rock, renewed effort in midfield rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Taken across from a poor gate to travel at the rear of the field, remained similar to straight, ran on under pressure down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Settled behind midfield, came under pressure after straightening, made steady headway without threatening.
Niggled along early stages, settled 3-wide without cover in a prominent position in 4th, took closer order to dispute the lead approaching the Rock, faded under pressure after straightening.
Ridden positively from the widest gate, obtained rails run in the front passing the winning post the first time, held running until headed by the winner 200 metres out, found no extra.

Jumped fairly, soon picked up to a prominent position outside the leader, became third passing the Rock, renewed effort rounding home bend but unable to sustain run under pressure after straightening.
Broke well, settled mainly one back on rails, came under pressure from approaching home turn, fought nil in straight.
Settled mainly wide in midfield, faded after straightening.
Settled well behind on rails, found nothing in the run home.
Began fairly, gradually settled 3-wide in last few, dropped to last entering straight, no further impression.
Eased at start to obtain cover and settled midfield, urged along home turn, took time to get balanced on straightening and then finished off strongly.
Fast out and settled in front, travelled nicely middle stages and quickened nicely on straightening to establish a break at 200m, run down on line.
Jumped smartly and allowed to take a sit behind leaders, moved up to challenge on straightening and finished strongly.
Taken back from wide gate, commenced to improve passing 400m and worked home strongly in straight.
Pushed forward from wide gate to settle on pace, tried hard in straight before weakening over concluding stages.
Crowded on jumping, settled midfield, travelling well home turn, took time to get going in straight and finished off okay.
Fast out, held rail to race on pace, tried to challenge for lead on straightening but unable to quicken and battled to the line.
Crowded at start, settled worse than midfield, raced greenly early and middle stages, finished off okay in straight.
Crowded at start and settled towards rear, commenced to improve near 400m, widest on straightening but did not run on.
Taken back from wide gate, urged along home turn but one paced in straight.
Jumped okay, ridden along early but unable to obtain lead and settled behind leaders, under pressure passing 500m, gradually weakened out of it in straight- must trial.
Hard ridden but no early pace and settled towards the rear, crowded at 900m, never traveled at any stage, never a chance.
Eased to rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slightly slow tempo, swung widest turning in, dashed strongly to score by a neck in a compact finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd in a compact finish.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L at slightly slow sectionals, headed 850M, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, kept on strongly for dead heat 3rd in a compact finish.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slightly slow pace, ran on well for dead heat 3rd in a compact finish.
Eased to settle midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the slightly slow tempo, ran on strongly for 5th in a compact finish.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader early, made an early move on its own 850M, benefited by the slightly slow sectionals, kept on strongly until final 50M headed.
Taken back to settle worse than midfield about 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow tempo, made some ground in the straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly slow pace, one paced home, blocked latter stages.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.

Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slightly slow tempo, ran on fairly, checked 200M. (substantial amount of blood in its trachea and also lame right front next day)
Raced midfield, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, dropped off soon after straightening.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Always at rear, broke down 200M.
Smart start, rolled wide to lead 950m, crossed to rail 750m, 1L clear & kicked on 300m, tapered final 100m, just held on.
Snagged at start & crossed to rail, rolled forward to sit behind midfield, bustled for progress 400m, ran home strongly down inner, just failed.
Fast start, settled on rail fore of midfield, shifted out 400m & driven, outpaced initially, closed late, just failed.
Speed to lead, restrained in front & headed 950m, sat 1 back on rail 750m, ridden 350m & led pursuit, dour closer but edged out of frame late.
Tardy break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted wide for progress out of backstretch, wider on turn, driven 350m, stayed on for minor headway.
Moderate start & bustled, raced 1 off behind midfield, shifted 3 wide for progress 480m, very wide final turn & driven, closed off for minor inroads.
Moderate start, bustled to rail midfield, off heels & shuffled back a spot 600m, shifted out 400m, not clear run into stretch, switched inside, closed until no run final strides.
Broke well & rousted to race handy, eventually settled 2nd 1 off no cover, 3 wide & driven into stretch, one-paced to wire.
Taken back to race rail last pair, niggled 500m, driven 420m, outpaced & never a factor.
Broke OK, settled midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 500m, wide turning in, struggled in fading stretch run.
Taken back to last pair 1 off, niggled 650m, under pump 450m, shifted out 300m, found nil in plodding run home.
Smart start widest, caught 3 deep no cover, rolled to midfield at 600m, very wide & backpedalling final turn, found nil.
Sluggish start, raced 1 off with cover near rear, swung wide into straight & driven, limited progress until switched outside 160m, rattled late to lead close home.
Speedy start & vied for lead initial strides, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, shaken up to press lead home turn, outpaced & lost position, battled on dourly to regain 2nd last stride.
Broke OK, mustered to midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, shifted out 300m & quickened to press lead, close tussle to wire, missed 2nd on head-bob.
Broke OK, mustered to race 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off & driven 270m, boxed to lead 60m, no extra close home & swamped last strides.
Trapped 4 wide no cover until taken to rear rank, slotted 3 wide with cover 700m, bustled 420m, wide into stretch, strong closer, just missed frame.
Pushed to lead & scooted 2L clear on rail 1000m, restrained back to field 700m, 0.5L ahead & driven turning in, kicked on, emptied & headed 60m, no extra.
Decent break, settled back 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m, driven turning in, stayed on evenly.
Broke well, soon slid back to rail near rear, driven into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Tardy start, raced 3 deep with cover behind midfield, over-raced 850m & rolled on a spot, 4 deep & driven final turn but found nil & weakened.
Broke well but soon outpaced & bustled on rail, raced midfield, driven 350m & shifted out, found nothing & faded.
Broke OK, caught 3 deep no cover midfield, rolled forward backstretch to race handy, ridden 400m, faded tamely.
Slow start & niggled at rear, soon detached several lengths & remained adrift, never a factor.
Settled in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, progressed steadily 350M to score.
Settled in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 2Ls at fast sectionals, hung on until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
At rear, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made some ground 300M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace along the fence, ran on ok in straight.
At rear, 6Ls off the leader on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, made early move 800M to sit 3Ls off the fast pace, soon reduced 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, steadily improved just off the leader on the fence, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Eased at start, raced 3 wide throughout, never a factor.
Eased back, raced keenly 2-3 wide, tailed out.
Behind midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, tailed off.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling and then steadied tempo to straight. Lengthened stride passing 300m and kept finding under hard riding to hold off late challenger.
Began well and soon in box seat 2L from leader. Took closer order entering straight but no clear run until after passing 150m. Finished strongly.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling three-quarters of a length outside leader. Got to within a neck passing 300m but could not find extra and kept on gamely to the line.
Quickly into stride settling 2-back, one-off to straight. Put under pressure passing 300m but unable to close gap and boxed on gamely.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield before settling three-back, one-off before turn. Lost position entering straight and boxed on one-paced.
Got off fairly, severely checked approaching 1000m and shifted in abruptly 4.5L from leader. Stayed on fence around turn but unable get run in straight until late. Kept on.
Crowded for room on jumping and then hampered when a number of horses were checked passing 1000m. Switched out wide in straight and kept on fairly.
Began fairly, badly unbalanced when several horses forced to check 1000m, allowed to roll forward 3-wide to within 3L of leader. One-paced in straight.
Ridden to challenge pacemakers, sitting three-wide without cover some 1.5L from leader. Continued to race wide in straight and tired quickly after passing 200m.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw but severely checked 1000m dropping to near last. Made little headway after that.
Began well but severely checked 1000m and then raced keenly to and passing 800m. One-paced in straight.
Began fairly, struck heels 1000m and blundered, dropping to last. Soon detached from field. Never competitive.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, made steady headway from 300M, fought off persistent 2nd to score.

Taken across from wide barrier, settled down behind midfield 5Ls off the pace in middle stages, switched out 350M, responded well under urge, went head to head with winner final 100M, narrowly beaten.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, loomed a threat 250M but clipped heels 200M and blundered, regrouped to take 3rd near line.
Restrained, settled down near last 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, swung wide 400M, closed off well but always held by first two final stages.
Chased pace, moved up alongside leader when pace slackened 900M, took narrow lead entering straight, headed by first 4 over final 40M.
From draw 10 soon taken across behind runners, settled near last over 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, still 5Ls to make up on straightening, closed off willingly.
In mid-division along the fence, 3-4Ls behind leaders turning for home, stayed on mildly up the inside, held up for a while passing 100M but never a serious threat to leaders.
Sped to the lead, restrained passing 1100M, taken on by rival back straight when pace slackened, battled on to 100M, gave way late stages.
Always in the 2nd flight in touch with leaders, kept on same pace in straight, no extra late stages.
Unable to slot in, caught 3-wide no cover in midfield, came under pressure turning for home, kept on one paced, never likely.
Held up behind midfield along the 2-path, 4Ls off the pace 400M, gave limited response only, never reached contention.
Switched off to last, well off the pace early stages, moved closer to be 7-8Ls back passing halfway, wide bid 400M, stayed on only fairly, no significant progress.
