Jumped fairly, settled in forward of midfield 3-wide, circled the field on home bend to lead into the straight, hung on well under pressure.
Taken back from a wide draw, settled just worse than midfield far side, commenced move entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.

Jumped fairly from a wide draw, remained very wide without cover in midfield before making rapid progress passing the 1200 metres to lead briefly coming out of far side, headed 500 metres out, kept on under pressure for a place.
Slow into stride, remained well behind to straight, made significant progress inside final 200 metres down the centre of the track, nearest at finish.
Broke well, amongst leaders before hampered and lost position turning into back straight, not far off in 5th or 6th far side, ran home one-paced under pressure.

Broke well, travelled with leaders on rails before badly checked to 7th to 2.5L off the pace 1200m out, carried further back passing the 800m, angled out for a run on top of home bend, fought on steadily in straight.
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate, kept on early in straight before finishing off race nicely.
Jumped fairly, raced wide in a prominent position, similar turning into home straight, faded gradually closing
Never better than midfield, towards the rear around home bend, made no impression in straight.
Niggled along to take up running, but soon joined on stables bend, headed about 800 metres out before dropping further back around the bend, faded steadily in straight.
Slightly slow out, responded to early reminders to pick up to one back position on rails, carried backward passing the 800 metres shuffling back to midfield entering straight, found nothing.
Raced wide just worse than midfield, never seen with a chance.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, never a danger.
Pressed on from a tricky draw to be joint leader approaching back straight, yielded ground from home bend.
Pushed forward at start to settle behind leader, moved up to challenge strongly home turn, broke clear at 400m and easily held of all challengers.
Ridden along early but did not show any pace and settled midfield, commenced positive move at 700m, travelled strongly at home turn, finished strongly but no match for winner.
Settled worse than midfield, travelling well passing 600m to improve along rail, held up home turn, eased out passing 400m and finished strongly once clear.
Jumped well and settled midfield, improved quickly near 600m to issue strong challenge at home turn, no match for winner but fought hard to the line.
Jumped well and pushed forward to settle behind leaders, hard ridden home turn but fought hard entire straight.
Jumped awkwardly, ridden along early to settle midfield, checked when awkwardly place at 600m, lay inwards in straight and finished okay.
Commenced awkwardly, ridden along when caught wide early to settle on pace, ridden hard to challenge at home turn, awkwardly placed when tiring at 300m.
Eased back from wide gate to settle worse than midfield, hampered at 600m, kept to inside in straight and one pace to the line.
Jumped okay and allowed to settle in midfield position, albeit wide, bumped and unbalanced at 600m, battled on one paced in straight.
Taken back from wide gate at the start to settle towards rear, urged along and taken wide at home turn but could not make ground in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settle at rear, last into straight and made no ground.
Fast out to settle in front, stayed there until weakening out of it at 500m.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slightly fast sectionals, dashed strongly to score easily by 2Ls.
Pushed to settle midfield about 5Ls behind the leader along the fence, suited by the slightly fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Settled worse than midfield 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slightly fast pace, closed off nicely to get 3rd.
Eased to midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly fast tempo, ran on steadily.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until final 100M weakened.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, not suited by the slightly fast pace, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one paced until final 100M weakened.
Jumped slowly, then settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slightly fast sectionals, ran on fairly.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly fast tempo, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
Taken back to rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the slightly fast pace, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the slightly fast tempo, never looked competitive.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the fast sectionals, never ran on.
Eased to rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slightly fast tempo, never a factor.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, harmed by the slightly fast pace, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Tardy start & bustled initially, settled rail midfield, shifted out 420m & shaken up, closed off strongly to lead close home.
Sharp start, settled 1 back on rail, 2L back & niggled 600m, driven 400m & dour advance to lead 260m, edged 1L clear, tapered late & mugged at wire.
Speed to dispute early lead, settled 3 wide no cover 3rd, shaken up 420m & progress to vie for lead 350m, soon headed & one-paced to wire.
Speedy break, driven to lead 1330m, narrow advantage on rail, edged 0.75L ahead 850m, driven turning in, all out & headed 260m, tapered thereafter.
Broke OK widest, taken back to race near rear 1 off with cover, driven wide final turn, checked 430m, clear running 400m, ran on for minor inroads.
Good start, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, driven 400m, stayed on evenly.
Taken back at start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, nudged along 500m, hard-ridden 400m plugged on moderately.
Snagged back from wide gate, detached 2L until in touch 650m, hard-ridden turning in & shifted out, stayed on for moderate headway.
Prominent at break, settled handy 1 off with cover, niggled 700m, driven 600m, outpaced & plugged on tepidly.
Missed break, switched to rail early & bustled to sit rail fore of midfield, shifted out & driven 500m, one-paced & tapered in run.
Missed break & rousted to race rail behind midfield, hard-ridden 520m, struggled in run home.
Disputed lead at break, raced close 2nd 1 off no cover, driven into stretch, every chance but emptied 350m & weakened tamely.
Eased back at start, caught 3 wide no cover back of midfield, slid back near rear 800m, driven 600m, struggled in run, eased when beaten.
Snagged back at start, raced keenly midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep 800m, forced widest home turn & driven, faded tamely.
Sharp start & pressed lead on rail, shared lead 750m into stretch, shaken up 350m, headed 320m, battled back to lead close home & held on.
Jumped well, positioned a length back in 3rd, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd, just missed.
Taken back from wide gate, raced near rear 1 off with cover, shifted out on turn, shaken up 400m, switched wider for run 300m, flew home, just failed.
Good break, caught 3 wide with cover handy, lost cover 750m, driven 600m, kept on dourly.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide no cover, rolled to lead 900m & slotted 1 off 750m to share lead, shaken up 400m, headed 320m, tapered to wire.
Smart start, over-raced a touch 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shifted out & driven 450m, kept on to maintain position.
Broke OK, settled behind midfield 3 wide with cover, very wide on turn, driven 420m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Broke well outpaced & bustled initially, sat rail fore of midfield, shifted off fence final turn & driven, boxed on evenly.
Tardy start, raced rail midfield, progress blocked 300m, daylight & driven 230m, not clear run from 120m & rolled home not fully tested.
Good break widest, trapped 4 deep no cover midfield, driven into stretch, kept on evenly.
Taken back at start, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, driven turning in, plugged on dourly without threatening.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, ridden 400m, tepid run home.
Taken back from wide gate, sat last pair on outer, very wide into stretch, struggled in run home.
Missed break & lost 3 lengths, raced last pair on rail, ridden 500m, found nil in stretch.
Hard ridden to take the rail from wide draw and led by 1L, made all.
Box seat, enjoyed a perfect trip, closed off strongly for 2nd, just missed by a neck.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, held ground in straight for 3rd.
Very slow away, 6.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 400M, run ended 150M.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader along the fence, little dash 400M.
Pressed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, flattened 200M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
At back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, checked 400M, ran on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward, checked first bend, 3.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, reduced 250M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, never improved.
Midfield, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, never nearer.
At back, trapped 4 wide throughout, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, dropped off quickly 300M.
Eased to rear, trapped wide, never competitive.
Began OK, did not have the early speed, dropping about 4L from leader along outside rail. Picked up momentum passing 600m, squeezed through gap to lead 200m, kept on strongly.
Hard ridden to stay with pacemakers, 0.5L from leader and four-away from outer fence. Put under pressure 250m and kept on strongly to the line.
Began well but no early speed gradually crossing from inside draw to outer fence but kept four-deep. Picked up momentum from 500m and kept on well to grab minor placing.
First out, led for a few strides before dropping to neck second at the 900m. Put under pressure and retook lead 350m but soon challenged and passed. One paced final stages.
Ridden along early, moving quickly from inside draw to outer fence but kept 4-deep, 3L from leader. Urged forward passing 400m, got to within striking distance 200m but one-paced thereafter.
Jumped with field, racing at rear down centre track while edging closer to outer fence. Improved position steadily after passing 800m but one-paced final 200m.
Quickly into stride, racing up with pacemakers a neck outside leader. Raced in restricted room 500 and got shuffled back 2L from leader at the 400m. Weakened gradually.
Ridden along to obtain forward position settling 4-wide from outer fence and 1L from leader. Switched out to get run but awkwardly placed from 400m and drifted back gradually.
Bumped start and last on settling. Crossed over to outer fence to find better ground but switch in passing 400m. Finished off fairly down centre track.
Began awkwardly but quickly made up ground while crossing to outsider fence to get within 2.5L of leader passing the 400m. Steadied and shifted out 300m. Faded gradually.
Began well, quickly taken to outer fence some 5L from leader. Switched in passing 400m to make run but only one-paced.
Began well, urged forward along outer fence to lead passing 900m. Set good pace to 400m when caught and weakened quickly. Jockey reported wanted to lay-in mostly.
Began fairly, shifted across behind horses to outer fence and second last on settling. Raced at the rear throughout.
Quickly into stride, racing along centre track 2L from leader. Got to within striking range 400m when lost action and dropped back quickly. Jockey reported horse did not handle conditions.
Led from 2200M, pressed by rival 800M, shook off pursuing horses entering straight, kept finding under pressure, held off late challenge from 2nd.

Placed ahead of midfield, 4Ls behind leaders making the turn for home, fought on gamely final 400M and one of very few who managed to make ground on this yielding track, slowly getting to winner at the line.
In mid-division, settled down 6Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly to go 3rd 200M, not reached leaders.
Reserved in mid-division, made limited progress over final 500M, nor reached leaders.
Caught wide early, settled down in 4th 2-3Ls behind leader, hard driven 600M, failed to pick up, never a threat.
Chased the pace, moved up alongside leader 800M, failed to keep up entering straight, soon beaten.
Held up behind midfield. 8Ls off the pace making the turn for home, swung wide 600M, run ended mid-straight, eased towards finish. (Jockey : did not handle the track conditions)
Tracked leaders, hard driven 500 out but not responding, gave ground 350M. (Jockey : did not handle the track conditions)
Given a waiting ride, 10Ls off the pace middle stages, had impossible task in hand turning in, didn't find much under pressure, ran past eased runners only.
Restrained near the rear, 10Ls off the pace home turn, failed to quicken, eased when no chance 200M.
Slow to begin, near rear over 10Ls off the pace, gave no response when pushed along 600M, never involved.
Always 3-4Ls behind leader, settled 5th entering back straight, came under pressure 600M, soon dropped out of contention.

Placing: PU
Comment: Held up last over 10Ls behind leader, eased out of the race near 800M. (Jockey reported his mount his mount became unbalanced in its action and was not stretching out. Irregular Heart Rhythm 2nd time)
Began well, eased to find cover, settling 4L from leader but 3-wide. Proved difficult to settle and urged forward from 1000m, going wide around turn. Surged ahead to lead 200m and pulled clear.
Ridden along to hold fence 2L behind leader. Urged forward around turn sneaking through along fence to lead 650m. Kicked clear 400m but shifted out under pressure and caught 250m. Kept on.
Ridden along from wide draw and kept three- and four-wide at the rear. Last into straight, taken widest and finished strongly down centre track to grab minor placing.

Taken forward from an outside draw, racing three wide without cover 2L behind leader. Urged forward around turn to look a chance 400m, but only one-paced final 200m under hard riding. Had cut on right hind leg.
Began fairly, no pace, settling one-off at the rear. Got close to heels entering straight, switched out and ran on well to be closest at finish.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, settling three-quarters of a length behind leader approaching the turn. Kept on well early in straight to look a chance 300m but only one-paced final stages.
Ridden along but unable hold position and drifted back settling 2.5L from leader but three wide. Was wide around turn but found inside run in straight before running out of stamina from 200m.
Slow into stride, ridden but failed to respond, settling last along rail. Improved position around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Began OK, traveling three-wide and three back along back stretch and turn. Found little response when put under pressure at 500m and did not close off.

Pressed forward from a good start before eased off, settling 3L from leader but 3-wide. Forced to race wide around turn and began losing ground soon after straightening. Jockey reported not comfortable in action.
Jumped with field, no speed, settling at rear along fence. Made up ground around turn but found little under hard riding.
Ridden along early to hold rail position three-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn to look a chance entering straight behind pacemaker. Found little final 200m and faded.
Hard ridden to lead on settling but kept a little wide around turn allowing inside horse to take over 650m. Gave ground quickly in straight.

Got a small bump on jumping, but pushed forward to sit just behind the leaders on the rail. Pulled out to challenge leader on turn, but took until 100m to get the nose in front. Didn't canter away, but was to strong late.
Began well, and had no trouble getting to a share of the lead on the rails. Let down when challenged at the 300m. Briefly unbalanced at the 150m. Ran on strongly, but bested by the winner late.

Began fairly, and found a position just behind midfield 1 off the fence when slightly unsettled. Got moving at 300m, and raced tight a couple of times in the straight. Best in a blanket finish for 3rd.

Began OK, but had no luck finding a position, sitting midfield 4 wide with no cover. Ran on well in the straight, despite racing tight on a couple of occasions, and was only beaten out late for third.
Slow out of the gates then steadied soon after, settling second last. Bumped at the 950m. Came inside for a run in the straight, and finished off OK, just missing 4th.
OK away, and taken forward to sit in a handy position 3 wide with no cover. Ran on well in the straight, and running on for third, before weakening and swamped in the last 100m.
Dropped back from the wide gate to sit wide and clear last. Came wide on turn, and was running on OK. Awkward on heels late, but not threatening a place.
Moderately away, and went back from the wide barrier to sit 3rd last. Unbalanced 950m. Widest in the straight, and plugged away without threatening.

Only fairly away and pushed up to sit midfield 3 wide with cover. Luckless trying to get a run in the straight. Awkward on heels 250m, and then checked out of a run at 200m losing any chance of finishing off the race.
Began well, and established a handy position behind the leaders with cover. Faded from the 300m, and played no part in the finish.
OK away, and sat just in front of mid, near the rails with cover. Didn't respond when asked the question, and dropped out from the 200m.
Began OK, and eased forward to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Under pressure from the turn, but never responded and eased out late.
Kicked well, and pushed ahead to share the lead, one off the fence. Under pressure on turn, and faded badly. Not persevered with in the straight.
Stuck 3 and 4 wide early trying to settle, before being hampered at the 1000m. Eventually got into a position behind midfield 3 wide. Weakened badly from the turn, and found to have been bled.

Jumped fairly, settled 2-wide in 5th in forward of midfield, became 6th briefly at Rock, commenced move entering straight, sustained effort despite weaving his way through final 200 metres.
Broke well, settled just better than midfield in 4th on rails just over 3L back, switched out for a run on straightening, ran on steadily under pressure to just fail to peg back the winner.
Ridden positively from the widest gate, settled in 1L 2nd one off the rails, hit the front briefly 100 metres out only to be outsprinted close to home.
Broke well from a wide draw, soon gained rails run after passing the winning post the first time setting a smart pace, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 100 metres.
Settled behind midfield, gained closer under pressure entering straight, continued to make ground steadily but without threatening.
Broke well, settled just off the pace in 3rd on rails, remained similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Never better than midfield on rails, kept on steadily in the run home.
Slightly slow out, settled in rear, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Travelled mainly 3-wide in midfield, made no progress in straight. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled just worse than midfield on rails, gradually dropped to second last spot in back straight, no further impression.
Always well behind.
Fast out, sent forward settling behind leader, asked to quicken on straightening, gradually wore down leader to gain upper hand final 100m.
Fast out and taken straight to front, kicked strongly on straightening, fought hard but overpowered final 100m.
Settled 3 back on rail, pushed along home turn, hard ridden in straight to challenge and gradually made ground without threatening.
Pushed hard from wide gate to go forward and settle on pace, battled gamely in straight and had every chance.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled towards rear, commenced to improve around field at 500m, widest on straightening but could not sustain run and weakened final 200m.
Jumped nicely and sent forward to settle in handy position, hampered near 450m, could not quicken in straight and one paced to the line.
Eased back from wide gate to settle worse than midfield, urged along passing 500m, took time to get going in straight before finishing off solidly.
Settled at rear, crowded at 850, hampered at 600m, commenced to improve near 450m but made little impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, no early pace and settle towards rear, wide without cover in middle stages and unable to make ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, drifted back towards rear passing 500m, one paced in straight.
Jumped well but no early pace and settled towards rear, weakened out of it from the home turn.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, dashed strongly to score by 1-3/4Ls.
Camped midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on steadily to get 3rd.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L at slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line without serious threatening.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader at slow tempo, kept on steadily in straight.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow pace, kept on steadily without any extra acceleration.
Taken back from a wide draw, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, ran on only fairly.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on until final furlong weakened.
Jumped slowly, then settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, swung widest turning in, made minor ground in straight.
At rear, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, soon flattened after straightening.
Urged forward from wide draw and quickly slotted into good position 3-back, one-off. Continued to roll forward around turn, three wide into straight, hit from 220m and kicked clear for easy win.
Pressed forward between horses before grabbing box seat on settling. Switched in straight to make run and kept on steadily though no match for winner.
Hard ridden early to hold rail position, three-back from leader. Travelled nicely around turn, looked a chance early in straight, kept on OK without looking a danger.
Slow into stride, settling in one-off position towards the rear. Improved position around turn and early straight turning once-paced from 200m.
Began fairly, shaken up but steadied 800m and checked shortly after when shifted out make run. Ran on fairy in straight.
Urged forward from outside draw and raced three-wide initially until cutting in 3-back, one-off. Looked chance early in straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Aggressively ridden from outside position to lead but forced to raced three-wide before cutting to one-off position entering straight. Caught passing 220m but kept on OK until flattened 50m.
Ridden along to hold position 4-back from leader. Switched out around turn and made some ground initially in straight before turning one-paced.
Began OK but then raced in restricted room, dropping toward rear but three wide. Mad up some ground around turn, very wide in straight, one-paced.
Aggressively ridden to hold forward position inside leader. Kept on well till passing 200m when tired quickly and dropped out.
Slow into stride and then steadied, dropping to rear along rail. Hampered 600m when seeking way out. Found nothing in straight.
Jumped OK, hard ridden by failed to muster and shifted across behind runners but still wide without cover. Found nothing in straight. Stewards said performance unacceptable.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing three-wide until crossing in to sit outside leader at the 1000m. Shaken up approaching the straight, took lead 80m and pulled clear.
Ridden forward from gate 6 to take lead on settling. Not pressed and set steady sections. Kicked ahead passing 300m to look top chance 200m but collared 80m. Kept on.
Bumped, recovered, urged forward from inside draw, settling 3-back from leader. Switched three wide in straight and finished off strongly.
Ridden to hold fence behind leader soon after the start. Travelled well and looked well placed passing 200m. Kept on fairly.
Bumped start, ridden along in midfield but kept away from fence. Switched out for run passing 200m and finished off nicely.
Hard ridden to hold forward position one-back, one-off to straight. Lost position when field speeded up 350m and weekend final 200m.
Shifted across behind horses from outer position but still kept wide and towards the rear. Improved position around urn but one-paced in straight.
Ridden along in a one-off position towards the rear. Made up some ground early in straight but no-extra from 200m.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling near fence at rear. Never looked likely though did run past a couple of tired horses final 200.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear in a one-off position. Clear last around turn. Never competitive.
Slow into stride, then raced keenly along fence. Made up some ground around turn, but found nothing in straight.
Ridden along early but trapped wide without cover some 6L from leader. Hung in passing 500m and dropped out. Steward ruled performance was unacceptable.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1L, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score with comfort.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader along the fence, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the sedated early sectionals, just ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, raced "flat" in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Eased at start, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Very slow away, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed only fairly.
Pushed early, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 250M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader, raced 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Began well, ridden to initially hold box seat before eased three-back from leader. Switched out turning for home, picked up momentum from 300m and just got to the line on time.
Hard ridden to stay with pacemakers 3L from leader, easing to four-back the fence around turn Got inside run final 200m and was finishing strongly when shifted in from heels 150m Kept on well.
Got off with field, ridden along to hold midfield position one-away from fence. Shaken up top of straight, shifted out 250m to obtain clear running, finished strongly.

Made to work from an outside draw, racing three-wide outside early leader before hitting the front and crossing to rail 600m. Kicked clear 400m, looked top chance 200m, swamped on line to miss a placing.

Pressed forward to lead on settling but badgered by four other runners. Eased one-back, one-out around turn, urged forward again in straight to be 2nd at 200m when one-paced. Found to have blood in trachea.
Not much speed, taken to rear along fence. Improved position around turn, switched out in straight and kept on steadily to be closest at finish.
No pace, racing wide at the rear and away from the fence. Picked up momentum entering straight and ran on fairly past tired horses.
Pushed along between horses at the rear after awkward start, crossing in from wide draw. Checked and lost position 600m. Ran on fairly in straight when shown daylight.
Began well, hard ridden to hold forward position settling three-back, one -off. Taken out very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Began well, aggressively ridden to hold lead along fence but unable to prevent another from crossing over. Still in contention 200m before weakening badly. Stewards ruled performance unacceptable.
Pushed along early to hold forward position 2L from leader but then taken wide from 800m and lost position. Faded off in straight.
A little slow to move and clear last on settling. Never competitive. Stewards ruled performance unacceptable.
Soon led, took them along steadily, fought on gamely under pressure and fended off strong challenge from 2nd late on.
Patiently ridden early on, settled near the rear 5Ls off the pace, wide bid 500M out, loomed a strong threat 200M, ran on well but winner had enough to hold on.
Travelled one out one back, battled on well over final 300M but always held by winner, held on 3rd just.
Held up behind midfield, saved ground on inner, held up a bit on the turn and not fully ridden until 300M, stayed on moderately towards finish.
Settled in 5th, never far off 2-3Ls behind leader, kept on evenly in straight and was slowly getting to leaders.
Close up behind leaders, kept on steadily over final 300M and not far off at the finish, raced tight closing stages.
Slow out, settled down at the rear, not much room near 200M, did best work late when switched clear final stages.
Reserved in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly when clear 200M, not reached leaders.
Used a bit early to keep up with leaders, caught 3-wide no cover throughout, weakened 250M.
Never better than midfield, 3-wide throughout, didn't find much under pressure entering straight, soon out of contention.
Gradually eased to the rear of the field to avoid racing wide, bid wide 450M, emptied mid-straight, eased towards the line.
Unable to slot in and travelled wide no cover throughout the race, dropped away from his midfield position 400M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)

Ridden along in midfield early, carried backward on rails coming out of back straight, obtained a clear run down the centre of the track over 350 meters out, asserted authority near the line.
Jumped well from a poor draw, gradually settled back in 2L 5th and then 2-wide in 4th around the bend, ran on under pressure to hit the front 150 metres out only to be headed close to home.
Began moderately, niggled along out wide behind midfield improving to midfield onto home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Pressed on from the widest gate to join the leaders taking over coming out of far side, led until finding no extra inside final 150 metres.
Driven to lead off the rails far side, gradually obtained rails run while ceding advantage for cover in 2nd spot, switched out for a run over 200 metres out, ran home one-paced.

Broke well from a poor draw, travelled 3-wide in a prominent position between runners early, became 2L back in 3rd 2-wide around the bend and closer up in 2nd turning in, soon faded after straightening.
Jumped fairly, niggled along in midfield early, lost position coming onto home bend, kept on well in straight.
Soon dropped towards the rear, kept on well in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Sluggish at start, trailed the field most of way, ran past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, soon picked up along rails to join the leaders, drifted back to over 3L 5th around the bend, made no impression in run home.
Slow into stride, always well behind, never a danger.
Prominent early, gradually drifted back to worse than midfield, dropped out soon after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Began fairly but quickly gathered pace to settle on pace, travelled strongly and quickened nicely at 300m to open a break an win comfortably.
Jumped fast and taken forward to settle o pace, urged along at 300m and finished well but unable to make ground on winner.
Jumped well and settled midfield, pushed along passing 400m to issue challenge and worked home solidly final 200m.
Jumped smartly and sent forward, fought on strongly final 300m.
Jumped well and sent forward to share lead, unable to quicken when challenged passing 350m but battled strongly right to the line.
Slow to begin and crowded shortly after, raced keenly middle stages behind leaders, challenged strongly at 300m and lay out concluding stages.
Ridden along early but could on settle midfield, travelled nicely midrace, took time to pick up but finished nicely final 100m.
Showed early pace to settle behind leaders, urged along to challenge passing 400m, got going late but held up final 100m.
Settled midfield, unable to quicken and held position to the line.
Slow to begin, unable to muster early pace and settled towards rear, battled to the line.
Crowded on jumping and settled towards rear, one paced throughout.
Began awkwardly and lost ground to settle towards rear, unable to make up any ground in run to the line.
Pushed along early to settle midfield, under pressure from 500m and weakened out of it.
Began fairly, awkwardly placed at 900m and always at the rear.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, finished off strongly to score by 3/4L.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow pace, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals and held up early straight, made steady ground thereafter.
Eased to settle worse than midfield early about 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made early move 1250M to park outside the leader, kept on until 250M headed.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow sectionals, held up early straight, made minor ground thereafter.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the slow pace, one paced until final furlong weakened.
At rear as usual, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, failed to make any impression in straight.
Sent forward to take the lead along the fence at slow sectionals, kept on steadily until 300M emptied.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Raced midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Bustled & handy until checked 1150m, shuffled to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, shifted out & driven 420m, gradual closer to lead last strides.
Fast start, bustled to settle 1 back on fence, shifted out & niggled 600m, driven into stretch, grinding run to lead 90m, all out & headed close home.
Speedy start, rolled wide to slot 1 off 1100m & pressed leader, driven 400m, outpaced & lost ground but stayed on to nick 3rd.
Fast & bustled to lead, 2L clear & to rail 1300m, restrained & pressed from 1100m, driven 430m & soon 1L clear, tapered & headed 90m, no extra.
Taken back from widest to rear rank 3 wide with cover, ridden 550m, 7L back turning in, strong closer, just missed frame.
Good start, taken back from wide gate but trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, very wide turning in & driven 400m, stayed on evenly.
Missed break & last, soon to rail & rolled to sit behind midfield, ridden 450m, boxed on evenly & shifted off fence closing stages.
Missed break, rolled on rail to midfield, shifted out & driven 450m, plugged on one pace.
Moderate start, raced 1 off behind midfield, hard-ridden into stretch, slight bump 320m, stayed on evenly.
Broke OK, taken back to rear & raced rail, advanced a spot 700m, driven 430m, plugged on one pace.
Missed break, over-raced early, settled 3 wide with cover near rear, under pump 500m, wide in stretch, plugged home tepidly.
Moderate break, sat 3 wide behind midfield, driven turning in, crowded & bumped 320m, shifted inside 220m, one-paced in tame run to wire.
Sharp break, raced 1 off no cover 1L back, over-raced 1150m, gained cover 1100m, forced 3 deep 600m, outpaced & driven 430m, found nil.
Tardy start, soon in rear rank 1 off with cover, niggled 800m, driven 550m, found nil & faded out.
Bustled start, slotted midfield 1 off with cover, to rail 700m, shaken up 450m, no clear run early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to score.
Broke well, settled midfield 1 off with cover, edged out 500m & ridden, bumped 420m, vied for lead, battled ahead 100m, headed 70m, no extra,
Good break, settled 1 back 1 off, shifted out & ridden 430m to press lead, battled on gamely for 3rd.
Sharp break, raced 1 back on rail, in pocket turning in, checked 400m, switched out & driven 350m, boxed on.
Fast start, snagged to race handy in midfield 3 deep no cover, bumped 420m & driven, led narrowly 340m, headed 100m, tapered.
Fast start, rousted to lead wide on track, joined 800m & slotted 1 off 700m, close 2nd 600m, driven to slim lead 420m, soon headed, tapered to wire.
Slow start & raced 1 off with cover, outpaced 8L back, edged wide on turn & driven 500m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Broke OK, outpaced & niggled to race back of midfield on rail, shifted out on turn & driven 400m, one-paced to wire.
Taken back from midfield, soon at tail & bustled, wide into stretch & driven, kept on moderately.
Stumbled start, raced last pair on rail 11L back, shifted out & driven turning in, plugged on moderately.
Snagged back, soon outpaced on rail near rear 7L back, niggled 800m, shifted out 650m, shaken up 430m, kept on same speed.
Fast start & bustled early to snag rail, vied for lead from 800m, led 600m, headed 420m, faded out & eased from 200m.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score despite hanging in abruptly in early straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 400M, unleashed its strong finishing effort when clear and got 2nd.
Pushed early, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 250M.
Crossed in front easily, took box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Very slow away, 6.5Ls off the leader along the rails, not suited by the slow pace, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the lead 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, emptied 300M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not tested.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, however soon reduced 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Very slow away, 8.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, showed some late dash 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing three-wide without cover. Made no attempt to improve position around turn, changed gears top of straight, hit front 250m, held off late challenge.
Began OK, settling three-back, one off. Took closer order turning for home, picked up momentum gradually in straight and finished off strongly final 200m.
Not much early speed, racing towards rear in a one-off position. Did not make any move until reaching home stretch when switched to middle track and finished off nicely.
Ridden to maintain forward position settling one-back, one-off. Took closer order entering straight, kept on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
Got off well, settling three-back the fence. Improved position turning for home, made use of inside runs to be closest at 200, no extra.
Pressed forward, settling outside leader passing 800m. Tended to lay out at turn, urged forward to lead on straightening, caught 250m but kept on well till tiring final 200m.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw but kept away from fence. Travelled keenly back stretch, taken very wide in straight to get clear running but only one-paced.
Quickly into stride from inside draw, holding box seat. Lost position slightly turning for home when unable find run. Kept on OK to 200m before tiring.
Began well, settling three-back from leader along fence. Taken out turning for home, improved position slightly before turning one-paced.
Hard ridden to take lead on settling then set steady sections to straight when gave ground gradually.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Attempted to improve position but taken wide at 1300m. Never likely. (Hit rail before start but past fit to run).
Crowded out start, dropping to rear close to rail. Hard ridden around turn with little response. Never likely. (Jockey expressed concern with action).
Sent forward, led steadily to straight, kept on well final 400M and fended off several challenges inside 200M.
Settled down behind mid-division, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, headway on outer 500M, loomed a strong threat 150M, battled on to line but was readily held by winner.
Tracked leader on outside, kept up the chase in straight but was always held in the run to the line.
Settled near the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, wide bid passing 500M, closed off well, just missed 3rd.
Reserved in midfield, made rapid headway when taken wide 600M, loomed 250M, run ended 150M and no extra late.
Taken back to near last, stayed on only fairly entering straight, not reached leaders.
Slow to begin, guided to fence and improved to a position behind midfield, switched away from fence 600M, responded well early straight, flat final 150M.
In 5th about 3Ls off the pace, kept on same pace turning in, no threat to leaders.
Held up in rear, 10Ls off the pace middle stages, made limited progress in straight, never near leaders.
Chased leading pair along the 2-path, struggled to keep up passing 450M, gave ground 300M.
Given a patient ride, settled near last 8Ls off leader, driven along 450M but never going the pace to challenge.
Along the rails, chased leaders in 4th,came under pressure 500M, weakened passing 300M.
Towards the rear along the 3-path, left with no cover from 1000M, out-dashed in straight, eased 200M.
Raced in mid-division along the fence, didn't respond to riding, eased when no chance 200M. (Jockey reported his mount did not travel on the bit at any stage./ Unacceptable Performance)
Began OK, taken to fence behind leader before turn. Squeezed though gap 350m to hit the front and then involved in bumping match before kicking back to win on the line.

Pressed forward to hold position one-back, one-off on settling. Bumped at top of straight, taken out and surged forward to look winner 300m, lay in twice during bumping match with winner, beaten on line.
Bumped and unbalanced start then hard ridden to get up outside hind-quarters of leader on settling. With leading trio passing 300m but unable to keep up with first two and held for third.
Ridden along from awkward draw to be placed in one-off position 3L from leader on settling. Taken a little wide entering straight, kept on fairly to 200m before turning one-paced.
Bumped start, ridden along to settling three-back from leader along fence. Urged forward entering straight but unable close gap. One-Paced.
Bumped and checked shortly after start, dropping four-back from leader along fence. Made good ground turn and early straight but could find no extra from 200m.
Hard ridden from inside box to lead on settling. Increased tempo around turn but collared soon after passing 300m. Weakened.
Ridden along behind midfield in one-off position. Improved around turn, widest in straight, made early ground before running out of steam.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Made ground close to fence to within 5L of leader at the 200m before turning one-paced.
Pressed forward from awkward but forced to race wide. Kept on fairly until home straight before turning one-paced from 250m.
Ridden to hold midfield position but kept wide throughout. Put under pressure early in straight but found little and slipped back gradually.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw settling at rear in a one-one position. Put under pressure turning for home. Faded.
Bumped and checked soon after start, dropped to rear but in a one-of position. Hard ridden around turn but failed to make ground. Never competitive.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling towards rear. Dropped to last entering turn and became detached from field. Never likely.
Began well, and pushed forward early to steal an easy lead. Dictated pace, and set quick sectionals. Was 3 lengths clear mid straight, before weakening slightly, but was too far clear to be caught.

Started only fairly and dropped back to sit just worse than midfield 3-4 wide early. Came 2nd widest on the turn, and kicked well when asked the question, swooping past the majority of the field for 2nd.
Pushed forward after beginning only fairly, eventually sitting midfield on the fence. Awkwardly placed on heels at the 800m. Battled on gamely in the straight without threatening the first two home.

Began well, and pushed forward from the wide barrier to sit just forward of midfield, 2-3 wide. Handy position on turn, and pulled into 2nd by 200m, but faded from there, and just held on for 4th late.
Only fairly away, and sat at the back of the pack 4-5 wide. Came widest on the turn, kicked and ran on well late, without threatening a place.
Scrambled out and sat midfield, 1 off the fence. Slightly 1 paced in the straight, and not suited to the quick tempo.
Began OK, but dropped back to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Briefly held up at 300m, and only ran on fairly from there.
Began well and taken forward to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Asked the question at the top of the straight, but never responded and weakened out from the 200m.

Bounded out of the gates, and was stuck at the back of the field 4-5 wide. Kicked from the turn, and was making up some ground. Tendency to lay out late, steadied off heels 150 and never ran on from there.
Began OK, and pushed forward to sit in a handy position, on the fence, after being crossed by the leader. Didn't run on from the 200m, and eased out late.
Awkwardly away from the widest barrier, before sitting midfield 3 wide with no cover. Under pressure before the turn, but didn't respond. Weakened badly from the 300m, and eased out late.
Began OK, but drifted back from there towards the rear before becoming unbalanced at the 800m. Beaten horse by the turn, and not persevered with in the straight.

Settled at the back from a wide draw waited with, widest runner turning in, finished off race well to snatch victory in the shadow of the post.

Jumped fairly, tightened and lost position on rails passing the winning post the first time, soon settled in 5th just over 2L off on rails, ran on dourly from a similar position into straight only to be pipped at post.
Broke well from the middle gate to soon take up running attempting to make all in a steady pace, held just over 1L advantage turning for home but unable to sustain effort and worn down close to home.
Ridden along from the one draw before settling one-back on rails, soon came to challenge from a similar position into straight but unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled in rear on rails, remained similar to straight, made steady headway along rails until running too close to heels late, nearest at finish.
Settled in last few 2-wide, commenced move from the Rock rounding the bend 3-wide, tight between runners over 200 metres out, kept on steadily under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, travelled 3-wide towards the rear without cover before improving to midfield down back straight, in similar wide position turning for home, one-paced.

Ridden positively from a wide gate travelling wide, raced awkwardly over 1200m out before settling one-off the rails towards the rear in back straight, amongst last few turning for home, produced moderate late impression closing stages.

Close up before tightened passing winning post the first time, settled in midfield or slightly worse far side, came under pressure approaching home straight but was a difficult ride running home one-paced.
Travelled keenly in 4th, remained in similar position far side, commenced move rounding home bend, soon weakened in straight.
Close up early, tightened before settling in 6th in midfield, one-paced when jostled passing the 300 metres, dropped out.
Jumped well from a wide draw, niggled along to search for front positions before settling in 1L second outside 3rd, yielded ground from the 400 metres. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Jumped well, settled behind leaders, travelled comfortably home turn, hard ridden to challenge in straight, gradually gained upper hand final stages.
Jumped fast and pushed along to share lead, travelled strongly home turn, kicked clear on straightening, overpowered concluding stages.
Crowded at start, settled towards rear, awkwardly placed at 600m, kept to rail in straight and worked home solidly.
Jumped well and sent forward from wide gate to settle behind leaders, one paced in straight holding position to the line.
Pushed along early to settle behind leaders, drifted back to midfield near 500m, made up some late ground.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, settled midfield, battled to the line one paced.
Jumped well and pushed along early to settle forward of mid, checked at 950m, awkwardly placed for room at 800m and 500m, one paced in straight.
Jumped okay, sent forward from wide gate to share lead, under pressure home turn and weakened out of it.
Commenced awkwardly, crowded at 1100m, checked at 1000m and lost ground, made up some ground in straight.
Crowded and unbalanced at start, settled towards rear, urged along passing 500m, unable to quicken in straight and finished one paced.
Settled towards rear and remained there throughout.
Began awkwardly, wide without cover throughout, gave ground in straight.

Camped midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, accelerated strongly to score by a nose. (Objected by the 2nd placegetter and the protest was overruled)

Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 2nd. (Objected against the winner and the protest was overruled, see incident report also lost plate 450M)
Settled worse than midfield about 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, closed off nicely for 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, despite the fast sectionals, ran on well until final 50M headed.
Pushed to settle worse than midfield about 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast pace, ran on only fairly.
Taken back to rear, 1300M rider almost dislodged, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Eased back to settle worse than midfield from a wide gate, 8Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, never ran on.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls at fast pace, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, kept on until final furlong flattened.
Ridden forward to settle 1.5Ls behind the leader, hampered by the fast pace, flattened rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened soon after straightening, tailed out.
Camped handy, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, flattened badly rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Broke well, rolled wide to slot 2nd 1off no cover, under pump 550m, hard-driven turning, responded with grinding run to lead 200m, drew clear.
Speed to lead, restrained & headed 1630m, camped 1 back on rail, niggled 450m, driven 320m, battled on to 2nd close home.
Snagged back to rail from widest gate, last & niggled 650m, driven & shifted out final turn, rattled late to nick 3rd.
Smart break, rolled to lead 1630m, to rail 1st turn, extended 1.5L clear 500m, driven into stretch, all out & headed 200m, tapered & lost 2nd late.
Restrained at break & over-raced, sat rear 1 off until switched 3 deep with cover 940m, keen 850m, hard-ridden wide 500m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Broke OK & bustled to rail, raced midfield, driven 450m, switched out 250m, plugged on one pace.
Broke OK, settled rail behind midfield, hard-driven 500m, one-paced in tepid run home.
Moderate start, off heels 1570m, caught 3 wide no cover behind midfield, ridden 600m, wide into stretch, plodded one pace.
Tardy & crowded at break, recovered to sit 1 off 1 back in 4th, niggled 500m & soon hard-ridden, weakened tamely in stretch.
Slow start, sat rear rank 3 deep with cover until shifted to 1 off at 940m, under pump 600m, plodded on one pace.
Broke OK, bustled initially to sit midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 500m, wide on turn, struggled in run home.
Decent break & niggled initially, impeded 1570m, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 650m, driven 500m, snatched off heels 250m & eased.
Moderate start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, bustled along 420m, driven turning in, angled outside 150m, relentless run to overhaul lead close home.
Fast start, raced 4th 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 wide 450m & ridden for progress, swept to lead 200m, soon all out & tapered, headed close home.
Smart break, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, niggled 500m, hard-driven & wide into stretch, ran on centre track to claim 3rd.
Speed to lead & busted initially to hold lead by a neck, 1L clear & shaken up 300m, all out & headed 200m, faded.
Tardy start, bustled early & settled midfield on rail, niggled 500m, hard at it turning in, boxed on evenly down inner.
Taken back from widest gate to 1 off near tail, ridden turning in, stayed on in stretch for minor inroads.
Sharp break wide, rolled to press lead 1 off no cover, niggled 500m, 1L down & under pressure turning in, unable to quicken & plodded on tamely.
Broke well, snagged back but caught 3 wide no cover near rear, ridden along 600m & shifted to 1 off, plugged on in stretch.
Fast break, settled 1 back on rail, shifted wide & driven into stretch, found nil & struggled in run home.
Taken back from wide gate, slotted rail near rear & rolled to race back of midfield, driven final turn, struggled in run home.
Broke ok but lacked pace, raced 1 off behind midfield, under pump 3 wide 500m, found nil in stretch & eased.
Slow start, raced at tail on rail, never travelling & soon under pump, never a factor.
Eased at start, 7.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost considerable amount of ground at bends, dashed strongly 300M despite negative racing situations.
Hard ridden to share the lead along the fence, hung on well until last few strides overhauled, just missed by a head.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 7.5Ls off the leader, unleashed it strong finishing efforts 250M.
Slow away, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, ran on until 200M flattened.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, little dash 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain a spot in front of midfield, 2Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, no progress in final stages.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, no turn of foot.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide throughout just off the leaders, reduced 300M.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead 2 wide, soon weakened 300M.

Allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling three back from leader in one-off position. Crossed to fence turning for home, closed in gradually, got clear run top of straight and ran on strongly to the line.
Ridden along to hold forward position before easing one-back, one-off back stretch. Checked and lost ground passing 600m. Shifted out to make new challenge and finished strongly.
Pressed forward from wide draw but unable to cut in and forced to race three-wide without cover. Rolled forward passing 500m, led into straight, caught half-way up the straight but boxed on gamely.
Made full use of inside draw to grab box seat on settling. Allowed to stride at own pace before shifted out 400m to make run. Closed in to 200m when looked a chance before turning one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide gate but still held three-deep at the rear. Rolled forward around turn to look a chance entering straight. Kept on fairly till flattened 200m.
Ridden along between horses to stay with the pace, racing tightly 1300m and taken wide. Looked a chance when swung into straight but ran out of steam from 200m.
Slow into stride, taken to fence and made up some ground initially. Kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
No early speed, settling at rear away from fence. Taken out approaching turn, very wide into straight but found nothing under pressure.
Began well, racing inside leading pack before being passed 1000m. Retook lead 800m, put under pressure 500m, headed 300m and gave ground gradually.
No early speed and last on settling. Switched out turn and made up good ground. Wide into straight and tired gradually.
Hard ridden early to share early pace before being eased back 3L from leader approaching 800m. Turned wide and found nothing in straight.

Hard ridden to stay with leader, taking over 1000m but easing off 800m. Kept on under pressure till passing 600m when gave ground abruptly and dropped back through field becoming tailed off. (Performance unacceptable)
Had a ground saving trip along the fence, tracked pace from 700M, switched out nearing 400M, quickened to lead 200M, drew nicely clear at the finish.
Shoved to the lead soon after the break, led at a reasonable pace on soft going, unable to hold off winner 200M but continued on well to hold 2nd, clear from rest.
Never far off from leader 2-3Ls away, shaken up 450M, kept on steadily in the run to the line but couldn't reach first two.
About 3Ls behind leader, travelled 3-wide throughout, driven along 500M, stayed on moderately.
Reserved at the rear of the field, 5-6Ls of the pace middle stages, kept on to inside turning home, stayed on mildly, not reached first two.
Close up behind pace but 3-wide no cover throughout, kept on same pace final 350M. (Jockey dropped whip 150M)
Held up towards the rear, no closer than 3-wide throughout, bid widest 500M, stayed on fairly down outside, not reached leaders.
Began awkwardly, restrained in the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, ran on same pace final 400M, never a serious threat.
Held up behind mid-division, found disappointingly little inside 400M on soft going, never reached contention.
Held up in mid-division, saved ground on the inside, failed to go on passing 250M and dropped out. (Lame right fore)
Failed to slot in from draw 11, travelled wide without cover throughout, crept closer to pace middle stages but didn't respond to riding 500M out, soon gave ground.
Positively ridden out the gate, crossed from 12 to track leader, came under pressure rounding home turn, gave ground rapidly from 450M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)

Never far off, racing keenly behind leaders early, came to challenge inside the 200 metres and soon took charge, won readily.
Broke well to lead from the best draw attempting to make all, outsprinted inside final 150 metres.
Travelled keenly in midfield, took closer order after coming onto the course proper, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon came across from the lowest draw to join the leaders near stands rails, unable to sustain effort and faded under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Travelled keenly better than midfield without cover, gave ground steadily from the 300 metres.
Soon came across from a low draw to dispute the lead, folded up quickly inside final 250 metres.
Never better than midfield, faded under pressure closing stages.
Not far off in 5th, gave ground from the 300 metres.
Always well behind.
Always in last few.
Broke well, gradually shifted back to midfield on stands rails, gave ground steadily from the halfway mark.
Bumped at the start, never seen with a chance.
Jumped well and settled on pace, unbalanced at 900m, challenged strongly on straightening, fought hard in straight before eventually gaining upper hand final 150m.
Jumped well and sent forward to lead, travelling nice home turn, quickened nicely passing 400m, fought on strongly before overpowered final 150m.
Taken back from wide gate to settle at rear, travelled nicely home turn and ran home strongly.
Settled midfield, pushed along to issue a challenge at 400m, gradually made up ground in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, kept to inside in straight and made up nice ground in straight.
Pushed along early to settle behind leader, asked for effort at 400m but could not quicken, battled gamely to the line.
Taken bake from wide gate to settle towards rear, positive move around field near 500m, widest on straightening and made steady ground to the finish.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield, held up and crowded at 350m, one paced thereafter.
Settled on pace behind leaders, shifted out to issue challenge at 350m but could make no impression.
Settled worse than midfield, under pressure on straightening and one paced to the finish.
Settled on pace behind leaders, inclined to lay out in running, under pressure on straightening and weakened out of it.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, pushed along to settle worse than midfield, did not run on in straight.
Hard ridden forward to take the lead along the fence by 1.5Ls, kept on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 2nd.
Taken back to worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well to get 3rd.
Ridden forward to obtain the box seat, kept on steadily without any threatening in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, unable to show any acceleration in straight.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide early straight, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, kept on one paced until final furlong weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one paced until final 150M weakened.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3-4 wide with cover, never ran on.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, settled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on. (Questioned for running, see incidents report)
Taken back to last from a wide gate, 8Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Crowded start, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover from 900M, weakened soon after straightening.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Smart start, camped 1 back on rail, angled out & ridden 400m, quickened to lead 150m, edged away.
Broke well, bustled to lead 1080m, snagged rail, led 1L turning in, driven 400m, all out & headed 150m, fought on but no extra.
Broke well, taken back & caught 3 deep no cover fore of midfield, slotted in 1 off 700m, shifted out home turn but outpaced, stayed on for closing 3rd.
Broke OK, rousted initially to race fore of midfield on rail, shifted out & ridden home turn, edged inside for gradual inroads to wire.
Fast break, raced 1 off 1 back, shifted 3 wide no cover 650m, driven into stretch, boxed on evenly.
Sharp start, bustled to race 2nd 1 off no cover, 1L back & driven turning in, soon all out, battled to hold place until emptied 160m & faded.
Tardy start & rousted early, raced 3 deep with cover behind midfield, forced 4 wide 550m, plugged on one-pace centre track.
Outpaced at break, raced rail last pair, clear last & driven turning in, plugged on for minor headway.
Taken back at start, niggled at tail 1 off, under pump heading into final turn, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Moderate start, nudged along to sit midfield 1 off with cover, under pressure 550m & shifted wide into stretch, plugged on tepidly until emptied & faded late.
Broke ok but outpaced & bustled on rail behind midfield, niggled 700m, driven 500m, found nothing in weakening run home.
Missed break, mustered to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 500m & shifted out 420m, found nil & weakened out.
Fast start widest & soon led, crossed to rail 1350m, 1L clear & shaken up 420m, kicked on & scooted away, tapered late but clear.
Awkward start, niggled on rail midfield, checked off heels 500m & switched outside in stretch, driven 350m, closing when impeded rivals close home, nicked 2nd at wire.
Outpaced & rousted early, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, not clear run & stumbled on heels 310m, driven 250m, closed to 3rd late.
Tardy break & rousted early, mustered to race 1 off with cover midfield, edged 3 deep 500m, driven into stretch, progress to 2nd 200m, tapered out of frame late.
Tardy start & settled last pair 1 off, bustled 3 wide to improve 800m, driven 550m, ran on centre track, pressing for minors when back-end bumped close home.
Outpaced at break, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, advanced a spot 850m, shifted wide 550m, ran on to dispute 2nd 300m, tapered & swamped late.
Taken back from wide gate, raced rail near rear, checked off heels 500m, not clear run in stretch, kept on late but not fully tested.
Sluggish start, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 850m, driven wide home turn, closing on minors when badly impeded late & snatched up.
Fast break & bustled to rail 1 back, unable to quicken in stretch & plugged on tepidly.
Missed break & raced at tail on rail, minor advance 800m, shifted out & driven 430m, some headway when badly hampered & stumbled close home.
Smart break, sat rail fore of midfield, driven 350m, plodded on same pace.
Moderate start, mustered to race close 3rd 3 wide no cover, niggled 860m, driven into stretch, soon emptied & weakened out.
Sharp break, sat 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden under pressure 600m, found nil & faded tamely.
Broke OK, quickly dropped back through field despite urgings, at tail 800m, tailed off & eased turning in.
Pushed to secure box seat, ran on strongly to the line and scored.
Pushed forward, settled just off the leaders 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, unleashed its usual strong finishing efforts 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, little dash in straight.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead, emptied 300M.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, never progressed.
Slow away, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, no progress.
Pushed forward to share the lead 2 wide, soon reduced 350M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to gain a midfield spot along the fence, out of fuel 250M.
Eased at start, raced very wide at rear, never a factor.
Hard ridden from wide draw before cutting in and settling on rail three back from leader. Checked 500m when improving, pushed through gap 300m, kept finding when pressured final stages.
Began well, ridden along early settling 1L outside leader before turn. Urged forward top of straight, joint leader at 200m, kept on well to line.
Bumped after start, urged forward between horses settling 3L from leader. Rolled forward 400m to look a chance but awkwardly placed concluding stages and not ridden out.
Began OK, not much speed, settling behind midfield close to fence. Improved position turning for home, kept on well closing stages.
Pressed forward from good draw to hold box seat on settling. Urged forward entering straight to look a chance 200m but unable to find extra closing stages.
Slow into stride, hard ridden but didn't muster, settling at rear. Made some progress around turn, got inside run in straight, kept on fairly under hard riding.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide before settling 4L from leader. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Vigorously ridden from the start but failed to muster and held wide behind midfield. Kept on between horses without making much headway.
Badly hampered at start, dropping to last but away from fence. Taken wide entering straight, making up some ground initially before turning one-paced.
Pressed forward from wide draw to take lead before cutting to fence before turn. Collared soon after straighten and weakened gradually.
First into stride before being eased, settling 2L but two-wide from leader. Lost position turning for home but kept on fairly to 200m before weakening. Lame left front leg.
Outpaced and soon last along fence. Made up some ground around turn but never likely.
Ridden along early to stay in midfield but kept three-wide without cover from 800m. Started to give ground soon after straightening.
Outpaced, racing towards the rear but wide. Awkwardly placed from 700m and tailed off in straight. Performance considered unacceptable.
Restrained to near the rear, proved difficult to settle when pace slackened 800M, went through gap 250M and challenged strongly, got up 50M and drew off late stages.
Began only fairly, driven forward and crossed to lead 850M, slowed down tempo once in front, picked up pace again 300M, ran on well to the line only caught at 50M.
Held up in mid-division along the 2-path, swiftly into clear 400M, ran on well and loomed a threat 200M, not reached first two but finished a clear 3rd.
Taken across behind runners from 14, settled at the rear 7Ls off the pace, remained on inside throughout, steadied near 100M, kept on evenly to go 4th near line.
In touch behind leaders, advanced to 2nd 450M, strongly pressed leader early straight, run ended 150M and faded towards finish.
Held up midfield, settled along the inside, kept on the chase to 200M, one paced final stages.
Forwardly placed, stalked leader from 900M, lay out home turn, kept on steadily under pressure until no extra and faded over final 150M.
Settled behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, lay out entering straight, stayed on fairly, never reached contention.
Chased early pace, raced a shade keen, 3Ls off the pace 400M, kept on same pace in straight, never near leaders.
Slow to muster speed despite vigorously ridden, behind midfield and unable to slot in , taken widest home tur8th.n, not quickened inside 400M and passed only the tired ones.
Restrained from wide barrier, settled 7Ls off the pace in rear pair, shifted wide 600M, gave limited response entering straight, never involved.
Settled in mid-division, 3-wide no cover making the turn for home, weakened rapidly passing 300M. (Unacceptable Performance)
Fractious in stalls before the start, raced without cover and no closer than 4-wide throughout, came up empty entering straight and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)
Began OK, ridden along behind pacemakers while edging toward but three-wide from outer fence. Picked up momentum gradually, surged forward 200m, hit front 100m on way to easy win.
Quickly into stride, racing with pacemakers away from outer fence. Swooped to the front passing 700m, looked the winner 200m before swamped with 100m to go.
Fractious before start. Best out and led to 700m before settling in second close to outer fence. Began forward move passing 400m, kept on gamely without being able to close the gap.
Began quickly, pressed forward, settling third 2L from leader. Caught flat-footed 400m when leaders speeded up, picked up again and kept on gamely to the line.
Slow into stride then ridden along down centre track, racing mostly on its own behind midfield. Made progress from 400m, though never really dangerous.
Pressed forward to stay with pace, settling 3L from leader. Took closer order approaching 400m but one-paced after 200m.
Ridden along early to stay with pacemakers but kept away from outer fence. Got to within range of leader passing 400m but could not persevere and weakened final stages.
Crowded out start, taken to outer fence and made up ground quickly to within 3L of leader. Was still in contention passing 400m before weakening.
Slow into stride, recovered and made ground along outer fence to get within 7L of leader. Put under pressure from 400m but little response.
No early speed, left alone in midtrack and soon last. Stayed on inner track throughout, making up some late ground.
Bumped at start, taken towards outer fence, racing at the rear mostly. Never competitive. Found to have substantial blood in trachea.
Began fairly then crowded for room passing 950m and again 750m, dropping to rear about three-wide from outer fence. Never likely.
Began OK but failed to muster, dropping to near last along outer fence. Checked 600m and again 400m but never likely.
Unbalanced start, hard ridden to make up ground progressing to midfield 600m out. Weakened gradually.

Checked on jumping, but recovered to sit midfield on the rail. Switched inside for better position in the straight, before angling out again at 200m. Ran on strongly from there to roll 2nd on line, and hold out 3rd.

Began OK and eventually settled just forward of midfield, 2-3 wide. Came wider on the turn, and ran on strongly. Just peaked in the last 50m, allowing winner to get through, but held out fast finishing 3rd.

Began awkwardly, then bumped and unbalanced. Sat 2nd last on the fence until pushed forward 800m. Came off heels when pushing forward 600m. Came out looking for run 350m. Finished off best, and just missed 1 and 2.
Shifted out on jumping, then pushed forward to just behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Ran on OK in the straight, but had no kick when first three went past in the last 100m.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier to sit near the lead, but 4 wide no cover into the first turn. In a prominent position 300m, weakened late and dropped back.

Bumped and unbalanced jumping and taken back to sit near the rear of the field 4-5 wide early, before finding cover 2nd last mid race. Came 2nd widest on turn, finished off reasonably well, picking up some stragglers late.

Began well, and taken forward to sit in a handy position on the fence. Came wider for a run on the turn. Lost a run at the 250m, before coming off heels at 200m and losing ground. Finished fairly, without being pushed too hard.
Began OK, and pushed forward to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Dropping back by turn, and failed to finish off late.
Began very well, and pushed straight to lead early. Under a hold until asked to go at the 350m, but was one paced and easily passed by the majority of the field.
Unbalanced on jumping, before being pressed forward to sit 3rd, three off the fence. Asked the question on the turn, but never responded and faded badly from there.
Awkwardly away, and sat worse than midfield. Came widest on the turn, but didn't respond to pressure from 400m. Faded back, and eased out late.
Began OK, but dropped out quickly when hampered 1150m to sit 4 lengths off the 2nd last horse by the 800m. Never stretched out and faded from there. Only cantered to the line when well beaten.
Taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back in midfield, angled out near 500M, finished off well in straight to get 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader in 3rd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening the first two.
Bumped start, raced 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made some progress to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with some cover behind midfield throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently in 2nd, travelled well throughout, took the lead after turning in, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back at rear, there to turn, severely checked near 250M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, headed after turning in, kept on one-paced, emptied final 100M.
Taken back from a tricky draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, still 3 wide on turn, taken to the stands' side after straightening, failed to make any impact.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 4th, there to turn, failed to close off in straight and eased.
