Jumped moderately, travelled in last few early, made steady headway from half-way mark and around the bend to lead early in straight, asserted authority over 200 metres out. (Jockey injured during race)
Pressed on from a poor draw, settled not far off in 4th in back straight, commenced move rounding home bend hitting the front briefly entering straight but soon out-sprinted.
Jumped well, settled one back for cover after obtaining rails run on first bend, came under pressure to challenge entering straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled well back, circled the field from half-way out, wide in better than midfield in 6th entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Began moderately from the one draw settling in midfield on rails, failed to quicken under pressure from a similar position into straight.
Slightly slow out, travelled in last few, ran on past well-beaten horses from last into straight.
Jumped awkwardly, soon in rear of field, went widest into straight, only went past well-beaten horses. (Lame next day)
Vied for lead from a tricky gate before settling in midfield, faded steadily from a similar position into straight.
Settled in midfield from the widest gate, yielded ground steadily in straight.
Jumped fairly, never better than midfield, faded in the run home.
Broke well, soon took up running holding slender lead most of way to home straight, soon dropped out.
Niggled along from a poor draw settling in 5th just over 3L back on rails, soon faded under pressure after straightening.
Jumped well, settled in midfield early, raced awkwardly towards the rear far side, dropped out from approaching home bend.
Worked hard around the field from a wide draw to join the leader approaching back straight, folded up quickly from 600 metres out.
Jumped well and sent forward to settle on pace, crept closer passing 600m, challenged strongly on straightening eventually gaining upper hand to hold off all.
Crowded at start, settled midfield, positive move around field at 600m, challenged strongly at 300m before weakening final 100m.
Settled midfield, in need of clear running home turn, took time to get going and finished off strongly.
Crowded at start and settled at rear, pushed along and commenced to improve near 500m, widest on straightening and finished gamely.
Unable to muster early pace and settled worse than mid, taken wide home turn and battle to the line.
Taken back from wide gate to settle at rear, tried hard in straight and made up steady ground.
Pushed along early and settled leaders back, held up home turn but could on finish one paced.
Ridden hard early to settle midfield, held up for clear running near 300m, awkwardly placed at 200m and finished nicely once clear.
Jumped smartly and ridden along to settle midfield, pushed along to improve passing 500m but quickly under pressure and one paced to line.
Settled in front, urged along home turn but quickly under pressure and weakened out of it.
Took back at the start, trapped wide throughout, never a factor.
Jumped awkwardly but sent forward to settle on pace, loomed up to challenge on straightening but quickly dropped out of it.
Fast out and pushed along to go forward but caught wide and raced midfield without cover, under pressure home turn and weakened out of it.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, dashed on strongly to score easily by 3-1/4Ls.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly until final 100M headed by the impressive winner to get 2nd.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat in 5th position, ran on steadily for 3rd.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, gradually improved rounding the Home Turn, ran on well for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on until final 150M weakened.
Travelled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Ridden forward to find a cover from a wide gate, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, weakened 300M.
Pushed forward to take the fence and share the lead, soon flattened after straightening.
Eased at start, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Broke ok, settled in rear rank on rail, advanced 800m to within 2L turning in, shaken up 400m & shifted out 330m, driven to lead 200m & drew clear.
Fast start & prominent, soon snagged back & niggled along 1 off with cover midfield, outpaced & driven on turn, picked up mid-stretch & closed to wire.
Good break, taken back to 3 wide with cover midfield, shifted wide final turn & driven, solid closer to claim 3rd.
Broke ok, rousted early & worked forward to track 1 back 1 off, under pump throughout, boxed on to 2nd 120m, tapered out of frame late.
Broke OK, taken back from widest gate to race 3 wide with cover near rear, very wide turning in & driven, stayed on mid-track for minor headway.
Sluggish but immediately mustered to lead 1050m, headed 970m & settled outside leader, shaken up to lead 350m, all out & headed 200m, faded.
Lacked early pace & raced behind midfield, soon shifted back & niggled in rear rank 620m, driven 400m, plugged on evenly.
Smart start, rousted to lead 3 deep, headed 1050m & settled 4th without cover, weakened tamely in stretch.
Broke well, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, niggled 550m, ,driven 430m, found nil in tame run home.
Sharp break, hard-ridden on rail to lead 970m, pressed turning in & driven, found nil & headed 350m, faded out.
Taken back from wide gate to race back of pack 1 off, to rail 650m, driven 400m but found nothing.
Slow start & rousted, soon detached, tailed off & never a factor.
Broke ok, raced 3 wide no cover until pushed forward to track 1 off in 2nd 1030m, nudged along 2.5L back at 600m, driven 400m & grinding run to lead 100m, held on.
Decent break, settled midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 600m, shifted wide & hard-ridden final turn, closed centre track & flew late, just failed.
Fast start, soon led & crossed to rail 1400m, rolled 2.5L clear 600m, cuddled into stretch, shaken up 350m, joined 200m, battled until headed 100m & tapered.
Fast break & settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, pushed 3 wide no cover 950m, driven 550m, closed off for solid headway without threatening.
Decent start, niggled on rail to sit handy, shuffled back to midfield 1000m, niggled 900m & recovered to 3rd 750m, under pump 450m, kept on evenly.
Snagged back from widest gate to rail near rear, niggled 750m, progress out of backstretch, 7L back & driven 400m, closing when checked off heels 150m, ran on for late gains.
Broke ok, settled back 3 wide with cover near tail, shuffled to 10L last turning in & driven widest, closed off centre track for solid late inroads.
Missed break & raced at tail, over-raced 950m, minor progress on turn, 9L back & shaken up 400m, shifted out & stayed on for moderate headway.
Sharp break, crossed to sit 2L 2nd on rail1300m, soon shuffled back, 4th at 750m when niggled, driven 450m to vie for 3rd, emptied 200m & faded.
Restrained at start, sat 1 off with cover near rear, bustled for progress out of backstretch, hard-ridden turning in, one-paced to wire.
Tardy start, taken to rail near rear & soon advanced to race midfield, minor progress out of backstretch, ridden turning in, plodded on tepidly.
Sluggish start, mustered to race back of midfield but 5 wide no cover, hard-ridden 450m, struggled & faded.
Broke ok, bustled 4 wide no cover 1st turn, settled 3 wide no cover midfield until forced 4 wide 950m, driven 550m, weakened tamely in stretch.
Tardy break & bustled to behind midfield 4 wide with cover, lost ground on turn & ridden, found nil in run home.
Settled just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the soft early sectionals, ran on well to the line and scored.
Hard ridden to hold the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Slow away, 4Ls off the leader on the rails, dashed well 250M for 3rd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 7Ls off the leader, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
At back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 200M.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, soon reduced 400M.
Very slow away, never competitive, tailed out.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3 wide, dropped off rapidly 600M.
Began fairly, ridden to stay in midfield one-away from fence. Shaken up passing 500m, turned 4-wide and ran on steadily to win on the line.
Ridden to stay with pacemakers before settling three-back along the fence 2L from leader. Had clear run entering straight, urged forward to lead100m but run down close to line.
Bumped start, ridden vigorously but failed to muster, settling in midfield. Shaken up around turn, made steady progress in straight to be closest at the finish.
First out, led to 1200m before dropping into box seat. Put under pressure top of straight and battled on gamely to make the frame.
Jumped with field but eased back to find cover, settling at rear one-away from fence. Began forward move 600m racing three and four wide around field, very wide into straight, battled on gamely.
Began awkwardly, then pushed along between horses behind midfield. Made progress around turn and kept on well in straight without looking dangerous.
Ridden along early though kept wide, before settling behind midfield. Got shuffled back around turn to near last before making up some ground in the straight.
Began well, racing keenly outside leader before taking over lead passing 1200m. Kept on strongly to 100m when running on empty and swamped.
Steadied soon after start then bumped and unbalanced, dropping to rear. Raced keenly approaching turn and blundered. Ran on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing three wide in midfield along backstretch and turn. Made up some ground early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Crowded shortly after start, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Got shuffled back turn, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, outpaced, settling towards rear along fence. Hard ridden from 500m but no response.
Pressed forward from start, settling third 2L from leader. Started to give ground midway through final. Never likely.
Ridden along from wide draw but unable to find cover and kept three-wide outside leader passing 800m. Lost position around turn and found nothing in straight.

Began awkwardly, close up along the fence 2Ls off leader, unable to improve behind leaders from 450M, quickened up well when clear 250M, led 130M and continued on willingly to win in class record time.
Shifted across behind runners, 7-8Ls off the pace in the rear, shifted to outside 400M, closed off strongly to get up for 2nd near line, not reached winner.
Towards the rear, 5Ls off the pace middle stages, held up inside 500M, squeezed through a narrow gap to lead 300M, headed 130M, run ended and lost 2nd last few strides.
Soon taken across behind runners, settled at the rear group 7Ls behind leader, no clear run until 300M, stayed on moderately for non- threatening 4th.
Held up mid-division, never far off from pace, wide bid 500M, kept on same pace in straight, outdashed over final 200M.
Settled along the fence in mid-pack, angled out 3-deep near 500M, loomed a threat early straight, run ended 200M and weakened.
Travelled 3-wide in midfield with cover, came widest home turn, kept on same pace to line, never a serious threat.
Restrained near the rear along the 3-path, not picked up entering straight and soon left behind by leaders.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, ended up near the tail of the field 5Ls off the pace, didn't have a lot to offer and only ran past well beaten runners in straight.
Positively ridden, settled just off the pace and appeared to be travelling well, took over 400M but failed to go on from 300M, gave ground rapidly. (Jockey questioned)
Shaken up early, shared the lead at a steady tempo, slowed things down home turn, had little left passing 400M and soon on the retreat.
Caught wide on the 1st turn, strolled forward to race outside leader 1200M, came up empty 350M, soon weakened and finished tailed-out. (Unacceptable Performance)
Unable to slot in from 13, caught wide no cover behind leading pair throughout, weakened in straight and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)

Settled just worse than midfield, responded well after straightening to take charge over 150 metres out, won comfortably.
Settled behind midfield on rails, baulked for a run early in straight until the 200 metres, ran on to snatch 2nd close to home.

Broke well from a poor draw, slightly better than midfield when raced keenly and steadied approaching home bend, midfield into straight, ran on quite well to reach 2nd passing the 200 metres, unable to sustain run close to home.
Broke well from a middle draw, settled mainly one-out-one-back in 3rd or 4th, hit the front under pressure briefly over 200 metres out, soon swamped.
Gradually settled at the back, trailed the field and went widest into straight, made modest headway while hanging in under pressure.
Settled in midfield on rails, shifted out to challenge upon straightening, kept on steadily without quickening.
Broke well from a wide gate to soon take up running setting a sound pace around the bend, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 250 metres.
Crossed to rails at the back from the widest gate, settled a couple from last to straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Ridden along before settling for 5th just better than midfield and over 3L off the lead, remained similar turning for home but found no extra after straightening.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, gradually improved to settle in 4th or 3rd just over 2L off the pace, faded steadily shortly after turning into straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, settled in last few, saved ground turning in, made no impression in straight.
Slow to begin, always in last few, one-paced in straight.
Jumped fairly, ridden positively before settling one-back on or near the rails, folded up quickly after straightening.
Moderate start, travelled keenly towards the rear, shifted wider rounding home bend, soon struggled. (Bled)
Jumped smartly and sent straight to the lead, travelled strongly and always in control.
Fast out and settled behind leader, travelling strongly and tried to challenge at 300m but no match for winner despite finishing well.
Jumped smartly and urged forward to race on pace, travelled well midrace, fought on strongly right to the line.
Allowed to settle behind leaders, urged along passing 400m, got going final 100m to finish nicely.
Fast out to race on pace, under pressure at 300m when pace quickened, one paced to the finish.
Positive early to settle midfield, under pressure from 400m but battled solidly to finish.
Settled worse than midfield, picked up midrace and finished off nicely final 400m.
Crowded at start, settled towards rear, hampered at 450m, one paced to the finish.
Crowded at start, quick gathered pace to race on speed, unable to quicken passing 400m and commenced to weaken from 200m.
Jumped fairly, settled midfield, always towards rear.
Commenced awkwardly, settled midfield, quickly under pressure at 400m and unable to make ground.
Settled rearward and never in it.
No early pace, under pressure at 400m and weakened out of it.
No early pace, always rearward.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the strong pace, ran on strongly to score by a short head.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, dropped to midfield when the pace quickened 700M, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well to get 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the strong tempo, dashed well for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 4th.
Jumped awkwardly, then pushed to settle in a handy position, made an early moved from 1200M gradually, kept on steadily in straight.
Midfield early, made an early moved from 1100M gradually, placed pressure 600M, kicked 4Ls clear 300M, however weakened over the last furlong.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the strong pace, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, checked 700M, despite the fast sectionals, kept on one pace in straight without any threats.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite benefited by the strong tempo, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, found cover when the pace quickened 1000M, harmed by the fast pace, soon weakened after straightening.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Raced midfield, however trapped 4 wide without cover until 1200M, despite the fast tempo, unable to show any dash in straight. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Taken back from wide gate, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the strong tempo, never ran on.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led early, dropped to the box seat 1000M, emptied rounding the Home Turn.
Bustled & prominent from gate, camped rail 1 back, shifted 1 off 420m, shaken up 400m & joined leader 200m, grinding duel, bumped but edged verdict at wire.
Tardy start, mustered to track pace 1 off no cover, gained cover 1200m & raced 2L 4th, under pump & shifted out for progress 550m, led 280m, duelled & bumped rival, lost on nod.
Missed break, mustered to midfield 1 off with cover, slight check turning in, shaken up 400m, battled on between runners to nick 3rd at wire.
Outpaced at break, bustled to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 1000m, shifted very wide 500m & driven, rattled home late, just missed frame.
Good start, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, ridden briefly 500m, progress checked 420m, shifted out & driven, closed to 3rd 200m, tapered & swamped.
Moderate start & sat behind midfield 3 wide with cover, over-raced 1300m, minor advance 1100m, inroads under strong drive but hung erratically in stretch, impeded rival 100m.
Taken behind to race near tail on inner, shifted out & driven turning in, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke ok, taken back to 3 wide with cover near rear, driven 400m, kept on for minor inroads.
Broke well, caught 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, driven turning in & shifted out, plugged on one pace, bumped & snatched up 100m, eased.
Broke OK, caught 4 wide no cover midfield, rolled to 2nd 1250m & parked outside leader, 1L 2nd & ridden under pressure 480m, soon swamped & wilted.
Snagged back at start, niggled at tail, ridden 400m, struggled in tame run home.
Fast start, rolled to lead, to rail 1450m, 1L clear & shaken up 420m, emptied 300m, headed 280m & faded out.
Sluggish start, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 1000m, hard-ridden into stretch, found nil & weakened.
Broke well, sat rail midfield, niggled 600m & hard ridden under pressure soon after, struggled in run home.
Good break, raced rail fore of midfield, shifted out & shaken up 400m, gradual closer to lead 100m, drew clear.
Fast break to race handy & settled 1 off with cover 4th, pulled out & driven 400m, grinding run to edge lead 150m, headed 100m, just held on for 2nd.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted wide & ridden 430m, quickened to close, nicked 3rd late.
Broke ok from wide gate, slotted 1 off with cover fore of midfield, ridden 500m & edged out, kept on dourly without threatening.
Sharp start, soon niggled & sat rail midfield, driven 430m & initially tapped for toe, stayed on for solid late headway.
Slow start & ridden, settled near rear 1 off with cover, shifted wide & hard-ridden into stretch, stayed on centre track for minor inroads.
Sharp start widest, worked deep to slot 2nd 1 off no cover at 950m, driven 420m, lacked toe and plugged on same speed.
Sharp break & pushed to lead, snagged rail 1200m & raced 1L clear, all out & headed 150m, tapered out.
Broke well but taken back, soon mustered to camp midfield 1 off with cover, switched out 430m, lacked toe & plugged on evenly.
Tardy start, sat rail near rear, under pump 550m, struggled in run to wire.
Slow start & bumped, raced rail last pair, driven into stretch, plodded on tamely.
Fast break, sat 1 back on rail, hard-ridden 400m but found little in tepid run home.
Shifted right & bumped rivals at break, sat last pair 1 off, clear last & niggled 800m, under pump 600m, plodded on, never a factor.
Moderate break & bumped, raced 3 wide no cover near rear, driven widest into final turn, found nothing & faded to last.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, lack room 400M, dashed strongly when clear and scored with some in hand.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, harmed the slow pace, unleashed its strong finishing efforts 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, took rail and lead just prior to the 800M turn, benefited by the slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased to rear, 8.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in final stages.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to the rail and lead, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 400M.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, ran on well until 200M emptied.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, reduced 300M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Very slow away, never competitive and tailed out.

Allowed to slide forward at own pace, holding rail three-back from leader. Stayed on rail until final turn when switched out for clear run. Hit front 300m out and kept finding under pressure for narrow win.
Began OK, not pushed and allowed to settle towards the rear in a one-off position. Bumped and unbalanced final turn, switched out for clear running and ran on strongly to just miss out.
Ridden early to stay with pacemakers, settling 3rd about 2L from leader. Took closer order turning for home, got clear run top of straight, finished off strongly.
Not pushed early, settling three-back, one-off. Not asked for an after until straightening for home when made ground gradually to be closest at the finish.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after the start and clear last on settling. Still last entering straight but found inside runs and finished off strongly.
Bumped start, no speed, settling at rear along the rail. Hampered and unbalanced passing 1600m, shaken up final turn, kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Began well, ridden along outside leader before settling 2L behind but away from fence. Urged forward turning for home, led soon after straightening before running out of condition and fading.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set slow sections to straight when tired quickly and finished tailed off. Stewards said performance unacceptable.
Not hurried after the jump, settled down 3Ls back in midfield, into clear 400M, picked up strongly under mainly hands and heels riding, drew away for another comfortable win.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, took time to pick up entering straight, did best work final 200M and got up for clear 2nd over the concluding stages, no impression on easy winner.
Strolled forward to share lead, set steady pace to straight, kept on well under 10lbs claiming rider, not finishing pace of first two final 150M but battled on to hold 3rd.
Positive ridden, shared lead on the outside, kept on evenly under pressure inside 300M, not finishing pace of first two final 150M, narrowly lost out on 3rd at the line.
Took keen hold in a midfield spot along the 2-path, shifted out 550M, ran on steadily for moderate 5th. (Lost right hind plate 250M)
Settled down 3-wide ahead of mid-division, 6th for most of the way, stayed on mildly over final 300M.
Close up behind leaders along the fence, shifted out for clear passage 350M, ran on one pace, never on terms.
Never far off 2-3Ls behind leading pair, kept on same pace entering straight and not trouble leaders, faded final stages.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield along the inside, 9th turning into straight, couldn't pick up under pressure, never reached contention.
Eased back from wide barrier, travelled 3-wide towards the rear, over 6Ls to make up 400M, not quickened when asked, no danger.
Taken back to the rear from wide barrier, 7-8Ls off the pace halfway, one pace and no threat final 400M.
Tracked leading pair but caught 3-wide no cover throughout, came up empty 300M, weakened rapidly.
Dropped back to rear from widest barrier, 7Ls off leaders along the rails, one pace and no impression after straightening.
Began only fairly, towards the rear and proved difficult to settle, gave ground from 400M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)
Hard ridden early to hold rail inside leading pack before easing into box seat 1000m. Held up for run top of straight before getting rails run. Pushed through to lead 200m before pulling clear.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Began forward move 500m, widest into straight, finished strongly while hanging in to get second.
Bounced well, hard ridden to hold position before easing three-back the rail. Not much room top of the straight, got rails run passing 200m and finished off nicely.
Ridden along from an outside draw, racing wide about 3L from leader. Took closer order entering straight to look a chance 200m. Kept on well under pressure.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide about 1.5L from leader at turn. Urged forward on straightening, led momentarily passing 200m, then inconvenienced when passed and not ridden out.
Hard ridden from wide draw, racing 4-wide into turn but only 2L from leader. Tightened 500m but kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Began well, ridden forward, settling one-back, one-off. Got close to heels around turn, not much room top of straight, kept on fairly until weakening final stages.
Began OK, no speed, settling at rear in one-off position. Checked turn, shuffled back to last entering straight, switched wide but only one-paced final 200m.
Jumped with field, pressed forward racing 3-wide. Not much room 800m when bumped and taken wider. Bumped twice up the straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along between horses some 4L behind leader before being hampered at turn. Switched wide in straight but found little under hard riding.
Jumped well but not much speed and held wide at the rear. Covered extra ground around turn and one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward to share early lead before settling outside leader around turn. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
No early speed, settling along fence at rear. No run top of straight, then got close to heels. One-paced straight.

Strolled forward from jump to lead on settling. Tried to steady pace but became keen when joined by another runner. Looked to be going well entering straight but came under pressure from 300m and faded.

Began well from widest gate. Not used up and sat midfield 4-5 wide before moving forward to sit handy 3 wide mid race. Kicked from turn, but never fully clear, and had just enough to hold on late in a very tight finish.

Began fairly, before pushing forward to sit just behind leader 1 off the fence with cover after 900m. Clean run in the straight, on inside of winner. Got head in front 100m, but reached the end near line and just held 2nd.
OK away, and dropped back to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence with cover. Began a run on the turn. Lost whip at 350m but finished off strongly, only ridden hands and heels to the line.
Dropped back from the wide barrier to sit near the rear of the field 3-4 wide early. Came widest on turn, and one of the strongest finishers late, just missing a place in a very tight finish.
Began OK, and came across to sit midfield, 3 wide. Kept on well in straight, but run down late on outside for a place.
Began OK from the wider gate to eventually sit a half-length behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Struggled to improve in straight and peaked 100m out, dropping out in a highly contested finish.
Began well, and allowed to push forward to take an uncontested lead early. Asked the question 300m, and was prominent until peaking 100m and swamped late.

Began OK, but unsettled when awkwardly placed in the back straight, before settling midfield 1 off the fence. Awkwardly placed on heels when looking for a run 400m, and only got the chance to stretch out in last 100m.
Began awkwardly, before coming off heels. Eventually got to a position worse than midfield, 3 off the fence. Came 2nd widest on turn, but failed to run on late.
Awkwardly away then hampered, eventually settling worse than midfield on the rail. Let down from the 300m, but never kicked.
Dropped back from the wide barrier to sit last, 3 wide with cover. Stayed with the main body, but never improved late.
Began well, and not pushed out to sit midfield on the rail. Briefly tightened at 350m, but didn't find much in the run home.
Fractious in the barrier before jumping well to sit in a handy position behind the leader on the rail. Under pressure before the turn, but never responded and faded from 300m, and eased out late.
Slow away and sat at the rear of the field. Didn't settle and checked off heels through 1300m. Saddle shifted, and never in the race before being eased out from 300m.

Settled just off the pace on rails, soon came to challenge upon straightening, fought on dourly to gain upper hand close to home.
Soon took up running under pressure attempting to make all, unable to sustain effort and worn down inside final 100 metres.
Broke well before settling in midfield, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on well without threatening.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, saved ground on rails turning in, ran on steadily under pressure down inner of straight.
Settled in rear of midfield on rails, clipped heels and lost position 700 metres out, saved ground on rails turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well, gradually taken back just off the pace, similar turning in but found nothing in straight.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, widest runner into straight, ran on steadily.
Began fairly, settled 3-wide in rear of midfield, swung wider into straight, ran home one-paced.
Travelled in a prominent position 3-wide without cover, found no extra from approaching home turn.
Never seen with a chance.
Ridden along from the middle gate, gained a spot outside leader early in back straight, dropped out under pressure over 400 metres out. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped awkwardly, settled leaders back, eased out of heels at 400m, let down nicely at 300m to hold off all challengers.
Eased back behind runners to settle towards rear, pushed along to improve passing 600m, finished strongly in straight.
Eased back to rear from wide gate, kept to rail home turn, gradually eased out to obtain clear running in straight and finished off nicely.
Slow out and raced at rear, finished nicely making up good ground in straight.
Settled midfield, pushed along to improve near 500m, worked home steadily.
Settled on pace, unable to improve home turn, battled to line one paced.
Jumped well, eased to settle forward of midfield, kept to rail in straight and fought right to finish.
Crowded at start, settled midfield, tried hard in straight and made up some ground.
Settled worse than midfield, one paced in straight.
Jumped well, settled midfield, under pressure home turn, one paced in straight.
Sent forward to lead, under pressure home turn and weakened out of it.
Settled behind leaders, unable to quicken in straight and dropped out of it.
Pushed forward to settle in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, quickened well to score by 3/4L.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead on the fence, hung on strongly until final 50M headed by the winner.
Hard ridden forward to obtain the box seat, kept on nicely to get 3rd.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on nicely until final 50M weakened.
Failed to muster pace, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Hard ridden to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground until latter stages weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, never ran on.
Settled in front of midfield 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on only fairly in straight.
Niggled along throughout, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
At rear throughout, never looked competitive.
Good start, dropped back to 3 wide midfield, closed to sit handier 700m & slotted 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide turning in & driven, swept home to lead final stride.
Fast break, worked outside to lead 1000m, clear & to rail 770m, soon pressed, shaken up 320m & kicked clear, tapered late & mugged at wire.
Smart break, soon niggled 4L back 1 off with cover, closed to 1L 3rd 700m, lost touch with front pair on turn, driven 320m, boxed on evenly.
Snagged back at start, trapped wide no cover near rear, rolled 3 deep to press lead 1 off at 700m, 1L 2nd & driven 300m, fought on evenly until tapered late.
Tardy start & rousted, raced rail near rear, 2nd last & niggled 450m, steady inroads when switched out for clear ground 150m, closed off for minor late headway.
Broke ok, taken back to 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m & hard-ridden turning in, lacked toe but stayed on for minor late headway.
Moderate break, raced 3 wide no cover behind midfield, rolled on to 6th exiting back side, driven 450m, stayed on evenly.
Bustled to early lead, to rail 1050m, eased & headed 1000m to sit 1 back, 3L 4th & under pump 500m, lacked toe & weakened out.
Fast break to race 3rd on fence, shuffled back to midfield 800m, bustled 550m, hard-ridden & shifted out into stretch, plodded on one pace.
Taken back at start, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m, ridden wide into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Missed break, recovered to 1 off with cover near rear, bustled 500m, driven 420m, plugged on tepidly.
Missed break, raced at tail 1 off, over-raced 700m, under pump 500m, struggled in run home.
Broke ok, outpaced & bustled to sit behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven 300m & edged out, quickened centre track & ran on to get up close home.
Good break & driven to lead 1040m, sat 1 off, headed 870m & raced close 2nd, shaken up to lead 270m, kicked 1.5L clear, emptied late & headed close home.
Broke ok, bustled to settle 1 back on rail, shaken up turning in but in pocket & checked 230m, switched 1 off, kept on for 3rd but always held.
Broke ok, rolled to stalk pace 1 off 1 back, shaken up final turn, boxed on to 2nd 150m but no extra in closing stages & edged out of frame.
Lacked pace at break, raced rail behind midfield & rousted briefly 800m, bustled along 500m, stayed on under drive.
Slowly away & niggled last pair 1 off, edged 3 wide 400m, very wide turning & driven, boxed on dourly centre track.
Fast break, pushed through on rail to lead 870m, driven turning n, all out & headed 270m, faded thereafter.
Broke ok widest, raced 4 wide with cover back of midfield, very wide final turn & driven, plugged on evenly.
Sharp start, caught 4 wide no cover 2L back, rolled on to within 1L 500m, found nil in run home.
Smart start & prominent initially, settled 1 back 3 wide, shuffled back 650m & niggled, driven into stretch, struggled in run.
Snagged to tail at start & raced rail, edged to 1 off 450m, last into stretch & driven, struggled in run home.
Speed to lead, eased a touch & headed 1040m, raced on pace 3 wide no cover until snagged to 1L back at 720m, driven turning in but emptied & weakened tamely.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden early to keep up in midfield but trapped 3 wide, 3Ls off the good pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, checked early, 3.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to secure the box seat, pace good, flattened 200M.
Awkward away, 6.5Ls off the leader on the rails, demonstrated good finishing efforts 250M.
Slow away, eased back, 5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground in straight.
At rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace, made some ground 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at good pace, ran on until 250M emptied.
Eased back from wide draw, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no turn of foot in straight.
Slow away, 4.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, reduced quickly 400M.
Began well, ridden along to hold position one-back, one-off. Picked up momentum soon after entering straight and just managed to get to the line on time.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set solid sections, kicked 3L clear top of the straight but unable sustain effort and run down final strides.
Ridden to hold rail position, three back from leader. Not asked for effort until straightening for home when picked up momentum and finished strongly.
Pressed forward while looking for cover, settling 4-back from leader into first turn. Switch wide passing 350m, and finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Ridden early to hold forward position, settling three-back, one-off into first turn. Not pressured until straightening for home, picked up the bit 200m and finished of nicely.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader going into first turn. Stayed about 1L behind to straight, kept on gamely but swamped final stages.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw settling along rail in last pair. Improved position final turn, and kept on fairly in the straight without looking dangerous.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling in one-off position. Hampered and taken wide passing 400m, inconvenienced 200m when making ground, kept on fairly.
Pushed along early to hold rail, lay out around first turn but held on to box seat. Put under pressure 350m but only one-paced.
Began OK, not pressured, settling at rear away from fence. Hampered and taken wider approaching 400m, wide into straight, one pace.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw, settling behind midfield but away from fence. Bumped approaching 400m and taken wider, one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, stumbled, settling towards rear along fence. Attempted for improve position turning for home but found nothing. Jockey reported did not stretch out at any stage.
Reserved in midfield on the fence, travelled well to straight, moved up strongly along the inside to take lead nearing 100M, held off late challenge of 2nd.
Settled down near the rear, saved ground on inner, held up early straight, closed off strongly over final 200M, just failed.
Took up early running, tracked leader from 900M, kept on steadily over final 300M, bumped 100M and shifted out, recovered in time to take 3rd.
Unable to slow in from 10, 3-wide no cover early stages, strode forward to the lead 1000M, responded well entering straight, headed nearing 100M, drifted out under pressure late stages.
Soon taken across to the rails, settled down at the back 8Ls off the pace halfway, taken wide home turn, still last at 200M, closed strongly late stages to get 5th..
Positively ridden from wide barrier, restrained to sit behind leader entering back-straight, kept on one pace and found less than expected, well held by leaders.
Began well from inside draw, never far off from leaders, switched out from fence near top of straight but held up until 200M, ran on same pace when clear.
Slow to begin, in last until 1000M, 3-wide back-straight and crept closer home turn, stayed on mildly, nor reached leaders.
Taken back on jumping from 12, caught wide throughout and no cover from 1000M, pushed along 500M to reach a contending position, kept on one pace, checked 100M and eased.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, shuffled back towards the rear back-straight, driven 400M out but gave limited response, steadied 100M but beaten already.
Began only fairly, failed to show early speed, travelled in 7th in midfield further back than intended, shoved along 450M, not quickened and never reached a contending position.
Shaken up early to take up a forward position, raced keenly, in 4th making the turn for home, failed to find extra when placed under pressure.

Began moderately, settled just worse than midfield, came to challenge upon straightening, fought on dourly to gain upper hand final strides.
Broke well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on rails, soon came to challenge after straightening holding every chance throughout final 300 metres only to be caught close to home.
Driven from the widest draw to soon take up running on rails attempting to make all, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 100 metres.
Never far off, shared 4th in about 2L back into straight, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.
Ridden along behind midfield gaining closer on rails coming out of back straight, snuck up to joint 4th turning in, kept on for 5th.
Well there to 100 metres, weakened.
Settled at the back, wide trailing the field into straight, steadied for a stride 400 metres out, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Soon dropped to last, hampered coming out of back straight, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced after straightening.
Raced wide throughout, ridden along early before taken back to rear of midfield without cover, widest runner turning in, faded in straight.
Tightened at start dropping well back, took slightly closer order when wide around home bend, beaten when hampered 250 metres out, one-paced thereafter.
Jumped in midfield, gradually settled behind midfield on rails, came under pressure around home bend, fought nothing.
Raced wide in better than midfield from a poor draw, remained similar entering straight, found no extra. (Tactic questioned)
Raced 4-wide in a prominent position far side, shuffled back towards the rear around the bend, no further impression.
Raced mainly 3-wide between runners in better than midfield, in similar position turning in, folded up quickly after straightening.
Fast out and straight to the front, travelling easy home turn, quickened nicely on straightening, kicking clear to win easily.
Pushed along early to hold position midfield, eased out home turn to challenge and finished strongly.
Jumped well and settled midfield, widest on straightening and finished strongly.
Went back from wide gate, urged along near 500m, kept to rail and made up good ground in straight.
Jumped well and settled behind leader, unable to quicken on straightening and battled to the line.
Pushed along early but could only settle midfield, urged along at 500m to improve and battled strongly to finish.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled worse than midfield, commenced to improve passing 600m and worked home nicely.
Ridden along early to settle on speed, tried hard to challenge home turn but could not respond and weakened final 200m.
No early pace and settled at rear, passed tired horses in the straight.
Sent forward from wide gate and raced wide without cover until 700m, under pressure at 500m and weakened in straight.
Jumped smartly and settled midfield, worked home one paced in straight, crowded at 300m.
Crowded on jumping and settled at rear, hard ridden home turn and one paced to the line.
Eased back from wide gate to settle towards rear, under pressure home turn and finished one paced.
Jumped awkwardly and ridden along to settle on speed, under pressure from 800m and weakened out of it soon after.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat along the fence, switched wide turning in, dashed strongly to score by 2Ls with plenty in hand.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung widest rounding the Home Turn, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on strongly until final 250M headed by the impressive winner, hung on for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight despite blocked for some distance 200M.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on only fairly in straight without any acceleration.
Eased to worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made some ground despite inclined to lay in in straight. (Substantial amount of blood in its trachea)
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace in straight.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, soon after straightening weakened. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until 300M flattened.
Missed break, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, failed to show any acceleration in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, flattened badly soon after straightening, tailed out.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor, collapsed after the race.

Began well, eased, taken to fence and made progress settling four back from leader. Popped off fence 550m, held in restricted room to 200m when switched out and finished off strongly to win close home.
Began well, allowed to slide forward at own speed, settling between horses 3-back from leader. Held for clear run early in straight, took split 350m out, hit from 200m, run down close to the wire.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing wide before settling one-back, one-off into turn. Looked a chance when contesting lead 200m out but unable to match first two closing stages.
Began OK, settling along fence three-back from leader. Improved position around turn to get within 3L of leader entering straight. Kept on gamely but badly held for a run final 100m.

Began awkwardly and then held in restricted room. Hard ridden but didn't improve and held wide in midfield 4L from leader. Made progress from turn but tended to lay in under pressure and difficult ride final stages.
Jumped well, taken to the front before easing into box seat 1200m. Came off fence on straightening for home but unable to get clear running concluding stages and not fully tested.
Eased back soon after start, taken to fence and last on settling. Made no move until straightening for home when took inside run and finished off nicely.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader back stretch. Hit front on straightening, joined up front 200m, weakened.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, settling towards rear close to fence. Improved position around turn and early in straight before tiring final 100m.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling towards rear but in one-off position. Steadied around turn, switched out straight, one-paced.
Ridden along to hold forward position, racing mostly 3-wide without cover. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Began well, racing along fence inside leaders before forging to the front approaching 1100m. Caught soon after straightening for home but kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Began OK but unable keep up with the field and clear last around turn. Never likely.
Hard ridden from start, racing three-wide at the rear and mostly without cover. Weakened badly in the straight and tailed off.
Hard ridden to lead on settling. Set fair pace stringing out field. Kicked 2L clear entering straight and then kept finding more under pressure to just hold on.
Began well quickly settling in box seat behind leader. Put under pressure on straightening, gradually closing in on leader to just fail.
Pressed forward from wide draw, sitting outside leader early stages before settling 3rd, 2L back. Gave chase soon after straightening but unable to close gap to first two.
Began well but unable handle early pace settling three-back, one-off. Taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Quickly into stride, racing wide without cover 3L from leader. Three-wide into straight and boxed on gamely without looking a threat.
Began OK, taken closer to fence but began racing ungenerously from 1000m. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along early to hold rail position three back from leader. Close in around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw. settling last. Made some progress around turn but only one-paced in straight.
No early speed settling behind midfield close to fence. Put under pressure a long way from home but made little progress. Rider reported not suited by pace and never comfortable in action.
No early pace, dropping to rear soon after start. Put under pressure turning for home but found nothing.
Ridden along early to hold position behind midfield but wide. Weakened gradually in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Shuffled back to last around turn and never likely after that.
Eased back, 11Ls off the good pace 2 wide, dashed well 300M to score.
Midfield, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, box seat, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, 3.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace on the rails, just held ground in final stages.
At back, 9Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on fairly in straight.
Behind midfield, 8Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Eased to rear, 12Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground 200M.
Eased at start, too cover at rear, 12Ls off the good pace, made minor ground 200M.
In front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace on the rails, flattened 250M, on heels 200M.
Eased back, 10Ls off the good pace along the fence, lack room 250M, no turn of foot.
Pressed forward, took rail, led by 2Ls at good pace, hung on until 200M emptied.
Bumped start, at rear, never improved.

Began well, racing along rail inside leading pack before easing into box seat 1300m. Came off fence 500m, got clear run when field fanned out 400m, forged to the front 150m and held off late challenge.
Jumped with field, allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling three-back along fence. Stayed on rail turning for home but badly held for run until 300m. Finished strongly to just fail.
Pressed forward from awkward draw racing four-wide to 1300m before settling outside leader. Strode to the front on straightening, joined 200m out, unable match first two closing stages.
No early pace, shifted across from wide draw to settle along rail at rear. Shuffled back to last entering straight, lay in but finished off strongly to be nearest at the finish.
Settled at rear in one-off position. Switched wide 500m turning for home and rolled forward to within 1L of leader at 200m before running out of gas. One-paced final.
Ridden along early settling in one-off position three-back from leader. Lost position around turn and blocked for run top of straight. Made late ground after getting clear 300m.
Began well, motoring gradually to take clear lead passing 1200m. Tended to hang out at turn but kept lead till straight before weakening gradually.
Raced with leading pack before easing one-back, one-off passing 1200m. Taken a little wide into straight but only one-paced final stages.
No speed, settling last despite being ridden along. Started forward move passing 600m, swooping around field to be 3L from leader entering straight. Tired quickly. Rider reported did not stretch out.
Sent to the front from draw 1, led uncontested, edged away from pursers mid-straight, had enough in hand to fend off 2nd late stages.
Sat reserved behind midfield, well covered in a 2-wide position, responded positively inside 300M, got up for 2nd 80M and was closest to winner at the line.
Behind midfield, unable to slot in from 13 and was strung out in the 4-path making the first turn, no cover to straight, ran on well enough to take 3rd despite covering more ground than rivals.
Never far off but unable to tuck in and raced primarily in the 3-path without cover, kept up the pursuit in straight before flattening out 100M. (Blood in trachea / Lame next day.)
Settled down along the rails 4Ls behind leader, angled out into clear 300M and stayed on moderately.
Settled along the rails near the rear, travelled strongly in the race, held up and unable to improve position until 350M, closed off well between runners.
Began awkwardly, eased to the rear before first turn, 7-8Ls off the pace middle stages, still last 300M and not clearest of runs mid-straight, kicked home belatedly showing the best stride late.
Chased leader along the 2-path from the start, pushed along 500M but offered limited response, swamped by rivals final 150M.
Stayed within striking distance, taken keen hold, came out 3-wide in pursuit from 800M, kept up the chase on winner in straight and held 2nd to 100M, no extra late stages.
Reserved near the rear 5-6Ls behind leader, was primarily 3-wide throughout the race, pushed along top of the bend, stayed on mildly down outside, not reaching leaders.
Towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, remained patiently handled until top of the straight, gave limited response only and never a threat to leaders.
Fractious in stalls, jumped awkwardly and lost significant amount of ground, recovered along the fence to race within range of the leaders to top of the straight before fading away 250M.
Began awkwardly, settled down 4Ls back in midfield but no closer than 3-wide throughout, not picked up when asked for effort entering straight.
Slow to begin, raced fiercely early stages, held up behind cover 2-wide in midfield, under pressure nearing home straight, had little left by 200M and weakened away.
Out quickly but eased, settling midfield in one-off position. Began forward move 700m racing three-wide into straight. Pushed through gap 350m, hit front 180m, pulled clear.

Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling last along fence. Made good progress around turn, found spilt between horses top of straight and ran on strongly till steadied 100m and shifted out.
Not much early speed, racing behind midfield in one-off position. Lost position around turn, taken wide into straight, ran on steadily to snatch third placing.
Began well, leading field to 1200m before easing back between first two. Urged forward soon after straightening, joined 300m out but kept on well till swamped final 100m.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing five wide to 1000m before sitting three-wide outside leader around turn. Joint leader to 200m before running out of steam and tiring.
No early pace, gradually drifting to fence three back from leader. Improved position around turn, took inside track in straight but held for clear run till 200m. Kept on fairly.
Began only fairly but quickly made up ground along rail to snatch box seat before turn. Held for run until passing 200m when boxed on one-paced despite being hard ridden.
Began well but not pressured, easing three-back, one-off. Took turn a little wide but kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
No speed, racing between horses at rear. Lost position around turn and plodded on one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling close to fence towards the rear. no clear run on entering straight but only one-paced when clear.
Aggressively ridden early to stay with pacemakers but wide. Failed to settle and hung out turn losing ground. Bumped 400m and weakened gradually. Performance deemed unacceptable.

Began well, holding position one-back, one-off to 700m when racing on heels and shifted wide. Put under pressure soon after straightening but weakened. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea. Unacceptable performance.
Began well, racing with leading pack before taking lead passing 1200m. Put under pressure by outside horse but led till 400m when collared. Weakened quickly. Stewards ruled performance unacceptable.
No speed, settling at rear but wide. Clear last entering turn. Never competitive.
Began well, and pushed forward to sit just behind leader, on his outside. In the gun run at the top of the straight and was pushed out from 300m Ran on strongly, and was never challenged late.
Slightly awkward away, and allowed to move forward to sit in a handy position 3 wide with cover. On terms with the winner at 250m, but didn't have the same kick. Weakening late when holding 2nd.
Began OK, but dropped back to sit towards the rear of the field early. Came 2nd widest in straight, and was finishing very strongly to overtake the majority of the field in the last 300m for 3rd.
Began well, but not used up early to sit midfield on the fence. Came out for a run at 250m, and ran on OK when given room late.
Came out of the gate slightly awkwardly, then pushed out early to lead. Held rails run, but looked 1 paced in the straight, and never responded to rider, and weakened late.
Began OK out of the wide gate, and dropped back early to sit 3 wide at the rear of the main group. Came widest on turn, and ran on OK in the dying stages, without ever threatening.
Began OK, and settled in a handy position behind the leaders on the fence. 1 paced in straight, and never ran on. Jockey reported abnormal breathing noise.
Began only fairly, and dropped back to sit at the rear of the main group. Made up some ground in the concluding stages, but was never going to be a threat.

Began OK, but was stuck 4 wide early looking to settle, and was bumped and unbalanced at the 900m, before eventually finding a handy position. In a prominent position on the turn, but was tired in the straight and never ran on.
Began OK, and found a position midfield on the rail. Raced fierce and off heels mid race. Faded from turn, and never in it.
Only fairly away, and found a position just worse than midfield 4 wide. Shifted out, bumped heavily and unbalanced at 900m. Race was over by turn, and faded out.
Began very awkwardly, missed the start and eventually settled in last place after being pushed up to sit with the main group. Used up early, and didn't have much left in the tank late.
Began OK, and taken forward to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence just behind leading pair. Faded from turn, and dropped out.
Began OK, before settling just worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Faded badly from turn and tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, positioned nicely in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Nicely away, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 3rd, similar position to turn, kept on well in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in 4th, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest gate, difficult to settle after 1000M, raced wide with no cover thereafter, 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, stayed on evenly to wire.
No early speed, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, angled out after turning in, made some progress to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, crowded near 750M, 6 lengths back near 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, bumped shortly after the start, raced 3-4 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, emptied final 100M.
Away with them, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, steadied near 1000M, raced 7 lengths back at tail, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off.
Jumped with them, showed no early speed, raced 6-7 lengths back at rear, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Jumped smartly and sent forward to box seat behind leaders, pushed along home turn and gradually wore down leader in straight.
Pushed along early to hold rail and lead, urged to quicken home turn and establish a break, overhauled final 100m.
No early pace, finished strongly to make up good ground in straight.
Settled midfield, kept to inside in straight and fought on gamely to the finish.
Pushed along early but caught wide at 1200m, sent forward to sit outside leader at 700m, tried to challenge in straight, weakened final 100m.
Taken back from wide gate at start, made up steady ground in straight.
Fast out and settled on pace, under pressure home turn and gradually gave ground in straight.
Taken back from wide gate at start, hard ridden near 500m, one paced in straight.
Crowded at start and taken back, wide without cover from 700m, weakened in straight.
Commenced awkwardly, settled on pace, drifted back to midfield near 600m and one paced thereafter.
Settled worse than midfield, raced keenly near 1100m, did not run on in straight.
Settled midfield and gave ground in straight.
Eased back, travelled 13Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover mid stages, improved gradually 900M, ran on strongly to score by a nose.
Sent forward to follow the leader along the fence, switched to 2 wide 800M, kept on strongly until final stride beaten by the winner.
Taken back to rear, travelled 14Ls behind the leader on the fence mid stages, improved steadily when the pace slackened 900M, peeled wide turning in, stormed home for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 11Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover mid stages, improved steadily when the pace slackened 900M, ran on nicely for 4th.
Settled worse than midfield about 12Ls behind the leader along the fence mid stages, improved steadily when the pace slackened 900M, ran on well.
Raced midfield, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence mid stages, improved steadily when the pace slackened 900M, made ground steadily.
Prominent, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence in 4th position mid stages, improved steadily when the pace slackened 900M, kept on fairly in straight.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L, soon weakened after straightening.
Travelled worse than midfield about 10Ls behind the leader on the fence mid stages, improved steadily when the pace slackened 900M, failed to make any impression in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover mid stages, under pressure 700M, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.

Raced midfield, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover mid stages, improved gradually when the pace slackened 900M, dropped off rounding the Home Turn. (Questioned for disappointing performance, blood in trachea)
Bumped start, rolled forward, settling one-off, one-back. Switched wide 350m to make run, joined leader 150m, pulled clear final stages.
Bumped start, pressed forward to lead 1300m. Set good sections and still clear with 200m to go. Tired final stages but held for second.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling three-back, one-off. Switched wide on entering straight and ran strongly to just miss the quinella.
Used inside draw to hold fence three-back from leader on settling. Took closer order around turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily to just miss a placing.
Began well but not much speed, settling midfield in one-off position. Switched out top of straight to make run and finished off nicely down centre-track.
Began only fairly, settling at rear close to fence. Popped off fence around turn, taken wider in straight and ran home steadily though reluctant to shift into clear running 100m.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw, settling at rear in a one-off position. Left racing wide without cover from 800m. Boxed on gamely down centre-track final 300m.
Bumped start but quickly into stride, leading field to 1400m before slipping into box seat. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring. Rider reported saddle shifted back at top of straight.
Not much speed, settling along rail behind midfield. Made up some ground around turn, switched out in straight to find clear running but only one-paced.

Hard ridden from start but slow to muster and trapped wide without cover in midfield around first turn. Allowed to stride forward from 1000m to race outside lead from 800m to straight before tiring gradually.
Not pushed, striding out at own pace four back from leader along rail. Kept on steadily early in straight before tiring from 200m.
Began fairly but failed to stretch out and soon last. Trailed field thereafter.
Began well but not pushed and allowed to hold rail inside leader. Inched forward along rail around turn to hit the front on straightening. Kept finding under heavy pressure for narrow win.

Pressed forward to lead on settling but unable to cross to rail and held in one-off position. Started to hang out from 1000m, hung badly 600m and again 300m. Kept on well to hold second, Racing manners unacceptable.

Pressed forward from awkward draw, racing wide till finding cover three-back, one-off at 1000m. Closed in top of straight and boxed on gamely to the line without being able to narrow gap on first two.
Tightened after start, pressed forward, settling three-back from leader. Not asked for effort until straightening for home when switched out and finished off strongly to just miss a placing.
Began well, ridden to hold forward position 2-back from leader along rail. Stayed on rail around turn, got inside run in straight and kept on gamely without narrowing gap to leader.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing three-wide without cover outside leader. Covered extra ground turn but kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden to hold position one-back, one-off. Lost position turn, taken wide in straight and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw but still away from fence at the rear. Switched wide entering straight but only one-paced when checked 200m.
Crowded out start and last on settling. Last into straight, took rails run and ran past tired runners close home.
No early speed, settling in one-off position behind midfield. Had open running on entering straight but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling at rear in a one-off position. Put under pressure entering straight got no response.
Began awkwardly, shifted out abruptly and lost ground, dropping to rear but away from fence. Continued to race wide at the rear and never competitive.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, illustrated strong finishing efforts 250M and scored.
Eased to rear early, however trapped very wide, allowed to improve 900M, sat 2.5Ls off the slow pace 3 wide, closed off well 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, took rail, checked early, 8Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M, creditable debut performance.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leaders 2 wide, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, soon eased back for cover, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leaders 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leaders on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Prominent early but checked, sat midfield, 3Ls off the leaders along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened in straight.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling three-back, one-off. Shaken up turning for home, rolled forward to hit front 150m before pulling clear.
Quickly into stride, led on settling before easing into box seat behind leader 1300m. Got clear run when field fanned out 350m, battled on gamely to lead momentarily 150m before swamped close home.
Fast out, raced with pace to first turn before easing one-off, one-back. Urged forward turning for home, hit front on straightening, joined up from 150m, weakened final strides.
Slow from the gates, ridden along to grab rail position four back from leader. Switched wide on straightening and finished off strongly to just miss a placing.
Pressed forward from awkward draw to lead passing 1300m and then dropped anchor, setting slow sections. Caught 350m but kept battling to 200m before running on empty.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw and last on settling. Switch out and made ground around turn, taken wider in straight but only one-paced under pressure final 200m.
Bumped and unbalanced start, then raced keenly in one-off position behind midfield around first turn. Switched wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden to hold forward position 3L from leader but three-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, wide into straight, boxed on one-paced.
No early speed, checked 1400m dropping to rear along fence. Shuffled back to last entering straight turning one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw but unable to cross to rail and held wide at rear. Allowed to roll forward around turn to within 3L of leader before turning one-paced.
Began only fairly and then bumped and unbalanced but recovered quickly along rail to settle 3-back from leader. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Outpaced and last on settling, before switched out entering first turn and making up some ground, Shuffled back to last final turn and found nothing in straight.
Began well form draw 1, settled 3Ls back in 5th, pushed along 500M, closed relentlessly under pressure to collar leader 50M, edged away at the finish.
Close up within 2Ls of leader, advanced to 2nd 400M, continued on well to lead passing 150M, but was unable to hold off winner over final 50M.
With leaders early then restrained to sit in 4th, kept on steadily over final 300M but well held by first two.
Unhurried early stages, settled down behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, finished willingly for 4th.
Strolled forward to take command from 800M and set good pace to straight, headed 130M, no extra and faded towards the finish.
Reserved behind midfield, saved ground along the inner, driven along and switched wide 500M, no threat to leaders despite making some ground down the outside.
Sent forward, led from 1000 to near 800M, failed to kick on inside 200M.
Towards the rear 6Ls behind leader, had little offering turning home, remained one paced to the line.
Bounded in the air on jumping, settled down midfield, blundered 600M when hampered by a rival, failed to fire on straightening.
Eased back after the start, caught 3-wide no cover for most of the race, outpaced 450M, soon beaten.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, in last 8-9Ls off the pace, found disappointingly little inside 300M, never involved.
Restrained after the start, placed near rear and difficult to settle from 900M, had plenty to do turning home, gave no response and eased when no chance.
