Away with them, positioned a length behind the leader in 4th, easy run to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently in 2nd, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, headed final 100M, stayed in 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 to 3 lengths back in midfield, 2 wide on turn, made some progress in straight to get 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, difficult to settle near 900M, positioned 2 wide in 5th throughout, finished off evenly in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, angled out early in straight and made some progress to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead until near 600M, peaked early in straight and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 11, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover throughout, finished off only one-paced in straight when hard run took effect.
Bumped start, positioned 6 lengths back on rail at rear, there to turn, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Slowly away, raced 8 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, failed to close off.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back in midfield, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Jumped well and settled behind leaders, in need of clear running on straightening, fought hard entire straight to get up on line.
Settled towards rear, commenced to improve home turn, challenged strongly 300m, hit lead 200m but faded late to go down narrowly.
Jumped smartly and sent forward to settle on speed, quickened nicely at 400m to take lead, fought on strongly final 200m to go down narrowly.
Settled forward of midfield, kept to rail in straight, unable to quicken but fought all the way to line.
Crowded at start and settled towards rear, steadied off heels at 350m and worked home strongly.
Crowded at start and settled towards rear, held up early part of straight, commenced to make ground passing 300m, crowded at 250m, finished off nicely.
Settled behind leaders, unable to quicken on straightening, hampered passing 250m and one paced to the line.
Slow to begin and crowded shortly after, settle at rear, commenced to improve passing 500m, bumped and unbalanced when laying in near 250m.
Jumped smartly, sent forward but caught wide without cover, under pressure on straightening and gradually weakened out of it.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve home turn, bumped and unbalanced near 400m, lay out near 250m and again became unbalanced when bumped having to be straightened.
Jumped awkwardly, steadied and lost ground near 500m, hampered having to be steadied near 250m when searching for clear running.
Raced in midfield position wide without cover, under pressure on straightening, bumped and unbalanced at 350, crowded and unbalanced near 250m.
Slow to begin and settled towards rear, travelled keenly passing 800m, did not run on in straight.
Fast out and sent forward to lead, immediately under pressure on straightening and quickly gave ground.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the slow pace, ran on nicely to score by 3/4L.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, enjoyed the slow tempo, kept on strongly to get 2nd.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L, hung on well until final 80M headed for 3rd.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow pace, kept on steadily to the line for 4th.
Eased back at start, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow tempo, ran on steadily in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow sectionals, peeled widest turning in, made some ground in straight.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace to the line.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Failed to muster pace, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Camped handy, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Jumped slowly, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked competitive.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Quickly into stride, grabbing one-back, one-off spot on settling. Urged forward but wide entering straight and gradually overhauled leader to win on the line.
Driven forward to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1800m. Set steady sections, kicked 2L clear entering straight, kept finding under pressure only to be run down on last stride.
Got off fairly but over-raced, got close to heels and unable to improve, settling at rear. Still well back entering straight, but motored home strongly final 200m to just fail.
Began well, using inside draw to hold box seat. Stayed on rail throughout and kept on well in the straight without threatening leader.
Slow into stride, recovered and made ground quickly along fence three back from leader. Switched out entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at the finish.
Jumped with field, taken to fence, settling four-back from leader. Switched out around turn and ran on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly and then steadied and shifted across behind horses, settling last in one-off position. Trailed field around final turn but ran on fairly in the straight.
Allowed to stroll forward at own pace from outside draw, settling behind midfield but away from fence. Switched out on entering straight to make run but only one-paced.
Bounded in air as gate opened and lost ground. Ridden forward but checked 1700m. Crowded out 1400m when trying to get nearer fence. Taken wide entering straight but found little under pressure.

Began well, making use of good draw to settle three-back, one-off. Travelled well to turn when put under pressure without responding. Not tested latter stages of race. Jockey reported not comfortable in action.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, settling outside hind-quarters of leader. Stayed in that position to straight but when asked for an effort 400m started to shorten stride and faded.
Outpaced, taken to rail, settling in last pair. Failed to quicken at any stage and never competitive.

Pushed forward from an outside draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1200m and setting slow early sections. Kicked 2L clear entering straight and then pulled further away before being eased down close to line.

Hard ridden from wide draw to go forward, sitting half a length behind leader to and around turn. Caught flat-footed when leader kicked 400m but picked up the bit and gave chase though unable to close gap.
Pressed forward from inside draw to hold rail three back from leader. Switched wide on entering straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Jumped with field but not pushed, racing between horses in midfield. Not much room early in straight but kept on steadily to be closest at the finish.
Ridden to hold midfield position though kept two or three wide mostly. Taken very wide in straight to make challenge picking up momentum in final 200m.
Urged forward from inside draw to hold box seat on settling. Stayed on fence from start to finish but never able to get closer. One-paced.
Began only fairly, ridden aggressively but failed to muster, dropping to rear but kept three wide. Raced fiercely going into final turn, still well back entering straight, ran on fairly final 200m.
Pushed forward from start, racing between horses till settling two-back, one-off. Urged forward entering straight but failed to respond, turning one-paced.
Restrained early, taken in behind horses but still kept wide at the rear. Switched wide entering straight but found little under pressure and plodded to the line.
Ridden along from an outside draw, racing three wide behind midfield mostly. Taken wider entering straight but failed to respond to hard riding.
Began fairly, ridden to find cover but unable get closer than four-wide back stretch. Lay out around turn and gave ground in straight.
Slow into stride, dropping to rear along fence. Made forward mover turning for home but one-paced in straight and never competitive.
Restrained, shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Never competitive. Found to have substantial blood in trachea.
Pressed forward, racing three-wide without cover outside leading pair to turn. Lost position entering straight and weakened gradually.
Eased back, 8.5Ls off the leader on the fence, favoured by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, 8.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M, hung in badly 250M.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, led by 3Ls at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Bumped start, 10Ls off the leader on the rails, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased to rear, 10Ls off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the fast sectionals, made steady ground 250M.
At rear, 10Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made some late ground 200M.
Midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast sectionals, never improved.
Pushed forward, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, hung out 300M whilst weakening.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 8.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
In front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, checked 300M and weakened.
Behind midfield, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, out of fuel 400M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made minor ground 350M, checked 200M, emptied.
3Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the fast pace, reduced quickly 300M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast tempo, but dropped off rapidly 500M.

Pressed forward from wide draw to settle one-off, one-back before turn. Rolled forward in straightening, hit front 200m, shifted in abruptly 100m forcing rider to stop riding but had enough in hand to hold on to win.
Began only fairly, ridden to make up ground settling along fence four-back from leader. No clear run top of the straight, switched out and finished off strongly. Found to be wounded left hind leg.
Ridden along from wide draw, racing three-wide abut 3L from leader. Covered extra ground turn while improving position, taken wider in straight and ran on solidly.
Began well, allowed to stride forward at own pace settling along fence three back from leader. Closed in around turn but blocked for run early in straight. Ran on steadily final 200m.
Quickly into stride, sharing early pace before taking clear lead passing 1200m. Set good sections, tried to kick clear entering straight, collared 200m but kept on well till swamped final stages.
Hard ridden from wide draw to get forward position, settling outside leader before and around turn. Put under pressure passing 300m and gave ground gradually final 200m.
Began only fairly, ridden but failed to muster, settling in last pair. Made some progress around turn and kept on fairly in straight.
Pushed early to hold forward position, settling in box seat. Allowed to relax around turn, shaken up top of the straight and kept on fairly till tiring final 150m.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners but unable to get to rail and held 3-wide behind midfield. Wide around turn and only one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Outpaced, settling at rear away from fence. Made some progress early in straight but never competitive.
Ridden along between horses in midfield early. Tried to improve around turn but got close to heels 500m and dropped back. One-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position settling 2.5L from leader in one-off position. Started to give ground on entering straight and fell back gradually.
Slow into stride, settling in last pair but away from rail. Shuffled back to clear last around turn and never competitive.
Up with early leaders, crossed to lead 950M without being pushed, led slowly and uncontested mid-race, sprinted home well and had enough in hand to hold off pursuers.
Never far off 2.5Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, sprinted home well from 350M, chased winner all the way to line, held by diminishing neck.
Settled down near the rear 3-4Ls off leader, shifted out into clear passing 300M, responded well when asked, nearest line.
Held up near the rear 7th of 9 in a slowly run race, stayed on well enough final 400M under top weight, got up for 4th near finish.
Within striking distance always, tracked pace in 2nd making the turn, kept on steadily early straight, lost 2nd 150M, no threat to leaders thereafter.

Tracked leaders early stages, shuffled back a bit making the turn but remained in touch, brief effort early straight to go 3rd, failed to kick on final 200M. (Jockey said tempo of the race did not suit.)
Led early stages, restrained to track leaders in 3rd, had every chance turning home, kept on same speed, faded final stages. (Blood in trachea.)
Eased to the rear about 5-6Ls back in a slowly run race, ran on same pace with main rivals over final 400M, couldn't make any real progress.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, travelled in rear pair 5-6Ls behind, over-raced in early and middle stages, not picked up pace inside 400M, left behind mid-straight.

Began awkwardly and bumped, recovered to race with leading pack before slipping back to behind midfield 600m, came off outer fence 350m to take split between horses and finished strongly to win on the line.
Began well, quickly moving towards outer fence about 2L from leading duo. Began forward move from 350m, hit front 150m, run down on the line.

Aggressively ridden from inside draw to stay with leading pack while edging towards outer fence, settling 2.5L from leader. Urged forward passing 300m and kept on well to the line but unable match first two.
Began fairly, ridden along down centre track while edging forward gradually to 400m when picked up momentum and motored home strongly to just miss a placing.
Jumped with field and quickly taken to outer fence, settling one-away about 3L from leader. Switched out passing 400m and made ground gradually to be closest at the finish.
Quickly into stride, sharing early lead before slipping 3L back along outer fence. Put under pressure from 350m and made ground gradually without looking dangerous.
Jumped well and shared early pace before taking clear lead entering course proper. Joined up front passing 150m but kept on well till running on empty final 50m.
Crowded out and lost ground start, hard ridden to stay at midfield one-away from outer fence. Urged forward from 350m but hampered 150m when finishing nicely.
Outpaced early, settling toward rear close to outer fence. Put under pressure passing 400m and kept on fairly to the line.
Began OK, hard ridden early but failed to muster, settling towards rear along outer fence. Well back passing 400m before running on fairly final stages.
Began awkwardly and then crowded before picking up pace some 5L from leader. Kept on fairly till passing 200m before tiring.
Jumped with field then taken to outer fence, losing contact with main bunch and settling second last. Hard ridden from 500m but little response.
Quickly into stride but once in front started racing keenly. Under pressure from 500m and weakened quickly from 300m. Performance deemed unacceptable.
A little tardy from the gate, ridden but failed to muster and clear last from 800m. Never likely thereafter.

Crowded on jumping before settling worse than midfield, on the fence. Came wide on the turn, and asked the question from the 300m. Ran on strongly and had the race won at the 50m, before easing across the line.

Pushed forward from the widest gate to sit just behind leader. Lead from the turn, but never kicked clear. Overtaken for the lead by the fast finishing winner late, but plugged away and held on for 2nd.
OK away, before eventually settling midfield, 1 off the fence. Pushed from the turn. Battled on in the straight and was weakening late, but just held 3rd.
Began well and taken up to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Awkwardly placed on turn, and didn't have a clear run until the 300m. Battled on OK from the 250m, just missing 3rd late.
Began OK, before dropping back toward the rear of the field, 12L off the leader at the 800m. Was 2nd last at the 300m, but ran on impressively late to take 5th.
Began OK, but dropped back early to sit a conspicuous last 15 lengths off the leader. Ridden along before the turn, and came widest in the straight. Came on OK late, and passed a few stragglers late.
Only fairly away, then pushed forward to sit midfield on the rail. Lost momentum when steadied out of a run at 150m, and only finished off fairly after that.
Began OK, but didn't muster early and dropped back to sit towards the rear of the field. Asked the question from the top of straight but only ran on fairly, and did his best work in the last 100.
Began OK and eased forward, sitting just worse than midfield and over racing slightly. Came 2nd widest on turn, but didn't run on in the straight and faded late.
Began well, and taken forward to sit in a handy position, 3L off the leader on the fence. 1 paced in the straight, and never saw out the trip.
OK to begin, and taken forward to sit better than midfield, 1 off the fence. Pushed forward for a run on the turn, but found wanting from 300m, and faded back from 200m.
Began well, and elected to sit back worse than midfield 2-3 wide early. Never stretched out in the straight, and awkward on heels towards finish.
Broke quickest from the outside gate, and pushed forward to lead. Never kicked in straight, and faded out from 300m.
Crowded on jumping. Pushed forward and sat 3 wide, no cover for the first 500m before settling handy, 1 off the fence. Tried to go from turn, but didn't respond and weakened quickly from the 200m.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently, 3/4 length back in 2nd on turn, continued on willingly to the finish and fought off the late challenge to score.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 4 wide with some cover at rear initially, slightly improved thereafter, 3 wide with cover in midfield, finished off strongly in straight to get 2nd.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, difficult to settle near 1000M, there to turn, in traffic early in straight, angled out after 300M and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just missed 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back behind midfield, similar position on turning, angled out in straight and made good progress to make frame.
Away with them, raced 2 lengths or so back in midfield, saved ground to turn, no daylight early in straight, closed off evenly when in clear thereafter.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, steadied near 1250M, raced 4 lengths back on rail, awkwardly placed near 700M, no clear run in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 to 5 lengths back, still 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover throughout, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, difficult to settle near 800M, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail at rear, last on turn, made no progress in straight, never competitive.
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, set a moderate to slow tempo to turn, peaked after turning in, emptied final 200M, finished last.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear after straightening, won easily.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader in 4th, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Average to begin, awkwardly placed near 900M, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some progress in straight to get 3rd.
Fast into stride, raced prominently in 2nd, hampered near 700M, peaked turning in, kept on evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Bumped start, raced 2 lengths back in midfield, similar position to turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from barrier 11, raced 5 lengths back at tail, slightly improved on turn, angled out in straight and made minor progress.
Began well, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length behind the leader, same margin back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail at rear, last turning in, finished off one-paced.
Crowded out start, raced 4 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, travelled 4 wide and without cover throughout, emptied in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, positioned 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight, failed to close off, finished last.
Jumped well, pushed along early to share lead on rail, travelling strong home turn, kicked clear on straightening to hold off all challengers.
Slow out, quickly improved along rail midrace, angled out on straightening and finished off strongly once clear.
Bumped at start, unbalanced when bumped near 1000m, settled forward of midfield, improved nicely on home turn and tried hard in straight.
Taken back at start from wide gate and worked home steadily in straight.
Jumped smartly and sent forward to share the lead, unable to quicken on straightening and fought on one paced in the straight.
Jumped well, drifted back to worse than midfield to find cover, widest on straightening and finished off fairly.
Bumped at start and hampered shortly after, settled midfield, hampered on straightening and one paced thereafter.
Taken back at start from wide gate, crowded at 900m, checked when crowded at 500m and did not run on in straight.
Went forward but caught wide without cover, travelling okay home turn but quickly under pressure and weakened in straight.
Jumped smartly and allowed to settle behind leaders, pushed along at 600m to hold position, commenced to drop out of it on home turn.
Settled towards rear and remained there throughout.
Pushed along early to settle forward of midfield, tried to improve passing 500m, hard ridden home turn and weakened out of it in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover 1200M, despite the slow tempo, stormed home to score easily by 2Ls.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, kept on strongly until final 100M headed by the winner, hung on for 2nd.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, under pressure 550M, kept on one pace to the line for 3rd. (Lame right fore after racing)
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, ran on steadily for 4th.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, despite the slow pace, under pressure 550M, kept on only fairly to the line.
Eased back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence 1200M, harmed by the slow tempo, peeled wide turning in, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence 1200M, hampered by the slow tempo, made no impression in straight. (Lame Left fore after racing)
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover 1200M, not suited by the slow tempo, under pressure 700M, flattened soon after straightening.
Hard ridden from inside draw to lead on settling. Kept up strong pace to straight, kicked clear passing 300m and kept finding when challenged final 100m.
Began well, using inside draw to grab box seat on settling. Took closer order around turn, kept on strongly in straight but unable catch winner.
Quickly into stride, racing outside leading pair to 750m before easing one-back, but held 3-wide without cover. Kept wide around turn, finished off strongly in straight but unable catch first two.
Had head up when gate opened and a little slow into stride. Made up ground along rail to be three-back around turn. Stayed on rail in straight and kept on gamely to the line.
Restrained after start, dropping to last before cutting to rail and making up ground around turn. Stayed on rail in straight, raced tightly to 200m before finishing off nicely.
Quickly out, racing alongside leader to and around turn. Kept on well early in the straight before giving ground final 150m.
Began awkwardly, then pressed forward to settle one-back, one-off around turn. Got close to heels 650m, unable to get run 300m and tightened, kept on fairly.
Crowded out at start, recovered and settled between horses behind midfield. Travelled OK to straight but failed to quicken when put under pressure. One-paced.
Began fairly, then crowded for room and shuffled four-back, one-off on settling. Lay out 500m, bumped and unbalanced 450m, wide into straight, one-paced.
Taken back from wide draw but unable to cross to rail and kept wide at the rear. Got close to heels and blundered 400m but never looked likely.
Bumped and unbalanced at start but pressed forward racing 3-wide to turn. Got shuffled back turning for home and one-paced in straight.
Taken back soon after start, racing towards rear before dropping to clear last around turn. Switched out in straight but failed to muster despite hard riding.
Began well, ridden along early before easing into slipstream of leader 1300m. Took inside run on straightening, hit front 100m out and kept on well to hold off late challenges.
Speared to the front from outside gate, cutting in to fence 1300m and then slowing pace. Shaken up top of straight, under strong challenge from 150m but kept fighting to the line.
Began awkwardly then crowded out, dropping to last into first turn. Stayed on rail back stretch, unable switch out final turn, took inside run in straight and finished strongly.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-back, one-off. Niggled at around home turn to hold position, a little wide into straight, boxed on gamely.
Hard ridden from wide draw, racing 4-wide before edging towards fence three-back, one-off. Swung very wide into straight but ran on strongly, doing best work final 100m.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, settling 1L behind leader but wide. Shaken up turning for home, kept pace with leading pack to 100m before tiring.
Began OK, not pushed and taken to fence four-back from leader. Switched out for clear run top of straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden to hold position early, settling three-back from leader along fence. Shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Outpaced early, slipping behind midfield in a one-off position. Switched out turning for home but only one-paced.
Restrained early, shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear but away from fence. Put under pressure turning for home but found nothing.
Bumped start, ridden to get forward position but found a few others faster and forced to race wide without cover at midfield. Put under pressure 300m but found nothing and faded.
No speed, dropping to rear, becoming clear last along back stretch. Trailed field thereafter. Never competitive.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M and scored.
Checked start, 5.5Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, however raced "flat" in straight.
Very awkward away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok in final stages.
Bumped start, at rear, 7Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Crowded out start, allowed to stride forward at own pace settling one-off, three back before turn. Took inside run on entering straight, burst through narrow split 200m, pulled clear for easy win.
Ridden to hold forward position but held wide about 3L from leader. Kept racing wide around turn, taken to centre track in straight and finished off strongly.
Began well, holding rail three back from leader. Took closer order around turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Quickly into stride, grabbing box seat along back stretch. Edged closer around turn, switched out approaching straight to make run, kept on steadily in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear in a one-off position. Still well back entering straight, unable to get a run until passing 200m when finished off strongly.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing with leading pack before settling one-back, one-off before turn. Taken wide entering straight and boxed on gamely without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, then raced in restricted room, dropping to rear along rail. Inconvenienced soon after straightening for home, blocked for run 200m, kept on fairly when clear.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw and last on settling. Still last entering straight, shifted out 300m when blocked for run, kept on fairly final stages.
Pressed forward, racing inside leader before taking over passing 1300m. Slowed pace down back stretch, tried to kick clear entering straight but caught 200m out and faded. Lame right front leg.
Ridden forward but unable find cover and kept three wide along back stretch behind midfield. Covered extra ground turn, very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Began OK but eased off heels 1600m and then kept wide without cover from 1300m about 2.5L behind leader. Made progress around turn, wide in straight, gave ground steadily final 200m.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead initially before allowing inside horse to roll forward. Stayed a length behind leader to straight before tiring and dropping back.
Positively ridden and cut over to the rails shortly after the start, allowed easy lead upfront, quickened up 400M, opened up 1.5L lead mid-straight, kept on well to deny fast finishing 2nd.
Began awkwardly, lost ground on jumping, recovered to race along the fence in midfield, 4.5Ls off leader (winner) 400M, kicked home belatedly showing the best stride late, nearest finish.
Broke well, settled one-out-one-back, kept up the pursuit on winner in straight but was always held, lost 2nd concluding stages.
Began only fairly, restrained in 5th 3Ls off the pace, lay in under pressure early straight, closed off steadily final 200M for modest 4th.
Chased leaders 2-wide, stayed within striking distance always, kept on evenly final 400M but was always held by leaders.
Taken across behind runners, sat reserved along the fence 5Ls off the pace, driven 450M and taken wide leaving the bend, stayed on well without threatening first few.
Began only fairly, took up position in the middle of the field, 3Ls off the pace 400M, ran on mildly for non-threatening 7th.
Began well, sat just off the pace, pushed along 450M, not quickened under pressure, weakened final 200M.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, travelled in rear pair 7Ls back, raced keenly under restraint early stages, made no real progress when driven 400M, never reached contention.
Away well enough, intended to lead but did not muster early pace despite ridden in early stages, ended up behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, not picked up entering straight.
Eased back to the rear, detached and 9Ls off the pace 400M, never involved.
Towards the rear, gave no response nearing top of straight, well beaten 200M, eased. (Jockey expressed concern regarding the action of his horse)

Travelled in rear of midfield near rails, switched in for rails run after straightening, ran on nicely to snatch victory final strides.
Jumped fairly, gradually took up running and obtained rails run after first 400 metres, led the field to straight kicking clear early on only to be collared close to home.
Well there and wide without cover far side, improved to race outside leader around the bend, unable to sustain effort after straightening, found nothing under pressure.
Began well, raced 2 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening. (Lost right front plate)
Moderate start from the one draw, settled in forward of midfield on rails, shifted off rails for a run entering straight but failed to quicken to challenge.
Well back, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight, did best work late.
Towards the rear, one-paced in straight.
Travelled keenly in midfield 3-wide, slightly wider turning in, found nothing in straight.
Never better than midfield on rails, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield one off the rails, soon faded after straightening.
Slow to muster, chased leaders to straight, found nothing under pressure.
Broke well from a wide gate, soon taken back towards the rear, moved slightly closer approaching home bend, found nothing in the run home.
Ridden along out wide just better than midfield, remained similar in 5th around the bend, yielded ground steadily after straightening.
Slowly away, raced 7 to 8 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Jumped smartly and went straight to the front, travelled strongly home turn, quickened nicely on straightening holding off all challengers.
Jumped well before easing back to obtain cover midfield, moved out on home turn to make run and finished strongly.
Eased back at start from wide gate to settle towards rear, kept to rail home turn, eased out for clear running at 300m and ran home nicely.
Pushed along from wide gate to settle on pace, tried to challenge on straightening, battle solidly to the line.
Taken back at the start to settle towards rear, ran home fairly.
Unable to muster early pace and settled worse than midfield, ran home fairly making up some late ground.
Crowded at start, settled worse than midfield, tightened at 750m, ran home fairly in straight.
Jumped fairly before improving along rail to settle on speed behind leader, one paced in straight.
Crowded at start, pushed along to settle on speed, challenged briefly on straightening before weakening in the run home.
Settled forward of midfield, weakened out of it final 200m.
Crowded on jumping, raced wide without cover in midfield position, weakened final 300m.
Settled at rear and remained there throughout.
Rolled forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on strongly and scored with plenty in hand.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 2nd, however, beaten by an impressive winner.
Hard ridden forward to obtain a prominent spot, kept on well for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually for 4th.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on only fairly, weakened over the concluding stages.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, weakened 300M.
Pushed forward to share the lead, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened soon after straightening.
At rear throughout, never looked competitive.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, eased down soon after straightening.
Broke ok, bustled to settle midfield 1 off with cover, nudged along 580m for 3 deep progress, driven 4 wide to challenge home turn, grinding run to lead close home.
Broke well & bustled to sit outside leader, shuffled 1 back 1 off 1000m, shifted 3 deep to challenge 450m, driven 380m & led 200m, all out & headed close home.
Sluggish start & rousted to sit 1 off with cover near rear, driven 400m, closed off to claim 3rd close home.
Smart start, dropped in to slot 1 off with cover behind midfield, 3 wide on turn & driven 500m, outpaced into stretch but closed off to just miss frame.
Speed to lead & rousted to snag rail, headed 1000m, regained lead 800m, shaken up 380m, kicked on but soon all out & headed 200m, tapered to wire.
Speed out wide, rolled 3 deep to press lead 1130m & posted 1 off to edge lead 1000m, headed 800m, driven 380m but one-paced, tapered closing stages.
Sharp break, settled 1 back on fence, niggled 2L back 950m, 1L 4th & hard-ridden into stretch, shifted 1 off & boxed on one pace.
Started ok, unable to slot & raced 3 wide no cover near rear, gained cover 850m, shifted wider & driven turning in, plugged on moderately.
Taken back to tail on inner, settled last pair 1 off, niggled 650m, shifted out final turn, driven 350m, plugged on one pace.
Broke ok to race on inner behind midfield, shaken up 350m, outpaced in run home.
Tardy start, raced rail midfield, advanced a spot 650m, bustled 500m & shifted out, faded in run home.
Taken back from widest gate, sat rail near tail, driven turning in, struggled in run & faded out.
Dropped in at start to race 3 wide with cover last pair, detached last & driven into stretch, never a factor.
Smart break, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, driven along 500m, soon beaten & weakened.
Started ok, settled 3 back on rail, driven 430m, shifted out 350m & bumped rival, quickened & led 120m, driven clear.
Fast break & prominent, soon snagged to 1 back 1 off, niggled 800m, ridden along 500m, shifted out 400m & ran on to lead 220m, headed 120m, no extra.
Crowded start, sat midfield 1 off with cover, progress impeded 350m to 250m & lost momentum, switched out & strong closer to snag 3rd.
Broke ok, raced 1 back on rail, shifted out turning in, switched deeper 350m & ridden, progress to vie for lead 220m, peaked 150m & tapered.
Taken behind from widest gate to 1 off near rear, shifted out home turn & ridden, ran on centre track for minor headway.
Slow start & ridden, settled rail back of midfield, edged out & shaken up 340m, kept on evenly.
Sharp start, raced 3rd 3 wide no cover, shaken up to lead 380m, soon all out & headed 220m, emptied & faded.
Broke well, raced close 2nd outside leader, ridden under pressure turning in, weakened out.
Taken back at break to rail near rear, shifted out final turn & driven, plugged on for moderate headway.
Dropped in to race last pair on outer, niggled & shifted out 500m, widest in stretch & stayed on without threatening.
Taken back at start to race last pair on inner, over-raced 1000m, switched wide in stretch & driven 400m, stayed on moderately.
Started well, caught 4 wide midfield until slotted 3 wide with cover 1000m, driven 4 wide into stretch, struggled in run home.
Smart start, ridden to lead & to rail 1400m, narrow lead & driven 420m, headed 380m, found nil & faded out.
Moderate start, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 700m, shifted out 550m & driven wide, struggled in run home.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, progressed steadily 600M, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M to score.
Eased at start, 6.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, steadily moved forward 600M, dashed well for 2nd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, made early move 600M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in front midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace on the rails, ran on well until 100M flattened.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace, run ended 150M.
Hard ridden early, maintained a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Pushed early but not muster, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, checked 1000M, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to rear, took rail, 7Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok in final stages.
Settled just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, gave ground 250M.
Pushed early, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, ran on well until 250M emptied.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by1L, clocked slow sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, checked 1200M, harmed by the slow pace, no progress, reduced in straight.
Pressed forward from outside draw before settling half a length behind and outside leader before turn. Shaken up top of straight, hit the front 300m and pulled clear.
Pushed forward after good start to hold the rail inside leading pack before slotting into box seat. Came off rail turning for home and kept on solidly to hold second.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling, cutting in to rail passing 900m. Overtaken passing 300m but battled on gamely to the line.
Ridden along early to hold forward position but kept three-wide without cover from 800m. Wide into straight but boxed on gamely without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, ridden to make up ground travelling three-wide without cover 5L from leader. Covered extra ground around turn but kept on fairly in straight.
Began OK, racing a little wide before settling one-back, one-off. Put under pressure from 500m but only one-paced in straight. Jockey reported may not have handled the wet track conditions.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Taken wide around turn, made up some ground before turning one-paced in straight.
Made use of inside draw to hold rail position three back from leader. Made progress around turn but found little when popped the question final 400m.
Jumped OK but steadied shortly after, settling 5L from leader in one-off position. Kept on fairly early in straight before tiring.
Jumped with field but raced ungenerously early stages and clear last at 800m. Made some progress around turn and early in straight before tiring.
Began fairly, ridden along between horses but wide. Got shuffled back around home turn and found nothing when asked in straight.
Began well, ridden along to hold forward position settling 3L behind leader. Lost position around turn and weakened further in straight.
Taken across from wide barrier, not hurried and held up at the rear 7Ls off the pace, fanned wide 600M, offered up a good kick down outside, led 150M and drew away.
Shifted across from wide barrier, patiently handled in 2nd last, moved up on the outside 600M, ran on well but no match with winner 150M, rallied on to edge out rival for 2nd.
From draw 11 raced no closer than 3-wide in mid-division throughout, swung wide into straight, picked up well to lead 250M, not pace of winner final stages, lost 2nd close home after a duel.
Unable to slot in for cover, raced keenly, 3-wide in pursuit of leaders home turn, kept on through final 400M despite tough trip, not pace of first few final stages.
Began awkwardly, held up behind midfield early stages, shuffled back further 800M, brief effort inside 300M down the inside, lacked the needed late response.
Off a bit slow, sat reserved towards the rear, in last place passing 400M, made some progress down outside without threatening.

In midfield early but difficult to settle when being restrained, strode forward to join leaders from 1100M but remained wide to straight, kept pace with the front runners until 200M then steadily backed away.
Close up early stages, fell back to midfield middle stages, ran on only fairly inside 400M and never reached a contending position.
Eased back after the jump, crossed to race along the fence 4L off the pace, taken keen hold middle stages, slowly picked up early straight, lacked room 250M but failed to kick on when clear.
Settled down midfield, 3Ls off the pace along the 3-path, driven along 550M, offered limited response early straight, no threat to leaders from 200M, eased towards the line.
Went straight to the lead but was soon taken on by rivals, asked to quicken 500M, headed 300M out then faded towards the finish, (Jockey questioned.)
Tracked leaders along the fence, kept on same pace entering straight, no threat from 250M.
Settled 2-wide in range of the leaders, came under coaxing 600M out, failed to pick up pace, soon beaten 300M.
Sent forward from wide barrier, vied for lead to straight, found nothing under pressure 400M, weakened rapidly.
Crowded out start but recovered quickly and ridden along to grab box seat. Sweated for a run early in straight but got clear passage 250m and gradually overhauled leader to win in final strides.
Jumped well to lead initially before being eased behind leading pair and kept well away from fence. Urged forward soon after straightening, looked winner 200m before being run down close to line.
Began OK, ridden along early but wide, settling 4L from leader. Wide around turn and into straight, bumped 300m but kept finding to be closest at the finish.
Jumped with field, ridden along wide to take lead passing 1000m and cutting to rail. Caught shortly after straightening but kept on gamely to the line.
Bumped start but pressed forward, settling two-back, one-off before turn. Kept on well early and still in contention 200m before tiring final stages.
Began OK but not much speed, settling close to rail behind midfield. Switched out and made progress around turn, still a chance passing 200m before running out of stamina.
Slow into stride, then taken across behind runners, settling last. Made good progress around turn, kept on fairly in straight before steadied 100m, turning one-paced.
Jumped with field, restrained and shifted across behind runners, settling close to rail behind midfield. Got shuffled back around turn and plodded on in straight.
Ridden along from an ousted draw but didn't muster and kept wide without cover towards the rear for most of the race. Never likely.
Bumped at start, then outpaced, dropped to rear. Shuffled back to last around turn and found little in straight under hard riding.
Crowded out at start and pressed forward between horses, settling behind midfield 5L from leader. Came under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Hard ridden from outside draw but took time to muster before settling outside leader at the turn. Started to give ground shortly before entering straight and finished tailed off.
Began OK and settled just forward of midfield on the rails. Came to the middle of the track for the best running in the straight and worked strongly, leading at the 150m. Weakening late, but held on.

OK away and taken forward to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence trailing the leader. Came wide on the turn, looking for better running, with the winner getting the jump inside. Chasing best late, but just missed.

Began well and taken forward from the wide barrier to sit forward of midfield, 3 wide no cover. Came wide on the turn looking for better going. Responded when asked the question at 200m and ran on solidly late.
Good start and taken up to sit just behind leader on the fence. Stuck closest to the fence in the straight, but never kicked and went to the line looking 1 paced.

Began fairly and eased forward to sit midfield, 3 wide with cover. Started to move wide in straight, before switching back in to avoid the traffic. Ran on fairly late, without ever threatening the first 3.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after jumping, and positioned midfield 3-4 wide. Wider on turn, and plugged away in the straight, picking up a few of the slower ones.
Dropped back from the jump to sit 2nd last, 8L off the leader by the 800m. Was the widest turning for home, but only plugged away fairly in the straight.
Began well, and pushed forward from the wide barrier to lead. Still had a share of the lead at the 200m, but faded from that point and dropped back.
Began OK and found a position midfield 1 off the fence. Came to the better part of the track in the straight, but never closed off late.
Jumped poorly and pushed forward early, eventually settling worse than midfield closest to rail. Travelled well until the turn, but never responded to pressure and ran to the line 1 paced late.
Began OK, and was being taken forward early before losing a run and settling worse than midfield 2-3 wide. Dropped back to last on turn, and showed no improvement in the run home.

Reared on jumping, struck head on the barriers and was very slow to begin. Sat at the tail of the field, 4-5 wide, before moving forward mid race. Never improved better than midfield, and never ran on in the straight.

Niggled along behind midfield, in last few before taking off under pressure at the 1000 metres, made swift progress down far side to chase leader round home bend, sustained effort down home straight to gain upper hand final strides.

Began moderately, well behind when given reminders on home bend the first time, made swift headway to join the leader rounding stables bend taking over passing the 1000 metres, however unable to sustain effort and caught close home.

Ridden early from a wide gate, just behind slow-paced leader early before shuffling 2L back in 5th on stables bend and in midfield in back straight, came under pressure rounding home bend and ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, settled just worse than midfield on rails, commenced move and wide entering straight, fought on steadily down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.

Ridden to a prominent position early, difficult to settle for slow pace and strode forward to find cover behind leaders stables bend,lost position when pace quickened 600m out, renewed effort to reach 3rd into straight, one-paced.

Travelled wide just better than midfield early stages, obtained cover in home straight the first time but difficult to settle to slow pace at times, slightly worse when pace quickened far side, found nothing in the run home.
Began moderately, settled in midfield on rails, gave ground from approaching home straight.
Jumped awkwardly, soon taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field most of way to straight, went past only well-beaten horses.
Jumped fairly to be midfield early, gradually dropped back far side to reach tail-end over 500 metres out, no further impression.

Ridden early, settled just off the pace in 4th or 5th on rails, remained similar before losing position passing the 600 metres, made no impression in the run home. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Broke well to lead early setting a sedate pace, joined around stables bend before headed turning into back straight, folded up quickly passing the 600 metres.
Settled midfield, ridden along to improve approaching 400m, widest on straightening, finished strongly final 200m for comfortable win.
Taken back from wide gate to settle towards rear, urged along passing 500m, kept to inside in straight and finished off nicely making up good ground.
Ridden along early to hold position forward of midfield, hard ridden near 600m, eased out to challenge on straightening finishing strongly final 200m.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, pushed along to settle on lead, travelled comfortably home turn, kicked clear on straightening, fought on gamely before overpowered final 100m.
Settled worse than midfield, pushed along to improve near 500m, kept to rail in straight and finished off one paced.
Sent forward at start to settle in handy position, hard ridden to improve home turn, one paced in straight.
Hampered at start, no early pace and settled at rear, commenced to improve at 600m, finished nicely in straight, held up final 100m.
Bumped at start, settled on pace, under pressure home turn and failed to run on in straight.
Crowded at start, settled midfield, failed to run on in straight.
Taken back at start from wide gate, ridden along near 400m to improve, one paced in straight.
Bumped at start, settled on pace, under pressure home turn, steadied at 100m when weakening out of it.
Ridden along early to go forward, wide without cover until 800m, gave ground quickly in straight.
Rolled forward to settle outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, kept on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow pace, dashed well for 3rd when clear 200M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader, despite the slow tempo and trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, ran on well in straight.
Pushed to midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, made minor ground over the concluding stages.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final 200M weakened.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, failed to make any impression in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suite by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Sent forward to take the lead along the fence at slow sectionals, flattened 250M.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, raced at rear throughout, never looked likely.
Speed to lead, to rail 1060m & handed up lead 900m to track 1 back, shifted out & driven into stretch, quickened to lead 230m, driven clear.
Sharp break, raced rail fore of midfield, shaken up final turn, hard-driven & switched out 200m, closed off to 2nd late, always held.
Fast break, settled handy 1 off with cover, niggled 750m & under pump 400m, fought on to go 3rd close home.
Sharp start, bustled to lead 1 off 1030m, 1L clear & to rail 900m, shaken up 300m, all out & headed 230m, tapered.
Good break, rolled wide no cover to sit 2nd outside leader at 850m, bustled 500m, hard-ridden turning in, boxed on evenly.
Taken back & caught 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, ridden 450m & wide into stretch, kept on evenly.
Taken back from widest gate to sit 2nd last 1 off, checked wide to avoid faller 850m, driven very wide home turn, stayed on for minor inroads centre track.
Smart start, sat 1 off with cover midfield, driven 400m, switched wide in stretch, one-paced in run.
Outpaced at break & bustled initially, settled rail behind midfield, heavily impeded by faller 850m & lost ground, shifted out & ridden 410m, found nil in run home.
Tardy start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, checked away from faller 850m & rousted to recover, settled rail, found nothing & faded final turn.
Missed break, soon bustled & detached at tail, veered wide to avoid faller 850m, tailed off.

Placing: FE
Comment: Started OK, raced rail midfield, broke down & fell 850m.
Tardy start, settled rail midfield, shifted out 400m & driven into stretch, grinding progress to lead close home.
Bustled to lead & snared rail, headed 1500m, shifted off fence to stalk outside leader, urged to challenge final turn, led 250m & kicked 1L clear, run down & headed close home.
Broke ok, raced rail & stalked leader 1.5L back in 3rd, driven 320m & drifted out, lacked toe but stayed on dourly to hold place in frame.
Smart start, raced handy but exposed until gained cover 1 off 1 back 1200m, niggled 650m, under pump 500m, 4 wide turning in, kept on doggedly until faded close home.
Missed break & niggled early, raced rail near rear, ridden 550m, shifted out 200m & dour progress without threatening.
Dropped behind from widest gate, raced rail last pair, shaken up 450m & edged 1 off for progress, hard-ridden into stretch, stayed on moderately.
Sharp break, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, ridden 550m & 5 wide progress into stretch, kept on evenly.
Broke well, tight for room mid-pack 1st turn, settled midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m & forced out, shifted wider into stretch, kept on one pace.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, outpaced & driven 550m, shuffled back, plugged on evenly to wire.
Broke well & rolled wide to lead 500m, clear & crossed to rail 1300m, shaken up turning in but all out & headed 250m, weakened out.
Taken back to sit last pair 1 off with cover, last & scrubbed 550m, wide into stretch, plodded on tamely.
Started well & rousted initially, 4 wide no cover 1st turn, slotted 3 deep with cover behind midfield 1250m, under pump 600m, struggled & faded out.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, made early move 500M to take advantages of the slow pace, dominated 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash in final stages.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
At back, checked early, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, raced keen, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Box seat, benefited by the soft sectionals, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, made ground quickly 600M, but just held ground in straight.
Took rail easily and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, however reduced steadily 250M.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, soon weakened 400M.
Hard ridden early to hold rail and grab box seat. Got open run on straightening, co-leader 100m, battled strongly final 100m to win on the line.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Set steady pace to straight, caught 100m but kept battling only to lose on the line.
Urged forward from inside draw, settling one-back, one-off along back stretch. Switched out on entering straight and ran home strongly.
Made use of inside draw to hold rail, three back from leader. Came off fence turning for home and kept on gamely in straight to be closest at the finish.
Bumped start, steadied, then taken across behind horses to hold rail position four back from leader. Still well back entering straight before picking up momentum and finishing off nicely.
Began fairly, steadied and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear but away from fence. Raced ungenerously back stretch, but picked up momentum final 200m.
Pressed forward but held three-wide early before settling in midfield in one-off position. Taken very wide on entering straight but kept on fairly without looking dangerous.
Hard ridden but wide early, getting to within 3L of leader back stretch. Covered extra ground and lost position around home turn. One-paced in straight. Lame left front leg.
Jumped well, pressed forward to hold second spot, 1L from leader. Looked a chance top of straight but ran out of stamina 200m and weakened. Lame right front leg.
Hard ridden early but slow to muster and kept wide early before being steadied and getting cover before turn. Lost position around turn and faded in straight.
Shifted out and bumped start, outpaced and soon last, gradually losing contact with field. Never competitive.
Settled just off the pace, had a smooth run to straight, closed nicely along the inside, wrestled the lead inside 100M and held on under drive.
Took up early running from draw 1, set slow fractions early stages, taken on by rival 900M, rallied well enough entering straight, just failed to hold off winner late stages.
Settled down in 5th, stayed within striking distance passing halfway, closed off willingly for 3rd beaten only a neck.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, loomed up 3-wide outside leaders home turn, vied for lead early straight, remained prominent to 100M then faltered in closing stages.
Held up behind midfield, 3-4Ls behind leader 400M, kept up his pursuit without ever posing a serious threat.
Slow to begin, guided to the fence, settled down 3-4Ls back in midfield, kept on steadily entering straight, no impression on first few. (Lost RF plate 1600M)
Took up a 3-wide position in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, stayed on moderately final 300M, not reached leaders.
Eased back from widest barrier, patiently handled, detached from the field early and middle stages, had 5Ls to make up turning home, made some progress when taken out into clear 200M.
Underwent a 3-wide pursuit on leaders, unable to slot in and covered extra ground, weakened 300M. (Lost RH plate 400m)
Soon guided to a position behind midfield, saved ground on inner and 5Ls off the pace throughout, had no offering final 300M, never a threat.
Taken across behind runners, not suited by the slow early pace, strode forward passing 1100M to race outside the lead, emptied 300M and backed away to last.
