Taken back from the widest gate to travel just behind midfield, shifted out for a run entering straight, responded well to take charge inside final 200 metres.
Given reminders in rear early, improving to midfield coming out of back straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Jumped fairly, niggling along but soon dropped behind midfield, given reminders on rails inside 900m, improved to forward of midfield along rails on home bend, sustained progress down inner of straight, did best work late.
Ridden along to hold 4th spot within 2L of pace, became 3-wide in 6th around home bend, failed to quicken under pressure after straightening.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, held inside run turning in, finished off race well inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, niggled along to hold prominent spot outside the leader, in similar position turning in, swamped for 2nd inside final 150 metres
Began fairly, dropped to rear of midfield before picking up along rails to be just off the pace into straight, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Awkward start losing ground, trailed the field to straight, fought on steadily past well beaten horses.

Began well from a wide gate, niggled along wide in close up position early, gradually dropped back to midfield and remained wide and without cover around the bend, became last into straight, went past well beaten horses.
Broke well from the one draw, driven along to assume lead on rails, broke over 1L clear early in straight but soon tiring.
Began moderately, ridden along in midfield, gained slightly closer to 5th just over 2L back around the bend, soon yielded ground in straight.
Niggled along out wide amongst leaders, remained 3-wide without cover rounding home bend, folded up quickly upon straightening.
Jumped smartly and sent straight to the front, quickened nicely at 300m and fought on strongly holding off all challengers.
Commenced awkwardly, steadied at 900m when settling on speed, challenged strongly at 400m and tried valiantly in the run to the line.
Ridden along early to settle on speed, asked for effort at 400m and battled gamely to the finish.
Jumped fairly, eased across behind runners to settle midfield on outside rail, ridden along passing 600m, picked up late and finished nicely final 100m.
Jumped smartly, hampered at 900m, improved nicely near 400m but unable to quicken when asked for effort, held position to the line.
Allowed to settle midfield, travelled nicely midrace but could only finish one paced in middle of track.
Jumped well and raced on pace in centre of track, quickly under pressure at 400m and gradually weakened out of it.
Began fairly, settled behind leaders, pushed along at 600m to hold position, unable to make ground final 400m.
Jumped well, crowded and checked at 900m and lost ground, ran home oaky final 300m.
Jumped awkwardly and settled towards rear, made up some ground in run to the line.
Jumped okay, bumped and raced tight near 900m, under pressure at 400m and weakened thereafter.
Fractious in gates, hampered and bumped near 900m, raced on pace, under pressure at 300m and gave ground quickly.
Jumped well and sent forward, niggle at near 700m, hung in badly and gave ground quickly, eased down final 150m.
Settled at rear and remained there throughout.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at very slow sectionals, ran on well to score comfortably.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at very slow tempo, fought on strongly until final furlong headed by the winner, hung on for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on nicely to get 3rd.
At last, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the very slow tempo, ran on strongly to the line.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the very slow pace, peeled wide turning in, dashed well in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the very slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, despite benefited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Pushed to midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the very slow tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the very slow sectionals, one paced home.
Midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the very slow pace, made an early move rounding the Home Turn, kept on one pace until final 250M weakened.
At rear, travelled 7.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the very slow sectionals, made no impression in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the very slow tempo, never ran on.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened soon after straightening.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Broke ok, rousted to lead on fence, driven under pressure 350m, fought off challengers to hold on at wire.
Sluggish break, rousted to 1 off with cover behind midfield, slid to rail near rear 800m, shaken up 400m & shifted 1 off, strong run to nick 2nd at wire, just failed.
Broke ok widest, soon rousted along & worked to sit midfield 3 wide no cover, driven 4 deep final turn, grinding run to 2nd 50m, back to 3rd at wire.
Smart start & bustled, settled back of midfield 1 off with cover, edged out final turn, driven 320m, stayed on for sound inroads.
Broke ok, sat 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 wide turning in, driven 360m, closed to share 2nd 150m but soon emptied & swamped late.
Tardy start, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven wide final turn, stayed on for minor late gains.
Fast break, posted outside leader no cover, driven 360m to press lead, duelled but held, emptied 200m & tapered out.
Slow start, raced rail mid rank, shifted out & hard ridden final turn, stayed on evenly.
Slow start, raced 1 off with cover near rear, shifted 3 wide 500m, lacked toe turning in, plugged on one pace.
Hustled to dispute early lead, caught 3 wide no cover & taken back to 5th, bustled 700m, 4 & 5 wide on turn, boxed on until faded final 200m & eased.
No pace from start, rousted but soon detached at tail, never a factor.
Broke well & prominent until settled 1 back on rail, bustled a touch 850m, ridden turning in, found nil & faded right out.
Moderate start, sat 1 off with cover back of midfield, forced 3 wide on turn, shifted deeper turning in & driven, quickened to lead 280m, drifted to stands rail, held on.
Broke ok, settled midfield 1 off with cover, 3 wide on turn, peeled 4 deep & shaken up 400m, quickened to 2nd 250m, held in run.
Tardy break, sat rail midfield, shifted 1 off 650m & shuffled back, shaken up 400m, stayed on gamely to claim 3rd.
Smart break, raced 4th 1 off with cover, driven to lead 360m, all out & headed 280m, tapered thereafter.
Taken back from wide gate, raced rail at tail, niggled throughout, shifted out 420m & driven, stayed on for solid inroads.
Broke ok, raced rail fore of midfield, edged out on turn, not clear run 400m, shaken up 350m, kept on evenly.
Dropped back from widest gate, sat 2nd last 1 off, driven 430m, stayed on for minor headway.
Tardy break, raced 1 off near rear, shifted wide & driven for progress 600m, widest into stretch, kept on one pace.
Taken back at start, sat rail near rear, advanced on inner 650m, shifted out in stretch & plugged on one pace.
Sharp start, soon led & crossed to rail, extended 3L clear, restrained & back to field 900m, 1L clear final turn, ridden 430m, headed 360m, faded.
Tardy break, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, minor 4-wide advance 800m, driven final turn, checked 420m, plodded on tamely.
Rousted wide to settle 2nd 1 off no cover, driven 430m, found nil & weakened early in stretch.
Sluggish start, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, pushed 4 wide on turn & hard-ridden 500m, forced even wider into stretch & found nil.
Speed to lead but soon headed & sat rail in 3rd , shifted 1 off 420m but not clear run, shuffled back & lost several lengths, found nil thereafter.
Took lead easily, hung on well to win.
Hard ridden forward, parked just off the leaders, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Pushed forward, settled in prominent spot, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leaders, illustrated strong finishing efforts 200M.
Checked start, hard ridden to gain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leaders, lack room 400M, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Eased to sit behind the front group, 2.5Ls off the leaders, just held ground in final stages.
Awkward away, 4.5Ls off the leaders, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4Ls off the leaders, dashed well 200M.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leaders, ran on fairly.
Settled just off the lead, reduced 200M.
Checked badly at start, 7Ls off the leaders, no dash.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, 6Ls off the leaders, no progress.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders, emptied 300M.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, dropped off 400M.
Began fairly, ridden to make up ground, settling in box seat 2L from leader. Blocked for run early in straight, found gap 200m out and powered through to win in final strides.
Pushed hard to lead passing 1250m and then steadied pace. Kicked clear on straightening for home, still well ahead 200m, run down final stages.
Outpaced early, settling at rear along rail. Held for clear running around turn, hampered shortly after entering straight, shifted in 150m to get run and finished strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Made up some ground around turn, switched wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, pressed forward racing three-wide but only 2L from leader. Kept wide but within striking distance to 200m when tightened, turning one-paced.

Fractious before start and sat in stall but passed fit. Jumped OK, ridden to hold fence three back from leader. Kept on steadily in straight. Found to have blood at left nostril, abrasions on right eye and lame right front leg.
First out but forced to race wide, dropping back to third before moving outside leader around turn. Kept on fairly in straight before tiring final stages.
Crowded out at start, dropping to rear but away from fence. Clear last around turn, taken wide in straight and ran on fairly.
Slow into stride, racing at rear before being switched three-wide and making up ground to within 4L of leader. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward from outside draw to race outside leader but proved difficult to settle. Shifted out turning for home and lost position, one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden from outside draw but slow to muster, racing wide without cover about 3L from leader. Boxed on gamely until 200m when tired. Found to have substantial blood in trachea.
No early speed, racing between horses at the rear. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position, one-away from fence but got shuffled back around turn and found nothing in straight when popped the question.
Began well, racing in midfield early before slipping back entering turn. Gave ground quickly in straight.
Never far off the pace, travelled strongly along the fence, loomed up behind leaders near top of straight, driven 300M and soon quickened to lead, lengthened away final 150M, comfortably.
Driven forward and crossed to the lead 900M, proved no match when confronted by winner inside 300M, kept on steadily to hold 2nd, nicely clear from pursuing rivals.
Just off the pace tracking along the 2-path, stayed on mildly to go 3rd near the line.
Sent forward from wide barrier, shared lead on outside 750M, remained prominent until 250M, faded to 4th closing stages.
Slightly slow away, in mid-division along the fence, raced ungenerously over the turn and held up for clear running until 300M but made no additional headway when clear.
Settled down in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, had cover along the 3-path, ran on steadily without threatening.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, sat reserved in last 6Ls off the pace, finished final 400M quickest, produced modest late impression closing stages.
Held up in mid-division, well covered, brief effort early straight, turned one pace final 200M.
In midfield early stages, shuffled back to 3rd last approaching home turn, held up for clear running early straight, failed to respond when ridden to chase leaders. (Muco)
Began well but soon restrained to midfield, raced keenly passing 800M and fell back to near the rear, was put to a serious drive inside 250M but couldn't pick up the pace.
Unable to get closer than 3-wide, left with no cover after 800M, gave limited response turning home, out of contention mid-straight. (Muco)
Patiently held up in 2nd last, driven 350M but came up empty.
Jumped with field, eased to rear while edging closer to fence. Began forward move 950m racing four-wide around turn. Picked up speed in straight to nail leader on the post.
Hard ridden early to stay in contention before moving forward 930m to race outside leader around the turn. Hit front 400m, challenged soon after but battled on, losing only in final strides.
Began fairly, eased back while edging closer to fence. Popped off fence 800m to take turn three-wide, switched wider in straight before finishing strongly down centre track.
Began awkwardly, shaken up, urged forward but wide to lead 1400m, crossing to fence. Overhauled shortly after straightening but boxed on gamely, losing a placing in final strides.
Pressed forward, racing in one-off position 2L behind leader back stretch. Got shuffled back around turn, blocked for run top of straight, angled out 350m to get clear and finished off nicely.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw but still held three-wide at the rear. Improved position racing wide around turn, got to within striking distance 200m, then one-paced.
Urged forward from wide draw, gradually improving position until joint leader turning for home, kept on early in straight before tuning one-paced final 200m.
Ridden along early to hold one-off position in midfield before being shuffled back around turn when racing tight inside horses. Switched wide in straight and boxed on fairly.
Jumped OK but over-raced and refused to settle, dropping back gradually until clear last entering straight. Taken wide and made up some late ground.
Pressed forward to hold box seat before being tightened and losing position around turn. No run entering straight, got split 300m but tightened again 150m, kept on well.
Outpaced early, dropping towards rear but kept wide. Urged forward 1000m racing wide around horse to within 3L of leader entering straight. Kept on fairly before eased final 150m.
Quickly into stride, holding rail and leading to 1400m before taking box seat. Got shuffled back before turn but kept on well along rail until flattened final 100m.
Pushed forward from outside draw to share early lead before being eased back to third 2L from leader. Wide entering straight and gave ground gradually.
Ridden along early but kept wide at rear before taking off from 1000m to share four-way lead turning for home. Spent force in straight.
Began well and taken forward to sit in a handy position on the rails. Took very little encouragement to kick from the 300m, and went to the line under a hold, with plenty left in the tank.

Began awkwardly, but taken forward to sit better than midfield on the rail. Crowded at the 400m. Came through the gap left by the winner when he kicked at 250m. Ran on strongly from there, grabbing 2nd on line.
Taken forward from the jump to lead, and held the rail for the trip. Asked to go when winner began to loom up at 250m, and ran on well. Peaked towards the finish, and just lost 2nd.
Began well and taken forward initially, before easing to find cover midfield 1 off the fence. Pushed forward to be well placed at the top of the straight, and ran on well, but fading late.
Fairly away, and settled worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Kept on steadily in the straight, improving in the last 200m.
Began well and not used up early, sitting midfield on the fence. Wider on the turn for a run and ran well in the straight, improving from the 200m.

Taken forward from the wide draw to sit 2nd, 1 off the fence on the leaders flank. Handily placed on the turn and asked the question early in the straight, but never responded and faded from the 200m.
Crowded on jumping, before sitting at the rear of the field 2-3 wide. Came 2nd widest round the turn and ran on OK, picking up a few of the slower ones, without threatening late.
Began fairly before sitting at the rear of the pack 3-4 wide. Eased back to sit last on the fence, before coming wider on the turn. Only plugged away in the straight.
Began well and taken forward to sit in a handy position 1 off, 1 back with cover. Lost his run at the 400m, but never ran on when given the chance, and eased across the line late.
Slightly awkward to begin and stuck 3-4 wide at the rear early. Under pressure around the turn, but never responded and faded late, beating a few easing up.
Began OK, settling at the rear of the field on the fence. Came wider on turn, but never in it and eased out late.
OK to begin, and taken to a position just behind midfield. Taken wider 1100m, and forced race wide. Never finished off, and well beaten in the straight. Unacceptable performance.
Began fairly, but couldn't settle into a position, and ended up worse than midfield, 4 wide without cover. Widest on the turn, and dropped out soon after.

Midfield early, gained closer despite interference about 800 metres out, just off the pace in 4th turning in, hung in a difficult ride early in straight, switched into the clear over 200m out, asserted authority close to home.
Pressed on from a wide draw to soon take up running on rails, held narrow lead most of way, came under pressure to maintain advantage after straightening only to be caught close home.
Began fairly from the one draw, travelling two back in 4th when carried backward coming out of back straight, remained not far off in midfield to straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, gradually improved to 2nd outside the leader disputing the lead into straight, unable to sustain effort and faded close to home.
Began well, settled just off the speed on rails, remained similar into straight, kept on without quickening under pressure.

Ridden but soon dropped to midfield, took closer order in 3rd coming out of back straight when 3-wide, remained similar around home bend but unable to sustain effort and faded under pressure in straight.
Jumped in rear, remained well behind to straight, kept on past well-beaten horses.
Taken back from the widest gate, remained wide throughout, gained slightly closer coming out of back straight, widest runner turning in, kept on past well-beaten horses.
Jumped moderately, worse than midfield on rails despite niggling along, hampered approaching home bend and stumbled dropping in last few, made no impression in the run home.
In rear on rails when hampered and shifted wide in the wake of interferences approaching home bend, remained in rear turning in and ran home one-paced.
Began moderately, travelling behind midfield when raced awkwardly and lost position approaching home bend, took slightly closer order around home bend but made no further impression in straight.
Pushed along to settle midfield, improved passing 800m to race behind leaders, challenged on straightening, took control at 300m and held off all.
Began fairly, settled at rear, travelled nicely at 600m, tried hard entire straight making good late ground.
Taken back from wide gate to settle at rear, widest on straightening and finished strongly.
Jumped well, got head up when steadied at 1100m, inconvenienced at 1000m, traveled nicely near 600m, ridden along to challenge home turn, brief chance at 300m but weakened final 150m.
Jumped well and settled on speed, held up near 350m, finished well final 250m once clear.
Taken back from wide gate to settle towards rear, pushed along home turn, made up some ground in straight.
Inconvenienced at start, settled midfield, impeded near 300m but had every chance thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear, checked passing 350m when in need of clear running, ran home steadily once balanced and clear.
Jumped well and sent forward to share lead, held together home turn, tried to quicken on straightening, overpowered at 300m and battled to the line.
Raced on pace wide and without cover, asked for effort and quickly under pressure on straightening, weakened from 300m.
Began awkwardly and settled at rear, one paced on straight.
Pushed along to settle on pace, bumped and unbalanced at 350m and gave ground quickly when steadied at 250m.
Settled on pace, raced keenly and steadied passing 1000m, under pressure home turn and the weakened in straight.
Midfield, travelled 1L behind the leader in a small field, enjoyed the slow tempo, ran on well to score comfortably.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on strongly until final 100M headed by the winner, hung on well for 2nd in a compact finish.
At rear, travelled 2Ls behind the leader in a small field, despite the slow sectionals, dashed well for 3rd in a compact finish.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, kept on steadily to get 4th in a compact finish.
Eased back to find a cover early, travelled 2Ls behind the leader in a small field, harmed by the slow pace, ran on steadily to the line in a compact finish.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at slow sectionals, kept on steadily until final stages weakened in a bunched finish.
Broke ok, rolled to lead 1660m & soon crossed to rail, headed 1400m & keen in close 2nd, led again 1000m, stretched 2L clear turning in, quickened away, tapered late, just held on.
Broke ok & bustled to slot 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shifted out & driven 450m, 5L down turning in, quickened to 2nd 250m, closed to wire, just failed.
Taken back at start, hampered 1st turn, aced rail back of midfield, advanced into final turn & shifted wide, driven unto stretch, closed to 3rd.
Slow start & rousted to race fore of midfield on rail, driven turning in, shifted 1 off, stayed on dourly to wire.
Broke ok, bustled a touch, raced 1 off with cover, ridden 500m, shifted out final turn, stayed on solidly.
Led at break, eased & headed 1660m, sat 1 back 1 off, ridden 600m, stayed on one pace.
Broke ok, raced 1 off with cover in midfield, driven under pressure 550m, forced very wide home turn, plodded on one pace.
Fast start, handy 3-wide 1st turn, rolled 1 off to edge lead 1400m, headed 1000m, 2L back & ridden 470m, emptied 300m, swamped & faded.
Broke well, raced 1 back on rail, under pump 560m, struggled in tepid run home.
Taken back at start, raced last pair on rail, niggled 1000m, ridden 600m, plodded on past beaten rivals.
Lacked pace at start, raced 1 off near tail, niggled 650m, plodded on weakly.
Missed break, sat rail behind midfield, progressed a spot on turn, ridden into stretch, found nil & faded tamely.
Dropped back at break, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Started ok, sat 1 off with cover near rear, under pump 620m, emptied turning in & eased.
Speedy break to press lead close 2nd 1 off, shaken up 400m, battled to lead 260m, gritty effort under pressure to just hold on.
Good break, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, 2L back & driven turning in, quickened 300m, gradually closed to wire but just failed.
Broke well & rousted to 3rd 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep 600m & advanced to lead 430m, all out & headed 260m, fought on but held, lost 2nd late.
Awkward start, raced midfield on rail, shifted out turning in, shaken up 400m, kept on under hard drive without threatening.
Broke well, dropped to midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 500m, kept on solidly without threatening & tapered final strides.
Taken back at break, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, hard-ridden into stretch, stayed on dourly.
Broke ok, raced1 back on rail, shifted out & driven 400m, kept on evenly.
Slow start, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, hard ridden into stretch, stayed on dourly.
Smart start, taken back & caught 3 wide no cover back of midfield, wide & driven turning in, plugged on evenly.
Taken back to race last trio 1 off, driven final turn, plugged on tamely.
Taken back & soon at tail, 3 wide 600m, driven 500m, kept on tepidly.
Outpaced initially, bustled along on rail behind midfield, shifted out & driven into stretch, struggled in run home.
Slow start, taken behind to rail last trio, hard-ridden turning in, found little in.
Fast start to lead, to rail 1200m, headed turning in, faded tamely.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly 400M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Settled in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M, run ended 150M.
Hard ridden early, hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, just held ground when clear.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, ran on ok in final stages.
Hard ridden forward, parked just off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 250M.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, held up 4-2, no progress when clear.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 400M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden early, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, flattened in straight.
Pressed forward, sat just off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5L, clocked fast sectionals, reduced quickly 300M.
Ridden to hold third early before settling one-back, one-off first turn. Dropped back 1250m when several back-markers took off. Got clear run from 400m, hit front 200m, edging clear final strides.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, crossing to rail 1750m and slowing pace. Shuffled back to 3rd 1100m but retook lead 400m. Battled strongly final 200m, losing in final strides.
Restrained and shifted across behind horses from wide draw but difficult to settle. Allowed to roll forward from 1250m to take lead at 1100m. Collared 400m but kept on well to hold minor placing.
Quickly into stride, sliding into box seat before first turn. Got shuffled back during mid-race moves 1100m, stayed on rail entering straight and ran on strongly to just miss a placing.
Began fairly, racing at rear till tightened near 1800m. Taken wide and allowed to roll forward circling field to one-back, one-off position around final turn. Kept on well till tiring final strides.

Began well, racing with leading pack to first turn before settling three-back, one-off. Allowed to roll forward three-wide passing 1100m, even wider entering straight but kept on well to be closest at finish.
Began well but kept wide before sliding forward to race outside leader passing 1650m. Shuffled back to fourth 1100m, cutting to rail and holding box seat. Kept on well in straight.
Began OK, allowed to stride forward but three-wide, gradually edging forward to race outside leader turning for home. Kept on well early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Bumped start, shaken up to hold rail, settling three-back from leader. Got shuffled back during mid-race moves 1100m, switched out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Began well but not pushed, settling four-back, one-off. Got tightened and lost position 1100m, one-paced in straight.
Began OK, restrained and taken across behind horses to rail at rear around first turn. Came off rail entering straight but only one-paced.
Began fairly, taken in but kept away from fence, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched three-wide around final turn to make challenge but only one-paced in straight.
Crowded out and bumped start, ridden but failed to muster, settling in midfield. Lost position back stretch when others moved forward and found little in straight when asked.
Jumped OK, restrained and taken across behind horses but difficult to settle and kept wide at rear. Never competitive.

Travelled strongly in midfield 4Ls off the slow early pace, advanced to a striking position passing 500M, quickened impressively to collar the leader 150M, drew away towards the line for 6th win on the surface. (Course record time)

Positioned in 4th 2-3Ls off leader in slowly run race, made an early move to challenge passing 600M, led 350M, rallied on when GUN PIT drew alongside, proved no match final stages but finished nicely clear from rest.
Reserved in midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the pace in a slowly run race, driven along 500M, lacked finishing pace of first two, stayed on to take non-threatening 3rd just before line.
Allowed an uncontested role in front, set slow fractions especially in 2nd quarter, pressed by rivals 600M, remained prominent until 150M then faded away, lost 3rd near line.
Closest to the leader for most of the way, helped by the slow pace in first half, moved to the front line 500M, outpaced by leaders 250M, kept on one pace final stages.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, driven near top of the straight but lacked acceleration of rivals, kept on same pace to finish.
Unable to slot in and raced in midfield 3-wide no cover throughout, moved closer inside 600M, failed to pick up on this first attempt over 1650M.
Not hurried, eased to a position behind midfield about 6Ls off the slow pace, kept to inside throughout, stayed on past weakening horses, no impression on leaders.
Settled down 3-wide behind mid-division and 5Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, kept on only fairly, never a threat to leaders.
Shuffled back to near the rear passing 1400M, over 7Ls off the pace in middle stages, had plenty to make up 400M, made no headway and never able to reach a contending position.
Fractious in stall, reared at the jump and lost about 3-4Ls, detached from the field until halfway, already beaten turning in.
Soon taken across from widest draw, held up 3rd last 6Ls off the pace, moved closer 600M, lacked further response 200M, dropped off rapidly. (Lame RF leg)
Bumped start, driven forward three-wide to race outside leader before settling one-off, one-back at turn. Urged forward on straightening, took lead 250m and held off late challenge.
Began well, rolled forward before settling three-back on fence. Badly held for a run in straight before getting clear 200m and finishing strongly.
Bumped and unbalanced start, then raced in restricted room 1100m before settling 3-back, one-off. Edged closer around turn, kept on well in straight but no match for first two.
Tightened start, urged forward grabbing box seat before turn. No clear run early in straight, switched out and ran on steadily closing stages.
No early speed, dropping to rear while edging closer to fence. Blocked for run entering straight, gut clear final 200m and finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Began OK, taken to fence four-back from leader without being pushed. Stayed on fence around turn, raced tight approaching 200m before getting clear and finishing strongly.
Began well holding rail inside leader to 700m before taking over lead. Caught 250m out but kept battling until flattened final 100m.
Ridden to hold forward position but held wide behind midfield and over-raced. Shifted out 750m, taken even wider in straight but only one-paced.
Began OK but not much speed, settling at rear but away from fence. Kept wide around turn and found little in straight despite hard riding.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind horses, settling a long last. Taken very wide in straight and ran past beaten horses.
Fractious in gate and slow into stride. Ridden to hold midfield position but proved difficult to settle. Hampered 200m when giving ground. Found to be a "roarer."
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling but kept away from fence by inside runner and dropped to 2nd passing 700m. Kept on well till 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward 3-wide but only 1.5L from leader before losing position around turn. Kept on fairly in straight before tiring rapidly final 200m.
Began well and taken across to sit forward of midfield, 3 off the fence. Ran on very strongly late, passing leader at 50m, and looked to have more in hand as he crossed the line.
Began well and taken forward early to sit just behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Shared the lead at 400m, and ran on strongly in the straight to hold onto 2nd after being passed at 50m.
OK away and taken across from the wide barrier to sit midfield, 3 wide. 5L behind leaders at the 300m, showed a good turn off foot to run on well from there, picking up 3rd place.
Began well and taken forward early to lead. Travelled OK in the straight and lead until the 200m, but ran like a tired horse late, and was beaten out of a place.
Began well, and allowed to ease forward to be handily placed, 1 off the fence. Slightly 1 paced in the straight, but plugged away steadily.
Began awkwardly and didn't settle early before being taken midfield, one off the fence. Came wider on the turn, but only ran on fairly in the straight.
Began fairly, before being taken forward of midfield, on the fence. One paced in straight, and never threatened a place.

Crowded on jumping, and initially at the rear of the field on the fence. Worked forward in early/mid stages to sit midfield. Worked forward steadily from the turn, but never a threat, and peaked 100m.

OK away and found a position forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Checked off heels and raced ungenerously at the 900m, and lost ground. Handily placed at the top of the straight, but faded out from the 400m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last up the back straight. Plugged away in the straight, picking up a few stragglers.
Began OK, before finding a position worse than midfield 1 off the fence. Badly overreacted when checked off heels at 900m. Last on turn, and only plugged away late, picking up a couple easing up.

Began OK and taken forward early. Was crossed for the lead at 1000m, and badly placed on heels. Didn't settle when on heels from 1000m until the home turn. Raced tired late, and faded out in the straight.
Bounded out of the gates, and sat at the rear of the field. Came widest from the 300m, but delivered nothing, and only beat one home.
Taken back from the wide gate to sit mid back, 3 off the fence. Widest on the turn. Lay in towards heels at 300m, but race was already run, and dropped out to finish last.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back at rear, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off strongly to score by a length.
Jumped well, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Began well, raced prominently early, difficult to settle and unbalanced near 1200M, positioned 2 wide in 6th on turn, closed off well in straight to get 3rd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 3 wide with cover until near 1100M, left racing wide with no cover thereafter, 4 wide on turn, kept on well until near final 150M, just stayed on for 4th.
Away with them, raced 2 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Steadied early to obtain cover, positioned 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider near 1100M, still raced wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 8 lengths or so back at tail, 3 wide turning, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Jumped with them, positioned in midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, no daylight until near 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 2 lengths or so back on rail, same position on turn, no daylight early in straight but found little when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a tricky gate, 7 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, only passed a few tired runners in straight, never a threat.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after 200M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward to take the lead near 1100M, peaked on turn, kept on evenly until headed near 200M, weakened thereafter and eased final 100M.
Jumped well from the gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide on turn, peaked on turn, weakened gradually early in straight and eased final 150M.

Jumped well, taken one back in 3rd on rails, briefly baulked for a run early in straight, responded well to assert authority over 100 metres out.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, only to be denied close to home.
Travelled in 2nd just outside the leader, failed to quicken to match pace with first two after straightening.
Settled on rails in 5th within 3L of pace, similar turning in, failed to quicken to threaten.
Settled 2-wide in 4th within 3L of pace, remained similar turning in, failed to quicken to threaten.
Fast out and went straight to the lead, quickened nicely on straightening to comfortably hold off all challengers.
Jumped well and settled behind leaders, stoked up to challenge home turn, tried hard in straight but could not run down leader.
Settled midfield, traveled nicely passing 600m and ran home strongly in straight.
Taken back from wide gate to settle towards rear, awkward near 1400, commenced to improve home turn and finished strongly final 300m.
Taken back from wide gate to settle towards rear, kept to inside home turn and made good steady ground in straight.
Settled midfield, ridden along approaching home turn and finished one paced.
Settled behind leader but unable to quicken when asked for effort on straightening.
Slow to begin, crowded for room at 1400m, settled towards rear, one paced in straight.
Raced keenly when caught wide early, strode forward to settle outside leader near 1200m, ridden along home turn but weakened in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, widest on straightening but unable to make up ground in straight.
Settled just behind speed, 3 wide from 600m when trying to improve, tried to challenge on straightening but quickly under pressure and weakened out of it.
Settled midfield and race wide without cover, weakened in straight.
Taken back from wide gate and remained at rear throughout.
Slow to begin, raced keenly near 1400m, under pressure home turn before weakening in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader, fought on gamely to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader, ran on well for 2nd, beaten by a neck.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader, made ground steadily for 4th.
Sent forward to share the lead, kept on only fairly and weakened over the last furlong. (Questioned for performance, see incident report)
Pushed to settle in a prominent spot, travelled about 2.5Ls behind the leader, kept on one pace to the line.
Crowded start, then travelled 4Ls behind the leader, made minor ground until final 50M weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield, 2.5Ls behind the leader, never ran on. (Lame right fore)
Ridden forward to share the lead, dropped off rapidly 300M.
Jumped awkwardly, niggled along throughout, never responded.
At rear throughout, never a threat.
Sharp start widest, soon led & crossed to rail 1230m, 1L clear turning in & quickly extended 4L clear, eased close home for impressive win.
Fast break to press early lead, settled 1 back 1 off, checked off heels 940m, shifted 3 wide final turn & driven, quickened to 2nd 230m, kept on well but no match for winner.
Tardy start, recovered to race fore of midfield, over-raced & checked 920m, thereafter settled 6th 1 off with cover, driven 500m, shifted out turning in, stayed on to 3rd late.
Fast start & bustled to dispute initial lead, soon headed & niggled 1 back on rail, checked off heels 940m & over-raced, driven 530m, lacked kick, kept on one pace.
Broke well, worked to race upside leader in 2nd, niggled 500m, driven 430m, unable to quicken, all out & lost 2nd 230m, tapered & swamped close home.
Broke ok, raced 1 off with cover midfield, checked off heels 900m, driven final turn, kept on without threatening.
Missed break, mustered on rail to fore of midfield, over-raced & checked 1150m, continued to over-race, ridden turning in, shifted out in run, kept on evenly.
Tardy start & raced 1 off near tail, switched 3 wide 650m, wide into stretch, driven 420m, stayed on centre track for minor headway.
Moderate start, caught 3 wide no cover behind midfield, slotted 1 off with cover 850m, shaken up 420m & shifted out, plugged on tepidly centre track.
Sluggish break, raced rail midfield, shifted 1 off & driven 500m, plugged on moderately.
Taken back from wide gate to race at tail, sat 1 off, driven wide into stretch, plodded on moderately.
Lacked early pace & bustled, mustered to race rail behind midfield, niggled 600m, driven 500m, plodded on same speed.
No early zip & raced near tail on rail, ridden 420m, struggled in weak run home.
Slow start, mustered & over-raced midfield 1 off with cover, checked 3 wide no cover 900m, driven 450m, faded tamely.
Tardy start & bustled initially, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, nudged along 450m, quickened in stretch & swept to lead 50m, drew clear.
Smart break, sat 3rd 1 off, had cover until exposed 820m, shaken up to lead 400m & scooted 2L clear, emptied 150m & headed 50m.
Fast break but immediately outpaced & soon rousted at tail, 2L detached & hard-ridden 550m, wide into stretch, flew home centre track to nick 3rd late.
Good break, raced handy but 3 wide no cover, driven turning in, boxed on to 2nd 300m, unable to make inroads, tapered late & edged out of frame.
Speed to lead under drive, headed 1130m, sat 1 back from 820m, shifted 1 off & driven 350m, plugged on evenly.
Broke well but soon outpaced, raced rail near rear, crowded & not clear run turning in, shaken up 300m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Lacked early pace & raced 3rd last 1 off with cover, niggled along 600m, shifted out 500m, kept on evenly under drive.
Moderate break wide, caught 4 deep no cover back of midfield, hung out on turn 600m, plodded on one pace in stretch.
Slow start, settled rail near tail, driven 400m & shifted out, found little & plugged on evenly.
Tardy start, lacked pace & rousted early to race midfield on rail, niggled throughout, driven 500m, found nothing & weakened in stretch.
Missed break, recovered to sit midfield 1 off with cover, driven 450m, found nil & faded tamely.
Sharp start, rolled to lead 1 off 1030m, to rail 820m, all out & headed 400m, faded tamely.
At back, 7Ls off the leader on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear, only won by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly and led 300M, only beaten by a narrow margin on the line in 2nd.
Eased back, 8.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, took advantages of the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M whilst hanging in.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Further forward in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M, run ended 100M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 4Ls off the leader on the rails, suited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, closed off well when clear.
Eased back, 9.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed forward, shared lead under fast sectionals, ran on until 250M flattened.
Behind midfield, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden forward to battle for the lead, clocked fast sectionals, reduced quickly 350M.
At back, 8.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Struggled to keep up with the field, 10Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Away well, settling half a length behind and outside leader. Made no move until 400m, throwing out a sustained challenge before gaining upper hand in the final strides.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to lead on settling and crossing to fence. Tried to kick clear on entering straight and kept finding when challenged only to lose in final strides.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling towards the rear in one-off position. Made some progress around turn, switched wide halfway up straight and finished strongly.
Began OK, settling three-back, one-off back stretch. Urged forward between horses around turn but blocked for run in straight until 200m. Finished off nicely.
Jumped well, grabbing box seat 3L from leader on settling. Not much room top of straight, shifted out 100m to get run, kept on well despite racing close to heels.
Jumped fairly, crossing to fence about 6L from leader. Switched out around turn and made some progress, before taken wider in straight where boxed on steadily.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear close to fence. Improved position around turn, shifted in abruptly 400m to get run and finished off nicely. Rider dropped rein 200m.
Pressed forward early but unable find cover and forced to race three-wide, mostly without cover. Taken even wider on entering straight but only one-paced.
Jumped with field but not enough pace to go forward and held wide in midfield on settling. Kept wide around turn and found little in straight when put under pressure.

Crowded out start, then hard ridden to go forward, settling one-back, one-off 3L from leader. Lay out around turn but remained in contention till 200m before tiring. Found to be a roarer. Unacceptable performance.
Shifted across behind runners from widest draw, dropping to last but away from fence. Made some progress early in straight before turning one-paced.
Ridden to hold forward position while edging closer to fence, settling three-back from leader. Travelled nicely around turn but gave ground shortly after entering straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw and forced to race wide before being taken further out passing 700m and slipping back. Last into straight and never competitive.
Began well but unable find cover and raced wide back stretch. Lost position around turn, and tired soon after entering straight.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division 4Ls off the steady pace, driven nearing 400M, quickened up in good style to lead inside 200M, soon drew away from rivals winning it decisively.
Began awkwardly, settled towards rear 6Ls off the pace, bid wide 500M, closed off soundly to go 2nd near line, not reached winner.
Up with early pace, restrained to 6th place middle stages, responded well leaving the bend to go 2nd 150M, proved no match with winner, one paced final stages and lost 2nd near line.
Not hurried, settled in last place 7Ls behind leader, 5Ls down 400M, did not enjoy the clearest of passages but stayed on well when switched out wide.
Positively ridden but unable to get across from draw 5, settled along the 3 path in chasing group, no cover from 800M, battled on in straight and was always held by leaders.
Close up early stages, fell back to midfield middle stages, stayed on final 300M but never able to trouble leaders.
Moved up to the fore 1200M, led to 900M, driven and regained lead early straight, remained prominent until weakening 150M.
From draw 14 caught wide early stages, tracked leader 1100M, dueled for lead turning in, remained in contention until 200M, faded towards the line.
Taken across behind runners, 7Ls off the pace in rear, kept to inside throughout and had to make his run from an unpromising position passing 350M, made limited progress.

Proved difficult to settle in the lead passing 1400M, fell back to midfield 750M, crept closer to leaders 500M, held up in straight and not able to ridden out until 100M when leaders have already gone beyond reach.

Settled down behind midfield, made only fair progress before running to heels of leaders mid-straight, not ridden out over concluding stages. (Jockey : saddle shifted early stages, disadvantaged for the remainder of the race)
Unable to slot in, in midfield early, caught 3-wide without cover until moving to the lead 800M, headed 350M, no extra in tank.
Ended up in a 3-wide position behind midfield, soon outpaced and beaten 350M, no impression
Fractious in stalls, began awkwardly, settled 5Ls back towards the rear, failed to pick up entering straight, eased mid-straight. (No abnormal findings)
Began well, hugging outside fence in 4th place 3L from leader at 800m. Popped off fence 550m to get clear run, hit front 200m out and pulled clear to win comfortably.
Jumped with field, racing down centre track before edging towards outer fence passing 800m. Shifted in 400m for clear running and finished strongly to snatch 2nd placing on line.
Quickly into stride, setting up big lead at 700m and easily crossing from inner to outer fence. Put under pressure 400m, caught 200m out but kept on well to line.
Began OK but outpaced, dropping to last pair passing 800m. Still well back passing 400m but picked up momentum final 200m and finished strongly.
Began well, racing outside leader initially but not clear enough to cross and kept 4-wide from outer fence, 2L from leader. Put under pressure from 400m and boxed on gamely.
Jumped well but crowded and lost position 800m, settling along fence 4L from leader. Edged closer passing 400m to look a chance before turning one-paced.
No early pace, racing behind main bunch on settling but well away from outer fence. Took closer order passing 400m but only one-paced under hard riding.
Got off nicely, racing close to outer fence 3L from leader. Raced in restricted room 700m but remained in contention till final 200m when tired slightly.
Outpaced and raced on own towards rear along outer fence. Remained out of touch until final 200m when made some late ground.
Bumped at start, recovered and taken quickly to outer fence just 1L from leader. Closed in to within a half length of lead passing 400m before giving ground gradually. Lame left hind.
Pressed forward between horses, settling 3L from leader and one-away from outer fence. Kept tabs on leading pack until 200m before tiring.
Began fairly, racing behind main pack but well away from outer fence. Hung badly and difficult to ride from 600m, racing alone down centre track. Stewards said racing manners unacceptable.
Bumped start, pressed forward but 4-wide from outer fence, settling 3L behind leader at half-way mark. Began giving ground passing 400m and finished well back.
Began fairly, then crowded and lost ground, settling last. Lost contact with the field 400m and never competitive.
Cruised out on jumping to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran on strongly from 300m, and drew clear from 150m. Looked to have something left, and eased near the line.
Began OK, eased forward early to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran on steadily from top of the straight. Improved tempo when challenged at the 200m, but outpaced, but not threatened for 2nd.
Began OK, but slow into stride. Found a position midfield on the fence. Never got fully clear until the last 200m and ran on well late, grabbing 3rd place in the shadows of the post.
Taken forward early to sit just behind the leader, on the fence. Raced tight when improving into a run at 300m, but only ran on fairly in the straight, and just lost 3rd on the line.

OK away, and cruised forward to sit in a position worse than midfield, on the fence. Still 5L off leaders on the turn and had a tendency to hang out in the straight. Finished off the last 200m strongly.
Pushed up early to ensure he led, setting a decent tempo. Led until the 200m, but peaked on his run and faded back.
Taken back from the wide draw to sit 10L off the leader equal last, 1 off the fence. Came widest on the turn and plugged away steadily without threatening.
Taken back early to sit towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Never fully ridden out in the straight, and found to be lame in the off fore leg.
Began OK and initially in a handy position 3 wide, but moved forward early to sit behind the leader one off the fence. Well placed on the turn, but faded from the 200m and battled to line.
Pushed forward from the jump to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Prominently placed early in the straight, but had a tendency to lay in, peaked at the 200m and faded back.
Began well and found a position forward of midfield, on the fence. Briefly held up in the straight, but faded when given the opportunity to improve in the straight.
Taken back from the wide barrier early to sit at the rear of the field, on the fence. Under pressure before the turn, but never responded and eased out before the line.
Began fairly, raced 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the clear lead on turn, kept on well in straight, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight to hold 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide with some cover behind midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to make frame.
Moderately away from the widest draw, taken back to race 6 lengths back at rear, found rail on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began well, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, crowded near 700M and lost ground, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, showed no early speed, raced wide and without cover throughout, failed to close off in straight when hard run took toll. (Lame right front leg next day)
Crowded out start, raced at tail throughout, taken wide in straight and finished off one-paced, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced at rear, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight, never competitive.
Bumped start, recovered to race prominently, unbalanced near 450M, folded up quickly after straightening, finished tailed out.
Began well, raced tight and unbalanced near 900M, lost position thereafter, failed to close off in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Jumped moderately, soon recovered to 2nd just outside the lead, took up running 800 metres out, hung on dourly under pressure.
Jumped best to soon take up running, held lead to the 800 metres, one-back on rails turning in, unable to peg back the winner despite coming under strong pressure.
Began fairly, settled one-out-one-back in 4th, became 5th entering back straight, took closer order under pressure down far side, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Broke well, settled mainly in midfield on rails, commenced move entering straight, ran on steadily.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, came closer to 2-wide in 5th at the Rock, fought on steadily from a similar position into straight.
Settled behind midfield, came under pressure around the bend, fought on steadily without threatening

Ridden along from the one gate settling just off the pace on rails, in similar 1 back position but became 5th midway down back straight, left flat-footed when pace quickened around home bend, made some late headway in the run home.
Taken back from a wide gate for rails run behind midfield, switched off rails for a run upon straightening, made modest progress without threatening.
Soon taken back on rails from a wide gate, remained in last few to straight, found nothing.

Began from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover in behind midfield, strode forward around stables bend to reach 3rd without cover into back straight, dropped out under pressure from 2nd turning for home.
Jumped fairly, gradually steadied back to last few, trailed the field into back straight, saved ground turning for home, one-paced.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, never seen with a chance.
Jumped smartly, settled leaders back, eased out to challenge on straightening, quickened nicely to win easily.
Settled behind leaders, rifted back to midfield near 500m, pulled out to challenge on straightening, ran home well but no match for winner.
Allowed to settle towards rear, commenced to improve at 400m and ran home nicely.
Began fairly, no early pace and settled at rear, ran home steadily in straight.
Taken back from wide gate to settle at rear, pushed along home turn and finished off fairly.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve 450m but one paced in straight.
Pushed hard from wide gate to go forward and lead, travelling nicely home turn but quickly under pressure in straight and weakened from 200m.
Ridden along early before easing back to obtain cover worse than midfield, hard ridden passing 500m when laying out, one paced in straight.
Hard ridden from wide gate to go forward and settle outside leader, under pressure from 450m and weakened in run home.
Slow to begin, settled worse than midfield, ridden along near 600m to hold position, hard ridden home turn and could not pick up in the straight.
Jumped smartly and sent forward, hampered and checked at 1000m, under pressure passing 600m and weakened out of it.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, dashed well to score by a neck.
Sent forward to obtain the box seat, ran on strongly to get 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Ridden forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on well until final 100M headed, hung on for 3rd.
Pushed forward to settle in front of midfield about 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 4th.
Pushed along to take the fence from the outside gate, 3Ls behind the leader, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made ground steadily.
Eased back, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, ran on fairly.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Slow to muster despite ridden along, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, weakened rounding the Home Turn.
Prominent, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened badly rounding the Home Turn.
Broke ok, slotted midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 4 wide to challenge turning in, quickened to lead 150m & drew clear.
Slow start & bustled to camp near rear 1 off, ridden a touch 450m, switched out & driven 350m, run checked 300m, driven again 250m, closed late to 2nd.
Broke ok, rousted on fence to press lead, edged ahead 620m, kicked for home 300m, all out & headed 150m, tapered to 3rd.
Missed break & rousted initially to race rail 2nd last, advanced on turn, in contention & driven 300m, kept on dourly.
Broke ok, raced rail 1 back, shifted 1 off & driven in 2nd 300m, one-paced & swamped in tapering run home.
Fast start & rousted to press early lead, soon taken back to fore of midfield 1 off with cover, driven very wide 400m, vied for 2nd 300m, tapered in run.
Speed to lead & bustled, headed 960m, shuffled to 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 deep 400m, driven into stretch, boxed on one pace.
Outpaced at start, niggled on rail behind midfield, closer order & shifted 1 off 400m, not clear run 300m, ridden 250m, kept on moderately until checked close home.
Broke ok and bustled to race handy 3 deep with cover, slipped back to midfield & niggled 600m, very wide turning in, driven 300m, plugged on tamely.
Broke ok, taken back to tail 1 off, hard-ridden turning in & shifted out in stretch, plugged on tepidly.
Broke ok, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, under pump 520m & shuffled back, hard-ridden at rear 300m, plodded on weakly.
Smart start widest, pace to edge lead 3 deep 960m, headed 620m, ridden 450m but emptied 300m, eased down.
Speed to lead, rousted to snare rail, 1L clear & driven into stretch, tapered close home, held on.
Decent break, camped 1 back on rail, shifted out & ridden 300m, fought on in pursuit, closed final strides, just failed.
Sharp break, raced midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 450m, shifted out on turn & stayed on dourly to edge 3rd.
Tardy start & bustled near rear initially, progress to midfield on inner, green on turn, driven into stretch, boxed on to 3rd 75m, tapered & lost place at wire.
Tardy start & bustled, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven 300m, kept on dourly for headway.
Broke ok, soon outpaced & niggled near rear, hung out exiting back stretch, under pump 400m, wide into stretch, shifted inside 200m, ran on for minor headway.
Slow start & niggled 2nd last, raced 1 off until hung out exiting backstretch, ridden 450m, widest turning in, closed off for minor inroads.
Taken behind from wide gate, raced at tail on rail, progress on turn, driven into stretch & plugged on dourly for some headway.
Broke well & bustled throughout to race handy 3 wide no cover, hard-ridden turning in, outpaced & swamped in fading run.
Fast break, settled handy 3 wide with cover midfield, driven wide final turn, plugged on one pace.
Fast start widest, caught 4 deep no cover until slotted 3 deep behind midfield 500m, under pump turning in & swung wide, one-paced in run home.
Broke ok & rousted to sit 2nd 1 off with cover, hard-ridden 3 deep turning in, weakened tamely.
Settled along the fence, 2Ls off the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide just off the leader, harmed by the fast pace, closed off strongly for 2nd despite all negative racing situations.
Took rail easily and led by 1L, clocked fast sectionals, saddled shifted 500M, hung on well until 150M despite rider couldn't riding out fully, ran on for 3rd.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, progressed steadily 250M.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, lack room 300M, no dash when clear.
At back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, checked 700M, favoured by the fast tempo, made some ground 200M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, just held ground in final stages.
Slow away, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, checked 500M, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader, not suited by the fast pace, bumped 300M, emptied 200M.
Bumped start, at rear, no progress.
Tightened for room at start and clear last on settling. Made up ground around turn, taken to centre track in straight and finished strongly to win pulling clear.
Hard ridden early to go forward, settling between horses three back from leader. Urged forward 500m but got close to heels before getting clear 250m. Finished off nicely.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling between horses at rear. Improved position around turn, switched out entering straight and finished off strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from awkward draw, settling at rear close to fence. Crowded for room 500m dropping to last, taken wide in straight and ran on strongly.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Urged forward turning for home, looked a chance passing 200m before turning one-paced.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail 3-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn, kept on OK early in straight before tiring final stages.
Began fairly, holding rail 4-back from leader. Shaken up entering turn but little progress. One paced in straight, giving ground quickly final 100m.
Began well, pressed forward to hold position one-off, one-back. Urged forward turning for home, took lead early in straight before running on empty from 200m and dropping back.
Pressed forward racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Rolled forward to look a chance turning for home, still in contention 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward from inside draw, holding box seat and travelling strongly. Appeared reluctant to take splits up the straight and weakened noticeably. Stewards ruled performance unacceptable.
Used early to lead from an outside draw, crossing to the fence and setting fast early sections. Led field into straight, collared 250m and weakened quickly.
Hard ridden to go forward but not enough speed and held wide, dropping back gradually. Rider reported did not travel well from 800m.
Sat 3-wide behind leaders and had no cover for most of the trip, moved up to lead before home turn, duel with rival from 450M, kept finding under pressure.
Had rail run throughout, tracked leaders, did best work final 200M, nearest finish.
Settled down near the rear early stages, raced keenly in midfield down back straight, stayed on well to be closest on the line.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, raced keenly after 900M when left without cover, strolled forward to press leader 500M, dueled to 100M, faded late and lost 2 placings near line.
Settled mid-pack 3Ls off the pace, coaxed along 500M, swung wide into straight, closed off mildly, not reached leaders.
Unable to obtain outright lead, caught 3-wide first turn, sat behind leaders from 600M, ran on one pace to line.
Switched off to last 6-7Ls off the pace, 3-wide bid 600M, stayed on moderately down outside.
Slow to begin, settled midfield along the fence, driven 350M but made no additional headway over final 200M.
Taken across behind runners, held up near last over 5Ls off the pace, take wide 400M, ran on same pace, never a threat to leaders.
With leaders early, caught 4-wide until crossing to lead 1100M, fell back to 3rd home turn, under pressure 400M but found very little in the finish.
Held up in midfield first half of the race, shuffled back to rear passing 800M, already beaten turning into straight. (Jockey said his mount did not travel well throughout the race)
Up with early pace, tracked leaders entering back straight, gave ground 400M, eased when well beaten.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling, setting strong pace. Joined by another before entering straight but kicked clear passing 200m and held off late challenge.
Hard ridden early but not enough pace, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Edged forward 450m, switched in halfway up the straight and finished strongly.
Began well but checked 1000m and lost position. Ridden to make up ground close to fence, taken 3-wide entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began well, hard ridden between horses to stay 1L behind leader. Urged forward turn to get within a neck of leader 400m but unable to keep pace in straight and swamped final stages.
Pressed forward from awkward draw, racing three-wide first turn and back stretch. Lost position around final turn, switched wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling between horses 3L from leader. Got shuffled back final turn, taken wide in straight and boxed on gamely.
Began fairly but pressed forward and trapped very wide first turn. Steadied and shifted across behind runners to fence towards rear. Made late ground weaving between horses.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace, crossing quickly to rail behind midfield. Given early reminder back stretch. Steadied 250m when making ground and denied run close home.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling in last pair away from fence. Still well back entering straight but kept on fairly to line.
Crowded out at start, dropping to last pair along fence. Clear last turning form home and boxed on one-paced in straight.
Quickly out along rail but steadied 1000m, dropping 2L from leader. Stayed on fence keeping tabs on leaders but started to give ground after passing 200m.
Pressed forward, racing wide without cover about 1L behind leader. Lay out around turn but remained in contention until weakening final 200m.
