Settled in last few, switched out for a run passing the 400 metres, quickened well to assert authority over 100 metres out.
Restrained well back from the widest gate, trailed the field before circling them on the bend, widest runner turning in, ran on to hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, swamped nearing finish.
Jumped well but soon dropped to midfield or just worse, made modest headway on outside rounding the bend, ran on to hold some chance 200 metres out, faded.
Settled towards the rear, kept on steadily without threatening.

Hard ridden early but had to settle for forward of midfield position, continued to be niggled along around home bend but shuffled back to last entering straight, however, made significant progress down for late impression.

Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate, soon driven down outside to hold 3L 6th, unbalanced briefly coming out of back straight, did not find much room and shuffled backward early in straight, failed to respond inside final 200m.
Began moderately, gradually improved to 2nd one off the rails 1200 metres out, gained slender advantage briefly after straightening, unable to sustain effort and soon swamped.
Broke well from a wide draw, pressed on to take up running off the rails far side, obtained rails run at the 1200 metres, led until headed upon straightening, weakened badly.
Broke well from a poor draw to take rails run, settled just off the pace in close-up 3rd, saw daylight when leader drifted off the rails turning in, however, soon dropped out tamely.
Settled in midfield on rails, awkwardly placed behind runners rounding the bend, ran home one-paced.
Slightly slow out, settled 3-wide in midfield, made steady headway rounding home bend to join the leaders briefly turning in, soon faded under pressure.
Began well, settled just over 2L back in 5th on rails, shuffled backward rounding home bend, badly baulked in straight.
Began well, settled within 2L of pace, badly baulked for a run after straightening, never recovered.
Always towards the rear, caught in the backwash of interferences coming out of far side, no further impression.

Jumped smartly and allowed to settle midfield, travelling nicely home turn, eased out on straightening to challenge, finished strongly in middle of track, raced tight near 200m, gained upper hand final 50m.
Settled worse than midfield, commenced to make ground at 400m, challenged strongly at 200m, fought right to the line going down narrowly.
Commenced awkwardly, pushed along from wide gate to settle on pace, awkwardly placed on heels at 800m, tried hard in straight and battled steadily to the line.
Settled worse than midfield and ran home steadily in straight.
Jumped smartly and settle behind leader, tried to challenge on straightening but unable to quicken and finished one paced.
Ridden along early to go forward and lead, travelled well home turn, established a break in straight before being overpowered final 100m.
Hampered shortly after start, settled towards rear, ground home steadily in straight.
Commenced awkwardly, settled forward of midfield, niggled at home turn and unable to make up ground in straight.
Bumped on jumping and hampered shortly after, settled towards rear, pushed along passing 600m and ran home one paced.
Slow into stride and settled at rear, widest on straightening and ran home fairly.
From wide gate obtained midfield position on rail, niggled at passing 600m and unable to make up ground in straight.
Settled in midfield position, quickly under pressure in straight and weakened out of it.
Bumped at start and hampered shortly after, settled towards rear and remained there throughout.
Ridden along early to race on pace, asked for effort on straightening and immediately under pressure, weakened final 200m.
Jumped slowly, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, peeled wide turning in, stormed home to score by a neck.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, dashed strongly until final 50M headed by the winner, beaten by a neck.
Rolled to obtain the box seat, ran on well until final 50M weakened, hung on for dead heat 3rd.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched to the widest 300M, ran on strongly for dead heat 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on nicely until final 100M weakened.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, sung wide turning in, ran on ok.
Rolled to settle in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on only one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in the straight.
Ridden to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, blocked early straight, ran on only fairly thereafter.
Pushed to settle in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on until final furlong weakened.
Ridden forward early, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, checked badly 300M, well beaten thereafter.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened over the last furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, emptied 300M.
Fast start, stalked 1 back on rail, shaken up 430m, responded well to lead 200m, pressed at wire but never in doubt.
Sharp start, restrained to camp behind midfield 1 off with cover, shaken up 420m, strong closer to 2nd 130m, pressed winner at line but held.
Broke ok, raced fore of midfield on inner, switched centre track 420m & driven, closed to 3rd without threatening.
Broke well but niggled to race handy 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven 420m, ran on to vie for 3rd until emptied close home.
Smart break, checked 860m, raced 2nd 1 off no cover, 3 wide into stretch & driven when switched 4 deep 350m, lacked toe, stayed on evenly.
Broke ok but lacked toe, bustled to race midfield 3 wide no cover, ridden 450m, stayed on for moderate late inroads.
Speed to lead from widest g ate, crossed to rail 870m, slight lead turning in & shifted off fence, lacked toe & headed 410m, tapered to wire.
Broke well, rousted to lay up handy 3 wide no cover, pressed leader 560m & in front 410m, soon all out, emptied & headed 200m, faded.
Taken behind to race rail near rear, shifted wide home turn, short of room in stretch run, shaken up 350m, kept on for modest late inroads.
Broke well but soon taken back to near rear 1 off with cover, bustled 600m, driven wide final turn, one-paced.
Tardy start & back to rail behind midfield, off heels 820m & stumbled, shifted to 1 off near rear, crowded 400m, ridden 250m, plugged on tamely.
Tardy start & rousted, mustered to race handy 3 wide with cover, slight check 800m & slid back a spot, under pressure on turn, tepid run home centre track.
Missed break several lengths, joined tail 1 off 630m, swung widest into stretch, driven & plodded on until emptied 150m & faded.
Sluggish break, mustered to midfield on fence, hampered 870m & knocked back to behind midfield, found nil in stretch.
Decent start, sat 1 back on fence, switched 3 wide turning in, crowded but driven between runners to lead 260m, battled to hold challengers.
Taken back to race near tail 1off with cover, driven very wide into stretch, rattled home down centre, drifted in closing stages to join principals, nicked 2nd & just failed at wire.
Broke ok, bustled along to settle rail fore of midfield, switched 5 wide into stretch & driven, quickened to press lead 150m, held & lost 2nd at wire.
Moderate break, rousted & soon prominent 1 off no cover, snagged to 1 off 1 back 1000m, niggled 500m, driven 4 wide into stretch, boxed on dourly.
Sharp start, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, driven centre track in stretch, boxed on solidly without threatening.
Slow start, sat rail towards rear, shifted out into stretch, switched out further for clear run 300m, stayed on for minor late inroads.
Taken back at start, soon bustled at tail, shifted wide on turn, under pump & widest into stretch, ran on towards stand side for solid headway.
Moderate start & bustled to race midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 600m, shifted wide into stretch, lacked toe, stayed on ok centre track.
Fast break, raced wide to vie for early lead 1050m, close 2nd until ridden to edge lead 380m, headed 260m & swamped in tepid effort.
Missed break, raced rail midfield, ridden final turn & shifted out 420m, plugged on evenly, eased late when no extra.
Sharp start, restrained to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide home turn & driven, plugging one-pace when bumped 250m, no extra & faded.
Fast break to dispute lead, soon restrained & raced fore of midfield 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, one-paced & faded out final 200m.
Driven to lead 1330m, to rail 1150m, under pressure to maintain lead from 1050m, narrow advantage turning in, driven & headed 380m, wilted.
Snagged back towards rear 1 off with cover, switched very wide final turn, driven 400m, plodding on moderately when bumped 250m, no extra & faded.
At back, not suited by the slow pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M for 3rd.
Eased back, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased back for cover, illustrated strong finishing efforts 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
At back as usual, trapped wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Pushed forward to take rail and led, clocked advantages slow sectionals, weakened 200M.
Pressed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Settled nicely in prominent spot, benefited by the slow tempo, however no progress.
At back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Never improved at back.
Hard ridden early to go forward, settling half a length behind and outside leader. Stayed close around the turn, took over lead 350m and pulled clear, won eased down.
Jumped with field, restrained and taken across behind runners, settling at rear in one-off position. Entered straight behind horses, got split 300m out and finished strongly.
Niggled early before shifting across behind horses, settling five-back, one-off. Held behind horses early in straight, switched out widest 300m and finished off well.
Jumped OK, ridden but not much speed, settling behind midfield 5L from leader. Switched out wide in straight to get run and ran on steadily.
Outpaced, settling well back along fence. Made up some ground around turn, stayed on fence in straight and ran on well to be closest at finish.
Pushed early to hold forward position, grabbing box seat but difficult to settle 800m. Not much room early in straight, got clear 300m, kept on steadily till swamped final stages.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling four-back along fence. Popped off fence before entering straight but blocked for run till 100m when forced to switch out. Finished off nicely.
Began well, urged forward settling one-back, one-off to and around turn. Still in contention 200m before turning one-paced.
Urged forward from outside draw and held three-wide behind midfield. Taken even wider in straight and boxed on one-paced.
Ridden to hold forward position but held wide without cover three-back from leader. Continued to race wide around turn and into straight turning one-paced. Lame right hind.
Began well, ridden along between horses three-back from leader. Had every chance entering straight before tightened 100m out, boxed on. Found to be lame right front.
Hard ridden from an awkward draw to lead on settling before crossing to fence. Set strong pace to 350m when collared and faded quickly.
Jumped fairly, shifted across behind runners from an outside draw, settling a distant last. Well back entering straight and never competitive.
Began well, battling for early lead before restrained, settling three-back from leader along fence. Started to give ground on straightening and finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Not hurried, held up near the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, angled out into clear nearing 200M, closed off strongly up the center for narrow victory.
Reserved in mid-division, saved ground along the rails, headway 400M and loomed a strong threat behind leader mid-straight, held up until 150M, closed off well final stages, just missed.
Unable to slot in, raced 3-wide towards the rear for most of the way, fanned widest into straight, closed off willingly, just held narrowly by first two.

From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled in the rear 8Ls off the pace, had no clear run early straight, made stealthy headway from 300M, hampered twice late stages but managed to go 4th before line.
Strolled forward from wide draw, crossed to the lead 850M, kept on well in straight and remained a presence until 50M, crowded for room late and lost 4th near line.
Up with early pace, crossed to the fence 1000M, tracked leader home turn, kept on steadily under pressure final 300M, got outfinished final 100M but not beaten far. (Lame left front)
Never far off from leaders, taken out 500M and advanced to a contending position mid-straight, kept on steadily, hampered late and not able to be ridden out near the finish.
Up with pace, settled in 2nd and turned for home in the 2-path, remained prominent until 100M, turned one pace final stages, got squeezed late.
With early leaders, retrained along the fence 3Ls behind leader, had every chance inside 300M, kept pace with the leaders until weakening final 100M.
Settled down behind midfield along the 2-path, drifted outward for clear running 400M, lacked the needed response, well held by leaders.
Held up in mid-division 4Ls back, failed to fire when fully set down early straight, faltered final 100M.
From widest barrier unable to get closer than 3-wide, 5Ls off the pace behind midfield, not going the pace to seriously challenge passing 400M.
Chased the pace, 3-wide no cover home turn, had little left passing 350M and retreated.
Held up near the rear, soon outpaced entering straight, eased when no chance final 150M.
Urged forward but held wide outside early leader before taking over lead 1200m and crossing to fence 1000m. Set soft sections to 300m when challenged but kept finding for narrow victory.
Began OK, racing between horses three-back from leader. Urged forward turning for home, switched out wide in straight and finished strongly to miss narrowly.
Pressed forward from inside draw to settle a neck behind leader back stretch and turn. Threw out strong challenge on straightening but unable to catch winner. Rider dropped whip 100m.
Began well, ridden along to hold position one-back, one-off. Took inside run on straightening and kept on gamely without looking dangerous.
Jumped with field but tightened 1500m. Urged forward, racing three-wide 1.5L behind leader, and mostly without cover. Kept on well in straight.
First out, leading initially before slipping into box seat when leader crossed over 1000m. Stayed on fence entering straight and kept on steadily without being a threat.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling towards rear along fence. Made up some ground in straight. Rider reported saddle shifted but able to ride out final 300m.
Began awkwardly, settling at rear in one-off position. Dropped to clear last entering straight and ran past tired horses closing stages.
Began well, ridden along to hold fence three-back from leader. Lost position around turn and one-paced in straight under hard riding. Found to have a heart irregularity.
Urged forward from an awkward draw and forced to race wide back stretch. Lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Checked on jumped and dropped to clear last. Urged forward around turn but unable to progress and tired, dropping back.

Taken back early to sit worse than midfield, 3 off the fence. Towards the rear of the field rounding the turn, showed tremendous turn of foot from the 400m. Too strong late, and still looked to have something in hand.

Began OK and settled midfield, on the fence. Running on well in the straight, and forced a run at the 200m when blocked. Ran on well late, only outpaced by winner, and easing when clear 2nd near line.
Dropped back from the jump to eventually sit midfield, 3 wide with cover. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Only fairly away, but pushed forward to placed 2nd 2.3L off leader at the 800m. Well clear of the majority of the field on the turn. Began a run at 350m, but slightly 1 paced and lost a place late.
Pushed forward from the jump to lead by 2L over 2nd place at the 800m. Lead easily rounding the turn, but faded from the 200m, and was swamped late. Hung out under pressure late.

Dropped back early to eventually sit worse than midfield, on the rail. No clear run early in the straight, but ran on OK when coming back into the rail. Came onto heels the last 50m, but didn't affect placing.
Dropped back from the jump to sit 3rd last, 1 off the fence. Ran on OK late, with minimal urging.
Taken back from the wide gate to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence and 10L off the leader. Came widest on the turn, and ran on OK, making up ground late.
Began OK and eased forward to sit handily on the fence early. Began to run on in the straight, but was bumped and unbalanced at the 200m and never recovered, only plugging away late.
Eased forward on jumping to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Under pressure on the turn, and never finished off.
Taken forward from the wide draw to sit forward of midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Pushed from the turn, but never responded and was easing out late.
OK away and taken forward to sit just behind the leader, 1 off the fence early. Fading by the turn, and never pushed in the straight.

Began awkwardly, and positioned at the rear of the field early. Crowded out of a run and lost some ground at 800m. Asked to go at 350m, but had already lost contact with the field, and was eased out late.
Began OK, but over raced early when positioned midfield. Eased out of the race from the 250m, and found to have cardiac arrhythmia.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 4th, travelled well on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score easily.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout out, kicked clear early in straight, headed near 150M, kept on for 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, 2 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to get 3rd.

Bumped on jumping, steadied near 1200M, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back in midfield, difficult to settle near 900M, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, showed early speed to race 1-2 length back in 3rd, easy run on turn, just stayed on evenly in straight.
Average to begin, taken back to race at tail, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, angled out after 300M and made some progress.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with some cover in midfield, similar position on turn, bumped near 300M, made minor headway thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with some cover at rear, bumped and carried wider near 700M, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Bumped start, raced 3-4 lengths back in midfield, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 7 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, there to turn, showed no response in straight, never competitive.
Slowly away, recovered to race on the fence in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, weakened gradually after turning in, eased final 200M.

Placing: PU
Comment: Slightly slow out, steadied near 1300M, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, retired from the event rounding the home turn. (Lame left front leg with a swelling over the tendon region)

Soon dropped to the last few from the widest draw, made significant progress down the centre of the straight to just get up on line, driven out.
Settled just worse than midfield, shifted out for a clear run upon straightening, quickened well to hit the front 150 metres out only to be collared close to home.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, ran on under pressure to hold every chance over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Behind midfield far side, took slightly closer order when wide rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Crowded early, remained in rear to straight, shifted wide for the turn, finished off race nicely.
Ridden along from a poor draw racing mainly 3-wide one off the pace, remained similar turning for home but unable to sustain effort inside final 300 metres
Failed to muster early stages travelling towards the rear on rails, fought on steadily behind horses in the run home.
Moderate start, worked his way down back straight to lead or dispute lead rounding home bend, kept on before faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from the one draw settling in midfield, baulked for a run most of straight.
Slowly away, caught up with the backend of the field on rails approaching home bend, ran home one-paced.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on rails, baulked behind runners after straightening, made no show at the finish.
Broke well from a moderate draw, crossed to rails in front coming out of back straight, dropped out of contention inside final 250 metres.
Broke well to share the pace early, soon shifted back to one-out-one-back position, faded out of contention upon straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled just off the leaders, pace good, held up 4-2, closed off strongly when clear and scored.
Hard ridden to hold the fence and shared the lead at good pace, overhauled 150M, ran on for 2nd.
Shared the lead easily at good pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Awkward away, hard ridden to hold the spot behind the leaders, pace good, flattened 150M.
Bumped start, struggled to keep up at back, pace good, made steady ground 300M, lack room 200M.
Pushed to obtain a midfield sport, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Hard ridden to share the lead at good pace, emptied 200M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, pace good, flattened 400M.
Awkward away, hard ridden to keep up with the field, lack room 400M, ran on fairly when clear.
Never traveled comfortable towards the rear of the field.
Bumped start, never competitive at rear.
Bumped start, at rear, crowded for room 300M, no progress.
Pushed to settle 3Ls behind the leader along the fence, dashed strongly when clear 300M to take the trophy.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Prominent, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on strongly until final 100M headed by the winner, hung on for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, blocked early straight, dashed well when clear 250M.
At rear, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, finished off nicely until final 50M weakened.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader from a wide gate, battled on well until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line without any threatening.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until final 150M flattened. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led, kept on until final 250M weakened.
Failed to muster pace despite ridden along, travelled 4 wide without cover throughout, never ran on.
Sent forward to occupy the box seat, kept on fairly, flattened 250M.
Sluggish break, soon advanced to midfield on fence 4L back, edged out final turn, driven 400m, reeled in leader 130m, driven clear.
Snagged at start to race behind midfield 1 off with cover, edged 3 wide 600m, wider into stretch, shaken up 400m, closed to nick 2nd at wire.
Good start & bustled, settled 1 back on fence 950m, shifted 3 deep 550m, shaken up into stretch & led 360m, all out & headed 130m, tapered.
Broke ok, over-raced 1000m & caught 3 wide no cover midfield, 5 deep & driven 400m, stayed on dourly, just missed frame.
Moderate start, raced near rear 3 wide with cover, very wide home turn, driven 380m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Settled rail near tail, shifted 1 off 550m, switched out & ridden 400m, kept on for moderate headway.
Slow start, raced at tail 1 off, bustled 920m, under pump 750m, shifted out & hard-driven home turn, widest in run, stayed on for sound inroads.
Broke ok, taken back & settled 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 550m, wide final turn, driven 400m, crowded in run & tapered late.
Broke ok but bustled along fore of midfield 1 off with cover, scrubbed along 650m, hard-ridden turning in, weakened in run.
Awkward start, over-raced 1 off with cover near tail, niggled & to rail 600m, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on evenly.
Sharp break, niggled to dispute lead 1200m, settled close 2nd 1000m, driven 400m, found nil & weakened.
Speed to lead, joined 1200m & vied, won that battle & settled 0.5L up from 1000m, niggled into stretch, all out & headed 360m, faded out.
Fast start widest, crossed to 3 deep & niggled along handy, to 1 off 1 back 950m, forced 4 deep 550m & ridden into stretch, soon emptied.
Taken back at start, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out turning in, driven 350m, found nil & faded tamely.
Good start widest, bustled to race handy 4th 3 wide no cover, loomed up 400m, ridden 360m, had to dig & battled to lead 100m, edged away.
Broke well & prominent, soon slotted one back on rail, driven 400m, quickened to narrow lead 210m, peaked on run & headed 100m, no extra.
Broke OK, snagged back to slot 1 off behind midfield, niggled 600m, shifted out & driven 500m, edged wider turning in, grinding run to nick 3rd.
Awkward start & bustled early to 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, slotted 1 off at 800m, shifted out turning in, kept on to just miss frame.
Fast start & rousted to lead, soon headed & settled close 2nd 1 off no cover, driven 420m, battled to press lead, no extra 200m, tapered to wire.
Tardy start & bustled, progressed to 3 wide behind midfield at 550m, switched widest into stretch & driven 410m, kept on for minor headway.
Speed at break, snagged to slot 1 back 1 off, ridden 400m but not clear running until shifted out 300m, kept on one pace.
Good break on rail, drifted back to midfield, driven into stretch & shifted wide, stayed on dourly.
Sluggish start, soon at rear & niggled along, hard-ridden 410m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Sharp start, raced 1 off with cover fore of midfield, to rail 800m, shifted out & driven 400m, kept on tepidly.
Broke well, allowed to slide back to rail behind midfield, driven 410m & shifted out, plodded on one pace.
Moderate start, raced rail near rear, niggled 600m, driven into stretch, plodded on evenly.
Sharp start, rolled to lead 1100m, to rail 860m, edged out turning in & shaken up 420m, all out when headed 210m, weakened out.
Fast start wide, taken back but caught wide, slotted 1 off in last pair 650m, ridden turning in, found nil.
Jumped slowly, settled into midfield, 3 wide with cover. Unleashed strongly upon 300M to score.
Pushed forward to take the rail by 1L. Kept on strongly until 50M and beaten by the winner.
Jumped slowly and awkwardly before settling 7L behind leader. Hanged wide in the straight and raced strongly to finish third.
Eased to settle into worse than midfield, 2 wide. Ran on nicely to make ground in straight.
Rolled to settle into front of midfield. 3-1/2L behind, 2 wide with cover. Maintained one pace until final.
Eased into midfield, 5L behind, 2 wide with cover. Weakened upon 300M.
Pushed to take position in front of midfield 2L behind without cover. Kept on well until 100M, and well beaten thereafter.
Began slowly and held wide without cover 3L behind. Kept on early in straight but weakened upon 200M.
Restrained from start to hold position at back. Kept to the rear and did not have the chance to improve in the straight.
Restrained from start to take up running along the rail. Did not create an impression throughout.
Maintained forward of midfield position from inner gate. Swamped and faded out upon final 200M.
Pushed forward to obtain box seat, kept on until swamped in last 200M.
Started out from the widest gate. Never created an impression.
Began well and then eased, settling one-back, one-off. Peeled 3-wide entering straight, hit front 300m, pulled clear.
Began awkwardly, threw head about and lost ground. Ridden forward along rail to sit three back, came off fence 500m, ran on well final 300m.
Bumped, unbalanced shortly after start, made up ground quickly to grab box seat. Not much room entering straight, ran on nicely when clear 300m.
Began OK but inconvenienced 1100m, dropping four-back along the rail. Taken very wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Jumped with field, steadied 1200 when awkwardly placed, then settled 3-back, one-off. Boxed on gamely in straight without looking dangerous.
Urged forward to sit three-quarter length behind leader to turn. Drew level with leader soon after straightening then one-paced to line.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners but trapped 3-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, one-paced in straight.
Urged forward to lead on settling, then set steady pace to straight. Caught passing 300m and weakened gradually.
No early pace, settling towards rear in a one-off position. taken wide entering straight but found little under hard riding.
No early pace, settling at rear along rail. Improved position slightly around turn but found nothing in straight.
Bumped at start, shifted out bumping another runner, then steadied, dropping to last. Never competitive.
Within striking distance always, driven to lead inside 200M and gradually lengthened his advantage towards finish.
Began only fairly, hugged stand's rail and took them along at good pace, kept on well passing halfway but unable to hold off winner inside 200M.
Tucked in behind midfield, came under urging midway, stayed on moderately to go 3rd 100M out.
Settled 2Ls back from leaders, closed off steadily over final 400M.
Moved up from draw 2 to join leaders 800M, given every chance, outsprinted over final 150M and laying out under pressure.
Established a good position just off leaders, kept on one pace final 400M, no threat inside 150M.
In 2nd last for much of the way, 6Ls off the pace 400M, gradually picked up the pace towards the finish.
Not far off from leaders along nearside rail, ran on same pace under pressure inside 400M, never threatened.
Pushed along early to take up position at the fore, first to come under pressure, weakened from 400M. (Blood in trachea)
Failed to muster speed despite ridden early, not picked up pace when the race got serious, eased when beaten.
Detached in rear well off the pace, made some progress final 300M but never got back to it.
In midfield early and middle stages, dropped away rapidly inside 400M, eased. (Jockey concerned with horse's action / OVE)
Began well, ridden between horses 3L from leader in one-off position. Urged forward 3-wide at 500m, hit front 150m, held off strong challenge.
Ridden up between horses in one-off position behind leading pack. Tightened 450m, no run till 240m, challenged strongly but just failed.
Urged forward, racing fiercely 3-wide without cover outside leading pair. Took over lead passing 400m, caught 150m, boxed on.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw but held 3-wide at rear. Covered extra ground turn, very wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Began fairly, then steadied, racing between horses at rear, Improved position turn, wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Crowded out start, picked up then bumped and unbalanced 1100m, dropping behind midfield along rail. Improved turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Hard ridden from wide draw but failed to muster, settling 3-wide behind midfield. Wide around turn, urged forward 500m, one-paced final 200m.
Began well, led for a few strides before settling half length behind and inside leader. Looked chance entering straight but flattened 200m and weakened.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Urged forward at turn, no clear run till 150m when one-paced.
Jumped with field, ridden along to grab box seat but lost position, dropping 4L behind leader 800m. Looked chance at 400m but tired quickly.
Began OK, hard ridden to lead on settling. Set steady pace to 450m when passed. Weakened gradually.
Jumped well, ridden between horses in midfield to turn. Lost position entering straight and faded gradually.
Slow into stride, taken to rail but outpaced, dropping to last before turn. Never likely from then on.
Began well, and pushed forward early before dropping back to sit midfield 4-5 wide with no cover. Ran strongly in the straight. Pushed by 2nd, but found extra late.
Began well, before electing to drop back and find a position midfield on the rail. Ran on strongly from 250m, and challenged winner right to the line.

Slightly crowded on jumping before finding a position worse than midfield, 2-3 wide. Raced onto heels and was checked and unbalanced 700m. Came wide on the turn, and ran on strongly, making up a lot of ground late.
Slightly awkward to begin, but pushed forward early to lead on the rail. Held on to 50m, but a tired horse and swamped out of a placing late.
Elected to drop back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, 2-3 wide. Ran onto heels 700m when improving, before coming widest on the turn. Steadily improving late.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, before recovering to sit just worse than midfield 1 off the fence. Ran on fairly in the straight picking off a few slower ones.
Jumped well from the widest gate, and pushed forward early to share the lead 1 off the fence. One paced in the straight, and dropped back quickly from the 200m.
Began awkwardly, before pushing forward to sit just behind the leaders on the rail. Stuck with leaders until 250m but didn't kick, and faded out late.
Began OK, but had to come across from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield, 4-5 wide. Came wide on the turn, but only battled on fairly and was easing out late.
Missed the kick, and dropped out to be a very conspicuous last. Caught up by the turn, and improved in the run home but had too much ground to make up.

Only fairly away, and lost a plate early. Reluctant to settle early, sitting midfield 3 wide, and checked off heels at the 1200m. Hampered and taken wider at 700m. Race was over by the turn, and battled to the line.
Began well, but happy to sit midfield 1 off the fence early. Came wider on the turn, and awkward on heels briefly. Never saw out the trip, and never pushed out late.
Began OK, and taken forward to sit in a handy position 3L off the leader 1 off the fence. Fading before the turn, gave nothing late and was eased out.
Began on terms, and taken forward early to sit just behind the leaders 1 off the fence. Under pressure by the turn, and had nothing to give in the straight. Eased up late when well beaten.

Settled one back in 3rd on rails, shuffled 2 back in 4th when the joint leader outside made forward move for rails run passing the Rock, commenced move entering straight hitting the front 100 metres out, caught close to home.
Disputed lead early, took up running and rails run passing the 800 metres, led until headed 100 metres out.
Settled 2-wide in 4th 2 lengths back, similar turning for home, ran home one-paced.
Held narrow advantage early, headed coming off the Rock, fought on under pressure but lost placing close to home.
Jumped moderately, picked up gradually along rails to reach midfield at Rock briefly, saved ground on rails turning in, making ground under pressure until running out of room inside final 200 metres.
Settled one from last from a wide gate, came under pressure upon straightening, never nearer.
Settled in last few on rails, kept on one pace under pressure in straight.
Soon taken back from the widest draw, trailed the field throughout.
Hard ridden for a prominent spot 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, clocked slow sectionals, hung on until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground.
Behind midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to back from wide draw, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Very slow away, trapped 3 wide at rear, no progress.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Punched forward to occupy the box seat, ran on strongly to score by a neck.
Pushed to midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well to get 2nd.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Began smartly, driven forward to take the fence and led from a wide gate, kept on nicely until final 100M flattened.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Taken back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight. (Questioned for riding)
Eased to rear from a wide gate, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, ran on only fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls off the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Ridden forward to settle in a prominent position 2 wide without cover, found nothing when placed under pressure. (Substantial amount of blood in the trachea)
Driven at break to settle midfield on rail, bustled 600m, smart progress & switched wide 400m, powered on outer to lead 220m, kept on to hold off challenger.
Snagged back at start, sat last pair 1 off, bustled along 600m, driven 420m, shifted wide final turn, rattled home on outer to press winner at wire.
Speed to lead, snagged rail & headed 1300m, off heels 1020m & settled 1 back, in pocket turning in, extricated & driven 220m, boxed on one pace.
Rousted from gate, sat rail fore of midfield, niggled 600m, driven & shifted out 320m, bumped 250m, boxed on evenly.
Broke ok, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 420m, kept on tamely.
Awkward start & bustled, recovered to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, outpaced on turn, plugged on one pace.
Broke ok, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 420m, kept on tamely.
Smart start to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, hard-ridden final turn, outpaced & faded in run.
Rousted to lead 1300m, to rail 950m, headed 650m & ridden to vie for advantage, led again 420m, all out & headed 220m, faded out.
Missed break, taken to rail & raced at tail, bustled 500m, driven into home turn, plugged on tamely.
Tardy start, rolled forward to track leader 1 off no cover, 1 back 1 off from 650m & niggled, driven 400m, 3 wide final turn, bumped 250m & weakened.
Moderate start & bumped, harried early 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, lost cover 950m, pushed on to narrow lead 650m, headed 420m & driven, emptied & faded.
Sharp start, snagged to 1 off with cover midfield, briefly forced 3 wide no cover at 750m, swung wide final turn, shaken up 300m to close, led close home.
Fast start, bustled to lead 1120m, to rail 900m, niggled along, hard-ridden 250m, tapered in run home.
Smart start, settled rail midfield, shifted 1 off 750m but outpaced a touch exiting back stretch, hard-ridden final turn, shifted deep, closed to 3rd at wire.
Fast break, caught handy 3 wide no cover, snagged 950m to slot fore of midfield on rail at 750m, driven final turn, switched out 300m, kept on evenly.
Fast start to lead, snagged & headed 1120m to race 1 back 1 off, shifted wide home turn & driven to go brief 2nd 200m, emptied & swamped.
Tardy start, sat near tail on inner, shifted out 430m & ridden wide into stretch, plugged on moderately.
Slow break, raced 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 650m & some progress on turn, shifted out & driven into stretch, kept on one pace.
Broke well, speed to press leader 1 off, settled 2nd at 900m, niggled along, hard-ridden 250m, tapered in run home.
Taken back from wide gate & raced at tail 1 off with cover, niggled from 900m, very wide & driven turning n, kept on tamely.
Good break, raced 1 back on rail, bustled 500m, driven turning in, found little & weakened out.
Prominent at break, outpaced & slid back to near rear on rail, niggled 800m, outpaced & under pump 500m, struggled & faded in stretch.
Began fairly and rolled into a prominent position, 1-1/2L behind, 2 wide with cover. Shifted out upon final 300M to run and stormed home to score.

Very slow to jump. Recovered well to take up position in the rear and raced along the rail. Made steady headway rounding the home turn, widest runner turning in, continued on to lost by less than a length.
Began well from a good draw. Settled in a forward position 1L behind, 2 wide without cover. Maintained position to come home third.
Jumped well and raced into the lead before shifted in for racing along the rail. Kept on evenly in straight.
Began slowly before easing into midfield and settled 4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Finished off evenly in the straight.
Bumped upon starting but recovered well to obtain midfield position. Shifted out to obtain clear running position in straight but never improved.
Settled towards the rear. Ride home one paced.
Restrained well back from the widest gate. Stayed always to the rear and created no further impression.
Raced into forward of midfield from gate 1. Maintained position 1L behind along the rail. Faded out in last 100M.
Restrained from start to take position in worse of midfield. Shifted out wide to obtain clear running but no dash.
Shifted across behind runners after a slow start from gate 11. Never ran on.
Jumped well to maintain forward position, 3 wide without cover throughout. Faded after home turn and well beaten. (Questioned for running)
Pressed forward but wide to lead 1400m cutting to rail 1300m. Joined by another 1100m, nosed ahead 500m, kicked clear 300m, held on well under intense pressure.
Bumped shortly after start, tightened 1400m, settling one-back, one-off 1200m. Urged forward 400m, looked chance 150m, just failed.
Began fairly, taken in gradually settling at rear in one-off position. Niggled at passing 500m, widest into straight, finished strongly down centre track.
Jumped with field, no pace, dropping four-back along rail. Swung wide into straight, ran on well but hung in closing stages.
Began OK but raced fiercely first turn and didn't settle until 700m when three-back along fence. Badly held up for run 200m, shifted out abruptly, finished strongly.
Began well but not pressured, dropping to last along rail. Urged forward passing 500m, picked up momentum 200m but not fully tested in restricted room.
Ridden early to hold rail, settling behind leader first turn. Urged forward 350m but steadied 200m when denied run and not properly tested.
Ridden forward between horses, settling three-back, one-off. Taken a little wide entering straight and boxed on gamely under hard riding.
Bumped start, ridden to stay with leaders but awkwardly placed 1400m. Drew alongside leader 1100m, kept on fairly in straight until flattened 100m.
Steadied soon after start, shifted in, settling in one-off position behind midfield. Very wide in straight but found little under hard riding.
Allowed an uncontested lead, kept on soundly entering straight and had enough in reserves over final 200M, held off pursuing rivals comfortably.
Overcame wide barrier to sit just behind leaders, chased home winner inside 300M but always held, sound effort under top weight.
Badly hampered at the start, 3 wide no cover in mid-division, stayed on well to claim 3rd late stages. (lost left front plate at start)
Settled 3Ls off the pace, went 3rd mid-straight, battled on and slowing getting to top 2, beaten into 4th late stages.
A shade keen early stages, restrained to race behind midfield, progress over final 200M, made good late impression.
Taken back to rear from wide barrier, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, stayed on under pressure.
Badly hampered at the start, settled down 5Ls back in rear group, ran on mildly final 300M, not reach leaders.
Held up 4Ls off the pace along the fence, kept on same pace turning home, never a serious threat to leaders.
Restrained to the rear early, 3-wide bid 600M, stayed on same pace entering straight, steadied near 100M, not troubled leaders.
Chased leader, ridden and no extra 300M out, weakened towards the line.
Saved ground from inside draw, never far off in 4th, but was readily outpaced 300M.
Shifted out abruptly at start and badly unbalanced, proved difficult to settle middle stages, 3-wide at the rear making the turn, first to be beaten.

Began well, soon taken back to settle off the pace near midfield, about 3L back in 3rd rounding home bend, commenced move entering straight, took charge just inside the 200 metres, won with ease.

Jumped moderately, took up running after the first 200m kicking over 2L clear around home bend, remained similar approaching straight, came under pressure on straightening only to be overshadowed inside the 200m.
Soon taken back from a wide draw, travelled towards the rear most of way to straight, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.

Slow out, soon picked up to midfield near rails, slightly worse when pace quickened in 2nd quarter, commenced move given strong reminders passing the 500m, made short-lived effort to reach remote 3rd briefly inside the 200m.
Soon taken well back from the widest draw, trailed the field most of way to straight, widest turning for home, fought on steadily down the centre of the straight but never threatening.
Settled just worse than midfield near the rails, found nothing in straight.
Ridden along off the rails from a middle gate, settled in 2nd just over 2L off the lead approaching home bend, faded out of contention shortly after straightening.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Jumped fairly, niggled along on rails to keep in touch, gave ground steadily from coming out of back straight.
Eased to rear, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M to score.
At back 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M flattened.
Eased to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, blocked and checked 300M, ran on well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, settled just off the lead 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, weakened 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, no turn of foot when clear.
Behind midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, soon emptied 300M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Shortly after the start commenced to buck for a considerably distance, tailed out.
Rolled forward to settle in a prominent position with cover, ran on well to score by 1/2L.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, finished off strongly to get 2nd, beaten by 1/2L.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on steadily for 3rd. (Questioned for riding)
Pushed to settle worse than midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader along the fence, dashed well for 4th.
Pressed forward to take the lead from a wide gate, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Rolled to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off fairly until final furlong weakened. (Lame right front the day after racing)
Raced midfield, travelled 4 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Taken back to near last, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, travelled nicely until final 300M, failed to respond when placed under pressure. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Fast start & prominent, soon snagged to camp midfield 1 off with cover, edged out & driven 430m, quickened centre track to lead 220m, edged clear.
Missed break, soon recovered to race midfield on rail, restrained on heels 700m, not clear run & crowded, daylight 300m, driven to 2nd 100m, always held.
Smart break, raced 2.5L 5th on rail, ridden 450m & shifted out, progress to challenge early in straight, boxed on but always held.
Broke OK, dropped in to sit behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m & shifted out, driven wide into stretch, stayed on for minor inroads.
Snagged back at start & raced near tail 1 off with cover, driven 420m & shifted out in stretch, stayed on for solid headway.
Decent break, soon disputed lead on outer, settled close 2nd 1 off at 1300m, pressed lead 1000m, niggled 500m & driven into stretch, led 260m, all out & headed 200m, faded.
Broke ok & rousted a touch, rolled to lead 1400m, keen 1300m & crossed to rail, continued to over-race until settled on turn, shaken up 420m, headed 260m & tapered.
Smart break, nudged along to race 1 back 1 off, niggled 600m, 3 wide & driven into stretch, kept on one pace.
Speed to lead initially, headed 1400m & camped 1 back on rail from 1300m, ridden along 500m, plodded on tepidly.
Slow start widest, unable to slot & raced 3 wide no cover near tail, under pump 550m & hard-ridden into stretch, tepid run home.
Smart break but lacked toe & soon niggled along near tail on rail, hard-ridden 410m, plodded on one pace until tapered late.
Taken back from wide gate, soon niggled at tail, 1L adrift & driven into stretch, plugged on tamely, never a factor.
Speed to lead & bustled initially, soon settled in front, 1L clear turning in, challenged & driven 350m, kept on & edged away close home.
Good break, bustled along to race handy but trapped 3 wide no cover, rolled to 2nd turning in, driven to challenge down stretch, always held & tapered close home.
Broke ok, snared rail 1200m & raced midfield, edged out final turn & driven, advanced to 3rd 270m, closed gradually to wire, always held.
Broke well, bustled early & 3 wide with cover, pushed on to slot 1 back 1 off at 900m, niggled & outpaced 600m, swung out & driven into stretch, stayed on dourly.
Moderate start, raced rail behind midfield, switched out turning in, driven 400m, stayed on for minor headway.
Sharp break, lacked pace & taken back, soon niggled 1 off with cover near rear, switched 3 wide & ridden 600m for minor advance, wide home turn, plugged on moderately.
Taken back from wide gate, raced last pair but trapped wide no cover, over-raced 900m, driven 400m & shifted widest in run, stayed on for minor late inroads.
Started well, settled back 1 off with cover midfield, shifted 3 deep & ridden 550m, wider into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Sluggish break, raced at tail 1 off, improved a spot on turn, driven 400m, kept on for minor late headway.
Broke well, bustled early to settle 1 back on fence, driven along 600m, found little in stretch & tapered out.
Taken back at start, slotted 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted out final turn, driven 350m, struggled in run home.
Slow start, bustled early to race rail near tail, last trio & ridden under pressure 550m, struggled in run home.
Smart start & pushed on to sit close 2nd outside leader, niggled 600m, driven into stretch, soon emptied & weakened out.
Jumped well and quickly took lead by 1/2L along the rail. Never looked challenged in straight and cruised to victory.
Began right up to speed before settling 1/2L off the leader, 2 wide without cover. Ran on strongly until weakened upon final 100M.
Settled front of midfield 1L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Kept on well to finish third but never challenged the first two.
Began fairly. Raced wide without cover, 3L behind the leader. Continued to run on consistently for dead heat 4th.
Slotted in midfield 3L off, 3 wide with cover. Finished off the race evenly for dead heat 4th.
At rear 5L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Shifted wide for a clear run upon straightening, before finishing the race off nicely.
Ridden along from a wide draw racing mostly 1L off, 3 wide without cover. Maintained moderately until weakened upon final 100M.
Took position at rear along the rail after shifting in from a wide draw, 5L behind the leader. Kept to the rear until last 200M when room opened for running.
Began fairly and settled worse than midfield 4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Kept on and weakened upon final 150M.
Jumped well before settling worse than midfield along the rail, 4L off. Failed to muster speed when ridden along in straight.
Shifted across from the widest draw to take position at rear 6L behind, 3 wide with cover. Made no progress in straight, and was never competitive.
Showed early speed to take position in front of midfield along the rail, 2 L off. Weakened in straight and swamped upon final 250M.
Began well, led for a few strides before cutting to rail in third sport 800m. Urged forward from 400m, hit front 120m, held off late challenge.
Began well but unable go early speed, dropping behind midfield. Switched out passing 300m, finished strongly to just fail.
Began OK, hard ridden to lead passing 950m then steadied pace. Kicked 2.5L clear on straightening, caught 120m, weakened but held 3rd.
Crowded out start, pressed forward from wide draw, settling in 2nd outside leader passing 900m. Boxed on gamely in straight.
Began awkwardly, got close to heels 1000m, then raced fiercely after 800m. Shifted out 700m, widest in straight, kept on steadily under hard riding.
Began fairly, beaten for early speed, dropping to near last in one-off position. Taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily.
Slow into stride, ridden to make up ground settling three-back, one-off. Stayed inside entering straight and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Slow into stride, ridden to make up ground close to rail but kept behind midfield. Switched out 350m and kept on fairly.
Began OK, urged forward but difficult to settle passing 1000m. Kept in one-off position 4L from leader to straight, boxed on one-paced.
Jumped with field but no early speed settling close to rail towards rear. Steadied 400m when bumped, no clear running top of straight, one-paced.
Began fairly, unable to go early pace and soon last along rail. Never likely.
Pressed forward from outside draw but held wide in midfield without cover. Covered extra ground turn, still wide in straight, tired quickly.
Held up in mid-division, saved ground along inside from draw 1, came through to lead near 150M, eased when well in control final 50M.
Obtained a trailing position along the inside, every chance form 300M, not matched winner's acceleration mid-straight, well held.
Pushed along early, took lead before turn, battled on well entering straight but no impression with winner 150M, held on for 3rd just.
Tracked the pace, proved difficult to settle when steadied for cover 1000M, effort inside 400M, loomed a threat 250M, kept on steadily late stages, lost out on 3rd narrowly.
Towards the rear 4Ls back, switched out 300M, closed off well, nearest line.
Sent forward to track leader, vied for lead from 450M, outsprinted 200M, one pace towards finish.
Settled down midfield, chased leaders 400M, stayed on, not clearest run inside 200M, checked near line.
Held up midfield, 3-wide no cover from 900M, inclined to lay out home turf, found less than expected when driven, eased when no danger passing 150M. (Blood in trachea)
Eased on jumping from 12, raced 3-wide towards the rear, ran on same pace to line, never on terms.
Dropped back to rear 6Ls off the pace, brought to outside 400M but not making progress on leaders.
Began awkwardly, near last 5-6Ls off the pace, driven along 500M but gave no response, soon detached form main group.
Settled down 4Ls back along the fence, badly outpaced 400M, soon beaten.
Crowded, unbalanced start, shifted out 1000m when checked, wide without cover 800m, wide into straight but accelerated steadily to win on the line.
Began well, grabbing one-off, one-back spot but lost position 1000m. Urged forward top of straight, hit front 200m, battled but pipped on line.
Began OK but caught wide and allowed to stride forward 1000m to lead 800m. Kicked clear entering straight, caught 200m, kept on well.
Shifted out start, ridden vigorously but slow to muster, checked 1000m, dropping three-back the fence. No run till 300m and finished off nicely.
Began fairly, ridden along but hampered before 1000m dropping to last. Taken wide entering straight and finished off strongly.
Began fairly, caught wide in midfield, strode forward passing 1000m settling one-back, one-off. Boxed on steadily in straight under hard riding.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw but held three-wide at rear. Covered extra ground turn, widest in straight, finished off fairly.
No early speed, dropping to last along rail approaching 800m. Made up some ground around turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Began well but not much speed and held in one-off position towards rear. Switched out in straight but denied run 200m and steadied 100m.
Under the whip early, taking lead 1200m, shaded by another 800m but kept on well to 200m before running on empty, faded.
Hard ridden early to stay with the pace, settling in box seat. Under pressure turning for home but tired soon after passing 300m and faded.
OK to begin and only eased forward early to sit just forward of midfield 1 off the fence. Battled away early in the straight before showing a good turn off foot in the last 100m to win it late.
Anticipated the kick, and cruised forward early to sit in a handy position on the rails. Strong run in the straight, and looked the winner at 100m, before being taken by the fast finishing winner.
OK away, but checked early and dropped back to worse than midfield, on the fence. Never got a clear run until the 200m, and showed plenty of dash late to take 3rd on the line.
Began OK, before being hampered early and finding a position midfield 1 off the fence. Wanted to lay out under pressure in the straight, and was weakening slightly late, and just rolled for 3rd.
Jumped well, and pushed forward to lead early. Battled on gamely in the straight, but never kicked and overtaken late.
Began OK, and drifted forward to eventually sit in a handy position 1 off the fence. Well placed late, but slightly 1 paced and dropped back.

Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, on the rails. Ran on strongly in the straight before being held up 300m. Regained momentum after getting clear and finished off OK.

OK away from the wide barrier, but couldn't find an early sit, and dropped back to be worse than midfield 3 wide with no cover. Ran on steadily in the straight. Taken wider 200m, but not finishing well enough.
Began only fairly, but cruised forward early to sit forward of midfield on the rail. Battled gamely in the straight, but only 1 paced and never figured in the finish.
OK away, and dropped back early to be placed just worse than midfield on the fence. Dropped back to near last on the turn. Finished off OK, but had too much to make up in the quick run to the line.
Began well and pushed forward early to sit just behind the leader. Well positioned at the top of the straight, but dropped out from the 350m, and gave nothing late.
Dawdled out of the gate before finding a position slightly worse than midfield, on the fence. Only battled on fairly, and never threatened in the straight
Taken back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field, 2-4 wide. Came widest on the turn, and only plugged away late.

Dropped back from the jump to sit a clear last, 10L off the leader. Attempted to improve mid race, but was forced 3 wide with no cover. One paced in the straight, and eased when well out of contention late.

Settled in midfield from a poor draw, came under pressure approaching home turn, quickened well under pressure down the centre of the straight to prevail late.

Jumped fairly from a poor draw, gradually settled in the last, one from last rounding home bend before saving more ground on rails turning in, fought on well between runners near the centre of the straight.
Soon taken back from a wide draw settling just worse than midfield one off the rails, went wider turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Slightly slow out and slow to muster, settled just off the pace on rails and a close-up 3rd turning in, hit the front briefly inside the 200 metres but soon swamped by the placegetters.
Broke well, niggled along and sharing the pace before gaining narrow advantage halfway down back straight, held same into straight, headed inside the 200 metres and ran on one-paced.
Not far off in one-out-one-back position, similar turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Well there just outside the leader, came under pressure to challenge turning in but unable to quicken the length of the straight.
Settled in midfield on rails, came slightly closer around the bend angling off the rails to challenge entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Began fairly from a poor draw, with leaders early before shifting back to midfield while wide throughout far side, remained wide on home turn and ran home one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw for rails run, soon picked up to rear of midfield along rails saving ground on home turn, found nothing under pressure.
Travelled prominently 3-wide without cover, gave ground from home bend.
Ridden along early, soon dropped to last few.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M.
3 back on the fence, improved along the rails from 450M, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased to take box seat, raced keenly, no turn of foot in straight.
Behind midfield, progressed along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to rear for cover from wide draw, harmed by the slow pace, trapped wide throughout, dashed well in straight despite negative racing situations.
At back 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Very slow away, midfield 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress in straight.
At back, trapped wide throughout, never progressed.
Hard ridden forward, faded 300M.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by 1-1/4Ls.
Prominent, however raced wide without cover, made an early move to obtain a position closer to the rail 900M, suited by the slow pace, fought on gamely for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow tempo, dashed well for 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow sectionals, finished off steadily to get 4th.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat from the outside gate, suited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace to the wire.
Settled worse than midfield, 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow pace, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly.
Jumped slowly and then failed to muster speed, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along early, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
At rear, travelled 9.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, made no impression in straight. (Lame right fore next day)
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, weakened soon after straightening.
Always at rear, never a factor. (Lame right fore next day)
Speed to lead on fence, headed 800m & raced 1L 2nd, shaken up turning in, driven to lead 150m, drew clear.
Steady start, rolled wide no cover midfield until slotted 1 off at 450m, switched out on turn & shaken up centre track 300m, closed to edge 2nd late.
Speedy break, raced wide until slotted 1 off 1 back 700m, niggled 600m, driven 4 wide into stretch, ran on to contest minors.
Taken back to 1 off with cover near rear, shifted wide final turn & ran on to just miss frame.
Fast start, rousted 1 off to lead 800m, driven 1L clear at 600m, all out & headed 150m, swamped in run home.
Taken back at break to 3 wide with cover near rear, hard-ridden & widest into stretch, closed off for fair inroads.
Tardy break, bustled & advanced to race 1 back on rail, niggled 600m, 3L 3rd & driven final turn, plugged on evenly.
Broke ok, raced back of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven turning in, plugged on for modest headway.
Lacked pace at start, raced rail near rear & bustled throughout, shifted out & hard-ridden 300m, never a factor but kept on past beaten horses.
Started ok, bustled along fore of midfield 1 off, to rail 500m & under the pump, hard-ridden into straight, one-paced & tapered.
Moderate start, soon bustled on rail to hold its berth back of midfield, hard-ridden into stretch, plodded home tamely.
Slow start, soon 4L detached at tail & niggled along, well adrift & struggling turning in, found nil.
Led at start & crossed to rail, eased & headed 1450m to settle 1 back, shaken up turning in, quickened on inner to lead 150m, held on under pressure.
Broke ok, rousted early to press lead & 3 deep 1st turn, slotted 1 off no cover at 1250m to race 1L 2nd, driven 3 deep to lead turning in, headed 150m, battled on but held.
Started ok, rolled to camp 3 back on rail, driven 320m, 1L back when shifted 1 off 200m & driven to challenge, closed on lead but held close home.
Good break, soon settled rail back of midfield, off fence & driven 300m, switched out 250m & bumped rival, solid closer without threatening.
Broke ok, taken back to sit 1 off with cover back of midfield, shifted out & driven 310m, bumped 250m, stayed on ok.
Smart break, settled handy 4th 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, boxed on one pace centre track.
Tardy start, rolled 1 off to lead 1450m, clear & to rail 1250m, set tempo, swung off rail turning in & headed, tapered to wire.
Tardy start, sat 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 500m, shifted 3 deep & driven 400m, widest into stretch, one-paced in run.
Taken back to race at tail 1 off, niggled 600m, driven final turn & widest in stretch run, plugged on moderately.
Lacked toe at start & bustled, settled rail near rear, driven 350m & shifted out, plodded on weakly.
Began from widest gate. Settled 1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide without cover. Ran strongly in straight and cruised to victory.
Settled worse than midfield along the rail, 3-1/2L behind the leader. Came off rail upon final 100M and finished off well for 2nd.
Urged forward to take up lead on settling. Raced along the rail steadily before caught passing final 200M.
Began well and quickly grabbed box seat, 1L behind the leader. Shifted wide when straightening for a clear running before finishing off steadily.
Took up position in midfield and raced along the rail, 3L behind the leader. Kept on one pace to the line.
Pushed forward to settle for position front of midfield 1-1/2L off the leader, 2 wide with cover. Shifted wide in straight but never improved.
Settled just behind midfield 5L off, 3 wide with cover. Failed to muster speed in straight and weakened upon final 100M.
Maintained forward of midfield position from wide gate 1-1/2L behind the leader, 3 wide without cover. Kept on fairly but weakened after final 150M.
Rolled into midfield 3-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Found no extra after straightening.
Began slowly from inner gate and rolled into position at rear 5L off, 2 wide with cover. Was never involved.
Eased back after the start, settled 6L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Never improved.
Settled at rear along the rail, 6L off the leader. Never a factor.
Began well, ridden to hold box seat, travelled comfortably to straight, blocked attempting inside run, switched out 200m and finished strongly.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling. Set steady pace, shifted out turning for home but cut in again, caught 200m but kept on well.
Ridden forward, settling one-back, one-off. Lost momentum when swung wide but picked up against from 100m and finished strongly.
Began well, unable handle early pace dropping three back the rail. Took inside run in straight and kept on steadily.
Jumped with field, settling in one-off position behind midfield. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Began OK, no speed, taken to fence settling four-back from leader. Shifted out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Began awkwardly, hard ridden but failed to muster, settling at rear away from rail. Never in a challenging position.
Began awkwardly, shifted in and bumped another, urged forward settling three-back, one-off. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Began well, shifted across behind horses to find cover, settling behind midfield. One-paced in straight. Lame left front leg.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in one-off position at rear. Switched in turning for home but only one-paced.
Began well, sitting half length behind leader. Lay out 400m, shifted in under pressure 300m, faded. Found to be a roarer. Performance considered unacceptable.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon last. Trailed field thereafter.
Sped to the lead, took them along at good pace first 800M, still comfortably in front 400M, kept on well under 10 lb claiming rider, well in control late stages.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden early, settled down 7-8Ls off the pace, produced fastest 400M finish to go 2nd just in time.
Held up midfield 5Ls behind leader, saved ground to home straight, stayed on for 3rd but well held by winner.
Moved forward to sit just behind the pace, chased eventual winner from 350M but always held, lost 2 placings near line.
Settled down 8Ls behind leader, still plenty to do passing 500M, soon driven along, stayed on well outside.
Held up in mid-division, mild bid turning home, gave out final 100M.
Eased to the rear, not hurried nearly 10Ls off the pace middle stages, taken wide 350M and closed off moderately.
Took up trailing position behind leaders, came under pressure 500M and didn't respond to riding, weakened mid-straight.
Held up 4Ls back in mid-division, raced along the 2-path, gave only limited response, steadily faded late.
Caught 3-wide early stages, strolled forward to track leader, weakened inside 300M.
Slow to begin, settled at rear 10Ls off the pace, outpaced 450M and had nothing to offer.
