Worked from a wide draw to lead on rails after the first 200 metres, steadied pace and maintained narrow advantage around the bend, kicked over 1L clear after straightening, held on under pressure closing stages.
Broke well from a wide draw, settled wide in forward of midfield, gained closer up 3-wide around home bend, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Sluggish at start, in last few early, took closer order 3-wide to be midfield around the bend, sustained progress in home straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well from a wide draw, settled just off the pace in 3rd far side, gained outside leader when pace slackened on the bend, unable to sustain effort in the run home.
Niggled along early from the one draw settling just off the pace, awkwardly placed on heels of leader when pace steadied home bend, made no show in straight.
Close up early, settled in 5th just better than midfield, steadied behind heels 800 metres out, similar position turning for home, produced some late impression inside final 100 metres.
Settled at the back, wide around home bend and wider turning in, fought on steadily down the centre of straight but without threatening.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to straight, ran on under pressure past well-beaten horses.
Ridden along on rails in midfield, steadied behind heels about 1100 metres out, faded from midfield into straight.
Slightly slow out, settled towards the rear on rails, faded gradually in straight.
Never better than midfield, gave ground noticeably from towards the rear into straight.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, lack room 4-2, ran on strongly when clear and scored.
Pushed forward, just off the leaders 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, flattened 200M.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the slow tempo, held ground in straight.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot in straight.
Pushed to hold a midfield spot 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
On jumping got its head in the air and lost a considerable amount of ground after being very slow to leave the barrier stalls. Tailed off most trip, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Driven forward to take the lead along the fence at very slow sectionals, kept on strongly and scored by 1-1/4L.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the very slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Camped handy, benefited by the very slow pace, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Hard ridden early to settle worse than midfield , 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the very slow sectionals, made ground steadily for 4th.
Pushed forward to settle 1L behind the leader, suited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, one paced home.
On jumping bounded in the air and lost a considerable amount of ground, never looked likely thereafter.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Raced midfield, trapped wide without cover throughout, never looked likely. (Substantial amount of blood in its trachea)
Always at rear, never a factor. (Heart irregularity)
Speedy start & prominent early, soon to rail & settled 3rd, edged 1 off no cover 1150m, driven 400m, quickened to lead 180m & drew away.
Broke well but outpaced a touch, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, driven into final turn, progress to 3rd 270m, kept on to 2nd without threatening.
Rousted at break, prominent & 4 wide 1st turn, led 1200m & scooted 2L clear on rail, ridden 400m, all out & headed 180m, tapered to wire.
Smart break, snagged back to midfield 1 off with cover, driven 450m, ran on evenly.
Snagged at break to race rail near tail, ridden 450m, switched out in stretch, ran on centre track for solid late headway.
Tardy start, settled midfield 3 wide with cover, driven turning in, stayed on centre track for minor inroads.
Fair start, outpaced & niggled to go forward, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, driven 450m, kept on one pace.
Broke well, raced handy on rail, 3.5L 4th & niggled 550m, under pump turning in, outpaced & tapered to wire.
Fast start to lead 3 wide into 1st turn, crossed to rail but restrained & headed 1200m, sat 2L 2nd 1 back, ridden 450m, found nil & faded weakly.
Snagged at break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven for progress 500m, plugged on evenly.
Smart break but immediately outpaced & bustled, slid back to midfield on rail, over-raced 850m, niggled 700m, driven 550m, struggled in run home.
Taken back & raced 2nd last, niggled along 3 deep with cover, driven 500m, widest into stretch, plodded home tamely.
Taken back at break, raced at tail, soon detached & bustled, tailed off turning for home & eased.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Rousted to sit prominently 1st turn, settled 1 off 1 back but hung out on turn 1200m, wide on course & pulled up in back stretch.
Speed to lead, snagged rail 1040m & headed, stalked handy 3 back, switched out & driven 300m, quickened to lead 110m, edged away.
Sharp break to 1 back on rail, checked off heels 1000m & shuffled to midfield, switched 1 off 600m, ridden into stretch & shifted out, ran on to nick 2nd, no match for winner.
Sharp break, led 1 off at 1040m, to rail 950m & restrained, headed 850m & sat 1 back, shifted 1 off final turn, driven 400m to lead 320m, headed 110m, tapered & lost 2nd at wire.
Good start, raced handy 3 wide no cover, 4 deep turning in & driven, boxed on evenly.
Slow start, raced rail near tail, shifted out on turn, driven 400m, kept on for minor inroads centre track.
Fast start & rousted wide initially, trapped without cover & rolled to lead 850m, to rail 750m, under pressure when hard-ridden 390m, headed 320m & faded.
Slow start & raced at tail, shifted very wide into stretch & driven 400m, closed dourly deep on track for minor inroads.
Good start, taken back from wide, eventually slotted 1 off near tail, raced keenly, shifted out on turn, driven 410m, checked 350m, shaken up again 300m, kept on evenly.
Sluggish start, niggled 3 deep with cover midfield, settled 1 off on turn, shifted wide & driven into stretch, emptied 250m & faded.
Good start, raced 1 off with cover midfield, 3 wide turning in, driven 400m but outpaced, struggled in fading run home.
Tardy start & rousted wide no cover to midfield, 4 wide & awkward 900m, slotted 3 deep with cover on turn, driven 570m & very wide into stretch, found nil & tailed off.
Settled worse than midfield 3-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Obtained clear running upon final 350M, demonstrated a strong finish to score.
Jumped well and ridden along to grab box seat. Shifted out to obtain clear running upon final 200M, kept finding but only to be beaten by a nose.
Pushed to camp handy 1/2L off the leader, 2 wide without cover. Suited by the slow tempo and continued to run on steadily for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield 3-1/2L behind the leader, 3 wide with cover. Despite the slow tempo, dashed well to get 4th.
Began slowly and settled towards the rear 5L off, 2 wide with cover. Despite hampered by the slow pace, made some ground in straight.
Pushed forward to take position front of midfield 2-1/2L behind the leader, 3 wide with cover. Ran on one pace to finish.
Started from a wide barrier and raced to camp handy 1-1/2L off, 3 wide without cover. Hampered by the slow pace, swamped upon final 150M.
Shifted in from a wide barrier to race along the rail towards the rear, 5-1/4L behind the leader and never looked likely.
Rolled to the lead and led the field at slow sectionals, remained along the rail in straight but swamped upon final 100M.
Raced forward to take position forward of midfield 2-1/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Was bumped upon final 200M, and finished only fairly.
Began from widest gate then shifted in behind across other runners. Remained at rear and never looked a factor.
Restrained from gate 1 to take position worse than midfield, lost ground in Home Bend, not likely from then on.
Began well, ridden forward to sit 1L behind leader at turn, hit front and kicked clear 400m, coasted to line holding off late challenge.
Jumped with field, taken to rail but shuffled three-back passing 1050m. No clear run till 300m, shifted in and finished strongly.
Urged forward from outside draw, racing three wide before settling two-back, one-off at turn. Had clear run entering straight and ran on well.
Hard ridden wide to take lead passing 1150m before cutting to fence at turn. Caught soon after straightening but battled on gamely.
Crowded out at start, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Held up top of straight, switched out and ran on steadily.
Began fairly, unable hold position and unbalanced when crossed, dropping back. Had to shift out several times in straight to get clear running, finished off fairly.
Began fairly from wide draw, settling towards rear in one-off position. Urged forward turn, switch out straight but one-paced final 200m.
Pressed forward inside leader to 1100m before slipping into box seat around turn. Looked chance top of straight but only one-paced from 300m.
Jumped sideways at start, ridden to find cover in midfield but left wide without cover from 900m. Hard ridden in straight but failed to respond.
Began OK, not pressed, racing in midfield in one-off position. Shown whip early in straight but found little.
Began well, urged forward inside leading pack before settling three-back along rail. Under pressure turning for home but found nothing and faded.
Began awkwardly, shifted across runners from wide draw, settling in one-off position at rear. Urged forward at turn but didn't respond.
Slow into stride and soon last, trailing field. Never competitive.

Shifted in behind runners early stages, settled 5Ls back along rails, was merely cantering into contention inside 300M, driven out near 200M and quickened up impressively against quality field, soon well clear.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, responded well when driven out 400M, went 2nd near 100M but no match with impressive winner.
Taken back from wide barrier, 5Ls back towards the rear, brought wide for run 400M, stayed on well to claim 3rd near line.
Reserved in midpack 4Ls off the pace, kept to inside throughout, did best work late stages for 4th, no threat to winner though.
Sent forward as expected, on the pace but caught 3-wide until 700M, kept on steadily before flattening out late stages.
Settled 3-wide in the group chasing the pace, left with no cover 700M, pushed along 450M, lacked a strong closing response, no threat 150M.
Waited with behind mid-division, stayed on when guided to outside of field passing 250M but was not a threat over this inadequate trip.
Stalked leaders, loomed a threat early straight, brief effort to challenge for the lead, evened out final 200M.
Hustled along early, took lead 950M and set sound pace upfront, fought on early straight but couldn't sustain run, gave way 200M.
Up with early leaders, took a trailing position before home turn, had every chance turning in, ran home one paced however.
Settled down 3Ls back in midfield, not quickened behind leaders, held up by weakening rival late stages and not able to be ridden out. (Lame next day)
Outpaced from the start, detached from field 1000M, never involved. (Lame next day)
Began fairly, taken to centre track, made ground steadily to hit front 150m, kept finding when challenged strongly for narrow win.
Began OK, taken closer to outer fence in midfield. No clear run until 250m, finishing strongly while laying out under pressure to miss narrowly.
Began well, urged forward sharing lead to course proper, took over running 400m but caught 150m. Boxed on gamely.
Began OK, settling behind leading trio to course proper. No clear run till approaching 100m, finished off nicely.
Jumped with field, switched out but kept 4-away from outer fence, racing on own behind leading pack. Boxed on gamely under pressure.
No early speed, settling toward rear. Urged forward approaching course proper to get within range. Boxed on steadily.
Fractious in gate, began awkwardly then unbalanced. Made up ground to settle 4L behind leader. Kept on fairly in straight.
Began well, ridden forward to share lead passing 800m, still in contention 200m before laying out under pressure and weakening.
Beaten for early speed, taken closer to outer fence and made up some ground to 400m before turning one-paced.
Outpaced early, ridden to make up ground to 400m before turning one-paced.
Began well, led for a few strides before joined up front by two others. Started to give ground passing 300m, faded.
Tightened shortly after start, dropping to clear last. Never in a challenging position.
Jumped with field, led for a few strides before settling behind leading pack to 400m. Gave ground quickly final 200m. Substantial blood in trachea. Lame left hind.
Crowded for room at start, recovered, ridden forward to within 4L of leaders. Gave ground quickly final 300m. Wounded left hind leg.

Jumped well and eased into stride, settling forward of midfield 1 off the fence. Came around runners at the 400m. Pulled away from the 200m to run on strongly and cross the line easing late, when well clear.
Jumped well and taken forward early to be handily placed behind the leaders, 1 off the fence. Held up for a run until the 200m before coming out for a run, and ran on strongly from there.
Began awkwardly and slowly away before eventually finding a position midfield, on the rail. Ran on strongly in the straight for an impressive Hong Kong debut.
Jumped well from the widest barrier and pushed forward to share the lead, 1 off the rail. Well placed for the run home, but ran on 1 paced from the 200m, and missed a place.
Only fairly away and sat just behind midfield on the rails. Came widest on the turn, and ran on OK in the straight, without kicking strongly.
OK away and taken forward early to sit better than midfield 3 wide. Only battled on fairly in the straight and was never threatening.
Began well and taken forward early to sit in a handy position behind the leaders, 3 wide with no cover. In a prominent position at the 200m, but never stretched out from there and dropped back late.
Pushed forward from the jump to lead on the rail. Only 1 paced in the straight, and never a threat late.
OK into stride before finding a position behind midfield 2-3 wide. Came wider on the turn, but only battled on fairly late.

Began well, and pushed forward early to sit in a handy position just behind the leaders on the rail. Held up for clear running for the majority of the straight, only getting clear at the 200m. Only ran on fairly after that.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Only battled away fairly in the straight, and was never a threat.
Didn't push hard from the wide barrier and eventually sat worse than midfield, mostly 2-3 wide. Never responded in the straight, and was eased out late when out of contention.
Dropped back from the wide barrier to be a conspicuous last, 10L off the leader at 800m. Never kicked in the run home, and was eased across the line late.

Began OK, and found a position forward of midfield on the rail. Dropped back quickly from the 700m and couldn't keep up with the rest of the field. Tailed off to be 46L last. Unacceptable performance.

Gradually shifted across from a wide draw to settle in midfield, a bit keen when pace slackened far side, soon came to challenge after straightening, took charge 100 metres out.
Led from a wide-ish draw, obtained rails run passing winning post the first time setting a steady pace, unable to sustain effort and headed 100 metres out.

Slow out, settled in rear of midfield on rails, shuffled slightly backward in slackened pace off the Rock but re-gained to midfield on rails turning for home, finished off race well with clear running final 150 metres.
Jumped awkwardly sideway, settled 2-back in 5th on rails about 3L off the pace, similar rounding home bend but saved ground turning in, baulked for a run inside final 200 metres.
Close up 2nd, came under pressure in similar position after straightening, found nothing.
Settled just off the pace on rails, tightened passing the 200 metres and remained tight between runners throughout closing stages.
Towards the rear most of way, came under pressure around the bend, produced moderate late impression closing stages.
Slow out, travelled well back, switched out for a run turning into straight, made moderate progress without threatening.
Raced wide without cover in midfield to straight, kept on well.
Settled in 4th within 3L of pace, found nothing in straight.
Never on terms.
Settled mainly 2-wide in rear, came under pressure from the 800 metres, made no impression from last into straight.
Eased at start, took rail, suited by the fast sectionals, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Settled in midfield, took rail, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, steadily took rail, led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up at back, favoured by the fast pace but lost ground when racing wide at home bend, closed off strongly 300M.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
Awkward away, hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 150M.
Hard ridden early, behind midfield 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M, on heels 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, raced keenly, not suited by the fast tempo, soon emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped wide, harmed by the fast pace, reduced quickly 300M.
Prominent early, soon eased out of race.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader at very slow sectionals, placed under pressure 600M, kept on strongly to score by a short head.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, found cover 600M, benefited by the very slow pace, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the very slow tempo, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Pushed forward to take the lead along the fence at very slow sectionals, kept on gamely until final furlong, hung on for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the very slow tempo, made no impression in straight.
Rolled to obtain the box seat, despite the very slow pace, kept on only fairly, weakened final 100M.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the very slow tempo, unable to make any ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the very slow sectionals, never looked likely.
At rear, travelled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Near last, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, well beaten rounding the Home Turn.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never a factor.
Led at break on rail & bustled, headed 1060m & raced a neck 2nd without cover, edged lead 400m, driven 1L clear turning in, battled to wire, just held on.
Smart start & rousted prominently, trapped wide no cover, slotted handy 1 off with cover 800m, wide into stretch & driven, rattled to nick 2nd final stride.
Fast start & prominent, niggled along 1 back 1 off, switched 3 deep final turn, quickened to 2nd 260m, kept closing centre track but lost 2nd at wire.
Fast start widest, taken back to midfield 3 wide with cover, slotted 1 off 800m, ridden along 500m, shifted out turning in, stayed on for solid inroads.
Moderate start, raced rail near rear, shifted out & driven home turn, switched centre track 200m, stormed home late.
Broke ok, rolled to sit 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off turning in & driven in 3rd, ran on only evenly & edged out of frame.
Broke ok, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven wide into stretch, kept on without threatening.
Good break, bustled & raced 1 off with cover fore of midfield, niggled 620m, under pump 400m, boxed on one pace.
Broke well, soon outpaced & bustled midfield on rail, plugged on one pace.
Taken back from wide gate, niggled 2nd last 1 off, driven 420m, hard-ridden into stretch, found little in tepid run home.
Taken back at start & soon detached at tail, gradually closed to be 1L adrift & ridden 420m, plugged on, never a factor.
Sharp break, driven to narrow lead at 1060m & raced 1 off no cover, headed 400m, driven into stretch, found nil & faded out.
Broke well, raced midfield 1 off with cover, rolled to 1 back 1 off 500m, shaken up 300m, quickened in pursuit & progress to lead close home.
Fast start, edged lead 1 off at 900m, 1L clear & to rail 700m, driven & kicked on 330m, tapered & headed close home.
Dropped in at start & soon niggled at tail, ridden & progress 1 off from 450m, strong closer to 3rd without threatening.
Taken back from wide gate, slotted 1 off with cover near rear, progress from 500m to midfield turning in, shifted centre track & kept on for solid headway.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 900m & shuffled to 1 back 700m, driven 450m, plugged on evenly.
Taken back at start to rail near rear, last trio turning in, driven & shifted out, boxed on past beaten rivals.
Sharp start & rousted, settled 1 back 1 off until advanced to 2nd upside leader at 500m, driven into stretch, found little & tapered in run home.
Smart start, caught wide & taken back to 3 wide with cover near rear, driven widest home turn, stayed on evenly.
Moderate break, squeezed up & shuffled back to rail, rousted to settle midfield, driven 450m, outpaced & found little in tame run home.
Broke well to race close up 3 wide no cover, driven turning in, found nil & faded tamely.
Moderate start & rousted, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, under pump 500m, wide into stretch, struggled in weakening run.
Tardy break, rolled 4 wide to press front rank, unable to slot & taken back 900m to midfield 3 wide with cover, wide & driven turning in, weakened tamely.

Worked from a wide draw to camp handy 2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Steadied and shifted out to obtain clear running upon final 300M. Dashed well, as benefitted by the slow tempo, to score by a nose.
Pushed to settle front of midfield, travelled 3-1/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Suited the slow tempo, finished off nicely only to be beaten by a nose.
Rolled into front of midfield and raced along the rail 2-1/2L off with cover. Continued to run on steadily for 3rd.
Settled in midfield 4-3/4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Benefited by the slow tempo and kept on steadily for 4th.
Ridden along to take lead at slow sectionals, remained 2 wide and caught passing upon final 100M.
Began slowly and settled at the rear 8-3/4L off along the rail. Made some ground in the Straight.
Raced along the rail in worse than midfield from a wide gate, 6L behind the leader. Ran on only fairly as hampered by the slow sectionals.
Settled at rear, 7-3/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Never looked likely.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along early from a wide gate, settled in worse than midfield 6-1/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Found nothing in the Straight.
Rolled to obtain box-seat 1-1/4L behind the leader. Weakened and swamped upon final 150M.
Camped at the rear 8-1/4L off along the rail. Was never a factor.
Settled in midfield 6L behind the leader, weakened soon after straightening.
Began well, not hurried, settling 4L behind tearaway leaders. Took closer order 750m, hit front 250m, kept finding when strongly challenged final 150m.
Pressed forward from outside draw before settling in one-off position 5L from leader. Under pressure from 400m, switched in 150m to get split, finished strongly.
Began well but eased off fast pace, settling in midfield along rail. Tightened 650m, switched out, swung wide entering straight, ran on strongly.
Hard ridden to hold rail before easing off fast pace in 4th place. Improved passing 600m but only got going final 200m when finished strongly.
Began fairly, held and taken closer to fence at rear. Rolled forward from 700m when pace slowed, skirting field three-wide to look chance 200m. One-paced final stages.
Jumped OK, not pushed, racing behind midfield to turn when unbalanced and hit rail. Unbalanced top of straight but finished off nicely.
Slow, steadied, dropping to rear along rail. Came off fence and shaken up approaching 400m, switched in top of straight, boxed on fairly.
Began OK, restrained and taken to fence, settling last. Urged forward from 500m, swung wide into straight, boxed on fairly.
Aggressively ridden from start to 1100m inside leader before steadied and settled in 2nd along rail. Battled on gamely to 200m when flattened, faded.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, ridden forward settling midfield in one-off position. Shifted in and bumped top of straight, found little under pressure.
Used early and set fast pace to get to the front, finally getting clear lead 1000m before cutting to fence 800m and slowing pace. Caught 250m and faded.
Away well enough, sat in 3rd and always well poised to strike, pushed out to take lead 250M, quickened clear under hands and heels riding, won impressively.
Restrained in midfield along the 2-path, ran on well inside 300M to go 2nd near 50M, no match with runaway winner.
Began well from inside draw, held back to race in midfield 4Ls back, not matched winner's acceleration inside 300M, held 2nd until 50M.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled down 5-6Ls back towards the rear, into clear 250M, stayed on.
Caught 3-wide no cover from draw 10, 3Ls behind leaders turning home, pushed along 450M, kept on same pace for non threatening 5th.
Failed to muster speed after start, got back to the tail of the field 700M, some progress final 300M but not reached leaders.
Taken across behind runners from 11, held up near the rear 6Ls back, guided to outside coming off the bend, kept on same pace.
Broke well, restrained sit 4th 3Ls off leader, lacked the necessary response when driven out in straight, no threat to leaders. (Jockey dropped rein 100M)
Failed to muster speed and consequently raced back in the field, driven wide 550M, kept on only fairly on outer passing well beaten runners.
Ended up 3-wide in midfield, had cover, came off bridle 500M, failed to deliver a finish. (No Vet findings)
Rushed to the lead under 10lbs claimer, led steadily to straight, was quickly swept aside passing 250M, weakened towards the line.
Used a bit early to obtain a forward position behind leader, found no extra 300M, soon beaten. (Blood in trachea)

Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to score narrowly.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield 3-wide, widest runner in midfield turning for home, quickened well to hit the front just inside the 100 metres only to be pipped at post.
Driven to lead before joined by eventual last on the bend, re-gained 1L advantage early in straight when fellow joint leader dropped away, swamped under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, commenced run out wide rounding home bend, sustained good progress near the centre of the straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped best, pushed along before settling just off the pace mainly in 5th on rails, kept on at the one pace under pressure in the run home.
Ridden along from a wide gate before settling 3-wide in 6th just over 2Ls off the pace, similar into straight, fought on steadily until tired late.
Moderately away from gate 2, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderate jump after the one draw settling in midfield, remained similar entering straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Bumped at start, raced 1-1/2 length back in 4th, no cover after 800M, peaked early in straight, emptied final 100M.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to last few, baulked briefly upon straightening, kept on steadily without threatening in the run home.
Sluggish at start, recovered to just worse than midfield approaching home bend, similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Ridden along one off the pace, bumped on home turn, soon dropped out of contention.
Driven along and given reminders 1000 metres out, moved on to race upsides of leader while awkwardly around home bend, unable to sustain run and dropped away quickly passing the 400 metres.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, closed off well to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, on heels 900M, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pressed forward, led easily at good pace, just ran on for 3rd.
Rolled forward easily, pace good, dominated from 400M, hung on until 50M flattened.
Bumped start, pushed forward, hard ridden from 500M, raced greenly on the inner part of track, lack dash, just held ground.
Pushed forward, pace good, raced on the inner part of track, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased to take cover on the inner part of track behind midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Eased back, pace good, ran on fairly until 250M, picked up well and made good ground.
Hard ridden forward, on heels early, checked 600M, off the bridle and lost ground, regained momentum 150M.
Bumped start, sat in front of midfield on the inner part of track, pace good, lack turn of foot, emptied 200M.
Very slow away, at rear, ran on ok in final stages.
Hard ridden forward, soon weakened 300M.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, never improved on the inner part of track.
Eased back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, dashed well to score by 1L.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, ran on steadily until final 100M weakened, hung on for 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield about 2.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on gradually for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Driven forward to park outside the leader at fast tempo, kept on until 300M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the fast pace, unable to make any impression in straight. (Roarer)
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast tempo, never ran on. (Questioned for performance)
Lacked early pace, settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader, never looked likely.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led at fast sectionals, soon flattened after straightening.
Sharp break, camped midfield 1 off with cover, cruising but in pocket turning in, clear & driven 330m, quickened to lead 70m & kept on.
Broke ok, taken back to race behind midfield 3 wide with cover, bustled 750m, under pump 550m, bumped 400m, rattled to 2nd late, closing at wire.
Smart start, bustled to lead 1550m, soon to rail & raced 1L clear, nursed into stretch, shaken up 340m, soon all out, headed 70m.
Broke ok, taken back to rear trio 1 off with cover, 7L last & driven turning in, shifted wide & closed for solid inroads.
Slow start & bustled to rail, rolled on to midfield, shaken up 430m & shifted out, not clear run 350m to 200m, driven for minor late headway.
Broke well, raced 1 back on rail, niggled a touch 800m, attempted to shift out & driven 300m, lacked toe & found little, plodded on one pace.
Prominent at start, sat 2nd 1 off no cover, shuffled to 1 off 1 back 1000m, niggled 800m, under pump 550m to hold spot, one-paced in run home.
Rousted at break to midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled back gradually to near rear turning in, driven 400m & bumped in sandwich down stretch, bumped again 160m, kept on late.
Taken back, settled midfield 3 deep with cover, wide & driven into stretch, outpaced & plodded on tamely, shifted out & bumped rival late.
Good break on outer, trapped handy 3 wide no cover, to 2nd 1 off no cover 1000m, 1L down & ridden 400m, outpaced & then emptied 250m, faded in run.
Taken back at start & raced rail in rear rank, shifted out turning in, bumped 400m & unbalanced, bumped again 160m & impeded to wire.
Tardy start, raced last trio 3 deep with cover, driven widest into stretch, found nil in weak run home.
Broke ok, niggled a touch early, caught 4 wide no cover & unable to slot, pushed on to 3rd 3 wide no cover at 1000m, ridden 500m, found nil & weakened tamely.
Broke ok, settled midfield 1 off with cover, progress on turn, 3rd & driven 400m, quickened to lead 250m, drew clear.
Missed break, taken to rail, rolled on to midfield at 950m, shifted 1 off on turn, crowded until driven 350m, ran on to 2nd late.
Prominent initially, soon settled handy 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide with cover 970m, driven 530m, fought on to 2nd 150m, tapered & lost 2nd late.
Taken back at break & bustled at tail, soon dropped to rail & advanced to sit behind midfield, ridden 500m, switched 1 off 350m, stayed on dourly for gradual headway.
Missed break, raced near tail on rail, niggled 800m, shifted out & ridden final turn, staying on when bumped 250m, raced tight to rival in run, kept on for minor gains, bumped at wire.

Broke ok but lacked toe, raced 1 off near tail, niggled 650m, shifted out & driven into stretch, bumped 250m raced tightly with rival in closing stages & unbalanced, kept on for minor gains, bumped at line.
Tardy break & rousted to settle behind midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 500m, stayed on for modest inroads.
Fast start & led, soon headed& settled 2nd 1 off no cover, shifted 3 wide on turn, driven to press lead 450m, emptied 150m & tapered to wire.
Smart start wide, taken back to slot midfield 3 wide with cover, checked & shuffled back 770m, driven turning in but crowded, checked & switched out 220m, outpaced & tapered.
Driven wide to lead 1500m, to rail 1250m & raced 1L clear, driven under pressure 430m, all out & headed 250m, weakened.
Tardy start, niggled along at tail, ridden 500m, ran on centre track for minor inroads.
Sharp break, caught wide & taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 700m, driven into stretch, one-paced when squeezed up & checked 250m, no extra.
Moderate start, bustled to 3 wide no cover handy, rolled on & 2nd at 970m, driven 460m, outpaced & bumped 350m, faded tamely.
Broke ok, raced 1 back on rail, driven turning in, found nil & faded weakly.
Settled midfield 3-1/4L behind the leader. 3 wide without cover and travelled nicely rounding the Home Turn. Held off challenge of 2nd to score by a nose.
Began awkwardly and slowly away. Settled near the rear 5-1/2L off, 2 wide with cover. Despite the slow tempo, closed off strongly in the Straight, just failed.
Began slowly and settled at rear 6-1/4L behind, 3 wide with cover. Finished off nicely a nose behind the 2nd.
Soon taken across close to the rail from a wide gate. Remained at rear 7-1/2L off, 2 wide with cover. Held up for clear running early in the Straight. Kept on steadily for 4th.
Camped handy from a wide gate 3L behind the leader, 2 wide without cover. Improved rounding the Home Turn but caught passing approaching final 200M.
Pushed forward to obtain box-seat and trailed the leader by 3/4L. Found less than expected and only kept on one paced.
Rolled into worse than midfield along the rail, 3-1/2L behind the leader. Obtained clear running upon final 150M, finished off fairly.
Rolled into front of midfield 2L off, 2 wide with cover. Ran home one paced.
Settled worse than midfield 4-1/2L behind, 2 wide with cover. Never looked likely.
Settled towards the rear along the rail, 5-1/4L off the leader. Failed to obtain clear running and found nothing in the straight.
Rolled into midfield 2-3/4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Emptied and swamped upon final 150M.
Camped at the rear 7-1/2L off, 3 wide with cover. Was never a factor.
Raced to camp handy along the rail, 2L behind the leader. Swamped soon after passing final 300M.
Pushed forward to take lead along the rail at slow sectionals. Found noting in the Straight.
Hard ridden inside leader before taking over lead approaching 600m. Kicked clear top of straight and though tiring final stages held on to win.
First out but prevented from crossing to rail by inside horse. Slipped into second approaching 600m, kept challenging in straight, just failed.
Slow, ridden to make ground but checked and unbalanced 1100m, then failed to settle dropping to rear. Taken wide in straight and finished nicely.
Began well but unable match early pace, dropping to rear. Improved around turn, took inside run in straight, kept on fairly.
Unbalanced start, ridden to make up ground grabbing box seat before turn. Stayed on rail in straight and boxed on fairly.
Pressed forward, racing 3-wide without cover behind leading pair. Under whip top of straight and boxed on fairly.
Ridden early to hold midfield position, racing two- and three-wide around turn. One-paced in straight, while laying out under pressure.
Jumped OK but restrained, looking for cover. Held three-wide around turn toward the rear, one-paced in straight.
Began well but unable go early pace, dropping to last in one-off position. Found nothing in straight when asked for an effort.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing 4-wide without cover around turn. Tired shortly after straightening and dropped back gradually.
Slotted into a 2-wide position midfield, stayed on well when driven 350M , hung in late stages under pressure but managed to get up just before line.
Sent to the front as expected, led evenly, still going well passing 100M, all out only to be headed last stride.
Tracked the pace along the 2-path, responded well inside 300M to chase leader, came within 0.5L of first two, brushed by winner late on.
Settled down midfield, stayed on under pressure in straight, did best work late stages.
Prompted the pace outside leader, outdashed by rivals 200M, faded to 5th.
Settled just off leaders, kept on same pace in straight, no threat from 250M.
Held up behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, no clear run early straight, gave limited response when shifted out to clear.
Bounded in the air and lost ground, ended up in last 7-8Ls back, stayed on past beaten runners in straight.
Restrained behind midfield, proved difficult to settle near 1000M, not picked up pace to challenge and showed signs of greenness in straight.
Shifted across behind runners, raced 3-wide near the rear 6Ls off the pace, ridden 450M out soon no impression.
Slow to begin, soon driven along but caught wide no cover in midfield throughout, never dangerous, beaten mid-straight.
Dropped back to near the rear, ridden nearing 400M, no response and soon beaten.
Taken across behind runners, raced keenly middle stages, 6Ls to make up 400M, not picked up and never involved.
Ridden forward between horses, settling three-back, one-off before turn. Peeled 4-wide into straight and finished strongly to just get there.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1000m. Travelled strongly in straight when challenged but caught on wire.
Ridden forward from wide draw looking for cover, but left three-wide in midfield from 1000m. Lay in and bumped another 250m but kept on well to the line.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace settling between horses in midfield. No clear run top of straight, switched out 300m and finished strongly.
Began awkwardly, shifted out abruptly, ridden forward inside leader before settling one-out, one-back. Looked chance 400m, boxed on gamely.
Hampered start, pressed forward four-wide in midfield. Lost position approaching 1000m, very wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Ridden along early, settling in box but shuffled three-back around turn. No room early in straight, boxed on fairly when clear.
Began OK, not pushed, settling towards rear before crossing to rail at turn. Shifted out continually in straight to get run. Finished well.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 4-wide before settling 1L behind leader at turn. Boxed on fairly under hard riding in straight.
Pressed forward, quickly moving to hold fence behind leader. Got close to heels 400m, boxed on gamely in straight, flattened final strides.
Began fairly, ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield before turn. Switched out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced start and soon trailing field in one-off position. Under pressure turning for home but one-paced.
Bumped heavily start and then again shortly. Checked severely 1300m when refusing to settle, dropping to rear. Never in contention.
Heavy contact and unbalanced start, ridden to make up ground but still well back. Gave ground soon after straightening for home.
Began well, and eased forward to sit midfield on the fence. Well placed on the turn, and responded well to pressure from the 250m to go well clear for a strong win, easing on the line.
Eased forward from the jump to be midfield, 1 off the rail. Waited for a clear run at the 200m, and stormed home late still running on strongly at the wire.

Steadied off heels early and taken back to be at the rear, on the rails. Came wider on the turn, and was ridden for luck in the straight. Ran on strongly from the 200m when clear, and grabbed 3rd place late.
OK away, and taken back early to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Worked on well from the rear of the field in the straight, and kicked well in the last 100m.
Began well and taken forward early to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Ran on well in the straight and loomed up at the 200m to make a claim before shifting out under pressure late.
Crowded on jumping and taken back from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide. Ran on well in the straight to improve his position late.
Only fairly away and dropped back to be in the last two, 1 off the fence. Came widest on the turn, and was finishing off well until slightly inconvenienced late.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping before being taken forward to sit behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Ran on OK until last 100m, and faded back.
OK away and eased forward to sit worse than midfield, on the rail. Only ran on fairly in the straight, and never threatened.
Began awkwardly and pushed forward to sit in a handy position, on the rail. Well placed when put under pressure on the turn, but didn't respond and only ran to the line fairly.
Began OK, and take across from the wide draw to lead. Led until 150m, but race was run and faded out quickly from there.

Began well and taken forward early, but came off heels when crossed at the 900m, and ended up forward of midfield 3 wide. Only plugged away fairly in the straight, and not persevered with after losing a run at 75m.
Jumped well, but not used up early to sit midfield, 4-5 wide. Came wider on the turn, but was beaten a long way out and eased out early.

Had the wide draw and drifted in to sit midfield 4-5 wide, before moving forward at the 1000m to be in a handier position. Was battling early in the straight, and faded to be 19L last in his Hong Kong debut.

Moderate start, pressed on along the rails to take up running from the 1000 metres producing fast early sectionals, sustained effort to spread-eagling the field in the final stretch.
Began from a poor gate, settled just better than midfield in 6th, fought on steadily for remote 2nd.
Jumped fairly settling towards the rear at his own pace, finished off race nicely producing the fastest final sectional of the field at the finish.
Settled towards the rear on rails, produced good late impression down the inside of straight, nearest at finish.
Jumped well, settled for 3rd one off the rails in fast early sections, shifted slightly wider rounding home bend, had nothing to give under pressure upon straightening.

Vied for lead from a wide draw, holding narrow advantage briefly before shifting back to sit just outside the leader around the bend, unable to sustain effort and faded out of contention upon straightening.
Taken back to trail the field, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on steadily past well-beaten runners in the run to the line.
Taken back from a tricky gate to race one from last, trailed the field into home straight, fought on dourly under pressure past well-beaten horses.
Settled in midfield to straight, one-paced.
Settled in midfield on rails, given early reminder approaching home straight, soon faded after straightening.
With leaders early before settling in 4th just over 2L off the pace, folded up quickly in straight.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Settled not far off in 5th on rails, dropped away quickly 500 metres out, failed to finish.
Slow away, pushed forward, benefited by the slow sectional in the lead, closed off strongly to score.
Eased back, saved ground round the home bend, dashed home strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
Secured box seat, good trip, however held up 4-2, dashed well when clear for 3rd.
Pushed to take rail and led, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, flattened 150M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up at back, on rails, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight and checked, ran on ok.
Very slow away, at back with cover in 2 wide initially, made early move from 1100M, trapped 3 wide off the lead, emptied 400M.
Pushed early but failed to muster, just off the leaders 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Midfield, shuffled further back from 1100M, forced 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Very slow away, at rear 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield 2 wide with cover, raced keenly, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Very slow away, at rear but on the fence, made some ground 300M, lack room 150M.
Eased back 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, flattened 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, made some ground when clear.
Pushed forward on the fence, harmed by the fast pace, no progress, flattened 200M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, weakened 300M.
At rear 3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, never improved.
Pressed forward 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, crossing to fence and slowing tempo. Kicked clear top of straight and bolted home. Eased down final stages.
Slow, ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield at turn. Switched in top of straight to get clear running and finished off nicely.
Began well, ridden to hold fence three-back from leader. Came off fence passing 700m, shaken up 300m and kept on steadily.
Began well, unable find cover and drifted to behind midfield but wide. Taken very wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, holding 2nd behind early leader before settling one-back, one-off at turn. Boxed on gamely in straight, flattened late.
Jumped with field, not pushed, sliding to midfield before switching three-wide 700m to move forward. Battled on gamely in straight.
Got off OK, steadied in midfield, holding one-off position to turn. Swung wide in straight but one-paced under hard riding.
Unable to find cover early and slipped back towards rear. Hampered 800m, kept switching out in straight to get clear running but one-paced.
Jumped OK, restrained, taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Taken wide in straight, ran on fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, losing ground start. Settled at rear, switched out around turn, ran on fairly in straight while laying in under pressure.
Began fairly, ridden to hold forward position 2L from leader. Rolled forward around turn to eyeball leader 600m, tired rapidly from 200m.
Lost ground start when jumped awkwardly, ridden to make up ground but checked 800m. One-paced in straight before tiring from 150m.
Jumped awkwardly, unbalanced and lost ground settling at rear close to fence. Never competitive.
Hard ridden to hold box seat but under pressure from turn and faded quickly in straight. Stewards ruled performance unacceptable.
Began smartly, not pushed, settling ahead of midfield in one-off position. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 150m, held off late challenge.
Restrained early, settling midfield in one-off position. Rolled forward around turn, kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Began well but unable to go early pace settling behind midfield. Improved position between horses around turn and kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold rail then steadied turn. Held up temporarily passing 350m, lay in passing 200m, kept on steadily.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Switched out in straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, ridden but failed to muster, settling well back. Made up ground early in straight turning one-paced. Substantial blood in trachea.
Shifted across behind runners from a wide draw, settling at rear close to fence. Well back entering straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden aggressively to lead passing 1000m before crossing to fence. Was 6L clear turn, kept on well until caught 150m. Flattened late. Rider wrapped for ill-judged race.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw, settling at rear but wide. Kept wide around turn, ran on fairly in straight.
Began OK but no speed, dropping to rear but two-wide. Shaken up top of straight but found little under hard riding.
Jumped with field, ridden forward to sit 6L behind tearaway leader. Closed in early in straight before tiring noticeably final 200m.
Began well, ridden to hold fence three-back from leader. Made some headway early in straight before tiring from 250m.
Hard ridden to lead on settling before taking the sit passing 1000m. Kept on to 250m before tiring. Pulled up with irregular heart rhythm.
Began well but raced keenly before turn and kept wide without cover. Hung out in straight and difficult to ride, dropping back. Racing manners ruled unacceptable.
Settled front of midfield 2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Shifted wide to obtain clear running at the entrance of the Straight, dashed well to score by 1-1/4L.
Pushed to obtain position in front of midfield 2-1/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Unable to obtain clear running until final 300M, finished strongly, only beaten by 1-1/4L.
Raced forward to take lead along the rail by 1/2L. Kept on steadily in the Straight, held off challenge for 3rd.
Steadied shortly the start. Settled midfield 3L off, 3 wide with cover. Kept on steadily to the line.
Settled midfield along the rail, 4L behind the leader. Made some ground in the Straight, finished one pace.
Rolled to settle worse than midfield 5-1/4L off, 3 wide with cover. Finished off only fairly.
Raced to camp handy 1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide without cover. Kept on well until final 250M, weakened thereafter.
Race at rear 6-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Kept on one pace without threatening.
Settled just worse than midfield along the rail, 5-1/4L off the pace. Shifted out after final 350M, maintained one pace in the straight.
Kept at rear 6-1/2L off, raced 3 wide with cover. Swung widest upon straightening, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled along the rail 3-3/4L behind the leader. Kept on one pace until final 200M weakened.
Settled at rear from widest gate. Travelled 8L off, 3 wide with cover. Was never a factor.
Ridden along to race outside the leader 1/2 off, 3 wide without cover. Swamped upon final 200M.
Settled worse than midfield 6L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Found nothing when asked and finished tail out.
Bumped start, recovered quickly to sit 1L behind leader. Rolled forward to make in a 4-way tie 400m before pulling clear for easy win.
Began well, sitting behind early pace before switching out and rolling forward to join leaders at 400m. Kept on gamely final stages though no match for winner.
Jumped with field, staying close to outer rail while stalking leaders. Shifted in and brushed another when held for clear running 200m, tightened 100m, kept on well.
Bumped start, beaten for early speed dropping back. Still well back at the 200m before picking up and finishing strongly.
Pressed forward close to outer rail, sitting behind leading trio before joining leaders passing 400m. Clear 2nd at 200m, flattened late.
Jumped OK, beaten for early speed, dropping to behind midfield. Switched in 400m to find clear running and kept on fairly.
Hampered start, rolled forward down centre track to sit behind early pace. Pressed forward 400m to look a chance before turning one-paced. Fattened late.
No speed, dropping to 2nd last while hugging outer rail. Urged forward from 400m but taken in 200m. No clear run final 100m and not properly tested.
Hampered start, urged forward, settling midfield on centre track. Put under pressure from 400m but only one-paced.
Beaten for early pace and last on settling. Trailed field to 200m when checked. Plodded to line.
Lifted leg at start but recovered quickly to chase leader before sharing lead 400m. Started to give ground 400m and unbalanced 200m. Not tested final stages. Substantial blood in trachea.
Quickly into stride, leading down centre track to half-way mark when joined by three others. Under pressure from 400m and faded. Performance unacceptable.
Chased leaders along the fence, quickly accelerated to lead 300M, soon well clear and well in control, won impressively.
Settled midfield but caught wide no cover throughout, stayed on well to go 2nd inside 150M, no threat to runaway winner.
Held up near the rear 5Ls off the pace, saved ground along inside, switched out 350M, stayed on mildly to go 3rd near line.
Positioned 3Ls back in midfield, waited with along the fence, tight for room inside 300M, stayed on moderately over final 200M when gap opened up.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, 7Ls off the pace in last, brought wide 400M, ran on well to go 5th late stages.
Chased leaders, ended up 3-wide no cover from 800M, kept on same pace inside 400M for non-threatening 6th.
Close up behind leaders, lacked winner's acceleration inside 400M, kept on moderately until flattened over final 150M.
Shared lead on the inner, couldn't contain winner 300M, fought on till no extra 150M.
Ended up 4-wide behind midfield from draw 7, not quickened to challenge leaders in straight, no impression.
Reserved in midpack along the 2-path, driven out 450M, kept on same pace behind main rivals.
Restrained near the rear 5Ls off the pace, over-raced middle stages, not picked up on straightening, never a threat.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, towards the rear and fanned 3-wde home turn, taken wide in straight but gave limited response, weakened towards finish. (No Vet findings)
Strode forward and prompted the pace on outside, under serious pressure 500M, dropped off quickly passing 300M.
Held midfield spot along the 3-path, pushed along to keep up halfway round home turn, soon beaten entering straight.
Began well, urged forward, settling one-back, one-off. Shaken up passing 400m, rolled forward to lead passing 200m, kept on well to line.
Ridden along early, settling along rail three-back from leader. Not much room top of straight, got split 150m, finished well.
Pressed forward but unable to find cover and raced three-wide mostly in midfield. Swung wide into straight and finished strongly under whip.
Jumped OK, racing wide before steadied 1100m and taken to rail towards rear. Not much room top of straight but finished nicely when clear.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide until settling a neck behind leader. Rolled forward to lead passing 300m, kept on well when passed 180m.
First out but steadied, looking for cover and settling in one-off position behind midfield. Not much room early in straight but ran on steadily when clear.
Began OK but not pushed, gradually dropping back to last before the turn. Switched out in straight to make run and ran on fairly when clear 200m.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting steady pace. Kept on well initially when joined up front 300m before running out of gas 100m.
Began fairly, taken quickly to fence, settling 4-back around turn. Stayed on rail, looked chance 250m before blocked and steadied 200m. One-paced
Began awkwardly, bumped, then taken across behind runners, settling 3-wide at rear. Very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Steadied soon after start and taken in, settling between runners at the rear. Switched wide entering straight but found little under pressure.
Began well, rolled forward holding box seat to straight. Switched out to make run but didn't let down. Plodded to line.
Bumped start, taken across behind runners but held three-wide at rear. Widest into straight but never likely.
Began well but held three-wide to 800m when shifted in to find cover. Urged forward top of straight but hung out and failed to respond. Faded.
Fairly away, but pushed forward early to sit in a handy position, 3 wide with no cover. Full of running in the straight, and ran on strongly when let down from the 200m to win easily.
Jumped well, and was pushed forward early to lead. Travelled well in front when setting his own pace, but running tired late overtaken by a fast finishing winner.
Began well from the inside barrier before being eased forward to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Had to wait until the 250m to get a clear run, and ran on steadily without threatening to win.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Came widest when last at the top of the straight. Big run down the outside to finish with the fastest final 400m time.

Eased back from the jump to sit at the rear of the field, on the fence. Came wider when 7L off the pace, turning for home. Ridden for luck, and produced a strong effort in the straight to pick up the majority of the field.
Fairly away, and allowed to drift forward to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wide on the turn, and battled on fairly in the straight, passing a few of the slower ones.
Scrubbed up early to be place just behind the leader, on the fence with cover. Prominently placed at the 250m, but faded from that point and dropped back.
Eased across from the wide draw to be placed midfield, 3-4 wide. Wider on the turn, but never responded to pressure, and went to the line 1 paced.
Pushed hard early to grab a position one behind the leader, one off the fence. Used up early and was beginning to fade on the turn. Only plugged away late.
OK into stride, settling midfield 1 off the fence. Only battled to the line fairly from the turn in his Hong Kong debut.
Began OK and taken forward to a handy trailing position, 1 off the fence. Under pressure before the turn but never responded and faded out in the straight, easing late. Unacceptable performance.

Dropped back from the wide draw to be 10L last early. Was detached from the rest of the field on the turn, and had a lot of ground to make up. Battled on fairly late, but was left with too much to do.
OK away and found a position midfield, 1 off the fence before being taken back when hampered at the 900m. Over raced throughout the race, and only battled on in the straight and well beaten.
Began OK, and eased forward to sit midfield on the fence. Came wider on the turn, before moving back to the rails at the 300m. Was a beaten horse by the 200m, and faded back from there.

Settled well behind, finished off race well down the inner of straight to snatch victory final strides.
Settled not far off in 5th, snuck up to 2nd on rails on home turn hitting the front over 250 metres out, only to be worn down close to home.
Broke well, settled just off the pace in 3rd near rails, came to challenge turning in, ran home one-paced.
Slow into stride, recovered to midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield, kept on steadily past beaten horses in the run home.
Settled in last few, made modest progress past well-beaten horses in straight.
Settled at the back from a poor draw, ran on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Sluggish at start, raced wide in midfield or just worse, came under pressure entering straight, one-paced.
Given reminders early, never better than midfield.
Worked his way forward from a wide draw to take up running turning into back straight, held clear running to about 300 metres, folded up quickly.
Settled in midfield, dropped out of contention from halfway out.
Travelled wide in prominent position early stages, yielded ground from approaching home bend.
Broke well in front briefly, settled just inside the leader on rails and chased him from halfway out, folded up quickly from approaching home straight.
Never better than midfield, dropped away quickly from the 400 metres.
Took lead easily, clocked fast sectionals, drifted away 400M, dominated onwards.
Settled in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Midfield early, lost ground middle stages, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, raced on inner part of track, just held ground in final stages.
Settled at back, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, raced on inner part of track, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, raced on inner part of track, flattened 200M.
Settled nicely in midfield, left rein snapped 500M, couldn't be ridden out.
Hard ridden but not muster, at rear, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, at back, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
Bumped start and checked, never progressed.
Midfield, suited the fast pace, soon emptied 400.
Bumped start, pressed forward, harmed the fast pace, checked badly 300M whilst weakening.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, ran on strongly to score impressively by 2-3/4Ls.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on well for 2nd.
At rear as usual, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched widest turning in, dashed strongly for 3rd.
Slow to muster pace, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, ran home ok.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off one pace.
Crowded on jumping, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Ridden forward to settle in a prominent position with cover from a wide gate, stayed on one pace to the line.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, unable to make any impression in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Driven forward to share the lead along the fence, hung on until final 200M headed.
Prominent, trapped 3-4 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until 200M weakened.
Blundered on jumping, then hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, flattened badly 300M.
Pushed to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor.
Sharp start, settled 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off 400m & driven, battled to lead 250m, kept on to line.
Sharp break & prominent, soon bustled to settle 1 off 1 back, driven & crowded 300m, bumped rival 220m, quickened to 2nd 140m, always held.
Smart start, settled back 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden 530m, stayed on centre track for dour gains.
Speed to lead widest, snagged 1010m & headed 970m, sat 2nd 1 off no cover, driven & led 350m, drifted out under pressure & headed 250m, weakened to wire.
Taken back from wide gate, raced rear rank 3 wide with cover until slotted 1 off 800m, driven into stretch, kept on for minor headway.
Broke well, bustled along early, raced handy 3 wide no cover, driven 420m but one-paced, bumped 220m & unbalanced, tepid run home.
Broke well, rousted to lead 970m & snared rail, strode along 1L clear, niggled 500m, pressed & driven 400m, soon headed, tapered to wire.
Taken back at break, trapped wide no cover until 3 wide with cover 800m, wide into stretch & hard-ridden 300m, plugged on for modest inroads.
Sharp break, slotted back to race midfield, shifted off fence final turn, switched out farther 400m & driven, one-paced in run & on heels close home.
Stumbled start & soon at tail, crossed to rail, progress to 3rd last 800m, 1 behind when shifted out & driven final turn, plodded on one pace.
Slow start & bustled to race behind midfield on rail, driven 600m, plodded on at same speed.
Slow start, bustled to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven into stretch, found little & tapered.
Tardy start, raced near tail 1 off until unbalanced 850m & dropped to 2L detached last, driven final turn, plodded home tamely.
Broke ok, soon outpaced & rousted early to race back of midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 600m, struggled & weakened tamely in stretch.
Prominent early, snagged to race 1 off with cover midfield, switched out 400m & driven, quickened to lead 270m, kept on to wire.
Disputed initial lead, snagged to race midfield on rail, niggled 650m, driven in stretch to press lead & go 2nd at 270m, held in run.
Taken back at break, sat 3wide with cover near rear, niggled 650m, wide & driven final turn, checked 380m, stayed on to 3rd late.
Smart start wide, raced 3 deep no cover midfield, driven wide into stretch, bumped rival 400m & again 200m, stayed on evenly.
Snagged at break, rolled to sit behind midfield on rail, driven & shifted 1 off 400m, boxed on to wire without threatening.
Sluggish start, raced last pair 1 off, reminder 560m, shifted wide & in pocket 400m, driven 350m, run blocked 300m, switched into clear 150m, closed late.
Tardy start & bustled for progress, settled 1 back 1 off 1200m, niggled 3.5L 4th no cover at 850m, outpaced 600m & shuffled back, kept on evenly.
Sharp start, soon led & to rail 1350m, headed 1000m & sat 1 back, shifted 1 off final turn, one-paced & tapered late.
Moderate start, rolled wide no cover to 2nd 1 off 1400m, advanced to lead 1000m & scooted 1.5L clear on rail, ridden final turn, shifted out under pressure & headed 270m, faded.
Sluggish start, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 850m, shifted out & driven into stretch, one-paced in run.
Tardy break, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven wide final turn, bumped & checked 400m, kept on until bumped again 200m & emptied.
Broke ok, soon bustled & outpaced, slid back on rail to near rear, driven 550m, struggled in run home.
Tardy break & rousted to advance, raced rail 1 back, shuffled to 2 back 3rd at 800m, switched 1 off 720m, 3 wide home turn & driven under pressure, bumped 400m, emptied.
Slow start widest, taken to tail 3 wide with cover, under pump 570m, wide into stretch, found nil.
Pushed forward to lead along the rail, led by 1/2L. Unleashed upon straightening and held on to score by 3/4L.
Obtained box-seat and travelled 1-3/4L off. Despite unable to obtain clear running until 200M, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Settled midfield 2-1/2L behind the leader, 3 wide without cover. Despite shifted out wide when exiting the Home Turn, dashed well for 3rd.
Hampered at the Start then settled in midfield along the rail, 3-1/4L off. Made ground in the Straight, finished off steadily.
Rolled to worse than midfield 4-1/4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Kept on steadily in the straight.
Settled midfield 4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Ran on only fairly.
Raced 2 wide with cover in worse than midfield, 5L off. Unable to make significant ground in the straight.
Pushed from widest gate to settle outside the leader, 1/2L off the pace. Found nothing when asked after passing final 200M, never looked likely thereafter.
At rear from a wide gate, travelled wide and with cover, 6-1/4L behind. Never ran on.
Camped handy initially before settling in midfield 3L off, 2 wide with cover. Unable to make ground in the straight.
Raced to obtain position in front of midfield 2L behind, 3 wide without cover. Emptied and swamped upon after final 200M.
Settled worse than midfield along the rail, 5-1/2L behind. Unable to make any impression in the straight.
Began from a wide gate then settled worse than midfield 5-1/4L off, 3 wide with cover. Never looked likely.
Slow to begin. Remained at rear 7-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Was never competitive.
Began well, pressed forward between horses to take lead approaching 1200m. Strongly challenged in straight but kept finding for narrow win.
Ridden forward but three-wide without cover, settling 3L behind leader at turn. Rolled forward to challenge 250m but unable get past winner.
Jumped with field, not pressed, slipping behind midfield but three-wide. Swung very wide into straight and battled on gamely under the whip.
Out quickly, led to first turn before giving way and slipping into box seat 1200m. Came off fence entering straight and battled on gamely.
Began fairly, taken to fence from wide draw, then made up ground to sit three-back from leader. Looked chance 350m but unable close gap.
Crowded for room at start, ridden forward but steadied 1400m, settling one-back, one-off 1100m. Rolled forward top of straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward three-wide to first turn before settling outside hind-quarters of leader. Urged forward passing 350m but soon out of gas and faded.
Flat-footed at start, losing considerable ground. Caught up to field approaching 1200m, brushed rail entering straight, one-paced.
Bumped shortly after start, urged forward to sit behind pace. Lost position around turn and finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Jumped fairly, ridden but failed to stretch out, racing mostly four-wide at the rear. Finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Close up tracking leaders, pushed out to take lead nearing 250M, kicked clear and never looked in danger final 150M.
Held up near last 6Ls off the pace middle stages, crept closer to pace from 600M, stayed on to go 2nd 70M, not reached easy winner.
Settled down midfield 4Ls off the pace, lacked winner's acceleration inside 300M, kept on steadily to line, lost 2nd 70M out, held 3rd just.
Dropped back to the rear about 6Ls behind leader, brought wide 500M, on heels 250M, picked up strongly when switched clear 200M, just missed 3rd. (Jockey questioned re riding in straight)
Eased back to sit behind midfield, awkwardly placed from 600M and unable to improve position until 250M, still last 200M but closed home well for never nearer 5th.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden, ended up last 7Ls off the pace in middle stages, bid extremely wide 550M, made mild progress to mid-straight, run ended 150M.
Restrained from start, raced keenly and unable to slot in behind runners, difficult to settle 900M and caught wide no cover, brief effort to 250M, flattened out.
Went forward, tracked leader from 1100M, outpaced passing 300M, weakened towards finish.
Sat in handy 3rd but gave only limited response when driven 400M, soon no threat to leaders.
Rushed forward from wide barrier, taken keen hold when restrained in the lead, headed nearing 250M, faded away.
Slowly away, recovered to race in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, had nothing to offer when shaken up 400M, soon weakened out of contention.
Began OK, not pushed, gradually dropping back to last passing 700m. Picked up from 400m, taking splits between horses to hit the front 50m, pulling clear.
Began well, taken to outer fence 1L behind leader. Urged forward passing 450m, took lead 250m, run down final stages.
Quickly into stride, taken closer to outer fence 1.5L from leader. Lost position 500m, urged forward 350m and kept on well to line.
Began fairly, shifted across behind horses towards outer fence 800m, urged forward but held up 200m before finishing strongly.
Began well, raced on own down centre track before steadied 800m and switched out. Ran on steadily from 500m to be closest at finish.
Quickly out, setting good pace along outer fence. Collared passing 250m after which one-paced to line.
Pressed forward, racing four-away from outer fence 2L behind leader. Under pressure from 400m, one-paced final 200m.
Bumped head before start. Out quickly, taken to outer fence in midfield. Put under pressure from 450m but only one-paced. Had small wound top of head.
Began fairly, ridden forward, bumped and shifted in 800m, racing alone down centre track just behind pacemakers. Flattened final 100m.
Pressed forward 4-away from outer fence behind pacemakers. Looked chance when urged forward from 500m but gave ground quickly final 150m.
Hampered start, driven forward to get within 1L of leader at the 400m before tiring and dropping back. Had substantial blood in trachea.
Began OK, raced down centre field before laying out 800m. Under whip from 300m but little response.
Began awkwardly, urged forward along outer rail but ran out of gas passing 400m and finished tailed off.

Eased back from the jump to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover. Came wider on the turn, and came home up the centre of the track. Only ever ridden hands and heels, and won going away from them.
Began well and cruised up early to sit in a handy position, on the rails. Held up early in the straight, before finding clear running at the 300m. Ran on strongly, but well beaten by the winner late.
Eased into stride, settling midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Came wider on the turn, and plugged on gamely in the straight. Was weakening late, but held third.

Inconvenienced on jumping and taken back early to sit equal last, 9L off the leader and on the rail. Came wider on the turn, and ran on strongly in the straight, claiming the majority of the field and closing on 3rd.
Ridden forward early to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Battled on OK in the straight, only beginning to fade in the shadow of the post.
Began OK and eased forward to sit midfield on the fence. Boxed in on the fence until the 200m, when coming off heels for a run. Ran on OK when allowed to stride out from the 150m.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field, 2-3 wide. Came wider on the turn, but never responded to pressure, and only battled fairly to the line.

Allowed to drift back from the wide draw to sit equal last, 1 off the fence and 9L from the early leader. Came widest on the turn, and had a lot of ground to make up. Only ran on fairly, catching a few stragglers late.
OK away and eased forward to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Plugged away fairly in the run home.
Taken forward from the wide draw and crossed early to sit behind the early leader. Held up for a run at the top of the straight, getting clear at the 350m, but only went to the wire 1 paced.
Began OK, and taken forward early to sit just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Prominently placed at the top of the straight, but never responded. Dropped back and eased to the line.
Began awkwardly, but pushed hard early to lead by 3L at the 1000m. Led at the 300m, but weakening and dropped out from there to fade quickly in the run home.
Only fairly away and positioned just behind midfield, on the rail early. Only ran on fairly in the straight, and well beaten a long way out.
Began only fairly and only eased forward to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Only plugged away in the straight, and was easing up a long way from home.
