Broke well, settled just worse than midfield in 6th on rails, in similar position but became 5th midway down far side, saved ground turning in, obtained a clear run 250 metres out, quickened well to lead inside the 200 metres.
Taken back from the widest gate, waited with, came to challenge under pressure and went widest into straight, ran on well to miss narrowly.
Minor interference at start, settled in last few one off the rails, commenced run approaching home turn and wide turning in, finished off race nicely.
Broke well settling just over 2L back on rails in 4th before becoming 3rd far side, came under pressure entering straight, fought on steadily without quickening.
Slightly slow out, settled towards the rear on rails, baulked and forced to switch for a run upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start from a poor gate, worked his way forward before settling one off the rails in 2nd, hit the front from tiring leader momentarily upon straightening, soon weakened under pressure.
Ridden early, shared the pace on rails before kicking just over 1L clear, gave ground soon after straightening.
Niggled along from a poor draw to keep up with the pace early, settling in midfield from over 1000 metres out, dropped away steadily from home bend.
Jumped well from the middle draw, amongst leaders while crossing to rails before settling 2-wide 2L back in 4th far side, dropped away quickly from the 400 metres.
Settled in front of midfield on the fence, pace good, drifted away 200M to score.
Eased back as usual, pace good, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, lack room 300M, ran on ok.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, then hard ridden to take a midfield spot, pace good, lack room 4-2, made some ground.
Pushed to sit in midfield 2-3 wide, pace good, little dash 250M.
At back along the fence, pace good, lack room 250M, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward, just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, emptied 250M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, pace good, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, pace good, no turn of foot.
Eased back, pace good, never progressed.
Pushed early but not muster, never better than midfield.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, battled on strongly, hit the front final 50M, scored by 1/2L.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow tempo, kept on gamely until final 50M headed by the winner.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, ran on steadily to get 3rd.
Eased to rear, 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals, dashed well when clear for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow tempo and held up over the concluding stages, ran on nicely.
Taken back from a wide gate to take the rail, 6Ls behind the leader, despite the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Crowded start, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, one paced home.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, failed to make any impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Pushed to settle in front of midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, despite the slow pace, weakened soon after straightening.
Broke well, raced handy 3 wide with cover, ridden 450m & shifted wider into stretch, relentless progress to lead close home.
Outpaced at break & bustled to sit rail midfield, rolled on a spot 500m, driven 400m & switched out, closed off determinedly, nicked 2nd at wire.
Fast break, raced 1 off 1 back, driven 450m, progress & switched to rail in stretch, closing run to nick 3rd in blanket finish.
Sharp start & rousted early, rolled 3 wide to lead 1000m, slotted 1 off & restrained 910m to 0.5L 2nd, under pump 450m, grinding pursuit, edged out of frame late.
Speed to lead, snared rail & headed 1000m, led 910m & set tempo, shaken up final turn & quickened clear, emptied 75m, swamped close home.
Taken back at start, raced 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 500m, hard-ridden turning in & shifted out, ran on for minor late gains.
Broke ok, caught 3 wide no cover handy, niggled 500m, 3rd & driven into stretch, one-paced.
Dropped back from wide gate, raced 3 wide with cover & rolled on to sit behind midfield at 800m, driven wide into stretch, plugged home same speed.
Started ok but outpaced & bustled early, settled midfield 1 off with cover, outpaced & driven 300m, plodded on tamely.
Tardy start, recovered to race 1 back on rail, niggled 500m, weakening when driven final turn, tapered out.
Taken back from widest gate, soon detached at tail, under pressure to pass fading rival at 350m, plodded home weakly.
Slow start & busted initially to rail behind midfield, over-raced 1080m, soon niggled along 3rd last, under pump 650m, gave ground & last at 350m, faded out.
Rousted at break & handy, trapped wide & snagged 900m to slot rail midfield, niggled 450m, ridden into stretch & shifted centre track, battling closer, led last stride.
Slow start, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 500m, under pump & lacked toe turning in, responded & stayed on for strong late inroads, just failed.
Broke well, soon taken back to 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m, 5L back & driven wide into stretch, strong closer, just failed.
Sharp break, camped 4th 1 off with cover, shifted out final turn, shaken up 4 deep 300m, ran on to lead 70m, all out & headed last stride.
Sluggish start & niggled along 1 off with cover near rear, under pump 420m, staying on when checked off heels 100m, ran on again late.
Fast start widest & led 1100m, crossed to rail 970m, rolled 2L clear, driven 280m & boxed on, wandered out under pressure 150m, headed 70m, swamped.
Fast start, settled 1 back on rail, ridden 430m, outpaced & tapered in run home.
Slow break, raced rail near tail, driven 300m, kept on evenly.
Slow start, soon at tail & bustled along on outer, under pump 450m, 2L adrift turning in, stayed on for minor late headway.
Disputed lead at break, rousted 1050m to sit 2nd 1 off no cover at 830m, bustled 550m, hard-ridden into stretch, boxing on one-pace when checked off heels 150m & eased.
Smart break, soon outpaced & bustle, slid back to race 3 wide no cover near rear, driven widest into stretch, one-paced in run.
Rousted & handy 3 deep early stages, no cover & snagged to eventually slot midfield 1 off with cover at 550m, ridden under pressure 400m, wide into stretch, found little.
Pushed forward to occupy box-seat, 1-1/2L behind the leader. Ran on strongly down the Straight and held off challenge to score by a head.
Settled front of midfield 2-1/4L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Kept on challenging only to be beaten by a head.
Bumped on jumping, eased back to sit at rear along the rail, 4-1/2L behind. Remained along the rail down the Straight, dashed strongly for 3rd.
Raced forward to take lead by 3/4L along the rail. Hung on until final 150M headed.
Settled midfield and travelled 3L behind the leader on the rail. Remained one pace to the line.
Started from a wide gate and remained at rear along the rail, 6-1/4L behind. Unable to make significant ground in the Straight.
Settled midfield 3-1/2L off, 2 wide with cover. Obtained clear running after passing final 250L. Ran on only fairly.
Raced to obtain a forward position 3/4L off the pace, 2 wide without cover. Weakened after final 150M.
Remained at rear 5-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, shifted out to widest on straightening, was never a factor.
Settled in midfield from widest gate, 2-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover. Never looked likely.
Prominent, 1-1/4L behind, 3 wide and without cover. Swamped passing final 200M.
Jumped OK, settling midfield in one-off position. Picked up momentum entering straight and finished strongly between horses to win on line.
Got off fairly, taken to rail four-back from leader and allowed to settle. Took inside runs in straight and finished strongly to just fail.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Kicked clear entering straight and kept on strongly till swamped final 50m.
Jumped with field, ridden forward to hold one-off, one-back position. Urged forward top of straight but only one-paced final stages.
Away nicely, checked 1000m but able to hold on to box seat behind leader. Boxed on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly, ridden forward to sit outside leader to and around turn. Kept on well early in straight before tiring final stages.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail three-back from leader. Switched out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear along rail. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
Urged forward from outside draw, racing three-wide 3L from leader. Kept wide in straight but found little under pressure. Lame with cuts to right front leg.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide around turn towards the rear. Found little in straight when asked.
Ridden along early but not much speed, settling in one-off position at the rear. No response when popped the question in straight.
Bounded in the air when the gates opened, lost ground, dropping to last. Trailed field after that and never likely.
Had uncontested lead, took them along slowly middle stages, quickened up again 400M, opened up 2Ls lead mid-straight, dug deep late on to hold off fast finishing 2nd.
Began only fairly, settled down midfield 4Ls off leader, into clear 300M and closed off well, just one stride short of catching the winner.
Began well from draw 1, eased back to a position behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, made stealthy progress up the fence final 300M, got up for 3rd last stride but no impression on first two.
Chased leader in 3rd, kept on steadily in straight but not pace to challenge leaders, edged out to 4th final stride.
Held up 7-6Ls towards the rear, did best work final 200M, stayed on for non-threatening 5th.
From wide barrier slotted into 2-wide spot in 4th before the first turn, still within striking range 400M but kept on at the same pace under pressure.
Behind midfield and no closer than 3-wide for much of the way, stayed on only fairly over final 300M.
Went forward to sit one out one back, shaken up 400M but soon readily outpaced.
Failed to muster speed, caught 3-wide no cover, in mid-division from 1300M, not quickened turning in and never threatened.
Settled down 6Ls back near the rear, gave limited response when brought wide 400M.
Waited with in midfield, saved ground along inside but unable to obtain clear running to 100M, not properly tested.
Taken across behind runners, last of 12 8Ls off the pace, failed to pick up the pace when driven down outside of field.

Moderate start, settled behind midfield, came through nicely between runners over 200 metres out, gained upper hand close home.
With leaders briefly from a wide gate settling in rear of midfield, soon came to challenge under pressure in straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Very slowly away, trailed the field to straight, went widest on the turn, made significant progress down the centre of the track.
Broke well but soon settled better than midfield near rails, baulked for a run in similar position early in straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Slow out, travelled in last few, switched wide into straight, fought on nicely until unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Well there, failed to quicken to challenge the length of the straight.
Vied for lead from a poor gate, eventually crossing to rails in front coming out of back straight, under pressure to maintain advantage after straightening, swamped inside final 200 metres.
Settled just better than midfield mostly one off the rails, ran on steadily to hold some chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped well from a poor gate to travel amongst leaders, not far off in 3rd when 3-wide around home bend, one-paced when badly checked over 200 metres out.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, ridden along to hold position before settling one back on rails coming out of back straight, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Jumped well from the widest gate, ridden along to hold place eventually gaining narrow advantage 2-wide rounding home bend, dropped out tamely shortly after straightening.
Slow out, always well behind.
Hard ridden to share the lead 2 wide, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Settled in midfield along the fence, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden for box seat, ran on well for 3rd.
Midfield 2-3 wide, pace good, made steady progress 300M.
Eased at start, too rail at rear, pace good, progressed steadily 400M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward 2 wide, pace good, ran on until 100M flattened.
Eased back 2-3 wide, pace good, made some late ground 200M.
At rear along the fence, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, paced good, soon out of fuel 300M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, reduced 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, soon emptied 300M.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader without cover, enjoyed the slow sectionals, battled on strongly, hit the front final 100M, scored by 3/4L.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, fought on gamely until final 100M headed by the winner, hung on for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at slow pace, kept on nicely until final furlong weakened for 3rd.
Eased to rear, travelled 11Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals, closed off well for 4th.
Settled midfield, 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Camped handy, travelled 4Ls behind the leader along the fence, suited by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo and unable to find a day night early straight, dashed well thereafter.
Jumped slowly as usual, travelled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow sectionals, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, trapped 3 wide without cover most race, never a threat.
Settled worse than midfield about 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, never looked likely.
Always at rear, travelled 10Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Raced in front of midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on once pace until final 300M flattened.
Sharp break, bustled along initially to settle 2nd 1 off no cover, closed to press lead 400m, hard-ridden down stretch, edged duel at wire.
Good start & bustled to lead 1150m, scooted 2L clear & to rail 950m, restrained in front exiting back stretch, driven under pressure 300m, lost duel final stride.
Speed to lead, quickly to rail & headed 1150m, stalked 1 back, switched 1 off 400m, & driven, battled on evenly to claim 3rd.
Smart start, camped 4th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep 530m & progress to press lead turning in, peaked on run 230m & tapered to wire.
Stumbled start, bustled rail to race fore of midfield, shifted out final turn & stayed on evenly centre track.
Broke well, snagged back to sit 1 off with cover near rear, checked off heels 700m, driven into stretch & stayed on moderately.
Fast break, taken back from wide gate but caught on outer without cover, progress from 550m, driven 7 wide into stretch, kept on one-pace.
Slow start & niggled on rail at tail until advanced a spot 700m, outpaced & ridden 450m, stayed on past beaten rivals.
Taken back from widest gate to race rear rank 1 off with cover, driven widest into stretch, plugged on tepidly centre track.
Slow break, raced behind midfield on rail, outpaced on turn & shuffled back under pressure, unable to quicken, plodded on tamely.
Dropped back from wide berth to sit 3 wide with cover near rear, off heels 700m & to tail, niggled 550m, shifted centre track, never a factor.
Broke ok, slotted midfield 1 off with cover, driven 500m & 6 wide into stretch, found nil & faded to wire.
Broke well, bustled until soon settled mid rank 3 wide with cover, progress on turn, switched out turning in & driven, quickened to lead 340m, drew clear.
Slow start & bustled last pair, settled1 off near rear, over-raced 850m, progress on turn but crowded until driven 320m, quickened to 2nd 200m, always held.
Sluggish start, raced 1 off behind midfield, switched 3 deep with cover 650m, driven wider turning in, tracked winner's run, stayed on but always held.
Broke ok, sat rail 1 back, retrained off heels 800m & shuffled to midfield, under pump final turn, not clear run 400m, stayed on final 250m for minor headway.
Broke well, raced wide to lead 1100m, crossed to rail 900m, 1L clear & driven 400m, all out & headed 340m, tapered to wire.
Tardy start & rousted wide, soon taken back & niggled 3 wide with cover near rear, edged 4 wide no cover 600m, widest & driven into stretch, plugged on for modest headway.
Broke ok, soon outpaced & drifted back to last pair, niggled along 1 off, shifted 3 deep 550m, driven into stretch & plugged on centre track.
Broke ok, driven forward to rail & sat 1 back, niggled 650m, driven turning in, tame progress checked when not clear run 70m.
Broke well & rousted to lead, eased & headed 1100m, raced 1L 2nd 1 off no cover, to 3rd & ridden under pressure home turn, plodded on tamely.
Sharp start, restrained to race 1 off fore of midfield, driven under pressure final turn, struggled in fading run.
Fast start, snagged back to mid rank but trapped 4 deep, rolled to 3rd 3 wide no cover at 800m, eased way to 2nd turning in, driven 400m, found nil & faded.
Slow start & raced rail last pair, under pump 500m, clear last & hard-driven 440m, plodded on tamely.
Broke well, lacked toe & raced rail behind midfield, snatched off heels 580m, 3rd last & driven 430m, struggled in run home.
Urged forward to occupy box-seat, 1-1/4L behind. Despite the fast pace, dashed well from final 400M, gradually overhauled leader to score.
Raced worse than midfield 3-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Suited to the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Taken out on jumping, settled midfield 3L off, 2 wide with cover. Gradually improved, suited the fast face, finished off well for 3rd.
Pushed forward to take rail and led at fast sectionals by 1-1/4L. Eventually overtaken by winner when passing final 200M.
Eased to sit worse than midfield from a wide gate 4-1/2L off, 2 wide with cover. Benefited by the fast tempo, improved gradually from final 300M.
Prominent, however raced 3 wide without cover initially, 1-1/2L off. Not suited to the fast tempo, weakened after final 150M.
Settled midfield 3L behind the leader, initially 3 wide with cover then without. Crowded when approaching final 300M, faded thereafter.
Eased back to sit at rear 6-3/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Raced widest in the Straight. Never created an impression.
Travelled at rear along the rail throughout, 5L off. Never a factor.
Raced front of midfield 2-3/4L behind the leader, initially 2 wide without cover. Not suited to the fast pace, swamped passing final 200M.
Eased back and travelled at rear from widest gate 6-1/4L behind along the rail. Never a threat.
Crowded on jumping. Raced along the rail in midfield, 2-3/4 off. Offer little when asked in the straight.
Bumped heavily start, not pushed, dropping behind main bunch in one-off position. Swung wide into straight, finished strongly to just get there.
Pressed forward to hold box seat. Got clear run 400m, ridden forward but kept shifting under pressure. Hands and heels final stages and pipped on post.
Hard ridden early to hold rail inside leader before being eased 1L back in one-off position 950m. Urged forward 400m, took lead 250m, run down final 50m.
Began fairly, driven forward to settle 3-back along rail 900m. Stayed on rail entering straight and boxed on gamely.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, crossing to rail 850m. Kept on well when collared 250m but swamped final stages.
Began fairly, ridden but didn't muster, then taken across behind horse to find cover at rear. Swung wide into straight and boxed on fairly.
Began OK, ridden aggressively but didn't muster, dropping to last along rail. Shaken up 450m, made some ground but checked 150m when laying in.
Driven forward and held 3-wide without cover 1.5L from leader. Awkwardly placed 300m and lay in after 100m when giving ground.
Bumped heavily start, driven forward settling three-wide 3L behind leader. Unbalanced 500m, kept on fairly in straight until tiring final stages.
Urged forward but wide, settling behind midfield. Swung very wide into straight but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners settling at rear in one-off position. Shaken up top of straight but found little.
Hard ridden to go forward from outside draw, racing wide to and around turn 3L from leader. Gave ground in straight and finished tailed off.
Never far off in 5th, unleashed 400M and quickened impressively to lead 200M, drifted in when clear, continued on strongly final stages for fifth consecutive wins.
Held up in mid-division, 8th and 5Ls off the pace middle stages, stayed on well to go 2nd near 50M, no chance with impressive winner.
Tracked leaders, switched out 450M to challenge, quickened to lead 300M, not pace of winner 200M, failed to sustain run final stages, lost 2nd 50M out.
Settled 4Ls off the pace, 3-wide no cover throughout, ridden to challenge 500M, stayed on well and every chance in straight, just missed 3rd.
Settled down behind midfield 6-7Ls behind leaders in strongly run race, rallied final 200M, did best work towards finish.
Held up behind mid-division, 6Ls off leaders 400M, stayed on moderately and every chance throughout final 300M.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, loomed a threat early straight, run ended passing 150M and turned one pace, swamped by rivals late stages.
Dropped back to last, over 10Ls off the pace mid-stages, made some progress final 400M but never reached contention.
Crowded for room on jumping, soon pushed along to take up position ahead of midfield, kept on same pace in straight, never a threat to leaders.
Sent forward, vied for lead on outside setting fast pace, not finishing pace of rivals inside 300M, weakened towards the line.
Near the rear, 8Ls behind leaders in a strongly run race, driven wide 400M but gave limited response.
From wide barrier shifted across behind runners early stages, settled 2nd last 10Ls off the strong pace middle stages, ran past only beaten runners in straight.
Driven forward, vied for lead setting fast pace, gave way 300M, weakened rapidly towards finish.
Found cover in midfield before making the turn but no closer than 3-wide throughout, outpaced early straight, no extra 200M.
Began well, urged forward to sit outsider leader to straight, rolled forward to lead passing 300m before pulling clear.
Pressed forward to take lead along rail on settling. Set steady pace to straight, collared 300m but kept on gamely.
Jumped with field, ridden along to sit one-back, one-off. Shaken up top of straight and battled on gamely.
Pressed forward from an outside draw and held three-wide, three-back but with cover. Made steady progress in straight under whip.
Began well, restrained and shifted across behind runners, settling towards rear away from fence. Had clear running from 350m and kept on steadily under vigorous riding.
Quickly out but eased into box seat on settling. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance at 300m, then one-paced.
Bumped start, steadied, shifted across behind runners to rail, settling just behind midfield. No clear run in straight until passing 200m, kept on fairly.
Allowed to roll forward at own pace, settling between horses in midfield. Raced in restricted room top of straight but only one-paced when clear.
Pressed forward, racing three-wide without cover behind leading pair. Shaken up top of straight but found nothing and weakened.
Ridden along early but unable find cover and drifted towards rear in one-off position. Swung very wide into straight but failed to quicken under pressure.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling a long last. Never competitive.
Began OK, pressed forward in one-off position behind midfield, taken wide in straight, kept on fairly till 200m before tiring.

Started well from the inside gate, finding a handy position on the rail. Went to the turn under a hold, and was let down from the 350m. Didn't need much encouragement in the straight, and was easing late.
Began well, but not used up and steadied into a position forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Well placed on the turn and stayed on well, but lost touch of winner at the 150m.
Slowly away and dropped back to be towards the rear of the field, on the rail. Needed some luck in the run, but ran on well from a rear position in the straight, gaining on 2nd late.
Broke well from the wide barrier and allowed to drop back to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider in the straight, and ran to the line solidly.
Began OK and pushed forward before easing and eventually settling towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Ridden for luck in the straight, and finished off OK without threatening a place.
OK away and taken forward to sit midfield, on the fence. Ran on OK in the straight, without much luck, but was never threatening a place position.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to eventually sit behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Well placed at the top of the straight, but failed to kick, and went to the line 1 paced.

Shifted out on jumping, and taken back to sit at the rear of the field, 2-3 wide with some cover. Came onto heels 700m. Began to run on from the top of the straight, but never got clear and went to the line untested.
Came across quickly from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield, 2-3 wide. Came wider on the turn, and only battled away to the line.

Slightly awkward away and sat back in a position towards the rear of the field, 2-3 wide with limited cover. Came onto heels 900m. Came widest from the 300m and only ran on fairly, saving his best for the end.
Began well and taken forward early to be handily placed, 1 off the fence. Well place on the turn, but only plodded to the line and was easing late.
Crowded on jumping and forced to drop to the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Came onto heels 800m, and dropped back further to be 10L last. Plugged away in the straight without much pressure.

OK away, and pushed forward to take the early lead before being crossed at the 900m. Slightly boxed in at the top of the straight, but never responded to pressure at any time and dropped out quickly, easing late.

Began awkwardly, but stoked up and taken forward to lead by the 1000m. Bumped and unbalanced at the 900m, and pulled from that point until the top of the straight. Burnt out early and faded out to be a long last.

Broke well settling one-out-one-back to straight, soon came to challenge upon straightening, gained upper hand final strides.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on rails, kept to inside run on straightening, fought on steadily only to be denied in the shadows of the post.
Settled in forward in midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on to just claim remote 3rd.
Broke well from the one draw and attempted to make all holding narrow advantage on rails, but unable to sustain effort and headed under pressure 200 metres out.
Sluggish at start, settled in rear of midfield, came under pressure entering straight, kept on same pace under pressure down the centre of the track.
Moderate start, soon recovered to better than midfield on rails, similar turning for home, one-paced.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped towards the rear, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Well behind, ran past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight.
Trailed the field most of way to straight, only ran past well-beaten horses.
Crowded out start, raced 5 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to sit outside leader, same position on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 100M.
Worked overtime from the widest draw to keep in touch but remained wide throughout, tired noticeably from approaching home straight.
Hard ridden to obtain the rail and led by 1L, hung on to win just by a nose at the post.
Eased back 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M, just missed by a nose in 2nd.
Very slow away, took rail at back, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, pace good, ran on well until 100M flattened.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, at back 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
Bumped start, at rear 2 wide, pace good, progressed around the field 4 wide, made some ground.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, flattened 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, never improved.
Hard ridden forward 2 wide, pace good, dropped off quickly 400M.
Driven forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to the line by 1/2L.
Pushed forward to settle outside the leader, enjoyed the slow tempo, kept on nicely to get 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow pace, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, one paced home.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Failed to muster despite being ridden along, settled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Jumped slowly, then settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, never looked a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, never looked likely.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slow pace, weakened 200M.
Eased to settle worse than midfield from a wide gate, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Broke well but niggled a touch to race midfield, shifted 3 deep with cover 1000m & shuffled back, driven wide for progress 420m, quickened but hung in 250m, led 200m, held on at wire.
Sluggish start & niggled at tail on rail, rapid advance 1000m to midfield, driven into stretch, powered home & just failed.
Good break, settled rail in 4th, shifted 1 off 1000m & shuffled to midfield, driven 400m, quickened to 2nd at 150m but emptied & tapered.
Taken back at start & raced at rear, niggled along 700m, driven wide 400m, stayed on centre track for minor headway.
Broke well & shared early lead, eased to stalk 1 back on rail, switched out final turn & driven, boxed on one pace.
Tardy break, raced rail midfield until shifted 3 wide 1000m, under pump 400m, swung wide final turn, squeezed up & lost momentum 250m, kept on evenly.
Held up at break, raced near tail 1 off with cover, niggled 750m, not clear run & switched off heels 250m, recovered for minor inroads.
Smart break & rousted to lead 1600m, to rail 1300m, slowed tempo in backstretch, wound it up on turn, neck ahead & driven into stretch, all out & headed 200m, weakened.
Taken back from wide gate & bustled along near tail, advanced wide from 1000m to sit 3rd 3 deep no cover at 800m, hard-driven turning in, lacked toe, badly hampered 220m, no extra.
Sharp start to share early lead, snagged to settle 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed leader final turn & driven, emptied 300m & faded fast.

Placing: PU
Comment: Moderate break but driven & soon prominent, snagged to slot fore of midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 1200m & hung out, eased 1100m & pulled-up.
Fast start, led under hold 700m & to rail 600m, kicked-on 300m, driven out to maintain advantage to wire.
Fast break on fence, settled 1 back, shifted out final turn & driven to 2nd 200m, kept on but always held.
Pressed early lead, relented 750m & bustled along 1 off 1 back, under pump 450m, 5th & shifted out home turn, bumped rival 240m, boxed on to 3rd 170m, one-paced to wire.
Rousted start to settle midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 550m, driven wide into stretch, rattled home late, just missed 3rd.
Missed break, soon recovered & rolled on rail to midfield, strong traveller 400m, driven into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Held up at start, 3 deep initially & slotted 1 off at tail 600m, switched widest into stretch & shaken up, ran on centre track for minor headway.
Sharp start, soon outpaced & rousted 3 deep with cover midfield, under pump & outpaced 550m, wide into stretch, plugged on tamely.
Fast break, rousted to dispute lead but unable to dominate, settled close 2nd 1 off at 600m & niggled along, under pressure turning in, driven 400m, emptied 200m & faded.
Broke ok, outpaced & raced near tail on rail, rousted to push 1 off 500m, hard-driven & continued to shift out turning in, ran on moderately.
Broke ok, niggled along on rail behind midfield, driven & shifted out home turn, plugged on tepidly.
Sharp start widest, pumped along handy but unable to press lead & raced 2L back 3 deep no cover, plugging on centre track when bumped 240m, weakened out.
Snagged back at start to race near tail 1 off with cover, forced 3 wide 500m, checked on turn, found nil in run home.
Rolled into front of midfield 5L behind, 2 wide with cover. Dashed well from final 200M to score.
Restrained from a wide gate to travel along the rail at rear, 9-1/2L off. Made steady headway down the Straight, only to be beaten by an impressive winner.
Raced midfield along the rail, 4-1/4L behind the leader. Remained along the rail down the Straight, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain box-seat 1-1/4L off the pace. Remained prominent down the Straight until weakened passing final 100M.
Prominent, 3-1/2L behind, 2 wide with cover. Swung wide when rounding Home Turn, ran on fairly.
Settled front of midfield along the rail, 2-3/4L behind the leader. Ran home one paced.
Settled worse than midfield 6-1/2L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Shifted out to widest on straightening but unable to make significant ground.
Crowded shortly after the Start. Travelled worse than midfield along the rail, 6-1/4L behind. Failed to make any impression.
Eased to rear, 7-1/2L behind the leader on the fence. Improved when rounding the Home Turn, however, weakened passing final 150M.
Race in restricted room shortly after the Start. Remained at rear 7-3/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Never a factor.
Pushed to take up lead along the rail from widest gate and led by 1-1/4L, weakened soon after straightening.
Pushed to settle just off the leader 1-3/4L behind, 2 wide without cover. Swamped when rounding the Home Turn.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners, last on settling before edging forward at turn. Wide into straight, finished strongly down centre track for comfortable win.
Began well, racing outside leader to 700m before being eased to sit 1.5L back in one-off position. Took inside run in straight, hit front 200m, run down final stages.
Ridden forward from outside draw before getting cover one-off, three-back at turn. Shaken up 350m and kept on well to grab minor placing.
Vigorously ridden to stay with pace, racing 4-wide without cover. Urged forward 300m to look a chance but hung in from 100m, one-paced.
Hard ridden to lead on settling then steadied pace. Joined up front 850m, kicked ahead 300m but caught passing 200m, swamped final stages.
Beaten for early pace, settling behind midfield close to fence. Took inside run on entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield but away from fence. Checked 400m, awkwardly placed in straight and not ridden out final stages.
Not pushed, settling between horses at rear. Urged forward top of straight, made some ground to 200m before turning one-paced.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners but still forced to race wide at rear. Improved position around turn but one-paced in straight.
Began well, urged forward but crowded and lost ground 500m, dropping three-back. Crowded again 400m, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden to go forward, joining leader from 850m to straight. Spent force passing 200m and faded.
Badly crowded out at start, losing ground and dropping back. Clear last approaching 800m and trailed field thereafter.
Prominently placed, pressed leader from 1000M, responded well when driven along 400M, led 200M out and always had enough to hold off rivals.
Chased leaders 2-wide, proved difficult to settle when pace slackened middle stages, 3-wide bid outside eventual winner 450M, ran on well but was always held.
Held up in mid-division, switched out from fence 550M, ran on steadily to line, almost got up for 2nd but couldn't reach winner.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace down the back-straight, waited with on the inside, stayed on moderately, one paced final 150M and no threat to leaders from thereon.

Driven after the start but outpaced by early leaders, settled 3-4Ls back, pushed to 2-wide from 1200M, under pressure and looked beaten at top of straight but responded to jockey's perseverance to claim 5th.
Held up towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, left with no cover 1000M then strode forward to take up running, hung on to the lead till 200M, weakened towards finish.
Near the rear, caught wide throughout, moved closer to pace passing 900M, kept on fairly in straight, never a serious threat.
Shifted across behind runners early, settled down 7Ls back in the rear, made limited progress final 350M, not reached contention.
Shifted across behind runners early, reserved in the rear 7Ls behind leader, driven wide into straight, ran on only fairly.
Patiently ridden in a rearward position along the fence, bided his time but couldn't pick up when asked inside 350M.
Crossed to the lead 1400M, proved difficult to settle when being steadied behind leaders, kept on same pace in straight, no extra passing 200M. (Lame next day)
Caught wide early stages, used a bit to find the lead, relinquished lead 600M out, weakened to last in straight.

Soon took up running and gradually crossed to stands side while setting a smart pace, held on well to finish.
Broke well to travel just off the pace behind the leader, switched in to challenge coming onto course proper, unable to draw level throughout final stages.
Moderate start, raced in 5th well over 5 lengths back while heading the detached group, fought on under pressure to reach remote 3rd 150 metres out.
Settled well back, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, niggled along near the centre of the track in distant 6th, one-paced closing stages.
Well there on rails, unable to sustain effort inside final 300 metres.
Soon dropped to last few racing keenly, only ran past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Bumped at start, raced in first few but behind heels 400 metres out before folded up quickly.
Slightly slow out, soon in rear on rails, baulked at around halfway out, made no impression closing stages.
Settled behind midfield, found nothing in the run home.
Bumped after a moderate start, always in last few.
Soon dropped behind midfield, gave ground noticeably while racing awkwardly after coming onto course proper.
Settled in prominent spot 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, enjoyed the slow sectionals outside the leader, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, overhauled 300M, ran on for 3rd.
Slow away, hard ridden to hold box seat, blocked 4-2, little dash when clear.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Eased to rear, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, little dash 200M.
Midfield 2 wide, dashed only fairly in straight.
Very slow away, at back but on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up most straight, not tested.
AT back 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
At rear, never improved.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Eased back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, dashed strongly to score comfortably.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, ran on well for 2nd until final 50M headed by the winner.
Settled in front of midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 3rd until final 100M weakened.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, stayed on well despite being held up early straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, shifted out rounding the Home Turn, ran on steadily until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on gradually despite lack of room after 200M.
Raced worse than midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Raced in front of midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until final 200M weakened.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led from a wide gate, kept on until final 300M weakened.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover most race, soon weakened after straightening.
Taken back to snag rail behind midfield, advanced a spot 750m, switched out final turn, shaken up 350m & quickened under drive to lead 150m, drew clear & eased final stride.
Fast start to dispute early lead, raced 1L 2nd 1 off no cover, shuffled to 4th 1 off 1 back 1000m, 3 deep final turn, rolled to lead 350m, driven 1L clear 300m, peaked & headed 150m, kept on.
Broke ok, raced midfield on rail, rolled forward a spot 800m, switched out 400m & driven 350m, advanced to 3rd in even run home.
Taken back at start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, edged wide into home stretch & bumped rival, driven 400m, closed off soundly to wire.
Started well & prominent, soon snagged to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, switched out & driven in contention 440m, briefly vied for 3rd, one paced & tapered late.
Slow start, taken to rail & raced last trio, advanced a spot 900m, driven into stretch & shifted out, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke well, rousted to settle midfield 1 off with cover, edged out final turn, driven centre track 350m, kept on one pace.
Broke ok but trapped 4 wide no cover behind midfield, niggled 1050m, driven on turn, hard-ridden 400m, plugged on evenly.
Taken back at start to 1 off with cover last trio, last & niggled 800m, driven into stretch, stayed on moderately centre track.
Sluggish start, taken back to race rear rank 3 deep with cover, 2nd last & driven 500m, plodded home tamely.
Broke ok to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, pushed widest final turn & bumped, driven 400m, ran home tepidly.
Fast start & rousted to sit 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off 400m & shaken up, hard-ridden in 2nd 300m, emptied 250m & faded.
Driven from wide gate to lead 1500m, crossed to rail 1320m, shaken up 430m, all out & headed 350m, weakened out.
Sluggish start from widest gate & hard ridden back in field, pushed on wide no cover to press lead 1000m, slotted 0.5L 2nd 1 off, under pressure 500m, soon emptied & faded.
Broke well, taken back & settled behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in & switched wide, quickened up 300m & charged late to lead close home.
Good break, taken back to midfield, rousted 1150m to fore of midfield 3 wide no cover, pushed 4 deep 600m, advanced to press lead final turn, driven in 3rd 430m, kept on dourly to 2nd.
Speed widest & pressed leader 1 off no cover, vied for lead final turn & bumped rival, driven 350m & led 300m, kicked 1L clear, peaked 100m, tapered & headed close home.
Decent break, taken back to behind midfield but caught 4 deep no cover, driven centre track 400m, closed off for sound headway without threatening.
Missed break, recovered & pace to advance & slot 1 off 1 back at 950m, shifted 3 deep no cover 620m, rolled to lead turning in, outpaced & headed 300m, boxed on evenly.
Taken back at start to 1 off near tail, over-raced 750m, shifted out final turn, driven 400m, stayed on for minor late inroads.
Fast start to lead, bustled to snag rail 1020m, headed 520m & under pressure when bumped turning in, outpaced but plugged on when beaten.
Fast start, settled on rail fore of midfield, shuffled back on turn, stayed on one pace.
Moderate break, quickly rolled forward to settle 1 back on rail, driven 430m, plodded on tepidly.
Dropped in from wide gate to sit 3 deep with cover near tail, driven wide final turn, plugged on same speed.
Dropped in from wide gate to race at tail, shifted widest into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Slow start, over-raced 1200m, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, advanced a place on turn, driven into stretch but struggled in run home.
Missed break, rolled on to sit rail behind midfield, under pump home turn & shifted centre track, found nil in weak run to wire.
Broke well, sat fore of midfield 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, found nil & weakened tamely.
Settled worse than midfield 6-1/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Suited to the fast tempo, made steady headway from 400M and found extra gear from 250M to score.
Raced forward 1-1/2L off the pace along the rail. Despite the fast tempo, kept on strongly for 2nd.
Restrained to travel at rear along the rail, 8-1/2L behind the leader. Shifted out widest upon straightening, benefited by the fast pace, dashed well for 3rd.
Settled midfield 4-3/4L off, 3 wide with cover. Suited to the fast tempo, ran on nicely.
Raced front of midfield 4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Remained one paced to the line.
Midfield, 5-1/4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Towards the rear when straightening, progressed steadily from final 400M.
Prominent, 2-3/4L off the pace, along the rail. Not suited to the fast tempo, headed passing final 200M.
Eased back from a wide gate, remained 8-1/4L behind the leader, 3 wide with cover. Made steady headway, one paced home.
Raced forward to take lead by 1-1/2L, not suited to the fast tempo, headed passing final 250M.
Travelled front of midfield 2-1/2L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Harmed by the fast pace, run ended passing final 300M.
Worse than midfield, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover. Did not improve.
Raced at rear along the rail, 7L off the pace. No impression throughout.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Settled midfield 4-1/2L behind the leader, flattened passing final 300M.
Quickly into stride, taking clear lead passing 800m. Put under pressure final 400m but kept finding for solid win.
Began OK, not pushed, settling behind pace. Lengthened nicely from 400m, checked by riderless horse 50m, kept on well.
Crowded out at start, taken to outer fence, settling 3L from leader. Badly held for clear run until 150m when finished strongly.
Jumped with field, not pressured, racing four-wide behind pace. Rolled forward 400m, looked chance 200m, checked 50m by riderless horse.
Began well, racing between early leaders before taking sit 700m. Urged forward from 400m, kept on well to 200m, turning one-paced.
Began fairly, switched out, settling towards rear. Shaken up from 400m, lengthened stride nicely from 100m, doing best work at finish.
Pressed forward from inside draw, racing down centre track before edging closer to leader at halfway mark. Gave ground gradually final 300m.
Slow into stride, dropping to rear, then awkwardly placed passing 800m. Switched to outer fence 200m and finished off nicely.
Began best, leading for a few strides before settling a neck behind leader from 800m. Failed to respond when put under pressure from 400m. Had substantial blood in trachea.
Began well, racing between horses close to the pace. Got within striking range passing 400m before turning one-paced.
Quickly into stride, racing close to pace before easing off approaching 400m. Held up passing 100m when one-paced.
Began fairly, lost left front plate soon after start, settling at rear. Never competitive. Rider reported horse became unbalanced and reluctant to stretch out after losing plate.
Bumped start, used up early down centre track to get within 3L of leader passing 600m. Gave ground quickly final 400m.

Placing: UR
Comment: Lifted leg at start causing rider to make contact with barrier, becoming unbalanced and being dislodged.
Reserved behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, ran on determinedly entering straight, went past leader closing stages and just managed to hold off fast finishing 2nd on the line.
Outpaced early and middle stages, detached from main group 6Ls behind leaders, picked up strongly from 300M, switched out to chase leaders inside 200M, just one stride short of catching winner.
Soon led, took them along at good pace, continued on strongly in straight, caught by first 2 near line.
Never far off within 3Ls of pacesetter, chased leaders from 350M, battled between horses inside 200M, rallied and just missed 3rd.
Tracked leader along the fence, loomed a threat early straight, kept on moderately passing mid-straight, outpaced late stages.
Stumbled badly at the start losing ground, over 10Ls off the pace mid stages, driven 600M, made good progress in remainder of race to be beaten less than 2L.
Soon taken across to the fence, settled 3-4Ls back in midfield, stayed on mildly final 250M.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, ranged 3-wide 400M, always held by leaders, failed to sustain run final 150M.
Driven forward, unable to slot in and was wide without cover throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Pressed leader on outside, faded passing 300M, eased mid-straight. (No Vet findings)
Lost touch from the start, over 10Ls behind, never involved.
3-wide in midfield throughout, laid out making the turn, beaten at 400M.
Began well but restrained, dropping three back. Awkwardly placed 800m, switched wide turn, finished strongly under whip to just get there.
Jumped awkwardly, losing ground, settling at rear in one-off position. Still well back entering straight, switched wide and finished off strongly to just miss.
Began OK, racing between horses behind midfield to and around turn. Tightened 300m, no clear run early in straight, finished strongly when clear.
Jumped well, pressed forward while seeking cover, settling three-wide behind midfield. Taken wider in straight and finished off strongly.
Pressed forward from jump but caught three-wide from 900m without cover. Urged forward from turn, hit front 200m, flattened final 100m.
Began well, pressed forward to hold fence 2L from leader. Stayed on rail entering straight and kept on solidly until swamped final stages.
Pressed forward between horses, settling behind leaders in one-off position. Kept on well in straight to look a chance 200m before flattened final 50m.
First out, pressed forward before settling a half length behind leader 700m. Rolled forward to share lead 300m, kept on well till swamped final 50m.
Quickly into stride, taking lead on settling and crossing to fence. Slowed pace turn, joined up front 300m but kept battling till swamped final stages.
Crowded out start, taken to fence and urged forward, closing in to midfield around turn. Kept on well early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Crowded out start, dropping to rear on one-off position. Shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Outpaced and soon in last pair along fence. Never competitive.
Began well and pushed forward early to be in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, and was well positioned late. Hard ridden home, and just scraped in late.
Eased out early to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Ridden for luck early in the straight, before getting clear running at the 300m. Ran on strongly late, and closing on the winner at the wire.
Pushed out early from the wide gate to be handily place behind the leaders, 1 off the fence. Always in a nice position in the straight and led at the 100m, only to be run down late.

Eased forward early to find a position midfield, on the rails. Came wider on the turn looking for room, but had little luck early. Ran on well when clear, before off heels and tightened last 100m. Ran well late.
Began well and allowed to cruise forward early, just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Had no luck in the straight until the last 100m, and ran on gamely from there.
Crowded and stead soon after the jump and found a position 1 off the fence, just forward of midfield. Prominently placed early in the straight, but only plugged to the line late.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 4th, on the rails. No clear running until coming off heels at 200m, but only ran to the line fairly after that.
Cruised out early to be at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Widest in the straight, but only ran to the line fairly and 1 paced late.
Keen early and taken forward to lead, 1 off the fence. Well positioned in the straight, but was a tired horse late and dropped out from the 150m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to be the early back marker, 12L off the leader. Only ran on fairly in the straight, and never threatened.
OK away, and eased up to be worse than midfield before over racing onto heels at the 1400m. Didn't let down when asked in the straight, and packed up from the 150m when not improving.
Only away fairly from the inside barrier, and elected to sit at the rear of the field. Was never in the race, and was eased out late.
Began well and taken forward early to share the lead, on the rails. Never responded to pressure at any stage, and dropped back from the 300m to finish last.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back in 5th, travelled well on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Away with them, raced 5 lengths back in midfield, same position on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear final 200M to get 2nd.
Slightly slow out, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some headway, just missed 2nd.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 9 lengths back at rear, still 6 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail for the majority of the race, taken wide in straight and made decent progress.

Jumped well from gate 1, showed early speed to take the lead, kept them going at a moderate tempo, held narrow advantage on turn, kicked clear early in straight, headed final 100M and weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide behind midfield, got its head up when awkwardly placed on heels near 1000M, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.

Slowly away, recovered to race in 11th, 8 lengths back on rail, kept to inside after turning in, no daylight in straight and held up for clear running over the concluding stages, not able to be ridden out near the finish.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover early, found cover on turn, finished off one-paced.
Fast into stride from inside alley, positioned outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in 8th, similar position on turn, angled out near 500M, showed no response to riding in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover at rear, slightly improved on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail for the majority of the race, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Jumped with them, raced 3 lengths back on rail in 4th, easy run on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 150M.

Jumped well, niggled along just off the pace on rails, angled out to challenge turning in, gained upper hand close to home.
Broke well to lead and attempted to make all, headed under pressure close to home.
Soon settled 3-wide in midfield from a wide gate, widest runner turning in, ran on steadily under pressure down the centre of the track, nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled on rails in midfield or just worse, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped moderately, settled behind midfield, baulked 200 metres out, finished off well once into the clear in closing stages.
Broke well, gradually taken back to better than midfield to race mainly in 6th 3-wide, obtained rails run passing the 400 metres and saved ground turning in, failed to quicken under pressure.
Niggled along in midfield from a wide gate, improved steadily down far side to a prominent position 3-wide around the bend, faded gradually under pressure after straightening.
Taken back from a wide draw, remained one from last to straight, fought on steadily but without threatening.
Ridden along to keep in touch settling one-out-one-back, lost position rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Began moderately, soon driven up the firing line, obtained position just outside the leader coming onto home bend, however, folded up quickly after straightening.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Soon outpaced.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly to score.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pressed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off well to the line.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear.
Eased back 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 2-3 wide, weakened 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 4 wide throughout, flattened 250M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, dashed well when clear 300M, scored impressively with plenty in hand by 3Ls.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on well until 200M headed by an impressive winner.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to settle in a prominent position, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader from a wide gate, kept on one pace until 250M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, made no impression in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, weakened soon after straightening.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Taken back from a wide gate, never a factor.
Broke well, niggled to settle rail midfield, niggled briefly 700m, shaken up 300m, grinding progress to lead final strides.
Broke well widest & crossed to lead on rail 1st turn, steady tempo until shaken up a touch 700m, driven 1.5L clear turning in, all out 150m, dug in but headed close home.
Taken back after smart start, raced on inner behind midfield, niggled 500m & shifted out, driven 420m, wide into stretch, closed off centre track to nick 3rd late.
Taken back to rail at rear, last & ridden 450m for gradual progress, stayed on fence until shifted out 75m & impeded rival, kept on to just miss frame.
Broke well, sat 1 back on rail, driven 350m & shifted out entering stretch, boxed on one-pace in 2nd until tapered & swamped close home.
Tardy start & bustled early, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, niggled 450m, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on evenly.
Keen but restrained at break to race midfield 1 off with cover, niggled from 700m, hard driven 300m, one-paced in run, snatched off heels close home.
Fast start & raced 2nd 1 off no cover, niggled 650m, driven 500m, found little & gradually faded in run home.
Broke ok & bustled early to race fore of midfield 3 wide no cover, gained cover 700m & under pump 650m, plodded home one pace.
Broke ok & bumped, taken back to rear 1 off, last pair & ridden on turn, plodded on same speed.
Slow start & bumped, raced on outer at tail, shifted 4 deep 900m & rapid advance to 3rd at 730m, 4th & driven under pressure 450m, soon emptied & faded.
Broke well but immediately outpaced & bustled along 3 wide with cover behind midfield, under pump 700m & continued to drift back, driven 430m, plodded home tamely.
Broke ok, bustled early to race behind midfield 1 off with cover, shaken up 900m for 3 wide advance & led 770m, to rail 700m, 1L clear & shaken up 350m, quickened & forged on to wire.
Broke ok, early speed to slot 1 off with cover midfield, under pump 400m for 3 wide progress, ran on centre track to go 2nd at 150m, no match for winner.
Sharp start, camped 1 back on rail, shuffled 2 back 700m, 3rd & shaken up turning in, shifted 1 off & boxed on in even pursuit.
Taken back from widest gate to race at tail on rail, niggled 650m, shifted out & driven 400m, strong closer centre track for minor gains.
Snagged back at start, sat near rear 1 off with cover, driven wide turning in, stayed on centre track for minor headway.
Broke well but driven initially, settled rail midfield, driven into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Snagged at break to rail near rear, shaken up 340m, stayed on for moderate inroads.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 770m & shuffled 1 back 700m, shifted 1 off no cover 520m, driven 400m, found nil & faded out.
Fast break, settled 1 off 1 back, shuffled back 700m, back to 6t h & driven 400m, kept on one pace.
Tardy start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m, driven 400m & shifted wide home turn, struggled in run home.
Moderate start, raced rail behind midfield, driven 350m, found little in tepid run home.
Broke well & prominent 3 wide 1st turn, slotted outside leader 1300m & keen, pushed 3 deep no cover 520m, driven 400m, found nil & faded out.
Settled worse than midfield 6L off, 2 wide with cover. Suited to the fast pace, finished off strongly to score.
Pushed forward to take lead by 1-1/4L. Despite the fast tempo, finished off well, only to be beaten by a nose.
Rolled to obtain box-seat, 2-1/2L behind. Despite the quick tempo, ran on well to the line.
Travelled towards the rear, 7-3/4L off the pace. Suited to the fast pace, progressed steadily from final 200M.
Pressed forward and settled 1-1/4L off the leader, 2 wide without cover. Not suited to the fast tempo, remained one paced to the line.
Settled worse than midfield along the rail, 5-1/4L behind. Made steady headway in the straight, ran home only fairly.
Pushed forward to settle front of midfield 2-3/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Run ended passing final 200M when inconvenienced and headed.
Raced midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L behind. Not suited to the fast tempo, from final 100M weakened.
Travelled 3 wide and without cover throughout, 4-1/4L behind. Never ran on.
Settled midfield 4-1/2L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Failed to respond when asked and was eased down after final 100M.
At rear 9L behind, 2 wide with cover. Did not create any impression.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Began well, ridden to hold rail behind the pace and allowed to settle. Came off fence turning for home, rolled forward to lead 150m, kept on well.
Quickly into stride, racing a half length behind leader to 900m when drew alongside. Pressed ahead top of straight, caught 150m, kept on well.
Jumped well, ridden along to hold position one-off, one-back. Swung wide into straight and battled on gamely.
Jumped with field, not pressured, settling three-back along rails. Improved position turn, switched out in straight, boxed on gamely.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear but wide. Improved position back stretch, shuffled back turn, ran on steadily in straight.
Crowded out soon after start, dropping to last pair along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and ran on fairly in straight.
Began OK, ridden along between horses settling behind midfield in one-off position. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
Urged forward from wide draw, racing three-wide 3L from leader. Improved position around turn but one-paced in straight.
Began well but kept three-wide without cover 2L from leader. Urged forward 1000m but effort short-lived dropping back to 3rd. One-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, then got close to heels, dropping to last in one-off position. Never competitive.
Began best, quickly in front but raced fiercely until 900m when put under pressure. Collared 250m and tired quickly final 150m.
Close up from the start, took over the lead when pace slackened middle stages, kept on determinedly in straight and fended off late challenge of 2nd.
Reserved in midfield along the inside, advanced to 2nd 150M, chased home winner under top weight, just held.
Settled down 5-6Ls behind midfield, kept on moderately over final 300M for 3rd, not reached first two.
Raced in a trailing position just off leader, every chance in straight but not finishing pace of first 2, flattened final 150M.
Barged into a 2-wide spot in midfield passing 1400M, 5Ls to make up on leader 400M, made some progress without threatening.
Rushed to the lead from draw 9, slowed things down from 1100M, relinquished lead nearing 800M, no extra and faded mid-straight.
Never far off in 5th, 3Ls off leader as they settled down, ran on only fairly inside 300M, never a serious threat.
From wide draw, restrained to a rearward spot 8-10Ls off the pace, had plenty to do turning in, stayed on making minor headway.
Taken back on jumping from widest gate, not hurried 10Ls off the pace early and middle stages, driven 450m but found little under pressure however, no threat to leaders.
Restrained to race behind midfield, driven 400M but not making any real progress, never a threat.
Awkwardly away, settled near the rear 8Ls behind leader, similar position turning in, not picked up at any stage, eased 150M.
In touch with leaders, severely checked passing 1200M, proved difficult to settle after, came under pressure 500M, soon gave ground and weakened to last. (Blood in trachea)
