Settled in midfield, fought on dourly in straight to snatch victory just inside the 100 metres.
Jumped moderately, settled in last few, ran on well under pressure in straight, nearest at finish.
Worked his way up steadily to reach 2nd outside leader 1200 metres out, hit the front from the tiring leader 200 metres out but only to be collared close to home.
Jumped fairly but soon settled behind midfield, ran on under pressure in straight without troubling the first trio.
Niggled along from the one draw, settled for 5th on rails just over 2L back, ran home one-paced.
Niggled at early, settled just off the pace on rails, kept on same pace without quickening early in straight, found no extra nearing finish.
Ridden to lead from the middle draw, obtained rails run over 1200 metres out, led the field until faded over 200 metres out.
Settled in last few to straight, improving when baulked twice at 200 and 150 metres out, no further impression.
Never better than midfield, came under strong pressure after straightening, kept on steadily to the line.
Settled just better than midfield, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Broke well from the widest draw, settled just off the pace in 4th, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail in midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Broke well but soon taken well behind, trailed the field into straight, found nothing.
Soon dropped to the tail-end and never seen with a chance.
Took rail and led easily at good pace, drifted away 300M, not fully tested.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, pace good, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Midfield 3 wide, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, lack turn of foot.
At back 3 wide, hampered 700M, pace good, one paced in straight.
Hard ridden forward 2 wide, pace good, emptied 250M.
Behind midfield 3 wide, pace good, no progress.
At back, pace good, never progressed.
At rear, pace good, never improved.
Never better than midfield.
Pressed forward, pace good, dropped off 400M.

Placing: UR
Comment: At the start reared and rider being dislodged.
Eased back from a wide draw, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, improved gradually rounding the Home Bend dashed strongly to score by 1/2L.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, improved gradually rounding the Home Bend, suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, finished off well until final 50M weakened, hung on for 3rd.
Taken back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, closed off nicely for 4th.
Eased to rear from a wide gate, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, couldn't find a day night early straight, made some ground thereafter.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, under pressure rounding the Home Bend, kept on one pace to the line.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast sectionals, kept on nicely until final furlong flattened.
Prominent, however travelled 3 wide without cover from 1200M, one paced until final 300M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast pace, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast tempo, never looked likely.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, checked 300M, never ran on thereafter.
Driven forward to settle 1L behind the leader at fast sectionals, soon flattened after straightening, tailed out.
Sharp break, stalked 1 off with cover fore of midfield, switched wide final turn, shaken up 430m, quickened 350m to 2nd 270m, driven out to lead 170m, in command at wire.
Bustled at break, niggled along 1 off towards rear, shifted wide final turn, switched widest 400m & driven, rattled home centre track to nick 2nd at wire.
Fast start wide, dropped in to sit midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out final turn & driven centre track 430m, not pace of winner but closed off dourly.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 990m & raced very close 2nd, edged lead turning in & driven 430m, kicked 1L clear, all out & headed 170m, tapered to wire.
Smart start, raced 1 back 1 off, shifted out & driven in 3rd 420m, boxed on in pursuit, tapered closing stages.
Broke ok, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched out at 430m & driven, stayed on centre track for minor headway.
Broke well, settled rail fore of midfield, driven into stretch, outpaced & boxed on moderately.
Good break, bustled to lead 990m & sat 1 off, headed turning in, driven 430m, emptied 300m & faded tamely.
Started ok but lacked early toe, raced rail behind midfield, niggled along 750m, switched out & ridden 400m, kept on one pace.
Broke well widest, trapped deep until slotted 3 wide with cover behind midfield at 850m, shifted wider & driven home turn, kept on evenly.
Fast start, taken back to rail midfield, ridden along 500m, plugged on tepidly.
Dropped in from wide gate & raced 2nd last 11L back, ridden 500m, kept on same pace.
Broke with others but soon at tail & niggled 12L off the pace, plugged on past beaten rival.
Fast start, niggled along 1 back on rail, under pump 700m, hard-ridden turning in & found nil, weakened out.
Taken back to last, advanced a spot 800m, string traveller 3 wide with cover on turn, shaken up 500m, motored centre track to edge lead 220m, idled a little in front, in command at wire.
Dropped in from wide gate to race wide with cover near rear, progress on turn, driven 430m & ran on centre track to 2nd at 220m, always held in duel to wire.
Taken back to 2nd last on rail, switched off heels 1100m, to last 700m, 4.5L back when switched wide & driven 430m, strong closer to 3rd late.
Outpaced early & bustled, advanced to midfield 3 wide with cover 800m, niggled 530m, outpaced & driven into stretch, shifted out & stayed on gradually centre track.
Broke ok, ridden forward to 2nd 1 off no cover at 1000m, vied for lead 520m, shaken up to lead 380m, hung in 260m, headed 210m, swamped in run home.
Smart start but unable to slot & raced 4 deep no cover midfield, progress on turn to challenge 430m & shaken up, found little, one-paced.
Sharp start, settled midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 860m, caught on heels into stretch, switched out 300m & driven, kept on same speed.
Outpaced start & bustled initially on rail behind midfield, bumped & hit rail 1100m, over-raced 850m, driven 500m, plugged on evenly.
Fast start widest, led 1150m under hold & soon to rail, pressed for lead 520m, driven under pressure 430m, headed 380m & tapered tamely.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, checked off heels 1100m & bumped rival, over-raced from 850m & shuffled back, driven turning in, struggled in run home.
Smart start & raced fore of midfield 1 off with cover, 1L down & shaken up 400m, one-paced in run, emptied above 200m & faded out.
Broke ok & bustled initially, raced 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, rolled to close 3rd 700m, driven 430m, outpaced & weakened in tame run home.
Early speed & bustled to lead, headed 1150m & sat 1 back on rail, driven 380m & shifted 1 off, found nil & weakened.
Broke well but niggled to settle rail fore of midfield, slid back a spot on turn, driven into stretch, found nil in weakening run.
Raced in restricted room at the start. Traveled in midfield along the rail, 5L off. Harmed by the slow pace, finished off strongly to score.
Settled in front of midfield along the rail, 3L behind the leader. Despite the slow tempo, kept on challenging and finished 2nd.
Traveled in midfield 3-1/2L behind, 2 wide with cover. Not suited to the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
In midfield, 5-1/2L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Ran home gradually in the straight.
Pushed to settle in front along the rail, shared lead at slow sectionals, headed after final 150M.
Settled in worse than midfield along the rail, 6-1/2L behind. Ran home one paced.
Prominent, 1-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Benefited by the slow tempo, ran home one paced until weakened in the final stages.
Raced forward 2 wide without cover, shared lead by a nose. Suited to the slow tempo, weakened after 250M.
Eased from the start to sit worse than midfield 7-1/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Harmed by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Eased back to sit at rear 10-1/2L behind the leader, widest and without cover. Harmed by the slow tempo, only made minor ground down the outside straight.
At rear throughout, 9L behind, 2 wide with cover. Did not create an impression.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Settled front of midfield along the rail, 1-3/4L off the pace, swamped passing 200M.
Eased to settle at rear, 8-3/4L behind, 3 wide and without cover. Weakened soon after straightening.
Pressed forward 3-wide from outside draw before easing off 1150m to find cover 3L from leader. Turned 4-wide, rolled forward to hit front 250m, held off challenges.
No early speed, settling along fence towards rear. Stayed on fence turn, forced to switch out twice in straight to find clear running before finishing strongly final 250m.
Began well, ridden along between horses 4L from leader. Urged ahead turning for home, looked big chance 200m, boxed on gamely.
Began well, ridden along 1L from leader in one-off position. Joint leader on straightening, collared 250m out but kept on well.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold spot one-off, one-back before taken wide without cover 800m. Looked chance 400m but unable to close gap.
Quickly into stride, settling along fence 3-back from leader. Improved position around turn, kept on well to 200m turning one-paced.
Began fairly, restrained and taken to fence at rear. Stayed on fence to straight before switching out and finishing off nicely. Ride queried by stewards.
No early pace, dropping to behind midfield along fence. Improved position around turn, switched out straight to make run but one-paced. Rider dropped whip 400m.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, dropping behind midfield. Got close to heels around turn, taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along early to hold box seat. Lost position turning for home then unbalanced when trying to shift out and bumped. One-paced.
Began OK, restrained, shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Last into straight, switched wide, found nothing.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling but kept wide till 900m when crossed to fence. Joined up front 400m but kept battling to 100m when tired rapidly.
Awkwardly placed soon after start, ridden along three-wide at rear but didn't muster. Raced at rear throughout. Rider suggested horse not suited by firm track.
Began well, racing in midfield but wide. Under pressure turning for home and gave ground steadily in straight.
Chased outside the leader, waited with till 350M, gained the lead mid-straight, continued on willingly under steady hand ride and always had enough to hold off fast fin 2nd.
Settled down 7-8Ls down in 10th, driven at top of straight, rallied under urging and made sound progress over final 250M, nearest finish.
Held up in mid-division, stayed on moderately under top weight, got up for 3rd near line but made no impression on first two.
Set good early pace along the rail, steadied the pace middle stages, fought on briefly when challenged by winner 300M then gave out passing mid-straight, lost 3rd near line.
Jumped well from 14 but soon restrained to the rear, over 7Ls off the pace 400M, brought widest and closed off the race strongly, just missed 3rd in blanket finish.
Not hurried, settled down 8-9Ls near the rear, wide no cover from 1400M, stayed on mildly over final 300M under top weight.
7Ls off the pace behind mid-division, saved ground on the inside, made non-threatening progress up the fence final 400M.
Gained a midfield position along the 2-path, 4-5Ls back at top of straight, kept on one paced, never seriously threatened.
Urged to a gain a forward position just behind leader, lacked the needed kick inside 300M, faded from mid-straight.
4Ls behind leader in 5th as they settled, had every chance turning in, peaked 200M, no extra late stages.
Dropped back after start, over 9Ls off leader in early and middle stages, stayed on only fairly behind horses, never involved.
Towards the rear, waited with till 450M, gave limited response when driven.
Within striking distance in 4th, outpaced passing 350M, had nothing to offer.
Held up in midfield 5Ls off the pace, found disappointingly little in the straight, first to be beaten.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners settling at rear. Last into straight, shifted out 300m when denied run, finished strongly down centre track to win close home.
Lost ground start but picked up quickly to settle four-back into turn. Came off fence entering straight, powered through to lead 150m, run down final strides.
Bumped start but quickly into stride, settling behind leader to turn. Took split top of straight to roll forward, collared shortly afterwards but kept on well to line.
Shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Stayed on rail around turn, took runs between horses in straight before powering home final 150m.
Began well but not pushed settling one-off, three-back. Took closer order turning for home, swung wide, kept on steadily to the line.
Urged forward from an outside draw, racing three-wide without cover 2L from leader. Moved forward 400m to look a chance but one-paced final 100m.
Bumped, stumbled shortly after start, then ridden along 3-wide behind midfield. Made forward move top of straight to get within striking range 200m then one-paced.
No early speed and caught wide without cover toward the rear after jumping from an outside gate. Lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped, then pressed forward in one-off position 3L from leader. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance before flattened final 100m.
No early pace, settling toward rear close to fence. No clear run early in straight, switched out 300m but blocked again 200m when finishing well.
Began OK, not pressured, racing towards rear in one-off position. Switched out wide in straight to make run but found little under pressure.
Began well, ridden to hold rail three-back from leader. Got close to heels top of straight, gave ground steadily from 200m.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead before crossing to fence 800m. Set hot pace to 350m when collared and faded gradually.
Began well, ridden forward, stalking leader to straight. Under pressure from 400m and gave ground rapidly. Found to have irregular heart rhythm and substantial blood in trachea.
Dropped back early from the wide gate and stuck at the rear of the field, 4 wide with cover. Came widest on the turn, and produced a massive effort to run down 2nd in the last 25m.

Began well from the inside draw, and pushed up to be handily placed in 4th, on the rails. Held the rail in the run home, and easily burnt off the majority of the field. Lead until 25m, and only beaten by a huge run.
Only fairly away, but pushed hard early to lead. Ran on solidly in the straight, but well beaten by the first two, and weakening slightly late.
Began well, but elected to sit back early and take a position midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn for a clear run, and finished off well, hotly chasing 3rd late.
Taken back early to sit in his familiar position at the rear of the field, on the fence. Nearly last on the turn, but ran on well late to finish in the first five.
Began well, and pushed forward early to sit just behind the leaders, 2-3 wide, only getting cover at the 900m.Plugged away steadily in the straight.
Pushed hard from the wide draw to eventually share the lead by the 900m. Well positioned on the turn, but was used up early, and only ran to the line fairly.
Began well and taken forward to a handy position, 1 off the fence. Stayed close to the rail in the straight, but only ran on fairly and faded late.
Well away, but only eased forward to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide. Came wider and was handily placed on the turn, but only ran on 1 paced in the straight.
Began OK and took a position just forward of midfield 3-4 wide with no cover. Well positioned on the turn, but had nothing left for the run home and faded out in the straight.
Angled in from the wide draw to be placed midfield, 4-5 wide with limited cover. No luck early in the straight, but didn't run on when clear. Faded and lay out slightly late.
Eased out to find a position midfield, on the rails. Already weakening by the home turn. Failed to respond in the straight and dropped out quickly.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Only plugged away to the line to be beaten 9L in his Hong Kong debut.

Dropped back early and sat at the rear of the field. Over raced through the early/middle stages and came widest on the turn. Had very little left in the tank in the straight, and dropped out to be a well beaten last.

Settled better than midfield in 5th about 3L off the pace, switched out to challenge entering straight hitting the front inside the 200 metres, just held on to the line.
Settled in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, soon came to challenge upon straightening, closed in on leader every stride but the post came to soon.
Settled worse than midfield, came close rounding home bend, ran on steadily in straight, nearest at finish.
Began from a wide draw settling one back in 3rd on rails, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening but failed to quicken.
Slightly slow out settling towards the rear on rails, saved ground turning in, made modest progress without threatening.
Broke well settling in 2L 4th, came to tackle leader entering straight, hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, no extra close to home.
Settled in midfield on rails, remained similar into straight, kept on well.
Began from the widest gate, trailed the field to straight, finished off race well.
Moderate start, soon dropped to the rear, kept on steadily past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Settled in rear of midfield, commenced move and came to challenge when wide into straight, soon yielded ground.
Began from a wide draw, gradually came across to settle just outside the leader, hit the front passing the 500 metres, unable to sustain effort and soon headed after straightening.
Broke well from a low draw, led on rails setting a steady middle sectional, headed passing the 400 metres before dropping away noticeably. (Tactic questioned)
Eased to rear, too rail, favoured by the fast tempo, improved nicely from 400M, finished off strongly to score.
Slow away, pushed to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to hold box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly, just beaten by narrow margin in 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield along the fence, not suited by the fast tempo, made some ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked fast sectionals, ran on well until 150M flattened.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 200M, just held ground.
Behind midfield on the rails, favoured by the fast tempo, however held up in most straight, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 200M, checked 100M.
At rear, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Pushed forward to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow sectionals, dashed strongly to score by a narrow margin when clear 200M.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd, beaten by a nose.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow tempo and couldn't able to find a run latter stages, finished off nicely for 3rd.
Eased back from a wide barrier, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow pace, ran on well when clear 150M.
Driven forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on well until final 150M headed.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, one paced home.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at slow pace, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Eased back to rear from a wide gate, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Prominent, however tapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened 200M.
Always at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Speedy break, slotted rail & settled midfield, rolled forward a spot from 800m, switched 4 deep & driven final turn, quickened smartly to lead 150m, drew clear.
Fastest break, soon headed & raced 4th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide & ridden into stretch, driven to 2nd 100m, no match for winner.
Fast start, led 1140m & worked across to rail 1000m, nudged at 500m, pressed & driven turning in, headed 190m, battled on when beaten.
Tardy start& bustled initially, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 700m, driven turning in, stayed on to just miss frame.
Fast break widest, raced 2nd 1 off no cover, niggled 500m & driven upside leader turning in, edged to narrow lead 190m, headed 150m & emptied out.
Sharp start, soon to rail & sat 1 back, ridden 250m & edged 1 off, kept on one pace.
Taken back at start to last pair on outer, driven forward a spot & snared rail 700m, driven 350m, stayed on without threatening.
Broke well, taken back to rail behind midfield & bustled a touch, ridden 400m, stayed on evenly until checked close home.
Broke ok, outpaced & niggled 1 off near rear, switched 3 deep & ridden 450m, very wide into stretch, kept on moderately.
Broke well, raced midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 750m, bustled 450m, wide on turn & driven into stretch, found nil.
Outpaced at break & rousted on rail, soon at tail, detached & driven 500m, tailed off & eased 200m.
Fast start, sat 1 back on rail until switched 1 off no cover 870m, advanced to 1L 2nd 600m, shaken up 300m & battled to lead 180m, pressed to wire but held on.
Tardy start, camped rail back of midfield, progress on turn & driven into stretch, closed to 2nd at 50m, held in run to wire.
Broke well, sat rail fore of midfield, switched out & niggled 400m, driven 3 deep home turn, closed to within a neck at 200m, held in run & tapered late.
Broke ok, sat rail midfield, over-raced 1080m, switched 1 off in 5th 400m, driven turning in, boxed on evenly.
Sharp break & raced 2nd 1 off no cover, rolled to lead 1000m & to rail 870m, nursed into stretch, rolled off fence & driven 240m, all out & headed 180m & faded.
Restrained start to sit rail near rear, ridden 420m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Speed to lead & bustled to rail 1400m, keen in front, restrained & headed 1000m & sat 1 back, niggled 400m, driven turning in, weakened tamely.
Smart start, bustled initially to race fore of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 650m, driven 500m & lost ground, wide into stretch, plodded home tamely.
Taken back at break to last pair on rail, shifted 1 off & driven 400m, swung out home turn, ran on moderately past beaten rivals.
Slow start & sat 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 1000m, under pump 550m, plodded home weakly.
Slow start, bustled initially, raced midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 520m, checked off heels 380m & wide final turn, struggled in fading stretch run.
Restrained start & raced keenly last pair 1 off, never settled, driven wide into home straight, found nil.
Was bumped at the start before settling in midfield 4-3/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Obtained clear running passing 250M, dashed well to score by 1/2L.
Raced midfield, travelled 3-1/4L off the pace along the rail. Improved gradually in the straight, headed by the eventual winner at 100M, finished off well for 2nd.
Pushed forward to settle in front of midfield from a wide barrier, travelled 2-3/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Raced centre of the straight, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Pushed forward after taken in on jumping to race outside the leader 3/4L off, 2 wide. Maintained forward position in the straight, only headed when weakened passing 100M.
Began awkwardly, eased to sit worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Improved gradually when rounding Home Turn, finished off fairly.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, 1-3/4L behind. Taken to centre of the track after rounding the Home Turn, finished off one paced.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 5-3/4L off the pace. Stayed on the rail after the Home Turn and raced inner track, made ground in the straight.
Bumped at the start, eased to travel at rear 8-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Swung wide after Home Turn, improved marginally, never threatened.
Eased to settle at rear along the rail, 9-1/2L behind. Dashed strongly to the line.
Began awkwardly before settling towards the rear along the rail, 7-1/2L behind. Obtained clear running passing 200M, made minor ground.
Raced forward to take lead along the rail and led by 3/4L. Stayed on rail in the straight, weakened at 200M, and swamped passing 150M.
In midfield, raced wide and without cover for the majority of the race, finished tail out.
Vigorously ridden to go forward settling two-back from leader. Allowed to stride forward from 800m, taking lead 700m and pulling 3L clear. Tiring closing stages but held on.
Began well, ridden to hold rail three-back from leader. Urged forward from 400m, switched out 280m to get run, finished strongly.
Pressed forward, racing wide without cover outside leader to 700m when shuffled back to third. Shaken up top of straight and battled on gamely.
Bumped start, no pace, racing at rear in one-off position. Improved position around turn, ran on steadily straight.
Began awkwardly, then crowded, dropped to behind midfield along rail. Made progress turning for home, switched out straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, rolled forward holding rail 3L from leader. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced.
Began OK, not pushed settling midfield in one-off position. Came off bridle 500m and one-paced when asked for effort in straight.
Pushed forward three-wide to lead on settling before crossing to fence 1350m. Overtaken 700m but kept on gamely till flattened final stages.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last but away from fence. Ran past beaten horses final stages.
Shifted across behind from an outside draw, settling at rear along fence. Never competitive.
Pressed forward outside leader to first turn before dropping to 4th back stretch. Lost position around final turn and plodded in straight.
Shifted across from wide draw but left without cover 1000m to 800m and again from 700m. Rolled forward turn to look a chance before tiring quickly final 200m.
Pushed to obtain a trailing position behind leader, took over command 200M and drew off impressively towards finish.
Quickly into stride and set slow pace upfront under the reins of 10lb claiming rider, not finishing pace of winner 200M but kept on gamely to hold 2nd just.
Tracked the pacesetter from along the inside route, travelled well and loomed boldly at top of straight, shifted in 150M and had to be corrected, ran on again late just missed 2nd.
Held up 5Ls back near rear, closed off final 400M fastest for a never nearer 4th.
Close up in 4th racing along the 2-path, continued on well enough turning in but couldn't match pace with runaway winner, in contention for a minor placing until late stages.
Sat unhurried in midfield, 3-4Ls behind leader throughout, had every chance turning in but couldn't muster the pace to challenge.
Settled down 4Ls back in a rail position behind midfield, switched out 300M, kept on only fairly, not reached leaders.
Restrained after the start, towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, failed to quicken passing 350M, made no impression on debut.
Within 3Ls of leader early and middle stages, kept on same pace turning in, soon out of contention.
Began only fairly from wide barrier, taken back to rear 7Ls off the slow pace, gave limited response when driven 400M, never threatened.
Taken across behind runners to find cover, ended up 7Ls behind leader on settling, wide bid 400M, made no progress.
Eased on jumping and shifted across behind runners, lost cover from 800M, had little left turning home, eased mid-straight.
Steadied soon after start and taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair. Switched wide in straight and powered home to score drawing clear.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, cutting to fence 1400m. Picked up the pace from 500m to set up big lead in straight but cut down final 50m.

Began awkwardly, bumped, shifted across from wide draw and last on settling. Last into straight, rolled forward between horses to get close before rider forced to stop riding final stages when tight for space.
Beaten for speed, dropping to rear along fence. Took inside run in straight to get within striking distance but lay out under pressure final 200m.
Began well, settling in midfield close to fence. Raced tight early in straight but kept on steadily when clear to be nearest at finish.
Began well, racing with leading pack before left without cover when leader crossed over. Found cover going into final turn but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped with field but not pushed, settling three-back from leader. Took closer order turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early to hold box seat behind leader. Looked a chance on straightening but only one-paced and swamped close home.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling behind midfield but wide. Lost position around turn and one-paced in straight.
Aggressively ridden early to hold forward position 3L from leader but raced fiercely from 1100m. Swung wide into straight after which one-paced.
Pressed forward but unable match early leader, settling 3L second in one-off position. Kept on steadily to straight before giving ground steadily.
Hard ridden to stay with pace, racing wide without cover. Stayed within striking distance to straight before fading. Unacceptable performance.
Began well and handily placed behind the early leader, 1 off the fence. Well placed on the turn, and got the nose in front at the 50m. Did just enough to hold off two fast finishing placegetters.

Began only fairly before finding a position forward of midfield, on the rail. Became unsettled and checked off heels 800m. Gave the winner 2L on the turn, but chased hard to go down a diminishing 0.3L at the wire.

Dropped back from the wide barrier to sit last, on the rail with cover. 10L last and left with plenty to do on the turn. Showed a great turn of foot, and finished off strongly, despite being awkwardly placed last 50m.
Pushed out to be the early leader, before eventually being crossed at the 600m. Ran on well in the straight, just fading late and missing a place by the barest of margins.
Began well, but stuck 3 wide forward of midfield before pushing forward to lead at the 800m. Still in control at the 150m, but peaked soon after and swamped late.
Jumped out the best of them before being eased to find cover, midfield 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, and responded well early in the straight, before flattening out late.
OK away and found a position midfield, on the rails. Lay in down the straight, and never fully tested over the last 100m.
Dropped back from the jump to sit just forward of the back markers, on the rail. Plugged away late to be only 2.3L off the winner, but still well beaten.
Began well and handily placed behind the early leader, on the rail. One paced the trip, and easily passed in the straight.

Dropped back early to be near the tail of the field, 1 off the fence. Unsettled early and was forced 4-5 wide at the 800m. Unlucky at the top of the straight, and taken widest. Too much to do late and never in it.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Gave nothing in the straight, and plugged to the line.
Began OK and steadied early to sit near midfield, 1 off the fence. Forced wider to sit 3 wide, no cover from the 800m. Widest on the turn, but never responded to any persuasion and dropped out late.

Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored easily.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced 2 to 3 lengths back in 2nd on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Slowly away, raced 6 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some ground when clear thereafter to get 3rd.
Began well, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in 4th, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 7 lengths or so back behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after turning in and made reasonable progress to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back in 3rd, same position turning, kept on evenly until near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slow to begin, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 10 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, passed some tired rivals in the concluding stages.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced, never a threat.
Moderately away from gate 12, failed to muster early speed, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, still there on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slow away, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at tail, similar position throughout, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover in 5th, still no cover on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide with cover in midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, emptied early in straight, unacceptable performance.
Pushed to occupy box seat, favoured by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, hung out from 600M, just ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain a prominent spot on the fence, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up in midfield 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail behind midfield, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, dashed fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
Hard ridden early, at back along the fence, checked 750M, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 3 wide, no dash.
Pushed to take rail and led by a far margin but at slow sectionals, reduced quickly 350M.
Bumped badly at start, at rear, never a factor.
Never competitive, tailed out.
Driven forward to settle in a prominent position, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on strongly to score by 1L.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on nicely until headed by the winner final 150M.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, kept on one pace to the line without any extra acceleration for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on gradually for 4th.
Raced in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader, trapped wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace to the line.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 – 4 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
At rear, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 3 – 4 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never responded when asked for effort. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, held up rounding the Home Turn, never ran on thereafter.
Hard ridden forward to occupy the box seat, dropped off rounding the Home Turn. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Always at rear, never a factor.
Fast start & disputed lead 1st turn, settled 1 back on fence, shaken up 350m & shifted 1 off, grinding run to lead 110m, edged out & just held on.
Started ok, raced 3 back on rail, shifted out & driven 400m, kept on strongly to press winner late, just failed.
Missed break, recovered to rail back of midfield, driven final turn, quickened to challenge & switched 3deep 200m, closing when squeezed up final strides.
Broke well, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, over-raced 1100m, switched 3 wide no cover 800m, ridden 500m & quickened to press leader 350m, peaked 200m & tapered.
Broke well & rousted 3 wide 1st turn to lead 1350m, impeded rival when shifted in 1300m & snared rail 1250m, 0.5L clear & driven 370m, headed 110m & tapered to wire.
Dropped in from a wide gate, raced 3 deep with cover behind midfield, ridden 500m, stayed on centre track for sound headway.
Started ok, soon bustled to sit back of midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 470m, switched out 350m & driven, ran on for solid gains.
Fast start, dropped back to 3 deep with cover midfield, lost cover 1070m, pushed wider 800m & niggled 600m, driven 500m, fought on evenly until tapered final 200m.
Taken back from widest gate, raced rail near rear, shifted out 550m, crowded 350m, switched wide in stretch & driven 300m, boxed on centre track.
Awkward start & raced 3 wide with cover last pair, ridden 450m & widest into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Broke well & driven to dispute lead 4 deep at 1500m, eased back 1430m, rolled 3 deep to 2nd 1180m & slotted 1 off no cover 1070m, driven 400m, soon emptied & faded.
Good start, taken back & soon niggled at tail, under pump 600m, hard-ridden into stretch, struggled in run home.
Speed to lead, headed 1500m & 2nd 1 off when impeded 1300m, raced 1 back 1 off from 1070m, niggled 700m, outpaced turning in & found nil.
Broke with others, mid rank & niggled early stages, soon settled & travelled, 2L back & driven towards inner 400m, grinding run to lead close home.
Tardy start, tracked vanguard 1 off stand-side fence, ridden 400m & pressed leader on outer 250m, fought on to edge 2nd last stride.
Fast start to lead, kicked on 350m, all out & headed close home, lost 2nd at wire.
Good speed to race prominently centre track, 0.5L down & driven 400m, outpaced closing stages but battled on in defeat.
Speedy break centre track, soon outpaced & niggled midfield, under pump 550m, hard-ridden 350m, stayed on for minor headway.
Bumped start, crowded & checked 960m, raced near rear, trapped on heels 500m, shifted inside 400m & driven centre track, boxed on evenly.
Stumbled start, raced back of midfield, under pump 500m, hard-ridden 250m, kept on evenly.
Broke ok, crowded & bumped 920m & again 800m, raced near rear, checked off heels 600m, 3rd last & driven far-side at 500m, boxed on one pace.
Broke ok, slight bump early, crowded & checked 920m, badly impeded 800m & shuffled to last centre track, under pump 500m, hard-ridden 400m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Broke well, crowded & bumped early, raced mid-rank, checked off heels 550m & lost ground, plugged on tepidly under drive.
Sharp break, bustled close up on rail, ridden 530m, outpaced when slight bump & unbalanced 350m, faded to wire.
Awkward start, bustled to race front rank, under pump in 2nd 550m, outpaced & faded final 300m.
Crowded & bumped early, taken to rail & niggled along last pair, driven 550m, plodded on same speed.
Broke well & raced prominently, under pump & ridden 550m, outpaced & quickly lost ground.
Settled just behind midfield along the rail, 3L off the pace. Suited to the fast tempo, dashed strongly to score by 3/4L.
Rolled forward to take the rail, 3/4L behind the leader. Led once straightened, despite the fast tempo, only headed by the impressive winner at final 50M.
Rolled forward to occupy box-seat, 1-3/4L off the pace. Finished off well for 3rd despite the fast tempo of the race.
Settled worse than midfield 3-3/4L off, 2 wide with cover. Benefited by the fast tempo, closed off well for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 2L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Shifted wide after turn, kept on one paced to the line.
Sat inside the leader 3/4L behind, 2 wide without cover. Harmed by the fast tempo, weakened passing final 250M, one paced thereafter.
Eased back to travel at the rear 5-1/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Despite the fast tempo, only improved marginally, finished off one paced.
Travelled at rear along the rail, 4-1/4L off the pace. Improved gradually when rounding Home Turn, checked and lost its running at 400M, never ran on thereafter.
Rolled forward to take lead by 3/4L at fast sectionals, kept on nicely until final 250M weakened.
Raced in front of midfield from a wide gate, 1L behind wide and without cover. Flattened and swamped once straightened.
Settled in midfield from the widest gate 2-3/4L behind, 3 wide with cover. Despite the fast tempo, never looked likely.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Quickly into stride, racing with leading pack before taking box seat entering turn. Switched out 350m to make run, hit front 200m, held on gamely when challenged.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair in one-off position. Took inside runs in straight, finished strongly to just miss.
Bumped and unbalanced start, urged forward in one-off position 3L from leader. Switched out entering straight and finished strongly.
First out from wide draw and led narrowly before easing off a half length behind leader. Led momentarily on straightening, kept on steadily when passed.
Jumped with field, not pressed, settling three-back 4L from leader. Stayed on rail entering straight and kept on steadily.
Began fairly, racing close to rail behind midfield. Switched out in straight to make run and kept on fairly. Had cuts both hocks.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling along fence towards rear. Stayed on fence on straightening and ran on fairly.
Crowded out and unbalanced start, no speed and held 3-wide at rear. Unbalanced turning for home and one-paced in straight.
Lifted front feet when gates opened and began awkwardly. Pressed forward 3-wide 1L from leader to straight before giving ground gradually.
Began awkwardly, shifted in an bumped. Ridden to make up ground but wide, got within striking distance 200m before tiring. Bled for third time.
Hard ridden early inside leader before taking narrow lead entering straight. Collared passing 300m and faded quickly.
Began well, racing close to pace in one-off position. Raced keenly entering turn and gave ground quickly soon after straightening.
Crowded out start, recovered and pressed forward settling midfield. Lost position turning for home, held for run 300m, faded.
Slow into stride, racing at rear, dropping to last entering turn. Never competitive.
Slotted into a 2-wide position ahead of midfield, advanced to 4th making the turn, quickly asserted inside 300M, was strongly challenged by rivals passing 200M, held on under strong drive.
Never far off 3-4Ls behind leader, tracked the path of eventual winner 400M, strongly challenged passing final 200M, held towards the finish.
Waited with, settled 2-wide at the rear 8Ls off the pace, brought wide 400M and finished off strongly, nearest finish.
Dropped back to rear from wide barrier, ridden patiently 8Ls behind leader, ran on steadily to claim 4th just in time, no threat to first 3.
Reserved behind midfield along the 2-path, 4Ls to make up turning home, found less than expected under maximum pressure inside 300M, unable to reach leaders, lost 4th close home.
Slow to begin but not hurried, settled towards the rear 6Ls back, stayed on mildly, never a threat to leaders.
Forwardly placed, tracked leader one out one back, outsprinted by leaders inside 300M, faded final 100M.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division 4-5Ls off leader, had every chance entering straight and loomed a threat from 300M to 150M, run ended and weakened late stages.
Up with early pace, restrained to sit just off leaders in 3rd from 1200M, not quickened inside 400M, kept on same pace to 150M, eased.
Settled down in midfield 4-5Ls back, had to push along 550M to keep up, didn't find much entering straight, left behind by main rivals 200M. (No Vet findings)
Set steady pace and had uncontested lead throughout, headed near 300M, no extra towards finish and weakened to last 150M.
Began OK, crossed in from wide draw to settle along fence three-back from leader. No run early in straight, shifted out, finished strongly down centre-track.
Began well, ridden along to hold one-back, one-off position to straight. Tightened passing 350m, kept on strongly to line.
Pressed forward 3-wide from outside draw, settling 3-back, one-off. Urged forward top of straight and kept on well to line.
Began well, racing outside leader to and around turn. Led soon after straightening but swamped close to the line.
Pressed forward, racing 3-wide without cover behind leading pair. Tightened soon after straightening and again passing 200m. Boxed on gamely,
No early seed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Steadied shortly after straightening for home, kept on fairly to line.
Began well, ridden along early before settling in box seat around turn. No run early in straight but only one-paced when clear.
Jumped fairly, unable to cross in and kept three-wide behind midfield. Shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Got off OK, no speed, steadied 1100m in one-off position behind midfield. Raced keenly around turn losing position, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, ridden forward in one-off position but still well back entering turn. One-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling then slowed pace. Caught passing 350m and faded steadily.
Began fairly, hard ridden but failed to muster, settling at rear. Dropped to last turning for home. Never competitive.
Slow into stride, settling in last pair along fence. Shaken up top of straight but got close to heels 150m and blocked for run after that.
Ridden along early close to pace but wide before losing position around turn. Kept on fairly early in straight before tiring final 200m.

Began awkwardly, and dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Last on the turn, and ridden for luck along the rail. Travelled well, and had to take a very skinny gap at the 100m. Just got there on the line.
Began OK, and taken forward to sit midfield, on the fence. Held up until the 200m, and ran on strongly from there. Showed good turn off foot from the 100m, and just lost on the line in a head bobber.

OK away and eased forward to be handily place 1.5L behind the leader, on the fence. Came inside heels in the straight to hug the rail. Ran on well, and lead by the 150m, only to be swamped on the line.

Taken forward from the wide barrier to be handily placed, 1 off 1 back. Nicely positioned on the turn, and ran on well to have the nose in front at 150m. Peaked soon after, and swamped late to lose a place in first 3.
Only fair to begin and moved to be place midfield, 1 off the fence. Given a clear run in the straight, and ran on OK. Only hands and heels late.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier, eventually sitting handy, 3 wide with no cover. Well positioned in front on the turn, but only responded fairly when asked the question and plugged to the line.

Dropped back early sitting worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Never settled in the back straight, and checked off heels 1000m. In the last couple rounding the turn. Only plugged on, but passed a few slow ones late.
Taken forward from the inside run to have the sole lead. Held on to the 200m, but ran out of gas and dropped back quickly from there.
Began OK and pushed forward, but struggled to find cover. Eventually settled midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Only travelled to the line 1 paced in the straight.
Only fairly away and then crowded, dropping back to a position worse than midfield, on the rail. Only plugged away to the line, and eased late when well beaten.
Began awkwardly and was very keen early when worse than midfield, 3 wide. Came off heels at the top of the straight, but race was already run, and abled home late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to be a clear last 1.5L behind the 2nd last placed horse. Tried early in the straight, but never ran on and easing up late.
Slightly awkward away but pushed forward to be handily place, 1 off the rail. Jockey reported problem with horses action in the straight, and was eased out late without being tested.

Didn't respond to initial urgings and was stuck 5-6 wide no cover early, before dropping back worse than midfield, 4 wide with no cover. Forced wider at the 400m, but was already a beaten horse, and dropped out quickly.
Began well, raced 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, finished off very well to score easily.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail throughout, 7 lengths or so back on turn, no daylight early in straight, closed off strongly when clear to get 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back behind midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to race in 3rd, but no cover throughout, took the lead early in straight, kept on well until headed final 100M, stayed on for 4th.
Slightly slow out, positioned a length or so back on rail in 4th, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced 5 lengths back at rear, travelled well along the rail on turn, kept inside run in straight and made reasonable progress without threatening the first few.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 5th, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back at rear, similar position on turn, in traffic early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race 6 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover on turn, taken widest in straight and made little progress.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back behind midfield, angled out turning in but made no progress, never competitive.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, easy lead to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after 300M.
Began moderately from a tricky gate, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Slightly slowly away, recovered but unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently in 2nd for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter, finished last.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, found rail on turn and improved, angled out in straight and finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Bounced out well, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear early in straight but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slightly slow out from gate 10, raced 5 to 6 lengths back at tail, still last on turn, made very good progress in straight to get 3rd.
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind the leader in 2nd, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back at rear, slightly improved on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off strongly thereafter, just missed frame.
Bumped start, sent forward to race 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back in 4th, similar position turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced 5 lengths back on rail in 10th, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide with no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, failed to muster speed, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, showed no progress after turning in. (Jockey questioned)
Slightly slow away, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Jumped well from a wide gate, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover for the majority of the race, failed to close off in straight when hard run took effect.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leaders 2 wide, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Pushed forward, took rail, shared lead at good pace, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to secure box seat, pace good, lack room 4-2, closed off well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, shared lead at good pace 2 wide, hampered 200M, flattened afterwards.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
At rear 2-3 wide, checked 900M, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, just held ground in straight.
At rear along the fence, checked 900M, pace good, made good ground 100M.
Eased back, 2 wide, checked 900M, pace good, ran on only fairly.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, clipped heels and blundered badly 900M, no dash in straight.
Trapped wide throughout, never a factor at rear.
Pushed forward to settle in midfield about 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on strongly to take another victory in a row by 1/2L.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, closed off strongly to get 2nd.
Taken back early, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, gradually moved forward 1000M, ran on well for 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
Driven forward to park outside the leader, took the lead 650M, kept on nicely until final 100M headed.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader along the fence, ran on gradually without any threats to the place getters.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Hard ridden forward to settle in midfield without cover, gradually moved forward 1000M, flattened rounding the Home Turn.
Always at rear, never looked a chance.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led, under pressure 650M, dropped off rounding the Home Turn, crowded 350M, never looked likely thereafter.
Sent forward to obtain the box seat from a wide gate, dropped off rounding the Home Turn, severely checked 350M, eased down thereafter.
Broke well & bustled wide 1st turn, crossed to rail & led 1250m, nudged along 500m, driven 1L clear 400m, kicked 3L ahead in stretch, emptied closing stages, just held on.
Broke ok, bustled initially to sit rail fore of midfield, switched 1 off 400m, shaken up 3 deep 300m, ran on strongly, just failed.
Good break, sat 1 back 1 off, niggled 650m, switched 3 wide no cover 500m, shifted wide into stretch & driven, stayed on dourly for 3rd.
Smart start, raced 1 back on rail, under pump 450m, shifted out entering stretch & ran home evenly.
Moderate start widest & bustled along, lacked toe & sat behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 750m, driven 500m & outpaced, stayed on in stretch for minor inroads.
Taken back from wide gate, raced rail behind midfield, shaken up turning in, ran on one pace.
Tardy start, raced 2nd last & niggled on & off, driven 400m, boxed on for minor headway.
Slow break, bustled at tail, driven home turn, stayed on past beaten rivals.
Smart break & bustled forward to lead 5 deep at 1480m, headed 1250m & sat 2nd outside leader, niggled 500m, driven 400m, emptied 150m & faded out.
Tardy start, bustled to settle midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m & driven 500m, plodded on tepidly.
Fast start, soon outpaced & rousted, settled midfield 3 wide with cover, niggled 600m & soon under pump backpedalling, struggled in weakening run to wire.
Sharp start to dispute early lead, sat handy but trapped 3 wide no cover, bustled 600m, driven widest into stretch, found nil & faded out.
Snagged back at start to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, swung widest home turn, rattled centre track to lead inside final 100m.
Snagged back at break to sit midfield 1 off with cover, shifted wide & driven final turn, quickened to lead 130m, immediately pressed & headed close home.
Broke ok, & raced midfield, bustled & outpaced a touch 880m, shifted out & driven into stretch, closed off soundly to 3rd.
Smart start widest but taken back to 1 off near rear, driven wide turning in, closed off for sound gains.
Outpaced & rousted early, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 450m, fanned out & driven final turn, kept on for minor headway.
Sharp start, bustled up to vie for lead from 900m, rolled to lead 400m, shaken up entering stretch, all out & headed 140m, tapered closing stages.
Fast start wide, raced wide no cover in 3rd until slotted 1 back 780m, wide final turn, driven to edge lead 140m, immediately swamped & faded.
Slow break, raced rail near rear, driven wide home turn, edged back inside 200m, running on when not clear ground & checked 80m, kept on last strides.
Rousted start to race handy 5th 1 off with cover, edged wide home turn & driven, one-paced in run home.
Fast start & raced handy 1 off with cover, to rail 800m, under pump 700m & hard-driven into stretch, found nil & eased.
Sluggish start & raced detached at tail, 6L adrift & under drive 700m, closed on pack final turn & hard-driven, checked off heels 200m, no extra & eased.
Speed to lead on rail, pressed from 700m, driven & headed 400m, emptied 300m, faded & eased when beaten.
Settled in front of midfield 4L behind 2 wide with cover. Dashed strongly from 200M, headed 2nd place-getter just before the line to win.
Prominent, 2-3/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Maintained forward position down the centre of the straight, ran home steadily for 2nd.
Remained at the rear along the rail 8L behind the leader, finished off strongly for 3rd.
Settled in midfield 5-3/4L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Switched wide upon straightening, improved gradually for 4th.
Raced in midfield along the rail, 4-1/2L behind. Kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward to sit 1-3/4L behind and outside the leader. Led briefly after 250M, headed passing 200M, ran home one paced.
Eased back from a wide barrier, travelled at rear 10L behind 2 wide with cover. Switched widest once straightened, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1-3/4L. Weakened and headed passing 250M.
Initially at the rear, niggled briefly at 650M to be closer in midfield, did not create an impression in the straight.
Towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, remained one paced to the line.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat 3L behind. Stayed on the rail after turn and raced inner track, weakened after 200M.
Raced in midfield along the rail, 6-1/2L behind the leader, never looked likely.
Jumped OK, not pressed, crossing in to one-off position 3-back from leader. Swung wide into straight and powered home strongly to win close to line.
Vigorously ridden to lead on settling, crossing to fence 600m. Kicked clear entering straight but run down final 50m.
Ridden along early while seeking cover, settling one-off but 4-back from leader. Swung very wide into straight but kept on strongly while hanging in.
Began only fairly, then ridden to hold fence just behind midfield. Switched out in straight and finished off nicely final 200m.
Ridden along early to hold forward position before settling 3-back along fence. Unbalanced 400m but stayed on fence and kept on gamely to line.
Ridden along early to obtain forward position, travelled strongly around turn, looked chance on straightening but found little final 200m.
Bumped soon after start, ridden to hold fence behind leader to straight, then one-paced.
Pressed forward 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Rolled forward entering straight, shifted in150m forcing jockey to stop riding momentarily.
Beaten for early speed, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Under pressure turn but found little, one-paced.
Shifted out and bumped shortly after start, pushed forward between horses settling two-back, one-off. Keep on fairly in straight before tiring final 200m.
Began fairly then crowded out, dropping to rear along fence. Lost ground 600m when shifted out, found nothing in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter.
Dropped back to near the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, picked up momentum 400M, made rapid headway and led near 100M, swiftly shook clear under hands and heels riding, won with plenty in hand.

Caught wide early from 12 before slotting into a 2-wide position behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace 400M, responded when put to task, couldn't match winner's finishing kick but stayed on well for clear 2nd.
Settled down in mid-division 4Ls back, ran on steadily for non-threatening 3rd.
Pressed the pace on the outside, stayed on well in straight, headed 100M, weakened towards finish.
Caught 3-wide no cover throughout from draw 8, crept closer to leaders nearing home turn, kept on fairly in straight and not bridging the gap on leaders.
Restrained after the start and travelled near the rear 6Ls behind leader, made limited progress passing 300M, never threatened.
Broke a step slow, dropped well off the early pace, 8Ls to make up 400M, gave limited response, not reached contention.
Chased leaders, held every chance turning in, stayed on to final 200M and wilted. (No Vet findings)
Sent forward vying for lead, offered a mild bid early straight, headed near 200M, no extra late (No Vet findings)
Tracked leaders, rallied early straight but failed to make headway, eased late. (Blood in trachea)
Bustled along early but lacked pace, soon fell back to the rear 8Ls behind, faded away passing 400M, never involved.
Raced in midfield, niggled along middle stages to maintain position, dropped out from 300M, eased.
Began well, slotting in behind leading trio passing 1450m. Turned 3-wide into straight, pressed forward to lead 200m, kept on well.
Pressed forward from outside draw, crossing in to one-off position 3-back from leader. Wide entering straight and finished off strongly.
Steadied soon after start then shifted across behind runners to rail. Lost position back stretch, stayed on rail in straight and finished strongly.
Steadied and shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight but finished off strongly down centre track.
Shifted across behind runners, settling four-back along rail. Switched out in straight and ran home steadily to be closest at finish.
Ridden along but unable go early speed and trapped 3-wide behind midfield. Taken very wide in straight and boxed on fairly.
Ridden along early to stay with leaders before easing back to 3rd, 2L from leading pair at first turn. Urged forward top of straight to look chance 200m before flattened.
Lifted front legs at start and slow into stride but made up ground quickly crossing to fence in box seat. Looked chance early straight before checked off heels 250m, faded.
Slow into stride, dropping to last but away from fence. Trailed field to straight and ran past tired horses final 200m.
Began well, tightened passing 1400m, settling three-back along fence. Under pressure from 350m but found little.
Vigorously ridden early in search of lead but held out by inside horse. Stayed outside leader to straight before tiring badly final 200m. Unacceptable performance.
Used early to hold fence and prevent outside horse from crossing, setting two fast quarters before slowing pace. Caught 200m out and faded quickly.
