Broke well, settled off the pace near midfield on rails, renewed effort turning for home, ran on to hit the front passing the 200 metres, won readily.
Settled in last few on rails, baulked or a run from approaching home turn to about 350 metres out, finished off race nicely.
Prominent briefly, gradually drifting backward in midfield when hampered and lost further ground 1000 metres out, wide towards the rear when straightening, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide in midfield from a wide gate, took slightly closer order coming out of back straight, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Slightly slow out, remained well behind to straight, made steady headway down the centre of the track.
Well there, plugged on under pressure early in straight, but could find no extra inside final 200 metres.
Ridden prominently settling in close-up 3rd on rails, tightened for a run about 300 metres out, kept on steadily to finish.
Ridden in midfield, took closer order 3-wide rounding home bend, amongst leaders early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Never better than midfield when travelling wide, found nothing in straight.
Ridden along in rear of midfield on rails, similar turning for home, made modest progress in straight, baulked close to home.

Vied for lead from a wide gate, soon obtained rails run in the front after first 200 metres, changed legs a couple of times when jockey asked to steady pace coming out of back straight, soon weakened after straightening.
Always well behind after beginning from the widest gate, no response in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led casually at slow sectionals, drifted away 300M and scored.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M flattened.
Very slow away, towards rear, unleashed strong finishing efforts despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well despite negative racing situations.
Eased to rear, trapped 3 wide, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in front of midfield on the rails, lack room 400M, no turn of foot when clear.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, emptied 250M.
Pushed forward, checked severely 850M, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Very slow away, at back, along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, held up whole straight, not tested.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, ran on ok.
Eased back 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 300M, no dash.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no progressed.
Eased back, never competitive.
Settled in front of midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, favored by the fast tempo, dashed well to score comfortably by 2Ls.
Taken back, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, finished off strongly for 2nd.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at fast sectionals, steadied the pace after 1100M, kept on well until headed by the winner 200M. (Questioned rider for running)
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the fast tempo, one paced home for 4th without threatening.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, made minor ground in straight.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite favored by the fast tempo, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the fast pace, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.
At rear, travelled 12Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, made minor ground in straight.
Taken back as usual, travelled 10Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the fast tempo, never ran on. (Questioned rider fort disappointing performance)
Hard ridden to settle in front of midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.
Always at rear, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the fast pace, weakened rounding the Home Turn, tailed out. (Questioned rider for disappointing performance)
Ridden forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader without cover, harmed by the fast pace, flattened badly rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Disputed early lead wide, settled 2nd outside leader from 950m, shaken up 500m, driven to lead 280m, extended clear & coasted final strides.
Outpaced at break & bustled to sit midfield on rail, ridden 500m, switched out on turn, crowded 300m, quickened up & closed to 2nd late.
Speed to dispute lead, to rail 1050m & clear leader 950m, 1L up & driven into stretch, all out & headed 280m, boxed on but lost 2nd close home.
Taken back from wide to 3 deep with cover near rear, a touch keen, driven wide into stretch, stayed on centre track for sound gains.
Sharp start, settled 1 back on rail, ridden 500m, boxed on in 3rd down stretch & shifted out, lost 3rd 170m & tapered closing stages.
Good break, sat midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out on turn, driven 400m, plugged on one pace.
Taken back from widest gate, raced at tail, switched wide 600m, driven into stretch, kept on one pace.
Dropped back from wide gate, raced rail near tail, checked off heels 570m, driven into stretch, bumped rival 350m, plugged on one pace.
Rousted start & trapped 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, rolled forward from 800m to vie for 3rd final turn, driven into stretch, outpaced & emptied out 200m.
Broke well to park rail fore of midfield, shifted out & driven 430m, struggled in run home.
Sharp start, snagged back to eventually slot 1 off with cover behind midfield, hard-ridden 480m, plodded on weakly.
Fast break & prominent until snagged 1200m to 1 off 1 back, niggled 600m, hard-ridden into stretch, found little & weakened.
Lacked early pace & niggled to race 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 700m, under pump turning in, bumped rival 350m, struggled in run home.
Missed break, recovered to race rail back of midfield, niggled 700m, under pump 500m, found nil & weakened.
Broke ok, rolled to dispute lead 1200m, settled 1 back on fence, shifted 1 off & full of running 430m, not clear run between horses, switched to rail & driven 300m, battled to lead last strides.
Outpaced widest & rousted, progress to 2nd 900m & sat 1 off, niggled 500m & driven into stretch, led 250m, all out & headed close home.
Smart start & disputed early lead, settled 1 back 1 off, close up and driven into stretch, battled to wire but always held.
Taken back at start, raced near rear 3 wide with cover, driven 550m, outpaced in rear & hard-ridden 350m, responded & stayed on for strong late headway.
Snagged back from wide, sat tail 1 off, over-raced, 3 deep 600m, widest & driven home turn, stayed on for solid late inroads.
Moderate start, raced 3 deep with cover behind midfield, wide & under pump home turn, stayed on dourly for minor headway.
Fast start & disputed lead, snagged back 1200m to midfield 1 off, travelling but not clear run into stretch, off heels 350m, shaken up 300m & kept on evenly.
Rousted at start, settled midfield on rail, niggled 550m, driven 400m, plugged on tepidly.
Taken back from wide gate, raced rail near tail, driven 300m, kept on moderately.
Smart break but rousted & slid back to 1 off near rear, under pump 500m, one-paced in run home.
Broke ok, lacked toe & drifted back to behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled a touch 550m, found little in tame run home.
Smart break, over-raced 3 wide no cover midfield, driven 430m, weakened tamely.
Disputed early lead, pushed wide to lead 1050m, to rail 850m, driven turning in, headed 250m & faded quickly.
Slow start, recovered to race rail behind midfield, ridden turning in, found nil & weakened tamely.
Eased back from a wide barrier, settled towards the rear, 8L off 2 wide with cover. Improved gradually around turn, led passing 200M, finished off strongly to score.
Rolled forward to settle in midfield along the rail 5-1/4L behind. Taken away from the rail before straightening, shifted out further at 250M, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield along the rail 3-1/2L behind the leader. Raced inner track in the straight, finished off nicely when run opened up on the inside from 250M.
Eased back to travel towards the rear 9-1/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Taken widest and improved around turn, shared lead once straightened, closed off nicely until 250M headed.
Settled in midfield along the rail 6-1/2L behind the leader. Once straightened finished off evenly without threatening.
Was slow to begin, travelled at the rear along the rail 10L behind the leader. Inconvenienced at 300M after shifted wide to race on the outside of the straight, ran on fairly.
Ridden forward and led by 2L, 2 wide without cover. Was up with the pace until headed by the eventual winner at 200M.
Pushed forward to take the rail and sat inside the leader 2L off the pace. Maintained forward position and along the rail in the straight, kept on nicely until headed at 200M.
Rolled forward to sit behind the leader, 3-1/4L off 2 wide with cover. Remained close in the earlier part of the straight, weakened just before 200M.
Settled in midfield 6-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover. Lost position when others improved in the Home Turn, and was not competitive in the straight.
Eased back from a wide gate and settled at the rear 10-3/4L behind. Improved slightly when taken wide in the Home Turn, made no impression in the straight.

Slow to begin, settled at the rear 10-1/2L behind, 2 wide with cover. Shifted wide and improved gradually when rounding the home turn. Became unbalanced when checked at 400M. Did not run on thereafter.
In worse than midfield along the rail, 8-1/4L behind. Did not make an impression throughout.
Settled in front of midfield 5L off the pace, 2 wide with cover. Lost ground when rounding home turn, was not competitive in the straight.
Began well, racing down centre track before edging closer to outer fence 850m. Shaken up passing 400m, hit front 200m, held off late challenge.
Jumped with field, not pushed, sliding back towards rear between horses. Shown whip passing 350m and finished off strongly.
Began well, not pressed, settling 2L behind leader. Urged forward 400m, joint leader 200m, kept on gamely when passed.
Quickly into stride, racing one-away from outside fence 1L from leader. Urged forward from 600m, hit front 500m, collared 200m, kept on gamely.
Jumped well, ridden to hold outer rail 1L from leader. Urged forward to get within range 400m before turning one-paced.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to hold outer rail 4L from leader. Kept on steadily in straight without closing gap.
Crowded out start, got close to heels shortly after, then pressed forward between horses to get within 3L of leader at 400m. One paced thereafter.
Inconvenienced start, shifted across behind horses to outer fence, checked 500m when making ground, shifted in 200m to get run, one paced.
Bumped start, outpaced while gradually moving closer to outer rail. Shifted in 400m to get run but one-paced.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to last while moving closer to outer fence. Shaken up 500m and ran past tired horses.
Blundered start, then travelled keenly before tightened 900m and taken to outer fence. Made ground to 400m before turning one-paced.
Began awkwardly, recovered then steadied 800m dropping to rear. Never competitive.
Jumped with field, settling 3L behind leader away from outer rail. Put under pressure from 500m but found little and faded.
Began well, quickly in front setting decent pace to 500m when passed and weakened quickly. Had small cut left hind leg.
Overcame wide barrier to lead without making too much early use, travelled smoothly to straight, kept finding final 200M and held on safely.
Raced In mid-division early, took closer order through home turn and loomed behind leaders 400M, shifted out for racing room 300M, ran on well late but was readily held.
Patiently ridden behind midfield, fanned wide into straight, finished strong to go 3rd near line.
Bustled along early to go forward, crossed to race one out one back just before the turn, kept on evenly in the home run but was no match for the winner, faltered late and weakened to 4th.
Settled 3-wide near the rear, pushed wider mid-way through home turn, wheeled out widest in straight, finished well.
3Ls off leader in a 2-wide spot ahead of mid-division, switched out 3-wide 800M, fought on to 200M, flattened out late stages.
Reserved towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, offered a mild bid turning home, failed to seriously threaten.
Held up 4Ls back in midfield, saved ground on inside, was given a vigorous ride in straight but unable to improve position.
Taken back on jumping from 12, settled down 7Ls back in the rear, stayed on passing beaten horses only, not reached contention.
Unable to slot in and raced without cover in the 3-path throughout, moved closer to pace past 800M, kept on same pace in straight, out of contention 200M.
Dropped back from wide barrier, held up in the rear 7Ls off the pace, kept to inside throughout but failed to pick up inside 400M.
Slowly away, dropped back to near the tail of the field, held up behind horses from 300M, not tested.
Restrained in midfield early, no closer than 3-wide throughout, made early move from halfway to join leaders, run ended inside 300M, weakened.
Broke well, sat just behind leaders early stages, shuffled back a bit over home turn, gave limited response top to straight, eased when no chance 150M.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Shaken up passing 600m, wide into straight and finished strongly to win close home.
Began OK, hugging rail 4-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn, took inside runs in straight and finished strongly final 200m.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead, crossing to fence 900m and steadying pace. Joined by another 750m, kicked clear 400m, looked winner before run down final 100m.
Tightened shortly after start, then proved hard to settle to turn. Shifted out 400m to get run but had to switch in 200m, ran on well.
Hampered start, recovered and pressed forward to settle one-back, one-off. Rolled forward top of straight but unable to sustain effort. One-paced.
Began well, pressed forward to hold box seat, stalking leader to straight. Looked chance 250m but no extra close home.
Shifted across behind horses to fence from outside draw and last on settling. Trailed field to 600m when shifted out, widest in straight, ran on steadily.
Ridden forward to hold rail, three-back from leader. Switched out in straight to challenge, making ground to 200m before turning one-paced.
Hard ridden from wide draw, racing wide, to sit outside leader around turn. Kept battling in straight to 150m before flattened.
Began OK, ridden along behind midfield before checked 700m and didn't settle for some distance. One-paced in straight.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to last pair. Never competitive though did run past tired horses in straight.
Began well, bumped 1000m then taken 3-wide without cover from 700m, 3L behind leader. Kept tabs till 200m before tiring quickly.
Began fairly, no early speed but improved position around turn, making ground to 200m before running out of steam.
Jumped OK, outpaced and soon at rear along rail. Shifted out around turn but made little headway, dropping back to last entering straight. Never competitive.
Eased forward from an inside gate to sit midfield, 3 wide with cover. Given a run at the top of the straight, and pushed from the 200m. Slowing slightly late, but still easily in.
Dropped back from the jump to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Last on the turn, and ran home very strongly with the fastest last 400m, but had to share 2nd place.
Bounded out and began awkwardly before pushing up to sit midfield, on the rail. Held onto the rail in the straight, and kept grinding away late, just held on to share 2nd.
Eased back early to sit at the rear of the field, 3 wide. Came widest on the turn, and ran on OK to the line, but couldn't stay on with the first 3.
Dropped back from the kick to sit at the rear of the field, on the rail. Stayed close to the rail, and checked off heels at 300m. Plugged away OK late, without threatening to place.
Eased back early to be midfield, 4-5 wide with no cover. Moved back to sit further back, but still unable to find cover at 1200m. Led at the 200m, but peaked soon after, and dropped back late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last, one off the fence. Ran on solidly under hands and heels in the straight, without ever threatening.
Eased out to sit just forward of midfield, on the rail. Came wider on the turn, but only ran to the line fairly.
Pushed forward at all costs early to sit just behind the leader, on the rail. Held up early in the straight, but never ran on when clear, and only battled to the line.
Taken forward from the wide draw to shadow the leader, 1 off the fence. Not vigorously ridden to the line, and went in 1 paced.
Began well and taken forward early to sit in a handy position, 1 off the fence. Well positioned to strike on the turn, but didn't respond and finished off disappointingly.
Began well, and was pushing forward to a handy position before being checked out of a run 1300m, and settled midfield 1 off the fence. Didn't give a lot in the straight, but did beat a couple home.

Unbalanced on jumping found a position worse than midfield, 3 wide. Never fully settled early, before running onto heels 900m. Came wide on the turn, but already fading when losing a run 300m. Eased late.

Began well and taken forward early to lead. Tried to stoke up on the turn, but no response and dropped out quickly, becoming a speed bump for those behind. Eased for the majority of the straight, beaten 10.8L.

Jumped well amongst leaders, gradually shifted back to settle just better than midfield, quickened well to take charge over 200 metres out, held on well.
Began well from the widest gate, taken back before first bend to settle wide behind midfield, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Sluggish at start, settled wide in midfield far side, fought on steadily without threatening.
Shared pace on rails early, ceded lead to settle just off the lead in back straight, similar turning in, failed to quicken to threaten.
Settled mainly in midfield, did not find much room after straightening, kept on without quickening inside final 300 metres.
Failed to muster early, settled behind midfield, remained similar turning for home, ran past a few beaten horses inside final 200 metres.

Tightened at start, soon recovered to reach midfield briefly when baulked turning into back straight, remained in similar position in last few before sneaking up on rails turning for home, one-paced under pressure.
Raced keenly in midfield, kept on without quickening in the run home.

Began well from a poor draw, travelled 3-wide in better than midfield in 5th down far side, commenced move to gain narrow advantage 2-wide rounding home bend, but unable to sustain effort and swamped over 250 metres out.
Soon dropped to rear, ran home one-paced.
Began well, shared the pace 3-wide around first bend, taken back to race outside the leader far side, weakened under pressure in home straight.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, travelled very wide in midfield down far side, slightly closer up around the bend, soon weakened under pressure.
Missed the break badly, reached the back-markers briefly far side, weakened out of contention from approaching home turn.
Midfield early, took off entering back straight to soon take up running, joined around home bend, dropped out under pressure in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M for 3rd.
Slow away, but soon gained by the lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start, at rear 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 150M.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on ok.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, made some ground 200M.
Very slow away, behind midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, never progressed.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, soon reduced 250M.
Slow away, trapped 4 wide throughout, never better than midfield.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 4 wide with cover, dashed well to score by 1/2L.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on strongly for 2nd.
Driven forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L, kept on strongly until final 100M weakened, hung on for 3rd.
Taken back, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader along the fence, dashed strongly to the line despite couldn't find a day light most of the straight.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, stayed on one pace to the line without any extra acceleration.
Camped midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made some steady ground in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Pushed to park outside the leader, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
At rear, niggled along throughout, never a factor.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Pushed to settle midfield, however trapped very wide without cover throughout, dropped off soon after straightening. (Lame left fore next day)
Quickly into stride, not pushed, easing three-back along rail. Switched out 500m to make run, picked up momentum from 300m, finished strongly.
Pressed forward, racing inside early leader before settling one-off, one-back first turn. Shaken up 400m, challenged strongly but unable overhaul winner.
No early speed, racing at rear but wide. Switched to centre track on straightening and finished strongly.
Pressed forward 3-wide to lead before crossing to fence 1400m. Dropped to 2nd first turn, then 3rd along rails back stretch. Shaken up 300m and kept on well to line.
Ridden forward but held wide into first turn before striding ahead to lead passing 1280m. Set hot pace to straight, still well clear 200m, swamped final 120m.
Began OK, unable go early speed, settling midfield 6L from leader. Well back entering straight but kept on fairly to line.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear before making ground back stretch. One-paced in straight. Rider dropped rein after 200m.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, checked passing 1450m, settling at rear. Kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Outpaced early, racing in one-off position at rear. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced.
Unable handle early pace and held at rear but wide. Taken wider entering straight but only plodded to line.
Pressed forward from wide draw but unable to handle pace, settling 5L from leader in one-off position. Wide into straight, bumped 200m, faded.
Jumped OK but awkwardly placed first turn close to rail. Kept on fairly in straight, forced to shift in 250m then bumped 200m. One-paced.
Hard ridden from start but unable to muster, settling in one-off position 4L from leader. Kept tabs to straight before fading. Lame right front leg.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter and never competitive.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, taking over lead passing 1050m. Kicked clear entering straight and kept on strongly to line.
Bumped from behind at start, pressed forward to sit one-off, one-back, steadied entering turn, three-wide into straight, finished strongly.
Jumped with field but took time to find feet, improving along rail to sit at midfield entering turn. Had restricted room early in straight before finishing strongly final 100m.
Began fairly, ridden but failed to make ground, settling three-wide at rear. Put under pressure from turn, very wide in straight, kept on steadily.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped, dropping to behind midfield. Tightened around turn, sifted out in straight and kept on fairly.
First into stride before handing over lead passing 1050m and taking box seat. Took inside run entering straight, looking chance 200m, no extra close home.
Tightened start, pressed forward but wide to sit outside leader before turn. Put under pressure entering straight but only one-paced.
Began OK, ridden along midfield between horses before easing into one-off position 5L from leader around turn. One-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Stayed on rail around turn and kept on fairly in straight.
Ridden along to hold forward position, 3-wide about 3L from leader to straight. Found little when asked for effort and faded.
Tightened at start, then got close to heels 1000m, dropping to last around turn. Never competitive.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 4-1/4L behind. Improved slightly when rounding the home turn, ran on with ease to score.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover. Ran home steadily, only beaten by an impressive winner.
Rolled forward to take the rail and raced behind the lead, 2-1/4L off. Took lead for 100M after passing 300M, ran home ok for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover. Kept pushing to the line, missed out on 3rd place by 1/4L only.
Eased back to settle towards the rear 5-3/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Unbalanced after being bumped at 700M, finished off steadily thereafter.
Raced forward to take the rail from an inner gate and led by a nose. Kept on well until headed by the third place-getter at 300M.
Settled in worse than midfield, 5L behind and widest without cover. Responded well when asked from 550M, ran on one paced in the straight.
Hard ridden forward to sit outside the leader, a nose behind. Weakened and dropped off after 350M.
Settled towards the rear along the rail, 6L behind the leader. Checked at 700M after getting its head on the side, never looked likely in the straight.
Raced towards the rear, 5-1/4L behind and 2 wide with cover. Did not look likely.
Raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind and 3 wide with cover. Took the rail when rounding the home turn after shifted in, weakened passing 250M.
Prominent, 2L off the pace, 3 wide and without cover. Weakened and dropped off when rounding the home turn.
At the rear initially, but improved to midfield in the 2nd section. Travelled wide and without cover mostly, did not look likely.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Inconvenienced start, pressed forward to lead passing 1050m. Joined up front 700m, kicked clear top of straight, kept finding when challenged.
Inconvenienced start, recovered, pressed forward wide to sit outside leader entering turn. Challenged strongly in straight but unable to overhaul winner.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw then travelled keenly when checked 800m. Very wide into straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, ridden along, settling one-off, one-back. Shaken up top of straight and kept on steadily to line without looking dangerous.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last of main bunch on settling. Shifted out in straight and ran in fairly.
First out but raced keenly, handing over lead 1050m, then dropping to third in box seat from 700m. Switch out in straight to make run but kept on only fairly.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling midfield in one-off position. Urged forward entering straight but only one-paced.
Began OK, the vigorously ridden to go forward but held three-wide without cover 2L from leader. Lost position around turn and gave ground quickly in straight.
Fractious in gate and lost considerable ground start, trailed field to straight before running past tired horses.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail position three-back from leader. Kept on fairly to 200m when shortened stride noticeably.
Pressed forward but held wide without cover in midfield. Covered extra ground turn and gave ground quickly in straight.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Stood flat-footed at start and refused to leave gate.
Settled down behind midfield, in 8th place 6Ls off the pace middle stages, picked up well when clear 300M, dueled with 2nd mid-straight and responded determinedly through final stages to prevail.
Held up midfield in 6th place, loomed behind leaders 250M, dueled inside the winner final 150M, battled on strongly, just denied. (Lost left front plate early stages)

Began well from inside draw, tracked leaders along the fence and had the run of the race, squeezed through to challenge on inside passing 300M, briefly led 200M but not matched finishing pace of first 2 late stages.
Switched off to last, over 10Ls off the pace at one stage, patiently handled, closed off well when driven 350M, got up for 4th near line.
With leaders early, sat 2-wide in the group chasing the pace, moved up to challenge 400M, led briefly 250M but couldn't sustain run, flattened final 150M.
Lacked early pace, settled near last 8Ls behind leader, kept to inside throughout, closed off evenly from 350M, difficult obtained run near 100M but never looked like getting to leaders.
Unable to cross from draw 13, eased back to a 3-wide spot near the rear, brought wide 400M, stayed on moderately.
Eased back, settled at the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, urged along 600M but made limited progress in the straight only, not reached leaders.
Niggled along early to hold his spot in midfield, 5Ls off the pace turning home, didn't pick up sufficiently in straight, never a serious threat.
Caught wide first 600M from draw 14, tracked leader form 1000M, outpaced from 250M, faded out of contention.
Not far off from pace early stages, dropped back to mid-pack 4Ls off down back straight, pushed along 500M, failed to rally and gave ground 200M.
Guided to a 2-wide position in midfield, wide bid 500M, vigorously driven but failed to improve position from 300M, weakened towards the line. (No Vet findings)
Not hurried, settled down 6Ls behind midfield, wide no cover after 900M, lacked a closing response and left behind by rivals mid-straight.
Sent forward but could only cross to the fence passing 1000M, set good pace to straight, run ended 250M and swamped by rivals.

Well there from the widest gate obtaining rails run just off the pace coming out of back straight, baulked after straightening and had a tight run until 150 metres out, just got up.
Jumped moderately, travelled wide behind midfield, ran on steadily to just fail to get up on line. (Jockey questioned)
Settled in midfield, soon came to challenge upon straightening, ran on steadily to hit the front over 150 metres only to be collared close to home.
In last few to straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Bumped start, recovered to race 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 5th, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Jumped fairly, race wide in midfield before improving to 2nd onto home bend, hit the front briefly over 200 meters but soon swamped.
Began well, settled in midfield on rails, did not find much room after straightening, kept on steadily to finish.
Settled just worse than midfield, tightened passing the 400 metres, kept on steadily without quickening.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on rails, shuffled further back in 6th coming out of far side, baulked after straightening to the 200 metres, kept on. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Ridden to lead on rails from a wide draw, made the running to 350 metres, faded.
Always well behind, produced modest impression late.
Taken back from a wide draw, became last passing the 900 metres, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Began moderately, soon recovered to forward of midfield, took closer order 3-wide around the bend, weakened under pressure in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Never seen with a chance.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, lack room 400M, slightly hampered 100M, made ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made ground 300M.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, pace good, flattened 200M and hung in.
Eased to rear, took rail, pace good, lack room 4-2, made good ground when clear.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at good pace, soon emptied 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, interfered 1100M, pace good, ran on ok in final stages.
Eased back, checked badly 1100M, raced 2-4 wide, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight, checked 100M.
Hard ridden early, at back along the fence, hampered 1100M, pace good, never improved
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, no turn of foot.
Very slow away, at rear, raced 3-4 wide, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly to take the victory by a neck.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, closed to the line strongly for 2nd, missed by a neck.
Eased back to settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning home, dashed well for 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily along the inside for 4th.
Driven forward to settle outside the leader, kept on steadily to the line.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Ridden forward from a wide gate, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on steadily until final stages weakened.
Travelled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite hampered early straight, ran on nicely thereafter.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, Kept on steadily to the line without any acceleration.
Jumped slowly, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until 250M weakened.
Showed no early pace despite niggled along throughout, never looked competitive.
Taken back, trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Quickly in front, racing wide before crossing to fence 1400m. Steadied pace then kicked clear 300m, won easily though tiring last few strides.
Began well, racing inside leader to 1400m before settling 1L behind in one-off position. Chased leader throughout but unable to close gap.
Ridden to hold rail position, settling 3-back from leader. Came off fence passing 600m but caught in traffic until 300m before finishing strongly.
Pressed forward from an outside draw and held 3-deep without cover 2.5L from leader. Swung wide into straight and kept chasing without looking dangerous.
Jumped with field, not pressed, settling along rail 4-back from leader. Improved position turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, no speed, settling at rear in one-off position. Taken very wide in straight and boxed on fairly.
Began awkwardly, then raced keenly 3-wide with cover behind midfield. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Bumped start, outpaced, settling towards rear away from fence. Switched out in straight to make run but found nothing.
Began well, racing with leading pack before settling in box seat passing 1400m. Boxed on gamely in straight before tiring final 200m.
Began OK but hard to settle then got close to heels 1400m. Rolled forward between horses settling 2.5L behind leader to straight before tiring.
A little slow into stride, dropping to last on settling. Trailed field thereafter. Never competitive.
First out, racing very wide before cutting in 1300m to trail leader. Kicked 3L clear soon after straightening and went to the post with something in hand.
Ridden to maintain forward position, travelled strongly to 800m when got close to heels. Swung very wide into straight and finished off strongly.
Began well, eased and taken back, settling at rear in one-off position. Had to switch in and out early in straight before getting run 200m, finished strongly.
Bumped start, ridden vigorously but failed to muster, racing 3-wide behind midfield to straight. Kept on well under hard riding.
No early speed and held three-wide at rear along back stretch. Urged forward around turn, wide in straight, kept on well to line.
Jumped well but slow to muster, dropping to rear before picking up speed wide without cover from 1400m. Wide into straight, boxed on gamely.
Bumped start, then steadied shortly after when crowded, dropping behind midfield between horses. Kept on steadily in straight without making ground.
Ridden to hold rail, unbalanced 1600m before settling 3-back from leader. Switched out turning for home, kept on well to 200m before tiring and dropping back.
Beaten for early speed and last on settling. Still last passing 400m before making ground between horses final stages.
Ridden along from inside draw but unable hold off pacemakers, dropping 4-back from leader. Improved around turn but held up early in straight. Found little when clear.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear along fence. Made some progress around turn but one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward but wide before eased 1500m, settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward to challenge 400m but ran out of stamina and faded quickly from 200m.
Began well, settling in box seat. Switched out top of straight to make run but found nothing and faded quickly. Substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to lead on settling, then tried to slow pace approaching turn. Collared soon after straightening and faded. Bled from both nostrils.
Raced midfield along the rail, 3L behind the leader, dashed strongly from 300M to score by a head.
Settled in front of midfield 2-1/4L behind, 2 wide with cover. Led briefly in the Straight before headed by the eventual winner at 100M, kept on strongly for 2nd.
Eased back from the widest barrier, travelled 5-3/4L behind the leader along the rail, finished off well for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, finished off steadily without threatening.
Settled in worse than midfield along the rail, 4-1/2L behind the leader, finished off well despite being held up until 300M.
Travelled at the rear along the rail, 6L behind, one paced in the Straight and eased down inside 200M.
Started slowly, and then was hard ridden forward to lead by 3/4L along the rail. Headed passing 300M, did not run on thereafter.
Prominent, raced along the rail 1-1/4L behind the leader, reduced near 250M.
Sat outside the leader, 3/4L behind, weakened at 300M.
Began well before settling in slipstream behind leader. Came off fence entering straight, rolled forward to lead 300m, kept on strongly to line.
Jumped with field, pressed forward settling 2.5L from leader in one-off position. Urged forward to challenge entering straight but unable to close gap.
A little slow to move, then taken to fence 6L from leader. Held up in traffic entering straight, shifted in to get clear running, finished strongly.
Got off OK, not pushed, settling 5L from leader in one-off position. Switched out top of straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Ridden along to hold one-off position 4L from leader before taking closer order turning for home. Looked chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Began only fairly, restrained and taken to fence in last place. Widest into straight and ran on fairly closing stages.
Began well but no pace, settling at rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight but made little headway under hard riding.
Quickly into stride, holding rail position 3-back from leader. Brushed rail and unbalanced 900m, kept on fairly to 300m before tiring.
Quickly in front but wide, crossing to fence 1400m and setting hot pace. Collared passing 300m and faded.
Began awkwardly, soon recovered to race in midfield 3Ls off the good pace, kicked on well 300M and drove past leader 150M, well on top final stages.
Quickly across to the lead from 11 under positive riding, set a strong gallop throughout, responded well to pressure on straightening, headed 150M, rallied to hold 2nd.
Chased the pace along in the 2-path, loomed a threat 350M, ran on steadily final 200M but didn't have enough late and was readily held in 3rd.
Dropped back to last 7Ls behind leader in a strongly run race, peeled out 500M, finished final 400M fastest, just missed out on a placing.
Unable to slot in, caught wide no cover near the tail of the field past 800M, ran on well from off the pace.
Unhurried at the back, 6Ls off the pace making home turn, held up early straight, shifted out wide passing 300M and closed off the race well.
Guided to a 2-wide position behind midfield, in 7th place 5Ls off the pace, ran on mildly passing 400M, awkwardly placed final 150M and unable to ride out under full pressure towards the line.
From inside draw driven to a trailing position just behind leaders, had every chance in straight but unable to find extra, flattened out 150M.
Restrained to race towards the rear, saved ground along the fence, checked 200M when starting his run, made mild gain final 100M but was too late. (Blood in trachea)
Bustled along to go forward, caught 3-wide outside leader until 700M, contested the pace until weakened 300M, eased final stages.
Close up behind leaders early stages, 3Ls back in 5th turning in but lacked a finishing response, faded to last 150M. (Bled)
Jumped with field, racing with leading pack before settling 3-back along rail. Came off fence 600m, caught behind runners before switching out 350m, finished strongly.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out 500m, caught in traffic to 300m, awkwardly placed 200m before rattling home strongly.
Hard ridden to lead passing 1200m before allowing another to go ahead while holding rail. Retook lead and kicked clear 300m, run down final stages.
Pressed forward early before easing one-off, one back on settling. Rolled forward on straightening to look chance at 200m. Swamped final stages.
Urged forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide 3L from leader. Pressed ahead on straightening to look good chance 200m before flattened final strides.
Began well, quickly settling behind leader to turn. Disappointed for run passing 400m, rolled forward to within striking distance 200m, then one-paced.
Pressed ahead from outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 1L behind leader. Battled on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Jumped with field but not much speed, settling behind midfield 4-back from leader. Took closer order around turn but one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride, settling last along fence. Trailed field to straight when urged forward, shifted out passing 100m when close to heels.
Bumped start, urged forward but wide to midfield. Lost some ground turning for home, eased off heels passing 350m, one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing outside early leader before forging ahead passing 1000m. Caught soon after straightening and faded.
Began fairly, racing at rear in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Jumped OK but failed to settle, racing 3-wide behind midfield. Kept wide throughout and never likely.
Began OK but outpaced and dropped to last pair in one-off position. Clear last around turn and never competitive.
Pushed forward from the 1000m to be handily placed, 1 off the fence. Ran on from the turn, and didn't need a lot of persuading before pulling away from the 200m, and winning easily.
Pushed forward early to be handily place, 2L behind the lead pair. Tried to hold the rail, but had to come off to progress 200m. Ran on well, but weakening late. Held 2nd late.
Dropped back from the start to be worse than midfield, 3-4 wide early. Came wide on the turn and was impressive, running on strongly in the straight, gaining on 2nd late.
Steadied on jumping and dropped back to be last up the back straight. Checked at the 900m. Came widest on the turn, and ran on well late, without threatening the first 3.
Jumped OK and found a position just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Looked to run on from the turn, but wanted to lay in and needed be straightened. Never fully tested to the line.
Began well, settling just forward of midfield, on the fence. Well placed on the turn, but only 1 paced to the wire.
Only fairly away, eventually setting behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Responded early to pressure, but only plugged on fairly from the 300m.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to lead, on the rail. Looked to go at the top of the straight, but only ran on 1 paced and faded late.
Began well, but not used up early to sit midfield, on the fence. Didn't respond from the turn, and faded out from the 400m. Easing up late.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier to share the early lead. Gave nothing in the straight and faded from the 300m, easing late.
Drifted back from the jump to sit at the rear, on the rail. Hampered at the 900m. Never improve his position, and quietly ridden to the line in the straight.
Began OK, but was stuck midfield, 3 wide no cover after settling. Faded from the 350m, and never ran on in the straight.

Bumped and unbalanced early. Pushed to just behind midfield, before racing keenly onto heels at 900m, and checked back to the rear of the field. Was a beaten horse by the turn, and drifted out to a long last.

Placing: UR
Comment: Bucked out of the gate, and left the rider behind.

Jumped well, gradually settled in better than midfield on rails, quickened well under pressure to assert authority 100 metres out.
Vied for early lead from a poor draw, settled outside the leader most of way down far side and around the bend, fought on under pressure after straightening but outsprinted close to home.
Moderate start, settled 8th in midfield on rails, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening in straight.
Poor start from a poor draw, soon ridden positively circling the field to take up running on rails 900 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed over 100 metres out.
Ridden early before settling just off the pace on rails, found nothing in straight.
Jumped fairly from a poor gate, gradually settled 2L back in 4th 3-wide, gained closer order rounding home bend, but unable to sustain progress inside final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in last few near the rails, kept on steadily in the run home.
Jumped moderately, remained well behind to straight, ran on well down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Taken well back from the widest gate, remained similar turning in, ran on between runners, never nearer.
Travelled just better than midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, made no impression in straight.
Never better than midfield, found nothing in straight. (Tactic questioned)
Eased at start, took rail at back, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, closed off strongly 200M for 2nd.
Occupied a prominent spot, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made some ground 250M.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, soon under pressure 300M, hung in whilst weakening.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, made ground 300M, checked 200M, just ran on afterwards.
Pushed early, took rail at back, pace good, ran on ok in final stages.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, no turn of foot.
Failed to muster, checked 1100M, at rear, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, reduced 300M, checked 200M.
Pushed forward to settle in a prominent position, 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off strongly to score by 1/2L.
Settled midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly until final 50M headed, hung on for 3rd.
Eased back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran home strongly for 4th.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, kept on steadily to the line.
Driven forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on gamely until final 100M weakened.
Taken back from a wide draw, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well despite lack of room over the latter stages.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on fairly.
Pushed along to settle midfield, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened over the last furlong.
Failed to muster despite ridden along throughout, never looked likely. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Hard ridden along throughout, never responded, finished last. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped with field, ridden to find cover, settling three-back along rail. Took inside run entering straight, slightly unbalanced passing 100m, finished strongly
Pressed forward, holding one-off position two-back from leader. Urged forward on entering straight and finished off strongly to just fail.
Ridden to hold forward position before settling in box seat around first turn. Came off fence 500m, urged forward on straightening, kept on well to line.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw and last on settling. Improved position back stretch, very wide in straight, finished off strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear along fence. Well back entering straight, got close to heels before finishing off strongly final 200m.
Quickly into stride, led to first turn before easing off and following new leader. Shaken up 400m, hit front 300m, kept on well till swamped final stages.
Began well, racing outside leader to turn before dropping one-back, one-off. Kept on well early in straight before flattened 100m out.
Began fairly, then steadied when crowded, dropping to behind midfield in one-off position. Put under pressure 400m out and boxed on fairly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, dropping to last at first turn. Still well back entering straight but finished off nicely final 200m.
Began fairly, crowded and lost ground dropping four-back along rail. Under pressure from 500m but only one-paced. Unacceptable performance.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing outside leader before taking over passing 1400m. Kept steady pace to straight before tiring.
Began awkwardly, then stumbled. Ridden but didn't muster and held wide without cover in midfield. Tired quickly in straight. Slight wounds to right front foot heel. Unacceptable performance.
Began well, urged forward, settling in slipstream of leader. Had clear rails run entering straight, hit front 200m, kept on strongly.
Pressed forward from good draw to settle one-back, one-off back stretch. Shaken up passing 400m, looked chance 200m, kept on well to line.
First into stride and soon clear leader setting steady sections to straight. Caught passing 200m but kept on well to hold on for minor placing.
Shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Trailed field to straight, took inside run, hampered passing 300m, finished strongly.
Began well, moving to fence three-back from leader. Travelled comfortably to straight but only one paced when asked for an effort.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped. Shifted out and made heavy contact with another passing 600m. Switched out in straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward, settling in 2nd, 2L behind leader to straight. Kept battling to 200m before giving ground.
Fractious in gate and slow into stride, then shifted in from wide draw, settling towards rear along fence. Crowded and lost ground turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, pushed forward to midfield, then bumped and unbalanced again 600m. Found little in straight.
No early speed and held three-wide with cover towards rear. Taken very wide entering straight but no response when urged.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after start, settling in last pair away from fence. Never competitive.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing three-wide without cover 3L from leader. Swung wide into straight and faded quickly final 200m.
Eased back, 8-1/4L behind the leader, despite the slow tempo, unleashed strongly to score.
Sat behind midfield along the rail, 4-3/4L off, not suited to the slow tempo, dashed well for 2nd.
Eased back, travelled towards the rear along the rail, 6-1/2L behind, not suited to the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on steadily.
Hard ridden forward, sat 3/4L off 2 wide with cover, was finishing off strongly until hampered at 150M.
Settled midfield, 4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, finished off one paced.
Urged forward to take the rail and led, suited to the slow tempo, ran on ok until flattened and headed at 200M.
Raced in front of midfield along the rail, 1-3/4L behind, kept pushing until weakened at 100M.
Settled towards the rear, 7L behind 2 wide without cover, despite not suited to the slow tempo, improved marginally in the straight.
Initially at the rear, niggled forward in the 2nd section to sit outside the leader, checked at 150M, did not run on thereafter.
Sat in front of midfield, 2-1/2L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran home one paced.
Raced in midfield along the rail, 3-1/4L off, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash in the straight.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, setting good pace. Headed around turn but retook lead on straightening, kicked clear 200m, held off late challenge.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Last into straight, taken to centre track and finished strongly.
Bumped start, ridden forward, settling behind leader. Took rails run in straight and boxed on gamely though unable to close gap.
Urged forward between horses to grab one-off, one-back position to straight. Shaken up passing 400m and boxed on gamely.
Ridden along to obtain forward position, settling three-back, one-off. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced.
No early pace, then taken to rail four-back from leader. Stayed on rail entering straight and ran on fairly to be closest at finish.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear but away from fence. Put under pressure turning for home and ran on fairly.
Bumped start, recovered and taken to fence three-back from leader. Held position around turn but found little in straight.
Began fairly, ridden forward but wide, then steadied 1000m. Improved position around turn, wide in straight, gave ground final stages.
Quickly into stride, ridden to hold position outside leader before edging ahead around turn. Headed 400m but kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Jumped OK but not pushed, racing behind midfield but wide. Taken even wider in straight but found little though hampered 200m.
Began well, then pressed forward but held 3-wide without cover 1L behind leading pair. Still wide in straight before fading final 200m.
From wide draw quickly crossed to take up a one out one back position, had a good trip under the slow fractions, sprinted to the lead 300M, kicked nicely clear of the pursuers, well in control fin
Never far off 2-3Ls off leader in a slowly run race, lacked finishing pace of winner final 300M but stayed on steadily to go 2nd 50M.
In close pursuit of leaders but caught 3-wide no cover throughout, outsprinted by winner passing 300M, kept on evenly to hold 3rd.
Tracked leaders along the fence in a slowly run race, kept to inside turning home, fought on at the same speed final 200M.
Soon led from inside draw, set very slow pace upfront and had uncontested lead to straight, headed by winner 300M out, ran on same pace to 100M, faded late.
Held up midfield along the fence, 4Ls off the pace in a slowly run race, starting to pick up when no clear run final 200M, not tested.
Eased on jumping from 12, settled near the rear, 5Ls off leader at 400M, closed off soundly but left with too much to do in a slowly run race.
Held up towards the rear 6Ls back, not helped by the slow pace, no clear run early straight, ran on well final 200M.
Reserved near the rear, 3-wide with cover, stayed on only fairly passing 350M, not reached leaders.
In last place for most of the trip, 6Ls behind leader making the turn for home, ran on final 350M but had too much to make up in a slowly run race.
Failed to muster speed, caught 3-wide in midfield, lacked the needed response 350M, faded away 100M.
In 8th place, settled behind midfield 4Ls off the slow pace, not picked up when put under pressure 400M, faded mid-straight.

Settled in midfield, commenced move approaching home turn, ran on nicely to hit the front 200 metres out, won readily.
Jumped fairly, niggled along in midfield early stages, moved closer rounding home bend, improving when hampered 200 metres out, soon renewed effort to claim 2nd near the line.
Broke well from the wide draw, soon led and gradually came across for rails run 1200 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed inside the 200 metres.
Settled well behind from a wide draw, baulked until the 300 metres, ran on under pressure to reach 4th close home.
Moderate start, settled not far off in 5th, reached 3rd briefly after straightening, found nothing under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield or just behind, given reminders rounding home bend, made steady headway under pressure in straight.
Slightly slow out, settled towards the rear on rails, moved slightly closer approaching home bend, had a tight run on rails after straightening and baulked throughout closing stages.
Sluggish start, raced keenly behind midfield throughout far side, 3-wide around home bend, nothing to give in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Wide in last few, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Began from the widest draw, given reminders to keep up with the pace before settling just outside the lead, faded out of contention inside the 300 metres.
Slow to begin, soon recovered to prominent position just off the pace in 3rd on rails, weakened inside final 300 metres.
Always well behind, never seen with a chance.
Hard ridden to keep up with first few early, travelled off the rails without cover in 4th far side, dropped out after straightening.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Towards the rear, dropped out home bend.
Pushed forward, shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well to win.
Behind midfield, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Pushed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to share the lead at slow sectionals, soon flattened 200M.
Slow away, at back, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, hampered 150M.
Good gate speed but eased back for cover, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok.
In front of midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
At back, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, ran on fairly.
Very slow away, at back, harmed by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot.
Eased to sit behind midfield, not suited by the slow pace, no dash, checked 150M.
Prominent early, soon emptied 300M.
Never a factor, dropped off 300M.
Pushed along to settle in front of midfield, suited by the slow sectionals, dashed well to score comfortably by 1/2L.
Sent forward to take the fence and led at slow tempo, kept on gamely until headed by the winner final 30M.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace without extra acceleration to get 3rd.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, enjoyed the slow pace, kept on steadily for 4th.
Taken back from a wide draw, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the slow tempo, finished off well.
Eased to worse than midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, one paced home.
Taken back to rear, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow pace, kept on steadily to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace until weakened final 150M.
Prominent, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 – 4 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, soon flattened after straightening.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Hard ridden to lead from a wide draw, crossing to fence 1000m. Set good pace to straight, kicked clear entering straight, won with something in hand.
Bumped start, pressed forward inside leader before settling in box seat. Kept on well in straight but no match for winner.
Began OK, not pushed, settling in one-off position behind midfield. Steadied soon after entering straight, took inside run and kept on gamely.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling 1.5L behind leader before turn. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced.
Jumped with field but slow to muster, dropping towards rear away from fence. Taken very wide in straight and kept on steadily.
Ridden vigorously from wide draw but failed to muster and trapped wide at rear. Steadied 900m to find cover, swung wide into straight, one-paced.
Hampered start, ridden vigorously but failed to muster and last on settling. Last into straight before running past beaten horses.
Began OK, racing wide but fiercely passing 1000m. Improved position around turn, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Hampered start, pressed forward but held wide without cover. Urged forward around field turning for home, kept on to 200m before fading.
Bumped and unbalanced start, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out entering straight but found little under hard riding.
Bumped start, pressed forward to sit 3-back from leader before turn. Gave ground gradually soon after straightening.
Pressed forward, settling one-off, two-back to turn. Put under pressure from 500m but found nothing. Faded.
Began well, racing in one-off position behind leader before checked and moving to fence 1100m. Urged forward entering straight and overhauled leader close to line.
Hard ridden to lead on settling before crossing to fence 1300m and slowing pace. Kicked ahead entering straight but run down final stages.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling three-back along fence. Lost position around turn, stayed on fence in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, urged forward to settle one-back, one-off. Held for run early in straight, switched out 300m, kept on one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide before settling 1L behind leader before turn. Looked chance entering straight but one-paced final 200m.
Slow into stride, bumped and unbalanced 900m, then caught wide without cover towards rear. Very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Began fairly, not suited by space, over-raced and bumped another several times. Checked entering turn, one-paced straight. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began OK, not suited by tempo and bumped several times with another to 1300m. Crowded and unbalanced 1100m. One-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, over-raced and checked passing 1200m. Crowded for room entering turn, one-paced in straight.
Ridden early settling in one-off position three-back from leader. Lost position around turn, gave ground gradually in straight.
Began fairly, taken to rail and pressed forward four-back from leader. Checked and shifted out 1100m losing ground, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to last pair along rail. Hampered passing 900m and found nothing when put under pressure in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw and last on settling. Never competitive.
Began OK, ridden but checked 1100m. Rolled forward to sit 3-wide behind leader450m but dropped out quickly in straight. Suffered from irregular heart rhythm.
Settled in midfield, 3-1/4L behind, 2 wide with cover, responded well when asked at 300M, dashed well to score.
Eased back and travelled at rear along the rail 6-3/4L off, shifted wide in the Straight, ran on strongly for 2nd.
In midfield, 3-1/2L behind the leader, 3 wide without cover, closed off well to the line.
Sat towards the rear, 6-1/2L off, 2 wide with cover, ran on nicely for 4th.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind the leader, 3 wide with cover, improved slightly in the straight, just held on for 5th.
Settled in worse than midfield, 5L behind 2 wide with cover, finished off ok, just missed out on 5th.
Urged forward and shared lead in a 2 wide position, no dash and headed passing final 250M.
Eased back, at rear 8L behind the leader, 2 wide with cover, made ground steadily in the straight.
Sat just in front of midfield along the rail, 3L off the pace, checked at 200M, ran home one paced.
Pushed forward, held one-off and one-back position, prominent for the majority of the straight, weakened inside 100M.
Pushed forward to take the rail and shared lead, remained competitive until final 200M weakened.
Sat behind the lead along the rail, 1-3/4L behind, however had no clear running in the straight, not properly tested.
In midfield along the rail, 4-1/4L behind the leader, never looked likely in the straight.
At rear, raced wide and without cover rounding turn, never a factor.
Began well, ridden forward but wide, three-back from leader. Improved position turn, wide into straight, hit front 350m, pulled clear.
Fractious and bumped inside gate at start, steadied, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out turning for home, held for run early in straight, finished strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear away from fence. Bumped and unbalanced 350m, taken to centre track, finished strongly.
Quickly into stride, sliding into slipstream of leader but over-racing. Settled better around turn, took inside run in straight, kept on well.
Hard ridden from an outside draw, racing wide behind leading pack before moving up to sit outside leader. Looked chance 400m but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw settling at rear in one-off position. Well back entering straight but finished off nicely before getting close to heels final stages.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling behind midfield away from fence. Awkwardly placed early in straight, tightened 350m, ran on fairly when clear.
Pressed forward, settling 3L from leader but 3-wide without cover from 900m. Rolled forward entering straight, one-paced final 200m.
No early pace, settling along fence towards rear. Stayed on fence around turn and kept on fairly in straight though awkwardly placed 150m.
Urged forward to hold position rail, three-back from leader. Switched out 450m, kept on steadily before checked and blocked for run 50m.
Began well, pressed forward inside leading pack, taking over lead passing 1180m. Set good pace to 350m when caught, kept on till flattened 100m.
Quickly into stride, leading field to 1200m before taken wide by inside runner, dropping one-back, one-off. Travelled well to 500m when put under pressure and faded gradually.
Ridden to hold forward position but wide, 3L from leader. Under pressure from 500m, lay out 350m, checked 250m, faded. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Reared and lost ground start and trailed field throughout. Never competitive.
Sent forward to sit prominently behind leader early, moved up to press the pace home turn, took over 350M, continued on determinedly to line and fought off challenges from both sides late stages.
Close up in 4th, well placed to strike turning in, chased winner from 350M, put in late surge and finished nearest at the line.
Crossed to the rail 1300M, settled 3rd in touch, had difficulty obtaining clear run early straight, chased winner from 300M, held by the battling winner.
Held up behind midfield 5Ls off the pace and was given a rails run, took time to muster on straightening, got going 200M, went 4th 50M but not reached leaders.
Towards the rear, proved difficult to settle, waited briefly early straight, responded well when asked but shifted out abruptly under whip 200M and had to be corrected, could have been closer.
Reserved near the rear 6Ls behind leader, saved ground on the rails, closed off final 400M fastest but never threatened leaders.
Guided to the fence 3-4Ls back in midfield, shaken up 450M, kept on steadily in the run to the line, lacked extra final 200M.
Taken back from wide barrier, held up 3-wide near the rear early but moved closer home turn, made some progress early straight but unable to sustain run passing 150M.
Settled down 3-wide in midfield 4Ls off the pace, responded mildly inside 350M, hampered near 150M, one paced towards the finish.
In midfield along the 2-path, not far off about 3Ls back turning in, not quickened under pressure and outpaced by leaders passing 200M.
Soon took up running, set good pace first half while not under any pressure from rivals, lost lead 350M, no extra 200M and weakened.
Not hurried, raced in 2nd last for much of the way, swung widest 450M, lay in and proved difficult to ride in straight, never picked up the pace to challenge. (No Vet findings)
From wide barrier shifted across behind runners, raced as the backmarker 7-8Ls off leader, brought across to challenge down outside passing 400M but failed to menace.
Positioned 3-wide in the group chasing the pace, lost cover from 1200M, dropped away 300M, eased when no chance.
Vigorously ridden to lead, crossing to fence then set steady pace. Kicked 3L clear soon after straightening and never challenged.
Began fairly, made up ground along rail to sit 3-back before turn. Not much room top of straight but motored home nicely when clear final 300m.
Pressed forward, racing wide to 1200m before rolling forward to sit 1L behind leader. Caught flat-footed 450m when leader kicked but boxed on gamely.
Hard ridden early to sit outside leader before easing one-back, one-off before turn. Looked a chance when loomed entering straight but then only one-paced.
Bumped start, not pushed, settling along rail 4-back from leader. Improved position around turn, took inside run in straight, kept on fairly.
Jumped with field but over-raced back stretch between horses. Held up for run early in straight, steadied 200m, one-paced.
Began well, tightened and unbalanced 1300m dropping to midfield but wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, ridden but slow to muster, then checked 1400m, dropping towards rear but 3-wide. Taken wider in straight but found little under hard riding.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and in last pair on settling. Clear last entering straight, ran past beaten horses final stages.
Began well, pressed forward, taking box seat to turn. Got split top of straight but shifted out 200m and bumped, before fading final 100m.
Ridden to hold forward position but caught 3-wide without cover 4L from leader passing 1000m. Gave ground steadily in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw and last on rail on settling. Never likely.
Bumped start, slow to muster, then checked 900m, dropping behind midfield. Gave ground around turn and tired quickly in straight.
Not pushed early and sat forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Had clear running from the top of the straight. Took on leader at 150m, and had enough in the tank to hold out a fast finishing 2nd.

Cruised forward from the wide draw to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, and ran on solidly. Kicked late and was closing the margin on the winner, with the fastest final sectional.
Pushed forward early to sit just behind the early leader, 1 off the fence. Lead at the 400m, but challenged at 150m and lost his position in the first 2 late.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 5th. Over raced onto heels at 700m. Got a clear run from 400m, and ran on well from there. Unable to kick with first 3 late.
Began well, but not used up early, sitting midfield on the fence. Had to go searching for a run at the top of the straight. Ran on OK, and kicked well over the last 100m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last, 11L off the leader. Pushed forward from the 600m. Produced a big run in the straight, and finished off well.
Slow away and dropped back to sit at the rear of the field, on the fence. Pushed on OK from the top of the straight, and lost some momentum when steadied off heels 200m. Ran on OK late.
Drifted in from the outside draw to eventually sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Came wide on the turn, and plugged on OK in the latter stages.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to be the early leader. Held on until the 300m, before peaking on his run and dropping out quickly from the 250m.
Began well from the inside draw and taken forward to be well placed just behind the leader, on the fence. Held up briefly at the top of the straight, but never ran on and dropped back from the 200m.
Began OK, dropping back early to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Only plugged on in the straight, fading out late.
Slowly away, and only eased forward to be just worse than midfield, on the rail. Asked to go on the turn, but didn't respond and went to the line flat.

Taken forward from a wide draw to a handy position 1.5L off the leader, but 3 wide no cover. Bumped and unbalanced at 700m. Never responded to pressure from the top of the straight, and dropped out conspicuously.
Well place early, forward of midfield on the fence. Dropped out badly in the straight, and subsequently found to have blood in the trachea and cardiac arrhythmia.
