Ridden to the front for rails run before ceding advantage to hold one back position at the Rock, renewed effort to lead inside the 300 metres and soon drew clear.
Broke well settling just better than midfield in 3L 5th, fought on steadily from a similar position into straight to reach 2nd late.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled about 3L off the pace mainly in 4th, soon came to challenge upon straightening but could find nothing under pressure.
Worked from a wide draw, eventually crossing to lead for rails run at the Rock, led the field into straight but soon passed by the winner 300 metres out.
Quickly recovered from a moderate start to gain 3rd spot some 2L back and one off the rails, held similar into straight but soon faded.
Taken back for rails run, making headway towards midfield when checked 600 metres out, saved ground on inside turning for home, one-paced.
Niggled along before settling in midfield, similar but wider entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Towards the rear, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, came under pressure upon straightening, produced modest impression in straight running past beaten horses.
Raced wide and mainly just worse than midfield, remained wide into straight, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on rails, dropped out tamely in straight.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, never a danger.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed early but failed to cross in front, settled in midfield 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M for 2nd.
Failed to muster, midfield along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 200M for 3rd.
Pushed to hold the rail in the lead, pace good, ran on well until 100M flattened.
Pushed to occupy box seat, pace good, lack room 4-2, just held ground.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, flattened 200M.
Eased back, pace good, made some ground 100M.
Eased to rear, took rail, pace good, made minor ground 100M.
At back, 2-3 wide, pace good, lack turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, emptied 200M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, pace good, reduced quickly 300M.
Missed start badly, never a factor at rear.
Eased to take the fence from a wide draw, 3Ls behind the leader, finished off strongly along the inside to score by a nose.
Hard ridden forward to take the lead along the fence, fought on strongly to get 2nd, just beaten by a nose.
Bumped start, then pushed forward to occupy the box seat, kept on gamely to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on steadily to the line without extra acceleration.
Pushed forward to settle in midfield from a wide gate, 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on nicely.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, stayed on one pace until weakened 150M.
Pushed to settle in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Settled midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Taken back from a wide draw, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
Niggled along throughout, never a factor.
At rear throughout, never looked competitive, tailed out.
Began well, not pushed, dropping toward rear but away from fence. Ridden forward from 1050m, circling field to join leader 900m. Inched ahead 500m, battled strongly, pulling clear final 100m.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling three back in one-off position. Urged forward from 600m, three-wide into straight, ran on strongly final 200m.
Hard ridden to lead from outside draw, racing wide before crossing to fence 1300m. Speeded up when pressured 900m, headed 500m but battled strongly till flattened 50m.
A little slow to move, settling at rear. Improved around turn, took runs between horses in straight and finished strongly.
Away nicely, crowded 1700m but ridden to hold one-off position 3L from leader. Lost position 900m, rolled forward again to look chance, boxed on.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Urged forward around turn, hampered 500m, kept on fairly in straight.
Not much speed but able to hold rail 3-back from leader. Checked off heels around turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Bumped start, ridden to stay with pace, settling midfield but wide. One-paced in straight.
No early speed, settling at rear but away from fence. Hampered around turn, one-paced in straight.
Ridden to stay with pace but held wide without cover 5L from leader. Held position to straight before tiring.
Pressed forward, keeping tabs on leader before shuffled back to 3rd passing 900m. Stayed in contention to straight before tiring. Unacceptable performance.
Began well, holding box seat before pushed back to 4th passing 900m. Lost position around turn and finished tailed off. Found to have an irregular heart rhythm.
Began well, hampered 1050m, settled three back along fence. Put under pressure 400m, got split 250m, charged home strongly. Rider dropped whip 200m.
Quickly into stride, grabbing box seat before first turn and tailing leader. Urged forward along rail in straight, looked winner 250m, run down final stages.
Quickly away, pushed forward, settling one-off, three-back. Rolled forward 350m, shifted in 200m forcing jockey to stop riding, then one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide till joining leader passing 950m. Joint leader passing 200m but one-paced closing stages.
Hard ridden from outside draw to stay with leaders in one-off, one-back position. Battled on gamely early in straight, one-paced final 200m.
First out, showed way to 950m when pressured by another, caught passing 200m, kept on to 100m, faded.
Got off well, not pushed, settling along rail 4-back from leader. Tightened 600m, switched out 400m to make challenge but one-paced.
Outpaced, settling at rear along fence. Improved position around turn, took inside run in straight, kept on fairly.
Steadied soon after start, shifted across behind horses, settling at rear. Well back entering straight but kept on fairly.
Stumbled start and hit barrier stall, ridden to make ground but wide, settling behind midfield. One-paced in straight.
Pushed early, settling midfield away from fence. Kept tabs on leading pack to straight when tired quickly.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, dropping towards rear. Trailed field thereafter.
Settled in midfield along the rail 5L behind, suited to the fast tempo, dashed strongly to score.
Raced in front of midfield along the rail 3L off, suited to the fast pace, ran on well for 2nd, beaten by a length.
Prominent, 2L behind the leader 2 wide without cover. Took up lead in the 5th section, not suited to the fast tempo, ran home one paced.
In midfield 5-1/2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, benefitted by the fast tempo, ran home steadily for 4th.
Urged forward and obtained box-seat, sat 1-1/4L behind the leader, harmed by the fast tempo, run ended passing 150M.
Settled in worse than midfield along the rail 6-3/4L behind, suited to the fast tempo, no dash in the straight.
Eased back and travelled at the rear, 8-3/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover. Despite suited to the fast tempo, ran home one paced only.
In front of midfield, 3-3/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, weakened soon after straightening.
Travelled towards the rear along the rail, 8-1/2L behind the leader, emptied passing 200M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 7-1/4L off the pace, never ran on.
Urged forward and led by 1-1/4L until 700M, weakened near 250M.
Always at the rear, never competitive.
Quickly into stride, racing inside leading pack before settling in box seat back stretch. Got rails run in straight and gradually overhauled leader.
Quickly in front but forced to race wide before cutting to fence 900m. Came under pressure soon after straightening but kept on well till run down final strides.
Well away, racing between horses before settling one-back, one-off entering back stretch. Rolled forward passing 400m, looked chance 200m, kept on well.
Began OK, racing in midfield but wide with cover. Kept 3-wide around turn and boxed on gamely in straight to be nearest at finish.
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling 3L behind leader in one-off position. Boxed on gamely in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped with field, not pressured, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Urged forward but wide 400m, kept on fairly in straight.
Got off OK, taken to fence, 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail in straight and kept on fairly.
Crowded start, shifted across behind runners to fence, settling at rear. Switched out 400m, ran on fairly till blocked 100m. Not tested final stages.
Crowded out start, shifted across behind horses but kept away from fence at rear. Kept on fairly in straight making up some late ground.
Crowded out start, steadied, shifted across behind horses and last on settling. Never competitive though did run past beaten horses.
Began well but trapped wide without cover behind leading pack. Rolled forward from 800m to get within 1L of leader at 400m. Kept on till tiring quickly final150m.
Bumped start, recovered along fence 4-back from leader. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Began well, soon restrained to race behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace making the turn, swung wide for home, wound up strongly to get up near 50M.
Tracked leader, ran on well to take command from 200M, led to near 50M.
Driven to the lead, set strong early pace, slowed things down in 2nd quarter, lost lead 200M, fought on to hold 3rd just.
Jumped well, never far off from leaders, kept on steadily final 300M, just missed out on 3rd.
Settled down 3-4Ls off the pace, into clear 300M and had every chance, ran on moderately and failed to pose serious threat to first 2.
In midfield, raced keenly early, 4Ls off the pace 400M but lacked the necessary response in straight, held ground final 200M.
Began awkwardly, towards the rear and well off the pace early stages, moved a shade closer over the turn, stayed on only fairly up the home straight, never threatened.
Slowly away, 2nd last 7-8Ls away, not quickened when shoved along 400M, never involved.
Close up in 3rd, not found extra when pushed approaching top of straight, dropped away passing 250M.
Chased leaders, caught wide no cover from early stages, gave ground passing 300M.
Dropped back to rear from 10, severely checked 450M and forced extremely wide to avoid a broken down runner, out of contention. (Jockey not comfortable with horse's action / No Vet findings)

Placing: PU
Comment: Towards the rear, broke down passing 450M, pulled up.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, shifted in alongside race leader to settle one off the rails, relegated to 3rd when new race leader swept past them 800 metres out, came to challenge turning in, asserted authority 100 metres out.

Jumped well from a middle date, ridden to hold leading spot and soon crossed to rails, ceded advantage briefly coming out of far side before regaining lead shortly after straightening, outlasted by winner 100 metres out.

Jostled at start dropping to last early stages, picked up to rear of field along rails after first 300 metres, badly held up for a run from upon straightening to the 200 metres, finished off race well once into the clear.
Jumped fairly, settled on rails in midfield, baulked for a run upon straightening, obtained a clear passage about 250 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening.
Moderate start, soon recovered to a prominent position on rails, baulked for a run passing the 300 metres, could only keep on the same pace without quickening closing stages.
Moderate start from a middle draw, travelled wide just better than midfield when blundered, soon recovered and made rapid progress on the bend to share the pace into straight, faded under pressure.
Broke well, soon taken back towards the rear racing mainly 3-wide, took closer order rounding home bend and one of the widest turning in, could only plug on at the same pace in the run home.
Ridden along to hold a prominent place, lost position coming out of far side, dropped out tamely from just better than midfield into straight.
Crowded jumping out travelling in last few, wide around home bend and into straight, kept on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Jumped fairly, settled in rear of midfield, slightly worse rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Soon dropped well behind from the widest gate, trailed the field into straight, no further impression.
Broke well, settled just better than midfield 3-wide, similar turning in, soon weakened.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, favoured by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M, on heels 150M.
Eased back, raced wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
Eased to sit behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Hard ridden to obtain a prominent spot, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden early but not muster, midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, little dash 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, soon emptied 300M.
At back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, never improved.
At rear, never progressed.
Hard ridden to lead at slow sectionals, soon reduced 300M, on heels 150M.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, made an early move rounding the Home Turn, kept on strongly to the line to score by a short head.
Slotted in to a prominent position from a wide draw, tracked behind the winner nicely most race, however beaten by a short head.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 3rd, however not able to match with the first two.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran home steadily.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, kept on steadily until weakened over the latter stages.
Eased to worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, ran on steadily.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually without any serious threat.
Taken back as usual, travelled 8.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight without any real threat.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on only one pace until weakened 150M.
Blundered badly on jumping, then travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on fairly until weakened 150M.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along throughout, never looked likely.
Prominent, however trapped wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Always at rear, never ran on.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led, flattened badly rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1050m and slowing speed. Shaken up and kicked clear 350m, kept on well.
Began well, ridden forward, settling one-back, one-off. Switched 3-wide on straightening and kept on gamely without threatening winner.
Jumped with field, raced keenly before checked off heels 950m. Settling in box seat, staying on rail in straight and kept on gamely without closing gap.
Got off OK, ridden to hold forward position, settling 1L behind and outside leader. Caught flat-footed when leader kicked 350m, picked up and boxed on.
Pushed forward from an outside draw but held three-wide without cover 3L from leader. Swung wide into straight, kept on one-paced.
Began OK, not pushed, holding position along fence three-back from leader. Shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Began awkwardly, ridden along one-off, three-back before steadied off heels 800m. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride and clear last on settling. Switched out wide in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Lifted front feet when gates opening and began only fairly. Urged forward but wide approaching turn, one-paced in straight.
Ridden along behind midfield but caught wide without cover. Lost position around turn and plodded in straight.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after start and taken to rail towards rear. Hugged fence throughout without making ground.
Outpaced and soon in last pair in one-off position. Never competitive.
Pushed forward along rail, taking clear lead passing 850m and slowing pace. Kicked clear soon after straightening and kept on strongly to the line.
First out but wide, eased and settled behind leading pair but still wide. Rolled forward on straightening and finished strongly.
Began well but took time to muster, gradually edging into box seat back stretch. Revved up on straightening but unable to catch leader.
Began well but unable handle early pace, dropping towards rear between horses. Not much room top of straight, bumped 350m, got split 100m, finished strongly.
Began OK but kept wide and then steadied 900m, dropping to last pair. Last into straight, switched very wide, ran on well closing stages.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling behind the pace but wide. Wide into straight but kept on steadily.
Bumped start, not pressed, racing 3-wide behind midfield. Very wide into straight, bumped and unbalanced 350m, kept on well.
Began well but not pressured, settling between horses 3L from leader. Ran on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Outpaced early, dropping to last along rail. Switched out turning for home, hard ridden from 350m but only one-paced.
Began fairly, crowded out, dropping towards rear close to rail. Stayed on rail around turn but found little when asked in straight.
Began well, ridden to stay with early pace before taking position outside leader 850m. Under pressure from 350m and faded gradually.
Raced in midfield 4L behind 2 wide with cover, dashed well to score despite not suited to the slow pace.
Eased back from a wide draw, 8L off the pace 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strongly for 2nd.
Settled towards the rear, 7L behind 3 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, finished off nicely from 200M for 3rd.
Ridden forward to take the rail and settled 1L behind the leader. Benefitted by the slow tempo, ran on well until flattened at 100M.
Settled in front of midfield along the rail, 3L off the pace, suited to the slow pace, flattened passing 200M.
Settled just off the leader, 3/4L behind 2 wide without cover, despite suited to the slow tempo, found no extra at 200M.
Sat in just behind midfield, 5-1/4L off 3 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, slight dash passing 250M.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Raced in worse than midfield 6L behind 2 wide with cover, improved slightly before weakened inside 100M.
Urged forward and eventually took lead near 1100M, despite benefitted the slow tempo, emptied at 250M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind 3-4 wide with cover, never ran on.
Sat in midfield along the rail, 4-1/2L off the pace, harmed by the slow pace, weakened passing 250M.
Eased back to sit at the rear, never a factor.
In midfield 3-3/4L behind, widest and without cover, flattened at 400M.
Began well, not pushed, settling along fence 3-back from leader. Came off fence 400m, 5-wide into straight, finished strongly to win close home.
Bumped and unbalanced start, allowed to settle, sliding towards rear but wide. Kept 3-wide turn, shaken up 400m, finished strongly down centre track but unable catch winner.
Got off OK, holding rail 4-back from leader. Raced tight entering turn, got inside run in straight, close to heels 150m before flashing home final stages.
Began awkwardly, shifted in and bumped, then ridden to recover lost ground, settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward to look chance 200m, swamped final stages.
Worked way forward from wide draw to sit outside leader to and around turn. Pressed forward on entering straight, hit front 200m, flattened final stages.
Bumped start, then hard ridden to lead on settling. Headed passing 200m but boxed on gamely till tiring final strides.
Ridden along early but wide before edging closer to fence behind midfield. Hard ridden entering straight but only one-paced.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped another, dropping to rear. Travelled keenly passing 700m, taken very wide in straight, one-paced.
Ridden to hold forward position from an outside draw and left without cover from 800m. One-paced in straight under hard riding.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping to rear but away from fence. Shaken up around turn but found nothing.
Began well, ridden along behind midfield but under pressure from 750m to keep position, dropping to last around turn. One-paced.
Shifted out and bumped start, ridden to recover ground, grabbing box seat before turn. Ran out of steam on straightening and dropped out quickly.
Positioned 2-3Ls off leader in 7th place, ran on steadily passing 300M, established narrow lead inside 80M, fought off challenges from both side to prevail.
Dropped back to near the rear, 5Ls off the pace early stages, headway 450M, strongly pressed leaders final 150M, just held.
Always in firing line, took over command 300M, rallied when challengers loomed large 150M, headed by first 2 final stages.
Never far off in 6th, held up for some distance passing 400M, ran on moderately final 300M but always held by first 3.
Began awkwardly, settled down 3-4Ls in midfield, kept on moderately towards finish, pleasing debut.
Not hurried early stages, towards the rear 5Ls back, ran on well final 300M down center of track. (Blood in trachea.)
Behind mid-division 4Ls off the pace, kept on fairly passing halfway and couldn't match finishing pace of leaders final 300M.
Trailed behind pacesetter along the stands' rail, severely checked 250M when going for a narrow passage, made late gains without threatening leaders.
Settled down near rear 6Ls off the early pace, made limited progress final 300M, never reached contention.
Chased the pace early, kept on same pace when pushed along half-way, flattened out 200M.
Knuckled over at the start, taken across to stands' rail behind runners, under pressure 600M and had plenty to make up, ran past beaten horses only.
Towards the rear, never travelled well and had to be pushed along before midpoint, no impression.
Soon led, had uncontested lead first half, headed 300M out, weakened rapidly.
Raced keenly behind leader, brief effort passing 400M, inclined to shift ground under pressure, swamped by rivals 250M, eased late. (No Vet findings / Unacceptable Performance)
Bumped start, pressed forward to sit in slipstream of leader to straight. Got split between horses 300m, hit front 220m, pulled clear final stages.
First into stride, then shared pace to 900m before settling 1L behind leader in one-off position. Rolled forward to challenge 350m but unable match winner final stages.
Hard ridden to lead passing the 900m, then set good pace to 220m when passed but kept on gamely for minor placing.
Began well but unable handle early pace, slipping three-back along rail 5L from leader. Urged forward turning for home, bumped and unbalanced 200m, boxed on.
Steadied shortly after start and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Made some progress around turn and ran on steadily in straight.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing very wide before seeking cover towards rear entering turn. Widest in straight and kept on fairly.
Outpaced early and trailed field to straight before running on fairly in straight to be closest at finish.
Began fairly, then ridden to make up ground settling four-back 8L from leader. Made ground along rail early in straight but flattened final 100m.
Began well but held wide and eased to find cover, settling one-off, three back. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Hard ridden from an outside draw, racing 3-wide 1.5L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, bumped and unbalanced 200m, faded. Unacceptable performance.
Bumped shortly after start, ridden along ahead of midfield but 5L from leader. Faded quickly final 300m.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier to share the lead, on the fence. Held the lead throughout. Fading late, but just had enough to hold on by the barest of margins late.

Began well from the inside draw and pushed forward to be handily placed just behind the leaders, on the fence. Held up until the 300m, and ran strongly to the line wearing down the winner, but just missing late.
Began OK, settling just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran on strongly from the 300m, but failing to kick like 1st and 2nd late.

Steadied early, and taken back to sit at the rear of the field, on the fence. Held up early in the straight and had to come off heels at the 300m, losing momentum. Shifted out under pressure last 100m, but ran on strongly.
Began well and cruised up early to be forward of midfield on the fence, before running onto heels at the 900m. Didn't get a clear run until 250m, and went to the line well.
OK away and taken forward early to be handily placed behind the leaders, 1 off the fence. Tried to run on from the turn, but was held up until the 200m, and went to the line steadily when clear.
Steadied from the wide draw to sit at the back of the field, 3 wide. Came in to take the rails run from the turn, and ran on steadily without ever threatening.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier to sit just behind the leaders, 3 wide with no cover. Well placed and led at 300m, but peaked on his run soon after, and faded back through the field late.
Dropped back early, sitting at the rear of the field. Went to run on from the turn, but went to the line 1 paced, picking up a few slower ones late
Fairly away before settling just worse than midfield, on the rail. Never responded to pressure from the 400m, and only plugged away to the line late.
Began OK from the wide barrier before settling midfield, 1 off the fence. Fading from the 400m, and not pushed to the line.
Pushed forward early to take a share of the lead, 1 off the fence. Never ran on in the straight, and eased out late.
Didn't kick early, sitting worse than midfield 1 off the fence. Didn't respond to pressure from the top of the straight, and only plugged away to the line late.
Dropped back early, eventually settling midfield, 3-4 wide. Dropped back from the turn, and eased up a long way from home.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2 length behind the leader, easy run to turn, dashed well in straight to score.
Moderately away, taken back to race at rear, gradually improved after 1000M, 3 wide with cover in midfield on turn, finished off very strongly in straight, just beaten narrowly.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear early in straight, headed near 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Began well, positioned 1-out 1-back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, angled out on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening the first few.
Moderately away from gate 13, sent forward to race outside leader in 2nd, there to turn, kept on well until near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide, 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, improved to 5th in the middle stages, 3 wide no cover on turn, kept on evenly until steadied 150M, stayed on thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, similar position to turn, finished off evenly in straight. (See racing incidents)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at tail, slightly improved at the back straight, 3-4 wide turning, took widest in straight and made minor progress.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, kept to inside after straightening, closed off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced 5 lengths or so back behind midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 7 to 8 lengths back at tail, still 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced, never a threat.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress early in straight, got traffic and steadied near 150M, not ridden out thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 7 lengths back at rear, ridden on turn, showed no response, finished tailed out.

Began well to lead on rails from a middle gate, taken one back behind pace-setter around stables bend, resumed lead 400m out kicking over 3L clear early in straight, the post came in time for holding onto the fast-diminishing margin.
Settled in last few, finished off race well down the inner of straight, did best work late.
Sluggish at start, settled behind midfield on rails, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled in forward of midfield in 5th one off the rails, commenced run rounding home bend gaining 3rd into straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, wide into straight, finished off race well near the centre of the straight.
Settled in midfield racing one off the rails down far side, came under pressure rounding home bend, worked home steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, picked up gradually to settle 2L back in 3rd far side, slightly wide turning in, founding nothing in the run home.
Settled at the back after beginning from a wide gate, similar turning for home, kept on steadily past well-beaten horses in straight.
Broke well, settled mainly in midfield in 6th on rails, baulked for a stride when keen 800 metres out, similar position turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Broke well, settled towards the rear, made no impression in straight. (Tactic questioned) (Lame next day)
Not far off on rails, faded out of contention upon straightening.
Broke well from the widest draw, worked his way across steadily to lead on rails rounding stables bend, led to the 400 metres when weakened noticeably.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, pace good, dashed strongly 250M for 2nd.
Trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, pace good, made steady ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, box seat, pace good, ran on until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, hung on until 200M weakened.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, pace good, soon out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, lack turn of foot in straight.
Prominent along the fence, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, no dash.
Behind midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, ran on ok.
At rear, 2 wide, no progress.
Never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, accelerated nicely to score by a neck.
Jumped slowly, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, dashed strongly for 2nd, missed by a neck. (Questioned for riding)
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L, hung on until final 50M headed.
Camped handy, however travelled wide without cover throughout, kept on steadily to the line.
Driven forward to park outside the leader, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made plenty of ground in straight. (Questioned for riding)
Pushed to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace to the line without any threatening.
Nearly last, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Prominent, however trapped deep without cover throughout, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.
Taken back from a wide draw, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Pressed forward inside early leader before taking over 1400m and slowing field. Increased tempo entering final turn, kicked ahead 350m, challenged strongly 100m, just held.
Ridden early before crossing to fence, settling towards rear. Allowed to settle, swung wide into straight, ran on strongly to just miss.
Began OK, outpaced, settling at rear. Trailed field to straight, switched out and finished strongly.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling between horses four-back from leader. Taken wide in straight and ran on steadily doing best work final 100m.
A little slow into stride, then taken to fence four-back from leader. Got clear rails run in straight, ran on well to 100m before turning one-paced.
Ridden to maintain forward position but held three-wide without cover. Taken wider on straightening, kept on fairly to 150m then one-paced.
Shifted out and bumped start, pressed forward, settling one-off, three-back. Badly held for run till 200m, boxed on.
Urged forward from wide draw before edging closer to fence one-back, one-off. Boxed on well early straight before turning one-paced.
Ridden early, holding rail position three-back from leader. Took closer order around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Quickly into stride, grabbed box seat, then allowed to relax. Shaken up top of straight but found nothing and faded.
No early pace but still kept towards rear. Taken even wider around turn and a beaten horse soon after straightening.
Hard ridden to lead soon after jump before easing back a half length outside leader entering first turn. Stayed in contention to straight before tiring.
Ridden to hold forward position 3-back from leader but away from fence. Swung wide entering straight and finished strongly to just get there.
Bumped start, rolled forward, holding rail three-back from leader. Got inside run in straight, hit front 100m, challenged but held on for dead heat.
Slow into stride, settling in last pair. Clear last into straight, taken wide and finished strongly.
Bumped start, pressed forward, taking box seat. Urged closer around turn, hit front soon after straightening, kept on well before swamped final stages.
Began OK but outpaced, dropping to rear. Brushed rail turning for home, got inside run in straight, kept steadily to be closest at finish.
Shifted across behind runners shorty after start but then proved difficult to settle, dropping back. Picked up bridle on straightening, rolled forward but badly hampered 150m.
Began well, ridden to hold midfield position but away from fence. Turned wide, urged forward to look a chance 200m, then one-paced.
Quickly into stride, battling for early lead, before easing back into second, 3L from leader. Closed in top of straight but soon under pressure, crowded 150m and faded.
Began well, steadied passing 1500m then proved difficult to settle, dropping four back from leader. Travelled keenly to turn, no clear run in straight, checked 150m and not fully tested.
Began well, urged forward one-back, one-off. Rolled forward entering straight to look a chance 200m before turning one-paced and checked 100m.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw and last on settling. Pushed forward but wide turn, swung very wide into straight, faded.
Hard ridden but wide to take lead passing 1150m and kicking 3L clear. Started to shorter stride 400m, collared 250m, faded.
Sat in front of midfield 2-1/2L behind 3 wide without cover, niggled forward early at 700M, suited to the slow pace, dashed strongly from 200M to score.
Hard ridden forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L through slow sectionals, kept pushing until headed by the winner inside 50M.
Prominent, 1-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, finished off one paced.
Sat in worse than midfield, 4-1/2L off 2-3 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow tempo, made ground for 4th.
Settled towards the rear along the rail, 7-1/4L behind, not suited to the slow pace, ran on steadily.
Travelled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, one paced home.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat 1-1/4L behind, despite benefitted by the slow pace, no dash.
Settled just in front of midfield along the rail 2-3/4L behind, not suited to the slow tempo, kept on one paced until emptied inside 100M.
Pushed forward from a wide barrier to sit outside the leader 3/4 behind, suited to the slow pace, weakened passing 200M.
At rear along the rail 9-3/4L behind, did not improve.
Travelled towards the rear 6-1/2L off the pace 2-3 wide, never looked likely.
Always at the rear, not a factor.
Ridden along 3-wide in tightly-packed field 3L from leader to turn. Urged forward top of straight, hit front 150m, just held.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners from wide barrier and clear last on settling. Last into straight, pressed forward between horses, rocketing home final 100m to just miss.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw, settling toward rear but away from fence. Swung wide into straight and finished strongly.
Ridden early but took time to muster, holding rail 3-back from leader. Took inside run in straight and kept on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward from inside draw to hold box seat. Closed in top of straight before denied run and forced to shift in 200m. Boxed on.
Ridden to stay with pace but kept wide and eased one-back, one-off around turn. Urged forward 350m to look chance 200m before flattened 100m.
Hard ridden 4-wide to stay with pace before easing off around turn but still wide. Kept on steadily to 200m before turning one-paced.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Momentarily headed passing 750m, retook lead 400m and kicked clear, caught 150m, faded.
Ridden early but trapped wide, restrained and shifted across behind horses around turn. One-paced in straight.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, settling behind leader pair in one-off position. Came off bridle entering straight, boxed on to 200m before fading.
Ridden forward outside early leader before edging ahead 550m. Slipped back to 2nd passing 400m and tired quickly in straight.
Settled down midfield 5Ls off the pace, picked up strongly to lead near 100M, continued on well to the finish.
Positively ridden, always close up behind leader, ran on well to go 2nd near finish, held by winner.
Sent forward, took up the chase from the 2-path, driven to lead 250M, caught by winner near 100M, lost 2nd close home.
Settled along the fence ahead of midfield, crept closer home turn, ran on steadily towards finish.
Taken back to the rear from wide barrier, not hurried 10Ls off the pace in middle stages, made good progress up the fence final 300M.
4Ls off the pace in 5th, moved up to challenge 400M, run ended 150M, faded towards the finish.
Coaxed to the front setting good pace first 800M, led to 250M, weakened late stages.
Slow to begin, settled near the rear 7-8Ls behind leader, ran on one paced final 300M, not reached leaders.
Patiently ridden, held up behind midfield, not quickened when put to test 300M. (No Vet findings)
Held up midfield, saved ground on the inside, gave way shortly on straightening, eased. (No Vet findings)
Taken back on jumping, 2nd last 8Ls off the pace, moved closer passing 700M round outside of field, soon beaten top of straight and eased. (No Vet findings)
Never far off from the pace but caught 3-wide no cover throughout, gave ground 400M, first to be beaten. (Unacceptable Performance)
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, dropping to last. Picked up speed entering straight, found run between horses, finished strongly final 200m to win close home.
Ridden forward from an outside draw, settling 2L behind leader back stretch. Took inside run in straight, looked winner 100m, caught on line.
Quickly into stride, racing outside leader before settling one-off, one-back. Rolled forward to challenge 300m, kept on strongly to just miss.
Raced tight shortly after start, got close to heels 1400m, eased three-back, one-off. Shaken up 350m but took time to wind up doing best final 100m.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, pulled clear back stretch, put under pressure from 300m but kept battling till 50m when swamped.
Ridden along early to hold forward position before moving into box seat first turn. Kept on well early in straight before tiring final 100m.
Bumped start, ridden along between horses settling behind midfield. Kept on steadily in straight to be nearest at the finish.
Bumped start, no early speed, settling at rear but wide. Kept wide back stretch and final turn, ran on fairly in straight.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail three back from leader. Stayed on rail around final turn but only one-paced in straight.
Outpaced early, dropping to last pair but way from fence. Well back entering straight and never looked a threat.
Got off OK but not pushed, holding rail four back from leader. Kept on fairly to straight before fading.
Ridden along early but unable to find cover and trapped three wide behind midfield. Kept wide throughout and gave ground in straight.

Ridden forward to share the pace far side before gaining narrow advantage rounding home bend, soon kicked over 2L clear on straightening, won unchallenged.
Moderate start but with leaders early, settled one back one off the rails rounding home bend, failed to kick with winner early in straight and only kept on at the same pace without threatening.
Slow out, settled at the back on rails, took closer order passing the 1000 metres, similar position turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Broke well from a poor draw, racing wide in midfield before dropping to last few over 1000 metres out, ran on near the centre of the straight, did best work late.
Ridden early, then raced keenly before settling just better than midfield in 6th one off the rails, shifted out for a run upon straightening but ran all over the place without making any headway.
Settled towards the rear, baulked early in straight, finished off race well inside final 200 metres.
Ridden along mainly 3-wide in midfield, similar rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Taken back to rear while racing keenly, remained well behind to straight, baulked for a run until the 200 metres,
Broke well, held slender lead on rails far side before ceding narrow advantage rounding home bend, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Broke well, close up early before gradually shifted back towards the rear while 3-wide, in similar position in last few entering straight, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped well from the widest gate, gradually came across to race keenly without cover in a prominent position, dropped out tamely inside final 300 metres.
Never better than midfield, made no impression in straight. (Bled)
Niggled at early, improved along rails to soon reach 2L 5th but hampered and lost position 800 metres out, faded under pressure after straightening.
Moderate start, travelled on rails and never better than midfield, folded up quickly after straightening.
Eased back, 2 wide, made steady ground 300M to score with some in hand.
Eased back for cover, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made some ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on until 200M flattened.
At rear, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, held up most straight, made ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, ran on fairly when clear.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress, on heels 300M.
Midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, reduced 250M.
Pushed to take rail and shared lead, clocked fast sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Eased back, raced wide, never a factor.
Very slow away, never join competition.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, dashed well to score by 1/2L.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, finished off nicely to get 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover throughout, ran on well to get 3rd.
Rolled forward to settle in a prominent position, however trapped deep without cover throughout, one paced home for 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 – 3 wide with cover, closed to the line well when clear final 100M.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, kept on one pace until final 200M weakened. (Lost plate 50M)
Taken back from a wide draw, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never a factor. (Bled)
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
Jumped slowly, travelled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, checked 750M, never ran on.

Placing: UR
Comment: Driven forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L, kept on only fairly and rider dislodged final 50M.
Allowed to stride forward, taking lead on settling, crossing to fence first turn. Shuffled back to 3rd back stretch, shaken up 400m, hit front 150m, kept on strongly.
Began well, rolled forward, settling one-off, one-back and switched off. Urged forward passing 500m, hit front 300m, passed 150m, kept on well.
Got off OK, racing between horses in midfield before edging to fence back stretch. Took inside run in straight, ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Slow, urged forward but didn't settle. Checked and badly unbalanced 1800m dropping to rear. Well back final turn, ran on steadily in straight.
Began well, striding forward at own pace to grab box seat. Loomed outside leader on straightening, but only one-paced final 200m.
Jumped with field but soon outpaced, dropping to rear along rail. Still well back entering straight before running on fairly.
Began OK, allowed to find feet behind midfield but a little wide to back stretch. Lost position around final turn, one-paced in straight.
Lifted front feet when gate opened and slow into stride dropping to rear but away from fence. Last into straight, ran past tired horses.
Began well, racing with leading pack in box seat before being shuffled back around first turn. Not asked for an effort until straightening but only one-paced.
Began well but not pushed, striding between horses before moving forward to sit 1L behind leader back stretch. Gave ground soon after straightening.
Urged along from an outside draw and caught wide in midfield without cover. Stayed wide throughout, tiring final 200m.
Began fairly and held at rear before rolling forward from 1400m, circling field to lead passing 1280m. Led to 300m before tiring.
Began awkwardly, urged forward back stretch. Improved turn, ran out of stamina top of straight and faded.
Aggressively ridden to lead from wide draw, cutting to fence 1050m and slowing pace. Kicked 2L clear 300m and went to the post unchallenged.
Began well, ridden along between horses, settling three-back from leader. Took turn 3-wide, shaken up 350m, finished off nicely but unable to catch winner.
Bumped start, rolled forward, settling between horses 3L from leader. Surged forward top of straight but unable match first two.
Began OK, ridden to hold rail 3-back from leader. Improved position turn, stayed on rail in straight and kept on steadily.
Bumped start, urged forward racing wide 2L from leader. Taken wider home turn and left without cover. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Outpaced and soon at rear along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and kept on one-paced in straight.
Urged forward from an awkward draw, settling 1L behind leader before turn. Came under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Ridden along from an outside draw, racing wide without cover at midfield. Covered extra ground turn and finished off one-paced down centre track.
Jumped OK, ridden but didn't muster, dropping to rear but wide. Blocked for run entering straight, taken very wide, found little under pressure.
Began awkwardly then crowded and lost ground, settling between horses behind midfield. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
Got off OK but difficult to settle, dropping to rear away from fence. Taken wide in straight but failed to respond under pressure.
Outpaced early, gradually shifting to fence in last place. Shaken up on straightening but found nothing.
Bumped start, pressed forward to race in slipstream of leader to straight. Kept on fairly to 200m before fading.
Settled in front of midfield 2-1/4L behind, 2 wide without cover, unleashed strong finishing effort once cleared from 350M to score.
Travelled just in front of midfield along the rail 3L behind the leader, finished off strongly despite not suited to the slow tempo.
In worse than midfield 5L off the pace 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Rolled forward to sit just outside the leader, 3/4L behind 2 wide without cover, ran on well until flattened 200M.
In midfield 3-3/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, little dash from 200M. (Questioned for riding out over the concluding stages)
Settled in midfield 3-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, little respond when asked early in the Straight, slight dash at 300M.
Eased back, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, improved slightly in the Straight.
Towards the rear along the rail, 4-1/2L off the pace, harmed by the slow pace, little dash at 200M, flattened shortly thereafter.
At rear along the rail, 6-1/4L behind the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, ran home only one paced.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led at slow sectionals by 3/4L, headed at 300M, did not run on thereafter.
Prominent, 1-1/2L off the pace, trapped 3 wide without cover, despite benefited by the slow tempo, flattened at 350M.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, 1-1/2L behind the leader, flattened at 350M.
Always at the rear, not competitive.
Sat towards the rear 5L off the pace 3 wide with cover, did not run on.
Began well, rolling forward at own pace, settling three-back, one-off. Swung wide into straight, shaken up and urged forward, hit front 100m, kept on strongly.
Began well, hugging rail three-back from leader. Closed in around turn but held for run top of straight. Finished strongly when clear 250m.
Jumped with field, checked 1400m, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Swung very wide into straight, rolled forward to lead 200m, flattened late.
Got off OK, taken to fence 3-back from leader and switched off. Switched out on straightening and ran on nicely to be closest at the finish.
Pressed forward from an outside, settling in one-off position 1L behind leader. Rolled forward top of straight to share lead but one-paced final 150m.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling in box seat around turn. Urged forward on straightening, joint leader 200m, flattened late.
Began awkwardly, hampered 1400m then raced keenly, dropping to rear. Switched out straight, ran on well but bumped 200m, denied run 100m, not properly tested.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling in one-off behind midfield. Urged forward turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Outpaced, settling towards rear close to fence. Took closer order around turn and kept on fairly in straight.
Bumped start, urged forward, settling 3L behind leader in one-off position, Kept within striking range to 200m before tiring.
Bumped start, pressed forward, holding one-off position 1L behind leader. Boxed on gamely in straight before tiring and fading final 200m.
Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind runners from an outside draw at rear. Raced keenly when shaken up before turn, last into straight, plodded.
Began awkwardly, urged forward to lead clearly on settling, set decent pace to straight when soon collared. Bumped 200m when giving ground.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Urged ahead turn but soon beaten and dropped back.
Sent forward from wide gate, sped to a 3L lead back straight, kept on strongly turning in and still showed no signs of tiredness to 100M, impressive all the way victory in fast time.
In 9th / 10th position, over 10Ls behind the strong pace in middle stages, closed off strongly final 400M, got up for 2nd near 100M but not quite getting to winner.
Settled down in 4th 5Ls behind runway leader middle stages, responded well to pressure, briefly went 2nd passing 200M, not reached winner, turned one pace late stages.
Raced as the back-marker, over 14Ls off the pace mid stages, pushed along 600M, ran on well to go 4th late stages but no serious threat to first three.
Patiently ridden, held up at the back over 10Ls off the good pace, had plenty to make up 400M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 5th.
In 6th place, 10Ls off the strong pace in middle stages, stayed on fairly entering straight before turning one pace final 100M.
Chased leader in a strongly run race, nudged along to keep up 500M, out-finished and lost 2nd mid-straight, weakened towards finish.
Held up in 5th 7-8Ls off the strong pace, ran on only fairly when placed under pressure 400M, out-finished and never got into contention.
Towards the rear over 10Ls off the pace, under pressure 1000M out, fell back to last 400M, gave limited response when driven out in straight. (No Vet findings.)
Caught 3-wide no cover in 8th position, kept on same pace in straight, never got into contention. (No Vet findings.)
Dropped back from wide barrier, settled down towards the rear over 10Ls off the good pace, not quickened turning in, never threatened.
In 7th place over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, didn't find much when put to pressure top of straight, never involved.
Chased leaders in 3rd, appeared to travel well into straight but emptied passing 300M, weakened rapidly towards finish. (No Vet findings.)
Bumped but quickly into stride, sliding to rail inside leading pack and holding box seat to straight. Got split between horses 300m, shot ahead and held off late challenges.
Began well, urged forward, settling one-back, one-off. Straightened 3-wide, looked chance 200m, battled gamely to line.
Began awkwardly, shifted across from wide draw, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Still well back entering straight, switched wide, finished off strongly.
Used early to lead from an outside draw, pulling 2L clear before crossing to fence. Set strong pace to 300m when collared, kept on gamely.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2nd on turn, shared lead early in straight, headed near 250M, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield in one-off position to straight. Urged forward to get within range 200m before turning one-paced.
Slow into stride and last on settling, Switched out turn to improve but kept wide without cover. Ran on fairly down centre track.
Jumped with field but no early pace, dropping to rear along fence. Improved around turn, switched out wide in straight, ran on fairly.
Began fairly, shaken up to hold rail position behind midfield. Lay in and unbalanced turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Began well, ridden to keep close to pace, settling 3L from leader. Taken wide in straight and kept on fairly to 200m turning one-paced.
Outpaced early and soon at rear in one-off position. Stayed at rear throughout and never competitive.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear along rail. Hugged rail throughout but never likely.
Began well, pushed up between horses to get within 4L of leader in one-off position. Kept on fairly early in straight before giving ground final 200m.
Steadied soon after start and taken across behind runners at the rear. Clear last on straightening and never likely.
Pushed forward early to take the lead. Led by 2L turning for home, and kept kicking. Starting to weaken late, but well clear and couldn't be caught.
Steadied from the wide draw to be at the rear of the field, 2-3 wide with cover. Ran on from the turn, and produced a big run to take 2nd and gaining quickly on the winner.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier to be place just behind the leader. Tried to run on with the winner in the straight, but was outpaced. Ran to the line well, only losing 2nd late.
OK to begin, finding a position midfield on the rail. Pushed solidly to the line, and just stole 4th in the last stride.
Pushed forward from the jump to be handily place 3rd, on the rail. Began to work from the 300m, and ran to the line OK without threatening a place.
Began well, before easing back to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Stayed close to the rail and ran OK to the line under hands and heels, closing margins late.
Pushed forward early to sit just forward of midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Given clear running to the line, but on plugged away to the finish.
Eased forward early to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Had a dream run early in the straight, but couldn't quicken to take it and only plugged away to the line fairly.
Allowed to cruise forward from the wide barrier to sit midfield, 2-3 wide. Plugged on fairly in the straight, without threatening to improve his position.
Only broke fairly and took a position at the rear of the field, on the fence. Last on the turn, and only went to the line fairly when ridden out and picked up a couple of slower ones.
Only fairly away and dropped out to be at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, but never ran on, and eased to the line late.
Broke well and taken forward to be handily placed in 4th, 1 off the fence. Lay out on the turn, and didn't run on when asked to go early in the straight. Easing out late.
Began OK, finding a position worse than midfield, on the fence and slightly over racing. Asked to go from the turn, but didn't respond and went flat to the line.
Taken back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Started to improve from the top of the straight, but eased out of the race when jockey became concerned about horses breathing.

Settled towards the rear, made rapid progress down far side and a joint the leader leaving the Rock, shifted sharply out cornering for home, renewed effort from the 200 metres to assert close to home.
Settled mainly one off the rails in midfield, obtained rails run when commenced to improve rounding home bend, sustained progress from 2L 5th into straight to be nearest at the finish.

Jumped well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on rails, came to challenge under pressure entering straight, held minor chance passing the 200 metres but unable to sustain effort close to home.
Broke well in a wide-ish gate but soon obtained rails run just worse than midfield, remained in similar position to straight, finished off race quite well inside final 200 metres.

Restrained to last place from a tricky gate, took off after the 1000 metre bend to reach 3rd 2-wide just off the lead, inconvenienced by winner upon straightening over 300 metres out, fought on under pressure but without threatening.

Soon took up running setting a steady pace while throwing his head for first half of race, nearly headed by the eventual winner which shifted wide in straight, finally yielded lead over 150m out when fading under pressure.
Settled within striking distance most of the way in 3rd or 4th and then 5th, came under pressure in a similar position turning for home, faded out tamely.
Settled 2-wide behind midfield from the widest gate, met minor interference 900 metres out, made short-lived effort around home bend, but one-paced under pressure from 5L 7th into straight.
Slow out from a wide draw, settled in last few on rails dropping to tail-end after the 1000 metre turn, no response under pressure in the final stretch.
Began from a poor gate, raced mainly 3-wide without cover just better than midfield, lost position passing the Rock, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield on rails, yielded ground under pressure rounding home bend.
Bumped at the start, never better than midfield dropping near last into straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield on the rails, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Secured box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, settled along the fence, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, flattened 150M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, hung on until 200M emptied.
Midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 200M.
At back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed early, at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
At back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
At rear, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the run behind the leader, ran on well to score by 3/4L.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest, dashed well to get 2nd, missed by 3/4L.
Pushed to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, closed to the line well for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace to the line without any serious threat.
Failed to muster early, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground along the inside. (Questioned rider for running)
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls, kept on fairly until final 250M headed.
Taken back from a wide draw, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Always at rear, never ran on.
Pushed forward to settle in a prominent position, 3Ls off 2 wide without cover, kept on one pace until final 200M flattened.
At rear throughout, never looked likely.
Away well, restrained, taken to rail 4-back from leader. Came off fence back stretch, moved up 4-wide 500m, finished strongly down centre track for narrow win.
Jumped well, lead initially then took sit behind leader in one-off position, urged forward final turn, hit front 400m, kept finding when challenged only to lose narrowly.
Shared early pace before easing 3L back in one-off position. Urged forward final turn, looked chance 200m, unable match leading pair final 100m.
Quickly into stride, holding fence before sliding into box seat 1900m. Shuffled 3-back1300m, then 4-back 900m. Urged forward from 700m, but unable close gap.
Ridden along early to hold one-off position 4L from leader. Urged forward entering final turn but wide, one-paced in straight.
Shifted across from outside draw dropping to at rear. Took closer order final turn and early in straight before turning one-paced final 200m.
Bumped start, recovered, ridden to make up ground settling in midfield. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Trailed field to straight when switched out and ran past tired horses.
Outpaced early, settling well back close to fence. Dropped to last pair back stretch, put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Away nicely, stayed with early pacemakers before easing 3-back 1600m. Stayed within range to straight before fading gradually in straight.
Began well, racing with leading pack before forging ahead and crossing to rail 1600m. Passed 960m, 4th into straight, faded from 250m.
Allowed to find feet but left wide behind midfield. Not happy with tempo, rolled toward from 1100m to lead 900m. Collared on straightening and faded.
Bumped start, recovered, driven forward along fence to lead passing 1000m. Kicked 3L clear 500m, kept on well to 100m when shortened stride, just held.
Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind runners though still 3-wide at rear. Waited to straight, switched out wide, powered home strongly to just miss.
Shaken up early to stay with pace, racing wide before getting cover around turn 4L from leader. Took inside run in straight and ran on steadily.
Bumped start, urged forward to share early pace before sliding into box seat. Under pressure soon after straightening but unable close gap.
Jumped well, ridden along between horses before settling three-back close to rail. Lost position around turn, took inside run in straight, finished off nicely.
First out, shared early pace to first turn, then restrained looking for cover, dropping three-back, one-off. Switched out turning for home and ran on fairly.
Quickly away, racing with leaders to first turn, before easing off behind leader at 800m. Under pressure from 500m, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Outpaced and held at rear between horses. Switch out entering straight to make run but only one-paced.
Pressed forward early to sit behind the pace though wide before getting cover around turn. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Pushed forward from an awkward draw, racing 4-wide without cover back stretch. Under pressure in straight and weakened gradually.
Crowded out start, dropping to rear and taken to fence. Stayed on rail throughout without making any headway in straight.
Began OK, ridden along but failed to muster and kept 4-wide at rear. Crossed to fence turning for home but found nothing when asked in straight.
Obtained box-seat and sat 2L behind the leader, suited to the slow tempo, finished off nicely to score.
Raced just in front of midfield, 4-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Urged forward to take rail and led by a nose at slow sectionals, headed by the eventual leader at 150M.
In worse than midfield along the rail, 8L behind the leader, despite not suited to the slow pace, finished off strongly for 4th.
Sat outside the leader a nose behind, suited to the slow tempo, kept pushing but found no extra at 150M.
Prominent, 3L off the pace 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, finished off only one paced.
At the rear along the rail 9-3/4L behind, despite not suited to the slow tempo, finished off steadily in the Straight.
In midfield along the rail 6-1/2L behind the leader, harmed by the slow pace, improved slightly in the Straight.
At the rear 12L off the pace 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, made minor ground in the Straight.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
In midfield 5-3/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, made no impression in the Straight.
Travelled in midfield along the rail 4-3/4L behind, never ran on.
Away nicely, not pushed, crossing to fence 4-back from leader. Turned in behind horses, switched in to get run, powered home to win comfortably.
Hard ridden 4-wide from outside draw before settling outside hind-quarters of leader 1100m. Joined leader top of straight, battled on gamely.
Used early to lead, racing wide before crossing to fence 1200m. Joined by another top straight but boxed on strongly till swamped final 100m.
Ridden along between horses to share early pace before settling three-back, one-off back stretch. Kept on steadily in straight without threatening place-getters.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-back, one-off back stretch, put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced under vigorous riding.
Shifted across behind runners from a wide draw, settling at rear. Improved back stretch, taken wide in straight and ran on steadily. Rider fined for not riding out to the finish.
Urged forward with pacemakers before taking box seat back stretch. A little flat when leaders sprinted top of straight but kept on gamely. Had minor graze left front cannon.
Bumped start, then raced keenly and bumped again 950m. Taken wide in straight and boxed on fairly.
Began well, kicked up inside leading pack to hold rail before easing three-back along back stretch. Under pressure after straightening and faded.
Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden along then bumped again 950m and left without cover behind midfield. Faded gradually in straight.
Outpaced and soon a distant last. Trailed field to straight and never competitive.
Began awkwardly and lost ground at start, dropping to rear along rail. Never likely.
From draw 1 settled 3Ls off the pace along the fence, made steady progress up the rails final 300, got up to join leader 50M and prevailed in a close finish.
Sent forward setting steady pace, was allowed an uncontested lead, continued on well in straight, joined by rival 50M and only lost out in close finish.
Eased back to near the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, found his best stride inside 200M, raced tight between rivals late stages, nearest finish.
Taken back behind runners from 12, settled down in the rear 6Ls off the pace, kept to inside on straightening, closed off well final 300M, nearest finish.
Bustled along early on jumping from 11, sat one out one back, kept up the chase on leader throughout in the straight but was always held, lost 2 placings to 5th inside 50M.
Positively ridden, obtained a trailing position behind leaders along the rails, kept on steadily on straightening, not pace of pursuing rivals final 200M.
Caught 3-wide no cover from draw 9, took closer order nearing home turn, kept on one pace in straight and lacked extra.
Failed to muster speed, settled 3-wide at the back, closed off well from off the pace but not quite getting to leaders.
Never better than midfield, kept on same speed turning home, never involved.
No closer than 3-wide, settled down in midfield 4Ls off the pace, failed to pick up on straightening.
Restrained at the rear 6Ls behind leader, pushed along 300M but not making any progress, never a factor.
Held up behind midfield, proved difficult to settle in early and middle stages, driven nearing 300M couldn't finish the race off, left behind 150M. (No Vet findings.)
