Jumped fairly settling in midfield, soon came to challenge after straightening, quickened well to take charge 100 metres out.
Began moderately, worked his way forward to join the leader on home bend hitting the front on straightening, only to be outlasted over 150 metres out.
Not far off, came to challenge after straightening holding every chance over 200 metres out, no extra inside final 100 metres.
Ridden early on rails before settling just off the pace, baulked for a run until the 200 metres but one-paced under pressure once cleared.
Began well, settled wide just worse than midfield, in similar position turning into straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled behind midfield, came under pressure entering straight, found nothing.
Taken well behind from the middle gate, gained slightly closer on rails briefly rounding home bend, kept on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Soon took up running to obtain rails run, headed past the 300 metres, dropped out tamely.
Soon in rear, only ran past well-beaten horses near finish.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Broke well from the widest gate, raced wide without cover throughout far side and gradually dropped back to last at home bend, found nothing in straight.
Moderate start, soon recovered to forward of midfield position in 6th out wide, weakened in straight.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, raced wide in a prominent position and 3rd around home bend, dropped out tamely after straightening.
Close up early, gradually shuffled back to midfield on rails, lost further ground after straightening.
At rear, hard ridden half way, closed off strongly 200M to score by narrow margin.
Hard ridden to cross towards outside fence and led at good pace, hung on well until last 2 strides, just beaten by narrow margin.
Settled in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Behind midfield, on heels early, pace good, made some ground 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, pace good, blocked 4-1, dashed well to the line.
Bumped start, eased to sit just off the leader, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Checked early, midfield, pace good, blocked 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
At back, pace good, held up final 2 furlongs, not properly tested.
Pushed forward, just off the leader, pace good, emptied 200M.
Checked start, sat midfield, pace good, no progress.
Checked shortly after start, pace good, never improved at rear.
Pressed forward, reduced quickly 300M.
Pressed forward, dropped off 400M, confirmed bleeder.
Driven forward to take the fence and led by ½, kept on strongly to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed home nicely to get 2nd, missed by a neck.
Eased back as usual, settled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide rounding the Home Turn, closed to the line well for 3rd.
At rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, made plenty of ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on steadily until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, held up early straight, ran on only fairly thereafter.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader, made some ground in straight despite travelling wide without cover throughout.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Pushed forward to settle in a prominent position with cover, kept on until final furlong weakened. (Lame right fore next day)
Knocked over badly on jumping, then rolled forward to park outside the leader, flattened soon after straightening. (Lost plate and questioned for disappointing performance)
Hard ridden forward to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace until final 250M flattened, tailed out.
Rolled forward to settle in midfield along the fence, dropped off rounding the Home Turn, tailed out. (Bled)
Began OK and quickly taken to fence 4-back from leader. Niggled to keep pace, came off fence 500m, got split 320m, ran on strongly to win close home.
Hampered start, recovered, taken to fence 3-back from leader. Blocked for run 300m, switched out 200m, finished strongly to just miss.
First out but wide, eased, unable to find cover and rolled forward to join leader 900m. Edged ahead 300m, kept on well till swamped final 50m.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting good pace. Joined up from 900m, passed 300m, but boxed on gamely to line.
Began awkwardly, rolled forward, settling one-off, two back. Took closer order around turn, looked chance 200m, one-paced final stages.
Hampered start, ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield but wide. Taken wider in straight, made ground to 200m, then one-paced.
Slow into stride, outpaced, dropping to last along fence. Improved position around turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Bumped start, no pace, dropped to rear but away from fence. Made up some ground around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, shaken up and rolled forward to within 2L of leader in one-off position. Kept on fairly to 200m when gave ground.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling towards rear but away from fence. Lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward to hold rail, taking box seat and tailing leader to straight. Shaken up 400m but found little and faded.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, dropping to last pair in one-off position. Made some ground early in straight before tiring.
Urged forward but caught wide without cover 3L from leader. Kept wide around turn and gave ground quickly in straight.
Ridden early to stay with pace but held wide in midfield. Lost position around turn and faded in straight.
Ridden early to hold box seat, but shuffled 3-back 900m. Came off fence 700m, got run between horses, hard ridden to just get up in time.
Began well, racing outside early leader before easing one-off, one-back. Urged forward on straightening, took over lead 300m, run down on line.
Shifted in behind runners to rail, settling at rear. Taken out and urged forward turn, bumped and taken wider 500m, kept on well final 200m.
Not pushed early settling in midfield. Took turn a little wide, kept on steadily down centre track to be closest at finish.
Ridden along 3-back from leader before losing position turn and switched out. Took inside run in straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden along early before seeking cover, eventually getting to fence 800m. Mixed on gamely in straight while continually switching out to get clear running.
Jumped with field, allowed to slide forward at own pace, settling three-back one-off. Urged forward on straightening, closed in steadily to 200m, then one-paced.
Began OK then pressed forward but wide to lead passing 1100m, cutting to fence 850m. Under pressure top of straight, collared 300m, box on till flattened 100m.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Moved up around turn, hard ridden in straight but found little. Rider fined for excessive use of whip.
Slow into stride, ridden but didn't muster, settling in last pair. Switched out in straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from outside gate, racing wide till getting cover 900m behind midfield. Bumped 500m, switched out in straight but one-paced.
Began well, pressed forward but wide, then taken wider passing 700m when 3L from leader. Ridden vigorously to hold position to straight before weakening. Substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
Outpaced, dropping to rear along rail. Made some progress around turn, but found little in straight and faded.
Quickly into stride, leading to 1100m, then sitting behind leader to turn. Shuffled back turning for home and faded in straight. Irregular heart rhythm.
Settled just behind midfield along the rail, 7-1/4L behind, unleashed well from 300M when obtained clear running and held off close challenge to score.
Raced in midfield, 5-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, kept challenging and beaten by a head only.
At rear, 9-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, finished off well for 3rd.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 6L off the pace, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on steadily for 4th.
Travelled in midfield, 7L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, improve steadily in the Straight.
Urged forward and sat 1-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide without cover, suited to the slow tempo, found no extra from 150M.
Pushed forward to obtain box-seat, 1-1/2L behind the leader, steadied at 400M, and crowded at 150M, finished off only one paced.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, 8-3/4L behind the leader, not suited to the slow pace, made slight ground in the Straight.
Rolled into front of midfield, sat 3-3/4L off on the rail, checked at 250M, did not run on thereafter.
At rear, 11-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, was not competitive throughout.
Sat just behind midfield, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, did not run on.
In front of midfield, 3-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, faded soon after passing 350M.
Urged forward and led at slow sectionals, weakened soon after straightening.
Sat towards the rear, was not competitive.
A little slow to move but picked up quickly along the rails to sit 1L behind leader entering turn. Got clear run in straight, hit front 350m, pulled clear.
Ridden but slow to muster and shuffled to near rear soon after start. Improved turn, switched out 600m to make run, finished nicely.
Bumped start, pressed forward but left wide without cover 700m. Three-wide into straight, ran on well.
Began OK, unable match early pace and dropped to last approaching turn. Taken very wide in straight and finished off nicely.
Pressed forward but wide to lead 1100m but unable cross to fence till turn. Passed 350m, kept on well to 100m before fading. Lame left front leg.
Began well, rolled forward to sit behind leader but left wide without cover 900m. Urged forward turn, looked chance 200m before fading.
Ridden along between horses to hold midfield position away from fence. Improved around turn, kept on well to 200m before flattened.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, dropping to last pair. Improved along rails turn, kept on fairly in straight to 200m then one-paced.
Began fairly, hard ridden to make ground, closing in to within 1L of leader at turn. Under pressure top of straight and gave ground gradually.
Hard ridden inside leading pack but shuffled three-back 750m when outside horses crossed in. Found nothing in straight even after shown whip.
Pressed forward to midfield before being shuffled back around turn. Last into straight and plodded. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Travelled strongly behind midfield, moved closer to a contending position 500M, led 300M, continued on well down the outside and was always holding off the persistent 2nd.
Chased leaders along the inside, moved up to challenge 350M, contested the lead with eventual winner, fought on to the line but was always held.
Dropped back to the rear, crept closer when pace slackened over home turn, stayed on moderately final 400M, always held by first two.
Taken across behind runners from 14, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, took closer order inside 500M, stayed on mildly on straightening, not reached first two.
Settled down 4Ls back in midfield along the fence, ran on moderately final 400M, never a serious threat to first two.
Slightly slow out, held up 2-wide behind midfield, brought wide 500M, closed off only fairly.
Rushed forward, sat in 3rd chasing leaders, brief effort early straight, flattened final 200M.
Shared lead on the inside setting an even pace, tackled by rival 300M, gave way mid-straight. (overreach injury to LF medial heel.)
Never better than midfield, kept on same speed turning in, no extra 200M.
Never far off the pace, without cover and no close than 3-wide throughout, not picked up 350M, faded 200M. (No Vet Findings.)
Caught wide, dropped back to the rear nearing home turn, still last 400M, not picked up to challenge.
Raced 3-wide in midfield, proved very difficult to settle 1000M-800M, forced very wide 600M, found nothing top of straight, soon dropped out of contention.
In midfield early stages, shuffled to near the rear passing 1000M, no closer than 3-wide throughout, soon beaten 350M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Strode forward from wide barrier , shared lead on outside from 900M, weakened passing 400M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began fairly, picked up speed to sit between horses 3-back from leader. Turned wide, pressed forward to hit front 100m, pulled clear.
Bumped, recovered, pressed forward inside leader before settling 1L behind. Urged forward top of straight, hit front 350m, run down 100m.
Urged forward from inside draw, settling in one-off position 2L from leader. Rolled forward top of straight to look chance but no extra final 100m.
Hard ridden but wide to lead on settling then set slow pace. Kept on strongly when passed 350m but flattened final strides.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear but away from fence. Taken wide turning for home and ran on steadily.
Shifted across behind horses from widest draw, dropping to last. Switched widest in straight and ran on steadily. Rider dropped whip 100m.
Began fairly, not pushed, racing three-wide before settling one-off, 4-back. Not much room early in straight, switched in, kept on fairly.
Began well, pressed forward, checked 1400m, then difficult to settling, racing wide 3L from leader. Kept on fairly to 200m, then one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw but threw head about and hard to settle, dropping to rear. One-paced in straight.
Ridden early to hold forward position, racing wide without cover 1L from leader. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Bumped start, urged forward but kept 3-wide with cover in midfield. Wide around turn, found little in straight when asked.
Made use of inside draw to grab box seat and stay with leading pack to 200m before tiring.
Slow into stride, picked up momentum and rolled ahead to midfield before turn. Gave ground soon after straightening.

Began OK, and taken across to be midfield, 3 wide. Well positioned on the turn to sprint home after the lack of early speed. Took on the leader at the 200m, but had to fight right to the line, winning a bob late.
Pushed forward early to lead and set a slow tempo in front, and make the others chase him late. Taken on from the 200m, but fought back and ran to the line, just losing late in a bob.
Broke well and handily placed early, just behind the winner on the rail. Ran to the line well, just fading slightly late but holding 3rd.
Began well, and taken across from the wide-ish draw to be just worse than midfield, 3 wide. Strong run to the line, and wearing down 3rd late, but just missing.
Briefly crowded on jumping, but pressed forward to be midfield, on the fence. Kept close to the rail in the run home and stayed on well late, but never threatening the first four.
Crowded on jumping, and dropping back to be at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Last turning for home, ran on OK late but had too much to do.
Began OK and taken to a midfield position, 1 off the fence. Raced tight leaving the back straight, and into the home turn. Plugged away fairly to the line late.
Had to push forward from the wide barrier to be just behind the leader, 2-3 wide with no cover. Well positioned on the turn, but never finished off the race and dropped out late.

Crowded on jumping, dropping back from the wide draw to be near the rear of the field, 2-3 wide. Raced tight leaving the back straight, and into the turn home, coming off heels 550m. Plugged steadily to the line.
Only fairly away, but got to the rail to sit worse than midfield. Held the rail in the run home, and raced in restricted room mid-straight. Only plugged away when clear.
Dropped back from the jump to be a clear last, 8L off the leaders. Came wide on the turn and widest in the straight. OK late, but was left with too much to do.
OK away, and taken forward to be handily place in 4th, 1 off the fence. Gave nothing when asked at the top of the straight and dropped back, just missing last place on the line.
Began OK, finding a position forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Started to drop out before the turn, and ran flat when asked for an effort in the straight.

Settled towards the rear on rails after beginning from a wide gate, commenced move on straightening, ran on under pressure to hit the front about 100 metres out.
Settled mainly in midfield on rails, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on steadily to hit the front momentarily 100 metres out, soon outsprinted.
Slowly away, well behind before making swift progress far side to be prominent and wide in 3rd or 4th rounding home bend, held some chance 100 metres out, soon swamped.
Niggled along in 5th within 3L of pace most of way, tightened 200 metres out, one-paced closing stages.
Led from the one draw setting a good pace, unable to sustain effort and headed inside final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield in 6th on rails, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Never better than midfield, lost position into straight, kept on at the finish.
Began moderately, soon dropped well back, trailed the field into straight, only ran past well-beaten horses.
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate, ran home one-paced.
Chased leader to straight, weakened under pressure.
Travelled just off the pace on rails, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Worked his way across from the widest gate to settle wide in 2L 4th, dropped out of contention from the 600 metres.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the fence, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, led 350M, overhauled 200M, ran on for 3rd.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide just off the leaders, only held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 400M.
Eased back, took rail, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo, held up 50M.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok, on heels 50M.
Took rail and led easily at slow sectionals, soon dropped off 350M.
Midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on strongly to score by 3/4L when clear 200M.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, dashed well for 2nd.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, kept on well until final 100M headed, hung on for 3rd.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 4th.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, travelled nicely behind the leader, ran on steadily until final 50M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on steadily to the line.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, made no impression in straight.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward to settle in a prominent position, however trapped wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Sent forward to cross to the fence and led by 1/2L, soon weakened badly after straightening.
Began well, restrained, shifted across behind runners, settling one-off at rear. Under pressure 400m, weaved between horses, got clear 120m, bolted home to win on line.
First out, racing wide till crossing to fence 1300m. Kicked clear top of straight, kept finding to hold off challengers, caught in final strides.
Quickly away, grabbing box seat and trailing leader to straight. Got clear run when leader shifted out 300m, kept on gamely.
Pressed forward with leading pack, settling one-back, one-off. Shaken up top of straight and kept on gamely.
Ridden along early, settling 4L from leader. Urged forward top of straight, making ground steadily to be closest at finish.
Not pushed, moving smoothly two-back, one-off. Shaken up top of straight and picked up gradually, doing best work final 100m.
Stood flat-footed at start and lost considerable ground. Tagged on to field 750m, took inside run in straight and finished off nicely.
Outpaced, dropping to rear along rail. Still well back on straightening, switched out and ran on fairly.
Allowed to stride at own pace, settling towards rear in one-off position. Under pressure 500m but failed to respond, one-paced.
Began OK, ridden along holding rail 3-back from leader. Inconvenienced 1200m, stayed inside in straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along but wide early, settling in one-off position behind midfield. Switched out wide in straight but found nothing.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader initially before taking the sit 1.5L behind. Kept on well early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Quickly away, pressed forward but wide, then sat outside leader passing 850m. Rolled forward on straightening, took over 200m, scooted home.
Began well but allowed to settle two-back, one-off. Bumped 600m, shaken up turning for home, clear run 250m, finished off nicely.
Quickly out, racing with pacemakers to turn before easing one-off, one-back. Swung wide into straight and battled on gamely.
One of the first out, racing inside early leader before slipping into box seat. Shaken up top of straight and battled on well to just miss a place.
Pressed forward to lead on settling before crossing to fence back stretch. Shaken up top of straight, caught 200m, kept on gamely till swamped final 50m.
Began awkwardly, vigorously ridden but didn't muster, dropping towards rear close to fence. Switched out in straight and ran on fairly.
Pressed forward from outside draw, settling 2L behind leader but wide without cover. Kept wide around turn, one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Ridden along to find cover but kept wide and shuffled back before moving up 4-wide back stretch. Wide into straight and one-paced.
Restrained and taken closer to fence from a wide draw at rear. Not pushed till straightening when switched widest. One-paced.
Fast out but unable maintain pace dropping to midfield along fence. Unbalanced 800m, steadied 600, bumped turn, faded in straight.
Outpaced and soon at rear. Last into turn and never competitive.
Urged forward from a wide barrier, 1-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, unleashed strong finishing effort from 200M to score.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, sat 2-1/4L behind the leader, kept pushing and beaten only by a nose.
Sat in worse than midfield along the rail 4-3/4L off the pace, shifted out to centre of the Straight at 150M, closed off nicely from thereon.
Urged forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, gave little when asked in the Straight and headed passing 100M.
Travelled in midfield along the rail from an inner draw, sat 4-1/2L behind, swung wide after the Home Turn, and ran on steadily for 5th.
At the rear and travelled 8-1/2L behind the leader, made some ground in the Straight.
Sat just outside leader, 1/2L behind 2 wide without cover, did not run on in the Straight.
Sat in midfield along the rail, 3-1/2L behind the leader, no response when asked, never looked likely.
In midfield 3-1/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, finished off only one paced.
Always towards the rear, did not look likely.
At the rear throughout, was not competitive.
Travelled towards the rear, mostly wide and without cover, not a factor.
First out, led to 1300m before easing into box seat. Got inside run on straightening, hit front 200m, held off late challenges.
Got off OK, taken in, settling one-off, three-back. Checked off heels 800m. Switched widest entering straight and finished strongly down centre field.
Began well, ridden at own pace two-back, one-off. Switched out entering straight and finished off strongly.
Began well, ridden along two-back from leader along rail. Closed in turning form home, blocked for run 300m, kept on well when clear 150m.
Began OK, not pushed and held wide towards rear. Not happy with pace, took off 730m, circled field to lead 630m. Collared 200m, boxed on.
Pressed forward and wide before taking one-off position, one back. Closed in 350m, no clear run from 200m to 100m, kept on well. Suffered overreach injury left hind heel.
Ridden to stay with pace, urged forward to lead 1300m then dropped anchor. Overtaken 630m, kept on well till flattened 200m.
Steadied soon after start and taken across behind horses at rear but still wide. Taken wider passing 800m, one-paced in straight.
Began well from inside draw and pushed forward to hold rail 3-back from leader. Steadied 1200m, lost position turn, one-paced in straight.
Steadied shortly after start and taken across behind runners to rail at rear. In last pair to straight before passing tired horse.
Stood in gate and lost many lengths, trailing field to straight before passing beaten horse.
Bounced well, racing behind early pace before moving forward from 1250m to sit outside leader. Kept on fairly to 200m before fading.
Began well from gate 1, raced 6 lengths or so back on rail, angled out on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Fast into stride, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on very well in straight, took the lead near final 50M, but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail in 8th, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight to get 3rd.
Jumped well from gate 10, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, headed near final 100M, stayed on for 4th.
Began nicely, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in early, raced 3 wide in 4th, found cover on turn, finished off one-paced.
Slow to begin, raced 8 lengths back on rail at tail, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, steadied near 600M, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently in 3rd, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after 200M.
Began awkwardly, raced 8 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Slowly away, recovered to race 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight when hard run took effect. (Substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea)

Jumped fairly settling in midfield, quickly obtained a clear run passing the 400 metres, ran on to claim victory inside final 50 metres.
Raced wide with no cover at rear, widest runner entering straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to snatch 2nd late.
Ridden along from a wide gate to hold a prominent position, remained similar early in straight but failed to quicken to threaten.
Soon took up running setting a steady pace and attempting to make all, swamped under pressure closing stages.
Taken back for rails run from the widest gate settling in last few, switched off rails for a run upon straightening, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Slightly sluggish at start, raced mainly in worse than midfield, made steady headway at the finish.
Jumped moderately settling well behind, baulked for a run early in straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, close up early before losing position and shifted wide into straight, improved to hold every chance passing the 200 metres, only to be swamped final stages.
Broke well settling just off the lead on rails, did not find much room the length of straight.
Gradually drifted back to rear of field, wide entering straight, tight between runners early on, finished off race well.
Ridden to gradually gain close-up 3rd far side, forced to steady off heels and lost position inside the 800 metres, dropped out tamely in straight.
Midfield briefly, awkwardly placed on heels and raced fiercely around home bend dropping to last few into straight, made no further impression.
Began well, settled in midfield on rails, failed to make any impression on rails in straight.
Driven early from a wide gate racing wide without cover in a prominent position to home straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Settled in front, 2 wide just off the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed to stay close to midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Took rail easily, led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M flattened.
Slow away, at back 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, on heels 400M, made some ground 200M.
Pressed forward, secured box seat, not suited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, flattened 200M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide no cover, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden to sit in midfield, 2 wide, flattened 250M.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, never nearer.
Slow away, hard ridden to hold the rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Slow away, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, accelerated strongly to score by 1/2L.
Raced midfield, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, closed off well for 2nd.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast pace, ran on nicely to get 3rd.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 9.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, dashed well for 4th.
Hard ridden forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, kept on steadily to the line without extra acceleration.
Sent forward to take the fence and led at fast pace, kept on steadily until final 250M headed.
Raced midfield, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, peeled wide turning in, made plenty of ground in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader with cover, harmed by the fast sectionals, one paced until final 150M weakened.
Taken back to rear, settled 11Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast tempo, made minor ground in straight without any threatening.

Settled worse than midfield about 10Ls behind the leader, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, never ran on and eased down 200M. (Questioned rider and trainer for disappointing performance)
Raced midfield, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced home.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, soon weakened after straightening. ( Rider concerned the action of the horse)
Always at back, despite the fast run, never ran on.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Set steady pace to straight, kicked clear 300m, won easily.
Took a few steps to get going, then forged ahead to sit 1L behind leader in one-off position. Pressed forward on straightening but unable overhaul winner.
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered and pushed through between horses settling 4L from leader. Turned a little wide, kept on gamely in straight.
First out, not pushed, settling in box seat 3L from leader. Put under pressure turning for home and kept on fairly in straight.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Switched out 300m, held for run 200m, ran on nicely when clear.
Steadied shortly after start, dropping to rear. Improved slightly back stretch but switched out and lost position turn. Kept on fairly in straight.
Unable maintain pace, dropping behind midfield between horses. Shaken up on straightening and kept on fairly.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after start, settling close to rails at rear. Took closer order turn, ran on fairly on straight.
Shifted across behind runners but kept away from fence at the rear. Taken a bit wide on straightening but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after start but kept wide close to the rear. Switched very wide in straight but only one-paced
Pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off. Kept on fairly early in straight until flattened 200m and faded.
Began awkwardly, bumped, but pushed forward to settle two-back from leader along fence. Under pressure from 300m but found little.
Began OK, slow to muster, picked up speed passing 1050m, moving forward to sit outside leader 800m. Wide around turn and faded quickly in straight.
Got off OK, pressed forward but wide 4L from leader before shifting in for cover. Found little in straight under hard riding and faded.
Jumped OK, niggled at to hold box seat to and around turn. Blocked for run 350m, got split 300m, hit front 250m and pulled clear.
Pressed forward, racing three-wide 3L from leader before getting cover around turn. Kept on strongly in straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well, striding forward to settle behind leading pair but away from rail. Kept on well in straight.
Got off OK but not enough speed and held between horses in midfield. Bumped and lost position 700m. Wide in straight, picked up momentum, doing best work final 200m.
Restrained soon after start and shifted across behind horses, settling one-off, three back. Switched out in straight and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, got close to heels 900m, bumped and unbalanced 700m when seeking cover. Kept on fairly in straight.
Taken in soon after start but held wide and dropped to rear in one-off position. Cut in to rail around turn but switched out in straight. Ran on one-paced.
First out, led to 800m when pressured by another. Kicked clear 350m but run down 250m and faded gradually.
Pressed forward to sit behind leader initially, then rolled forward to sit outside leader from 800m. Kept on well to 200m when ran out of stamina and faded.
Outpaced and soon at rear trailing field. Switched out turning for home to make run but only one-paced in straight. Rider dropped whip 300m.
Taken in soon after start but held wide. Eased back and taken to rail approaching 800m. Blocked for run 300m, held in restricted room, then close to heels 100m. Boxed on.
Bounded in the air at start and lost ground, taken to rail and pressed forward to midfield. Hard ridden to 200m when spent force. Confirmed to be a "roarer."
Pressed forward but unable handle pace, dropping to rear but wide. Kept on fairly early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Jumped OK but outpaced and soon at rear, dropping to clear last around turn. Finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
From a wide barrier, urged forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L at slow sectionals, remained in the lead throughout and held off late challenge to score.
Settled just behind midfield 5L off 4 wide and without cover, niggled forward rounding turn, despite the slow tempo, kept challenging and finished off strongly for 2nd.
Sat in front of midfield 2L behind 2 wide with cover, benefitted by the slow tempo, closed off well for 3rd.
Eased back to travel towards the rear, 5-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, finished off nicely despite not suited to the slow pace and unable to obtain clear running early in the Straight.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind the leader 3 wide and without cover, improved slightly rounding turn, ran on ok in the Straight.
Pushed forward to sit just outside the leader, 1/2L off 2 wide without cover, benefitted by the slow tempo, however found no extra in the Straight and finished off only one paced.
At the rear, 6-1/4L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, made ground steadily in the Straight.
Rolled into midfield, sat 3L off the leader along the rail, finished off only one paced.
Sat in midfield 3-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home only.
Pushed forward and sat 1-3/4L behind the leader on the rail, despite suited to the slow pace, weakened passing 200M.
At the rear, 7L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, made slight ground in the Straight.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/2L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, found no extra passing 250M, not competitive throughout.
Settled in just behind midfield along the rail, 4-1/2L behind, raced on the inner track down the Straight, held up and unable to obtain clear running near 200M.
Always at the rear, not a factor.
Began well but unable handle early pace and allowed to slip back to midfield in one-off position. Wide into straight, picked up momentum gradually to hit front just before the line.
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling two-back one-off. Urged forward top of straight, hit front 150m, run down final 50m.
Crowded out start, shifted across to find cover, settling at rear. Wide in straight and finished off strongly from 300m with run ending just before the post.
Steadied and taken in soon after start, getting to rail four-back from leader. Kept on steadily in straight behind horses, got close to heels 50m, not fully tested.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear. Steadied 400m when blocked for run, switched out and ran on strongly to be closest at finish.
Jumped well, pressed forward to lead, then travelled keenly to 500m when joined by another. Kept on strongly to 150m when swamped.
Quickly into stride, striding forward to sit 0.5L behind leader before moving up to share lead 500m. Kept on strongly to 150m when swamped.
Steadied soon after start, shifted across behind runners, and last on settling. Switched out in straight and ran on fairly.
Restrained and taken in, settling towards rear in one-off position. Took inside run in straight and ran on fairly.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance 200m before flattened.
Began OK, not much speed, settling four-back from leader along rail. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Rolled forward, gradually cutting in to settle two-back along rail. Under pressure from 350m but only one-paced. Substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Pressed forward to grab box seat on settling and tailed leader to 200m before tiring and fading.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 to 4 lengths back at rear, gradually improved on turn, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to score in good fashion.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced outside the leader in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 5th, similar position on turn, no daylight until near 300M, then bumped 200M, finished off strongly thereafter, just missed 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 11, sent forward to race a length or so back in 4th, 3 wide with no cover on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Jumped well, raced 2 lengths or so back in midfield, 3 wide with cover on turn, bumped near 300M, then hampered 200M, ran on moderately thereafter. (Lost left front plate on jumping.)
Slowly away, raced 6 lengths back at tail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight and made minor progress without threatening.
Began fairly and steadied shortly after the start, raced 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, similar position on turn, lost all chance when severely affected by a broken horse near 300M,
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6 lengths back at tail, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back behind midfield, 3 wide with cover turning in, emptied early in straight.
Crowded out start, raced at rear throughout, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Placing: PU
Comment: Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, broke down near 300M.
Began well but not pushed staying behind early pace. Had difficulty finding clear run 300m, got split 200m, powered home to win on the line.
Jumped well, rolled forward, settling inside hindquarters of leader. Moved up to join leader 300m, pulled ahead 200m, looked winner till caught on the line.
Quickly into stride, hugging outside fence 3L from leader. Urged forward 400m, bumped and unbalanced when trying to improve 300m. Badly held up till 150m, finished well when clear.
Bounced well, travelled down centre track before edging towards outer fence passing 600m, 2L from leader. Put under pressure from 400m and kept on well.
First out, then raced with leading pack before settling along outer fence 2L from leader. Moved up 300m but one-paced closing stages.
Unable handle early speed, settling behind midfield but close to outer fence. Moved forward move passing 400m but one-paced closing stages.
Bounded in the air at start, knocked over, lost ground, settling at rear. Moved up approaching 400m, kept on fairly.
Began OK, racing down centre field behind early pace before edging closer to leading bunch 200m. One-paced final stages.
Outpaced, taken closer to outer fence while settling at rear. Ran past tired horses closing stages but never competitive.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting good pace to 300m when joined up front, bumped and unbalanced. Faded quickly.
Urged forward on jumping, racing between horses 3L from leader on settling. Hard ridden to hold place while laying in. Spent force final 200m.
Outpaced, dropping to rear, before switching out approaching 500m. Switched in again 200m but never a threat.
Crowded for room on jumping, dropping to last and edging towards outer fence. Never competitive.
Crowded out start, dropping towards rear. Clear last passing 800m then dropped back further. Unacceptable performance.

Began well and taken forward to be handily placed in 4th, 1 off the fence. Well positioned on the turn, coming wider for a run. Pulled away from the 300m and not challenged late, easing near the line.

OK away, sitting towards the rear of the field early before moving closer to midfield in the middle stages. Tight at the top of the straight. Wound up from the 300m, and ran home strongly making the only inroads on the winner late.

Slightly awkward away, finding a position worse than midfield, 2-3 wide. Pushed to share the lead 1400m when no pace on, but not allowed to cross to the rail. Stayed on OK, but couldn't kick with 1st & 2nd late.
Began OK and pushed forward early to be handily place behind the leader, on the rail. Only got clear in the last 200m, running on OK, before fading over the last 50m.
Began well and pushed forward to be just behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Pushed all the way in the straight, but only plugged away and never threatening a place.

Fairly away, but pushed forward early to be early leader. Set very slow pace early, tending to get the head up when restrained. Led on the turn, but had nothing left and faded late. Subsequently found to be lame.
OK away, easing forward early to be placed midfield, on the rails. Ran on OK to the line under hands and heels.
Dawdled out early, finding a position behind midfield, on the fence. Only went to the line 1 paced in the straight.
Crowded early and taken back to sit at the rear of the field, 2-3 wide. Went to go on the turn, but didn't have a lot in reserve, and only went to the line fairly.

Began OK from the wide draw, but had to settle towards the rear of the field, stuck 4-5 wide. Pushed forward in the back straight to find cover in a midfield positions, still 3 wide. Race run by the turn, and dropped out late.
Began OK, and crossed to the rail early at the rear of the field. Came widest on the turn, but only ran on fairly in the straight, easing late.

OK away, and taken forward from the wide draw to be better than midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Well placed on the turn, but gave nothing in the straight. Dropped back quickly from the 350m, and not persevered with late.
Began awkwardly, finding a position midfield, 1 off the fence. Became unsettled through early/mid stages after being crossed at 1700m. Had nothing left by the turn, and dropped out in the straight.
Jumped with them, raced a length or so back in 4th, easy run on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score easily.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, still 3 wide on turn, finished off well in straight to get 2nd, but never a threat to the winner.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight and made reasonable headway to get 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 to 5 lengths back in 9th, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from a wide draw, send forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, peaked shortly after turning in, headed 300M, just stayed on for 5th.
Slow to begin, raced at rear on rail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight, never a threat. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out from gate 9, raced 7 lengths back at tail, awkwardly placed near 1100M, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, showed early speed to take rail and race prominently, shared lead turning in, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths back behind midfield, same margin back turning, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 6-7 lengths back at rear, there to turn, angled our near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7-8 lengths back at tail, carried wide turning in, emptied early in straight, finished last.
